Abraão wuhenetlu Isaque, Isaque wuhenetlu Jacó, Jacó wuhenetlu Judá hiyrunu Judá molene.
Judá wuhenetlu Perez hiyrunu Zerá, wanna hinrokni Tamar tshinkaluro; waneya Perez wuhenetlu Esrom; Esrom wuhenetlu Arão;
Arão wuhenetlu Aminadabe; Aminadabe wuhenetlu Naassom; Naassom wuhenetlu Salmom;
Salmom wuhenetlu Boaz, Boaz hinrokni honra Raabe tshinkaluro; waneya Boaz wuhenetlu Obede. Obede hinrokni honra Rute tshinkaluro. Waneya Obede wuhenetlu Jessé;
Jessé wuhenetlu pohirtshi Davi (Israel pohire); Davi wuhenetlu Salomão pohirtshi. Salomão hinrokni Urias tshinkaluru hnunro.
Waneya Salomão wuhenetlu Roboão; Roboão wuhenetlu Abias; Abias wuhenetlu Asa.
Asa wuhenetlu Josafá; Josafá wuhenetlu Jorão; Jorão wuhenetlu Uzias;
Uzias wuhenetlu Jotão; Jotão wuhenetlu Acaz; Acaz wuhenetlu Ezequias;
Ezequias wuhenetlu Manassés; Manassés wuhenetlu Amom; Amom wuhenetlu Josias;
Josias wuhenetlu Jeconias hiyrun-koxa himolene judeu-nerune Babilônia tshijne ranikkoklunna papko.
Judeu-nerune Babilônia tshijne ranikkoklunna papko wkatanu Jeconias wuhenetlu Salatiel; Salatiel wuhenetlu Zorobabel;
Zorobabel wuhenetlu Abiúde; Abiúde wuhenetlu Eliaquim; Eliaquim wuhenetlu Azor;
Azor wuhenetlu Sadoque; Sadoque wuhenetlu Aquim; Aquim wuhenetlu Eliúde;
Eliúde wuhenetlu Eleazar; Eleazar wuhenetlu Matã; Matã wuhenetlu Jacó.
Waneya Jacó wuhenetlu José, José honra Maria tshinkaluro hnuru, walakni matkaklu Jesus, walekatkani Cristo tshinkaluru.
Hiyáhoni raptowrurna quatorze klopichane Abraão-klukananuko haté Davi-klu papko hiyrunu quatorze klopichanekotnaka Davi-klu papko haté judeu-nerune Babilônia tshijne ranikkoklunna papko hiyrunu quatorze klopichanekotnaka judeu-nerune Babilônia tshijne ranikkoklunna papko haté Cristo hapojinixka.
Jesus Matuxyawaka PiranapniWaneya wan-rixa matreta Jesus Cristo. Runro, Maria tshinkaluro, José tshinkaluru hnunro tixinripa, seyni hi rapokmanetawalo tmichiwatatka Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru pixkonuyma.
Seyni thanurupa José kihle hchinikanu rixle tshinanu, hi raluka patewkakletlo yine meyijyawakanuplo, hiyáhoni raluk-hiknoklechamtlo, hike mimaxyawakanuplu.
Seyni wane ruchinikanretakanatawa satu hiwejikaluru Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru hakanhayehitlu José rupnawleya. Waneya wane htshinru: — José, Davi whene, hi pkojwakahchinikanutanu Maria pipji panijyawakapa, phanunro tixyawakapa. Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru tshinanu tmichiwata.
Tmatuwhenetanu jejipni. Putakhiwakatanru Jesus, klu tshinanu riwekkakanna rayinetene hkonahektunutanunpatka.
Xye ptowruka wan-hixa, hpoyahokajyawakaplu ptowruka htshinyawaka Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu, Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshriya Isaías-ni tshinkalurni, wla htshina:
“Suxo, jeji mapokmanetanutowa michiwatanu, twuhenetanru jeji, hhiwakatko Emanuel.” (Emanuel raluka tshinreta “Hoyakalu hixaymalu”.)
Waneya ruyojinixka José, hkamhalu htshinyawaklu hiwejikaluru Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru. Ranikatkalo Maria hipji wale hnunro tixyawakapa.
Seyni tma matuwhenetkanu pchinika Maria hi rapokmanetlo José. Tmatkakatkalu mitshikananu toturu waneya rutakhiwakatlu Jesus.
Jimatkalerune Hapojyawaka Jesus Rexyawakapa PiranapniHmatuxinixka Jesus Belém poktshiya, Judeia tshijne poktshiko, phuru Herodes-klu papko, jejine jimatkalerune tkatshi hichpajyawaka sreta hichpajikatshine Jerusalém poktshi rapokna.
Waneya repomhana: — Hanurhe judeu pohirnepa matutatshri? Wetlo hkatahirite tkatshi hichpajyawaka sreta hakanikatshro. Wkata wuna wimalwuxyawakaplu.
Seyni Herodes jeminixkalu xye pirana hkojwakahchinikanuta hiyrunu ptowruneka Jerusalém hajene kojwakahchinikanuta Herodes-yma.
Waneya repujinixkana rapatjexyawakna ptowruneka tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hiyrunu hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine, Herodes hepomhana hanhe hmatuxini Cristo.
Waneya ruhitna, wla htshinruna: — Belém poktshiya, Judeia tshijne poktshiko. Klu tshinanu wane htshina yonawahleta Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri:
Waneya Herodes hepukna jejine jimatkalerune yohimawakaya waneya rimatatka Herodes wanna tshinanu klu papko potuko rakanhatka katahiri.
Waneya hyokanatatkana Belém poktshiya hyiywakapna waneya wane htshina: — Hyanu, hijhapanru mturu hihleko. Hikchijinru mturu hinkakhapkatanno, hit-koxa himukata wane yaleta nimalwuxyawakaplu.
Rali jemlexinixkaluna phuru, hyatkana. Waneya katahiri honra retakanatanruna tkatshi hichpajyawaka sreta hwatshro kosekatkana haté tutukatka mturu hohwaka.
Rexinixkaluna katahiri, hpoyikowpotutna.
Rapojinixkaluna pantshi, retluna mturu runro Maria-yma. Waneya hyinuwaka hipyoklemtna tshiji, hyoptsojityehitluna, rimalwutluna mturu. Waneya hkotpukluna hkapajirna kwenur-potuko hwiywaka waneya renekluna henekachalkaka ouro, phamluhalo incenso tshinkaluro, phamluhalojpa mirra tshinkaluru.
Waneya runkakkatkana jejine jimatkalerune rupnawleyna hma satkapyawakanupna phuru Herodes nwaka waneya hsatkapatkaluna htshijnena, pnu hapoko hyapatkana.
Egito Tshijne Rasujyawakna PiranapniHyinixkana jejine jimatkalerune waneya satu hiwejikaluru Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru hakanhayehitlu José rupnawleya. Wane htshinru: — Hajewa, ppalnanu. Panikanru mturu, runro koxa, pasukanu Egito tshijne hyanu. Wane hitukanu haté nunkajinipyi klu tshinanu Herodes hijhapanru mturu ruylaxyawakaplu.
Hiyáhoni hoyetshno José palnatka ranikatkana mturu, runroymakananu waneya hyatka Egito tshijne nwaka.
Waneya wan-rutukatka haté rupnanatka Herodes. Hiyáhoni rakanhatka hpoyahokajyawakapa Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri, wan-tshinatshri: “Egito tshijne ntomhiyatkalu noturu.”
Herodes Tshinkaluru Hiylaxyawakna Mturune PiranapniWaneya rexinixkalu Herodes hyokwijetatkaluna jejine jimatkalerune, hjihekanuwpotutatka Herodes. Waneya ruylajixanna mturunni jejinni ptowrunnika, hepi mhaleruni ruylajixa haté hepi mhale kayaholunniko ruylajixa. Belém poktshi hajenni hiyrun-koxa wanestsi hajene ruylajixa. Xye hkamhatka Herodes katahiri hakanhapiranyehixini klu papko jimatkalerune hinkajyatkalu pirana tshinanu.
Hiyáhoni rakanhatka hpoyahokajyawakapa Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri, Jeremias tshinkalurni, wan-tshinatshri:
“Ramá poktshi hjemiko tsru hima, tsru tshiyahlu jemiko, tsru wamonutshi. Raquel tshiyahamtanu twuhenene pohwaka tshinanu. Hike himukata hitshrokkakletanro klu tshinanu hnikawnanatkana twuhenenni.”
Egito Tshijne Hsatkapyawakna PiranapniWaneya rupninixka Herodes waneya hiwejikaluru Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru hakanhayehitlu José rupnawleya, José Egito tshijne rawakanaxini.
Waneya wane htshina: — Ppalnanu, panikanru mturu, runroyma, Israel tshijne hyanu klu tshinanu wanna mturu hiylapiratatshine hipnanatka.
Hiyáhoni José palnatka ranikatkana mturu, runroymakananuko. Israel tshijne hyatka.
Seyni hjeminixkalu Arquelau tshinkaluru rurni Herodes-ni kachrijru hjihloka, Judeia pohire rixyawakapa pirana, José pika wane yaletatka. José hiykotka rupnawleya tshinanu Galileia-stsi hwatshri poktshi hyatka.
Waneya hyatka Nazaré poktshi tshinikowaka waneko rawyawakpatka. Hiyáhoni rakanhatka htshinyawaka potuko Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine: “Nazaré hajeru htshinikowakapa.”
João Batista Hinkaklewaxyawaka PiranapniWaneklu papko João Batista hapoka, runkaklewakanata kahnete poktshiya, Judeia tshijneya.
Wane htshinamta: — Hehchinikanutanu hektunu tshinanu klu tshinanu hi howukatkalu tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka!
Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri, Isaías tshinkalurni yonatlu João pirana, wla htshina: “Kahnete poktshiri saplewaxikatshri tokanu: Halpokotanru Tsru Hixikatshriwa hatnu hapote. Hpotukatanru hatnu hapotkaka. Wale tshinanu hpotukatanru hatnu hapkaka.”
João mkalu camelo pixi kamhikolni, kpixnuru h-cinturão-te couro-mta kamhikolu. Hnijitu tsetseru, wrolha hocha hajeru.
Jerusalém hajene, Judeia tshijne hajene, hiyrun-koxa ptowruneka Jordão wennestsi hwatshinetka yanwakatlu, hyijnak-tokanuxyawakluna João Batista.
Waneya ruphujetluna rektunna. Waneya João batiza-tna yine Jordão wenneya.
Rexinixka João híxona fariseu-ne, saduceu-ne koxa hinanwakamtlu batiza-xikowak-yehi, waneya wane htshina: — Hixa himnu pixka hixatshinhi, katshinolunhi! Kathe hinkakhi hiwejyawaka Hoyakalu hapnokatle hinatshripa?
Hkamhanru xako kihleru himaxikowakapa hehchinikanutatka.
Seyni hi hkahwakanu hixa himukata hihlerexnawa wane htshinamxyawaka: Abraão-kni wutsrukate; klu tshinanu nunkakhi Hoyakalu himukata haté xyekaka sotlu kamhalexyalu Abraão klopichane.
Heptshi honra halpokotka hahmunkaka hkastajikowakapa haté hitskihi. Klu tshinanu ptowru hahmuna hektu sahiwleru, kayikako, tshitshmero ruknokko.
João Hiphujetlu Cristo PiranapniHita batiza-jethi honhaya himaxikowaka hixa hehchinikanutatka, seyni wale, hapkatatatshri batiza-tanhi Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluruya, tshitshmeroya koxa. Wale hinatshripa hita pnute himukatatshrini. Hikenno hita h-sandalha-te nanijyawaka.
Ruplokapre ralpokota ruplojyawaklu hitataji hkotspalaxyawakapa hipata. Hitataji himrexikowaka hruko rimretakjixinri seyni hipatapni yoxikkona tshitshmeroya hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa.
Seyni João wan-tshinru: — Hita haluklu n-batiza-xikowaka pixaya seyni pixlahe hinanwakatno n-batiza-xyawakapyi pixa?
Waneya Jesus hihita. Wane htshinru: — Petachatanutshi pchini hohnejiji, hpoyaho hakanhalexyawaka ptowruka Hoyakalu halukanru. Waneya João koxa hikchikhihlenutlu wan-rixyawaka.
Waneya hajeyri h-batiza-tkawa Jesus, honha ruchpajyatka waneklukawa tenhohne kotpukka. Waneya Jesus hetlu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru motkokoji pixka rixmanemta, rujrukamta, wale hohwaka rapoka.
Waneya satu tokantshi tenhohne hichpajya, wan-tshinatshri: — Xyekni Noturu namotleru. Wale poyikowkakno.
Jesus Yohnixikolu PiranapniWaneyakni Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru haniklu Jesus kahnete poktshiri tsru kamtshi Satanás yahotalexyawakaplu Jesus.
Waneya riknohinixka quarenta hohne, quarenta yetshno hi hnikawa Jesus, hnatshita.
Waneya tsru kamtshi Satanás Jesus-stsi hapoka wane htshinru: — Hoyakalu whene pixinipakni, ptowutanru xye sotlukaka pão rixinwa.
Seyni Jesus hihitlu: — Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu tokanu potukalu yonatkaluru wan-tshina: “Yine hi pão mixkonu tsonu hiwejya seyni wale ptowruka htshintokanuxyawaka Hoyakalu riwejya yineru.”
Waneya wane pnutetka tsru kamtshi Satanás haniklu Jesus haté Jerusalém poktshi, Hoyakalu nurreru poktshi waneya Jesus Hoyakalupji tenonwaka rutaklu tsru kamtshi Satanás.
Waneya tsru kamtshi Satanás wan-tshina: — Hoyakalu whene pixinipakni hewi puknojinwa teno wakaya klu tshinanu Hoyakalu tokanu potukalu yonatkaluru wan-tshina: “Hoyakalu towutanna htowrene hiwejikalune tenhohne hajene hinoxyawakapyi. Himyoymana ruchatkapanyina, pma mutshlixyawakanupa sotlu pijixiya.”
Seyni Jesus wan-tshinru: — Seyni Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru koxa wan-tshina: “Hi pyahtaletanru Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu Poyakalute.”
Waneya tsru kamtshi Satanás haniklu Jesus satu mriji tenolu hyiywakapa, rekhitlu Jesus ptowru tshijnekaka pohirewaxyawaka hiyrun-koxa ruhlenkaka.
Waneya tsru kamtshi Satanás wan-tshina: — Xyekaka ptowruko nenekanyi pyoptsojityehixinipno, pimalwuxinipno.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru: — Pyanutka Satanás! Wane htshina hinkakleta Hoyakalu tokanu potukalu yonatkaluru: “Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu Poyakalute tsonu pimalwutanu hiyrun-koxa wale tsonu pomkahitanu.”
Hiyáhoni tsru kamtshi Satanás hichomtlu Jesus waneya hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrerune tenhohne hajene hapokyehitlu Jesus. Rinotatkaluna Jesus.
Jesus Yinuwaka Kamrurewlexyawaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus jempiranyehixinri preso-tkalu João, Galileia tshijne hsatkapa.
Waneya Nazaré poktshi ruchpajinixka Jesus, Cafarnaum poktshi hya waneya wane rawatka. Cafarnaum poktshi hipowhastsi rawa, Zebulom hiyrunu Naftali tshijnestsi rawa.
Hpoyahokajyawakapa Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri Isaías-ni tokanu htshinyawaka mitshi wla tshinatshri:
“Zebulom hiyrun-koxa Naftali tshinikowaka tshijne hajene, Jordão wenne mar powha nwaka sreta hajenhi, judeu mixkane Galileia tshinikowaka tshijne hajenhi,
mapchahawaka hwatshine tsru katalu hetatshinhi; mapchahawaka hwatshine hipuktshi yehi pixkalutu hwatshinhi Hoyakalu hiwekkakle nikotyehitatkahi hohi himrekle pixka.”
Waneya wane pnute Jesus yinuwaka hinkaklewleta, wla htshinamta: — Hehchinikanutanu hektunu tshinanu klu tshinanu hi howukatkalu tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka!
Jesus Nuretna Satkaka Rikamrurewatjenepa PiranapniWaneya Galileia powha wnaha hyapamxini Jesus, retlu Simão tshinkaluru repuruyma André. Ruknokamtatkaluna h-tarrafa-tna hipowhaya klu tshinanu wanna mariskatatshine kchimahaklerune.
Waneya wane htshinna Jesus: — Hinanu hwahatjinitanno, yine kmariskahohoklerune nixkakanhi.
Waneya waneklukawa potuko ruknokamtatkaluna h-tarrafa-tna, romkahitatkaluna.
Wane pnutejiji hyapamtatnaka, retlu Tiago tshinkaluru, Zebedeu whene repuruyma João. Wanna koxa kanawa hwakanata rurnayma, ripxatluna tarraf-kaka. Waneya Jesus tomhana.
Waneya waneklukawa potuko ruknokamtluna rurna Zebedeu kanawaya, romkahitatkaluna Jesus.
Jesus Hinkaklewjeta Hiyrun-koxa Rutskalaklewjexyawaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus Galileia tshijne psoluka hyapamta, rasruklewjeta hanjihohnewakapjikakaya, kihle piranalu potuko Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka pirana runkaklewjeta. Yeyixatshine hiyrun-koxa hahijewnalkaka rutskalaka.
Jesus pirana Síria tshijne psoluka rupalpiranyehita. Ranikanwakatluna ptowru hixatshri yeyixatshri, satkaka tsru tshino jematshri, kkamtshiterukaka, satkaka hipukalewatatshine, hiyrun-koxa satkaka hiktehatshri waneya Jesus hitskalakna.
Hixolune yine homkahitatkalu Jesus, Galileia tshijne hichpajikatshine, Dez Cidades hajene, Jerusalém poktshi hajene, Judeia hajene hiyrun-koxa Jordão wenne pa sreta wnahlu hajene homkahitlu.
Waneya Jesus yinuwaka hasruklewleta, wla htshina:
— Poyikowatatshinni hike mwikane riwejinri tshinanu, klu tshinanu tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka wannanutkani.
— Poyikowatatshinni xye hohne wamonuwatatshine Hoyakalu tshinanu poyikotahchinikanutshinepa.
— Poyikowatatshinni mayohone klu tshinanu Hoyakalu henekanna xye tshijne psoluka.
— Poyikowatatshinni Hoyakalu halujyawaka hijhapotutatshine natshitatshine hiyrunu honnuhatewatatshine pixka klu tshinanu jinanurune pixkalunepni Hoyakalu tshinanu.
— Poyikowatatshinni jetwamonuklerune klu tshinanu Hoyakalu hetwamonutanna wanna.
— Poyikowatatshinni powra hchinikanurune klu tshinanu retanruna Hoyakalu wale yehiya.
— Poyikowatatshinni jejine himat-hiykokakatshine kihle hwachlu rixkakna klu tshinanu wanna Hoyakalu whenene htshinkona.
— Poyikowatatshinni salewnatshine Hoyakalu halukanru hkamhiywaka tshinanna klu tshinanu tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka wannanutkani.
— Poyikowatatshinephi hixa, pimrine hapaxiniklunhi, ho pimrine saletkajiniklunhi ho hma mixyawakanu hweyawyehixiniklunna, nomkahitjene hixyawaka tshinanu.
Waneko pixka rix-salewnaletnina mitshikawa hiwekakanatatshinni Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshinni. Hpoyikowatanu, himuwatan-koxa klu tshinanu himlujikolu tsru potuko hyoptotanu Hoyakalu yehiya.
Tuwu Piranapni— Hixa xye tshijne tuwre pixkalunhi. Seyni hma tuwrenuklunutka tuwu, kluneru tuwutkotnaka? Hike kihleyatkalu seyni ruknokachatkatka yine katsrexyawaklu.
Katalu Piranapni— Hixa xye tshiji katale pixkalunhi. Poktshi teno mriji hwatshri hi himukata yohimletka. Waneko pixka hix-hixa katalu pixkalunhi, hixa hi himukata yohimameroletka.
Hiyrun-koxa hikeklu yineru lamparina nikotatshri hachhaji hpuko hitakanro. Seyni halikaka lamparina hitajikowaka tutakka, ptowru yineru walepji hajene hapkathojixyawakapa tnikotle tshinanu.
Waneko pixka hixanu hixa, hiwejinri katalu pixka rixanu ptowru yineru yehiya rexyawakapluna hixa hkamrure kihleru, rimalwuxyawakapluna Hiru tenhohne hajeru.
Jesus Poyahokajyawaklu Moisés Hiykole Yonatkaluru Piranapni— Hi hkahwakanru nuna xye tshijne Moisés yonreru pirana ho Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshinni yonatkaluru pirana nnikaxyawakapa seyni nuna npoyahokajyawakapna.
Halikaka ntshina, haté tenhohne hiyrun-koxa xye tshiji nikawninri hohne, hi pa yonhajiji — hi yonapi yonhajiji nikawnanu yonruru piranaya hma makanhiywakanupa ptowru potuko.
Hiyáhoni katukta majnakowaxinri satu hiykolejijipka, hiyrunu rasrujinri satu waneko pixka rix-majnakowlexini, wale jeji mujhapotkotu htshinko tenhohne pohirewaxyawakaya. Seyni katukta kamhajetlu hiyrunu rasrukjetlu xye hiykolukaka wale jeji hijhakalur-potu hkahwakka tenhohne pohirewaxyawakaya.
Klu tshinanu wane ntshinhi, fariseu-ne hiyrunu kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine kamrure yohnik-potuknurutu hma kamhaknuklunu tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka hi himukata jihlokleta.
Hahnanuwlu Piranapni— Hixa jemlu mitshikawluru pirana wan-tshinatshri: “Hi puylalewatanu.” Hiyrun-koxa “hiylalewatatshri hikolukanuwnayehitko.”
Seyni hita wan-tshinhi katukta hahnanutlu himole hike mixkatuko rukolukanuwnanu Hoyakaluya. Hiyrun-koxa katukta heyiklu himole (wla htshininri himole: “Hike mkochpakkatyi”), jemahchinikankakjexikowaka ranikkotka. Hiyrunu katukta wla htshininri: “Mahchinikanutyi” salewaktshi nwaka rumukata yokanatkota.
Hiyáhoni penekachle panijinri papko, puchinijinri satu pimole pa hixanu hektuwaka htshinanwakaxinyi,
penekachle henekachalu yoxikowaka hinaple putakachatanrutshi waneya mitshikananhapka pyanwakatanru pimole, pimatletapanutkalu. Wane pnute psatkapanu yoxijikowaka yehi, penekachle penekanru Hoyakalu.
— Satu yineru jihyehixinipyi waneya jemahchinikanjexikowak-yehi hyamtkako pchini puhlehapkamtanru wale pirana, heta mayxaklerewatatshri hetanu hma manikkanuklunupyi waneya heta mayxaklerewatatshri kapna yochmaklewjetatshri hma menejyawakanupyi, kapna hitaklewjetatshri kapna mutajyawakanupyi.
Halikaka ntshinyi, kapna putakkoklunupa hi puchpakanu tiyiro ralujyawaka pso pma menekkanuklunuko pchinika.
Himopatlewlu Pirana— Hixa jematkalu mitshikawluru pirana wan-tshinatshri: “Hi pimopatlewatanu.”
Seyni hita wan-tshinhi: katukta sato suxo hexini waneya ret-sotanuxinro, rimopatlewatatka hihchinikanuya.
Piyhale tshinanu pumtuwnini, poplikanru, puknokanru. Klu tshinanu pimane psojite pamtajini pot-kihleyi psol-maneko tshitshmero yehi hma muknojyawakanupa.
Hiyrun-koxa pimyo tshinanu pumtuwnini, pkastakanru, puknokanru. Klu tshinanu kihle potlu pimane psojite pamtajini, psol-maneko tshitshmero yehi hma muknojikowakanupa.
Seyni hita wan-tshina: Katukta hichohnunrota, hapoklewlu tshinanu minje, rimopatkaklo hhanunro. Hiyrun-koxa katukta hhanunrotlo hichotkaluro rimopatlewata.
Hinkaklexyalu Pirana— Hiyrunukotnaka hixa himatlu Hoyakalu wan-tshinna wutsrukatenni, wla htshinna: “Hi pkachrijetanru ptshinyawakatka seyni halikaka pkamhanru ptshinyawakatkalu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu.”
Seyni hita wan-tshinhi: Hike hiwakako hmunanhanu. Hi tenhohne hiwakako hmunanhanu klu tshinanu tenhohne honra Hoyakalu tuplaxyawakni.
Hi tshiji hiwakako hmunanhanu klu tshinanu tshiji honra Hoyakalu hitspakajixiwakleni. Hi Jerusalém poktshi hiwakako hmunanhanu klu tshinanu tsru phuru potuko Hoyakalu poktshitekni wale.
Hi hixako hijiwu tshinanu halixkowata klu tshinanu hixa hi himukata klatalu hixkakletlu pa jiwutsakna, ho hsajiwkaklu.
Seyni hehe ho hike htshinini, hi satu pa hixanu hyokajinru. Klu tshinanu pa hixanu hyokajinri kamtshi runya.
Hi Hahnanutanna Hmukchikhihlenutjene Piranapni— Hixa jematkalu mitshikawluru pirana wla tshinatshri: “Yhaltshi, yhaltshikakluko. Yhitshi, yhitshikakluko.”
Seyni wla ntshinhi hixa: Hi hapnutanru hkamnitjeru. Satu yineru himpakhojixinipyi, pa sreta hoji koxa pumpakjixachatanu.
Hiyrun-koxa satu haluk-haniklexinipyi hetamayxaklerewatatshri yehi p-capa-te hkonyawakapa pimkal-koxa hi ptshipexinri.
Ho satu soldado romano-neru hwunru hitjijixinipyi satu quilômetro pchini, hiyrunu satu quilômetro putjitanru.
Satu yineru pa hixanu hanjixinyi, penekanru. Hiyrun-koxa katukta pa hixanu haluk-haniklechaxyayi, penekanru.
Hkamnitjene Hamoxyawaka Piranapni— Hixa jematkalu mitshikawluru pirana wla tshinatshri: “Puchinikanru pimwastsireru hiyrun-koxa pahnanutanru pkamnitjeru.”
Seyni hita wan-tshinyi: Hichinikanna hkamnitjene. Hanjihohneyehitanna hsaletjene.
Pimrine himaxyawaka tenhohne hajeru hiru Hoyakalu whenenetkahi. Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu hichpakaklu htkatshne muhlene tshinanu, kihlerune tshinan-koxa. Hiyrun-koxa hyokanatlu hina poyahokakatshine yehi, mpoyahokkakane yehi koxa.
Ha puchinikjene tsonu pamoxinipa, kluneru pkahwaka yoptolexnawa Hoyakalu yehiya? Hi he waneko pixka rixjetna jijhawenruklerune?
Ha himolepka halijinipa, hike hkamha pimrine pnute. Hi he moyakaluten-koxa wan-rixjetna?
Hiyáhoni potukalunephi, hixa hiru tenhohne hajeru pixka.
Jesus Hasrujyawaklu Pimrine Wepixyawaka Pirana— Xako hi yine hetanu hkamhanru hkamrure kihleru Hoyakalu tshinanu klu tshinanu wan-hixini, hiru tenhohne hajeru hike himlujikolu henekanyi.
Henekachlu Hike Mwikatu Tshinanu Piranapni— Hiyáhoni pa hixanu penekachaxinri hike mwikatu, hi punkaklexinwa tsru sejirtshiyma, kowi hima pixka, yine hexyawakyi. Waneko pixka hixachatatshine hanjihohnewakapjiya hiyrunu poktshi hanikajiteya yine himalwuxyawakapna. Halikaka ntshinhi yine himalwuxyawakna tsonu hijhatshine hike hiyrunu rumlujikolna hyoptotanutkana.
Seyni hike mwikane pa hixanu penekachaxinipa, potshkeruko peneklewachatanu pimrine mimatyehixyawakanuplu.
Potshkeruko peneklewachatanu waneya puru, ptowru pmeta kamhalexikolu hetatshri, henekanyi pumlujikolupa.
Hanjihohneru Pirana— Hiyrun-koxa hixa hanjihohnexini, hi pimrine hixachatatshine pixka hixanu. Wanna honra hikchikhihlenutlu hyopkaka hanjihohnerexyawakna hanjihohnewakapjiya hiyrunu hatnu hapo yoptowakkakaya ptowru yineru hexyawakapna. Halikaka ntshinhi yine hexyawakna wanna rumlujikolnina hike hma yoptoxyawakanupna.
Seyni panjihohnexinipa pixa, pihruko pyanu, puchyahiphaptotetanu, panjitanru puru, yohimaxikowaka hwatshri. Waneya Puru, ptowru pmeta kamhalexikolu hetatshri pumlujikolupa henekanyi.
— Hiyrun-koxa hanjihohnexinipa, hi himepetanru walerutu hima malixkane pixka. Klu tshinanu wanna kahwaklu hixo tokantshi tshinanu Hoyakalu henekanna ranjirerna.
Hi wanna pixka hixanu hixa klu tshinanu hixa Hiru himatlu hmahaxinri hma manjitkanuklunuwalu.
Jesus Hasrujyawakna Ranjihohnexyawakna PiranapniHiyáhoni wla hix-hanjihohneretanu: “Nuru, tenhohne hajeru, wanjityi pohitkalurupa pixa phiwaka potukalu.
Runanutka pixa ppohirewaxyawaka. Pixa halujyawaka kamhako xye tshijneya, tenhohne rix-kamhalexyawakatka pixka.
Wniklerupa xye hohne tshinanupa penekanwu.
Pamtakahchinikanyehixinwu wektunu pimrine hektunu wamtakahchinikanyehixyawaka pixka.
— Klu tshinanu hixa hamtakahchinikanyehixinri pimrinkaka hektunu waneya Hirtshi tenhohne hajer-koxa hamtakahchinikanyehitanru hixa hektunu.
Seyni pimrine hektunu hma mamtakahchinikanyehixinipa hixa, Hirtshi tenhohne hajer-koxa hi hamtakahchinikanyehixinhi hixa hektunu.
Hohajirewlu Piranapni— Hixa hohajirewaxini Hoyakalu tshinanu, hi wamonuwhojitatshinetka pimrine hixachatatshine pixka hix-hohajirewleta. Wanna honra rohajirewaxinna hektu rixhojixnawana pimrine hexyawaklu rohajirewatna. Hita wan-tshinhi yine hexyawakna tsonu kamhatshine hike hiyrunu rumlujikolna hyoptotanutkana.
Seyni pixa hohajirewaxiniklunu Hoyakalu tshinanu, pmachitanu, perohojitanu,
pimrine mimatyehixyawakapyi pohajirewata seyni Puru metkotu tsonu himatyehitanyi. Waneya Puru, ptowru pmeta kamhalexikolu hetatshri, pumlujikolu renekanyi.
Pohirewnalu Tenhohneya Piranapni— Xye tshijne pohirewnale hi hapatjeyehixinwa. Klu tshinanu xye tshijne pohirewnale himata tsalwata hiyrun-koxa kamla himtukjetlu. Katshowhuru koxa hiphapto yotkaka htshowhuxyawakaplu.
Seyni tenhohne pohirewnale himrexikatshinepwahi, tenhohne pohirewnale mimata tsalawatkatni, hi kamlako himtuklewaxya. Tenhohne katshowhuru hi himukata yotkakhiphaptotleta htshowhuxyawakaplu.
Klu tshinanu hanukta himrexyalu hpohirewnale wane koxlu hihchinikanu.
Mantshi Katalute Piranapni— Yhaltshi wimane katalute. Kihle yhale pixini, piman-koxa kat-yehi potpako.
Seyni hektu yhale pixinipa waneya piman-koxa mapchah-yehipa. Hiyáhoni katalu pimane hwatshri mapchahalu rixini, hi pa mapchahnukananuktalu!
Hoyakalu Hiyrun-koxa Pohirewlu Piranapni— Hi satukna towrertshi walerutu himukata kamhaletlu hepi phurune kamrure. Klu tshinanu ho rahnanutanru satu, satu ramotanu; ho satu repiretanu, satu reyikanu. Hixa hi himukata kkamrurewaklerune hixleta Hoyakalu tshinanu hiyrunu pohirewlu tshinanu.
Wma Kojwakahchinikanuxyawakapa Xye Hiwejinri Tshinanu Piranapni— Wale tshinanu wane ntshinhi: Hi hkojwakahchinikanutanu hiwejinri tshinanu, klu hnikanu ho klu hiranu. Hi himane tshinanuko koxa hkojwakahchinikanutanu klu hmakatanu. Hi he hiweklu, nikkaluru yohnik-hijhakalurni? Hiyrun-koxa hi he mantshi, mkatshri yohnik-hijhakalurni?
Hetanru tenhohne yapatshine kamejirune. Hi rutaklewatna, hi ramluna, hi honantshi himretawakako rimwana. Wanepnawaka Hiru tenhohne hajeru hohlutjetna. Seyni hi he hixa, wanna yohnik-hijhakalun-pothi hixa?
Hanunhe hixa satkakhi kojwakahchinikanruyma hixolethohneyehixikatshriwa rumukata hiweklexyawaka pejnu hohne?
— Klu tshinanhe hkojwakahchinikanuta mkatshri tshinanu? Hetanru kahwuru hanu rix-tseruwnaleta. Hi hkamrurewata, hi koxa hjiweta.
Seyni wane ntshinyi halikaka hi phuru Salomão-niko, phuru potukni, seyni mkatshri kihler-potuko rutakjereru hi kahwuru pa hihlenu rixa.
Hoyakalukni makawkaklu campo hwatshriptshe xawakni wetleru yetshikawa ramhannatka forno hyoxijikolu tshinanu. Hi he kchana hmakaxyawaka pnute rix-makawkakletanhi hixa pso halixle jijirunhi?
Hiyáhoni hi hkojwakahchinikanuxinwa, hi wla htshinanu: “Kluhe wnikanu?” ho “Kluhe wuranu?” ho “Kluhe wmakatanu”?
Klu tshinanu xyekaka rujhajetmakna moyakalutene hiyrun-koxa Hiru tenhohne hajeru himatlu xye ptowruka halukanru.
Seyni mitshikananhapka Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hijhanu hiyrunu Hoyakalu halujyawaka hkamhanu. Waneyakni Hoyakalu henekanhi xyekaka ptowruka.
Hiyáhoni hi hkojwakahchinikanuxinwa yetshikawa hohne tshinanupa, klu tshinanu waneplu kojwakahchinikanrewlu yetshikawapa. Pa hohnekaka kojwaklu hwatka.
Hma Jihyehixyawakanuplu Satu Yineru Piranapni— Hi hjihyehirewatanu waneya Hoyakalu koxa hi hikolukanuwnakakanhi hixa.
Klu tshinanu hanu hix-jihyehirewlexyawakna pimrine waneko pixka rixanhi Hoyakalu. Hiyrun-koxa yahotapi hixa hyahotapre pimrine tshinanu, walako hyahoxika Hoyakaluya.
Haklu tshinanhe petlu kapopejiru mtserutu pimole yhale hwatshri seyni piyhale hwatshri kaknalu psolutu hi pimatheta?
Hanhe pumukata wan-tshinretlu pimole: “Nomole, hitatshi pitshitanu kapopejiru piyhale hwatshri nkochpajyawakapa,” pma mimathetkanuklunru piyhale hwakanatatshri?
Hixachatatshrini wan-hixatshri! Mitshikananhapka puknokanrutshi kaknalu piyhale hajeru. Waneyapa petpotutanutkalu pkochpajyaplu pimole yhale hwatshri kapopejiru.
Kluneruktako Hoyakalunu Wma Menejyawakanupna Kawene Pixkalune Piranapni— Kluneruktapni Hoyakalunu hi penekanna kawene pixkalune. Klu tshinanu wane pixini, kawene hiprotakanwakatanyi, rachkaxyawakapyina. Tuwutu kwenuru pérola tshinkaluru hi puknokanu porco-ne pixkalune yehi klu tshinanu wane pixini, porco-ne pixkalune katsrehohochatanru.
Hoyakalu Chinikannu Piranapni— Hanjitanro henekko; hijhanu hikchikanu; hitpehiphaptotetanu, hkotpukko hiphapto.
Klu tshinanu ptowru hanjitatshri yoptotanru. Hiyrun-koxa ptowru hijhatshri hikchikanru. Ptowru yineru hiphapto hitpetatshri hkotpukyehitko hiphapto.
Ho chima ranjixinhi, himnurhe henekanru?
Hixa hektutu kkamhaklerunhi himata kihleru henekawheneta hiyáhoni wane yohnik-rixa heneklewleta Hirtshi tenhohne hajeru ranjitjeru.
— Hiyáhoni hanukta paluk-hixletko yine tshinanuya, waneko pixka pixanna wanna ptowru potuko tshinanu. Klu tshinanu walekni Moisés yonreru pirana hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshinni yonatkaluru pirana tshinyawaka potuko.
Mtseruswa Hiphaptotetu Piranapni— Pjihlokanru mtseruswa hiphaptotetu. Klu tshinanu tsru hiphaptoteru tsru hapolu hamhikowaka hapni hiyrun-koxa hi heppikna yine tsru hiphaptoteru jihlokatshinena.
Seyni mtseruswa hiphaptotetu hiyrunu kyapre hapolu hiweklu mnikawnakatu haniklewatatshri! Hi hixo yineru hikchiklu.
Hahmuna Hiyrunu Hisahi Hyapkakleta Jesus— Xako Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine yahole! Runyehithina carneiro hike mixlewatkatu pixka seyni halikaka hocha hajeru lobo tshinkaluru kmatsyiru pixkalunetkani.
Rimathetkana hkamrurna tshinanu. Kawchipiri chehirahe hjijrujiko uva sahi? Ho kawchipiri chehirahe hjijrujiko figo sahi?
Ptowru hahmuna kihleru, kihle sahiplu hiyrun-koxa hahmuna hektutu, hektu sahiplu.
Hahmuna kihleru hi hektu sahiplu hiyrun-koxa hahmuna hektutu hi kihle sahiplu.
Ptowru hixatshri hahmuna hektu sahiwleru hkayika, tshitshmero ruknokka.
Hiyáhoni waneko pixka rixna Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine yahole, hkamrurna tshinanu rimathetkana.
— Hi ptowru yineru “Nutsrukate, Nutsrukate” ntshinjene jihlokanru tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka. Seyni tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka jihlokatshri tsonu Nuru tenhohne hajeru halujyawaka kamhatshriko.
Hapnokaxikolu hohnepa hixo yine wla htshinanno: “Wutsrukate, Wutsrukate, hi he Hoyakalu tokanu wunkakletatka pixa hiwakaya? Hi he kamtshi wuknokatka pixa hiwaka tshinanu? Hi he hixo hetkalurkaka wkamhatka?”
Hiyáhoni nunkakpotutanna: “Hikeklu hohne nimathethi. Hyachatanutka, hektuwaka kamhaklerunhi!”
Sotlu Hoho ho Ksatu Hohowak-Panawaxikatshri Piranapni— Hiyáhoni ptowru yineru ntokanu jematshri hiyrunu ntokanu homkahitatshri, satu jeji jimatkaleru sotlumta hoho panawaxikatshri pixkalutni wale.
Waneya hinatkani, rapohamxinixka wenu, kanniphalu koxa herutpiratlu. Seyni hi hyawnapjita klu tshinanu sotlu hoho hkamhika pantshi.
— Seyni katukta ntokanu hjema seyni hi hkamhalu ntokanu wale satu jeji jipukaleru mchiko wakan-tshiji panawaxikatshri pixkalutni wale.
Hinatkani, rapohamta wenu, kanniphalu koxa herutpiratlu pantshi. Waneyakni hyawnamtanatka pantshini. Tsru yawnalu rixana walepjini.”
Jesus Tsru Hitakkaluruyma Rasrukjetna Yine PIranapniWaneya Jesus hali tshinrexinixkalu xyekaka pirana, hixolune yine himyekahchinikanpotutatka rasrukle tshinanu.
Klu tshinanu hi rasrukjenna kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine pixka rix-hasrukleta seyni tsru hitakkaluruyma rix-hasrukleta.
Hijirohitutatshri Rutskalajyawaka Jesus PiranapniWaneya Jesus himriji serpika, hixolune yine homkahitlu.
Waneya satu hijirohitutatshri yanwakatlu Jesus. Hyoptsojityehitlu Jesus, tshiji rutspakhojita waneya jeji wan-tshinru Jesus: — Palujiniplu pumukata hitskalakletno.
Waneya Jesus homyokanwakatlu. Hkamruklu. Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru: — Hehe, naluka. Putskalhatka. Waneklukawa potuko rujirhitle ramhiyatka, rutskalhatka.
Waneya Jesus hijretlu wla htshinru: — Petanu. Hike punkakanu seyni pyanutka. Sacerdote pekhimantapinwa putskalhinrixka. Waneya panikanru henekachalu henekawaka nwaka Moisés yonreru tshinyawaka pixka pimrine himaxyawakaplu putskalhiywakatka.
Jesus Hitskalajyawaklu Soldado Pohire Towreru PiranapniJesus Cafarnaum poktshi hapojiniklunu, satu soldado-ne pohire yanwakatlu, ranjitlu repixyawakaplu.
Wla htshinru Jesus: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, ntowreru hiktehatshri hikóluha nopjiya. Hsalewnapotutana.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru: — Wane nyanu, nutskalajyawakaplu.
Waneya soldado-ne pohire wla tshina: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, hita hike kochpakatshrino nopji potuko pjihlojyawakapa. Seyni pyanumanwakachatanru, ntowreru hitskalhanu.
Klu tshinanu hit-koxa k-chefe-tno, towutkalurno. Wanepnawaka soldado-ne ntowuta. Satu wane ntshina —“pyanutka” — hiyáhoni hya. Satutnaka wane ntshinru: — “puna” — hiyáhoni runanwakatno. Ntowreru koxa wane ntshininri: — “xye pkamhanu” — hkamhanru.
Wane ntshinhi hixolune yine hinanu, tkatshi hichpajyawaka sreta, rimxijyawaka sreta, ruchpajinna. Nikjexikowak-yehi tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka hwatshri htuplatanna Abraão-ni, Isaque-ni, hiyrunu Jacó-niyma tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka.
Seyni pohirewaxyawaka whenene hiknokkalunenapni maleka sreta hwininapa mapchahawakaya waneya rawanu tsru tshiyahlu haskiyhiru koxa.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinru soldado-ne pohire: — Pyanutka! Palixle tshinanu panjireru hakanhanu. Waneya waneklukawa potuko rutskalhatka htowreru.
Jesus Hitskalajyawaklo Pedro Himajiro PiranapniJesus Pedro-pji jihlojinixka, retlo Pedro himajiro, tukoluhakanata tpatshwapotuta.
Waneya hkachimyotlo tutuk-patshwalemtatka, tyotunomtatka tyinuwaka yomhaletlu.
Pimrinkaka Rutskalajyawaka Jesus PiranapniKayi rixinixka rimxijinixka tkatshi hixolune kkamtshiterune ranikanwakatluna. Waneya Jesus kamtshine maleka ruknoka htokanu tsonuyma hiyrunu ptowruneka yeyixatshine rutskalaka.
Wan-rixa hpoyahokajyawakapa ptowruka htshinyawaka Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri Isaías-ni, mitshikawluru tokanu wla htshina: “Wanepnawaka wahijewaklu ranikkatka, raniklu wwamonnu.”
Satkaka Jesus Homkahpiratatshinemka PiranapniWaneya Jesus hixolune yine walestsi hajene rexiniklunu, wenu hkopruhajixatkana rasruklene.
Waneya satu kasruklewakleru hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshri yanwakatlu Jesus, wla htshina: — Kasruklewakleru, hanuktako pyanu pixa nimotsatanyi hita.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinru jeji: — Kaweretshine kapna rawjetna. Kochitshin-koxa tenhohne yapatshine waneyna rawyawakna. Seyni Jeji Whene tshinkaluru tsonu hi jimkawakleru, hi rawya rapnanuwakle.
Waneya satu jejitnaka wla tshinru Jesus: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, pitshitanno mitshikananhapkatshi nsatkapamtanu. Nurutshi nkapnamtanu.
Seyni Jesus wla tshinru: — Pomkahitanno hita. Petachatanna hipnatshinekakluko kapnakajyawaka.
Jesus Hitukkajyawaklu Tsru Kanniphalu Tsru Powhaya PiranapniWaneya kanawa hpokowna Jesus, rasruklene homkahitlu.
Chinpotukawa tsru kanniphalu yopyoka tsru powhaya. Hiplojha tsepohjetlo kanawa. Seyni Jesus himkakananumta.
Waneya rasruklene yanwakatlu Jesus, hkomyekluna wane htshinruna: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, pepixanunwu. Wupnahetkotanuna!
Waneya Jesus wla tshinna: — Klu tshinanhe hpikatka hixa pso halixle jijirunhi? Waneya hyotunota htshihetjetlu kanniphalu. Pokokha rixatka hipowha.
Hiyáhoni hi rimat-hichinikanuwatna waleymalune waneya wane htshinna: — Han-hixatshri koxni xye jeji? Haté kanniphalu hipowha koxa yijnakotlu.
Jesus Yokanaxyawakna Kamtshine Kkamtshiterune Ruchpajyawakna PiranapniWaneya Jesus pa sreta wnahlu Gadara tshijne rapojinixka hepi jejine kkamtshiterune hyoptota. Wanna yomletsh-yehi ruchpajyatkana. Hike himukata hiknohlehapota hmatsyinna tshinanu.
Waneya wane htshin-saplewletna kkamtshiterune: — Klu pimalukwu, Hoyakalu Whene? Puna psaletkajyawakanapwuhe wapnokaxikolu hohnepa minjeko?
Hi howukatkana hixoluru porco, hnikakanatna.
Waneya kamtshine hipokananu hanjitlu Jesus wane htshinruna: — Porco-ne mane pyokanatanunwu wanna mane wjihlojyawakanapa.
Hiyáhoni Jesus wan-tshinna: — Hichpakanutka! Waneya ruchpakamtatkana kamtshine. Porco-ne mane hitokote hjihlokamtatkana. Waneya hixolunni porco-nni hipjita hijrujyanatka. Hipowha rapokanna waneya hipowha rahyejyanna.
Waneya porco-ne hinotatshine hasukamta tsru poktshi rapokna. Runkaklewatna ptowruka kkamtshithixapatshine pirana.
Hiyáhoni wane poktshi hajene ptowruneka hinamta retapyawakapluna Jesus. Seyni rexiniklunruna, hipokananu ranjitluna wanna tshijne ruchpajyawakapa.
Jesus Hitskalajyawaklu Jeji Hiktehatshri PiranapniWaneya Jesus kanawa pokownatka. Hkopruhatatka, hipoktshi hyatka.
Waneya yine hanikanwakatlu satu jeji hiktehatshri, hijeko hikoluhatshri. Jesus hexinri wanna halixle, wane htshinru hiktehatshri: — Kihle hichinikanupyi. Mturu, pektunu puknojikatka.
Hiyáhoni satkaka kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine wan-tshinahchinikanuta: — Hektuwaka htshinanwakatlu Hoyakalu.
Seyni Jesus himathetahchinikanutna waneya wane htshinna: — Klu tshinanhe wan-hixahchinikanuta xyekaka hektutu hichinikanretahajixyawaka?
Hanupothe kihle tshinko? Wla htshinikowaka hiktehatshri: “Pektunu puknojikatka”, ho wla htshinikowaka: “Pyotunotanu pkochtshekjekotanu pyanutka”?
Waneya hiktehatshri yotunomtatka, hkochtshekjekomtatka hipji nwaka hyatka.
Hixo yine hetakanatatshine pikatka. Rimalwutluna Hoyakalu klu tshinanu xye pixkalutu towuwlu renejyawakna yine.
Jesus Homkahjixlu Mateus Tshinkaluru PiranapniWaneya Jesus pnute hyamxinixka retlu Levi tshinkaluru. Htuplakanata tuplawaka hwenuxikolu hyoptoxyawakapa. Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru: — Pomkahitanno. Waneya Levi palnamtatka, romkahitatkalu Jesus.
Jesus Hektune Himinjiywaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus Levi-pji nijiniklunu, hixolune jijhawenruklerune, pimrin-koxa hektune Jesus hiyrunu rasrukleneyma tuplakanatatshine nikawakakwa yehi.
Waneya fariseu-ne hetlu waneya repomhatkana rasruklene wla htshinna: — Kluneru tshinanhe wannayma hnika, rura wanna jijhawenruklerune, hektuneyma?
Xye hjemini Jesus, wla htshinna: — Pomtalune hi haluklu kpinrewakleru seyni katshinomtalu haluklu.
Seyni hijha himatletanu hanu haluka tshinreta xye hima Hoyakalu piranaya: “Naluklu hetwamonrewlu. Hi henekachlu hiylatkaluru naluka.” Klu tshinanu hi nuna ntshanixyawakapna kihlerune seyni hektune ntshanixyawaka rehchinikanuxyawakapna.
Hohajirewlu PiranapniWaneya João Batista hasruklene yanwakatlu Jesus waneya repomhaluna wane htshinruna: — Haklu tshinanhe hixa João hasruklenwu, fariseu-ne hasruklen-koxa hohajirewata seyni pasruklene nika?
Waneya Jesus hihitna, wane htshinna: — Rumukata natshretnahe hnunrowlu hetatshine hnunrowatatshriymalune? Hike. Seyni rapokhohnexinpatka hnunrowpiratatshri hixolune yehi hkochpajikoklunpatka. Waneklu papko halikaka rohajirewatanutkana wanna.
— Hi kihle hipxatkolu mkatshri hitsruka herotu samayma. Klu tshinanu herotu sama himutskirhanunru waneya herotu sama hiskakkakanunru htseruwaswapotutanuna.
Hi kihle tsrutsoleji mapa hitakhatkolo vinho-ha hekamhakolha. Wan-rixkoklunutka vinho-ha hipchekkakanunru sac-kakapni. Tuyokhatanuna vinho-hapni waneya sac-kaka koxapni salewnanuna. Seyni vinho-ha herotu, saco herotu tutakhatka. Waneya hi satukna salewnanu hi vinho-hako hi saco-ko.
Tsru Hitakkaluru Hanjireru PiranapniWaneya hyanumsakanaxiniwa Jesus, runa satu tsru hitakkaluru hanjihohnewakapji hajeru. Hyoptsojityehitlu Jesus waneya wla htshinru: — Xawakni potuko tupnanatka nchítshoni. Punanu wala hoho putakamyotanu tutskalhiywakapa tiwejyawakapa.
Mpomtato Rutskalajyawaka Jesus PiranapniJesus hiyrun-koxa rasruklene waleyma wane hya.
Waneya waneklukawa sato suxo doze hwalapu hihrahawatatshro Jesus tjimne sretako tunya waneya tkamrukamkatlu.
Wala wla tshinnawa: “Nkamrukamkachaxiniplu, nutskalhanutka.”
Waneya Jesus heknojtata, retatkalo. Waneya wane htshinatkalo: — Chrima, kihlehchinikanupyi. Palixle hitskalakyi. Waneya Waneklukawhapka potuko tutskalhatka.
Jairo Hchitsho Riwekkajyawaka Jesus PiranapniWaneya Jesus jihlokapjixiniklunru Jairo-pji, retlu sejirtshi, saplewjepotutatshine hiyrun-koxa kowi tokaxikatshine,
wane htshinatkana: — Hyanutka. Mturo hi hipna seyni tumkachata. Seyni rutsolhitatluna Jesus.
Waneya ptowru yineru maleka hyinixkana, Jesus pantshi jihloka. Waneya Jesus kosemyoxininatkalo mtúroni, tyotunotatka.
Wale pirana pohiwatatka wale sreta psoluyaka.
Jesus Hitskalajyawakna Hepi Jejine Mtsawa PiranapniWaneya Jesus wane hichpajinixka, hepi jejine mtsawane wale hatjini hyana waneya wla htshin-sapletna: — Petwamonutanunwu, Davi-ni klopicha!
Pantshi hjihlojini Jesus, mtsawane yanwakatlu waneya Jesus hepomhatkana, wla htshinna: — Halixluhe numukata hitskalaklethi? Waneya ruhitluna: — Hehe walixlu, Tsru Hixikatshriwa.
Waneya Jesus kamrukayhaletna, wla htshinna: — Halixyawaka tshinanu, hkamhako.
Waneya retatkana. Waneya Jesus hijretpotutna, wla htshinna: — Hike hinkakanu.
Seyni ruchpakatkana, hkopalpiranatatkaluna wale tshijne psoluka.
Jesus Hitskalajyawaklu Myanumatkatu PiranapniWaneya hyinixkana jejine, satu kkamtshiteru myanumatkatu ranikyehitluna Jesus.
Waneya Jesus hali hiknoklexinixkalu kamtshi, myanumatkatu yanumatatnaka. Waneya hixolune yine wane hajene himyekahchinikanutatka. Wla htshinna: — Hikeklu hohne wane pixkalutu rexika Israel tshijneya.
Seyni fariseu-ne wla tshina: — Tsru kamtshi himukatleyma tshinanu hetko maleka ruknokna kamtshine.
Jesus Hetwamonuxyawakna Yine PiranapniWaneya Jesus ptowru poktshikaka hyapa, hanjihohnewakapjikaka rasruklewaxya, kihle piranalu potuko Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka pirana runkakletna. Ptowru hixatshri yeyixlu hiyrunu hahijewnalkaka rutskalaka.
Waneya wla htshinatkana rasruklene: — Hamkaluru halikaka hix-potuko. Seyni kamrurewatatshine hi hixo.
Hiyáhoni hanjitanru Tsru Hixikatshriwa hamkaluru towutatshri, kamrurewatatshine hyokanaxyawakapa ramyawakapluna.
Doze Rasruklene Hyokanaxyawaka Jesus PiranapniJesus tomhana rasruklene doze waneya renekpixkonutna kamtshine htowuxyawakapna ruchpajyawakapna yine maneya hiyrun-koxa ptowru hixatshri yeyixlu hiyrunu hahijewnalkaka rutskalajyawakna.
Xyeni Jesus nuretanune doze-na hiwakkakni: mitshikananhapka, Simão tshinkaluru (wale rutakhiwakata Pedro) hiyrunu André tshinkaluru Pedro mole; hiyrunu Tiago tshinkaluru, Zebedeu whene, João tshinkaluru, Tiago hepuru;
Wane koxna Filipe hiyrunu Bartolomeu tshinkalune; Tomé tshinkaluru hiyrunu Mateus (walekni wenuxikolu yoptotatshri); hiyrunu Tiago tshinkaluru Alfeu whene hiyrunu Tadeu tshinkaluru;
Wane koxlu Simão Zelote tshinkaluru hiyrunu Judas Iscariotes tshinkaluru, Jesus kamnitjerupa.
Jesus Hasruklene Kamrurepa PiranapniNyikaka doze jejine hyokanata Jesus, wan-rix-towutletna: — Hi judeu mixkane tskala hyanu, hi hjihlokanru samaritano poktshitekaka.
Seyni carneiro-ne hamhatshine pixkalune israel-nerune yehi tsonu hyanu.
Hyinipa hinkaklewakananumtanu. Wane htshinanu: “Hi howukatkalu tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka.”
Hitskalakanna yeyixatshine, hiwekkakanna hipnatshine. Hijirohitutatshine hitskalakanu. Kamtshine hiknokanna. Mwenutu xyekaka neneklewata, hix-koxa mwenutu henekanna wanna.
Hi hanikanru ouro proji hi prata projiko hi cobre projiko hiptshiji hanijini;
hi koxa hanikanru sacola, hi hepi mkatshriko, hi sandalha-ko hi kanojeruko hanikanu klu tshinanu kamrurewatatshri himukata yoptoletlu hkamrure hipekole.
— Hanur-poktshiktako hjihlojini, hijhanru satu hihle yoptoletjeru waneya wanepji hwanu haté hichpajini potuko.
Pantshi hjihlojinipa, kihle hwachle htshinanru wanepji hajene.
Waneya kihle yoptole hixkoklunupa, hanjitanru Hoyakalu kihle hwachle rixkajikowakapna. Seyni hma yoptohihlenutjene rixinna, Hoyakalu hanjixya kihle hwachle rixinrina hkonanna.
Katukta hma yoptotjenepa, hma jemjenepa, hichpakamxinpatka waneya wanna hetanu hiwlihkajpatjixitanu rimaxyawakapna hi hixako htshinanni seyni hma yoptotjene malixlenu tshinanni.
Halikaka ntshinhi, hapnokaxikolu hohnepa Sodoma hiyrunu Gomorra poktshinni salexikolu yohnik-hapnokatlu rixko hma yoptohihlenuxikowakanu poktshiya.
Salewaktshipni Hiyrun-koxa Kojwawaktshipni Piranapni— Nyokanathi hatatjewa ovelha-nhi lobo-ne pixkalune hanikajite hyiywakapa. Hiyáhoni halpokohchinikanutanu himnune pixka seyni myokwirenephi motkokoji pixka.
Hislahinwa yine tshinanu klu tshinanu hkachitanhi jemahchinikanyehixikowaka yehi ranikanhi hiyrun-koxa hkotshipjetanhi hanjihohnewakapjikakaya.
Hita tshinanu tsru hixikatshinwa hiyrunu tsrukakalune nwaka hanikko kihler-pirana Cristo pirana hinkaklexyawakapna wanna hiyrunu judeu mixkane.
Hkachitkoklunpatka, hi hkojwakahchinikanutanu klu piranakta htshinanu ho hanu htshin-hihretanu. Rapojinpapkopatka Hoyakalu henektokanutanhi
klu tshinanu htshinyawakapa hi hixako htshinreni seyni Puru Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru henektokanrepni.
— Moltshine himolene potuko ruylajixkakanna. Waneko pixka rixan-koxna hirtshine, hwuhenene ruylajixanna. Haté hwuhenene kamnitanna rurna ruylaxyawakapluna.
Ptowru yineru hahnanutanhi hixa hita tshinanu seyni poyehi halixleru haté hmahle papko, riwekanu.
Salewaktshi hexiniklunu satu poktshiya, wane hasujini pa poktshi pnute hajeru hyanu. Halikakni ntshinyi, Jeji Whene satokanu hi ptowru poktshi pejnu Israel tshijnetshi hyapanna.
Hike Mkojwakanu Piranapni— Hasrukkaluru hi rasrukjeru yohnik-hijhakalurni hiyrun-koxa towutkaluru hi htowutjeru yohnik-hijhakalurni.
Seyni hikamtutkalu hasrukkaluru rasrukjeru pixka rixyawaka hiyrun-koxa hikamtutkalu towutkaluru htowutjeru pixka rixyawaka. Kapjiru Belzebu (ho Satanás) rikahwajinrina, hi he pnute hektutu rikahwakkona walepji hajene?
Hiyáhoni hi hpikanna yine. Klu tshinanu ptowruka yohimluru ruphujetko. Ptowru tokantshi yohimatkaluru rimathetko runkakletko.
Klunerukta ntshinyi mapchahawakaya, katawak-hohne hinkakletanru. Hiyrun-koxa nunkajyahi, hihruko hitokoteya, ptowru yineru jemanu runkakletko.
Hi he hepi kochitshine hi kwenu hichanjika? Wanepnawaka hi satukna kochitshi tshiji hijruka Hiru Hoyakalu malukkanuklunu.
Haté wijiwutsa ptowruka hitakyahokalurni Hoyakaluya.
Hiyáhoni hi hpikanu klu tshinanu hixa yáholu satupka yineru tsonu, hixo kochitshine yohnik-hijhakalurni!
— Katukta hiphujtatno yine jemanu, hit-koxa hiphujtatanru Nuru tenhohne hajeru hetanu.
Katukta hi nimathetlu htshinanwakaxinipno, hi nimathetanunhi hixapni ntshinanu Nuru hetanu tenhohneya.
Kotspalaxikatshinwa Jesus Tshinanu Piranapni— Hixlahe kahwaklu nuna kihle hwachleru nanikanwakaxyawaklu xye tshijne? Seyni hi nuna hihle hwachlu nenejyawakaphi seyni nuna nkotspalaxyawakaphi halikaka.
Seyni nuna nkotspalaxyawakapna hituru ruru hkamnixyawakapa, suxo tunro tkamnixyawakapa, hnuruwatatshro thimajiro tkamnixyawakapa.
Hiyáhoni jeji kamnipotutjenepa walepji hajeneko.
— Katukta hi ramotno hita ruru ho runro pnute, hi rumukata nasrukleru hixleta. Katukta hi hamotno hita hituru ho richitsho pnute hi rumukata nasrukleru hixleta.
Hiyrun-koxa katukta h-cruz-te hma mutaykopitkanuklunupa hi rumukata nasrukleru hixleta.
Katukta haluk-hiwekkaklexinwa, ramtaklewatanun-honuka. Katukta hamtakanru riwekle hita tshinanu riwekanu halikaka.
Himlujikolukaka Piranapni— Katukta yoptothi hixa, Hita hyoptota hiyrun-koxa katukta yoptotno Hita, hyoptotlu nyokanatjeru.
Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri yoptotatshri Hoyakalu tokanu runkaklewaxyawaka tshinanu, wale koxa yoptotanru Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri himlujikolupa. Hiyrunu jeji potukalu yoptotatshri ruhlenu tshinanu jeji potukalu himlujikolupa koxa hyoptotanu wale.
— Hiyrunu katukta copa stono katshiklehalu satu mujhakotu heneka ruryawakaplu nasrukleru rixyawaka tshinanu, halikaka ntshinhi, rumlujikolupa halikaka hyoptotanu.
Jesus Hinkaklewaxyawakapa Pa Poktshikakaya PiranapniJesus hali towutlexinixkana rasruklene, wane ruchpajya rasruklewaxyawakapa, runkaklewaxyawakapa pa poktshikakaya.
João Batista Yokanaxyawakna Rasruklene Jesus Nwaka PiranapniWaneya preso rawinixka João jempiranyehixinri Cristo tshinkaluru kamrure, rasruklene hyokananwakatlu wale,
repomhiywakapluna, wla htshin-hepomhaletluna: — Pixakatkalhe hinatshripyi tshinkaluryi ho satuklatshi wkahwakanu?
Waneya Jesus wla tshinna: — Hajewa. Hinkakapanru João xye hetanrukaka hiyrun-koxa hyijnakotanrukaka.
Mayhalenekananu hetatka. Myankanekananu yanatka. Hijirhitukanatatshine hitskalhatka. Majnakonekananu jema. Hipnatshine hiwekkakka. Kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana runkakkatkana hike mwikane.
Poyikowatatshine hita nma mohweyatjene.
Jesus Hinkaklexyawaklu João Batista PiranaJoão hasruklene hichpajinitka, Jesus João pirana hyinuwaka hinkakletna hixolune yine wane hajene, wla htshinna: — Ha hixa, kluhe haluk-hetletapa kahnete poktshiriya? Kotshkawale kanniphalu kowchiklerlahe hetapa?
Ha klunerhe hetapa? Satu Jeji kihleru mkatshri hitakatshrirhe hetapa? Hike, kihleru mkatshri hitakjetatshine, honra phurupjikaka rawna wan-hixatshine.
Seyni klunerhe mitshi haluk-hetletpatka? Satu Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshrihe hetapa? Hehe, wane ntshinhi, Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshinni yohnik-hijhakaluru hetpatka.
Klu tshinanu João yonpiranyehitkalurni xye: “Hetanu, nyokanreru nyokanatanu pixa hnapu, ralpokohnapuxyawakaplu patnu hapote.”
Klu tshinanu wane ntshinhi João Batista ptowru matutatshri yohnik-hijhakalurumkani. Wanepnawaka mujhakon-potu tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka hwatshine, João yohnik-hijhakalunetkani wanna.
João Batista yinuwaka hinkaklexinri papko haté xawakni, tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka kamnitka hiyrun-koxa jejine mixkowatatshine haluka yotkakletlu.
Hma munkaklewatkanuklunuwa João, Moisés yonreru pirana hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshinni pirana yonatkaluru hinkakletlu Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka pirana.
Waneya haluka yoptolexiniplu walekni Elias tshinkalurni hinatshripa.
Katukta kajnakopnapa hyijnakoxyawaka, hyijnakotanru.
“Wtumlejyehithi poyikowlu hima seyni hi hahsat-hixa. Kwamonuru himamka wchikaletatka seyni hi htshiyahatatka.”
Hetanu. João Batista hohajirewata, hi vinho-ha rura seyni hixa wan-tshinru: “Waneylu kamtshi.”
Runa Jeji Whene tshinkaluru. Hnika, rura. Seyni hixa wan-tshina: “Haha hetanu, xye jeji tsru nikalu, vinho-ha jirakleru. Jijhawenruklerune hiyrun-koxa hektune rimatleta.” Hiyáhoni yine hetanru Hoyakalu himatkalewle potukalu rixyawaka, Hoyakalu himatkalewle himwatshri kamrure tshinanu.
Malixkane Poktshikaka Hapnokaxikowaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus yinuwaka jihyehiretlu poktshikaka himyekaklewatatshrikaka hix-potuko hkamhajexyawaka klu tshinanu hi rehchinikanutatkana. Wla htshinna:
— Hapnokatkalur-potupyi pixa Corazim poktshi hiyrunu Betsaida poktshi! Klu tshinanu himyekaklewatatshrikaka nkamhakmaka hita Tiro poktshiya hiyrunu Sidom poktshi hix-yehi hakanhikatshri pixkalutu, waneyamka mitshikawako rehchinikanutanutkana wane poktshikak-hajene, waneyamka mkatshri saco mapa kamhikolu hmakatanutkana hiyrunu tshitshi pahi koxamka hpolojiwuxinwana rimathexikowakna rehchinikanutatkana.
Seyni halikaka ntshinhi rapnokaxikolu hohnepa Tiro hiyrun-koxa Sidom poktshi hi hsaletpotukanatkona hixa salexikowaka pso.
Hiyrunu pixa Cafarnaum poktshi. Pkahwakhe patskoxyawakapa haté tenhohne? Seyni pixa halikaka puknokko tshiji hitokote hamhikowak-yehi. Klu tshinanu himyekaklewatatshrikaka nkamhakmaka hita Sodoma poktshi hix-yehi hakanhikatshri pixkalutu, haté xawakni hohnekananumka rawawa Sodoma poktshi.
Seyni halikaka ntshinhi rapnokaxikolu hohnepa Sodoma poktshi hi hsaletpotukanatkona hixa salexikowaka pso.
Hapnanuxikowaka Jesus Tshinanu PiranapniWaneya waneklu papko Jesus wan-tshina: — Nimalwutyi, Nuru, tenhohne tshij-koxa Towutatshriyi. Klu tshinanu pyohimatlu xye pirankaka jimatkaleruneya hiyrunu kahchinikanuruneya. Seyni puphujetlu hike mimatkane hetanuya.
Hehe, Nuru, xye pixa palujyawakni.
— Nuru, ptowru potuko renekno. Hike himathetlu Whentshi seyni Hirtshipka himathetlu. Hike himathetlu Hirtshi seyni Whentshipka himathetlu hiyrun-koxa katukta raluk-himatyehkakletlu Hirtshi.
Jesus Wla Htshinyawaka Punanwakatanno Piranapni— Runanwakatanno ptowru hamanu kamrurewletatshri tsru wunru hitjitatshri waneya hita hapnanukakanhi.
Hitshitanno nkosejyawakaphi, nasruklenephi klu tshinanu mayohotno hita, kihle hchinikanurno waneya hit-yehi hapnanuhchinikanrewlu hikchikanu.
Klu tshinanu hitjitpre nutajinhi myapretni hiyrunu wuntshiri minotni.
Jesus Hapnanuxikalur-hohne Hitsrukate Rixyawaka PiranapniWaneya howukchini hapnanuxikalur-hohnetkani hsana hyapakanatna Jesus rasrukleneyma. Rasruklene natshitatka hiyáhoni hyinuwaka jimlakhawletluna. Waneya hniktatajitluna.
Fariseu-ne hetakanatna hiyáhoni fariseu-ne wan-tshinru Jesus: — Petanu. Haklu tshinanhe wan-rixana hapnanuxikalur-hohne hinanchitkalur-hohne?
Waneya wane htshinna Jesus: — Hikeklu hohnehe het-yonhatlu Davi-ni pirana, hnatshixini waleni hiyrun-koxa waleymalune?
Davi-ni jihloklu Hoyakalupji, hniklu pão-kaka Hoyakalu henekachalurupa. Wale hinanchitkaluru hnikni. Sacerdote-ne tsonu himukata nikletanru hnikni. Seyni Davi-ni niklu hiyrunu rimotsatanun-koxa reneklu hnijyawakapluna.
Hikeklu hohnehe het-yonhatlu xye pirana koxa Moisés yonreya? Sacerdote-ne koxa Hoyakalupji kamrurewjexya hapnanuxikalur-hohne hiyáhoni hmajnakoxyalu Moisés hiykole yonatkaluru seyni hi jikolukanurunni.
Seyni halikaka xawakni satu hapokatka Hoyakalupji yohnik-hijhakalurni.
Himatjeminimkalu Hoyakalu tokanu wla tshinatshri: “Naluklu hetwamonrewlu, hi henekachlu yoxikaluru naluka”. Himka rukolukanuwnayehjixanna mukolukanuwnakanepni.
Klu tshinanu hapnanuxikalur-hohne hitsrukatekni Jeji Whene.
Jesus Hitskalajyawaklu Hiprihamyotatshri PiranapniWaneya Jesus wane hichpajyatka, satu hanjihohnewakapji hyatka.
Wane rawakanata satu jeji hiprihamyotatshri. Waneya satkaka wane hwakanatatshine haluk-hikolukanuwnakakletlu Moisés hiykole tshinanu. Wale tshinanu wla htshin-hepomhaletluna Jesus: — Ritshitkahe yineru satu rutskalajyawaka hapnanuxikalur-hohne?
Waneya Jesus hihitna, wla htshina: — Ha hixa, hipra carneiro kapna hijrujini hapnanuxikalur-hohne, hi he kapratu ptowruka kamha kapna hkochpajyawakaplu?
Seyni yineru carneiro yohnik-hijhakalurni! Hiyáhoni Moisés yonreru hitshitlu wepixkajyawaka hapnanuxikalur-hohne.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru jeji: — Pyosurukkanotanu. Waneya hyosurukkanotatka, ruhlewamyotatka, himyo pomtalu pixka rixatka.
Hiyáhoni wane ruchpakamxyana fariseu-ne waneya rujhahchinikanutatkana wannakakluko hanu rixa himukata hiylaletluna Jesus.
Jesus Hoyakalu Towreru Nuretkalurni PiranapniXye pirana rimaxinixka Jesus, wane ruchpajyatka. Hixolune yine homkahimtlu hiyrunu rutskalakna yeyixatshine.
Wan-rixa hpoyahokajyawakaplu Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshrini Isaías-ni tshinyawaka, wla htshinni mitshi:
“Xyetkani ntowreru nuretkaluru, namotleru, wale poyikowkakno. Niwejinri pixkonu nenekanru, Hoyakalu hapnokatlewle hapojinri pirana runkakletanu psol-tshijneyako.
Hi hyanhaklewatanu, hi hsaplewjetanu, hike yijnak-tokanutanru tsru poktshikakaya.
Katsluksu hichtshokatshri hi himlakanu, hiyrun-koxa lamparina mtserumerojijitu hi ruwakanu, hpaklutawa haté hikolukanuwnalu kayaxini potuko.
Wale hiwaka tshinanu ptowru tshijne hajene munanhanru riwekkajyawakapna.”
Jesus Hiyrunu Belzebu Tshinkaluru PiranapniWaneya satu jeji ranikanwakatluna Jesus, metkatu hiyrunu myanumatkatu klu tshinanu kkamtshiterni. Jesus hitskalakatkalu, retatnaka hiyrun-koxa hyinuwaka yanumletatka.
Hiyáhoni wane hwakanatatshine himyekahchinikanutatka, waneya repomhana: — Davi-ni whenrahe xye jeji?
Seyni fariseu-ne wale hjeminna wane htshinna: — Kamtshi pohire Belzebu tshinkaluru himukatleyma tshinanu hetko maleka ruknokna kamtshine.
Seyni Jesus himathetahchinikanutna hiyáhoni wane htshinna: — Ptowru tshijne rawa nikawnatshripa, pa hchinikanurutu hmixlenu tshinanna wane tshijne hajene. Hiyrun-koxa ho poktshi hajene ho pantshi hajene wannakakluko pnu pejnu rixahchinikanutna hi rumukata hwachaletna.
Hiyáhoni Satanás kamtshi hkamnixiniklunwa pnuko rixahchinikanuxinwana Satanás hayinetene hanhe rumukata pnute yaletanu htowuwle?
Hixa wan-tshinno Belzebu himukatleyma maleka nuknokna kamtshine. Hiyrun-koxa Belzebu himukatleyma maleka nuknokamkana kamtshine ha hixa hwuhenene katu hiwakaymahe kamtshine maleka ruknokjekanatna, kat-mixkonu tshinanu wan-rixna? Hiyáhoni hixako hwuhenene hikolukanunhi.
Seyni Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru towre tshinanuko kamtshine maleka nuknoka, hiyahokni himatanu Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hix-yehi rapokatka halikaka.
— Yineru hi himukata jihlokletlu satu jeji hixkolupji htshowhuxyaplu rimwaleru hma mostuhapkatkanuklunru hixkolu. Waneklu tsonu rumukata tshowhuretlu hipji hajeru.
— Hiyáhoni hita nmepixjetu, waleni nkamnitjeru. Hitayma mapatjetkatu, hkotspallewata.
Wale tshinanu wane ntshina: Ptowru hixatshri hektuwaka Hoyakalu mukchikhihlenreru hkamhini yineru, ptowru hixatshri hektutu htshinanwakaxiniplu Hoyakalu, ramtakahchinikanuxiko rektunu. Seyni katukta hektutu tshinanwakaxiniplu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hikeklu hohne ramtakahchinikanyehitkona rektunu.
Katuktako hektuwaka htshinanwakatlu Jeji Whene tshinkaluru, wanepnawakatshi ramtakahchinikanuxiko rektunu. Seyni katukta hektutu tshinanwakaxiniplu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru walepni hikeklu hohne ramtakahchinikanyehitkona rektunu, hi xawakni hohneko, hi wale hohne hinatshripako.
Hahmuna Hiyrunu Hisahi Hyapkakleta Jesus— Kihle sahiru hijhalu hahmuna kihleru. Hahmuna hektutu hi kihle sahiplu. Klu tshinanu ptowru hixatshri hahmuna pejnu rimathetka hisahi tshinanu.
Himnu kamaklewatatshri pixkalunhi! Hixa hike kihleru himukata tshinreta hektutu hixyawaka tshinanu. Klu tshinanu namtshi yanumaxyalu hix-potu raji hajeru.
Jeji kihleru, kihleru hkamha kihleru hihchinikanu rimrexinri tshinanu. Hiyrunu jeji hektutu, hektutu hkamha, hektutu rimretleru tshinanu.
— Seyni wane ntshinhi hixa, hapnokaxikolu hohnepa ptowru yineru htokanu yanumchaxinriko hikolukanunhi Hoyakalu yehiya.
Klu tshinanu htokanu tshinanu hpowratko ho htokanu tshinanu hikolujinwa.
Yine Hanjixyawaklu Hetkaluru PiranapniWaneya satkaka kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine hiyrun-koxa satkaka fariseu-ne wan-tshinru Jesus: — Kasruklewakleru, walukyi pixa satu hiyákolu pkamhiywaka.
Waneya Jesus hihitna: — Xawakni hiwekatshine hektutu kamhatshine potu, Hoyakalu tokanu majnakowaxikatshine hanjitmaklu satu hetkaluru seyni satu hetkalurupka tsonu nekhitanhi. Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshrini, Jonas tshinkalurni Hoyakalu henejyalu hetkaluru tsonupka nekhitanhi.
Jonas map-hohne, map-yetshno tsro chima nanwaka rawakanata hiyáhoni waneko pixka rixko Yineru Whene map-hohne, map-yetshno tshiji hitokote rawanu.
Hapnokaxikolu hohne hapojinipa Nínive hajene yotunotanu rukolukanuwnakakanhi hixa xawakni hiwekatshinhi klu tshinanu wanna hehchinikanutatka Jonas hiykole tokanu hjeminixkana. Xyekni hixa hetanu Jonas yohnik-himukatatshri.
Tsro phúroni sul sreta tshijne hajéroni howuk-tshijne tuchpajyani phuru Salomão-ni hasruklewle himatkalnu tjemyawakapa. Hiyáhoni jemahchinikanrewlu hohnepa tukolukanuna xye papko hiwekatshinepni. Haha hetanu, hewiru satu Salomão-ni yohnika kpohiru.
Hanu Rixyawaka Kamtshi Piranapni— Kamtshi yineru mane ruchpakamxini, hyanachata, popriwaka hyapachata. Rujhalu rapnanuxyawaka seyni hi rukchiklu.
Hiyáhoni wla htshina: “Nopjitapyawaka nsatokanutnak-honuka.” Waneya rapoka. Rukchiklu satolotkaluru, hihlepokoluru.
Hiyáhoni wla rixa. Hya waneya ranikna pimrine waleyma sete-ne kamtshine wale yohnik-hektunu kamhatshine. Hjihlokna, wane rawna. Ralipretka rallikanatatka xye jeji rekamtshitewle pnute. Waneko pixka rixanu xyeklu papko hwatshine hektune.
Waneya satu wan-tshinru: — Petanu, punro pepurun-koxa maleka rawna. Raluk-hiynumsaletyina.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshina: — Katnihe nunro hiyrunu nomolene?
Waneya rasruklene hyokhinwakata, waneya wla htshina: — Haha hetanu, hewitkana nunro hiyrunu nomolene.
Klu tshinanu Nuru tenhohne hajeru halujyawaka kamhatshine wannani nepuru, nepuro, nunro.
Hitaklu Tataji Jiplaljekleru PiranapniWale hohne potuko Jesus hipji ruchpajyatka waneya Galileia powhastsi hyatka. Waneya htuplatatka.
Seyni hixolune yine hapatjeyehitlu Jesus hiyáhoni sato kanawa hpokownatka htuplaxyawakapa. Waneya hixolune yine ksatuko yopkaka.
Waneya hi heppika pirana rasrukna Jesus yapkaklu piranayma. Waneya Jesus wan-tshinna: — Satu jitaklewakleru hichpakamta rutaklewaxyawakapa.
Waneya ruplaljetatajixinri, pimriji hatnu hapostsi hapoktatajita waneya kochitshine nikloktatajitanruna.
Pimriji sotlu hoho mteno tshijiwaka rapoktatajita. Waneya ruptshekhapkatamka klu tshinanu mteno tshijiwaka ruptshejya.
Hiyáhoni ruchpajinixka tkatshi, hjimanatkalu, ruprihanatka hitaklukaka hma matskinu tshinanu.
Pimriji kona yehi hapoktatajita. Waneya konaymakananuko htseruwna hiyáhoni hkakmokanatkalu.
Seyni hitataji kihle tshijiwaka hapokatshinetka hixolewnatka hiyáhoni satkakaji pejnu tshinanu cem-ji rawatka ho sessenta-ji ho trinta-ji rawatka.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinna: — Kajnakopnahi hyijnakoxyawakapa, hyijnakotanu.
Jesus Hasrujyawaklu Klu Hyapkakleta Jiplaljekleru PiranaWaneya Jesus hasruklene Jesus-stsi hapoka waneya repomhaluna: — Klu tshinanhe yapkaklu piranayma punkakletna wanna?
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinatkana: — Hixamka henekka himaxyawakaplu mimatyehitkotu pirana tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka pirana seyni wanna hike.
Klu tshinanu katukta himatjemlu, Hoyakalu pnute rimatjemkakanru wale haté rimatjempotuxyawakaplu. Seyni mimatjemkatu haté rimatjemlejiji hkonanu Hoyakalu.
Wale tshinanukni yapkaklu piranayma nasrukna. Klu tshinanu halikaka retmakna seyni hi rapkathojitna; hjemmakna seyni hi hyijnakopiratna hiyrun-koxa hi rimatjempiratna.
Hoyakalu tokanu hinkaklewatatshri Isaías-ni wane pixka hixatshine yonyehijekanata, wane htshina: “Hyijnakotmaklu seyni hi himatjemanru; Hetmaklu seyni hi himathetanru.
Hoyakalu wan-tshina: Klu tshinanu xye yine hchinikanu hi himatjempirata; ruchyajnakotna hiyrunu ruchyayhaletna. Wane hmixkanuklunumkana, rumukata hetletmakna hiyrun-koxa rumukata yijnakoletmakna. Wanna hchinikanu himukata himatjemletamka hiyáhoni rehchinikanutanumkana numukata hitskalakletmakna.”
Waneya pnuteko htshina Jesus: — Seyni hihlewahchinikanyehitka hixa! Klu tshinanu hiyhale hapkathojita hiyrun-koxa hijnako yijnakota.
Hichinikanru xako xye: Híxona Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshinni hiyrun-koxa pimrine potukalunni haluk-hetletmaklu hixa hetanru seyni hi rumukatatkana; hiyrun-koxa raluka yijnakoletmaklu hixa yijnakotanru seyni hi hyijnakotluna.
— Hyijnakotanu himatjemyawakaplu yapkaklu jiplaljekleru pirana.
Hatnu hapostsi hapoktatajitatshri yaholni Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka pirana jematshri. Hjemmaka seyni hi rimatjemlu. Waneya runa Satanás kamtshi hkonyawakaplu Hoyakalu tokanu raji hitakkaluru.
Sotlu yehi hapoktatajitatshine wannani Hoyakalu tokanu jematshine, waneklukawa potuko tsru poyikowluyma yoptotatshinetkani
seyni pchini tsonu hwatshinepni klu tshinanu matskitni wale. Runini yahtaletlewlu ho salewaktshi Hoyakalu pirana tshinanu, ramtakanruna tokantshi hjemlerna.
Waneya hitataji kona yehi hapoktatajitatshine wanna Hoyakalu tokanu jematshine pixkalune seyni kojwawaktshi xye hohne hajeru tshinanu ho pohirewnalu yokwire hakanhinipa, hkakmokannatkalu hiyáhoni hi hjiwatanatkana.
Seyni kihle tshijiwaka hapoktatajitatshine wannani Hoyakalu tokanu jematshine, rimatjemluna hiyrun-koxa hjiwatanutkana: satu trinta, satu sessenta, satu cem kata pnute hjiwatna.
Kchana Yapkaklu PiranapniJesus satu yapkaklu rutakatnaka, wla htshina: — Tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka satu jeji kihleru tataji hsana jitaklewakleru pixkalutni.
Seyni ptowru yineru himkakako pchinika, hkamnitjeru hsana hapoka waneya kchanatataji rutaka trigo-tataji hanikajiteya waneya hyatka.
Waneya susanateru htowrene yanwakatlu waneya wla htshinruna: “Tsru Hixikatshriwa, hi he kihletatajiru putaka pusanateya? Ha hanhe ruchpajya xye kchana?”
— Waneya ruhita: “Satu jeji nkamnitjeru wan-hixlu.” — Waneya htowrene hepomhalu: “Palukluhe wopliptshexyawakaplu?”
— Waneya ruhitna: “Hike klu tshinanu kchanaptshe hoplixini, trigo koxa hoplitanu.”
Hetacha tseruwnaletanna wanna hepi haté ramikolu papkopa. Waneya waneklu papko nunkakanna hamatshinepa: Mitshikananhapka, hapatjetanru kchana waneya hostuptajetanru tshitshipawa hiknokanru. Wane pnute hapatjetanru trigo, rimrexikowakapji hitakanru.”
Mostarda-tataji PiranapniJesus satu yapkaklu rutakatnaka, wla htshina: — Tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka mostarda-tataji pixkalutni. satu jeji haniklo, rusanate rutaklo,
Mostarda-tataji honukla pimri tataji kayaho mtsernurut-potu. Seyni ttseruwniniklunu wala pot-tseruwnatshroni ptowru hejnuji munaya. Hahmuna tixnawa waneya kochitshine teno yapatshine hina toplukaka hkamhachalexyawakna.
Chitshponatshri PiranapniSatu yapkaklu hkamhatnaka Jesus, wla htshina: — Tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka tserutatshri pixka rixa. Sato suxo hwalu. Mapa chiwatupso trigo pahi tyapjetlu haté psolujpako chitshponatka.
Klu Tshinanhe Jesus Yapkaklewaxyawaka PiranapniXyekaka Jesus yapkakluyma hinkakna hixolune yine. Yapkaklu minjeyma hi runkakna.
Wan-rixa hakanhaleta hpoyahokajyawakapa Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshrini tokanu, wla htshina mitshi: “Yapkakluyma nyanumatanu, xye tshijne hiyakotkoklunukawa yohimakanatkaluru pirana nunkakletanu.”
Jesus Hasrujyawaklu Klu Hyapkakleta Kchana PiranaWaneya hixolune yehi ruchpajya, pantshi hjihlokatka. Waneya rasruklene yanwakatlu, wla htshinruna: — Puhle hinkakletanwu kchana hsana hajeru yapkakle pirana.
Waneya wla htshinna: — Kihletatajiru jitakakleru walekatkani Jeji Whene.
Hsanni xye tshijne. Kihletatajiru wannakatkani Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hayinetene. Kchana walekatkani Hoyakalu kamnitjeru hayinetene,
hiyrunu hkamnitjeru walekni Satanás. Ramikowaka walekni xye tshijne nikawninri hohnepa hiyrunu hamatshine wannakni hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrerune tenhohne hajene.
Kchanaptshe hoplikkaluru yoxijikolu pixka rixanna xye tshijne nikawninri hohnepa.
Jeji Whene yokanatanna hiwejikalune htowrerune tenhohne hajene rapatjexyawakapluna ptowru hitspekaklewatatshri hiyrunu hektutu kamhatshine Jeji Whene pohirewaxyawakaya.
Waneya tshitshmero ruknokanna wane rawanu tsru tshiyahlu haskiyhiru koxa.
Hiyáhoni potukalunetka hatajiwnanu tkatshi pixka Rurna pohirewaxyawakaya. Katukta kajnakopnapa hyijnakoxyawaka, hyijnakotanru.
Halukkaluru Yohimatkaluru Piranapni— Tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka satu halukkaluru yohimatkaluru campo-ya pixkalutni. Waneya satu jeji hikchijiniklunru hyohimatatnaklu. Waneya hpoyiknu tshinanu, hyatka, rimwaleru psoluka ruchankatka, wale campo ranjixyawakapa.
Pérola Piranapni— Hiyrunuko tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka satu kmaronewakleru tuwutu kwenuru pérola tshinkaluru hijhatshri pixkalutni.
Satu pérola kwenur-potuko rukchijiniklunu, hyatka, rimwaleru psoluka ruchankatka wale pérola ranjixyawakapa.
Tarrafa Piranapni— Hiyrunukotnaka, tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka satu tarrafa pixkalutni. Hipowha ruknokkoklunutka waneya ptowru hixatshro chima hkachita.
Katsepo rixinixka, kchimahaklerune hwanha hkochpaxyatkalona. Waneya htuplatna, hkotspalatlona. Chima kihlero chiwatu rutakanna seyni chima muhleto ruknokachatna.
Waneko pixka rixanu xye tshijne nikawninri papko. Hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrerune tenhohne hajene hapokanu hkotspalaxyawakapna hektutu kamhatshine potukaluneya.
Waneya tshitshmero ruknokanna hektutu kamhatshine tsru tshiyahluyma raskiyhixyawakna koxa.
Jesus Hasruklewle Herotu Hiyrunu Rasruklewakanaxyawaka PiranapniHiyáhoni Jesus hepomhana rasruklene, wla htshinna: — Xye piranakaklahe himatjematka? Waneya ruhitluna: — Hehe.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinna: — Ptowru Moisés hiykole yonatkaluru hasruklewatatshri tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka himatyehitatshri satu kapjiru pixkalutni. Kapjiru pantshi hejnu herotu hiyrun-koxa hejnu tsrutsoleji himretawaka hkochpajyalu.
Jesus Nazaré Poktshi Rawyawaka PiranapniXyekaka yapkaklu pirana rali hinkaklexinixka, pnute hya.
Waneya Jesus htseruwniywaka poktshi Nazaré tshinikowaka rapokatka. Hyinuwaka hasruklewleta hanjihohnewakapjiya. Waneya ptowruneka himyekahchinikanuta. Waneya repomhakakna: — Hanhe ruchpajya rimatkalnu hiyrunu pixkontshi hetkalurkaka hkamhiywaka?
Hi he hahmuna chpatako kamruretakleru José tshinkaluru whenni wale? Hi he Maria tshinkalurokni runro hiyrunu repurune Tiago, José, Simão hiyrunu Judas tshinkalune?
Wale tshinanu hike hijhatkalu Jesus. Seyni Jesus wla tshinatkana: — Satu muphujewnakatuwa pirana hinkakletatshri kahwakpiratka ptowruchayaka seyni waleko htshijneya ho waleko himolene tsonuyma hi hkahwakpiratka.
Hiyáhoni hi hixo hetkalurkaka hkamha Jesus wale poktshiya hmalixlenna tshinanu.
João Batista Hipninri PiranapniWaneya phuru Herodes, Galileia tshijne pohire, hjemyehitlu Jesus kamhajekanatanru pirana,
waneya wla htshinatkana htowrene: — Xyekni hetko João Batista-ni; hipuktshi riwekkajikatka! Wale tshinanu tsru kpixkonru xawakni.
Wane htshina klu tshinanu Herodes preso rutakjixniru João-ni, rostujixniru waneya preso rutakniru Herodes repuru Filipe hnunrotakanatanro Herodias tshinkaluro tshinanu.
Klu tshinanu João-ni mitshi wan-tshinatkalu Herodes hinanchitkalurni pimwiywaklo.
Herodes-mka haluk-hiylaletniru João-ni seyni hpikna yine klu tshinanu yine kahwakniru satu Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshrini.
Seyni Herodes hohneru tshinanu Herodias tshinkaluro hchitsho hahsata wanna hanikajite waneya Herodes hikchikhihlenupotutlo.
Tpoyikoxyawaklu tshinanu runkaklexyalo kluneruktako tanjitanu renekanro.
Waneya tunro hanjijixlo wla ttshinyawaka: — Xawakni potuko hewi penekanno prato-tlo João Batista.
Waneya phuru wamonuwahchinikanuta tanjixyawaklu tshinanu. Seyni runkaklexyalo htshanixlene hetanu tshinanu, renekjixatkalo.
Htowrene hyokanata hkastaknojixyawakapluna João-ni preso yehiya.
Waneya makloji nwaka João-ni jiwu prato-tlo ranijyana waneya tunro yehi taniklu.
Waneya João-ni hasruklene hapoka ranikmanetatkaluna. Hkapnatatkaluna. Waneya runkakapatkaluna Jesus.
Jesus Hixolune Yine Rohluxyawaka PiranapniWaneya xye pirana hjemini, kanawa hpokowna kahnete poktshiri hya rapaluchaxyawakapa. Seyni hixolune yine jempiranyehitlu wane hyiywakapa hiyáhoni poktshikaka ruchpajyatkana, tshijiko romkahixyaluna.
Waneya ruptejinixka Jesus, retna hixolune. Retwamonutatkana rutskalakna ptowruneko yeyixatshine.
Waneya kayi rixinixka Jesus hasruklene hapyehitlu. Wane htshinruna: — Kayixkani hiyrunu hewi wwiywaka kahnete poktshirni. Pyokanatanna yine hixolune poktshikaka nwaka hyiywakapna rukchijyawakapluna hnikanrupna.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinna: — Hi rujhaluna hyiywakapna, hixa henekanna hnikanrupna.
Waneya ruhitna: — Nijittshi wimwalerutka cinco pão hepi chima tsonu.
Waneya wane htshinna rasruklene: — Hita nwakatshi hanikanru.
Waneya htuplajixna ptowruneka peklomta hoho. Waneya Jesus kochtsheklu cinco pão, hepi chim-koxa. Tenhohne hyihata hpoyahnutlu Hoyakalu. Waneya hjiknajrotlu pão. Rasruklene reneklu waneya hixolune yine rapsatna rasruklene.
Waneya ptowruneko nikatka. Jinanutkana. Waneya hkochtshekluna pão-ni hixetatshrini, chim-koxni, doze chiwatu htsepotana.
Nikatshine pejnu cinco mil jejine, suxone mturune hi hitakyahokka.
Jesus Honha Hoho Hyanamxyawaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus hixolune yokanatka pchinika hkosekjixna rasruklene pa sreta powha hkopruhaxyawakapna kanawaya.
Hixolune rali yokanrexinixka Jesus, walepka himriji hya ranjihohnexyawakapa. Kayi rixinixka wale tsonu wane hwakanata,
seyni kanawa hownahatkalo hiyrunu tsru kanniphalu satkajyawaklo tshinanu tenoplojhalu yotkajimtlo kanawa.
Waneya hoprikako Jesus yanwakatna rasruklene, tsru powha honha hoho hyanamta.
Rexiniklunruna Jesus honha hoho hyanamxyawaka, hpikpotuthonukna. Tsru pikluyma wla htshin-saplewletna: — Samentshitkani!
Seyni waneklukawa potuko Jesus wan-tshinna: — Hixkohchinikanuphi, Hitni! Hi hpikanu.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru: — Punanu. Hiyáhoni Pedro honha hoho yinuwaka yanwaklexyalu Jesus.
Seyni hixko nniphalu hjeminixka, hpikatka, hyinuwaka himxiklemtanatka waneya wla htshin-saplewleta: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, pepixanno nmahyejyawakanupa!
Waneklukawa potuko Jesus homyokanwakatlu Pedro, hkachitlu. Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Pixa pso halixle jijiryi! Klu tshinanhe putuk-munanhaletno?
Waneya kanawa hyohrejinixkana, kanniphalu hitukamtatka.
Waneya rasruklene kanawa hwakanatatshine yoptsojityehitlu Jesus. Wla htshina himalwuretluna: — Pixni halikaka Hoyakalu Whenyi!
Genesaré Tshijne Rawyawaka Jesus PiranapniWaneya rali kopruhalexinixkana, Genesaré tshijne rapokna.
Waneya wale tshijne hajene himathetatkalu Jesus hiyáhoni hpohitatkaluna Jesus hapojyawaka pirana wale sreta psoluka. Yeyixatshine ptowruneko ranikanwakatluna
hiyrunu ranjipotutluna yeyixatshine hyotnejyawakluna Jesus mkalustsipto waneya katukta yotneklu rutskalhatka.
Judeu Hitsrukatenni Hasruklewle PiranapniWaneya satkaka fariseu-ne hiyrunu satkaka kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine Jerusalém hiyakaxikatshine yanwakatlu Jesus. Waneya repomhaluna:
— Haklu tshinanhe pasruklene majnakowaxyalu tsrunni hasruklewle pirana? Klu tshinanu merojikanekwa nika!
Waneya Jesus hihitna, wla htshinna: — Klu tshinan-koxhe hixa majnakowaxyalu Hoyakalu tokanu tsrunni hasruklewle pirana homkahixyawaka?
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu wan-tshina: “Pkahwakpiratanru puru, punro.” Hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu wan-tshina: “Katukta hektuwaka tshinanwakatlu ruru, runro, walepni hiylatkona.”
Seyni hixa wan-tshina: Satu jeji himwinri pa hixanu repixyawakaplu ruru, runro seyni wale wan-tshina rimwaleru henekachlu Hoyakalunupa,
hi rujhalu ruru runro repixyawakapa. Hiyáhoni hiknokachatlu Hoyakalu tokanu tsrunni hasruklewle pirana hkamhiywakapa.
Hixachatatshinhi! Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri Isaías-ni hinkakletpotuthi hixa. Wla htshina yonatkaluru:
“Nyi yine himalwutno hinama tsonuyma seyni hihchinikanuyna howukayno.
Hmahijeru himalwuretnona; klu tshinanu rasrujikolna yineru hinanchireru tsonu.”
Waneya Jesus tomhana hixolune yine. Wane htshinna: — Hyijnakotanno himatjemyawakapa.
Hinama jihlojikatshri hi pitshotlu yineru Hoyakalu hetanuya seyni yineru pitshotjeru halikaka namtshi hichpakhimaxikatshri.
Waneya rasruklene Jesus yehistsi hyana wla htshinruna: — Pimathe fariseu-ne hima rumtuwnahchinikanutna ptshinyawaka tshinanu?
Waneya Jesus wla tshin-hihretna: — Ptowru hitaklu Nuru tenhohne hajeru mutakanutu hitskihi potuko roplijiko.
Hi hkojwakahchinikanutanu wanna tshinanu; wannakni mayhalene kosekatshine. Mayhaletu kosejinri mayhaletu waneya wanna hepi mayhalene kapna rujrukanna.
Waneya Pedro wan-tshina: — Punkakanwu klu htshina xye yapkaklu pirana.
Waneya Jesus hepomhana, wla htshina: — Wanepnawaka hi he himatjemawa?
Hi he himatjemlu xye — yineru nikleru, mitshikananu hinama hyapa, wane pnute hisatu hya waneya himane ruchpajya?
Seyni tokantshi hinama hichpajikatshri hihchinikanu ruchpajya walekni pitshotlu yineru.
Klu tshinanu hihchinikanu hichpajikatshri hektutu chinikantshikaka, hiylalewlu, himopatlewlu, hapoklewlu, tshowhuwlu, yokwijrewlu, hiyrun-koxa hektuwaka htshinanwakaxyawaklu Hoyakalu.
Walekaka halikaka pitshotlu yineru seyni merojikatukwa hnijini yineru hike.
Canaã Hajero Halixlewle PiranapniWaneya Jesus wane hichpajya, Tiro hiyrunu Sidom tshinikowakastsi hyamta.
Seyni Jesus hike tshina. Hiyáhoni rasruklene hyehistsi rapokna waneya hipokananu ranjitluna, wla htshinna: — Psatkakamtanro xako klu tshinanu hixa hatjini hi tutuka saplewjeremxya.
Waneya ruhitna, wla htshinna: — Nyokanatka carneiro-ne hamhatshine israel-nerune tsonu tshinanu.
Waneya tunatka suxo, tyoptsojityehitlu Jesus, waneya wla ttshinru: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, pepixanunno.
Waneya ruhitlo, wla htshinro: — Hi kihleru hkonikowakna mturune hnikanruna kawene nwaka ruknojikowakapa.
Waneya wla ttshinru: — Wanekni, Tsru Hixikatshriwa, seyni haté kawe whenen-koxa niklu nijittshi hpuratjeru mesa-te hijrujikatshri.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinro: — Suxo, palixle tsru potuko. Panijitanru penekko. Waneklukawa potuko tutskalhatka tchitsho.
Hixolune Rutskalajyawaka Jesus Galileia Powha Sretaya PiranapniWaneya Jesus wane ruchpajya, Galileia powhastsi hyapakananumta. Waneya satu himriji ratskotatka, wane htuplaxya.
Hixolune yine hanikanwakatlu satkaka myape, satkaka mayhaletu, satkaka myanumatkatu, satkaka myankatu hiyrunu hixo pimrinkaka yeyixatshine ranikna waneya Jesus jixi yehistsi rutakna. Waneya Jesus ptowruneka hitskalakatka.
Hixolune hetlu myanumatkanekananu yanumaxyawaka, hiyrunu myapenekananu kihletka, retna myankanekananu yanyawakatka hiyrun-koxa mayhalenekananu hetatka. Waneya xye rexinna, rimyekahchinikanutna, rimalwutatkaluna Israel Hoyakalute.
Jesus Quatro Mil Yine Hohluxyawaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus tomhana rasruklene, wla htshinna: — Netwamonutna nyi yine. Map-hohne hitaymana hiyrunu malechayna hnikanruna. Hi naluka yokanretna mnikkane hma muhrojyawakanupna hatnu hapoya.
Waneya rasruklene wan-tshinru: — Hanhe wixa hikchikletanru pão hewi kahnete poktshiri hixolune yine wohluxyawaka?
Waneya Jesus hepomhana: — Hi pejnu pão-pro himwa hixa? Ruhitluna, wla htshinruna: — Sete pão-pro wimwa hiyrunu satkaka chima mtseroto.
Waneya Jesus tshiji tuplakjixna hixolune yine.
Waneya hkochtsheklu sete pão hiyrunu chimane. Rali poyahnutlexini, hjiknajrotlu, rasruklene reneklu waneya rasruklene heneksatna hixolune yine.
Waneya ptowru yineru nikatka, jinanutkana. Waneya rasruklene tsepotlu sete chiwatu nijittshi hixetatshrini.
Nikatshine pejnu quatro mil jejine, suxone mturune hi hitakyahokka.
Jesus hali yokanrexinixkana hixolune, kanawa hpokowna, Magadã sreta hya.
Hetkalurkaka Ranjixyawakna Yine PiranapniWaneya satkaka fariseu-ne hiyrunu satkaka saduceu-ne yanwakatlu Jesus retumhiywakapluna. Ranjitluna satu hetkaluru Hoyakalu pixkonu tshinanuya hkamhiywakapa.
Seyni Jesus wla tshina: — Kayi rixinixka, wla htshina: “Kihle hohnehetkoplu klu tshinanu tenhohne sero kaynolu.”
Waneya yetshpotukawa wla htshina: “Hinhetkopatkani klu tshinanu sero hohneru, hiyrunu mapchahlu.” Tenhohne hyihaxini hixa himathetlu ho kihle hohneplu ho hike seyni hi himathetlu xye hohnekaka hetlerutka hanu rixa.
Xyeklu papko hiwekatshine hektutu kamhatshine potu, Hoyakalu tokanu majnakowaxikatshine hanjitmaklu. Seyni hi satukna hetkaluru rekhitkona seyni Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshrini, Jonas tshinkalurni hetkalurutepka rekhitkona pa hohne. Waneya Jesus hiknokamtna, hyatka.
Fariseu-ne Hiyrunu Saduceu-ne Tserutjeru PiranapniWaneya pa sreta wnahlu rapojinixkana, pão hi ruchinik-hanikletna.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinna: — Xako fariseu-ne hiyrunu saduceu-ne tserutjeru.
Waneya rasruklene yinuwaka hihjekakleta wannakakluko, waneya wla htshinna: — Wale wan-tshina klu tshinanu pão hi wanikatka.
Seyni Jesus yijnakotna htshinyawakna waneya repomhana: — Hixa pso halixle jijirunhi, klu tshinanhe hihjekaka pão hma manijyawakanu tshinanu?
Hi he himatjemawalu? Hi he hichiniklu hanu nixa hohluretna cinco mil yine cinco pão-yma? Hi pejnuhe chiwatu htsepota nijittshi hixetatshrini?
Ho hanu nixa hohluretna quatro mil yine sete pão-yma? Hi pejnuhe chiwatu htsepota nijittshi hixetatshrini?
Hi he himatjema pão pirana hi nkochtsheka? Seyni xako fariseu-ne hiyrunu saduceu-ne tserutjeru.
Waneklu rimatjematkaluna Jesus hijretna fariseu-ne hiyrunu saduceu-ne hasruklewle pirana tshinanu klu tshinanu rasruklewlena tserutatshri pão hitakkaluru pixka rixa, psolujpako hchitshponkaka.
Waneya ruhitluna, wla htshinruna: — Satkaka yineru wan-tshina pixa João Batista-yi; satuko wan-tshina Elias-yi; satuko wan-tshinyi pixa Jeremias tshinkaluryi ho satu mitshikawni Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshriyi.
Waneya Jesus hepomhana: — Ha hixa, kathe hkahwakno?
Waneya Pedro hihita: — Pixni Messias-yi, Hoyakalu hiwekatshri whenyi.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru: — Poyikowatatshripyi, Simão, João whene. Klu tshinanu xye pirana hi yine hekhityi seyni Puru tenhohne hajeru hiphujetlu.
Hiyáhoni nunkakyi: Pixni Pedro-yi. Hita halixatshine xye sotlu hoho panawaxikatshinepni. Hiyrunu hipuktshi himukatle hi himukata halliretanru.
Tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka yohpukapre nenekanyi pixa. Klunerukta pimaletanu xye tshijneya, Hoyakalu himaletanru tenhohneya. Hiyrun-koxa klunerukta pitshitanu xye tshijneya, Hoyakalu hitshitanru tenhohneya.
Waneya Jesus towutna rasruklene hike hma munkajyawakanuplu Messias rixinri pirana.
Jesus Hinkaklexyawaklu Rupninri Hiyrunu Riwejinritnaka PiranaWale hohnekananuko Jesus yinuwaka hinkakletna rasruklene Jerusalém rujha yalexyawaka pirana hiyrunu hsalewniywaka hixo pa hixanu tshinanuya pirana tsrukakalune judeu-ne hiyrunu tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne myoya, kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine myoy-koxa. Hiyrun-koxa ruylatko seyni map-hohne rixinri riwekanutnaka pirana.
Waneya Pedro haniklu Jesus kahnete, hyinuwaka hiykoletlu. Waneya Pedro wla tshinru Jesus: — Hikeklu, Tsru Hixikatshriwa! Wale hikeklu hohne rakanhayehitanyi!
Waneya Jesus hiprotakanwakatlu, wla htshinru: — Pasujinno, Satanás pixkalutu. Nutspekakjermakyi; pixa hi Hoyakalu hchinikanu pimwa seyni jeji hchinikanu halikaka pimwa.
Jesus Homkahitatshri Haluklu H-cruz-te Rutaykopixyawaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus wla tshinna rasruklene: — Satu yineru haluk-homkahrexinno, rujhanru wale ralujyawaka ruchoxyawaka, rutaykopitanru h-cruz-te waneya romkahitanno hita.
Klu tshinanu katukta haluk-hiwekkakletanru riwejinri, ramtakanru riwekle; seyni katukta hita tshinanu hamtakanru riwekle riwekanu.
Hanhe rixa hepixletlu yineru xye tshijne hihlenu psoluka hkayaxiniklunu seyni riwejinri ramtakanuna? Kluhe xawaka ripekotanru satu jeji riwejinri tshinanu?
Klu tshinanu Jeji Whene hiyrunu hiwejikalune htowrene tenhohne hajene hapokanu Hoyakalu hoyaknuyma. Waneya renekanru satkaka yineru hkamrure wenru.
Halikaka ntshinhi, satkaka hewi hajeru hma mupnaknukawa, retanru Jeji Whene hapokatshritka waleko hpohirewaxyawakaya.
Jesus Pnuko Hixamanexyawaka Rasruklene Hetanu PiranapniWaneya pa semana pnutejiji hiknohatka Jesus, Pedro, Tiago, hiyrunu repuru João ranika. Satu mriji tenolu hkankatkana wannapkatkani.
Waneya Jesus yokmanhojitatka. Katajhojru tkatshi pixka. Himkal-koxa klata, klat-potuko rixa katalu pixka.
Waneklukawa potuko hepi jejine hakanhatka, satni Moisés-ni tshinkalurni, satni Elias-ni tshinkalurni. Riynumsatluna Jesus.
Waneya Pedro wan-tshinru Jesus: — Kasruklewakleru, kihleru wiko wwiywaka. Hayeri wkamheru mapa pantshi; satu pixanupa, satu Moisés-nupa, satu Elias-nupa.
Wane htshinakanaxiniwa hohimkohi hichyatna. Waneya hohimkohi hitokote ruchpajyatka tokantshi wla tshinatshri: — Xyekni nowhene nalukleru. Hyijnakotanru hanukta htshinanhi!
Tokantshi hjeminixkana, tsru hpiklena tshinanu tshiji rutspakhojitna.
Seyni Jesus yanwakatna, hkamrutna waneya wla htshinna: — Hyopkakanu. Hike hpikanu.
Waneya teno hyihaxinixkana, hikeko retna seyni Jesus tsonu.
Elias-ni Hapojinri PiranapniWaneya himriji hserpijinixkana, Jesus hijretna, wla htshinna: — Hetakanatanru xako hike hinkakanu haté hma miwekkanuko pchini Jeji Whene hipuktshiya.
Waneya rasruklene hepomhatkalu: — Klu tshinanhe kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine wan-tshina Elias hapka hapokanu?
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinna: — Halikakni, Elias hapokanu ruhlexyawakaplu ptowruko.
Seyni wane ntshinhi Elias hapokatka seyni hi rimathetluna seyni ptowruka raluk-hixlexyawakluna rixatkaluna. Waneko pixka rixanu Jeji Whene, hsalewnanu wanna tshinanuya.
Waneyatka rasruklene himatjematkalu, himka Elias pirana runkakleta seyni João Batista-ni pirana halikaka runkakleta.
Jesus Mturu Kamtshite Hakajyawaka PiranapniWaneya hixolune yehi rapojinixkana, satu jeji yanwakatlu Jesus, hyoptsojityehitlu, wla htshinru:
Pasruklene nwaka nanikatkalu seyni hi rumukata hiskalakletluna.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshina: — Malixaklenhi, hektutu kkamhaklerunhi xyeklu papko hwatshinhi. Haté hi pejnu hohnekta nimwanhi hixa? Haté hi pejnu hohnekta nakotanhi? Waneya wla htshinru tsru: — Wkata panikanru pituru.
Waneya Jesus towutlu kamtshi mturu ruchpajyawakapa hiyáhoni kamtshi hichpakatka, waneklukawa potuko mturu hitskalhatka.
Waneya rasruklene yanwakatlu Jesus, wannapka rixinixkana, repomhanruna, wla htshinruna: — Klu tshinanhe hi wumukata hiknokletlu kamtshi?
Jesus hihitna: — Klu tshinanu hmalixlenu tshinanu. Halikaka ntshinhi, mostarda-tataji pso rixiniklunu halixle waneya himukata xye himriji wla tshinreta: “Wane puchpajini, klanu pyanu.” Waneyamka wane potuko rixanu. Hikemkapni hma mumukatanutu.
[Seyni xye pixkalutu hi hiknokka, hanjihohneru hiyrunu hohajirewlu tshinanu tsonu.]
Jesus Hinkakletahnapuxyawaklu Rupninri Riwejinixnaka Pirana Hiyrunukotnaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus hiyrunu rasruklene hapatjexinixka, wla htshinna: — Jeji Whene tshinkaluru yine renekko.
Ruylatanruna seyni map-hohne rixinri riwekkakotka. Waneya rasruklene wamonuwnapotutatka.
Hoyakalupji Hijhawenre Hwenuxyawaka Jesus PiranapniWaneya Jesus rasrukleneyma Cafarnaum poktshi hapojinixka, Hoyakalupji jijhawenruklerune yanwakatlu Pedro waneya repomhaluna: — Hi he pasrukjeru wenutanru Hoyakalupji hijhawenre?
Waneya Pedro hihitna, wla htshina: — Hehe, hwenutlu. Waneya pantshi hjihlokamxinixka Pedro, Jesus hapka yanumatatka, wla htshin-hepomhaletlu: — Kluhe pukchika pixa, Pedro? Kathe hijha wenutletlu hijhawenuxikolu xye tshijne phurute tshinanu? Ho wale tshijne hajene ho pa tshijne hichpajikatshine?
Waneya Pedro wan-tshin-hihretlu: — Pnu tshijne hichpajikatshine wenutna. Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Hiyáhoni wale tshijne hajene hi wenutlu hijhawenuxikolu.
Seyni wma jihejyawakanupna nyi yine, hipowha pyanu, pkowtshohtapanu. Waneya mitshikananu pkachrero chima, pkohreknamatanro waneya pukchikanro proji tiyiro prata kamhikolu hixanu wujhawenuxikolu poyaho wenutlexyawaka pso. Waneya proji tiyiro panikanu, pwenutapanru wujhawenuxikolu hita tshinanu hiyrunu pixa tshinanu.
Kat-pothe Hijhakaluru Hoyakalu Pohirewaxyawakaya PiranapniWaneklu papko Jesus hasruklene yanwakatlu Jesus, waneya repomhaluna, wla htshinna: — Katnihe hijhakalur-potu tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka tshinanu?
Waneya satu mturu hkachita Jesus, hyopkakkaklu wanna hanikajite.
Waneya wla htshina: — Halikaka ntshinhi, mturune pixka hma mixkanuklunu, hikeklu hohne tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka hjihlokanu.
Hiyáhoni katukta mujhakotu hikahwajnawa xye mturu pixka, walekni hijhakalur-potu tenhohne pohirewaxyawakaya.
Hiyrun-koxa katukta hihle yoptoletlu xye mturu nhiwaka tshinanu hit-koxa hyoptotanu.
Himtuwna Halixlekakatshri Piranapni— Seyni katukta himtuwna halixlekakna nalixjene mtserkakanewa, kihlepotmaklu tsru sotlu rostunojixikowaka waneya mar powha ruknojikowaka.
Hektupotna rixje yine xye tshijne hajene hektuwkakatshine. Hi rumukata himaletkota hitspetkalurukaka. Seyni hektumkalu wale yineru kojwakahchinikanrewatatshri!
Pimyo ho pijixi tshinanu pumtuwnini, pkastakanru, puknokanru. Klu tshinanu kihlepotmaklu mtsoji ho myape hiwekkakko, hepi myolu ho hepi jixiru tshitshmero hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa hiknokko.
Hiyrun-koxa piyhale tshinanu pumtuwnini, pkochpakanru, puknokanru. Klu tshinanu kihlepotmaklu pa yhalepkalutu hiwekkajikowaka, hepi yhaleru tshitshmero hiknokko.
Ovelha Pupjetatshro Piranapni— Xako hi heyikanru satu nyi mturune klu tshinanu wane ntshinhi, hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrene tenhohne hajene wanna tshinanu psol-hohneko rethojitluna Nuru tenhohne hajeru.
[Klu tshinanu Jeji Whene xye tshijne hinatka riwekkajyawakaplu pupjetatshri.]
— Klu hkahwaka hixa? Satu jeji cem ovelha rimwini seyni sato ramtajini, hi he pimri hiprane noventa e nove, ruknokamtanu kahnete poktshi rujhapyawakaplo pupjetatshro?
Waneya rukchijiniplo ovelha hamhakanatatshro, hpoyikowpotuta. Halikaka ntshinhi, wale himuwpotuta wala hamhakanatatshro tshinanu, pimri hiprane noventa e nove mamhakane pnute rukchijyawaklo tshinanu.
Waneko pixka rix-koxa Hirtshi tenhohne hajeru, hi raluklu satu mturu hamhiywaka.
Hanu Rixa Hepixletka Moletkakatshri Hektuntshi Hwaleru— Satu pimole himtuwnayehixinipyi, pyanwakatanru pekhixyawakaplu rektunu. Seyni pixa tsonu wane yanu hiyáhoni hixapkapatkani, wale hiyrunu pixa. Waneya hyijnakoxinipyi, pukchikmoletatka psatkaklu pimole.
Seyni hma yijnakotkanuklunupyi, waneya ho satu ho hepi yineru pixayma panikanu, pkamhiywakaplu Hoyakalu tokanu tshinyawaka, wla tshinatshri: “Hepi ho mapa yine hektutu hiphujetatshine tokanu hpoyehixika ptowru piranako.”
Seyni hma yijnakotkanuklunupna wanna koxa, punkakanna hapatjetatshine. Hapatjetatshin-koxa hi hyijnakoxini waneya judeu mixkatu ho jijhawenrukleru pixka pikahwakanru.
— Hiyrun-koxa wane ntshinhi: Yáholu hepi yineru xye tshijne hajenhi pa hchinikanurune hixa hanjirexinru, Nuru tenhohne hajeru kamhanru hixa tshinanu.
Klu tshinanu hanukta rapatjexyana hepi ho pnute yine nhiwaka tshinanu, wane koxno Hita.
Hi Pejnu Kata Nujhalu Namtakahchinikanuxyawakanru Nomole PiranapniWaneya Pedro yanwakatlu Jesus repomhiywaklu, wla htshinru: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, hi pejnu kathe namtakahchinikanyehitanru nomole hita nwaka hektutu kamhatshri? Haté sete katlahe namtakahchinikanyehixinri?
Jesus hihitlu, wla htshinru: — Wane ntshinyi, hi sete katapka tsonu pamtakahchinikanyehixinri seyni setenta kata sete kata pamtakahchinikanyehixinri.
Hepi Towrertshine Deve-tatshine PiranapniKlu tshinanu tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka satu phuru pixka rixa, conta-kaka haluk-hihleretatshri.
Waneya mitshikananhapka, satu htowreru hix-potuko proji deve-tatshri phuru nwaka ranikka.
Hma mumukata wenutlexyawaklu tshinanu, phuru hichankakjixlu deve-tatshri ptowru rimwaleru haté jeji ruchanjiynawakwa, hhanunro hiyrunu hiwhen-koxa ruchankakjixlu rumukata wenutlexyawaklu h-deve-leru.
Waneya deve-tatshri yoptsojitamta wale sreta, hipokananu ranjitlu, wla htshinru: “Pkahwakayakatanutshi, pa hohne psoluka n-deve-leru nwenutanyi.”
— Hiyáhoni phuru hetwamonutatkalu, ruchya-conta-tetlu, waneya ruchotatkalu.
Seyni ruchpajini wale jeji, hyoptotlu satu kamrurtshi repirexinri. Wale jeji hi hixo proji deve-tlu. Wanepnawaka hkachiplatanru, hkowchiwjitlu, waneya hwenutjixlu wla htshinru: “Pwenutanno p-deve-xyano!”
— Waneya deve-tatshri yoptsojityehitlu, hipokananu ranjitlu, wla htshinru: “Pkahwakayakatanutshi, pa hohne psoluka n-deve-leru nwenutanyi.”
— Seyni hi raluka wan-hixleta. Hiyáhoni hyatka, preso rutakjixlu haté rumukata wenutletlu h-deve-leru psoluka.
Seyni pimrine towretshine hexiniklunru, rimyekahchinikanutna. Waneya phuru nwaka hyatkana psoluka runkaklexyawakapna.
Waneya phuru tomhalu towrertshi h-deve-tjeru, wla htshinru: “Hektutu kamhatshriyi! Hipokananu panjixyawakno tshinanu p-deve-leru psoluka nuchyata.
Hi he pix-koxa hijhalu petwamonuxyawaklu p-deve-tjeru hita pixka?”
— Hiyáhoni phuru jihekanuwpotuta. Preso rutakjixlu hsaletpotuxyawakapluna haté rumukata wenutletlu h-deve-leru psoluka.
Waneko pixka rixanu Nuru tenhohne hajeru himole hektunu hma mamtakahchinikanyehitkanuklunupa halikaka.
Jesus Kopruhaxyawaklu Jordão Wenne PiranapniWaneya xyekaka rali tshinrexinixka Jesus, Galileia tshijne ruchpajya, pa sreta Jordão wenne Judeia tshijnestsi hyatka.
Hixolune yine homkahitlu waneya wane satkaka yeyixatshri rutskalajya.
Hiknokahnunrolu PiranapniWaneya satkaka fariseu-ne yanwakatlu Jesus hepomhalu retumhiyluna. Repomhaluna: — Moisés hiykole pirana yonatkalurlahe hi tshipetlu jeji hhanunro ruknojyawakapa klunerujiji tshinanuktako?
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinna: — Hi he het-yonhatlu xye pirana? Hyinuwajikolu yineru hiyakotatshri hixkajyawaklu jeji suxo rixyawakna,
Waneya wla htshina: “Wale tshinanu jeji hichotlu ruru, runro, rimwiywakaplo hhanunro hiyáhoni satu manepkalu hhanunroyma.”
Hiyáhoni hi hepitkana seyni pa manepkana. Hiyáhoni hike yineru xako hitspalkakanru Hoyakalu hapatjetanune.
Waneya wla htshinna fariseu-ne: — Seyni Moisés hiykole yonatkaluru wan-tshina jeji ruchohnunroxinipa ruchoxyalo pirana yonaxikolu renekanro, hhanunro tmixyawakanpatka waneya hyokanatatkalo. Haklu tshinanhe wane htshina yonatkaluru?
Waneya Jesus hihitna: — Hixa chiko hchinikanu hixyawaka tshinanu Moisés hetachatna yine hhanunrone ruknojyawakapna. Seyni xye tshijne yinuwajikolu klu papko hi wan-rixa.
Wale tshinanu wane ntshinhi: Ruchohnunroxini jeji hapoklewlu minje tshinanu, satoko hhanunroxini rimopatatkalo.
Waneya rasruklene wan-tshinru Jesus: — Seyni wan-rixini jeji hhanunro tshinanu, kihle potlu hma hnunrowaxyawakanu.
Waneya Jesus wla tshina: — Hi ptowru yineru himatjemlu xye ntshinyawaka seyni yine Hoyakalu himatjemkaklene tsonu himukata himatjemletanru.
Rawa satkaka jeji mumukata hnunrowletkatu runro nanwaka ruchpajinikawa. Raw-koxa satkaka mumukata hnunrowletkatu yineko wan-hixkakleruna. Hiyrun-koxa satkaka nuretlu hma hnunrowaxyawakanu tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka tshinanu. Katukta himukata himatjemletanru, rimatjemanutkalu.
Seyni Jesus wla tshinna: — Hetachatanna mturune hyanwakaxyawaknona. Hi himaletanna. Klu tshinanu tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka hayinetene mturune pixkalune koxni wanna.
Waneya Jesus mturune jiwu rali hitakamyolexinixka ruhlewahchinikanyehixyawakna, hyatka.
Jeji Phuru PiranapniWaneya satu jeji hapyehitlu Jesus repomhalu, wla htshinru: — Kasruklewakleru kihleru, klunerhe kihleru nkamhanu niwejinri hikeklu hohne nma nikawniywakanupa?
Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Klu tshinanhe pepomhayehitlu kihleru? Hoyakalu tsonu kihleru hikeni hiyrunu. Moisés hiykole pirana pkamhini, piwekkakko.
Waneya repomhalu Jesus: — Hanuru pirana nomkahitanu? Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru: — Hi puylalewatanu, hi hapoklewatanu, hi ptshowhuwatanu, hi pimrine pweyatanu,
pkahwakpiratanru puru, punro hiyrun-koxa pimwastsireru pamotanu pamoxnawakwa pixka.
Seyni jeji wla tshinru: — Xye hiykolu ptowruka nomkahita, kluneru tsonu nmaha kamhaletawa?
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru: — Potukalumka pixinipa, puchankanru ptowruka pimwanru, penekanna ptowruka mahaxikatshine. Wane pixa pohirewnaletanu tenhohneya. Waneya punanu, pomkahitanno hita.
Waneya wale pirana hyijnakoxinixka phuru, hyatka hwamonuwnapotuta klu tshinanu phurupotukni.
Pohirewnalu Hma Mepixyawakanru Yineru Hoyakalu Pohirewaxyawaka Hjihlojyawaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus wan-tshinna rasruklene: — Halikaka ntshinhi, hi pa yaprenukananru phuru tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka hjihlojyawakapa!
Hiyrunuko xye ntshinhi, kyapreru camelo tsapujripna hjihlojyawaka seyni yohnik-yapren-potlu phuru Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hjihlojyawaka.
Waneya xye hjeminixkana rasruklene, rimyekahchinikanpotuthonukna hiyáhoni repomhaluna: — Ha han-hixatshrihe xawaka hiwekkakko?
Waneya Jesus yopukhatna, wla htshinna: — Yine mumukatanutu, wale rumukata Hoyakalu.
Waneya Pedro wla tshina: — Petanu, ptowruka wuchota, pixa womkahixyawakatka. Kluhe xawaka wyoptotanu hixa?
Waneya Jesus wla tshina: — Halikaka ntshinhi, ptowruka herotetkoklunuklu papko hyinuwajiniklunupa Jeji Whene towuwle royaknuyma, wale towuwlu pixkalutu nenekanhi hixa nomkahitjenhi hiyrun-koxa phuru tuplawakle htuplatanu hikolukanuwnakakanna israel-nerune doze ptohkakapni.
Ptowru yineru hipji hichotatshri, ho runro, ho ruru, ho himolene ho himolerone [ho hhanunro,] ho hiwhenene hichotatshri ho hsana hichotatshri Hita tshinanu hyoptotanru cem kata pnute hiyrunu riwejinri hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa.
Hiyrun-koxa hixolune kosekakanatatshine hapkatatanutka. Waneya hixolune rapkatle hwatshine kosekanutka.
Uva-cha Kamrurewaxikatshine Piranapni— Tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka satu uva-cha himwatshri pixka rixa. Yetshpotukawa ruchpaka rujhana uva-cha kamrurewaxikatshinepa.
Rasruha hixlexyawaknina ruhlepokhapkatluna pa proji prata pso wenru pa hohne kamrurtshi tshinanu. Waneya rusanate nwaka hyokanatatkana.
Waneya nove horas rixinixka, ruchpakamtatnaka. Hanjijexikowaka nwaka hya wane rexyana jejine mkamrurene.
Waneya wla htshinna: “Hajewa. Hix-koxa kamrurewatanutka nutakle uva-chaya. Waneya hpoyahoxyawaka pso potuko nenekanhi.”
— Hiyáhoni wane hyatkana. Waneya hanikaj-hohne hiyrunu mapa hora kayno wane hyatnaka jitaklechalu. Waneko pixka rixatkana pimrine kamrurewatatshine.
Waneya kayi sreta cinco hora rixini, wane hyatnaka. Retna pimrine wane hwatshinewa waneya repomhatkana: “Klu tshinanhe hewi hwahohnechata hike mkamhakanekhi?”
— Waneya ruhitluna, wla htshinruna: “Klu tshinanu hike kamrurewjixwu.” Waneya wla htshinna: “Hajewa hix-koxa kamrurewatanutka nusanateya.”
— Waneya kayi rixinixka susanateru wan-tshinru kamrurewatatshine hislahatshri: “Ptomhana kamrurewatatshine pwenuxyawakapna hkamrurna wenru. Hapkatatatshine pyinuwaka wenutletanu haté mitshikananu kamrurewatatshine pwenutanu.”
— Waneya satkaka cinco hora yinuwaka kamrurewletatshri yoptotlu satu proji prata kamhikaluru.
Waneya mitshikananu yinuwaka kamrurewletatshine kahwaklu pnuteyaka hkayatanna wanna seyni wanna koxa satu projipka hkayatna.
Hiyáhoni hyoptoxinixkalu hkamrurna wenru, reyikatkaluna susanateru.
Wla htshinna: “Nyi jejine pa hora-pka tsonu hkamrurewatna seyni hixa psol-hohneruka hameru wsalewnahohneta wanepnawaka psokakaklu wenru wyoptota.”
Xawakni panikanru pkayleru, pipji pyanu. Pkayleru pso naluk-henekletkoxlu hapkatatatshri kamrurewatatshri.
Hi he nalujyawaka potuko numukata kamhaleta ntiyiroteyma? Ho phahxatlu kihle nixyehixyawaklu tsonu?”
Hiyáhoni hixolune rapkatle hwatshine kosekanutka. Hiyrun-koxa hixolune kosekakanatatshine hapkatatanutka. [Klu tshinanu hi heppikna tshanixkalunemka tomhaka seyni hi híxona nuretkalunetka.]
Jesus Hinkaklexyawaklu Rupninri PiranapniWaneya Jerusalém poktshi hyamxinixka Jesus, ranikna kahnete rasruklene waneya wla htshinatkana:
— Jerusalém poktshi nwaka wyamtanu. Waneya Jeji Whene tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne, kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine renekko, waneya rukolukanuwnakakanruna ruylajixanruna,
judeu mixkane renekko waneya reyikko, hkotshipjetko, ruylatko. Waneya map-hohne rixinri riwekanutnaka.
Zebedeu Hnunro Hanjireru PiranapniWaneya Zebedeu whenene hinro, towheneneyma yanwakatlu Jesus, tyoptsojityehitlu waneya pa hixanu tanjitlu.
Waneya repomhalo: — Kluhe paluka? Waneya wala wla tshinru: — Naluklu nyi hepi nowhenene punkaklexinri, satu ppotukle sreta htuplaxyawaka, satu pa sta sreta htuplaxyawaka ppohirewaxyawakaya.
Jesus wla tshinatkana: — Hixa hi himatlu klukta hanjita. Hixlahe himukata hirrexyalo copa salewaktshi yehi nurinropa? Waneya ruhitluna: — Wumukata.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinatkana: — Halikaka, hixa hirinro copa salewaktshi yehiya seyni htuplaxyawakaplu npotukle sreta ho npastate sreta hi hitanni neneklewaxyawakapa. Xye ptaklukaka sreta hajene Nuru halpokohnaplene tshinanupa.
Pimrine rasruklene dez jeminixkalu xye pirana, rahkanwakatna nyi hepi moletkakatshine.
Waneya Jesus tomhana wanna ptowruneka waneya wla htshinna: — Phurune xye tshijne hajene towutjetna yine hiyrun-koxa wanna towutjene towutjetna wanna koxa.
Seyni hixa hi wan-hixanu. Katukta hijhakalur-pira, pimrine repixanu,
hiyrun-koxa katukta haluka towuwletanu, walepni pimrine towrerupa.
Waneko pixka rixa Jeji Whene. Jeji Whene hi hina repixikowakapa, seyni runa repixyawakapna yine, riwejinri renejyawakapa, hixolune yine majnákonu hwenuxyawakapa.
Jesus Hitskalajyawakna Hepi Mayhalene PiranapniWaneya Jesus rasrukleneyma Jericó poktshi hichpajinixka, hixolune yine homkahitlu.
Hepi mayhalene hatnu tnumne tuplatatshine jeminixkalu Jesus wane hyapamxyawaka, hsaplewatna, wla htshinna: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, phuru Davi-ni whene, petwamonutanunwu.
Waneya hixolune hiykotna potshke rixyawakna mayhalene seyni wanna wane pnute hsaplewjepotutna: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, phuru Davi-ni whene, petwamonutanunwu.
Waneya Jesus hituka, htomhana. Waneya repomhatkana: — Klunerhe haluka nkamhiywakhi?
Waneya ruhitluna: — Waluklu petkajyawakwu.
Waneya Jesus hetwamonutatkana, hkamrukayhaletna. Waneklukawa potuko retatkana romkahitatkaluna.
Jesus Jerusalém Poktshi Jihlojyawaka PiranapniWaneya Jerusalém poktshi rapokpiraxinixka, Betfagé poktshi rapokastsixinixka, himriji Oliveiras tshinikowakastsi, hyokanatna hepi rasruklene.
Wla htshinna: — Poktshi pnute hajeru nwaka hyanu. Waneya chinpotukawa hyoptotanro jumento tsatkaluro towheneymaluto. Hichotanna wanna, hanikanna wkata.
Seyni satu yineru hepomhiniphi haklu wla himixa waneya wla htshinanna: “Kasruklewakleru haluklu.” Ritshitanhi chinpotukawa wkata hanikanna.
Xye ptowruka wan-hixa, hpoyahokajyawakaplu ptowruka htshinyawaka Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshriya:
“Wla ptshinanna Jerusalém hajene: Haha hetanru, hixa hpohire hinanwakathi mayohotu jumento yapatjitatshri, jumento whene jumento whenenni.”
Waneya hyatkana Jesus yokanrene ptowru hyokanaxyana hkamhana.
Waneya rasruklene Jesus nwaka ranikluna jumento hiyrun-koxa jumento whene. Waneya himkalna jumentonetji hoho rutakna. Waneya Jesus himkalna tuplahohota.
Hixolune yine koprakamkata hatnu hapo, hiyrunu pimrine hahmuna chehi hatnu hapo hitaka.
Waneya Jerusalém poktshi hjihlojinixka Jesus, ptowru yine wane hajene kaheknanuwata, repomsakakna: — Katnihe xye jeji?
Waneya hixolune rimotsane wla tshina: — Xyekni Jesus, Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshrini Nazaré poktshi Galileia tshijne hajeru.
Jesus Hoyakalupji Rapkapyawaka PiranapniWaneya Hoyakalupji hjihlokamta Jesus. Hyinuwaka maleka yokanretna hichanrewatatshine hiyrun-koxa maronewatatshine. Tiyiro proji hipekotatshine mesa-kaka hiyrun-koxa kamowa henekachalu tshinanu hichanretatshine tuplawakkaka hyotkakatka.
Wla htshinna: — Wla htshina yonatkaluru Hoyakalu pirana: “Nopji hanjihohnewakapjini.” Seyni hixa katshowhurune hwiywaka hkamhiyatkalu.
Jesus Hasruklewaxyawaka Hoyakalupjiya PiranapniWaneya Hoyakalupji mtsawane hiyrunu myankane yanwakaxyalu Jesus waneya rutskalhatkana.
Seyni tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hiyrun-koxa kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine rexinixkaluna hixo hiyakolukaka hkamhiywaka hiyrunu hjemna mturune Hoyakalupji hwatshine wla tshin-saplewjeretatshine: — Himalwutkalurni Phuru Davi-ni whene! Hiyáhoni rahkaluna Jesus.
Waneya repomhaluna Jesus: — Pjemnahe mturune tshinyawaka? Jesus hihitna: — Hehe, njemna. Hi he het-yonhatlu yonatkaluru potukalu wla tshinatshri: “Pyanumkakanna mturune hiyrunu hematlune himalwuru kihlewak-potuko htshinyawakna.”?
Waneya ruknokamtna, Betânia poktshi hya rumjiywakpatka.
Figueira PiranapniWaneya yetshpotukawa, Jesus Jerusalém poktshi satokamtawa, hnatshita.
Waneya satu figueira-muna reta hatnu hapostsi hwatshro seyni hi kasahlu, hisurkaka tsonu reta. Waneya wla htshinru: — Hikeklu hohne psahiwatanutnaka! Waneya waneklukawa potuko riprihanatka.
Xye rexinixkana rasruklene, rimyekahchinikanpotutna. Waneya repomhaluna: — Hanhe rixa chinpotu hiprihletanatka figueira-ni?
Waneya Jesus hihitna, wla htshinna: — Halikaka ntshinhi, halixinipa hiyrunu hi hmalixlenu hmixkanuklunupa, hi xyepka nkamhaleru pixkalutu himukata kamhaleta seyni hixa himukata wla tshinretkoxlu himriji: “Ppalnanu mar powha puknojinwa.” — Waneyamka wane potuko rixanu.
Halixinri hanjireru hanjihohneruya hyoptoxyawaka, hyoptotanru.
Jesus Tsru Potu Hitakkalurni PiranapniWaneya pa hohne Jesus Hoyakalupji jihloka, waneya yine rasrukakanatka pchinika, tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne, hiyrun-koxa tsrukakalune judeu-ne hapokanwakatlu. Waneya repomhaluna: — Punkakanwu hanhe ruchpajya ptowutjeru xyekaka pkamhiywaka? Kathe henekyi xye tsru hitakkaluru?
Waneya Jesus wan-tshin-hihretna: — Hit-koxa satu hepomhalu nixanhi hixa. Hihixinri xye, hit-koxa hinkakanhi hixa katu henekno xye tsru hitakkaluru xyekaka nkamhiywaka.
Ha João h-batiz-lewaxyawaka? Hanhe ruchpajya htowutjeru, ho Hoyakalu ruchpajya ho jeji ruchpajya? Waneya hyinuwaka hiynumsakakletna wannakakluko. Waneya wla htshinkakna: — Wla wtshininri Hoyakalu, waneya repomhanunwu: “Haklu tshinanhe hi halixlu João-ni?”
Seyni wla wtshininri jeji ruchpajya htowutjeru, nyi hixolune yine wpikanu. Klu tshinanu ralixluna João-ni Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshrini rixyawaka.
Wale tshinanu wanna wla tshina hi hima rimatna hanu ruchpajyatka wale towuwlu. Hiyáhoni Jesus wla tshinna: — Hit-koxa hi hinkakanhi hanukta ruchpajya xyekaka ntowuxijeru.
Hepi Wheneru Piranapni— Xawakni, kluhe hikchika hixa? Satu jeji hepi whenru. Hyanwakatlu tsrujru waneya wla htshinru: “Noturu, xawakni pkamrurewatanu nusanate uva-chaya.”
— Waneya ruhitlu ruru: “Hi jmerno.” — Seyni xekoyaka hyokmanahchinikanutatka, uva-cha hyatka.
— Waneya rurna waneko pixka rixa towutletlu hituru hepurtshi. Seyni wale wan-tshinru ruru: “Haté wuya, papa.” — Seyni hi wane hya.
Waneya Jesus hepomhana tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hiyrunu judeu-ne tsru hixikatshinwa, wla htshinna: — Hanurhe kamhalu ruru halujyawaka? Waneya wla htshinruna: — Hituru tsrujru. Hiyáhoni Jesus wla tshinna: — Jijhawenruklerune hiyrun-koxa kapoklewaklerone Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka jihlokanu hixa hkosejinna.
Klu tshinanu João Batista-ni hinyehithi rekhixyawakaplu powraxikowaka pirana seyni hixa hi halixatkalu. Seyni jijhawenruklerune hiyrun-koxa kapoklewaklerone halixatkalu. Waneya yáholu hexinixkalu ralixlena seyni hi hehchinikanutatka halixyawakaplu.
Hsana Kamrurewaxikatshine Piranapni— Hyijnakotanru satu yapkaklu pirana: Pa kata satu jitaklewakleru hitaklu uva-cha. H-cerca-tetlu, hiyrun-koxa hjitotlu uva katsrekjexikowaka vinho-ha hkamhiywakapa hiyrunu satu tenopjiru uva-cha hislahikowakapji hkamha. Waneya hsana hislahatshine renekamta. Waneya pa tshijne howuka hya.
Waneya rapokpapkoluxinixka ramikolu, jitaklewakleru yokanatlu satkaka htowreru hyoptoxyawakaplu hitaklucha hislahatshine nwaka psoji jitaklewaklerunupa.
Seyni hitaklucha hislahatshine kachitna htowrene, satu hkotshipjetluna, satni ruylatna waneya mapa rixinri htowreru hsotlujetanatkaluna.
Waneya pimrine htowrene hyokanata mitshikananu hyokanatanune yohnika seyni wanna koxa waneko pixka rixkana.
Waneya hnikawnaletka hituru potuko hyokanatatka. Wla htshina: “Wale hetko hkahwakpiratanna.”
Seyni rexinixkaluna hitaklucha hislahatshine, riynumsakakna wannakakluko, wla htshinna: “Ha xyekni jitaklewakleru whene. Hayeri wuylateru. Waneyakni ptowruka ruru henejyamkaplu hixanpatka!”
Hiyáhoni klunerhe hkamhinna jitaklewakleru rapojiniklunupa?
Waneya ruhitluna: — Runanu ruylatanunna hektune hitaklucha hislahatshinepni. Waneya pimrineko hitaklucha hislahatshine renekanu ramikolu papko hitaklu psoji renekjenepatka.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinna: — Hi he Hoyakalu pirana hexyalu xye pirana? Wla htshina: “Sotlu kpanawaklerune malukkotu rikahwakluna hepixlewatatshri potukni, psolupjiko poyehitatshrini wale. Tsru Hixikatshriwa kamhalerni hiyáhoni kihle potuklu hixa hetanuya.”
Hiyáhoni wane ntshinhi: — Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hixa hkonka, waneya pa neru renekko Hoyakalu halujyawaka kamhatshinepa.
[Katupnikta xye sotlu hoho hijrukanuna rumlokanuna. Hiyrun-koxa katupnikta xye sotlu hapokhohotanu, hipahi tsonunapni.]
Waneya fariseu-ne hiyrun-koxa tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne jeminixkalu Jesus, rimatluna Jesus kamnitna yapkaklu piranaya runkakletleru.
Raluka kachretmakluna Jesus seyni hpikna yine klu tshinanu hkahwakluna Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri rixyawaka.
Tsru Niklu PiranapniWaneya Jesus hinkaklewatatnaka yapkaklu pirankakayma, wla htshina:
— Tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka satu phuru pixka rixa. Phuru halpokojixlu tsru niklu hituru hnunrowle tshinanupa.
Hyokanatna htowrene htshanixyawakapna phuru tshanixlene seyni hi jmerna.
Waneya hiyrunuko pimrine htowrene hyokanata, waneya wla htshina: “Punkakanna ntshanixlene, nnijitu halixatka: noprane bezerro-ne hiyrunu boi-ne nixownakakanune nuylatatka, ptowruka halpokotatka. Hinanu tsru niklu hnunrowlu tshinanu.”
— Waneya tshanixkalune hi hislahatokanutna seyni ralimtna. Satu hsana yatka, satu maronewjexikowaka hyatka.
Pimrine kachitanna phuru towrenni, hkotshipjetatkana, ruylatanatkana towrertshinni.
Waneya phuru jihekanuwpotuta. Soldado-ne hyokanata ruylaxyawakapna jiylalewaklerune, hiyrun-koxa wanna poktshite hyoxijyawakapna.
Waneya phuru wla tshinna pimrine htowrene: “Nijittshi halixatka hnunrowlu tshinanu, klu tshinanu nyi rujhalna tshinanu hi htshanixkatkana.”
Hajewa poktshi hapkaka yoptowakkaka hyanu, htshanixanna katuktako hikchikanune.
— Hiyáhoni towrertshine poktshi hapo yoptowakkak-yehi hyatkana, rawapyawakapna rumukata hikchikletanune, kihlerune hiyrunu hektune koxa. Waneya tshanixkalune tsepotlu phurupji tsru nikawaka.
Seyni phuru jihlojinixka retapyawakapna hapokatshine, retlu satu jeji kihleru mkatshri mutakkatu.
Waneya repomhalu: “Nimatletleru, hanu pixa jihlokleta hewi kihleru mkatshri mutakamtkatyi?” — Waneya hi ktokanru jeji.
Waneya phuru wla tshinatkana htowrene: “Hostujixitanru, hostumyotanru koxa waneya maleka sreta mapchahawaka tsru tshiyahlu hiyrunu haskiyhiru yehi hiknokanru.”
— Klu tshinanu hi heppikna tshanixkalunemka seyni hi híxona nuretkalunetka.
Repomhaluna Jesus Ho Tiyiro Raluka Wenutluna César Ho Hike PiranapniWaneya fariseu-ne hapatjeta, rujhahchinikanutna hanhe rumukata kachretluna Jesus htokanu tshinanu.
Fariseu-ne hasruklene hyokananwakatluna Jesus Herodes-neyma. Waneya repomhaluna Jesus: — Kasruklewakleru, wimatyi pixa halikaka pirana ptshinjeta, pasrukjetkoxna. Hiyrun-koxa hi yine hixachatatshineko yokwityi seyni pasrukle halikakalutu Hoyakalu halujyawaka pirana.
Hiyáhoni punkakanwu, pkahwaklu minanchitkotlahe psoji tiyiro wenejyawaklu César Roma hajeru tsru hixikatshriwa? Ho wenejerhe ho hike?
Seyni Jesus himathetna hektu hchinikanu rixyawakna waneya wla htshinna: — Hixachatatshinhi! Haklu tshinanhe haluk-himlukantaletno?
Hekhitanno proji tiyiro César wenuxikolupa. Waneya proji tiyiro ranikna.
Waneya repomhana: — Katu yaholunhe kat-hiwaknihe toproji hwatshri?
Waneya ruhitluna: — César-ni. Waneya Jesus wla tshina: — Henekanru César kluneruktapni César-nu henekanru hiyrun-koxa kluneruktapni Hoyakalunu waleko henekanru.
Xye hjeminixkana, rimyekna Jesus hihixya tshinanna. Hiyáhoni ruchomtluna, hyatkana.
Waneya wla htshinna: — Kasruklewakleru, Moisés-ni yonaxyawu xye hiykolu pirana: “Jeji hipninipa ruknokamtanro hhanunro mwuhenetoko, walen-moleko hnunrotanro waleni hnunro. Twuhenewatanu hipnatshrini whenene hkahwajikowakapna.”
Waneya pa kata wan-rixa hahijewakatanna sete-ni jejinni moletkakatshinni. Tsrujruni hnunrowatni rupnana mwuhenetniko. Waneya repurni hnunrotlo hipnahnurutatshro.
Wale koxa hipnana mwuhenetniko. Waneko pixka rixa hahijewakatan-koxa satni mapa rixinri. Sete-ni hnunrotlewatni walaluto suxo. Rupnanna mwuhenenniko.
Waneya suxni koxa hipnanatka.
Xawakni hiwejikalur-hohnepatnaka, hanurpatkanhe thanuru? Klu tshinanu ptowruneko hnunrotaplo.
Waneya Jesus hihita: — Hixa pupjetatshinhi klu tshinanu hi himatlu Hoyakalu pirana, hi koxa himatlu Hoyakalu himukatlewle.
Seyni tujra hohne hiweklu yoptotatshinepa hi hnunrowatanu hiyrunu hi hnuruwatanu. Hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrene tenhohne hajene pixka rixanutkana.
Seyni hi he het-yonhatlu Hoyakalu tshinyawakhi hipnatshine hiwekkajikowaka pirana tshinanu? Wla htshina:
Abraão-ni Hoyakalutno, Isaque-ni Hoyakalutno, Jacó-ni Hoyakalut-koxno. Hoyakalu hiwekatshine Hoyakalutni seyni hi miwekkanepa Hoyakalutni.
Waneya hixolune xye jeminixka, rimyekahchinikanutna Jesus hasrujya tshinanna.
Yokanruru Hijhakalur-potuko PiranapniWaneya fariseu-ne jeminixkalu Jesus hitshrokkajyawakna saduceu-ne, rapatjetna.
Waneya satu fariseu, Moisés yonreru pirana himatpotutatshri, hetumhalu Jesus xye hepomhaluyma.
Wla htshina: — Kasruklewakleru, kluner-pothe hijhakaluru ptowru Moisés yokanreru yonatkaluruya?
Waneya Jesus hihitlu, wla htshina: — “Pamotanru Tsru Hixikatshriwa Poyakalute psoluka pajiyma, psoluka piwejinriyma, hiyrun-koxa psoluka pihchinikanuyma.”
Xyekni mitshikananu yokanruru, hijhakalur-potukni.
Yokanruru hepi rixinri waneko pixka rixa hijhakalurni: “Pamotanru pimwastsitanru pamoxnawakwa pixka.”
Nyi hepi yokanruru poyahokaklu Moisés yokanreru yonatkaluru hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine tshinyawaka psoluka.
Katnihe Messias PiranapniWaneya rapatjekananumtawana fariseu-ne, Jesus hepomhana:
— Klu hkahwaklu Messias? Katu klopichni wale? Waneya ruhitluna: — Davi-ni klopicha.
Waneya wla htshinna: — Seyni klu tshinanhe Davi-ni, Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru tshinanu, Nutsrukate htshinanwakatlu? Klu tshinanu wla htshinatka:
“Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu wan-tshinno Tsru Hixikatshriwa: Ptuplatanu npotukle sreta, haté pkamnitjene pijixi hpuko nutakanu.”
Davi-ni potuko Rutsrukate tshinru Hoyakalu hiyáhoni hanhe rumukata Davi-ni klopicha hixleta Messias?
Hike himukata hihretlu hiyáhoni waneklu kananuko hike tsru hchinikanu hepomhale hixatkalu Jesus.
Jesus Hinkaklexyawaklu Fariseu-ne Hiyrunu Hinanchitkaluru Tokantshi Hasruklewatatshine PiranapniWaneya Jesus wla tshinatkana rasruklene hiyrun-koxa hixolune:
— Kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine hiyrun-koxa fariseu-ne rawyana tsru towuwlu runkaklexyawakluna Moisés yonreru pirana.
Hiyáhoni hixa yijnakotanna homkahitanna ptowru htshinyawakhina. Seyni hi wanna pixka hixanu klu tshinanu htowuxyawakna hi hkamhana wanna.
Hatatjewa yine tsru hinolu rutjijixna seyni wanna hi hepixna rutjixyawaklu hinolu, hi pamyojiymakna repixna.
Ptowruka hkamhanruna yine hexyawaklu tshinanu hkamhaluna. Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru yonha paji htserutjetna. Xye pajkaka himkalna rostutna yine hexyawakaplu. Himkalna hyokakluna chichyoha samalu. Waneko pixka rixna ptowru potuko hkamrureyna Hoyakalu romkahpotuxyawakna hkahwajikolupna.
Ralukpotutluna kihleru niklur-yeh-potuko htuplaxyawakna hiyrun-koxa rujhaluna tuplawaka tsru hixikatshriwa tuplaxyawaka htuplaxyawakna ptowru hanjihohnewakapjiya.
Seyni hixa hi kasruklewakleru htshinko klu tshinanu satupkalu pasrukjeru hiyrun-koxa hixa ptowrunekhi moletkakatshinhi.
Hiyrun-koxa hike xye tshijne hajeru hiru htshinanu klu tshinanu satupkalu Puru, tenhohne hwatshri.
Hi koxa kasruklewakleru htshinkakanu klu tshinanu satupkalu pasrukjeru, Cristo tshinkaluru.
Hijhakalur-potni hixkakluko yehiya ptowutkoluya.
Klu tshinanu katukta kahwakpiratkaluru hitajinwa, malukkotu rutakko wale. Seyni malukkotu hikahwajikatshriwa, hkahwakpiratka wale.
Jesus Hikolukna Fariseu-ne Hiyrunu Hinanchitkaluru Tokantshi Hasruklewatatshine Piranapni— Hapnokatkalunephi kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine hiyrun-koxa fariseu-ne, hixachatatshinhi! Hixa himaletna tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka jihlokpiratatshine. Hi hixako jihloklu. Hiyrun-koxa wane jihlokpiratatshine himaleta.
[Hapnokatkalunephi kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine hiyrun-koxa fariseu-ne! Hipnahnurutatshrone hkonahejnunkatetna. Wanepnawaka hohanjihohneru rixjetna kihleru hkahwajikolupna. Seyni wanepnawaka tsru hapnokatlu rixkona.]
— Hapnokatkalunephi kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine hiyrun-koxa fariseu-ne, hixachatatshinhi! Psol-tshijne hyapa hixa, yáholu tshijiko yáholu mar powhako hyapa, judeu halixlewle halixkajyawaklu yineru waneya satu yineru halixiniplu htokanu, hixa hsalewninri hepi kata pnute hkayatanru tshitshmero.
— Hapnokatkalunephi hixa mayhalenni kosekatshinephuthi! Klu tshinanu wla htshina hasruklewleta: “Satu yineru Hoyakalupji hiwaka hmunanhiniklunutka, hi rujha kamhaletatkalu htokanu htshinakanaxyawaka. Seyni satu yineru ouro Hoyakalupji hajeru hiwaka hmunanhiniklunutka, rujha kamhaletlu htshinyawaka.”
Jipukalhi, mayhalenhi! Hi he himata Hoyakalupji potu hijhakaluru ouro walepji hajeru yohnika? Ouro Hoyakalupji hajeru kotspalatka Hoyakalu kamrure tshinanu.
Hiyrunu wla koxa htshina hasruklewleta: “Satu yineru altar hiwaka hmunanhiniklunutka, hi rujha kamhaletatkalu htokanu htshinakanaxyawaka. Seyni satu yineru henekachalu hmunanhiniklunutka, rujha kamhaletlu htshinyawaka.”
Mayhalene pixkalunhi! Hi he himata altar potu hijhakaluru henekachaluru yohnika? Henekachlu altar hoho rawyawaka tshinanu tsonu Hoyakalunutkani henekachlu.
Wale tshinanu satu yineru altar hiwaka hmunanhini, altar hiyrun-koxa henekachlukaka altar hoho hwatshri hmunanha.
Hiyrun-koxa satu yineru Hoyakalupji hiwaka hmunanhini, Hoyakalupji hiyrun-koxa walepji hajeru hmunanha.
Hiyrun-koxa satu yineru tenhohne hmunanhini, Hoyakalu tuplawakle tskihi hiyrunu wale hoho tuplatatshri koxa hmunanha.
— Hapnokatkalunephi kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine hiyrun-koxa fariseu-ne, hixachatatshinhi! Hixa henekjetlu Hoyakalu haté phamlu sureru, hortelã, erva-doce hiyrunu cominho tshinkaluru décima psojite. Seyni hi hkamhalu Moisés yonreru pirana hasruklewlukaka hijhakalur-potu, potuknutshi hchinikanni, hetwamonrewlu hiyrun-koxa halixlewlu. Xyekaka hijha kamhaleta halikaka seyni pimrine xako hi hichotanu.
Mayhalene kosekatshinhi! Hirhalerumka hixirijyalo yosla hma niklojyawakaplu seyni camelo hnikloka.
— Hapnokatkalunephi kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine hiyrun-koxa fariseu-ne, hixachatatshinhi! Hixa herokalu copa stono prat-koxa maleka sreta tsonu. Seyni hitoko hixa hinanwaka katsephi hahnanuwlu, sotanuhonutshi koxa.
Fariseu mayhaletyi! Mitshikananhapka ppowratanru copa stono prat-koxa hitoko sreta, roho hajer-koxa powra rixyawakapa.
— Hapnokatkalunephi kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine hiyrun-koxa fariseu-ne, hixachatatshinhi! Kapnatkalunenatka pixkalunhi. Hixa yomletshi sahatkaluru pixka hixatshinhi. Maleka sreta kihleylu seyni hitoko katseplu hipnatshri hapu hiyrunu ptowru hixatshri posuru.
Hixa waneko pixka hixa. Maleka sreta yine hexyawakhi potukalune phuthi seyni halikaka hixachatatshinhi, hektuwaka kamhatshinhi.
— Hapnokatkalunephi kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine hiyrun-koxa fariseu-ne, hixachatatshinhi! Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshinni yomle hkamhajeta hiyrunu hihlejetlu potukalunni yomlekaka.
Hiyrunu wla htshinna: “Ha hixako wiwekamka wutsrukatenniklu papko, himka wepixa hiylatanna Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshinni.”
Wan-hixa hiphujetlexnawa Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine hiylatatshine klopichanhi.
Hiyáhoni hnikata kamhaletanru hitsrukatenni yinuwaka kamruretanru.
Hixa himnu kamaklewatatshri pixka hixatshinhi, himnunerunhi. Hanhe hixa hasuklexinri salewaktshi nwaka hikolukanuwnayehixikolupa?
Hiyáhoni wane ntshinhi nyokananwakatanhi hinamtatshri pirana hinkakletatshine, jimatkalerune hiyrun-koxa kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine. Hixa satkaka wannapni hiylatanu, satkakapni cruz hitakko, pimrinepni hkotshipjetanu hanjihohnewakapjiya hiyrunu pa poktshi pejnukananu hkamnixinna pimrinepni.
Wale tshinanu hixa hapnokatko ptowruneka hiylatkalunni hike mixkanni tshinanu. Abel potukalni hiylaxikoluklu haté Zacarias, Baraquias tshinkaluru whene, honnira Hoyakalupji altar yehi hwatshri hanikajiteswa ruylaxikana.
Hehe, halikakni nyi hiwekatshinewa rapnokatkona xyekaka hiylalewlu hkamhale tshinanna mitshikawa hiwekatshinni.
Hetanru, xawakni hipji hichotkotka.
Halikaka ntshinyi hi hiyrunu petanutkano haté wla ptshininipa: “Hoyakalu hihlewahchinikanutlu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hiwaka hinikatshri.”
Hoyakalupji Kopalaxikowakapa PiranapniWaneya Hoyakalupji ruchpajinixka Jesus, rasruklene hekhitlu Hoyakalupjikaka.
Seyni Jesus wla tshinatkana: — Hetluhe xyepjikaka? Halikaka ntshinhi, ptowruka hetleru hkoptalhako hi satukna sotlu hwahohokakanu.
Salewaktshi Yinuwakle PiranapniWaneya Jesus Oliveiras mriji tuplaxini, rasruklene yanwakatlu wannapkani. Waneya repomhatkaluna Jesus, wla htshinna: — Kasruklewakleru, hikluhe wan-rixanu? Klunerhe rakaxrikletanu rekhixyawakaplu xye ptowru potuko hakanhapiraxinpatka? Hanhe wixa himatletanru punyawaka xye tshijne nikawnini hohnepa?
Waneya Jesus hihitna, wla htshina: — Xakoka hike yokwijetanhi.
Klu tshinanu hixo hiphujewnanu hita hiwakaya wla tshinatshripa, “Hita Cristo-no” waneya hixolune hyokwijetanna.
Hjeminiplu hiylakaklu ho pa tshijnekaka yahotkakle pirana hi hpikanu. Klu tshinanu xye ptowruko hakanhanu seyni hi hnikawnalepnitshi.
Pa neruymako hyahotkakanu satu neruko. Pa tshijneko yahotanru satupni. Natshipni. Hixo poktshi hiyolikanu.
Xyekaka mturu tshino yinuwakle pixkalutni.
— Seyni xye ptowruka hnapu, hsalewnakakko, hiylatko, ptowru tshijne hajene hahnanutanhi hita tshinanu.
Waneklu papkopa hixolune yine hiknoka halixletanu, yine kamnikakanu, rahkakakanna,
Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine yahole hakanhanu, hixolune yine hyokwijetanna.
Hektutu kamhaklerune hixolewniywaka tshinanu, yine hituk-hamotkakletanu.
Seyni poyehitahchinikanutatshri haté hmahle papko, riwekanu.
Hiyrun-koxa kihle piranalu potuko Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka pirana psol-tshijneko hpohixika, pa nerkaka himaxyawakaplu waneya waneklupatkani xye tshijne nikawninripatka.
Tsru Salewaktshi Piranapni— Hixa hexinixkalu Hoyakalupji hahnanutkaluru himtukpotlewatatshri, Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshrini Daniel-ni tshinyawaka, hixa himathethatatshinhi xako himatjemanru.
Waneyakni katukta Judeia hwanu, rasukanu, hipjita hyanu.
Katukta teno pantshi hohowaka hwanu, hi hserpikanu rejnunkate pantshi hajeru rawapyawakapa.
Campo hwatshri koxa hi satkapanu himkalu rawapyawaka.
Hi pa himtukalutu retanna suxone kamchirone waneklu hohnepa, hiyrun-koxa hachiwhenetatshinepni!
Hoyakalu hanjitanu hapnanuxikalur-hohne ho katshikleru papkolu hma makanhiywakanupa xyekaka.
Klu tshinanu tshiji rawanu salewaktshi tsrupotpákolu. Hikeklu hohne wane pixkalutu salewaktshi rawapa xye tshijne yinuwajikolukananuko haté xawakni hiyrun-koxa wane pixkalutu salewaktshi hikeklu hohne hakanhanutnaka.
Seyni Hoyakalu hma masatkanumkalu salewnikolu papkopa, hikemka hiwekanu. Seyni Hoyakalu nuretanune tshinanu, hmasatanru salewaktshiklu papkopa.
Waneya waneklu papkopa yineru wane htshinini: “Haha hetanru Messias!”, ho wane htshinini: “Hawlalu!” — hi halixanru.
Klu tshinanu hixolune Messias minjene hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine minjene hakanhanu hiyakolukaka hiyrunu himyekaklewatatshri kamhatshine hyokwijexyawakapna yine. Rumukatkamka haté Hoyakalu nurrene hyokwijetanu.
Hichinikanru xye, wane ntshinhi ptowru potuka hmuphujewnaknukawa.
— Hiyáhoni satu wla tshininiphi: “Hawlalu, potshkewaka rawa” — hi wane hyanu. Ho satu wla tshininiphi: “Hewitkalu, hitoko hruko rawa” — hi halixanru.
Klu tshinanu rawrakle pixka rixanu, pa sreta hyinuwaka hawraklexini haté pa sreta hohne rapokhawrakletsatanu. Waneko pixka rixanu Jeji Whene tshinkaluru hapojinri hohnepa.
Jeji Whene Hininri Hohnepa PiranapniXye hohne hajeru salewaktshi nikawninipa, waneklutka rutshpokanu tkatshi, hi katalupni ksuru, katahirine tenhohne hijrujini, hiyrun-koxa tenhohne hajerkaka hiyolikkako.
Hiyáhoni tenhohne Jeji Whene himaxikolepa hakanhini waneya psol-tshijne nerkaka htshiyahatanna kaheknanuwlu tshinanu. Waneya Jeji Whene retanna, hohimkohi rapojini royaknuyma tsru pixkonuyma koxa.
Kowi hima hajpokoklunpatka Hoyakalu yokanatanna htowrene hiwejikalune tenhohne hajene ptowru sretako rapatjexyawakapna Hoyakalu nurrene ptowru sreta tshijne hichpajikatshine.
Figueira Piranapni— Xawakni himatanru xye yapkaklu pirana figueira pirana: Hyinuwaka hiptsheklesurexinixka hiyrun-koxa rerotewapluxinixka, himatlu hi howukatkalu mhalu.
Wane koxa rixanu, hexinpatkalu xyekaka himatanutka hi howukatkalu rakanhiywakapa Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hatatjewa hiphaptostsitkalu.
Halikaka wane ntshinhi, xyekaka wan-hixa hiphujewnaletanu hmupnaknuhnapukawna xawakni mupnakanewa.
Tenhohne, tshij-koxa nikawnanu seyni ntokanu hikeklu nikawnanu.
— Hike himatlu wale hohne hi hipapkoluko rakanhiywakapa xyekaka. Hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrene tenhohne hajene hi himatlu, hi Whentshiko himatlu seyni Hirtshi tsonupka himatlu.
Noé-klu papko pixka rixanu Jeji Whene tshinkaluru hapojinri papkopa.
Klu tshinanu ptowrunniko yinni hniknina, rurnina, hhanunrowatnina, hhanuruwatnina, Noé-ni tsro kanawatlo jihlojinriklu potukananuko;
hi hkahwaknina hahyekachalu seyni runatka hahyekachalu, ptowrunnika yinni hnikata. Waneko pixka rixanu Jeji Whene hapojinri papkopa.
Waneya hepi jejine campo hwatshinepni, satu hanikko, satupni hiknokamtkona.
Hiyrun-koxa hepi suxone trigo-ji yojitatshinepa, sato hanikko, satopni hiknokamtkona.
Hiyáhoni hislahinri klu tshinanu hixa hi himatlu Hitsrukate hapojinri hohnepa.
Himatjemanru xye: kapjiru himatahnaputkamkalu katshowhuru, ruslahapjitanumkatka himka retachatanru hipji hyotpujyawakapa.
Hiyáhoni hkakonjetanu xako klu tshinanu Jeji Whene tshinkaluru hinanu hma kakonuxinri papko.
Hepi Hixatshine Towrertshine Piranapni— Katnihe towrertshi ptowutkolu, kahchinikanuru? Waleni towrertshi rutakko htowutjerupji rinoxyawakapa hiyrunu pimrine towrertshine reneka niklexyawakapa niklu papkokaka.
Hihlewahchinikanyehitkalurni wale towrertshi htowutjeru hininipa retamtlu wan-rixa kamrurekanata.
Halikaka wane ntshinhi, wan-hixatshri towrertshi rutakko ptowruka htowutjeru himwaleru htowuxyawakapa.
Seyni towrertshi wla htshinahchinikanuxini rajiya: “Ha hohamokpotukananutkalu ntowutjeru.”
Waneya hyinuwaka hiylakletna towrertshine. Hiyrun-koxa hnika, rura, jimekleruneyma.
Hiyáhoni towrertshi towutjeru hma kahwajinitu hohne runanu. Hma malpokoxinutu hohne runanu.
Htowutjeru hapnokatpotutanru towrertshipni. Waneya tsru tshiyahlu hiyrunu haskiyhiru yehi ruknokkona Hoyakalu halixatshine hixachatatshineyma.
Dez Maklojine Piranapni— Hiyáhoni tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka dez maklojine pixka rixanu. Maklojine lamparina hanikatshrone hichpakamta hyoptoxyawakapluna hnunrowpiratatshri.
Cinco-na kahchinikanurone hiyrunu cinco-na mahchinikanune.
Waneya mahchinikanune lamparina hanikamta seyni hi ranikluna óleo-ha.
Seyni kahchinikanurone hanikamtlu lamparina pa stono óleo-haymakananuko.
Waneya hnunrowpiratatshripa mapokhapkatkanuklunupa hiyáhoni maklojine hixapnewatatka, rumkatkana.
— Hanikaj-yetshno rixinixka, hjemka sapletshi wan-tshinatshri: “Hnunrowpiratatshripatkani! Hichpakanu hyoptoxyawakaplu!”
Waneya mahchinikanune wla tshinatkana kahchinikanurone: “Wuya, psojha óleo-ha henekanunwu klu tshinanu w-lamparina-te hiwnapiratatka.”
Seyni kahchinikanurone wla tshinna: “Ha hike! Klu tshinanu pa katako hi hpoyahotanu hixako w-lamparina-te tshinanupa hiyrunu hixa h-lamparina-te tshinanu. Seyni óleo-ha halujinipa, hanjitapanru.”
— Seyni óleo-ha ranjitapkako pchinikna hnunrowatatshripa hapokatka. Waneya maklojine halpokokanatatshrone hnunrowatatshripayma hjihlokna hnunrowlu nikle yehi. Waneya ruchyahiphaptotetkatka.
— Howukchini mahchinikanune hapokatka. Waneya wla htshinna: “Tsru Hixikatshriwa, Tsru Hixikatshriwa, pkotpukyehitanunwu.”
— Seyni wla htshinna: “Halikaka ntshinhi, hi nimathethi.”
— Hiyáhoni hkakonjetanmaklu klu tshinanu hi himatlu hihohne, hi hipapkoko runinripa Jeji Whene.
Cinco Ouro Proji Yapkaklu Piranapni— Hiyrun-koxa satu jeji pa tshijne yatshripa pixka rixanu tenhohne pohirewaxyawaka. Mitshikananhapka htomhanna hkamrurewkakjetanune htowuxyawakapna rejnunkate rinoxyawakapna.
Waneya satu towrertshi cinco proji reneka, satu hepi proji reneka, satu pa projipka reneka. Satkaka rumukaxyawakna renekna. Waneya hyatka.
Waneya chinpotukawa cinco proji yoptotatshri halimta, htiyiroteyma rikamrurewatlo waneya cinco proji hkayatatka.
Hiyrun-koxa hepi proji yoptotatshri waneko pixka rixatka, waneya hiyrunu hepi proji hkayatatka wale.
Seyni pa proji yoptotatshritka, hyatka, tshiji hjitota, hyohimaxyalo tiyiro htowutjeru henejyalu.
— Howukchini hpohirna satkapatka, ruhlepokotlu hkamrurna htowutamtanuneyma.
Cinco proji yoptotatshri hiyrunu cinco proji ranika waneya wla htshina: — “Tsru Hixikatshriwa, petanu, cinco proji penekamxyano dez ouro-tkalo.”
— Waneya rutsrukate wan-tshinru: “Hikamturu pkamrure! Kihleru towrertshiyi poyahokakatshriyi. Pixa psotsonuyaka kihle kamrure pixle tshinanu tsru kamrurtshi koxa penekka. Punanu hitayma ppoyikowatanu.”
— Waneya hepi proji yoptotatshri koxa yanwakatlu htowutjeru, wla htshinru: — “Tsru Hixikatshriwa, petanu hepi proji penekamxyano quatro ouro-tkalo.”
— Waneya rutsrukate wan-tshinru: “Hikamturu pkamrure! Kihleru towrertshiyi poyahokakatshriyi. Pixa psotsonuyaka kihle kamrure pixle tshinanu tsru kamrurtshi koxa penekka. Punanu hitayma ppoyikowatanu.”
— Waneya pa proji yoptotatshri hapokatka, wla htshina: — “Tsru Hixikatshriwa, nimatyi pix-honra jeji menekachalewakletyi. Mutakatúkoyi hamlu. Yineru pimrine hitakle hapatjetatshri pixka pixa.
Hiýahoni npikatka, nalimtatka, tshiji nyohimaxyalo proji tiyiro. Haha xyetkani ptiyirote.
— Waneya wla htshinru: “Hektutu towrertshiyi mmeretu. Pimatnohe jeji menekachalewakletu nixyawaka? Nma mutakanutuko namyawaka hiyrun-koxa nma muplaljetanutuko napatjeta?
Haklu tshinanhe hi banco putaklo ntiyirote tatskoxyawakapa? Wane pixkamka napojinitka nyoptotanmaklo tiyiro tsroyakalotka.”
— Waneya wla htshina: “Hkonanru ouro proji nenekamxyalu. Dez proji ouro himwatshri henekanro.
Klu tshinanu tsru himwatshriko pnute renekko wane yohnika. Hiyrun-koxa hike mwikatu seyo rimwalerujiji hkonko.
Maleka sreta mapchahawaka hiknokanru hektutu towrertshi tsru tshiyahlu haskiyhiru yehi.”
Hoyakalu Hikolukanuwnajixle Hohnepa— Jeji Whene ruphujewnin-hohnepa, royaknuyma runanu hiyrunu hiwejikalune htowrene tenhohne hajeneymalu. Phuru tuplawakle htuplatanu rukolukanuwniywakapa.
Wale hetanuya rapatjetanu ptowru yineru xye tshijne hajene waneya carneiro hinotatshri kotspalaxyawakna carneiro-ne bode-yma pixka rix-kotspalletanna yine.
Carneiro pixkalune (wannakatkani potukalune) hpotukle sreta rutakanu hiyrunu bode pixkalune (wannakatkani pimrine) pa sta sreta rutakanu.
Waneya pohirtshi wla htshinanna hpotukle sreta hajene: — “Hinanu, Nuru kihleru htshinyehixyahi. Hyoptotapanru hyoptolerupa Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hixa tshinanu halpokotkalurutka hma muyakotkonuklunuwa xye tshijne.
Klu tshinanu nnatshikanaxinixka hixa henek-nikletno, nonunnahatewakanaxini hixa henek-hirretno hiyrunu hma metjejetanutno hyoptokanata.
Mamkatno nixinixka, hmakatno. Nyeyixakanaxinixka, hixa hinotno hiyrun-koxa preso nwaka nwakanaxinixka, hixa hapkapyehitatkano.”
Hikluhe wetyi wma metjejetanutyi waneya wyoptotyi ho mamkatyi wmakata?
Hikluhe wetyi pyeyixyawaka ho preso nwaka hwatshriyi wapkapyehityi?”
— Waneya pohirtshi hihitanna, wla htshinanna: — “Halikakni wane ntshinhi, xyekaka hkamhiniklunna nomolene haté mujhakot-potu tshinanu hkamhinri, nkahwaklu hita tshinanu hkamhalu.
— Waneya wla htshinanunna pa sta sreta hajenepni: — “Hyachatanutka, hapnokatkalunephi! Tshitshmero hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa yehi tsru kamtshi hiyrunu htowrene kamtshine tshinanu halpokotkaluru yehi hyanu.
Klu tshinanu nnatshixiniklunu, hi henek-nikletno hiyrunu nonunnahatewaxiniklunu hi hohlutno.
Hma metjejetanutno hi hyoptota hiyrunu mamkatu nixiniklunu hi hmakatno. Nyeyixiniklunu ho preso nwaka nwiniklunu hixa hi hapkapyehitno.
— Wanna koxa wla htshin-hepomhaletanru: — “Tsru Hixikatshriwa, hikluhe wetyi pnatshixyawaka ho ponunnahatewaxyawaka ho wma metjejetanutyi ho mamkatyi ho yeyixatshriyi ho preso nwaka hwatshriyi waneya waneklu hi wepixyi?”
— Waneya ruhitanna, wla htshinanna: — “Halikakni wane ntshinhi, hma kamhanutu xyekaka nomolene haté mujhakot-potu tshinanu, hita tshinan-koxa hi hkamhalu.”
— Waneya wanna hapnokaxikowaka hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa yehi hyanuna seyni potukalune yoptotanru hiweklu hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa.
Hjemahchinikankakyehitluna Jesus Ruylaxyawakapluna PiranapniWaneya xye pirankaka rali tshinrexinixka Jesus, wla htshinatkana rasruklene:
— Hixa himatlu hepi hohne mahatlu Páscoa hohne tshinkaluru waneya Jeji Whene renekko cruz rupniywakpatka.
Waneya tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hiyrun-koxa tsrukakalune judeu-ne tsru pjiru tsru sacerdote Caifás tshinkalurupji rapatjexyana.
Waneya rujhahchinikanutna hanu rixa himukata preso hitakletluna Jesus yokwiruyma ruylaxyawakapluna.
Waneya wla htshinatkana: — Seyni xye hi wkamhanu tsru hohne pchinika hmakanhiywakanupa yin-sejire.
Suxo Phamluhalo Hiyokjiwuxyawaklu Jesus PiranapniWaneya Jesus, Simão tshinkaluru hijirohitutatshripji Betânia poktshi rawakanaxini,
sato suxo yanwakatlu. Pa stono phamluhalo kwenuro potuko yehi tanika. Jesus nikawakakwa rukóluha waneya Jesus jiwu tuyokhatlo phamluhalo.
Seyni rasruklene hexinixkalo, rumtuwnahchinikanutna, wla htshina: — Klu tshinanhe t-saletachatlo?
Phamluhalo tsru wenru tumukata hichankalexyalo waneya wale tiyirotemka tumukata henekletna hike mwikane.
Waneya Jesus himatlu klu htshinna hiyáhoni wla htshinna: — Haklu hikojwaklo twu suxo? Kihler-potuko tkamhiyno.
Hike mwikane ptowru hohneruka himwanu hixa tskalaya seyni hi ptowru hohneruka pimwanno hita.
Phamluhalo tutakmanexinno, talpokomanetno nkapnaxikolupa.
Halikaka ntshinhi, psol-tshijneko kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana hinkaklexiko, tkamhaleru koxa hinkakletko, tuchinijikolupa wala.
Judas Tshinkaluru Kamnixyawaklu Jesus PiranapniWaneya satu doze rixinri Jesus hasrukleru, Judas Iscariotes tshinkaluru yanwakatna tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne.
Waneya repomhana: — Kluhe henekanno Jesus nenejiniphi? Waneya rutakyahoklona trinta proji tiyiro renejyawakapluna.
Waneklu kananuko rujhalu hiklukta hpoyaho hekhiretanna, Jesus rekhixyawakapna.
Jesus Páscoa Hohne Hichinijyawaka PiranaPão myapjetu hnikjexinrina hohne rasruklene yanwakatlu Jesus, repomhapyaluna, wla htshinruna: — Hanurhe walpokotanru Páscoa hohne nikle wnijyawakapa tshinanu?
Waneya wla htshinna: — Tsru poktshi hjihlojinipa wane hyoptoxinri satu jeji waneya punkakanru: “Kasruklewakleru wla tshina: Nohohnestsitkani. Páscoa hohne nikle pipji wnijini.”
Hiyáhoni rasruklene kamhalu htowuxyawakna, ralpokotatkaluna Páscoa hohne hniklerupna hnijyawakapna.
Jesus Hekhixyawaklu Hkamnitjeru PiranapniPáscoa hohne kayno Jesus hiyrunu rasruklene doze nikawakakwa rukoluhana.
Waneya wanna wamonuwpotuta waneya satkaka yinuwaka hepomhaletlu: — Hitlahe?
Jesus hihitna: — Nkamnitjerukni hitayma pão yotshmota prato-ya.
Jeji Whene tshinkaluru halikaka hipnanu Hoyakalu hixahchinikanuxyawaka pixka. Seyni hektu potlu wale jeji, Jeji Whene tshinkaluru kamnitatshri. Kihle potlu wale jeji hma matuxyawakanutka.
Waneya Judas, Jesus kamnitjerupa, wla tshina: — Kasruklewakleru, hitlahe? Waneya Jesus hihitlu, wla htshinru: — Pixako wan-tshina.
Jesus Hipninri Yapkakle PiranapniWaneya hnikka pchinikna, Jesus pão hkochtsheka. Waneya hpoyahnutlu Hoyakalu. Hjiknajrotlu pão waneya rasruklene reneklu. Waneya wla htshina: — Pão hyoptotanu, hnikanru. Xyeni hatatjewa nomane.
Waneya copa stono hkochtsheka. Hpoyahnutlu Hoyakalu, rasruklene reneklu. Waneya wla htshina: — Xye copa himurkakanu hixa ptowrunekhi.
Twu copa stonha nunkakletleru, waleni herotu nohraha piranni. Xye nohraha hixolune yine tshinanu hiyokkalurupa hektuntshi hiknojikowakapa tshinanu.
Halikaka wane ntshinhi hikeklu hohne nnikanru xye Páscoa hohne tshinanupa haté rakanhanu Páscoa hohne potu Nuru Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawakaya.
Waneya satu chikale hchikaletna, ralimtna, himriji Monte Oliveiras tshinikowaka hyatkana.
Jesus Hinkaklu Pedro Wkatakluyakawa PiranaWaneya Jesus wla tshinna: — Xawakni yetshno potuko hixa ptowrunekhi hiknokanno niknohlerupa tshinanu klu tshinanu wla htshina Hoyakalu tokanu: “Nuylatanru carneiro-ne hinotatshri, waneya hiprane hipalatanu.”
Seyni niwejinpatnaka, hita kosekanhi hixa Galileia tshijne nwaka.
Seyni Pedro wla tshina: — Yáholu ptowruneka hiknojinyi, hita hikeklu nuknokanyi.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru: — Halikaka wane ntshinyi. Xye yetshno hma yanumatkanuklunuwa patlapa, pixa map-kata pma mimatletanutu ptshinanno.
Seyni Pedro wla tshinru: — Hike! Hikeklu hohne nma mimatletanutu ntshinanyi yáholu pixayma nupnanu. Waneya pimrine rasruklene ptowruneka koxa wane potuko htshinna.
Jesus Getsêmani Tshinikowaka Hyiywaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus rasrukleneyma Getsêmani tshinikowaka hya. Waneya wla htshina: — Hixa hewitshi tuplatanu, hawla nyanu nanjihohnexyawakapa.
Pedro hiyrunu Zebedeu whenene hepi ranika waneya hyinuwaka wamonuwleta, hsalewnahchinikanuta.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinna: — Niwejinri wamonuwpotuthonuka, hatatjewa nupnakastsitkani. Hewiphitshi, hitayma hislahanu.
Waneya pnutejiji hya, hyospaka tshiji rutspakhojita, wla htshina ranjihohnereya: — Nuru! Palujinipa pkochripaxinno twu copa salewaktshi yehiya. Seyni hi hitako nalujyawaka pkamhanu seyni pixako palujyawaka pkamhanu halikaka.
Waneya Jesus satokanwakatna rasruklene, retamtna himkatshine, waneya repomhalu Pedro: — Hi he pa hora-kna himukata hislahleta hitayma?
Hislahanu, hanjihohnetanu hmallixikowakanupa. Klu tshinanu jmeremkahi seyni mantshicha mmixkotni.
Hiyrunuko pnute hya ranjihohnexyawakapa, wla htshina hanjihohnereta: — Nuru, nma muriknuko pchinro twu copa salewaktshi yehiya hi tumukata hitneprikkakota, palujyawaka pkamhanu.
Waneya hsatokatnaka rasruklene nwaka, retamtna himkatshine hi rumukata himrekhayhaletna.
Hiyáhoni hyatnaka, map-kata rixinri ranjihohnetatnaka, htshinakanaxyawaka pixka htshina hanjihohneretatnaka.
Waneya Jesus satokanwakatatnakna rasruklene, wla htshinna: — Himkawhe, hapnanutawhe? Hetanu, rapokpapkolutatka. Jeji Whene tshinkaluru hektuwaka kamhatshinemyo rutakkatka.
Hpalnanu, hayewa! Tujrapa nkamnitjeru!
Jesus Kachixikowaka PiranapniJesus yanumakanaxiniwa, satu rasruklene Judas tshinkaluru hapokatka. Waleymalune hixolune tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hiyrun-koxa tsrukakalune judeu-ne yokanatanune. Yohlolewapi hiyrunu hahaje ranikna.
Kamnitatshri satu rimaxikole runkakna, wla htshina: — Katukta namlutanu, walekatkani. Hkachitanru wale.
Waneya Judas hajeyri hapokastsitlu Jesus waneya wla htshinru: — Hali, kasruklewakleru! Waneya ramlutlu.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru: — Nimatletleru, pkamhanru paluka kamhaletanru. Waneya hkachpiratjene hinanwakatlu Jesus, hkachpotutluna.
Seyni Jesus wla tshinru: — Pimretanru pyohlolewapre klu tshinanu katukta hiylalewata yohlolewapiyma, yohlolewapi ruylaxikotka.
Hixlahe kahwaklu hi numukata hanjiretlu Nuru waneyamka wale hixolune hiwejikalune htowrene tenhohne hajene doze ptohkakamka hyokanatanu repixyawakapnona?
Seyni wan-rixini hanhe xawaka rixa poyahokakletanu Hoyakalu tokanu tshinyawaka rujhalu wan-rixyawakapa yonatkaluru tshinyawaka pixka?
Waneklu Jesus wla tshinatkana hkachitjene: — Katshowhurlanohe wkata hina yohlolewapikakayma, hahajekakayma koxa hkachixyawakapno? Ptowru hohneruka Hoyakalupji nasrukjekanaxyahi. Seyni hi hkachitno.
Seyni xye ptowruka hakanha Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshinni yonreru tshinyawaka hpoyahokajyawakapa tshinanu. Waneya rasruklene ptowruneka hichotatkalu, rasukatkana.
Tsrukakalune Jemahchinikankakyehixyawaklu Jesus PiranapniJesus kachitjene hanikatkalu tsru sacerdote Caifás tshinkaluru yehi, wane koxa rapatjexyana kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine hiyrunu tsrukakalune judeu-ne.
Seyni Pedro hohatjinijiji romkahyehixyalu Jesus haté tsru sacerdote-pji maleka sreta potuko. Waneya tsru sacerdote hiputre hjihloka, htuplata Hoyakalupji soldado-teneyma rethixanuyehitlu.
Waneya tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hiyrunu pimrine tsrukakalune jemahchinikankakatshine hijhamkalu satu rukolukanuwninri yáhole rumukata hiylalexyawakapluna.
Yáholu hixolune hapokatshine weyawyehitlu Jesus seyni hi jikolukanuru rukchikna ruylalexyawakluna. Waneya hepi hapkatatatshine hapoka.
Wla htshinna: — Xye jeji wla tshina: “Numukata nikatletanru Hoyakalupji seyni map-hohne pnute, nkamhanutnaklu.”
Waneya tsru sacerdote palnatka, wla htshinatkalu Jesus: — Hanhe pixa hihletanru hjihyehixyayina?
Seyni Jesus potshkecha. Waneya tsru hixikatshriwa sacerdote wan-tshinru: — Ntowutyi Hoyakalu Hiwekatshri hetanuya. Punkakanwu, pixlahe Messias-yi, Hoyakalu Whenyi?
Jesus hihitlu, wla htshina: — Hehe, pixako wan-tshina. Seyni ptowruneka tshinanu wla ntshina: Xawaknikananuko hixa hetanru Jeji Whene, hohimkohi hoho hapokatshripa, Ptowru Himukatatshri Hoyakalu potukle sreta tuplatatshripni.
Waneya tsru sacerdote hjihekannu tshinanu hsuskamkaluxnawa waneya wla htshina: — Hektuwaka htshinanwakatlu Hoyakalu! Hi wujhana pimrine hiphujtatatshine. Hetanu, xawakni hjemlu hektuwaka htshinanwakaxyawaklu Hoyakalu!
Hiyáhoni kluhe hkahwaka hixa? Waneya pimrine hihitlu, wla htshinna: — Waleko htshinanu rujhalu rupniywakapa!
Waneya rutskahahojitlu Jesus, rutsojtakluna. Pimrin-koxa himpaklu.
Waneya wanna wla tshinru: — Xawakni Messias tshinikatshriwayi, pmetanutu punkaklewatanu kathe hiylakyi?
Pedro Wan-tshina Hi Rimathetlu Jesus PiranapniPedro honra tsru sacerdote hiputre tuplata waneya sato towretshro yanwakatlu, wla ttshinru: — Pix-koxa Jesus Galileia hajeruymalutyi.
Seyni Pedro ptowru yineru hetanu hmetjejetanutu htshinru, wla htshina: — Hi nimata klukta ptshina.
Waneya Pedro hiputu jihlokawakle hya, wane koxlo sato suxo. Waneya tetlu, wane hwakanatatshine tunkaka, wla ttshina: Xye jeji Jesus Nazaré hajeruymalutni.
Hiyrunuko hmetjejetanutu htshinatnaklu, wla htshina: — Nmunanhalu Hoyakalu, hi nimathetlu xye jeji!
Hi howukchini wane hwatshine yopkakatshine Pedro-stsi rapokna waneya wla htshinatkaluna: — Pixa halikaka wannaymalutyi klu tshinanu Galileia hajene pixka pixa yanumleta.
Waneya hyinuwaka hektuwaka tshinrexnawa, wla htshinatnaka: — Halikakni hi nimathetlu xye jeji! Waneya waneklukawa potuko patlapa yanumatatka.
Waneya Pedro hichinikaplu Jesus tokanu htshinakanaxyawaklu: “Hma yanumatkanuklunuwa patlapa, pixa map-kata hi pimathetno ptshinanu.” Hiyáhoni kahnete hya, tsru wamontshiyma htshiyahpotuthonukatka.
Pilatos Renejyawakapluna Jesus PiranapniYetshpotukawa tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hiyrun-koxa tsrukakalune judeu-ne ptowruneka hikchikahchinikanuta Jesus ruylaxyawakapna.
Rostutluna Jesus, waneya ranikluna Phuru Pilatos renejyawakapluna.
Judas-ni Hiylaxnawakwa PiranapniWaneya Judas, Jesus hiphujtatjeru, rexinixkalu rukolukanuwninritka Jesus, rehchinikanutatka hkamrure tsru hektutu tshinanu. Waneya trinta proji prata hsatkakatka tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hiyrun-koxa judeu-ne tsrukakalune tiyirote.
Waneya wla htshina Judas: — Hektuwaka kamhatshrino hita! Klu tshinanu hike mixkatuko nenekna hkamnitjene. Seyni wanna wan-tshinru: — Seyni hike wix-hixa. Waleni pixako ptshinanni.
Hiyáhoni Judas hiknokatkalo proji tiyiro Hoyakalupjiya waneya ruchpakatka. Wane pnute rostuplaxnanwa.
Hiyáhoni rukchikahchinikanutna ranjixyawakapluna Kajpako Kamni tshinkaluru tshijne. Walekni pnu tshijne hichpajikatshri kapnaxikowaka.
Wale tshinanu haté xawakni “Jratshijneru” htshinikowakatka wale tshiji.
Hiyáhoni wan-rixatka hpoyahokajyawakaplu Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshrini Jeremias tshinkalurni tshinyawaka, wla htshina mitshi: “Rawlona trinta proji tiyiro prata kamhikaluru rutakwenruxikolu wenru, pimrine israel-nerune klopichane hitakwenrutanru,
ranjixyawakapluna Kajpako Kamni tshijne, Tsru Hixikatshriwa tshinyawakno.”
Pilatos Yehi Ranijyawakluna Jesus PiranapniWaneya Jesus tsru hixikatshriwa Pilatos tshinkaluru hetanu hyopkaka waneya Pilatos hepomhalu: — Pixlahe judeu-nerune pohiryi? Jesus hihitlu, wla htshinru: — Pixako wan-tshina.
Waneya tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hiyrun-koxa tsrukakalune judeu-ne jihyehixinixkalu Jesus, hike htshina.
Waneya phuru Pilatos hepomhalu: — Hi he pjemlu hjihyehixyayina?
Seyni Jesus hike tshina, hi satukna hjihyehixikolu ruhita. Waneya phuru himyekahchinikanuta wan-rixyawaka tshinanu.
Tsru niklu hohne tshinanu phuru Pilatos hasruhlu satu preso hajeru hichoxyawaka, yine nurrer-potuko.
Waneklu papko satu jeji ptowru yineru himatyehreru Barrabás tshinkaluru preso hwa.
Hiyáhoni hixolune hapatjexinixka, repomhana: — Hanurhe nuchoxinhi ho Barrabás tshinkaluru ho Jesus, Cristo tshinkaluru?
Klu tshinanu Pilatos himathetna judeu-nerune tsrukakalune hhahxalna tshinanu, Jesus renekluna.
Waneya phuru Pilatos jihyehixikowaka htuplakanaxiniwa, wale hnunro yonawahlo yokananwakatlu, wla tshinatshri: — Petachatanru xye jeji hike mixkatu klu tshinanu xye yetshno nsalewnapotuta nupnawleya wale tshinanu.
Seyni tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hiyrun-koxa tsrukakalune judeu-ne hanjijixpotutlu hixolune hanjixyawakaplu Pilatos ruchoxyawakaplu Barrabás tshinkaluru hiyrun-koxa Jesus ruylajixyawakapa.
Waneya Pilatos hepomhana: — Hanurhe nyi hepi jejine nuchoxinhi? Waneya ruhitluna: — Barrabás.
Waneya repomhatnakna: — Kluhe nkamhinri Jesus, Cristo tshinkaluru? Wanna ptowruneka hihitlu: — Cruz putakanru!
Seyni repomhatnakna: — Haklu tshinanni? Klu hektuntshihe hkamha? Seyni pnut-potu hsaplewatna, wla htshinna: — Cruz putakanru!
Waneya phuru Pilatos hexinri pnute hi rumukatatka hiyrun-koxa tsru sejirtshi hyinuwakpiratna, honha ranikakjixatka waneya reromyohatka hixolune hetanu. Waneya wla htshina: — Xye jeji hiylaxikowakapa hi hitako ntshinanu seyni hixako htshinanupni.
Waneya ptowru yineru hihitlu, wla htshinruna: — Wale hraha hixa wtshinanupni hiyrunu wiklopichanepa tshinanupni.
Waneya phuru Pilatos henekna Barrabás tshinkaluru. Seyni Jesus hkotshipjejixa, waneya renekna cruz rutajyawakapluna.
Soldado-ne Heyijyawaklu Jesus PiranapniWaneya soldado-ne haniklu Jesus phurupji waneya soldado-ne ptowruneka Jesus-stsi hapatjexya.
Hkomkahatkaluna waneya mkatshri serolu hmakatluna Jesus.
Waneya kawchiriplu hsaxpatna sahyi hkamhiywakapna, Jesus jiwu rutajyawakapluna. Waneya Jesus potuklemyo rutakluna hahaje, hyoptsojityehitluna, reyikatkaluna, wla htshinruna: — Hali judeu-ne Tsru Hixikatshriwate!
Waneya rutskahjetluna, hahaje hkochtshekna, rutpejiwutluna.
Rali heyiklexinixkaluna, mkatshri serolu hkomkahatkaluna waneya waleko himkalu rutakleru hmakatatnakluna. Waneya ranikluna cruz rutajyawakapluna ruylaxikowakapa.
Simão Tshinkaluru Hanijyawaklu Jesus Cruz-te PiranapniWaneya ranikakanaxinixkaluna Jesus hatnu hapoya, satu jeji hyoptotna Simão tshinkaluru Cirene poktshi hajeru. Waneya cruz rutjikakluna.
Cruz Rutajikowakapa Jesus PiranapniWaneya rapokluna Calvário tshinikowaka. (Wale tokantshi yokakkaluru, yineru jiwuta pixkalutu yehi.)
Wane vinho-ha kapsalu yapjetkaluru ruxyaluna Jesus seyni retumhiniklunru hi hyoptotatkalu.
Waneya rali cruz hitaklexinixkaluna, hiknokkaluru ruknokna soldado-ne rimaxyawakapna katu kayatanru Jesus-ni mkalu.
Waneya Jesus jiwu hohwaka raw-yonhata Jesus jihyehixikolu pirana. Wla htshin-yonhata: “Xyeni Jesus judeu-ne pohire.”
Hiyrun-koxa katshowhurune hepi wan-rutakna. Satu Jesus potukle sreta rutakka. Satu pa sta sreta hitakka.
Hiknohatshin-koxa hektutu tshinanwakatlu, ruwnownojiwyehitluna.
Waneya wla htshinruna: — Pix-hima kopalatanru Hoyakalupji waneya map-hohne ppanawatanutnaka hiyáhoni piwekkajinwa! Halikaka Hoyakalu Whene pixinipakni, cruz pkochpajinwa!
Waneko pixka rixa heyikletluna tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne, kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine hiyrun-koxa tsrukakalune judeu-ne waneko pixka rixa heyikletluna.
Wla htshinruna: — Pimrine riwekkaka seyni wale nanuko hi rumukata hiwekkaklexnawa! Hi he judeu pohirni wale? Cruz hkochpajiniklunupwa tsonu walixanru.
Hi he Hoyakalu munanhalerni? Hi he Hoyakalu Whene tshinikatshriwani? Hiyáhoni wetanru ho Hoyakalu haluk-hepixletanru.
Jesus-yma cruz hitakkalune waneko pixka rixa heyikletkoxluna, hixo hektutu htshinanwakatluna.
Jesus Hipninri PiranapniWaneya hanikaj-hohnetkani rutshpokatka, três hora pchinika psol-tshijneka hitshpoka.
Waneya mapa hora-stsitkani Jesus wla tshin-saplewleta: — “Eloi, Eloi, lamá sabactâni?” Wale tokantshi yokakkaluru: “Noyakalute, Noyakalute, haklu pumuknokanno?”
Waneya satkaka wane hwakanatatshine xye jeminixka, wanna wla tshina: — Elias-ni htomha.
Waneklukawa satu jeji hasukamta kamkolu ruhajyawakapa. Vinagre-ha rutaka, hahajestsipto rutaklu, Jesus rurjixlu.
Waneya pimrine wla tshinru: — Petachatanru. Weteru ho Elias tshinkaluru hepixanru ho hike.
Waneya Jesus hipokananu saplewatatka, rupnanatka.
Waneklukawa mkatshri sama Hoyakalupji hwatshrini hiskakana hepi tshraj-samanru, teno haté tshiji ruskajyanatka. Tshiji hiyolikatka, sotlukaka hipokanatka.
Waneya yomletshikaka kotpukkatka, hixo yinni potukalunni hipnakanatatshinni hiwekkakkatka.
Yomletshikaka ruchpajyatkana waneya Jesus hiwejinritnaka hohne pnute, Jerusalém poktshi hyamtna, hixolune yehi ruphujewniyna.
Waneya romano-neru soldado-ne pohire hiyrun-koxa Jesus hislahatshine waleymalune tshiji hiyolikle hiyrunu ptowru hiknohatshri rexinixkaluna, rimyekahchinikanutna, waneya wla htshinna: — Halikakni xye jeji honnira Hoyakalu whene.
Wane koxna hixo suxone Jesus homkahitjene Galileia rumuchpajinine ruslahjerone, xye ptowruka howuka retakanaxyana.
Sato wannaymalune Maria Madalena tshinkaluro, sato Maria tshinkaluro Tiago hiyrunu José hinro hiyrun-koxa sato Zebedeu whenene hinro.
Jesus Kapnaxikolu PiranapniWaneya kayi rixinixka satu phuru José tshinkaluru, Arimateia hajeru, hapoka. Wale koxa Jesus hasrukleru.
Hyanwakatlu Pilatos, ranjixyawakaplu Jesus-ni mane. Waneya Pilatos henekjixlu.
Waneya José kochtsheklu Jesus-ni mane, mkatshri sama powralu, linho sama, ruwtoklu.
Waneya sotlu jitoxikolu hipjitaya José kapnaxikowakamkapa, satukna mutajikowakanuwa, rutakmanetlu Jesus-ni. Waneya tsru sotlu reruta yomletshi jihlojikowaka, ruchyaxyawakaplu waneya hyatka.
Hepi tuplakanatatshine koxa yomletshi yoptowakle sreta tuplakanata, Maria Madalena tshinkaluro hiyrunu sato Maria tshinkaluro.
Yomletshi Ruslahyawakna PiranapniWale prika, walekni hapnanuxikaluru prik-hohne, tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hiyrun-koxa fariseu-ne yanwakatlu phuru Pilatos.
Waneya wla htshinatkaluna: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, wuchiniklu wale kyokwirewaklerni riwekakanaxinni wla htshina, Map-hohne hiknohinpatka niwekkako.
Hiyáhoni ptowutanru kihle hislahle potuko rixanruna yomletshi map-hohne pejnu tshinanu. Himanni hma tshowhutapyawakanupna rasruklene wla hma tshinyawakanupna riwekatka hipnatshinetka tskalaya. Hiyáhoni xye rapkatle hyokwirewle yohnik-himtukaplu.
Waneya Pilatos hihitna, wla htshinna: — Nenekanhi soldado-ne yomletshi hislahatshinepa. Hajewa, hanukta hixa himukata hislahletanru, wan-hixanru.
Jesus Hiwejyawakatnaka PiranapniWaneya hyinuwakle seman-hohne, yetshpotukawa, Maria Madalena tshinkaluro hiyrunu sato Maria tshinkaluro yomletshi retapna.
Chinpotukawa tshiji hiyolikpotutatka, satu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru, tenhohne hichpajikatshri hapokle tshinanu waneya rerutlu sotlu yomletshi hajeru waneya htuplahohotlu.
Rawrakle pixka rixhojita hiyrunu himkalu klat-potu neve pixka.
Waneya yomletshi hislahatshine soldado-ne, rutatakna waneya hipnatshine pixka rixanatkana, tsru hpiklena tshinanu.
Waneya hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru wla tshinna suxone: — Hi hpikanu, nimatlu Jesus, cruz hipnapikatshri hijha.
Hi hewitkalu seyni riwekatnaka halikaka, htshinyawaka potuko pixka. Wkata hina, hetapyawakaplu rukoluhakanaxyawaka.
Waneya chinpotukawa hyanu, rasruklene hinkajyawakapa, wla htshinanna: “Hipuktshi riwekkajikatka. Wale kosekamtanhi hixa Galileia tshijne. Wane hexinri.” Xawakni hichinikanru ntshinyahi.
Waneya yomletsh-yehi ruchpajyana suxone, hchiretna. Hpikmakna seyni rumuwahchinikanupotutkoxna. Rasukamtna rasruklerune runkakapyawakapna.
Waneya chinpotukawa Jesus yoptotna. Wla htshinna: — Kihlehchinikanuphi. Waneya suxone hapokanwakatlu, hsaprikjixitluna, rimalwuxyawakapluna.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinna: — Hi hpikanu. Hajewa, nomolene hinkakapanu Galileia tshijne hyiywakapna. Waneko rexinnona.
Yomletshi Hislahatshine Hinkakle PiranapniRasruklene nwaka hyaka pchinikna suxone, satkaka yomletshi hislahatshri poktshi yatka runkaklewaxyawakapna tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne ptowru hakanhatshritka.
Waneya tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hiyrunu tsrukakalune judeu-ne hapatjeta hjemahchinikankajyawakapna hanu rixanna. Waneya tsru tiyiro renekatkana soldado-ne yomletshi hislahatshine.
Hiyrunu wanna wla tshinna soldado-ne: — Wla htshinanu: “Hoyetshno wumkakanaxinixka rasruklene tshowhutaplu himanni.”
Seyni xye pirana hjeminipa phuru Pilatos, wiynumsatanru hma kojwakahchinikanuxyawakanupa.
Hiyáhoni soldado-ne yoptotlo tiyiro waneya tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne tshinakjixyawakna potuko htshinatkana. Hiyáhoni xye pirana soldado-ne hinkakle hipalapiranatatka judeu-ne tskalaya haté xawakni.
Jesus Hakanhiywaka Galileia Tshijneya PiranapniWaneya onze rasruklene Galileia tshijne hyatkana, himriji Jesus tshinyawak-potukna.
Jesus rexinixkana, rimalwutluna seyni pimrine satkaka hi halixlu.
Tsru Towutlu PiranapniWaneya Jesus hapyehitna rasruklene waneya wane htshinna: — Hita henekka psol-potuko tsru hitakkaluru tenhohneya tshij-koxa.
Wale tshinanu hyanu. Hasrukanna ptowru tshijne hajene. H-batiza-tanna Hoyakalu Hirtshi hiwakaya, Hoyakalu Whene hiwakaya, Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hiwakaya.
Hasrukanna kajnako rixyawakapna wale pirana psoluka ntowuthi hinkaklexyawaka. Hiyrun-koxa hixayma nwanu psol-hohneko hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa.
<font color=teal>Marcos</font>Kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana yinuwajikolu Jesus Cristo, Hoyakalu Whene pirana.
João Batista PiranapniWan-rixa yonretatkalu Isaías-ni Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshrini: Wla htshina yonatkaluru mitshi: “Hita yokanatlu ntowreru pixa hnapu. Wale halpokotanru patnu hapote.
Kahnete poktshiri saplewaxikatshri tokanu wla tshinatshri: Halpokotanru Tsru Hixikatshriwa hatnu hapote. Hpotukatanru hatnu hapotkaka.”
João Batista kahnete poktshiri hiphujewniyatka. Runkakletluna yine h-batiza-xikolupna rehchinikanuxyawakna pirana, wla htshina: — Hehchinikanutanu hektunu tshinanu. Wan-hixko h-batiza-xikolupa hiyrunu hektuntshi hiknojiko Hoyakaluya.
Waneya hyanwakatluna ptowruneko Judeia sreta hajene Jerusalém hajen-koxa João hyijnakoxyawakapna. Waneya ruphujetluna rektunna waneya João batiza-tatkana wanna Jordão wenneya.
João mkalu camelo pixi kamhikolni, kpixnuru h-cinturão-te couro-mta kamhikolu. Hnijitu tsetseru, wrolha hocha hajeru.
João Hiphujtaxyawaklu Jesus PiranapniRunkaklewata. Waneya wla htshina: — Xekoyaka runanu hita yohnik-himukatkalutu. Hita hi Tsru Hixikatshrino nkochpirojyaplu h-sandalha-tetslu.
Hita halikakni n-batiza-thi honhaya seyni wale batiza-tanhi Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluruya.
Jesus Batiza-xikolu PiranapniWaneklu papko Nazaré, Galileia tshijne hajeru poktshi ruchpajya Jesus waneya João Batista batiza-tlu Jordão wenneya.
Waneya waneylu tokantshi tenhohneyalutu wan-tshinatshri: — Pixni Noturyi nalukanruyi, wale poyikowkakno.
Jesus Yohnixikolu PiranapniWaneklukawa potuko Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru yokanatlu Jesus kahnete poktshiri hyiywakapa.
Waneya quarenta hohne pchinika kahnete poktshiri rawakanata. Wane Satanás yohnixyalu Jesus. Hocha hajene kmatsyirune tskalaya rawakanata. Hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrene tenhohne hajene hepixlu Jesus.
Jesus Yinuwaka Kamrurewlexyawaka Galileia Tshijneya PiranapniWaneya hkachitkoklunutka João, Jesus Galileia hya. Runkaklewata kihle piranalu potuko Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka pirana.
Waneya wla htshina: — Rapokpapkolutatka, Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hi howukchinpatkalu. Hehchinikanutanu, halixanru kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana.
Jesus Nurexyawakna Satkaka Rikamrurewatjenepa PiranapniWaneya Galileia powha wnaha hyapamxini Jesus retlu Simão repuruyma André. Ruknokamtatkaluna h-tarrafa-tna hipowhaya klu tshinanu wanna mariskatatshine kchimahaklerune.
Waneya wane htshinna Jesus: — Hinanu hwahatjinitanno, yine kmariskahohoklerune nixkakanhi.
Waneya waneklukawa potuko ruknokamtatkaluna h-tarrafa-tna, romkahitatkaluna.
Wane pnutejiji hyapamtatnaka retlu Tiago, Zebedeu whene repuruyma João. Wanna koxa kanawa hwakanata, ripxatluna tarraf-kaka.
Waneya Jesus tomhana. Ruknokamtluna rurna Zebedeu kanawaya kkamrurewakleruneyma. Wane hyana, rawhatjinitluna.
Kkamtshiteru PiranapniWaneya hjihlokamtatkaluna Cafarnaum poktshi. Waneya hapnanuxikalur-hohne rixinixka hjihlokluna hanjihohnewakapji rasruklewaxyawakapa Jesus.
Waneya rimyekna yine rasruklewle tshinanu. Klu tshinanu Jesus tsru towutatshri pixka rixa hasrukletna, hi kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine pixka rixa hasrukletna.
Waneya hi howukchiniyaka satu jeji kkamtshiteru hanjihohnewakapji hwakanatatshri saplewata. Waneya wla htshina:
— Ya! Kluhe pixannatkawu Jesus Nazaré hajeru? Puna pumtukapyawakapwuhe? Nimatyi katyi pixa Potukalyi Hoyakalyi.
Seyni Jesus hi hinanchitlu. Waneya wane htshina: — Potshkepyi. Puchpakanutka wale maneya.
Waneya kamtshi kowchoklu jejni hipokananu, hsaplewata waneya ruchpakamtatka kamtshi.
Waneya ptowrunek-yine himyeka. Hiyáhoni repomhakakna, wane htshinna: — Klunerni xye? Klu herotu hasruklewlutkani xye? Tsru hitakkaluruyma kamtshi ruchpakjixa. Hiyrunu kamtshine jemlu htshinyawakna.
Waneya psol-tshijne potuko hpohiwhapkata Jesus pirana Galileia sretaya.
Pedro Himajiro Rutskalajyawaka Jesus PiranapniWaneya hajeyri ruchpakamxinixkana hanjihohnewakapji, wanna Tiago hiyrunu João-yma Simão Pedro hiyrunu himole André-pji nwaka hyatkana.
Simão himajiro hikóluha tyeyixa. Waneya runkaksatluna Jesus wala pirana.
Waneya Jesus yanwakatlo. Waneya hkosemyotlo, hyotunkaklo. Tutuk-patshwalemtatka. Waneya tyomhatna.
Jesus Hitskalajyawakna Katshinomtalune PiranapniWaneya kayi rixinixka rimxijinixka tkatshi ranikyehitluna ptowruneko yeyixatshine hiyrun-koxa kkamtshiterune.
Ptowruneko tsru poktshi hajene pantshi hiphaptote rapatjexyana.
Waneya Jesus hitskalakna hixo yeyixatshine ptowru hixatshri hahijewaktshi hwatshine. Maleka hyokanatna hixo kamtshine. Hi rutshi yanumsaletna kamtshine klu tshinanu rimathetluna.
Jesus Galileia Tshijne Yiywaka PiranapniWaneya yetshpotukawa hma mumrerekkanuklunuwa hyotunomta ruchpakamta Jesus. Waneya potshkewaka nwaka hya. Wane ranjihohnexya.
Waneya Simão Pedro hiyrun-koxa waleymalune hijhaplu.
Rukchijinixkaluna wla htshinruna: — Ptowruneko hijhayi.
Waneya wla htshinna Jesus: — Hayewa pimri poktshikaka hwastsitanune yehi wyanu, wane koxa nunkaklewaxyawakapa. Wale tshinanukni nuna.
Waneya Galileia tshijne psoluka hyapamtatka. Runkaklewakananumta wanna hanjihohnewakapjikakaya. Maleka hyokanatna kamtshine.
Jesus hetwamonutlu waneya romyokanwakatlu. Hyotneklu. Waneya wla htshinru: — Hehe, naluka. Putskalhatka.
Waneklukawa potuko rujirhitle ramhiyatka. Rutskalhatka.
<sup>(43-44)</sup> Waneya Jesus hijretlu wla htshinru: — Petanu. Hike punkakanu seyni pyanutka. Sacerdote pekhimantapinwa putskalhinrixka. Waneya panikanru henekachalu henekawaka nwaka Moisés-ni yonreru tshinyawaka pixka pimrine himaxyawakaplu putskalhiywakatka.
(-)
Seyni jeji hichpakamtatka hyinuwaka kopalpiranretlu hixo pirana potuko. Hiyáhoni wale tshinanu Jesus hi himukata phujewaka tsru poktshikaka jihloklexyawaka seyni kahnete yine mwiywakanu yehi rawjekanatatka Jesus. Wanepnawaka ptowru sretako hichpajikatshine yanwakjekanatlu.
Jesus Hiktehatshri Hitskalajyawaka PiranapniWaneya hi hix-hohne hiknohawa Jesus jihlokatnaklu Cafarnaum. Hyijnakpiranyehitka pantshitkalu.
Waneya wane rapatjexyana hixolune yine. Hiphaptostsiko maleka sreta hi hpoyahotatkana yine. Jesus tokantshi hinkaklewakanata.
Waneya yine yanwakatlu Jesus. Satu yineru hiktehatshri ranikyehitluna. Ranikjene quatro jejine.
Seyni hixolune yine tshinanu hi rumukata hijihlokletna hiktehatshriyma. Hiyahokni ranikluna pantshi hoho hwakwatatshri. Waneya hjihmikakwatluna Jesus hinaple waneya wane swa hkosputajyaluna hiktehatshri hijeko hikoluhamtatshri.
Waneya Jesus hexinri wanna halixle wane htshinru hiktehatshri: Mturu, pektunu puknojikatka.
Waneya wane koxa htuplakanatna pimrine kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine. Wanna wan-tshinahchinikanuta:
“Klu tshinanhe wane htshina xye jeji? Hektuwaka htshinanwakatlu Hoyakalu. Katu tsonhe himukata hiknokhektunutlu yineru? Satupkalu Hoyakalu tsonu.”
Waneklukawa potuko Jesus himatatka riwejinriya wan-rixahchinikanutna. Waneya wla htshina: — Klu tshinanhe wan-hixahchinikanuta?
Hanupothe kihle tshinko? Wla htshinikowaka hiktehatshri: “Pektunu puknojikatka”, ho wla htshinikowaka: “Pyotunotanu, pkochtshekjekotanu pyanutka”?
Seyni himatjempotuxyawakaplu Jeji Whene tshinkaluru hitakkalurutkani xye tshijiya ruknokhektunuxyawakapna yine hiyáhoni wla ntshinanru hiktehatshri:
— Pixa wane ntshinyi: Pyotunotanu, pkochtshekjekomtanu pyanutka pipji.
Waneklukawa hyotunomtatka, hkochtshekjekomtatka ruchpakamtatka ptowruneko hetanu. Ptowruneka tsru himyeklu rixna, rimalwutluna Hoyakalu. Waneya wla htshinna wanna: — Hikeklu hohne wane pixkalutu weta.
Jesus Tomhiywaklu Levi PiranapniWaneya Jesus hichpakatnaka. Tsru hipowha nwaka hyatka. Hixolune yine yanwakatlu. Waneya Jesus hasrukna.
Riknohamtka pchinika Jesus, retlu Levi Alfeu whene. Htuplakanata tuplawaka hwenuxikolu hyoptoxyawakapa. Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru: — Pomkahitanno. Waneya hpalnamtatka romkahitatkalu.
Jesus Hektune Himinjiywaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus rasrukleneyma Levi-pji nikawakakwa hwakanata. Wane koxa rawakanatna hixolune jijhawenruklerune hiyrun-koxa hektune. Klu tshinanu romkahitjene hixo.
Waneya kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine, fariseu-ne hajene hexinri Jesus jijhawenrukleruneyma hiyrun-koxa wanna hektuneyma hnika, repomhana Jesus hasruklene, wla htshinna: — Kluneru tshinanhe wannayma hnika, rura wanna jijhawenruklerune, hektuneyma?
Xye hjemini Jesus, wla htshinna: — Pomtalune hi haluklu kpinrewakleru seyni katshinomtalu haluklu. Hi nuna ntshanixyawakapna kihlerune seyni muhlene ntshanixyawaka rehchinikanuwaxyawakapna.
Hix-hohne Mnikkatu PiranapniWaneya João hasruklene hiyrun-koxa fariseu-ne hohajirewata. Runa satkaka yineru waneya Jesus repomhana, wla htshinruna: — Haklu tshinanhe João hasruklene hiyrunu fariseu-ne hasruklen-koxa hohajirewata seyni pixa hasruklene hi natshita?
Waneya wla htshinna Jesus: — Rumukata natshretnahe hnunrowlu hetatshine hnunrowatatshriymalune? Hike. Wannayma rawakanaxini hnunrowatatshri hi rumukata natshretna.
Seyni rapokhohnexinpatka hnunrowpiratatshri hixolune yehi hkochpajikoklunpatka. Waneklu papko halikaka rohajirewatanutkana wanna.
Hi kihle hipxatkolu mkatshri hitsruka herotu samayma. Klu tshinanu herotu sama himutskirhanunru waneya herotu sama hiskakkakanunru htseruwaswapotutanuna.
Hi kihle tsrutsoleji mapa hitakhatkolo vinho-ha hekamhakolha. Wan-rixkoklunutka vinho-ha hipchekkakanunru sac-kakapni. Tuyokhatanuna vinho-hapni waneya sac-kaka koxapni salewnanuna. Seyni vinho-ha herotu, saco herotu tutakhatka.
Jesus Hapnanuxikalur-hohne Yohnik-hijhakalurniHsana hyapakanata Jesus hapnanuxikalur-hohne. Waneya Jesus hasruklene jimlakahawamtlu hitakluhawa.
Hiyáhoni fariseu-ne wan-tshinru Jesus: — Petanu. Haklu tshinanu wan-rixana hapnanuxikalur-hohne hinanchitkalur-hohne?
Tsru sacerdote Abiatar tshinkaluru klu papko hjihloklu Hoyakalupji, waneya Davi-ni niklu pão-kaka Hoyakalu henekachalurupa. Wale hinanchitkaluru hnikni. Sacerdote-ne tsonu himukata nikletanru hnikni waneya rimotsatjene koxa reneklu hnijyawakapluna.
Waneya wla htshinna Jesus: — Hapnanuxikalur-hohne repixyawakaplu yine tshinanu hkamhaka. Hoyakalu hi kamhalu jeji hapnanuxikalur-hohne repixyawakapa.
Hiyáhoni Jeji Whene haté hapnanuxikalur-hohne yohnik-himukatatshrini.
Jesus Hitskalajyawaklu Hiprihamyotatshri PiranapniWaneya pa hohnepatnaka hjihloklu hanjihohnewakapji. Wane rawakanata satu jeji hiprihamyotatshri.
Ruslahpotukanatluna Jesus ho hapnanuxikalur-hohnerhe rutskalaklewatanu ho hike hjihyehixyamkapluna.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru jeji hiprihamyotatshri: — Yine hanikajite pyotunoxini.
Waneya wla htshinna Jesus: — Hanu phuthe htshina yonawahlo hapnanuxikalur-hohne hiykole pirana? Kluhe kamhako hapnanuxikalur-hohne? Kihleru ho hektutu? Ho renek-hiweklerewatanu ho hkamaklewatanu hapnanuxikalur-hohne? Seyni wanna hike tshina.
Waneya Jesus heknojtayehitmakna. Hjihekanuwata hwamonuwata chik-haji rixyawaka tshinanna. Waneya wla htshinru jeji: — Pyosurukkanotanu. Waneya hyosurukkanotatka, ruhlewamyotatka.
Waneya wane ruchpakamxyana fariseu-ne. Waneya Herodes-neyma rujhahchinikanutatkana wannakakluko hanu rixa himukata hiylaletluna Jesus.
Jesus Htokanu Tsonu Hihlexyana Katshinomtalune PiranapniWaneya Jesus wane hichpajyatka. Galileia powha hya rasrukleneyma. Romkahimtluna hixolune yine Galileia hajene Judeia hajen-koxa,
Jerusalém hajene, Idumeia hajene, pa sreta Jordão hajene, Tiro-stsi hwatshine, Sidom-stsi hwatshine koxa, Wanna ptowruneka yanwakatlu Jesus klu tshinanu hjempiranyehitluna ptowru Jesus kamhaleru.
Waneya Jesus hixolune yine hma mipxajyawakanupluna tshinanu ranjitna rasruklene sato kanawa rawapyawakapluna.
Klu tshinanu yine hi heppika rutskalaka hiyáhoni hkatshlikluna yeyixatshine mkojekananu hyotnejyawakapluna.
Waneya kamtshine hexiniklunru Jesus hyoptsojityehitluna. Hsaplewatna wla htshinna: — Pixni Hoyakalu Whenyi!
Waneya Jesus hipokananu hijretna hike hmunkajyawakanupna katni wale.
Jesus Nurexyawakna Doze Rasruklene PiranapniWaneya himriji hkankatka Jesus. Htomhana wale ruchinikanune. Waneya hyanwakatluna wale.
Jesus hitakna doze waleyma hwatshinepa. Hyokanatanunepa hinkaklewatatshinepa,
rutakko henejikolupa ruchpakjixyawakapna kamtshine.
Xyeni Jesus nuretanune doze-na: Simão, wale rutakhiwakata Pedro;
Tiago, Zebedeu whene, João, Tiago hepuru; (Hiwakatna Boanerges, waleni rutlohle pixkalune);
André, Filipe, Bartolomeu, Mateus, Tomé, Tiago Alfeu whene, Tadeu, Simão honukla Israel tshijne haluka mixkowkakletatshri,
Judas Iscariotes tshinkaluru, Jesus kamnitjerupa.
Yine Kahwaklu Jesus Kamtshi Rixyawaka PiranapniWaneya pantshi rapokatka Jesus, yine hixolune hapatjeyehitatnaklu. Hiyáhoni Jesus hiyrunu rasruklene hi himukata nikleta.
Waneya xye pirana hjeminna Jesus molene runna rawapyawakapluna Jesus klu tshinanu pimrine wan-tshinna jipukalerhetkoni.
Waneya Jerusalém poktshi hyopijyana kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine. Wanna wla tshinyehitlu Jesus: — Waneylu Belzebu tshinkaluru kamtshi pohire. Belzebu himukatleyma tshinanu hetko maleka ruknokna kamtshine.
Waneya htomhinixkana Jesus, wla htshina yapkakluya: — Hanhe rumukata Satanás maleka hiknoklexnawa Satanás?
Ptowru tshijne rawa nikawnatshripa, pa hchinikanurutu hmixlenu tshinanna wane tshijne hajene.
Hiyrun-koxa pantshi hajene wannakakluko pnu pejnu rixahchinikanutna hi rumukata hwachaletna.
Hiyrun-koxa Satanás kamtshi hkamnixiniklunwa pnuko rixahchinikanuxinwana Satanás hayinetene. Hi rumukata pnute yaletanu htowuwle.
Halikaka ntshinhi ptowru hixatshri hektuwaka Hoyakalu mukchikhihlenreru hkamhini yineru, ptowru hixatshri hektutu htshinanwakaxiniplu Hoyakalu, ramtakahchinikanuxiko rektunu.
Seyni katukta hektutu tshinanwakaxiniplu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hikeklu hohne ramtakahchinikanyehitkona rektunu seyni rektunu hikolukanuwnatshri hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupni.
Jesus wan-tshina klu tshinanu pimrine wan-tshinru, waneylu kamtshi.
Jesus Hinro Himolen-koxa PiranapniWaneya Jesus hinro, himolen-koxa Jesus yehi hapokatka. Maleka rawna. Htomhakjixluna.
Waneya hixolune yine rixiplatjene wane htshinruna: — Petanu, punro pepurun-koxa maleka rawna. Rujhayina.
Waneya Jesus hepomhana, wla htshinna: — Katnihe nunro hiyrunu nomolene?
Waneya reknojtayehitna rixiplatanune. Wla htshina: — Hewitkana nunro hiyrunu nomolene.
Hoyakalu halujyawaka kamhatshine wannani nepuru, nepuro, nunro.
Hitaklu Tataji Jiplaljekleru PiranapniWaneya hyinuwaka hasruklewletatnaka Jesus, Galileia powhastsiya. Rapatjeyehitluna hixolune yine hiyáhoni hyohreklo kanawa waneya htuplatatka. Rutneprijyalu ksatu hiyáhoni ptowruneko yine tshiji tsru powha wnaha hwa.
Waneya hi heppika pirana rasrukna Jesus yapkaklu piranayma. Wane htshina hasrukleta Jesus:
— Hjemanu. Satu jitaklewakleru hichpakamta rutaklewaxyawakapa.
Wan-rixa hipalajretlu. Pimriji hatnu hapostsi hapoktatajita. Waneya runna kochitshine hnikloktatajitanruna.
Pimriji sotlu hoho mteno tshijiwaka rapoktatajita. Waneya ruptshekhapkatamka klu tshinanu mteno tshijiwaka ruptshejya.
Hiyáhoni ruchpajinixka tkatshi, hjimanatkalu, ruprihanatka hitaklukaka hma matskinu tshinanu.
Pimriji kona yehi hapoktatajita. Waneya konaymakananuko htseruwna hiyáhoni hkakmokanatkalu. Waneya hi kajinatkalu.
Seyni hitataji kihle tshijiwaka hapokatshinetka hixolewnatka hiyáhoni satkakaji pejnu tshinanu trinta-ji rawatka ho sessenta-ji ho cem-ji rawatka.
Waneya wane htshinna Jesus: — Kajnakopnahi hyijnakoxyawakapa, hyijnakotanu.
Jesus Hasruklu Klu Hyapkakleta Hitataji Jiplaljekleru PiranaWaneya hyinixkana hixolune yine, doze rasruklene hiyrunu pimrine hitukatshine hepomhalu Jesus: — Hanhe htshina xye yapkaklu pirana?
Waneya wane htshinna Jesus: — Hixamka henekka himaxyawakaplu mimatkotu pirana Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka pirana. Seyni pimrine tshinanu yapkaklu nkamhiylu ptowru piranako.
Rexinna retmakna, hi rapkathojitna; hjeminna, hjemmakna hma mimatjeminixipna; wane hmixkanumka rehchinikanutanumkana, ramtakahchinikanyehitkomkana rektunna.
Waneya repomhana Jesus: — Hma mimatkanuklunru xye yapkaklu, hanu hixa himatletanru ptowruko yapkaklu?
Pnuteko hya hinkakletna: — Hoyakalu tokanu kkopalhimakleru kopalatlu Hoyakalu tokanu.
Hatnu hapostsi hapoktatajitatshri yaholni tokantshi jematshine. Seyni runa Satanás kamtshi. Hkonyana tokantshi rajiyna hitakkaluru.
Sotlu hanikajite hiknokkalune wannani tokantshi jematshine. Tokantshi hjeminixkana hyoptotmakluna tsru rumuwleymana.
Seyni hi waneyna hitskina wanna. Hiyáhoni pchini tsonu hwatshinepni. Runinipa yahtaletlewlu ramtakanruna tokantshi hjemlerna.
Kona yehi hapoktatajitatshine, wanna Hoyakalu tokanu jematshine pixkalune.
Seyni kojwakahchinikanrukaka, ho pohirewnalu, ho poyikowlukaka xye hohne hexikaluru mixkowpotuta waneya xekoyaka hkakmokannatkalu. Hiyáhoni hi hjiwatanatkana.
Seyni kihle tshijiwaka hapoktatajitatshine wannani Hoyakalu tokanu jematshine, rimatjemluna hiyrun-koxa hjiwatanutkana: satu trinta, satu sessenta, satu cem kata pnute hjiwatna.
Katalu PiranapniWane koxa htshinna Jesus: — Tanikkahe lamparina hachhaji hpuko tutajikowakapa? Hijeko hpukolahe tutakko? Hi wane tixanu. Seyni hi he lamparina kihle nikotle tixyawaka yehi tutakka?
Katukta kajnakopnapa hyijnakoxyawakapa, hyijnakotanu.
Wane koxa htshinna Jesus: — Hislahinri ptowruko hjemleru. Klu tshinanu yahotapi hixa hyahotapre, walako hyahoxika hiyrunu wala pso yohnik-hyahoxika.
Klu tshinanu katukta himatjemlu, Hoyakalu pnute rimatjemkakanru wale haté rimatjempotuxyawakaplu. Seyni mimatjemkatu haté rimatjemlejiji hkonanu Hoyakalu.
Hitataji PiranapniWane htshina Jesus: — Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka satu jeji jiplaljekleru pixkalutni. Ruplaljetatajita.
Waneya rumka, hyotunota wanepnawaka hitataji hiptsheka. Htseruwna. Seyni jitaklewakleru hi himata klu tseruwnakaklu.
Wale nanwaka jiwkajnawa tshiji mixkonu tshinanu. Mitshikananu ruptsheka. Wane pnute hhiwuwata. Wane pnutejiji ralixatka.
Rali serowlexinixka waneklutka kastakapiya hkastajikatka klu tshinanu rapokatka hipapkolu hjijiroxikolpatka.
Mostarda-tataji PiranapniWaneya pnuteko htshina Jesus: — Kluneru pixka rixa Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka? Kluneru nyapkakletanru?
Mostarda-tataji pixka rixa. Mostarda-tataji honukla pimri tataji kayaho mtsernurut-potu.
Seyni ttseruwniniklunu wala pot-tseruwnatshroni ptowru hejnuji munaya. Tsruplukaklo. Waneya kochitshine teno yapatshine hina toplukaka hkamhachalexyawakna hisure tshikle hpuko.
Jesus Yapkaklu Pirana Tsonuyma Runkaklewaxyawaka PiranapniJesus Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakna yine hixo xye pixkalutu yapkaklu piranayma. Rumukata hakotlexyawakna pso runkakna.
Yapkaklu minjeyma hi runkakna Jesus. Seyni rasruklene tsonu runkakpotutatka.
Jesus Kanniphalu Hitukkajyawaka PiranapniWaneya wale hohne kayi rixinixka Jesus wan-tshinna rasruklene: — Tujra sreta wnahlu powha wyanu.
Hiyáhoni hyokanatkatkana yine hixolune hyiywakapna. Waneya rasruklene yohreklo kanawa Jesus hwakanaxyawaka tlo. Waneya Jesus-ymapna. Hiyrun-koxa pimro kanawkaka waleymapa.
Waneya hyopyoka tsru kanniphalu. Htsepohjetlo kanawa hiyáhoni katsephatkalo.
Tostsi rumkakananumta Jesus hyostanojreya. Hiyáhoni rasruklene komyeklu. Waneya wla htshinruna: — Kasruklewakleru, hike pixhe wupniywakapa?
Waneya Jesus yotunotatka htshihetjetlu kanniphalu hiyrunu tenoplojhal-koxa. Waneya wla htshinru hipowha: — Potshke. Putukanutka. Waneya rutukatka kanniphalu. Pokokha rixatka hipowha.
Waneya repomhana Jesus: — Klu tshinanhe hpikatka? Hixlahe malixaklenhi?
Seyni tsru piklu rixna. Waneya wla htshinkakna wannakakluko: — Hanu hixatshri koxni xye jeji? Klu tshinanu kanniphalu hipowha koxa yijnakotlu.
Jesus Hitskalajyawaklu Jeji Hixolune Kamtshine Himwatshri PiranapniWaneya tujra wnahlu tsru hipowha Gerasa sreta rapokna Jesus rasrukleneyma.
Waneya kanawa ruptejinixka Jesus satu jeji kamtshine himwatshri yoptotlu. yomletsh-yehi ruchpajyatka.
Yomletsh-yehi rawjeta. Hike himukata hosturetlu hi yomuwatsaymako.
Hixo kata hkachitkamkatka. Yomuwatsamka rostutka himyonota, hihpeji koxamka. Seyni yomuwatsni hiknajromtana hmixkonu tshinanu. Hike himukata himaletletlu.
Psol-yetshnoko psol-hohneko himriji hiyrun-koxa yomletsh-yehi hsaplewjekananumxya. Rustajixnawa sotluya.
Waneya rexinixkalu Jesus howukaya rasukamta wale nwaka. Hyoptsojityehitlu.
Tsru saple rixa waneya wla htshina: — Jesus, Hoyakalu ten-potu hajeru whene! Kluhe pixannatkano? Nanjityi Hoyakalu hiwaka tshinanu hi psaletpotutanunno.
Wale wan-tshina klu tshinanu Jesus wan-tshinatkalu: — Kamtshi, puchpakanutkalu xye jeji.
Waneya Jesus hepomhalu: — Klu hiwakyihe? Waneya ruhitlu. Wane htshina: — Nhiwakni Hixoluru klu tshinanu hixolurun-potwu.
Waneya ranjipotutlu Jesus wale tshijne hma yokanaxyawakanupna.
Waneya kamtshine hipokananu ranjitluna Jesus, wla htshinruna: — Ptowutanwu porco mane wjihlojyawakanapa.
Waneya Jesus hitshitna. Hiyáhoni ruchpakamtatkana kamtshine. Waneya porco-ne mane hitokote hjihlokamtatkana. Waneya hixolunni porco-nni hepi mil hetkoni hipjita hijrujyanatka. Hipowha rapokanna waneya hipowha rahyejyanna.
Waneya porco-ne hinotatshine hasukamta. Runkaklewatna tsru poktshiya, hsana hajen-koxa.Waneya hixolune yine hinamta retapyawakanapna klu rixanna.
Gerasa Poktshi Hajene Hma Yoptoxyawakanuplu Jesus PiranapniWaneya rapokluna Jesus nwaka. Retluna kkamtshithixapatshri hixoluru hwakanatanru. Htuplakanata. Kamkatkalu kkamtshithixapatshri, kahchinikanutkalu. Waneya rimyekatkana yine.
Waneya kkamtshithixapatshri hetakanatjene hinkakna yine kkamtshithixapatshri pirana hiyrun-koxa porco-ne pirana.
Waneya hipokananu ranjitluna wanna tshijne ruchpajyawakapa Jesus.
Kanawa hyohrejinixka Jesus, kkamtshithixapatshri hanjitlu: — Pixaymanapno.
Seyni Jesus hi hitshitlu. Wane htshinhonuklu: — Pipji pyanutka pimwanune yehi. Punkakanna yine Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu rixa hepixlexyawakyi pirana. Punkakanna retwamonuxyayi pirana.
Waneya ralimta. Hyinuwaka hinkaklewletatka Decápolis poktshi Jesus hixyawakatkalu. Ptowruneko tsru himyeklu hixa.
Jairo Tshinkaluru Hanjireru PiranapniWaneya hkopruhatatnaka Jesus kanawaya. Pa sreta wnahlu hya. Rapatjeyehitluna hixolune yine. Tsru powha wnaha rawa.
Runa satu tsru hitakkaluru hanjihohnewakapji hajeru. Jairo hiwakatletatshri. Rexinixkalu hyoptsojityehitlu Jesus jixistsi.
Waneya ranjitlu Jesus wane htshina: — Nchítshoni tupnakastsinatkani. Punanu wala hoho putakamyotanu tutskalhiywakapa tiwejyawakapa.
Waneya Jesus waleyma wane hya. Hixolune yine romkahitjene hipxakjemtlu.
Jesus Hiyrunu Katshinomtalo PiranapniWaneya twa sato suxo hihrahawatatshro. Doze hwalapu hima tuhrahawatatka.
Hixo kpinrewaklerunemka pinixnixkalo hiyrunu tnikatlewatanatka ptowruka twinri. Wanepnawaka hi tuhlewata seyni tallikanatatka.
Waneya tjempiranyehixinixkalu Jesus, wale tjimne sretako tunya hixolune yehi waneya tkamrukamkatlu.
klu tshinanu wane tixa hichinikanuwleta: “Nkamrukamkachaxiniplu, nutskalhanutka.”
Waneklukawa potuko tutukahrahatatka. Timaxnawa tomaneya tuhlewaxinrixka t-salewnakanatapinri.
Waneklukawa Jesus himaxnawa ruchpakamtatka hpixkonu. Ruprotaka hixolune yin-yehi. Waneya repomha, wane htshina: — Kathe kamrukamkatno?
Waneya wla htshinruna rasruklene: — Petna hixolune yine ripxakjexyawakyina wanepnawaka wane ptshina katu kamrukamkatno?
Seyni Jesus heknojtata rexyawakaplu katukta yotnekamkatlu.
Waneya suxo pikatka. Tutataka. Timata wane tixyawaka. Waneya Jesus jixistsi tuknojnawa. Tunkaklu tyeyixle pirana ptowruka.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinro: — Chrima, palixle hitskalakyi. Pyanu kihlehchinikanpatkayi. Kihlepatkayi psalewnakanaxinriya.
Jairo Hchitsho Riwekkajyawaka Jesus PiranapniWaneya hyanumsakanaxiniwa Jesus, Jairo-pji hichpajikatshine htowrene hapoka. Waneya wane htshinruna: — Pchítshoni hipnanatka. Klu tshinanhe pkojwakawalu hasruklewatatshri?
Seyni Jesus jemachatlu xye tokantshi. Waneya wane htshinru Jairo, tsru hitakkaluru hanjihohnewakapji hajeru: — Hi pimyekanu. Palixachatanu.
Hi ritshitna pimrine himotsaxyawakaplu. Pedro, Tiago, João, repuru Tiago tsonu ritshitatka.
Hjihlokapjixinixkaluna Jairo-pji, retlu sejirtshi, tshiyahatatshine saplewjepotutatshine.
Waneya hjihlokamta. Waneya Jesus hepomhana, wane htshina: — Klu tshinanhe xye sejirtshi, tshiyahlu? Mturo hi tupna seyni tumkachata.
Seyni rutsolhitatluna Jesus. Hiyáhoni maleka hyokanatna ptowruneko. Waneya ranikna mturo hiru, tunro, waleymalun-koxa. Hjihlokna mtúroni hwiywaka.
Waneklutka mturo yotunotatka. Tyanatka klu tshinanu doze mhalerotni. Waneya ptowrunek-yine tsru himyeklu rixna.
Waneya Jesus hijretna hike hmunkajyawakanupluna wale pirana. Waneya rohlujixlo mturo.
Jesus Nazaré Tshijne Hyiywaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus wane hichpakamxya. Htshijne hyatka. Rimotsatluna rasrukjetanune.
Hapnanuxikalur-hohne rixinixka hyinuwaka hasruklewleta hanjihohnewakapjiya. Hixolune yine yijnakotatshine himyekahchinikanutatka. Waneya wanna wan-tshina: — Hanhe rukchijyalu wale xyekaka? Hanhe rukchijyalu rimatkalnu? Hanhe rixa kamhaletlu xye hetkalurkaka?
Hi he hahmuna chpatako kamruretaklerukni wale, Maria tshinkaluro whene? Hi he repurune Tiago, José, Simão hiyrunu Judas tshinkalune? Hi he hewi wimwana repurone? Wan-rixkalukni hike hijhatkalu Jesus.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshina: — Satu muphujewnakatuwa pirana hinkakletatshri kahwakpiratka ptowruchayaka seyni waleko htshijneya ho waleko himolene tsonuyma hi hkahwakpiratka.
Hiyáhoni hi hixo hetkalurkaka hkamha Jesus wale poktshiya. Seyni satkaka yeyixatshine hoho rutakamyota rutskalajyawakapna. Wale tsonu.
Rimyeka hmalixlenna tshinanu. Waneya pa poktshikaka nwaka hyapamta rasruklewaxyawakapa.
Jesus Hasruklene Kamrurepa PiranapniJesus tomhana rasruklene doze. Hyinuwaka yokanretna hepkaka. Renekpixkonutna kamtshine htowuxyawakapna ruchpajyawakapna yine maneya.
Htowutna hkanojerna tsonu ranijyawakapna xye yanre tshinanu. Hi hniklerna ranikanna, hi saco-ko, hi tiyiroko ranikanna.
Rutakanrona sandalha tsonu ranikanna. Hi hepi mkatshriko ranikanna.
Hiyrun-koxa wane htshinna Jesus: — Hanur-pantshiktako hjihlojini, wanepji hwanu haté hichpajin-potuko.
Hma yoptotjenepa, hma jemjenepa tshinanu, hichpakamxinpatka waneya wanna hetanu hiwlihkajpatjixitanu rimaxyawakapna hi hixako htshinanni seyni hma yoptotjene malixlenu tshinanni.
Waneya hyatkana. Runkaklewatna hehchinikanru pirana.
Hixo kamtshine maleka ruknokna. Nhihtshi ruyokjiwutna hixolune yeyixatshine waneya rutskalakna.
João Batista Hipninri PiranapniWaneya Phuru Herodes jemyehitlu Jesus klu tshinanu Jesus pirana ptowruchaka rupalpiranyehita. Hiyáhoni pimrine wan-tshina: — João Batista-ni hetko hiwekatnaka. Wale tshinanu kpixkonru hetkalurkaka hkamhiywakapa.
Seyni pimrine wan-tshina: — Elias-ni hetkoni. Pimrine wan-tshina: — Hoyakalu tokanu heneklewatatshrini. Wale Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshrini mitshikawluru pixkalutu.
Xye hjeminixka Herodes waneya wla htshina: — João-ni hetkokni wale! Nkastaknojikjixlerukni xawakni hipuktshi riwekkajikatka!
Klu tshinanu Herodes mitshi kachikjixniru João-ni. Rostukjixniru, preso rutakjixniru, Herodes repuru Filipe hnunrotakanatanro Herodias tshinkaluro tshinanu.
Klu tshinanu João-ni mitshi wan-tshinatkalu Herodes: “Hinanchitkalurni pepuru hnunro phanunroxyawaka!”
Hiyáhoni Herodias hahnanutniru João-ni. Taluk-hiylaletmakniru seyni hi tumukata,
klu tshinanu Herodes kahwakpiratniru João-ni. Rimatlu wale jejni kihlehchinikanurni, powrahchinikanurni. Hiyáhoni rinotniru João-ni. Waneya hjeminixniru João-ni hi rimatahchinikanuta seyni hyijnakotniru kihlehchinikanuymalu.
Waneya Herodias himukaxinri hohne, Herodes hohneru tshinanu tsru niklu hkamha tsrukakalune, soldado-ne chefe-tene, hiyrun-koxa tsru hitakkalune Galileia hajene tshinanu.
Herodias whene jihlokatkalu tsru niklu yehi. Waneya tahsata. Herodes hiyrun-koxa htshanixlene hikchikhihlenupotutlo. Waneya phuru wan-tshinro makloji: — Panjitanno kluneruktako paluka. Hita henekanyi.
Halikaka nunkakyi: — Klunerukta panjitanno nenekanyi. Yáholu hanikajiko npohirewaxinri nenekanyi.
Waneya wane tuchpajyatka. Waneya wane ttshinro tunro: — Kluhe nanjitanu? Waneya tunro wan-tshinro: — João Batista jiwu panjitanu.
Waneklukawa potuko phuru yehi tyatnaka. Waneya tanjitlu. Wane ttshinru: — Xawakni potuko naluklu penejyawakapno prato-tlo João Batista jiwu.
Waneya phuru wamonuwpotuta seyni runkaklexyalo htshanixlene hetanu tshinanu hi raluka yohikletlu htokanu.
Hiyáhoni waneklukawa potuko phuru yokanatlu satu htowreru rawapjiwuxyawakaplu João. Waneya hyatka, hkastaknojitatkalu João-ni preso yehiya.
Waneya hyijnakpiranyehixinixkaluna João hasruklene, runna. Ranikmanetanatkaluna. Hkapnatanatkaluna.
Jesus Hixolune Yine Rohluxyawaka PiranapniWaneya hnurrene satokanwakatlu Jesus. Runkakluna Jesus ptowruko hkamhapanruna hiyrunu rasruklewakanatanruna pirana.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinna: — Hinanu. Kahnete poktshiri wyanutka wapnanuxyawakapa pchini tsonu. Klu tshinanu Jesus rasruklen-koxa hi kapapkona hnijyawakna hixolune yine, hinamtatshine hiyrunu yatshine tshinanu.
Hiyáhoni wannapka kahnete poktshiri hyatkana kanawaya.
Seyni hixolune yine hetna wane ruchpajyawakna. Rimathetna. Hiyáhoni ptowru poktshikaka ruchpajyatkana yine rasukamtna Jesus hyoptoxyawakapluna. Seyni Jesus hma mapokkanuklunuwa rapokatkana wanna.
Waneya Jesus kanawa hiptejinixka, retna hixolune yine. Retwamonutna klu tshinanu carneiro-ne ruslahjerna mwikane pixkalunni. Waneya hixo pirana hyinuwaka hasrukletna.
Kayi rixinixka rasruklene hapyehitlu Jesus. Waneya wane htshinruna: — Kayixkani hiyrunu hewi kahnete poktshirni.
Pyokanatanna yine hixolune poktshikaka nwaka hyiywakapna hiyrunu hsankaka wi potuko hwatshri nwaka hyiywakapna ranjixyapluna hnikanrupna.
Seyni ruhita Jesus, wane htshina: — Hixa henekanna hnikanrupna. Waneya wane htshinruna rasruklene: — Wanjiterhe pão ptowru yineru tshinanu, duzentos hohne kamrurtshi wenru pso wenejyawakapna hnijinripna?
Waneya Jesus hihita, wla htshinna: — Hi pejnu pão waneyhi? Hetapanu. Waneya rimaxinixkana wane htshinruna wanna: — Wimwalerutka cinco pão, hepi chima.
Waneya peklomta hoho htuplajixna yine ptowruneka pa ptohkaka rixyawakapna.
Waneya htuplatna yine, pa ptohkaka rixna. Pa xkehkaka cem, pa xkehkaka cinquenta.
Waneya Jesus kochtsheklu cinco pão, hepi chim-koxa. Tenhohne hyihata hpoyahnutlu Hoyakalu. Waneya hjiknajrotlu pão. Waneya rasruklene reneklu hixolune yine rapsaxyawakapna. Waney-koxa rapsatkana ptowruneko hepipkalut-koxa chima.
Waneya ptowruneko nikatka. Jinanutkana.
Waneya hkochtshekluna pão-ni hixetatshrini, chim-koxni, doze chiwatu t-tsepota.
Pão nikatshine cinco mil jejine.
Jesus Honha Hoho Hyanamxyawaka PiranapniWaneklukawa Jesus hixolune yokanatka pchinika hkosekjixna rasruklene pa sreta powha hkopruhaxyawakapna kanawaya Betsaida poktshi nwaka.
Hixolune rali yokanrexinixka Jesus, walepka hipjita hya ranjihohnexyawakapa.
Seyni kayi rixinixka kanawa hownahatkalo. Jesus-pka tshiji hwakanatawa.
Waneya Jesus hetna hkaheknanuwaxyawakna rasruklene hsalwuhaxyawakna klu tshinanu kanniphalu satkakanna. Waneya hoprikako Jesus yanwakatna rasruklene, tsru powha honha hoho hyanamta. Raluk-hiknohlemtna.
Seyni retamxinixkaluna Jesus tsru powha hyanamxyawaka, hkahwakluna samentshi rixyawaka. Waneya hsaplewatna.
Klu tshinanu rexinixkaluna hpikpotuthonukna. Waneklukawa potuko Jesus hiynumatna wane htshinna: — Hixko hchinikanuphi, Hitni! Hi hpikanu!
Waneya kanawa hpokowna wanna yehi, kanniphalu hitukamtatka. Waneya rimyekpotutna rasruklene.
Hkojwakahchinikanutna klu tshinanu hi rimatjemluna hetkaluru pão hixolewkajyawaka pirana. Hchikohajiwatna.
Jesus Hitskalajyawakna Genesaré Hajene PiranapniWaneya hkopruhaxinixkana Genesaré tshijne hyana. Rutspakatkana.
Hajeyri kanawa ruptekawana yine hixolune himathetatkalu Jesus.
Waneyakni yine hasuktata wale tshijne psoluka rawapyawakapna katshinomtalune. Waneya ranikkatkana katshinomtalune hijekoyna Jesus jemyehixyawaka nwaka.
Jesus poktshikaka hya, mtserutu poktshikaka, tsru poktshikaka hiyrunu fazenda-kaka. Waneya Jesus satkaka jihlokawakako praça rutakkana katshinomtalune. Waneya ranjipotutluna yeyixatshine hyotnejyawakluna yáholu Jesus mkalustsiptoko waneya katukta yotneklu rutskalhatka.
Jesus Hiykoxyawakna Judeu-ne PiranapniWaneya fariseu-ne hiyrun-koxa kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine Jerusalém hichpajikatshine hapatjeyehitlu Jesus.
Klu tshinanu fariseu-ne hiyrunu pimrine judeu-ne homkahitlu rutsrukatenna hasruklewle, wan-tshinatshri: hma meromyohkanuklunu hma merokakanotkanuklunu hi hnikanna.
Niktshi hanjijexikowaka hichpajikatshri merokakotu hi hnikanru. Hiyrunu hixo pimri yokanruru pirana romkahitna, hirapkaka herojikolu pirana, hachhajkaka herojikolu pirana, hiyrun-koxa yomuwa himatkaka herojikolu pirana romkahitna.
Waneya repomhaluna fariseu-ne hiyrunu kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine: — Klu tshinanhe pasruklene hi homkahitlu tsrunni hixannu seyni kaptsho myoluneko hnikna?
Waneya Jesus hihitna, wla htshinna: — Hixachatatshinhi! Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri Isaías-ni hinkakletpotuthi hixa. Wla htshina yonatkaluru: “Nyi yine himalwutno hinama tsonuyma seyni hihchinikanuyna howukayno.
Hmahijeru himalwuretnona; klu tshinanu rasrujikolna yineru hinanchireru tsonu.”
Pnuteko htshina: — Hixa hiknokachatlu Hoyakalu yokanatanru tokantshi tsrunni tokanu homkahixyawakapa.
Wane htshin-koxna Jesus: — Hixa hijhalu Hoyakalu halujyawaka kahnete hitajyawaklu hixako halujyawaka hkamhiywaka.
Klu tshinanu Moisés-ni towre wla tshina: “Pkahwakpiratanru puru, punro.” Hiyrunu wane htshina: “Katukta hektuwaka tshinanwakatlu ruru, runro walepni hipnanuna.”
Seyni hixa wan-tshina: “satu jeji wan-tshininri ruru ho runro: Pa hixanu nimwinri nepixyawakamkapyi wale Corbã-ni (wale haluka tshinreta rimwaleru henekachlu Hoyakalunupa),
hi hima rujhalu ruru runro repixyawakapa.
Hoyakalu mahijeru towutlethi klu tshinanu hixako haluk-hixlexyawaka hkamhajeta hitsrukatenni yokchale tshinanu. Hixo wale pixkalutu hkamhajeta.
Waneya htomhatnakna hixolune yine. Wane htshinna Jesus: — Hyijnakotanno ptowrunekhi. Himatjemanru xye:
Hinama jihlojikatshri hi pitshotlu yineru Hoyakalu hetanuya seyni yineru pitshotjeru halikaka namtshi hichpakhimaxikatshri.
Katukta kajnakopnapa hyijnakoxyawakapa, hyijnakotanu.
Waneya hixolune yin-yehi ruchpajini Jesus, hjihloklu pantshi waneya rasruklene hepomhalu klu pirana raluka tshinreta xye yapkaklu tshinanu.
Waneya wane htshinna Jesus: — Hix-koxa mimatjemkanhi? Hi he himatjemlu ptowruko maleka hwatshri jihlojinri yineru hi rumukata pitshotletlu?
Klu tshinanu hihchinikanu hi hjihloka seyni hisatu hya waneya himane ruchpajya. Xye pirana runkakkatkana rimaxyawakna ptowru nikkaluru himukata nikletka.
Waneya pnuteko htshina: — Yineru hitokote hichpajikatshri walekni pitshotlu yineru.
Klu tshinanu hihchinikanu hichpajikatshri hektutu chinikantshikaka, himopatlewlu, tshowhuwlu, hiylalewlu, hapoklewlu,
pohirewlu tsonu ruchinikanreta, muhlentshi, yokwirewlu, mapatehonutshi, sotanuhonutshi, hektuwaka htshinanwakaxyawaklu Hoyakalu, tserpiranawlu wale nanuko, machinikantshi.
Xye hektuntshi ptowruka yineru hitokote hichpajikatshrini. Walekni himtukjetlu yineru.
Suxo Pa Tshijne Hajero PiranapniWaneya wane ruchpakamxya Jesus. Waneya Tiro [hiyrunu Sidom] tshinikowaka poktshistsi hyatka. Waneya satu pantshi rapokatka. Walemka haluklu hike mimaxyawakanumkaplu wane rawyawaka seyni hi rumukata yohimleta.
Seyni sato suxo jemyehitlu. Kkamtshitero tchitsho. Waneya tuna tyoptsojityehitlu Jesus jixistsi.
Suxni grega, siro-fenícia-neroni. Waneya tanjitlu maleka ruknojyawakaplu kamtshi tchitsho mane hajeru.
Seyni Jesus hihitlo: — Pohluhapkatanna whentshine jinanu rixyawakapna. Hi kihleru hkonikowakna mturune hnikanruna kawene nwaka ruknojikowakapa.
Waneya tuhitlu wala. Wane ttshinru: — Wanekni, Tsru Hixikatshriwa, seyni haté kawe whenene mesa hpuko hwatshine koxa niklu mturune nijitu mesa hijrujikatshri.
Waneya ruhitlo Jesus: — Xye tokantshi tshinanu pyanutka. Kamtshi hichpajyatkalo pchitsho.
Waneya topji tapojinixka tetatkalo tchitsho tukoluhakanata tojeko, kamtshi hichpajyatkalo.
Majnakotu Manrutu PiranapniWaneya ruchpakamtatnaka Tiro poktshistsiya, Sidom hiyrunu Decápolis hyapamta. Tsru powha Galileia rapokatka.
Waneya Jesus haniklu yine kahneteya. Waneya himyoji hyochmakajnakopnatlu. Waneya rutskahata. Waneya hkamrukanrutlu jeji hitskahayma.
Waneya tenhohne hyihata. Rinniphata. Waneya wane htshinru: — Efatá. Wale haluka tshinreta: kajnakopyi.
Waneyatka ruhlewajnakopnatatka. Waneklukawa potuko hinru himaletakanatatshri hamhatka waneya hyanumhihlenutatka.
Waneya Jesus-mka towutna yine hike hmunkajyawakanupna seyni yáholu hixo katamka rujretna wanepnawaka pnutetka runkaklewatna.
Waneya ptowruneka jematshine tsru himyeklu rixna. Waneya wane htshinna wanna: — Ptowruko kihler-potu hkamha. Hjemkakna majnakone, myanumatkane hyanumkaka.
Jesus Quatro Mil Yine Hohluxyawaka PiranapniWaneya hi howukchini rapatjetatnakna hixolune yine. Malechayna hnikanruna hiyáhoni Jesus tomhatkana rasruklene waneya wla htshinna:
— Netwamonutna nyi yine. Map-hohne hitaymana hiyrunu malechayna hnikanruna.
Hi naluka yokanretna mnikkane hma muhrojyawakanupna hatnu hapoya klu tshinanu satkaka yineru howuka hinya.
Waneya rasruklene hepomhalu: — Hanhe wixa hikchikletanru pão hewi kahnete poktshiri hixolune yine wohluxyawaka?
Waneya Jesus hepomhana: — Hi pejnu pão-pro himwa hixa? Waneya ruhitluna: — Sete pão-pro wimwa.
Waneya Jesus tshiji tuplakjixna hixolune yine. Waneya hkochtsheklu sete pão. Rali poyahnutlexinri Hoyakalu, hjiknajrotlu pão, rasruklene reneklu waneya rasruklene heneksatna hixolune yine.
Twa koxa satokaka chima. Waneya Jesus poyahnutlu Hoyakalu waneya htowutna rasruklene reneksaxyawakapna.
Waneya ptowru yineru nikatka, jinanutkana. Waneya rasruklene tsepotlu sete chiwatu nijittshi hixetatshrini.
Nikatshine quatro mil yine. Waneya Jesus yokanatna hyiywakpatkana.
Waneya chinpotukawa hyohreklo kanawa rasrukleneyma. Dalmanuta nwaka hyatkana.
Hetkalurkaka Ranjixyawakna Fariseu-ne PiranapniWaneya fariseu-ne hapoka hyinuwaka hihretluna Jesus retumhiywakapluna. Ranjitluna hetkalurkaka hkamhiywakapa rekhixyawakapna hpixkonu ho Hoyakallahe runya ho hike.
Hiyáhoni Jesus hinniphata hitokoya wane htshina: — Haklu tshinanhe xyeklu papko hiwekatshine hanjitlu hetkaluru? Seyni halikaka ntshinhi hi satukna hetkaluru rekhitkona.
Waneya Jesus yatka. Hyohreklo kanawa waneya pa sreta hipowha wnahlu hyatka.
Fariseu-ne Hiyrunu Saduceu-ne Tserutjeru PiranapniWaneya rasruklene hi hichinika hanikletlu pão. Satupka pão-pro kanawa ranikna.
Jesus towutna ruslahyawakapluna wane htshinna: — Xako fariseu-ne hiyrunu saduceu-ne tserutjeru, Herodes tserutjer-koxa.
Hiyáhoni hyinuwaka hihjekakletna wannakakluko. Wane htshinkakna: — Wane htshina klu tshinanu pão hi wanikatka.
Seyni Jesus yijnakotna ruhjekajyawakna waneya repomhana: — Klu tshinanhe hihjekaka pão hma manijyawakanu tshinanu? Hi he himatawalu, hi he himatjemawalu klu pirana ntshinatkahi? Chik-hajirunrahhe hixa?
Hixa kayhalmakhi seyni hi he heta? Kajnakmakhi hi he hjema? Hi he hichiniklu
hanu nixa kanipreletlu cinco pão cinco mil yine tshinanu? Hi pejnuhe chiwatu htsepota nijittshi hixetatshrini? Waneya ruhitluna: — Doze chiwatu wtsepotatka.
Waneya Jesus hiyrunuko hepomhana: Ha nkaniprexyawaklu sete pão quatro mil yine niklerupa tshinanu, hi pejnu chiwatu htsepota nijittshi hixetatshrini? Waneya ruhitluna: — Sete chiwatu wtsepotatka.
Waneya repomhana Jesus: — Hi he xawaka himatjemawa?
Mayhaletu Betsaida Hajeru PiranapniWaneya wane pnute Jesus rasrukleneyma Betsaida hapoka. Waneya satkaka yineru hanikanwakatlu mtsawa, waneya ranjitluna Jesus hyotnejyawakaplu.
Waneya Jesus kachimyotlu mtsawa. Raniklu kahnete. Waneya hitskaha hsahayhalexyalu, hkapxaklu, repomhalu, wla htshinru: — Petluhe pa hixanu?
Waneya jeji hetatka waneya wane htshina: — Netmaklu yineru seyni hahmuna nyanahota.
Waneklukawhapka Jesus yokanatlu jeji hipjiru hyiywakapa waneya wane htshinru: — Hi poktshi nwakatshi psatkapanu.
Pedro Wan-tshinyawaka Jesus Hoyakalu Whene Rixyawaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus rasrukleneyma Cesareia de Filipe poktshistsi hyana. Waneya hyamtka pchinikna repomhana, wla htshinna: — Kathe rikahwaknona yine?
Waneya rasruklene hihita: Satkaka yineru wan-tshina pixa João Batista-yi; satuko wan-tshina Elias-yi; satuko wan-tshinyi satu mitshikawni Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshriyi.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinna: — Ha hixa, kathe hkahwakno? Waneya Pedro hihita: — Pixni Hoyakalu yokanreryi Messias-yi.
Waneya Jesus towutlu xye pirana hike hmunkajyawakanupa.
Jesus Hinkaklexyawaklu Rupninri Hiyrunu Riwejinritnaka PiranaWaneya Jesus yinuwaka hasrukletna rasruklene, waneya wane htshinna: — Hita Jeji Whene tshinkalurno, nujhalu nsalewnapotuxyawakapa. Nuknokko tsrukakalune judeu-ne yehiya hiyrunu tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne yehiya, kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine yehiy-koxa. Nuylatko. Seyni map-hohne rixinri niwekanutnaka.
Jesus phujewak-potuko runkakletlu. Waneya Pedro haniklu Jesus kahnete hyinuwaka hiykoletlu.
Waneya Jesus heknokyehitna rasruklene, hyopukhatna waneya ruykotlu Pedro, wla htshina: — Pasujinno, Satanás pixkalutu. Pixa hi Hoyakalu hchinikanu pimwa seyni jeji hchinikanu halikaka pimwa.
Jesus Homkahitatshri Haluklu H-cruz-te Rutaykopixyawaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus tomhana hixolune yine hiyrun-koxa rasruklene. Waneya wane htshinna: — Satu yineru haluk-homkahrexinno, rujhanru wale ralujyawaka ruchoxyawaka, rutaykopitanru h-cruz-te waneya romkahitanno hita.
Klu tshinanu katukta haluk-hiwekkakletanru riwejinri, ramtakanru riwekle; seyni katukta hamtakanru riwekle hita tshinanu ho kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana tshinanu riwekanu.
Hanhe rixa hepixletlu yineru xye tshijne hihlenu psoluka hkayaxiniklunu seyni riwejinri ramtakanuna?
Kluhe xawaka ripekotanru satu jeji riwejinri tshinanu?
Klu tshinanu katukta hipatewatanno hita hiyrun-koxa ntokanu hipatewatatshri xye hektutu hiyrunu halixle mahle klu papko, waneya Jeji Whene tshinkalur-koxa hipatewatanru runinipa waleko royaknuyma hiyrunu Ruru hoyaknuyma rimapojinipa hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrene tenhohne hajene potukaluneyma.
Waneya Jesus hali hinkakletatkana wane htshina: Hichinikanru xye: Satkaka hewi hajeru hma mupnaknukawa, retanru Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hapokatshritka hpixkonuyma.
Jesus, Moisés, Elias PiranapniWaneya seis hohne pnut-hohne, Jesus teno mrijiwaka hanikna Pedro, Tiago, hiyrunu João. Wannapkatkani. Waneya wanna hetanu hyokmanhojitatka Jesus.
Himkal-koxa klata, klat-potuko rixa, katajru jeromkaklerone yohnik-powranu rixatka.
Retluna Elias-ni, hiyrun-koxa Moisés-ni. Riynumsatluna Jesus.
Waneya Pedro wan-tshinru Jesus: — Kasruklewakleru, kihleru wiko wwiywaka. Hayeri wkamheru mapa pantshi; satu pixanupa, satu Moisés-nupa, satu Elias-nupa.
Waneya rasruklene himyekpotuthonuka. Pedro hi himata klukta htshinanu.
Waneya hohimkohi hichyatna. Waneya hohimkohi hitokote ruchpajyatka tokantshi wla tshinatshri: — Xyekni nowhene nalukleru. Hyijnak-tokanutanru!
Waneklukawa hsajruruyhaletna seyni Jesus tsonu retna.
Elias Hapojinri PiranapniWaneya himriji hserpijinixkana Jesus hijretna retakanatanruna hike hmunkajyawakanupna hma miwekkanuko pchini Jeji Whene hipuktshiya.
Wanna yijnakotlu Jesus towuxyana seyni ruhjekakna wannakakluko klu pirana htshina riwejinpatnaka pirana.
Hiyáhoni repomhaluna Jesus, wla htshinruna: — Klu tshinanhe kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine wan-tshina Elias hapka hapokanu?
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinna: — Halikakni, Elias hapokanu ruhlexyawakaplu ptowruko. Seyni haklu tshinanhe yonatkaluru tokantshi wan-tshina Jeji Whene salewnapotutanhonuka malukkotupni?
Seyni wane ntshinhi Elias-ni hinpatka seyni rapnokatka raluk-hixlexikowaka rixka yonatkaluru tshinyawaka pixka rixluna.
Jesus Mturu Kamtshite Hakajyawaka PiranapniWaneya rapojinixkana pimrine rasruklenestsi, retna hixolune yine rasruklene sajrukastsitanune. Satkaka kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine hihjekakakanata.
Hajeyri yine hixolune hexinixkalu Jesus rimyekna wanna ptowruneka waneya rasukanwakatluna ralikluna.
Waneya Jesus hepomhana kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine: — Haklu himuhjekaka?
Ptowru hohneruka kamtshi kamnitlu, ruknoklu tshiji. Waneya hyinuwaka hichpaksolnamletana, raskiyhita, ruhrokamta. Pasruklenemka nanjita ruknojyawakapluna kamtshi seyni hi rumukatna.
Waneya wane htshinna Jesus: — Yine malixaklenhi. Haté hi pejnu hohnekta nimwanhi hixa? Haté hi pejnu hohnekta nakotanhi? Wkata panikanru mturu.
Waneya ranikanwakaxinixkaluna mturu Jesus nwaka kamtshi hetlu Jesus waneya hipokananu hkowchoklu mturu. Mturni tshiji hyana ruprurumtana ruchpaksolnamamtana.
Waneya Jesus hepomhalu ruru, wla htshinru: — Hi pejnu hohnehe wan-rixatka piwhene? Waneya ruru hihita, wla htshinru: — Hmatureyakawa.
Hixo kata kamtshi tshitshmero hiknoklu, honha ruknoklu koxa ruylaxyawakaplu seyni pixa himukata hepixlexinipno, pepixanno. Petwamonutanunwu hixni.
Waneya Jesus hihitlu: — Numukathe? Ptowru potuko himukata hakanhaleta ralixini yineru.
Waneya ruru wla tshin-saplewleta: — Nalixyi. Pepixanno nalixyawakpotupyi.
Waneya Jesus hexinixkana hixolune yine wale nwaka hapokatshinepa, htowutlu kamtshi, wla htshina: — Kamtshi majnaklu manrutu, puchpajinixkalu xye mturu, hikeklu hohne pjihlokanutnaklu.
Waneya kamtshi saplewata, hkowchoklu mturu waneya ruchpajyatkalu, ruchotlu mturu hipnatshri pixka hixatshriko. Wale tshinanu ptowru yineru wan-tshina, rupnanatka.
Seyni Jesus kachimyotlu mturu, repixlu hyopkajyawakapa.
Waneya Jesus jihlojinixka pantshi rasruklene wannapka rixinixkana, repomhaluna, wla htshinruna: — Klu tshinanhe hi wumukata hiknokletlu kamtshi?
Waneya Jesus hihitna: — Xye pixkalutu kamtshi hi hiknokka, hanjihohneru hiyrunu hohajirewlu tshinanu tsonu.
Jesus Hinkakletahnapuxyawaklu Rupninri Riwejinritnaka Pirana Hiyrunukotnaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus hiyrunu rasruklene hichpajyalu wale poktshi, riknohamtluna Galileia tshijne. Jesus hi halukna yine rimaxyawakapna rawyawaka,
klu tshinanu rasrukna rasruklene, wla htshinna: — Jeji Whene tshinkaluru yine renekko. Wanna hiylatanru seyni map-hohne rixinri riwekanutnaka.
Seyni wanna hi himatjema klu piranakta htshina Jesus seyni hpika hepomhaletluna.
Kat-pothe Hijhakaluru Hoyakalu Pohirewaxyawakaya PiranapniWaneya Jesus rasrukleneyma hapoklu tsru poktshi Cafarnaum tshinikowaka. Hajeyri pantshi rapojinixkana, Jesus hepomhana doze rasruklene: — Haklu himuhjekakamta hatnuya?
Seyni potshkena wanna klu tshinanu hatnu ruhjekajyana katnihe hijhakalur-potu.
Waneya Jesus tuplata waneya htomhana doze rasruklene. Waneya wla htshinna: — Satkaka yineru haluka tsru hixlexnawa, rujhalu wale nanwaka malukkotu rixyawaka ptowru yineru repixanu.
Waneya hkachitlu satu mturu, hyopkakkaklu wanna hanikajite. Hsapriklu. Waneya wla htshinna rasruklene:
— Katukta hihle yoptoletlu xye pixkalutu mturu nhiwaka tshinanu hit-koxa hyoptotanu. Hiyrunu katukta yoptotanno hita, hi hita tsonu hyoptota seyni hyoptotanru nyokanatjeru koxa.
Waneya João wan-tshinru: — Kasruklewakleru, wetlu jeji kamtshi hiknokatshri pixa phiwakaya seyni wimaletlu klu tshinanu hi hixa wepirni.
Waneya Jesus hihita, wla htshina: — Hi himaletanru klu tshinanu yineru hetkaluru kamhatshri hita hiwakaya, hi xekoyaka hektuwaka htshinanwakatanno.
Klu tshinanu katukta hi kamnitwu, repixwu.
Hichinikanru xye: Satu yineru honha copa stonha hixiniphi Cristo-nerunhi hixyawaka tshinanu, halikakni hyoptotanru rumlujikolupa.
Himtuwna Halixlekakatshri PiranapniWaneya Jesus wla tshina: — Katukta himtuwna halixlekakna nalixjene mtserkakanewa, kihlepotmaklu tsru sotlu rostunojixikowaka waneya mar powha ruknojikowaka.
Pimyo himtujinipyi, pkastakanru. Klu tshinanu kihlepotmaklu mtsoji hiwekkajikowaka, hepi myoluko tshitshmero tshitshi hikeklu muwnakatu yehi ruknokkona,
[tsomi mupniywakanu hiyrunu tshitshi hikeklu muwnakatu yehi.]
Pijixi himtujinipyi, pkastakanru. Klu tshinanu kihlepotmaklu myape hiwekkajikowaka, hepi jixiruko tshitshmero hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatunapa ruknokkona,
[tsomi mupniywakanu hiyrunu tshitshi hikeklu muwnakatu yehi.]
tsomi mupniywakanu hiyrunu tshitshi hikeklu muwnakatu yehi.
Tuwu Piranapni— Klu tshinanu satkaka yineru tuwutko tshitshmeroya.
Tuwu hijhakalurni seyni hma tuwrenuklunu hi repixlewata. Tuwu pixkalunephi, hike mixkanephi hixkakluko.
Jesus Kopruhaxyawaklu Jordão Wenne PiranapniWaneya Jesus wane ruchpajya, Judeia tshijne hyatka, hkopruhatlu Jordão wenne. Waneya hixolune yine hapatjeyehitlu hiyrunukotnaka. Wale hasrukna rixa hasruhlexyawaka pixka.
Hiknokahnunrolu PiranapniWaneya satkaka fariseu-ne yanwakatlu Jesus hepomhalu retumhiyluna. Repomhaluna: — Moisés hiykole pirana yonatkalurlahe hi tshipetlu jeji hhanunro ruknojyawakapa?
Waneya Jesus hihitna satu hepomhaluyma: — Kluhe ruykotatkahi Moisés-ni?
Waneya wanna hihita, wla htshinruna: — Moisés hiykole yonatkaluru wan-tshina jeji ruchohnunroxinipa ruchoxyalo pirana yonaxikolu renekanro, hhanunro tmixyawakanpatka waneya hyokanatatkalo.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshina: — Moisés yonatlu xye yokanruru hixa chiko hchinikanu hixyawaka tshinanu.
Hyinuwajikolu xye tshijne hiyakoxikolu klu papko Hoyakalu hixkajyawaklu jeji suxo rixyawakna.
Wale tshinanu jeji hichotlu ruru, runro, rimwiywakaplo hhanunro.
Hiyáhoni hepitkana seyni pa manepkalunetkani, wale tshinanu hi hepna, satupkalu.
Hiyáhoni hike yineru xako hitspalkakanru Hoyakalu hapatjetanune.
Waneya rapojinixkana pantshi, rasruklene yinuwaka hepomhaletlu wale pirana.
Waneya Jesus hihitna, wla htshinna: — Jeji hichohnunroxini, satoko hhanunroxini rimopatatkalo.
Hiyrun-koxa suxo hichohnuruxini, satuko thanuruxini, timopatatkalu.
Jesus Hiyrunu Mturune PiranapniWaneya wane pnute satkaka hanikna mturune Jesus yehi ruhlewahchinikanyehixyawakapna seyni rasruklene hi hitshitna.
Seyni Jesus hexinixkalu xye hi rukchikhihlenutlu, waneya wla htshina: — Hetachatanna mturune hyanwakaxyawaknona. Hi himaletanna. Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hayinetene mturune pixkalune koxni wanna.
Hichinikanru xye: Katukta hi yoptotanru Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka mturu pixka, hi hjihlokanru.
Hiyáhoni Jesus saprikna mturune, ruhlewahchinikanyehitna, rutakamyohohotna.
Jeji Phuru PiranapniWaneya hyinuwaka yanrexinixnaka Jesus, satu jeji hasukanwakatlu, hyoptsojityehitlu wale hoji sreta, waneya repomhalu, wla htshinru: — Kasruklewakleru kihleru, klunerhe nkamhanu niwejinri hikeklu hohne nma nikawniywakanupa?
Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Haklu tshinanu wane ptshinno kihle nixyawaka? Wale tsonu Hoyakalu kihle, hikeni hiyrunu.
Pimathonru hiykolu pirana: “Hi puylalewatanu, hi hapoklewatanu, hi ptshowhuwatanu, hi pimrine pweyatanu, hi pimrine pyokwijetanu, pkahwakpiratanru puru, punro.”
Waneya jeji hihitlu: — Kasruklewakleru, nmatureyakawa haté xawakni nomkahitlu xye hiykolu ptowruka.
Waneya Jesus yopukhatlu ramotleyma, wane htshinru: — Seyni satu pa hixanu pmaha kamhaletawa. Wane pyanu, puchankanru ptowruka pimwanru, penekanna ptowruka mahaxikatshine, wane pixa pohirewnaletanu tenhohneya. Punanu cruz putaykopitanu waneya pomkahitanno hita.
Waneya wale pirana hyijnakoxinixka phuru, hyatka, hwamonuwnapotuta. Hjihekanuwatatka klu tshinanu phurupotukni.
Pohirewnalu Hma Mepixyawakanru Yineru Hoyakalu Pohirewaxyawaka Hjihlojyawaka PiranapniHiyáhoni Jesus sajruruyhaletatka. Waneya wla htshina: — Hi pa yaprenukananru phurune Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hjihlojyawakapna!
Waneya rasruklene himyekpotuthonuka seyni Jesus pnuteko tshina: — Nowhenene, hi pa yaprenukananru Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hjihlojyawaka.
Kyapreru camelo tsapujripna hjihlojyawaka seyni wane yohnik-yapren-potu phuru Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hjihlojyawaka.
Hiyáhoni wale pirana hjeminixkana rasruklene rimyekpotuthonukna. Hiyáhoni repomhakakna wannakakluko: — Ha han-hixatshri hiwekkakko?
Waneya Pedro wan-tshina: — Petanu ptowruka wuchota pixa womkahixyawakatka.
Waneya Jesus hihita, wla htshina: — Nmunanhalu ptowru yineru hipji hichotatshri, ho himolene ho himolerone, ho runro, ho ruru, ho hiwhenene ho tshijkaka hichotatshri ramoxyawaka tshinanno hiyrun-koxa kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana ramoxyawaka tshinanu,
hyoptotanru yohnik-potu xawakni riwejinri. Hyoptotanru cem yohnik-kata hipji, himolene, himolerone, hinrone, hiwhenene, tshijkaka hiyrunu salewaktshi. Hiyrunu xye riwejinripa hinatshri hyoptotanru riwejinri hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa.
Hiyrun-koxa hixolune kosekakanatatshine hapkatatanutka. Waneya hixolune rapkatle hwatshine kosekanutka.
Jesus Hinkakatnaklu Rupninri Hiyrunu Riwejinritnaka PiranapniWaneyakni Jesus doze rasrukleneyma hatnu hapo hyana hkankaluna Jerusalém poktshi. Jesus kosekamta. Rasruklene hapkatatatshine himyeka Jesus tshinyawakna tshinanu pimrin-koxa wannaymalune pikatka. Hiyáhoni Jesus kahnete hanikna rasruklene hiyrunukotnaka. Waneya Jesus hinkakna riknohjerupa pirana, wla htshinna:
— Jerusalém poktshi nwaka wyamtanu. Waneya Jeji Whene tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne, kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine renekko. Waneya rukolukanuwnakakanruna ruylajixanruna, judeu mixkane renekko.
Jesus reyikanna, rutskahjetanruna, rutpehjetanruna, ruylatanruna; seyni map-hohne rixinri riwekanutnaka.
Tiago Hiyrunu João Hanjireru PiranapniWaneya wane pnute Tiago hiyrunu João, Zebedeu whenene, hapokastsitlu Jesus, waneya wane htshinruna: — Kasruklewakleru, wuya penekanwu wepuklerupa.
Waneya Jesus hepomhana, wla htshina: — Kluhe haluka nkamhiywakhi?
Waneya ruhitna, wla htshinruna: — Pitshitanwu satu ppotukle sreta htuplaxyawakapa, satu pa sta sreta htuplaxyawakapa poyaknu yehi ppohirewnale tuplawakle ptuplaxinipa.
Waneya Jesus hihitna: — Hixa hi himatlu klukta hanjita. Hixlahe himukata hirrexyalo copa salewaktshi yehi nurinropa? Himukata batiza-letkahe n-batiza-xikolu pixka?
Waneya wane htshinruna: — Wumukata. Waneya Jesus wan-tshinna: — Halikaka, hixa hirinro copa salewaktshi yehiya hiyrunu n-batiza-xikolu h-batiza-tko hixa.
Seyni htuplaxyawakaplu npotukle sreta ho npastate sreta hi hitanni neneklewaxyawakapa. Xye ptaklukaka sreta hajene Hoyakalu halpokohnapulene tshinanupa.
Waneya pimrine rasruklene dez, hjeminixkaluna wale pirana rahkanwakatna Tiago, João.
Hiyáhoni Jesus tomhana wanna ptowruneka walestsi rapojyawakapna, waneya wla htshinna: — Hixa himatlu phurune towutanune xye tshijne hajene towutjetna yine hiyrun-koxa wanna towutjene towutjetna wanna koxa.
Seyni hixkakluko hi wan-rixa. Katukta hijhakalur-pira, pimrine repixanu,
hiyrun-koxa katukta haluka towuwletanu, walepni pimrine towrerupa.
Klu tshinanu Jeji Whene koxa hi hina repixikowakapa, seyni runa repixyawakapna yine, riwejinri renejyawakapna, hixolune yine hektunu hwenuxyawakapa.
Jesus Mtsawa Bartimeu Hiwakatletatshri Hitskalajyawaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus rasrukleneyma hapoklu Jericó poktshi. Waneya wale poktshi ruchpajinixka rasrukleneyma, hixoluneyma koxa, hyoptotluna mtsawa Bartimeu hiwakatletatshri, Timeu whenni. Mtsawa tuplakanatlu hatnu tnumne. Ranjitlu renekachaxikolu.
Waneya hyijnakpiranyehixinixkalu Jesus, Nazaré hajeru, hiknohamxyawaka, hyinuwaka saplewletatka: — Jesus, phurni Davi-ni whene, petwamonutanunno.
Hiyáhoni hixo yineru hiykotlu mtsawa potshke rixyawakapa seyni hsaplewata hiyrunuko: Phurni Davi-ni whene, petwamonutanunno!
Waneya Jesus hitukatka waneya wla htshina: — Htomhanru mtsawa. Waneya htomhaluna waneya wla htshinruna: — Pmixkowahchinikanuyakatanu! Ppalnanu. Htomhayi!
Waneya Bartimeu hichale hiknokamta hiyáhoni hpalnamta chinpotu hyanwakatlu Jesus.
Waneya Jesus hepomhalu, wla htshinru: — Klunerhe paluka nkamhiywakyi? Waneya mtsawa hihitlu: — Kasruklewakleru, naluk-hetletatnaka hiyrunuko!
Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Pyanutka. Palixle tshinanu hihlerurutkayi. Waneklukawhapka Bartimeu yinuwaka hetletatka hiyrunuko. Waneya romkahitlu Jesus hatnu hapoya.
Jesus Jihlojyawaklu Jerusalém PiranapniWaneya Jesus rasrukleneyma hapokpiraxinixka Jerusalém poktshi, Oliveiras mriji rapokna, Betânia, Betfagé poktshikakastsitkana. Waneya Jesus yokanatna hepi rasruklene.
Waneya wla htshina yokanretna Jesus: — Poktshi pnute hajeru nwaka hyanu. Waneya chinpotukawa hjihlokanru, hetanru jumento whene tsatkaluru hikeklu myapatjitkotuwa. Hkochrikanru wale hanikanru wkata.
Seyni satu yineru hepomhiniphi kluhe wla himixa waneya wla htshinanru: — Kasruklewakleru haluklu. Seyni chinpotukawa hsatkakanru.
Waneya hyatkana. Rukchikluna jumento whene tsatkaluru hatnuya. Htsatka pantshi hiphaptotestsi. Hkochrijinixkaluna wale,
Waneya ruhitluna htshin-towutlexyawakna Jesus. Hiyáhoni ritshitluna waneya ranikluna.
Waneya rasruklene haniklu jumento whene Jesus nwaka. Waneya himkalna jumento-tji hoho rutakna. Waneya Jesus hatskotjihohotlu.
Waneya hixo yineru koprakamkata hatnu hapo, pimrine kopalatlu kachehiru tshij-hoho campo rawapyaluna.
Waneya kosekamtatshine hiyrunu hapkatamtatshine saplewamta: — Himalwutkalurni Hoyakalu! Kihlehchinikanuru Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hiwaka hinikatshri!
Kihlehchinikanurupni wutsrukatni Davi-ni pohirewaxyawaka hinatshripa. Tenoya hoyakawaxikowaka!
Waneya wane pnute Jesus jihloklu Jerusalém poktshi. Waneya Hoyakalupji hya. Retjetlu psoluka. Seyni kayi rixyawaka tshinanu Jesus, Betânia poktshi nwaka hya doze rasrukleneyma.
Figueira PiranapniWaneya wale prika hsatkapinixkana Betânia poktshi, Jesus hnatshnemnutka.
Waneya howuka rexyalu figueira katseplu hisure hiplu. Waneya wane hya hisahi rujhiywakapa. Seyni rapokyehitlu hisure tsonu reta klu tshinanu hi hipapkolni hisahi rawyawaka.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru figueira: — Hikeklu hohne pniksahitkotka. Rasruklene yijnakotlu xye hima.
Jesus Hoyakalupji Hapkapyawaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus rasrukleneyma hapojinixka Jerusalém poktshi, hjihlojinixka Hoyakalupji, hyinuwaka hakaklexyatkana ptowruneka wane maronewaxikatshine, hichanrewatatshin-koxa. Hyotkakanru mes-kakni tiyiro ripekowaklena. Tuplawakkakni koxa hyotkaka pombo ruchankawaklena.
Hi ritshitatkalu Hoyakalupji ranijikowaka hejnu.
Waneya wla rixa hasrukletna: — Wla htshina yonatkaluru Hoyakalu pirana: “Nopji hanjihohnewakapji htshinka ptowru yineru hanjihohnewakleni.” Seyni hixa katshowhurune hwiywaka hkamhiyatkalu.
Waneya tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne, kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine yijnakotlu xye. Hyinuwaka hijhaletluna ruylaxyawakapluna Jesus. Klu tshinanu hixolune yine ptowruneka himyekahchinikanuta rasruklewle tshinanu hiyáhoni hpikluna.
Waneya rutshpojinixka, Jesus rasrukleneyma poktshi ruchpajyatkana.
Figueira PiranapakotnakniWaneya wale prika yetshpotukawa figueira riknohamxinixkana retanatkaluna figueira-ni. Riprihanatka haté hitskih-potuko.
Waneya Pedro hichinkaplu Jesus tshinyawakanru. Waneya Pedro wan-tshinru Jesus: — Petanu kasruklewakleru, figueira-ni hektuwaka ptshinanwakatanroni hipnanatka.
Waneya Jesus hihitlu, wla htshinru: — Hichinikanru xye. Halixiniklunru Hoyakalu,
hixa himukata tshinretmaklu xye mriji: “Ppalnanu mar powha puknojinwa.” Waneya hma kahekkanuklunru hihchinikanu seyni halixinri wan-rixa hiphujewnalexyawakapa waneyamka wane potuko rixanu.
Wale tshinanu wane ntshinhi: Hanjihohnexini, pa hixanu hanjixini, halixanu hyoptoxyawakatkalu waneya hixa ptowruka henekkotka.
Hiyrunu hanjihohnexiniklunuwa, hektuwaka hkamhanwakatjeru hamtakahchinikanyehitanru rektunu. Waneya Hirtshi tenhohne hajer-koxa hamtakahchinikanyehitanru hixa hektunu.
Seyni pimrine hektunu hma mamtakahchinikanyehixinipa hixa, Hirtshi tenhohne hajer-koxa hi hamtakahchinikanyehixinhi hixa hektunu.
Jesus Tsru Potu Hitakkalurni PiranapniWaneya hsatkapna Jerusalém poktshi. Jesus Hoyakalupji yapakananumta waneya tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne, kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine judeu-ne tsrukakalutene koxa hapokanwakatlu.
Waneya repomhaluna: — Hanhe ruchpajya ptowutjeru xyekaka pkamhiywaka? Kathe henekyi xye tsru hitakkaluru?
Waneya Jesus hihitna, wla htshinna: — Hit-koxa satu hepomhalu nixanhi hixa. Hihixinri xye, hit-koxa hinkakanhi hixa katu henekno xye tsru hitakkaluru xyekaka nkamhiywaka.
Hinkakanno xako. Kathe xawaka towutlu João h-batiz-lewaxyawaka? Ho Hoyakalu ho jeji?
Waneya hyinuwaka hiynumsakakletna wannakakluko waneya wla htshinkakna: — Wla wtshininri Hoyakalu, waneya repomhanunwu: “Haklu tshinanhe hi halixlu João?”
Seyni wla wtshininri jeji ruchpajya htowutjeru…. Hpikna hixolune yine klu tshinanu ralixluna João-ni Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshrini rixyawaka.
Wale tshinanu wla htshin-hihretluna: — Hi wimatlu. Waneya wla htshina Jesus: — Hit-koxa hi hinkakanhi hanukta ruchpajya xyekaka ntowuxijeru.
Hsana Kamrurewaxikatshine PiranapniWaneya Jesus yinuwaka hinkakletanna satu yapkaklu pirana. Waneya wla htshina: — Satu jeji yinuwaka hitakletlu uva-cha. Rutaklu h-cerca-tetlu. Hjitotlu uva katsoxikowaka vinho-ha hkamhiywakapa hiyrunu satu tenopjiru uva-cha hislahikowakapji hkamha. Waneya hitaklucha hislahatshine renekamta. Waneya pa tshijne howuka hya.
Seyni hitaklucha hislahatshine kachitlu htowreru hkotshipjetluna. Hike manikamtkatuko hsatkakna.
Waneya jitakleru yokanatatnaklu satu htowreru. Wan-rixa kamhalpatetanruna. Hkotshipjejiwutluna.
Hiyrunuko satu hyokanata wane seyni hitaklucha hislahatshine hiylatanru. Waneko pixka rixyana pimrine htowutanune. Pimrinni ruylakkanna pimrinni ruylatkanna.
Xawakni jitakleru satupkalu hituru ramotleru rimwa hyokanatanrupa. Seyni wanepnawaka hyokanatlu. Klu tshinanu ruchinikanuwata: “Wale hetko hkahwakpiratanna.”
Seyni hitaklucha hislahatshine hiynumsakaka wannakakluko: “Ha xyekni jitakleru whene. Hayeri wuylateru. Waneyakni hitaklu hixanpatka!”
Hiyáhoni hkachitluna hiwhene. Ruylatanruna. Ruknokluna himane kahnete hitaklu mwiywakanu.
Waneya Jesus hepomha, wla htshina: — Klunerhe hkamhanu jitakleru? Runinipa ruylatanunna hitaklucha hislahatshine. Waneya renkapanna pimrineko hitaklucha hislahatshine.
Hi he het-yonhatlo Hoyakalu tokanu wla tshinatshri: “Sotlu kpanawaklerune malukkotu rikahwakluna hepixlewatatshri potukni, psolupjiko poyehitatshrini wale.
Tsru Hixikatshriwa kamhalerni hiyáhoni kihle potuklu hixa hetanuya!”
Waneya tsru hixikatshinwa judeu-ne himatlu Jesus kamnitna yapkaklu piranaya runkakletleru. Waneya ralukluna preso rutajyawakluna Jesus. Seyni hpikna hixolune yine. Wale tshinanu ruchotluna. Waneya hyatkana.
Repomhaluna Jesus Ho Tiyiro Raluka Wenutletluna César Ho Hike PiranapniWaneya fariseu-ne hasruklene hyokananwakatluna Jesus Herodes-neyma. Ralukluna rumlukanuxyawakluna.
Rapokna waneya wla htshinna: — Kasruklewakleru, wimatyi pixa halikaka pirana ptshinjeta, pasrukjetkoxna. Hiyrun-koxa hi yine hixachatatshineko yokwityi seyni pasrukle halikakalutu Hoyakalu halujyawaka pirana. Hiyáhoni punkakanwu, pkahwaklu minanchitkotlahe psoji tiyiro wenejyawaklu César Roma hajeru tsru hixikatshriwa? Ho wenejerhe ho hike?
Seyni Jesus himathetlu hixachatatshine rixyawakna waneya ruhitna, wla htshinna: — Haklu tshinanu haluk-himlukantaletno? Hanikanro proji tiyiro. Netanro.
Waneya raniklona. Waneya Jesus hepomhana: — Katu yaholunhe kat-hiwaknihe toproji hwatshri? Waneya wanna hihitlu: — César-ni.
Hiyáhoni Jesus wla tshina: — Henekanru César kluneruktapni César-nu henekanru hiyrun-koxa kluneruktapni Hoyakalunu waleko henekanru. Waneya rimyekna hihixya tshinanna.
Repomhaluna Yineru Hiwejyawakpatnaka PiranapniSatkaka saduceu hipnatshri mkahwak-hiwekletkane yanwakatlu Jesus repomhiywakapluna, wla htshinruna:
— Kasruklewakleru, Moisés-ni yonaxyawu xye hiykolu pirana: “Jeji hipninipa ruknokamtanro hhanunro mwuhenetoko, walen-moleko hnunrotanro waleni hnunro. Twuhenewatanu hipnatshrini whenene hkahwajikowakapna.”
Wan-rixa hahijewakatanna sete-ni jejinni moletkakatshinni. Tsrujruni hnunrowatni rupnana mwuhenetniko.
Waneya repurni hnunrotlo hipnahnurutatshro. Rupnana mwuhenetniko. Waneko pixka rixa hahijewakatan-koxa satni mapa rixinrini.
Sete-ni hnunrotlewatni walaluto suxo. Rupnanna mwuhenenniko. Waneya suxni koxa hipnanatka.
Xawakni hiwejikalur-hohnepatnaka, hanurpatkanhe thanuru? Klu tshinanu ptowruneko hnunrotaplo.
Waneya Jesus hihita: — Hixa pupjetatshinhi! Klu tshinanu hi himatlu Hoyakalu pirana, hi koxa himatlu Hoyakalu himukatlewle.
Seyni tujra hohne hiweklu yoptotatshinepa hi hnunrowatanu hiyrunu hi hhanuruwatanna. Hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrene tenhohne hajene pixka rixanutkana.
Hi he het-yonhatlu Moisés yonreru hipnatshine hiwekkajikowaka pirana tshinanu? Klu tshinanu kamxihiru ruchpakmeroxini Moisés-ni wla htshinyawaka Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu pirana: “Abraão-ni Hoyakalutno, Isaque-ni Hoyakalutno, Jacó-ni Hoyakalut-koxno.”
Hoyakalu hiwekatshine Hoyakalutni seyni hi miwekkanepa Hoyakalutni. Hixa psol-potuka pupjexya!
Yokanruru Hijhakalur-potu PiranapniSatu kasruklewakleru hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshri wane hwakanata. Hyijnakotlu hiynumsakaklu. Retlu kihle hihre rixlu Jesus. Wale tshinanu wla htshin-hepomhaleta: — Kasruklewakleru, kluner-pothe hijhakaluru ptowru Moisés yonreru yonatkaluruya?
Waneya Jesus hihita: — Xyekni yokanruru hijhakalur-potu: “Hyijnakotanu Israel-nerune! Tsru Hixikatshriwa Woyakalute, wale tsonni Hoyakalu.
“Pamotanru Tsru Hixikatshriwa Poyakalute psol-potuko pajiya, psol-potuko piwejinriya, psol-potuko pmixkonuya, psol-potuko pihchinikanuya.”
Yokanruru hepi rixinri wla htshin-yonhata: “Pamotanru pimwastsitanru pamoxnawakwa pixka.” Hi rawa satu yokanruru xyekaka yohnik-hijhakaluru.
Wamoxyawaklu Hoyakalu psol-potuko wajiya, psol-potuko wihchinikanuya, psol-potuko wmixkonuya hiyrun-koxa wamoxyawakna wimwastsirene wamoxnawakwa pixka ptowru henekachlu yoxikalurupa hiyrunu henekachaxikolu Hoyakalu tshinanupa yohnikayalutni.
Rexinixka Jesus tshipetkaluru yonatkaluru tokantshi hasruklewatatshri hihitlu rimatkalnuyma, waneya wla htshinru: — Pixa hi howukyi Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawakaya. Wane pnute hike tsru hchinikanutka repomhiywakatkana.
Cristo Davi-ni Klopichni Rixyawaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus hasrujinixkana Hoyakalupjiya repomha, wla htshinna: — Hanhe rumukata wla tshinretna kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine, Messias klopichnixkani Davi-ni?
Davi-ni potuko wan-tshina yonawahlo papel-mta, Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru pixkonu tshinanu, wla htshina: “Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu wan-tshinno Tsru Hixikatshriwa: Ptuplatanu npotukle sreta, haté pkamnitjene pijixi hpuko nutakanu.”
Davi-ni potuko Rutsrukate tshinru Hoyakalu hiyáhoni hanhe rumukata Davi-ni klopicha hixleta Messias? Yine hixolune yijnakotlu Jesus hasrujyawakna poyikowluyma.
Jesus Hikolujyawakna Hinanchitkaluru Pirana Hasruklewatatshine PiranapniWaneya Jesus wan-tshinjetna yine: — Xakoka kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine. Rukchikhihlenutluna mkatshri hopowalu riyanyawakna. Rukchikhihlenutluna ralijikowakna hixowaka hetanu.
Rujhaluna tuplawaka tsru hixikatshriwa tuplaxyawaka htuplaxyawakna ptowru hanjihohnewakapjiya hiyrun-koxa ralukpotutluna kihleru niklur-yeh-potuko htuplaxyawakna.
Hipnahnurutatshroni hkonahejnunkatetna. Wanepnawaka hohanjihohneru rixjetna kihleru hkahwajikolupna. Seyni wanepnawaka tsru hapnokatlu rixkona.
Hipnahnurutatshro Hike Mwikato Henekachle PiranapniWaneya Jesus tuplakanata Hoyakalupjiya. Hoyakalu henekachal-pajistsi htuplata. Ruslahakanatna yine henekachal-paji hitak-tiyirotetatshine. Hixo phurune tsru tiyiro hitaka.
Waneya wan-rixakanatawana hipnahnurutatshro hike mwikato hapokamtatka. Tutaklo tiyiro seyojiji hepi proji.
Hiyáhoni Jesus tomhana rasruklene. Waneya wla htshinna: — Halikaka wane ntshinhi, twu hipnahnurutatshro hike mwikato pimrine yohnik-tutaka wala.
Klu tshinanu nyi pimrine hixetatshro tsonu rutakna. Seyni wala, hike mwikato, teneklu psoluka timwakanatanru, tyoptojetanru tenekatka.
Waneya Hoyakalupji ruchpajinixka Jesus, satu rasrukleru wan-tshinru: — Kasruklewakleru, hi pa hihlenukananru pantshikaka hiyrunu hsotlutekaka.
Waneya Jesus hihita: — Petluhe xyepjikaka tsrukakalu? Ptowruka petleru hkoptalhako hi satukna sotlu hwahohokakanu.
Salewaktshi, Kojwaklewatatshri PiranapniJesus tuplakanata Oliveiras mriji Hoyakalupji nwaka hiyhata. Waneya Pedro, Tiago, João, hiyrunu André hepomhalu wannapkani:
— Hikluhe wan-rixanu? Klunerhe rakaxrikletanu rekhixyawakaplu xye ptowru potuko hakanhapiraxinpatka?
Waneya Jesus yinuwaka hasrukletna, wla htshinna: — Xakoka hike yokwijetanhi.
Klu tshinanu hixo hiphujewnanu hita hiwakaya wla tshinatshripa, “Hita Cristo-no” waneya hixopni hyokwijetanunna.
Hjeminiplu hiylakaklu ho pa tshijnekaka yahotkakle pirana hi hpikanu. Klu tshinanu xye ptowruko hakanhanu seyni hi hnikawnalepnitshi.
Pa neruymako hyahotkakanu satu neruko. Pa tshijneko yahotanru satupni. Hix-poktshi hiyolikanu. Natshipni. Xyekaka mturu tshino yinuwakle pixkalutni.
Wane ntshinhi ptowru potuka hmuphujewnaknukawa klu tshinanu preso hitakko, hjemahchinikanyehitko hiyrunu hanjihohnewakapjikaka hkotshipjexiko. Tsru hixikatshinwa hiyrunu tsrukakalune nwaka hanikko hita hiwaka tshinanu halikaka pirana hpohixyawakapa.
Hmapokkanuhnapukawa hnikawnahohnexyawaka ralukko kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana hinkajyawakapna ptowru neruka.
Hkachitkoklunpatka hi hkojwakahchinikanutanu hanu htshin-hihretanu hjihyehitjen-yehi hapojinipa. Klu tshinanu rapojinpapkopatka hyanumaxyawaka Hoyakalu henektokanutanhi. Klu tshinanu hyanumaxiniklunupa hi hixako htshinrepni seyni Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru henektokanutanhi.
Moltshine himolene potuko ruylajixkakanna. Waneko pixka rixan-koxna hirtshine, hwuhenene ruylajixanna. Haté hwuhenene kamnitanna rurna ruylaxyawakapluna.
Ptowru yineru hahnanutanhi hixa hita tshinanu seyni poyehi halixleru haté hmahle papko, riwekanu.
Tsru Salewaktshi PiranapniJesus pnute hya hinkakleta, wla htshina: — Hexinpatkalu tsru jhamleru mkahwajikowakanu yehi hixa himathethatatshinhi xako himatjemanru. Waneyakni katukta Judeia hwanu, rasukanu, hipjita hyanu.
Katukta teno pantshi hohowaka hwanu, hi hserpikanu rejnunkate pantshi hajeru rawapyawakapa.
Katukta campo hwanu, hi hsatkapanu hipji himkalu rawapyawakapa.
Hi pa himtukalutu retanna suxone kamchirone waneklu hohnepa, hiyrun-koxa hachiwhenetatshinepni!
Klu tshinanu tshiji rawanu salewaktshi tsrupotpákolu. Hikeklu hohne wane pixkalutu salewaktshi rawapa xye tshijne yinuwajikolukananuko haté xawakni hiyrun-koxa wane pixkalutu salewaktshi hikeklu hohne hakanhanutnaka.
Seyni Hoyakalu hma masatkanumkalu salewnikolu papkopa, hikemka hiwekanu. Seyni Hoyakalu nuretanune tshinanu, hmasatanru salewaktshi klu papkopa.
Waneya waneklu papkopa yineru wane htshinini: “Hetanu, hewitkalu Messias!”, ho wane htshinini: “Hawlalu!” — hi halixanru.
Klu tshinanu hixolune Messias minjene hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine minjene hakanhanu hiyakolukaka hiyrunu himyekaklewatatshri kamhatshine hyokwijexyawakapna yine. Rumukatkamka haté Hoyakalu nurrene hyokwijetanu.
Hiyáhoni hislahanru. Wane ntshinhi ptowru potuka hmuphujewnaknukawa.
Jeji Whene Hininri PiranapniWaneya Jesus wan-tshina: — Xye hohne hajeru salewaktshi nikawninipa, waneklutka rutshpokanu tkatshi, hi katalupni ksuru,
katahirine tenhohne hijrujini, hiyrun-koxa tenhohne hajerkaka hiyolikkako.
Waneya Jeji Whene retanna, hohimkohi rapojini royaknuyma tsru pixkonuyma koxa.
Hoyakalu yokanatanna htowrene hiwejikalune tenhohne hajene ptowru sretako rapatjexyawakapna Hoyakalu nurrene ptowru sreta tshiji hichpajikatshine.
Figueira PiranapniWaneya Jesus wan-tshina: — Xawakni himatanru figueira pirana hasrujyawakhi. Hyinuwaka hiptsheklesurexinixka hiyrun-koxa rerotewapluxinixka, himatlu hi howukatkalu mhalu.
Wane koxa rixanu, hexinpatkalu xyekaka himatanutka hi howukatkalu rakanhiywakapa.
Hichinikanru xye: Xyekaka wan-hixa hiphujewnaletanu hmupnaknuhnapukawna xawakni mupnakanewa.
Tenhohne tshij-koxa nikawnanu seyni ntokanu hikeklu nikawnanu.
Hike himatlu wale hohne hi hipapkoluko rakanhiywakapa xyekaka. Hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrene tenhohne hajene hi himatlu, hi Whentshiko himatlu seyni Hirtshi tsonupka himatlu.
Hiyáhoni hislahinri [hiyrunu hanjihohnetanu] klu tshinanu hixa hi himatlu rapojinri hohnepa.
Satu jeji howuka yatshripa pixka rixanu. Hmayaknuhnapukawa htowutna htowrerune, rapsatna kamrurewjetatshine kamrurtshi hiyrun-koxa htowutlu hiphapto hislahatshri ruslahyawakaplu.
Hiyáhoni hislahanu klu tshinanu hi himata hiklu hsatkapanu kapjiru. Ho kayiplahe ho hanikaj-yetshnoplahe ho hohistsiplahe ho yetshpotukawaplahe.
Chinpotukawa runinipa hma mapyehixyawakanuphi himkatshinhi.
Ntshinyawakhi ptowrunekhi ntshinanru: Halikak-potu hislahinri!
Hjemahchinikankakyehitluna Jesus Ruylaxyawakapluna PiranapniWaneya hepi hohne mahatatka Páscoa hohne tshinkaluru rexyawakapa. Waleni pão myapjetu nijikolu hohne. Hiyáhoni tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hiyrunu kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine hijhahchinikanuta hanu rixa himukata preso hitakletluna Jesus yokwiruyma ruylaxyawakapluna.
Waneya wla htshinatkana: — Seyni xye hi wkamhanu tsru hohne pchinika hmakanhiywakanupa yin-sejire.
Jesus Betânia Hapkapyawaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus Betânia poktshi hwakanata, Simão-pji hijirohitutatshripji. Waneya hnikka pchinikna tunamta sato suxo waneylo pa stonha sotlu kamhikolo phamluhalo katsephal-potuko nardo-ha, myapjetkoto kwenur-potukni. Tupokhatanro waneya Jesus jiwu tuyokhatanro.
Waneya satkaka yineru wane hwakanatatshine hahkalo. Hi rukchikhihlenutlona wane tixyawaka hiyáhoni wane htshinkakna: — Haklu tshinanu t-saletachatlo?
Trezentos hohne kamrurtshi wenru pso yohnikamka tumukata hichankaletmaklo wala phamluhalo. Wale tiyirotemka tumukata henekletna hike mwikane. Hiyáhoni hyanhaklona wala suxo.
Seyni Jesus wan-tshina: — Hetachatanro. Haklu hikojwaklo twu suxo? Kihler-potuko tkamhiyno.
Hike mwikane ptowru hohneruka himwanu hixa tskalaya. Hikluktako haluk-hepixletna himukata hepixletna seyni hi ptowru hohneruka pimwanno hita.
Ptowru tumukatleru tkamhatka. Nmupnaknuhnapukawa phamluhalo tutakmanexinno, talpokomanetno nkapnaxikolupa.
Hichinikanru xyekaka: Psol-tshijneko kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana hinkaklexiko, tkamhaleru koxa hinkakletko, tuchinijikolupa wala.
Judas Kamnixyawaklu Jesus PiranapniWaneya satu doze rixinri Jesus hasrukleru, Judas Iscariotes tshinkaluru yanwakatna tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne riynumsaxyawakapna hanu potu rixa hiphujetletanru Jesus wanna yehiya.
Jesus Páscoa Hohne Hichinijyawaka PiranapniWaneya mitshikanan-hohne pão myapjetu nijikolu hohne, carneiro-ne ruylajexinrina judeu-ne Páscoa hohne ruchinikjexinrina hohne, rasruklene hepomhalu Jesus: — Hanurhe walpokotanru Páscoa hohne nikle wnijyawakapa tshinanu?
Waneya Jesus wla tshina yokanretna hepi rasruklene: — Tsru poktshi hyanu. Waneya wane hyoptoxinri satu jeji hachhaji katsephalu hanikamtatshri. Homkahitanru.
Waneya hanupjiktako hjihlokamxinri jeji wane htshinanru kapjiru kasruklewakleru hepomhakjixhi: “Hanhe rawa hihruko hita, nasrukleneyma himukata niklexyawakapa Páscoa hohne tshinanupa?
Hiyáhoni wale hekhitanhi tsru hihruko pantshi hohwaka hwatshri, ralpokotka ptowruka hwiywaka. Wane halpokoxini.
Waneya hepi rasruklene tsru poktshi hyana. Waneya rukchikluna Jesus tshinyawaka pixka potuko. Waneya ralpokotluna hniklerupna Páscoa hohne kayno hnijyawakapna.
Jesus Hekhixyawaklu Hkamnitjeru PiranapniWaneya rutshpojinixka Jesus rasrukleneyma hapokatka.
Hnikka pchinikna mesa yehi, Jesus wla tshina: — Halikaka ntshinhi, satu hewi hwatshri niminkaleru nkamnitjerupa.
Waneya wanna wamonuwpotuta waneya satkaka yinuwaka hepomhaletlu: — Hitlahe?
Waneya Jesus hihitatka, wla htshina: — Nkamnitjerukni satu hixa doze-hi hitayma pão yotshmota prato-ya.
Klu tshinanu Jeji Whene tshinkaluru halikaka hipnanu Hoyakalu tokanu tshinyawaka pixka. Seyni hektu potlu wale jeji, Jeji Whene tshinkaluru kamnitatshri. Kihle potlu wale jeji hma matuxyawakanutka.
Jesus Hipninri Yapkakle PiranapniWaneya hnikka pchinikna Jesus pão hkochtsheka. Waneya hpoyahnutlu Hoyakalu. Hjiknajrotlu pão waneya rasruklene reneklu. Waneya wla htshina: — Pão hyoptotanu. Xyeni hatatjewa nomane.
Waneya copa stono hkochtsheka. Hpoyahnutlu Hoyakalu, rasruklene reneklu. Ptowruneka wale stono hirya.
Waneya wla htshina: — Xyeni hatatjewa nohraha hmunanhalerni Hoyakalu yineruyma hixolune yine tshinanu hiyokkalurupa.
Halikaka ntshinhi hikeklu hohne nuranutnaklu xye vinho-ha haté nurinri vinho-ha herotu Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawakaya hohnepa.
Waneya satu chikale hchikaletna, ralimtna, himriji Monte Oliveiras tshinikowaka hyatkana.
Jesus Hinkaklu Pedro Wkatakluyakawa PiranapniWaneya Jesus wan-tshinna rasruklene: — Ptowrunekhi hiknokanno klu tshinanu Hoyakalu tokanu wan-tshina: “Nuylatanru carneiro-ne hinotatshri, waneya hiprane hipalatanu.”
Seyni niwejinpatnaka, hita kosekanhi hixa Galileia tshijne nwaka.
Waneya Pedro hihitlu, wla htshinru: — Hikeklu hohne nuknokanyi pixa yáholu pimrine ptowruneka hiknokanyi seyni hita hike.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru Pedro: — Puchinikanru xye: Xye yetshno hepi kata hma yanumatkanuklunuwa patlapa, pixa map-kata pma mimatletanutu ptshinanno.
Seyni Pedro hipokananu wan-tshinatnaka: — Hike! Hikeklu hohne nma mimatletanutu ntshinanyi yáholu pixayma nupnanu. Waneya pimrine rasruklene ptowruneka koxa wane potuko htshinna.
Jesus Getsêmani Tshinikowaka Hyiywaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus rasrukleneyma Getsêmani tshinikowaka hya. Waneya rapojinixkana Jesus wla tshinna: — Hixa hewitshi htuplatanu, nanjihohnetka pchinika.
Waneya ranikna Pedro, Tiago, João koxa. Jesus yinuwaka wamonuwnalepotuta, hiyrun-koxa hsalewnahchinikanuta.
Waneya wla htshina: — Niwejinri wamonuwpotuthonuka, hatatjewa nupnakastsitkani. Hewiphitshi, hislahanu.
Waneya wane pnutejiji hya. Hyospaka tshiji rutspakhojita Waneya ranjitlu Hoyakalu hpoyahoxinipa hkochpajyawakaplu wale papko salewaktshi.
Waneya wane htshina hanjihohnereta: — Hirtshi! Nuru! Pixa ptowruko himukatatshriyi. Pkochripaxinno twu copa salewaktshi yehiya. Seyni hi hitako nalujyawaka pkamhanu seyni pixako palujyawaka pkamhanu halikaka.
Waneya Jesus satokanwakatna rasruklene, retamtna himkatshine, waneya repomhalu Pedro: — Simão, pumkawhe? Hi he pa hora-kna himukata hislahleta hitayma?
Hislahanru, hanjihohnetanu hmallixikowakanupa. Klu tshinanu jmeremkahi seyni mantshicha mmixkotni.
Hiyrunuko pnute hya ranjihohnexyawakapa waneya htshinakanaxyawaka pixka hanjihohneruya htshinatnaka.
Waneya hsatokatnaka rasruklene nwaka, retamtna himkatshine hi rumukata himrekhayhaletna. Hi rimatna hanu rixa hihretanruna Jesus.
Hpalnanu, hayewa. Hetanu, tujrapa nkamnitjeru!
Jesus Kachixikowaka PiranapniJesus yanumakanaxiniwa, satu doze rixinri rasruklene Judas tshinkaluru hapokatka. Waleymalune hixolune tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne, kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine hiyrun-koxa tsrukakalune judeu-ne yokanatanune. Yohlolewapi hiyrunu hahaje ranikna.
Kamnitatshri satu rimaxikole runkakna, wla htshina: — Katukta namlutanu, walekatkani. Hkachitanru wale. Kihle kachre hixanru. Wan-hixatshri hanikanu.
Waneya hajeyri rapokastsixinixkalu Jesus waneya wane htshina Judas: — Kasruklewakleru! Waneya ramlutlu.
Waneya wan-rixa kachretluna Jesus. Hkachpotuthonukluna.
Seyni satu wane hwakanatatshri kochpaklu hyohlolewapre. Waneya hkastakjepitlu tsru sacerdote towrer-jepi.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinna yine: — Ha hixa wkata hina yohlolewapikakayma, hahajekakayma koxa hkachixyawakapno? Hatatjewa katshowhurlanohe?
Hixayma nwakanata ptowru hohneruka. Ptowru hohneruka Hoyakalupji nasrukjekanaxyahi. Seyni hi hkachitno. Seyni xye ptowruka hakanha Hoyakalu tokanu tshinyawaka hpoyahokajyawakapa tshinanu.
Waneya rasruklene ptowruneka hichotatkalu, rasukatkana.
Waneya satu makluji mkatshri sama tsonu poyixikatshriwa homkahitlu Jesus. Waneya satkaka yineru yahot-kachretmaklu.
Seyni hkaspukamkalutlu. Rasuka malechkopiru.
Tsrukakalune Jemahchinikankakyehixyawaklu Jesus PiranapniWaneya ranikluna Jesus tsru sacerdote-pji nwaka. Wanepji rapatjexyana tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne, tsrukakalune judeu-ne, kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshin-koxa.
Seyni Pedro hohatjini romkahyehixyalu Jesus. Waneya tsru sacerdote hiputre hjihloka. Tshitshmerostsi htuplata soldado-neyma roljiywakapa.
Waneya tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hiyrunu tsrukakalune jemahchinikankakatshine hijhamkalu satu rukolukanuwninri yáhole rumukata hiylalexyawakapluna. Seyni hike rukchikna.
Hixolune yine weyawjechayehitlu Jesus seyni satkaka yineru pnuk-tshina. Seyni hi psokaklu pirana htshinna.
Satkaka yineru yotunota hweyawyehitluna Jesus malechawaka htshinyehitluna, wla htshinna:
— Wjemlu wla htshinyawaka: “Numukata nikatletanru xye Hoyakalupji yine kamhalerupji seyni map-hohne pnute, nkamhanutnaklu satu pantshi hi yinemyo kamhapjitanrupni.”
Seyni wanepnawaka hi pixkakaklu htshinna.
Waneya tsru sacerdote hixolune hanikajite yotunoxya waneya Jesus repomha: — Hi he puhitanru hjihyehixyayina?
Seyni Jesus hi hihita. Hike htshina. Waneyatnaka tsru sacerdote hepomhatnaklu: — Pixlahe Messias-yi, Hoyakalu himalwutkaluru whenyi?
Waneya Jesus hihitlu: — Hitakni. Hiyrunu hixa ptowrunekhi hetanru Jeji Whene, hohimkohi hoho hapokatshripa, Ptowru Himukatatshri Hoyakalu potukle sreta tuplatatshripni.
Waneya tsru sacerdote hjihekannu tshinanu hsuskamkaluxnawa waneya wla htshina: — Hi wujhana pimrine hiphujtatatshine.
Hjemluhe hektuwaka htshinanwakaxyawaklu Hoyakalu? Hiyáhoni kluhe hkahwaka hixa? Waneya ptowru yineru wan-tshina rujhalu rupniywaka.
Waneya satkaka yineru yinuwaka hitskahjeretlu. Ruchyahojitluna. Rutsojtakluna waneya wla htshinruna: — Pmetanutu punkakletanu kathe hiylakyi. Hiyrunu rinotjen-koxa kachitlu, rutsojtakluna.
Pedro Wan-Tshina Hi Rimathetlu Jesus PiranapniPedro honra tsru hixikatshriwa sacerdote hiputre rawakanata waneya sato tsru sacerdote towrero hapokatka.
Tetlu Pedro tshitshmero rolkakanata. Tyopukhatlu waneya wla ttshinru: — Pix-koxa Jesus Nazaré hajeruymalutyi.
Seyni wale weyawata wla htshina: — Hi nimathetlu. Hi nimata klukta ptshina. Hiyáhoni hiputu hichpajyawakle hya waneyatka hyanumatatka patlapa.
Waneya towretshro hexinitnaklu Pedro tyinuwaka hinkakletna wanestsi hwakanatatshine: — Xye jeji wannaymalutni.
Seyni Pedro weyawatatnaka hiyrunuko hi wannaymalutno htshina. Waneya xekoyaka wane hwakanatatshine wan-tshinatnaklu: — Ha hi wkahekyi, wimatyi pixa satu wannaymalutyi klu tshinanu pixa Galileia hajer-koxyi.
Waneklukawa patlapa yanumatatnaka. Waneya Pedro hichinikaplu Jesus tokanu htshinakanaxyawaklu: “Hepi kata hma yanumatkanuklunuwa patlapa, pixa map-kata hi pimathetno ptshinanu.” Hiyáhoni Pedro kaheknanuwahchinikanutatka waneya hyinuwaka tshiyahlepotuta.
Pilatos Yehi Ranijyawakluna Jesus PiranapniWaneya yetshpotukawa rapatjetna judeu-ne tsrukakalune, tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne, hiyrun-koxa kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine. Rapatjehchinikanutna ptowruneka judeu chefe-teneyma. Rostutluna Jesus, waneya ranikluna phuru Pilatos renejyawakapluna.
Waneya phuru Pilatos hepomhalu: — Pixlahe judeu-nerune pohiryi? Waneya Jesus hihitlu, wane htshina: — Pixako wan-tshina.
Waneya tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hixo jihyehixikolu htshinyehitluna Jesus.
Waneya phuru Pilatos hiyrunuko hepomhatnaklu: — Hi he puhitanu? Petanu hi heppika hima htshinyehityina!
Hiyrunuko Jesus hi hihita. Hiyáhoni phuru Pilatos himyeka.
Tsru niklu hohne tshinanu phuru Pilatos hasruhlu satu preso hajeru hichoxyawaka, yine nurrer-potuko.
Waneklu papko satu jeji Barrabás tshinkaluru preso hwa. Waleymalune poktshi tsrukakalutene hkamnikanaxyawakna klu papko ruylalenni tshinanu kapna rutakkana.
Waneya hixolune hapokanwakatlu phuru Pilatos waneya hyinuwaka hanjiretluna renejyawakluna satu preso hajeru hasruha hixlexyawaka pixka.
Waneya phuru Pilatos hepomha, wla htshinna: — Halukhe nuchoxyawaklu judeu pohire?
Klu tshinanu rimata tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hhahxalna tshinanu raluka kachretluna Jesus.
Seyni tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne komyekna yine Pilatos ranjixyawakapna hma muchoxyawakanuplu Jesus seyni Barrabás halikaka ruchoxyawakapa.
Waneya phuru Pilatos hiyrunuko hepomhatnaka: — Kluhe haluka nkamhiywaklu xye jeji judeu-ne pohire htshinreru hixa?
Waneya hsaplewatna yine, wla htshinna: — Cruz putakanru!
Waneya phuru Pilatos hepomhanna: — Seyni kluhe hektutu hkamha? Seyni hiyrunuko hsaplewpotuthonukna: — Cruz putakanru! Cruz putakanru!
Pilatos haluk-himuwkakletna yine hiyáhoni ruchoxyaluna Barrabás. Waneya hkotshipjejixluna Jesus katsaluya. Waneya reneklu cruz rutajyawakapluna.
Soldado-ne Heyijyawaklu Jesus PiranapniWaneya soldado-ne haniklu Jesus phurupji hanikajite hwapututatshri. Waneya soldado-ne ptowruneka wane hapatjexya.
Waneya mkatshri serolu hmakatluna Jesus. Sahyi kawchiriplu kamhikolu hijiwu rutakna.
Hyinuwaka halikletluna wla htshinna: — Hali judeu-ne Tsru Hixikatshriwate!
Rutpejiwutluna hahajeya, rutskahjetluna waneya hyoptsojityehitluna rimalwuhotluna.
Rali heyiklexinixkaluna, mkatshri serolu hkomkahluna waneya waleko himkalu rutakleru hmakatatnakluna. Waneya ranikluna cruz rutajyawakapluna ruylaxikowakapa.
Simão Tshinkaluru Hanijyawaklu Jesus Cruz-te PiranapniWaneya hatnu hapo hyoptoxyaluna satu jeji Simão tshinkaluru Cirene poktshi hajeru, Alexandre hiyrunu Rufo hirni. Campo ruchpajya tsru poktshi hyamta. Waneya cruz rutjikakluna.
Cruz Rutajikowakapa Jesus PiranapniWaneya Calvário tshinikowaka ranikluna Jesus. (Wale tokantshi yokakkaluru, yineru jiwuta pixkalutu yehi.)
Raluk-hitletmakluna vinagre-ha, mirra yapjerha seyni hi rurlu.
Waneya cruz rutakluna. Waneya himkalu hkanipretna wannakakluko. Hiknokkaluru ruknokna soldado-ne rimaxyawakapna katu kayatanru Jesus-ni mkalu.
Hohohne nove horas cruz rutakka Jesus.
Sato tábua cruz-stsipto hixpatka Jesus jihyehixikolu pirana. Wla htshin-yonhata: “Xyeni Jesus judeu-ne pohire.”
Hiyrun-koxa katshowhurune hepi wan-rutakna. Satu Jesus potukle sreta rutakka. Satu pa sta sreta hitakka.
[Wan-rixa poyahokakletka Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru wan-tshinatshri: “Hektutu kamhakleruneymalutu hkahwajikolupa wale.”]
Hiyáhoni cruz pkochpajinwa! Piwekkajinwa!
Tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne, kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine heyik-koxlu. Waneya wla htshinna: — Pimrine riwekkaka seyni hi rumukata wale nanuko hiwekkaklexnawa.
Messias, Israel pohire pixini, cruz pkochpajinwa wexyawakapa walixyawakapyi. Jesus-yma cruz hitakkalune waneko pixka rixa heyikletkoxluna.
Jesus Hipninri PiranapniWaneya hanikaj-hohnetkani rutshpokatka, três hora pchinika psol-tshijneka hitshpoka.
Waneya kayi nwaka mapa horas rixinixka Jesus wla tshin-saplewleta: — “Eloi, Eloi, lamá sabactâni?” Wale tokantshi yokakkaluru: “Noyakalute, Noyakalute, haklu pumuknokanno?”
Waneya satkaka wane hwakanatatshine jemlu xye hima waneya wla htshinna: — Hjemanu! Elias-ni htomha!
Satu jeji hasukamta kamkolu ruhajyawakapa. Vinagre-ha rutaka, hahajestsipto rutaklu, Jesus rurjixlu. Waneya wla htshina: — Hkahwakanu! Weteru ho Elias-ni cruz-lhe kochpajinru ho hike.
Seyni Jesus hipokananu saplewatatka waneya rupnanatka.
Waneya mkatshri sama Hoyakalupji hwatshrini hiskakana hepi tshraj-samanru, teno haté tshiji ruskajyanatka.
Waneya romano-neru soldado-ne pohire cruz sreta hwakanatatshri jeminixkalu hsaplewle hiyrunu rexinixkalu wan-rixa hipnaletatka Jesus-ni waneya wla htshina: — Halikakni xye jeji honnira Hoyakalu whenni.
Satkaka suxo wane koxa hwakanata. Howuka rexyana. Wannayma rawakanatna Maria Madalena tshinkaluro, Salomé tshinkaluro hiyrunu Maria tshinkaluro, José hiyrunu Tiago Hepurtshi tshinkaluru hinro.
Nyi suxone Galileia rawakanaxini Jesus, romkahjekanatluna ruslahjekanatluna. Wane koxna hixo pimrone wannaymalune Jesus Jerusalém nwaka himotsatatshine.
Jesus Kapnaxikolu PiranapniHalpokotkalur-hohnetkani, waleni hapnanuxikalur-hohne hnapu hajeru,
waneya rutshpokpiraxini rapokatka José, Arimateia hajeru. Wale yineru hijhakalurni, tsru jemahchinikankakatshine yehi hajerni. Hiyrunu Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka kahwakatshrini. Htseruwahchinikanumta ranjixyawakaplu phuru Pilatos Jesus mane renejikowakapa.
Waneya phuru Pilatos jeminixkalu Jesus-ni hali hipnaletatka rimyekatka. Hiyáhoni htomhalu romano-neru soldado-ne pohire waneya repomhalu klu papko potukla rupnanatka Jesus.
Waneya romano-neru soldado-ne pohire hinkajinixkalu Jesus hipninri pirana phuru Pilatos hitshitlu José Jesus manni ranijyawakapa.
Waneya Jesus-ni mane hkochtsheka cruz-ya, waneya linho sama mkatshri sama ranjireru ruwtoklu. Waneya kapna, sotlu jitoxikolu hipjitaya rutakmanetlu Jesus. Waneya tsru sotlu reruta yomletshi jihlojikowaka, ruchyaxyawakaplu.
Maria Madalena, hiyrunu Maria, José hinro koxa het-hitakkotlu Jesus-ni mane.
Jesus Hiwejyawakatnaka PiranapniWaneya hapnanuxikalur-hohne hiknohatka waneya Maria Madalena tshinkaluro, Salomé tshinkaluro hiyrun-koxa Maria tshinkaluro, Tiago hinro hanjitlo phamluhalo Jesus manni ruyohaxyawakaplona.
Domingo hohne yetshpotukawa ronoxinixka tkatshi yomletsh-yehi hyatkana.
Hatnu hapo hyapamtna wane htshinamtna: — Kathe heruxinwu yomletshi hichyatatshri sotlu?
Wane htshinna wanna klu tshinanu tsru potuklu sotlu. Seyni ronotamxinixkana retluna rerutkatka sotlu.
Hiyáhoni hjihlokyomletluna. Waneya retluna makluji klatalu mkatshri hitakatshri, hpotukle sreta htuplakanata. Rimyekpotutna.
Seyni wale wan-tshina: — Hi himyekanu! Nimatlu Jesus Nazaré hajeru cruz hipnapikatshri hijha. Seyni hi hewitkalu, riwekatnaka. Hetanru rukoluhakanaxyawaka.
Xawakni hyanu. Pedro, pimrine rasruklen-koxa hinkakanu xye pirana: “Wale kosekamtanhi hixa Galileia tshijne. Wane hexinri htshinyahi pixka.”
Waneya yomletshi nwaka ruchpajyatkana. Rasukamtna. Tsru piklu rixna. Rutatakna hiyrunu hike runkakna klu tshinanu hpikpotuthonukna.
Jesus Hakanhayehixyawaklo Maria Madalena PiranapniJesus hiwekatnaka domingo prika. Mitshikananhapka Maria Madalena rakanhayehita. Wala honra mitshikananu sete kamtshine takajika.
Wala yatka tunkakapyawakapna Jesus himwakanatatshine klu tshinanu hwamonuwnana, htshiyahakanatna.
Seyni hjeminixkaluna Jesus hiwejinritnaka hiyrunu texyawaklu pirana, hi ralixlona.
Waneya hsatkapna pimrine rasruklene nwaka runkaklewaxyawakapna seyni wanna hi halixlu runkaklexyana.
Jesus Onze Rasruklene Hakanhayehixyawaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus hapkata hakanhayehletna onze rasruklene. Hnikakanatna. Waneya wale hijretna hmalixlenna tshinanu hiyrunu hchikhajna tshinanna. Klu tshinanu hi ralixtokanutna pimrine Jesus hiwekatshri hetatshine.
Waneya wla htshina: — Ptowru tshijne hyanu hinkakanna kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana ptowru tshijne hajeneka.
Katukta halixanru hiyrunu h-batiza-xikowakapa riwekkaka hikeklu hohne mnikawnakanepni. Seyni katukta hi halixanru hamhatshripni.
Halixatshinepa pixkontshi renekkotkana xye hetkalurkaka hkamhiywakapna: kamtshine ruknokajyawakapna hita hiwakaya, hiyrun-koxa herotu nrukaka hyanumaxinna.
Hiyrun-koxa ho himnu hkachixinna ho hisa rurinna hike rixanna. Hiyrunu yeyixatshine hoho rutakamyoxinna rutskalhanna.
Jesus Tenhohne Yinri PiranapniWaneya rali hiynumsaletna Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus tenhohne hanikkatka. Hoyakalu potukle sreta htuplata.
Waneya rasruklene ptowru sreta hyana runkakletluna kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana. Hiyáhoni Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus hepixlewata hetkalurkakayma rekhixyawakapa halikaka pirana htshinna.
<font color=teal>Lucas</font>Teófilo Tshinkaluru TshinanupaHi heppika yineru yahot-yonretmaklu Jesus pirana rixjekanaxyawaka hix-yehi hkamhajekanaxinri pirana tshinanu.
Xyekaka pirana wunkakjene, reyinuwaklekananuko hetatshine hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu tokanu jinkakletaklerunekananni.
Hiyáhoni, kchinikanur-potni Teófilo, hit-koxa hikchikhihlenutlu nyonaxyawaklu xye pirana kihle pokowak-potuko nixyawakaplu pixa tshinanu. Klu tshinanu hit-honra xye pirana reyinuwaklekananuko nuslahpiranpotukanatlu.
Pimatpotuxyawakaplu pix-koxa psol-piranako halikaka pirana pasrujikolu.
João Batista Matuxinri Hinkaklexikolu PiranapniJudeu tshijne pohire Herodes tshinkaluru klu papko wanekanan-koxlu satu sacerdote Zacarias tshinkaluru. Sacerdote-ne Abias tshinkalune klopichni wale. Hiyrun-koxa Zacarias hnunro Isabel tshinkaluro sacerdote klopich-koxni Arão tshinkaluru klopichni wala.
Hiyrun-koxa powrahchinikanurunni wanna hepi Hoyakalu hetanuya. Kajnákona Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hiykolukaka. Hi psojikna hpupjexyana.
Seyni Isabel tshinkaluro hi michiwata hiyáhoni mwuhenewaklenni; hiyrun-koxa tsrutsolejinetkani.
Waneya pa kata Zacarias tshinkaluru sacerdote kamrure hkamhakanata Hoyakalu kamrure, rix-kamrurjexyawakna sacerdote-ne.
Wan-rix-kamhaljexyawakna sacerdote-ne, rutakka Zacarias tshinkaluru, Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalupji hjihlojyawakapa phamluhalo hyoxijyawakapa.
Waneya rapokpapkoluxinixka phamluhalo hyoxijyawaka, pimrine hixolune Hoyakalupji maleka sretate hwakanatatshine ranjihohnekanatna.
Waneyakni satu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru hakanhayehitlu Zacarias. Kapajiru henekachalu yoxikaluru hitajikowaka phamluhalo yoxijikowakastsi hpotukle sreta hyopkakakanata Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru.
Waneya Zacarias hexinixkalu hkojwakahchinikanuxnawa. Hpikpotutatka.
Seyni hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru wan-tshinru: — Hi ppikanu, Zacarias. Hoyakalu himatlu panjireru hanjihohneruya. Hiyáhoni phanunro Isabel matuwhenexinyi jejipni. Phiwakatanru xako João.
Hmatuxinipa pumuwatanu pixa hiyrun-koxa hixolune yine poyikowatanu.
Klu tshinanu tsru hitakkalurupni Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu yhaleya. Wale xako hikeklu hohne ruranru vinho-ha, hi katshwuhaloko ruranu. Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru tsepotmanetanru runro nanwaka ruchpajinikananuko.
Hixolune yine israel-nerune hsatkakanu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu Royakalutna romkahixyawakapna.
Hoyakalu towrerupni, jinkaklewaklerupni. Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshrini Elias-ni tshinkalurni hchinikanu pixka rixleyma hiyrun-koxa Elias-ni pixkonu pixka rixleyma rimatletkakanna tsrune hwuheneneymana. Hektutu kamhatshine ruprotakanna potuka hchinikanurune hiykole romkahixyawakapna. Ralpokohnaputna yine Tsru Hixikatshriwa hapojinripa.
Waneya Zacarias hepomhatkalu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru: — Hanhe xawaka nixa halixletlu xye pirana? Klu tshinanu tsrutsolejitkano. Nhanunro koxa hixo mhaletkalo.
Waneya hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru wane htshin-hihretlu: — Petanu. Nhiwaka Gabriel, Hoyakalu towrerno. Walekni nyokanatjeru pixa nunkajyawakapa xye pirana kihler-potuko.
Petanu. Hi palixlu nunkakle wanepnawaka rapokpapkoluxinipa rakanhanu ptowru piranaka nunkajyatkayi. Seyni pmalixtokanutkan-tshinanno, myanumatkatupyi. Hi pumukata yanumletanuna haté hmatuxinipa piwhene.
Seyni yine wane pchinika hkahwakakanatluna Zacarias tshinkaluru Hoyakalupji ruchpajyawakapa. Rimyekna klu tshinanu hohamokatkalu.
Isabel Tshinkaluro Poyikowaxyawakapa PiranapniWan-rixa. Rali kamruremxinixkalu, sacerdote kamrure, hipji nwaka hyatka.
Waneya pchini hohnejijitka Zacarias hnunro Isabel tshinkaluro michiwatatka waneya cinco ksuru hi tuchpaka topjiya.
Waneya wane ttshina: — Xawaknikananu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hepixatkano. Xawakni nimatlu ruchinijyawakno klu tshinanu hkonyano npatewle yine hetanuya, klu tshinanu kwhenepatkano. Mwuhenewakletno nixpatka.
Jesus Matuxinripa PiranapniWaneya seis ksuru rixinri kamchiro tixyawaka Isabel tshinkaluro Hoyakalu yokanatatnaklu hiwejikaluru htowreru tenhohne hajeru, Gabriel tshinkaluru, Nazaré poktshi Galileia tshijneya, hyiywakapa.
Makloji jeji mapokmanetanuto yehi hya. Twu suxo José tshinkaluru tunkaklexika, Phuru Davi-ni tshinkalurni klopichni, hhanunroxyawaka. Twu suxo jeji mapokmanetanuto hiwakni Maria.
Hiyáhoni hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru hapyehitlo wla htshinatkalo: — Hali, pixa Hoyakalu nurreroyi Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu pixaymalu.
Seyni Maria kojwakahchinikanuta wane htshina haliklexyawaklo. Tujhahchinikanuta klu tshinanhe wane htshintokanyehitlo.
Seyni hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru wan-tshinro: — Hi ppikanu, Maria, klu tshinanu kihlehchinikanru Hoyakalu pixa tshinanu.
Petanu. Pixa michiwatanu, jeji pmatkakanu. Jesus putakhiwakatanru.
Tsru Hixikatshriwa rixyawakapa. Hhiwakatko, Hoyakalu Tsru Potuko whenni. Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu henekanru rurni Davi-ni pohirewakanaxyawaka.
Jacó-ni klopichane pohirepni hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa, hiyrun-koxa hpohirewnale hikeklu hohne nikawnanutka.
Waneya Maria wan-tshinru hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru: — Hanhe rixa hakanhaletanu xye klu tshinanu hita hike hapokmanetno.
Seyni hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru wan-tshinro: — Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru pix-hohwaka rapokanu. Hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu Ptowru Potuka Himukatatshri himukatle pix-hitokote hwanu. Wale tshinanu mturu pkaylerupa Hoyakalu nurrerni. Hoyakalu whene htshinko.
Hiyrunu petanu. Pimole Isabel-mka tsrotsolejni. Seyni wala koxa kwajnanwaka mturu seyni jejni. Hike kahwaklo tmichiwaxyawaka seyni kamchirotkani. Seis ksurutkalo.
Klu tshinanu Hoyakaluyma hikeni kyapreru.
Waneya Maria wan-tshinru: — Hewitkano. Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu towrerno. Wane potuko rixanno ptshinyawakno. Waneya hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru yatka.
Maria Hetapyawaklo Tomole Isabel PiranapniWaneya hi hix-hohnepotu, wane tuchpajya Maria. Teyakawamta. Teno mrijiwaka tya. Judeia tshijne hajeru poktshi nwaka tya.
Zacarias-pji tjihlokatka waneya Isabel tshinkaluro talikatka.
Wane tixatka. Isabel jem-haliklexinixkalo Maria, mturu Isabel nanwaka hajeru ruptekapa. Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru pixkonu himwatkalo.
Hiyáhoni hipokananu tyanumata. Wla ttshina yanumleta Isabel: — Hihlehchinikanyehitkalúroyi pixje suxon-yehiya. Hiyrun-koxa hihlehchinikanyehitkaluru pixa nanwaka hichpajikatshripa.
Katnohe hita tyanwakaxyawakno Noyakalute hinro tetapyawakno?
Petanu. Hajeyrono yijnakotatkayi palijyawakno mturu nonanwaka hajeru hiptekapa hpoyikonuyma.
Hihlehchinikanyehitkalúroyi klu tshinanu palixanru rixa hakanhalexyawaka psol-piranako Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hinkajyatkayi halikaka.
Maria Himalwure PiranapniWaneya wla ttshinatka Maria: — Naji himalwutlu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu.
Niwejinri himuwata Hoyakalu Niwekkakjeru tshinanu.
Klu tshinanu hita ruchinikanretatka, hitako, htowrerno, hike makotkatokno. Xawakni pnut-hohne hihlewahchinikanyehitkalurno wane htshinnona ptowru hiwekhohnekanatatshine ptowru hixatshine jejine, suxone.
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu Ptowru Potuko Himukatatshriko tsru hetkaluru hkamhiyno. Hhiwakni Potukal-potuko.
Retwamonre rekhitna yine hkahwakpiratjene pejnu hiwekakanatatshine haté xawakni pnut-hohne hiwekatshinepa.
Rekhitlu hmixkonu hkamrureymakotka. Hkopalatna halixkotachaxikatshinwa ruchinikanretanruymana.
Jinanu rixkakna natshikanatatshine ptowru nijittshi kihleruya. Phurune hyokanatanna hyiywakatkana hike manikaneko.
Repixlu htowreru israel-nerune klu tshinanu hi ramtakatkalu retwamonrewle.
Runkajya pirannina wutsrukatenni. Wan-rixlu Abraão-ni hiyrun-koxa hiklopichaneya hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa.
Waneya Maria tshinkaluro mapa ksuru pchinika Isabel tshinkaluro yehi twa. Waneya topji nwaka t-satokatnaka Maria.
João Batista Tshinkaluru Matuxyawaka PiranapniWaneya rapokpapkoluxinixka Isabel tshinkaluro tmatuwhenexyawaka, twuhenetlu mturu jeji.
Waneya timwastsirene hiyrun-koxa tomolene jempiranyehitlu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hepixyawaklo Isabel tshinkaluro pirana. Hiyáhoni rumuwatna wanna ptowruneka walayma.
Waneyatka mturu oito hohne rixinixka ranikluna mturu hjiprojhaptojimtaxikowakpatka. Waneyakni rutakhiwakatmakluna Zacarias, ruru hiwakako.
Seyni runro wan-tshina: — Hike seyni João htshinko halikaka.
Waneya pimrine wan-tshinro: — Seyni hi satukna pimolene xye hiwaka hiwakatletatshri.
Waneya rutsejrihjetluna mturu hiru hanu htshinahiwakatlepiratlu wale.
Waneya Zacarias hanjitlu papel-mta. Waneya hyonatlu hituru hiwaka João. Waneya ptowruneka himyekatka.
Waneya waneklukawa potuko Zacarias himukata yanumletatnaka. Waneya hyinuwaka himalwuretlu Hoyakalu.
Waneyakni rimwastsitanune pikatkalu Hoyakalu. Hiyrun-koxa Judeia tshijne teno mrijiwakaya psoluchako hpohixikatka xye pirankaka.
Waneya ptowru yine xye pirankaka jematshine himretpiranatlu rajiyna. Repomhiynawana: — Klu hixatshripni xye mturu? Klu tshinanu halikaka phujetkalu Hoyakaluyma rixyawaka.
Zacarias Tshinkaluru Hinkakletlu Mapokatuwa PiranapniWaneya mturu hiru, Zacarias tshinkaluru, katsepoylu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hiyáhoni runkakletlu mapokatuwa pirana, waneya wane htshina:
— Himalwutkaluru Tsru Hixikatshriwa israel-nerune Hoyakalute, klu tshinanu runatka, riwekkakatkana rayinetene.
Hoyakalu henekatkawu satu hiwekkaklewatatshri, tsru pixkonurutu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu towreru Davi tshinkalurni klopichni.
Mitshikawako wane htshinatka Hoyakalu, htokanu hinkakletatshine nuretkaluneya.
Runkakletlu wkamnitjenemyoya riwekkajyawakapwu, waneya pnuteko runkakwu wahnanutjene jihekannu hkochtshejinwu.
Retwamonre pirana wutsrukatenni runkaklexinritka rekhitanu. Htshina hinkaklexyawaknina pixka potuko rixa halikakalutu pirana hi ramtaklu.
Hoyakalu hinkakniri wutsrukatni Abraão-ni, hiyáhoni Hoyakalu kamhiylu htshina hinkaklexyawak-potuko.
Hkochpajyawakapwu wkamnitjene hamlenu, wpoyaho homkahrexyawakaplu Hoyakalu, hike wpikanu,
Wumukata homkahretlu powrahchinikanurunwu, potukalunwu ptowru hohneruka wiwejinriya Hoyakalu hetanuya.
Hiyáhoni, noturu, Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu, tenhohne hajeru tokanu hinkakletatshri ptshinko. Klu tshinanu pixa yihapamtanu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hatnu hapote palpokoxyawakapa.
Hoyakalu hayinetene punkakanu hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana, rektunna hiknojikowakpatka.
Woyakalute retwamonrewle tsru potuko rixanwu. Hkotpukyehitanwu ratnuya hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana tenhohne hichpajikatshri pirana.
Hnikotyehitna mapchahawaka hwatshine, hipuktshistsi hwatshinena; rekhixyawakapwu hatnu hapo hapnanuhchinikankaklewatatshri hapo wyapyawakapa. (Seyokatkani Zacarias chikale.)
Waneya mturu João Batista tseruwnatka, hmixkowahchinikanutatka. Popriwaka rawjekanatatka haté rakanhayehitatkana israel-nerune.
Jesus Matuxinri PiranapniWaneya waneklu papko phuru Augusto tshinkaluru towutlewjekanata ptowru tshijne hajeneko rutakhiwakaxikowakapna rutakyahojikowakapna yine.
Hiyáhoni ptowruneka yatka satkaka waleko hipoktshi nwaka hyana rutakhiwakaxikowakpatkana.
Hiyáhoni wale tshinanu José tshinkaluru, Galileia tshijne Nazaré poktshi tshinkaluru, ruchpajya waneya pa poktshi nwaka hya Belém tshinikowaka Judeia tshijneya, phuru Davi-ni matuxyawaka poktshi. Wane hyatka José tshinkaluru klu tshinanu Davi-ni klopichni.
Waneya wane hya rutakhiwakaxikowakpatka Maria tshinkaluroyma, runkaklexikolo seyni kamchíroni wala.
Waneya Belém poktshi rapokatkana waneko tmatuwhenexyatka.
Tmatkakatkalu mitshikananu toturu. Waneya mkatshri sama tpoyitatkalu. Pratshine nikjexyawaka tutakatkalu mturujiji klu tshinanu hikeni hihruko pnu hichpajikatshine hwalerupa.
Hoyakalu Towrene Tenhohne Hajene Jesus Matuxyawaka Pirana Runkakapyawakna Yine PiranapniWale poktshistsi campo-te koxa rawna hinotaprayetshnotatshine.
Satu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru serpikatka wanna nwaka. Waneya Hoyakalu pixkonu hatnu nikotyehitatkana. Waneya hpikpotuthonukatkana.
Seyni hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru wan-tshinna: — Hi hpikanu. Klu tshinanu hetanu nuna nunkajyawakaphi kihler-pirana poyikowlu potukalu pirana, ptowru yinerunupni.
Xawakni hohne potuko, Belém tshinikowaka, Davi-ni poktshi, hmatuxyatka hixa hiwekkakjerupa. Waleni Tsru Hixikatshriwa Cristo.
Xyekni rimaxikolu: mturu matutatshri hikchikanu pratshine nikjexyawaka hikoluhatshri mkatshri sama poyitkalurupa.
Waneya waneklukawa potuko hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeruymatkana pimrine hiwejikalune tenhohne hajene hixolune Hoyakalu towrene. Hoyakalu himalwutatshine. Wla htshinatkana:
— Himalwutkalurni Hoyakalu tenhohne pnut-tennu hajeru. Kihlehchinikanurune yine xye tshijne hajene, rukchikhihlenrene.
Waneya hixolune hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrene tenhohne hajene tenhohne yinixka waneya hinotaprajetatshine wla tshinkaka: — Wuya, Belém poktshi wyanu xawakni. Wetapanru tukwala piran-yehi hakanhatshri Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hinkakjixyatkawu.
Waneya hchireta wane yaletatkana. Waneya wane rukchijyalona Maria tshinkaluro hiyrunu José tshinkalur-koxa. Rukchikluna mturujiji pratshine nikjexyawaka hikoluhatshritka.
Waneya hinotaprajetatshine pohitatkalu mturu pirana tshina hinkaklexyawaka pixka potuko Hoyakalu towrene tenhohne hajene.
Waneya ptowrunek-yine wanestsi hajene xye pirana yijnakotatshine himyeka hinotaprajetatshine hinkakle pirana tshinanu.
Seyni Maria tshinkaluro ptowru piranako timreta tajiya. Tuchinikanretpiranatlu.
Waneya hsatokatkana hinotaprajetatshine. Waneya runkakletatkaluna. Rimalwutluna Hoyakalu ptowru piranako hyijnakotanruna, retanruna, htshinakanaxyawak-potuko rix-hetkatatkaluna.
Mturu Jesus Rutakhiwakaxikolu PiranapniWaneya oito hohne rixinixka mturu jiprojhaptojimtatkatka. Waneya rutakhiwakatka Jesus. Klu tshinanu hma matutkanuklunuwa mturu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru hitakhiwakamtlu.
Hoyakalu Renejikowakatka Jesus Hoyakalupjiya PiranapniWaneya rapokpapkoluxinixka runkajikowakpatkana tsrune powralune rixyawakatkana, Moisés yonreru pirana pixka potuko rixa homkahrexyawakpatkana, waneya ranikatkaluna mturu Jesus Jerusalém poktshi nwaka. Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu renejikowakpatka.
Klu tshinanu yonatkaluru Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu yokanreru pirana wla tshina: “Ptowru mitshikananu matutatshri kanipretko Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakaluya. Hiyáhoni Hoyakalununni.”
Hiyrun-koxa wane hyana henekachalu ranikna hiylatkalurupa hepi kamowane ho hepi motkokoji whenene htshinyawak-potuko yonatkaluru Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu yokanreru.
Simeão Tshinkaluru Chikale PiranapniJerusalém poktshi rawakanata satu jeji Simeão tshinkaluru. Waleni jeji potukalu, kchinikanuru hike mixkatuwa. Israel-nerune hiwekkakatshripa kahwakatshrini. Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru waleymalu.
Waneya runkakkatka Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluruya hi himatshi rupnanu hma metkanu pchiniklu Cristo, Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu yokanrerupa.
Waneya Hoyakalupji hyatka Simeão tshinkaluru. Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru yokanatlu. Waneyatka tsrune hanikatkalu mturu Jesus, Hoyakalupji, Moisés yokanre hkamhiywakapna mturu tshinanu.
Waneya Simeão tshinkaluru kanpukatkalu mturu. Hpoyahnutlu Hoyakalu mturu tshinanu. Wla htshinatka:
— Xawakni, Nutsrukate Hoyakalu, wane potuko pixkakno ptshina hinkaklexyawakpotukno ptowrerno. Hiyáhoni xawakni nunhayi nupniywakpatka kihlehchinikanurukno.
Klu tshinanu netlu, noyhale potuko nexyalu, Hiwekkaklewatatshri pyokanreru.
Xye pkamhaleru ptowru yineru hetanru.
Waneya Jesus hiru, runro himyekahchinikanutatka wane htshinyawakatka Simeão mturu Jesus pirana tshinanu.
Waneya Simeão hihlehchinikanutatkana, waneya wane htshinro Jesus hinro: — Xye mturu Hoyakalu nurrerni, ramtakkajyawakanapna hixolunepni hiyrunu riwekkajyawakna hixolune israel-nerune. Xye mturu Hoyakalu hekhirewleni seyni hixolune yine hapatanru.
Seyni pixa, pyohlotko pihchinikanu hatatjewa yohlolewapi pyohloxiko. Hoyakalu nuretatkalu hixolune yine hchinikanu, hichinikanretjetanru yohimatkaluru, hiphujetatshripa.
Ana Tshinkaluro Hinkaklewaxyawaka PiranapniWane koxa twakanata sato tokantshi hiphujetatshropa, tsrotsoleji potukotkani, hipnahnurutatshro, Ana tshinkaluro. Fanuel tshinkaluru whenni, Aser tshinkaluru klopichni wala. Thanuruwata waneya sete mhale hiknohatka rupnanatka thanurni.
Waneklu papko oitenta e quatro mhalekananro. Hi tuchpaka Hoyakalupjiya. Seyni hohohne, hoyetshno koxa hi tutuk-himalwuretlu Hoyakalu tohajirewleyma hanjihohneruya.
Waneya waneklukawa potuko tapoka. Waneya tyinuwaka poyahnutletlu Hoyakalu mturu tshinanu hiyrun-koxa tyinuwaka hinkakletletlu mturu pirana ptowrunek-yine Jerusalém poktshi hicho towutlexikowakpatka pirana kahwaka hakanhaletatshineya yehiya.
Nazaré Poktshi Nwaka Hsatkapyawakna PiranapniWaneya hnikata kamhalexinixkaluna ptowru yonatkaluru tshinyawaka potuko, Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu yokanre piranaya, José hiyrunu Maria tshinkalune satokanwakatlu Galileia tshijne, hipoktshina nwak-potuko Nazaré tshinikowaka hyana.
Waneya mturu Jesus tseruwna, hmixkowahchinikanukananumtatka. Htsepotka rimatkaleya. Hoyakalu hamotlewleymalu.
Jesus Hoyakalupji Rawyawaka PiranapniPtowru mhaleko Jesus hinro ruru yaper-koxa Jerusalém poktshi hyana poyikowaxikalur-hohne Páscoa tshinkaluru tshinanu.
Waneya doze mhale rapkajinixka Jesus, hyanwakatluna Jerusalém poktshi poyikowaxikalur-hohne ruchinijyawakapluna, rixa hasruhlejexyawakna.
Waneya poyikowaxikalur-hohne pnutetka, Jesus hinro thanur-koxa pantshi nwaka hyamtatkana seyni mturu Jesus hitukatka Jerusalém poktshiko. Seyni wanna tsrune hi himatlu wan-rutujyawakatka.
Wanna tsrune kahwaklu rimotsaneyma rapkatamta Jesus. Hiyáhoni pa hohne yanru hyatkana tsrune. Waneya hyinuwaka hijhaletmakluna mturu Jesus himolene yehiya, rimatletlene yehiy-koxa.
Waneya hma mukchikkanuklunutkaluna mturu Jesus, Jerusalém poktshi nwaka hsatkaphonukna, hyana rujhapyawakapluna.
Waneya map-hohne hiknohinixka rukchikluna Jesus, Hoyakalupji rawakanata. Hoyakalu tokanu hasruklewatatshine hanikajite htuplakanata Jesus. Hyijnakokanatna mturu Jesus, repomhakanatna.
Ptowrunek-yine, Jesus yijnakotatshine himyeka mturu Jesus himatkalnu tshinanu. Hiyrun-koxa rimyekna wane htshin-hihrexyawakna repomhakjene.
Waneya runro thanur-koxa rexinrina Jesus, rimyekna. Waneya runro wan-tshinru: — Noturu, klu tshinanhe wane pixwu? Hi he puru, hit-koxa hijhakanatyi? Wkojwakahchinikanpotukanatatka.
Waneya Jesus hihitna: — Haklu tshinanhe hixa hijhakanatno? Hi he himata nurupjiko nwiywaka?
Seyni hi rimatjemluna klu potu pirana htshinna Jesus.
Waneya Jesus hya runro, ruru yaholeyma. Nazaré poktshi nwaka hyana. Jesus yijnakotna. Seyni Jesus hinro xye pirankaka ptowruka tuchinikanreta tohchinikanuya.
Waneya Jesus tseruwna rimatkalnuya, himaney-koxa. Htseruwna Jesus Hoyakalu hamotlewluya hiyrunu yineru hamotlewley-koxa.
João Batista Tshinkaluru HinkakleQuinze mhale pchinika hpohirewna romano-neru pohire Tibério tshinkaluru. Waneklukananuko koxa Pôncio Pilatos tshinkaluru towutjekanatlu Judeia tshijne. Herodes tshinkaluru towutjekanatlu Galileia tshijne hiyrun-koxa Herodes mole Filipe tshinkaluru Itureia tshinikowaka hiyrunu Traconites tshinikowak-koxa htowutjekanata. Lisânias tshinkaluru towutjekanatlu Abilene tshinikowaka.
Anás hiyrunu Caifás tshinkalune kosekakanatna sacerdote-ne tshinkalune. Waneklu papko Hoyakalu henektokanutlu João tshinkaluru Zacarias tshinkaluru whene, popriwaka rawakanaxini João.
Waneya João tshinkaluru wenu Jordão sreta hyapa wale tshijne psoluka runkaklewtapyawaka Hoyakalu tshinyawaklu. Wla htshina: — Hehchinikanutanu hektunu tshinanu. Wan-hixko h-batiza-xikolupa hiyrunu hektuntshi hiknojiko Hoyakaluya.
Htshinyawak-potuko tokantshi yonatkaluru rixa hakanhaletatka hinamtatshri pirana hinkakletatshrini Isaías-ni tshinkalurni tokanu, wla tshina: “Kahnete poktshiri saplewaxikatshri tokanu: Halpokotanru Tsru Hixikatshriwa hatnu hapote. Hpotukatanru hatnu hapotkaka.
Ptowru hitskata hichyatko. Ptowru mriji kihle tshijiwaka rixko. Katpahapolkaka potukatko. Hiyrun-koxa kaploj-hapolu phayamta rixhapotko.
Ptowru neruka hetanru Hoyakalu kamrure, yine riwekkajyawakapa.”
Hixolune yine yanwakatlu João h-batiza-xikolupna. João wla htshinatkana: — Himnu kamaklewatatshri pixkalunhi. Kathe hinkakatkahi hapnokaxikolupmaka Hoyakalu hapnokaxyapmakhi hasujikatshinhi hixyawakatka?
Hekhixinwa hehchinikanutatshinhi hixyawaka kihleru kamhatshinhi hixyawaka. Hi hyinuwaka wla tshinkakletanu hixkakluko: “Hixni Abraão-ni klopichanwu.” Klu tshinanu nunkakhi Hoyakalu himukata hakanhakakletanru Abraão-ni klopichane xyekaka sotluya!
Klu tshinanu heptshi pixkalutu halpokotatka hahmunkaka hkastajyawakapa haté hitskihi potuko. Klu tshinanu ptowru hahmuna kihle sahiwle mixkatu kaykako. Tshitshmero ruknokko.
Ruhjekakna, wla htshinjekanatna: — Hepi mkatshri himwatshri henekanru hike mimwakatu. Niktshi himwatshri hapikanru hike mnikatu.
Waneya satkaka jijhawenrukleru koxa hapoka. Waneya repomhaluna João. Wla htshinna: — Kasruklewakleru, klu wkamhanu hixa?
Waneya João wan-tshinna: — Hi hijhawenukjixikolu pso pnute hijhanu.
Hiyrun-koxa satkaka soldado hepomhalu: — Ha hixni? Klu wkamhanu? Waneya João wan-tshinna: — Hike yineru tiyirote hkonanu hipokananu. Hi hweyawyehitanuna yinni tiyiro himukata kaylexyawaka tshinanupa. Hiyrun-koxa hpoyahnutjetanru hwenuxikolu henekkoklunpatka.
João, Cristo Pirana Ruphujexyawaka PiranapniYine kahwaklurepotutatkalu. Ptowrunek-yine hihchinikanuyna ruchinikanuwyehitluna João, ho hiwekkaklewatatshri hinatshripaklahe ho hike.
Seyni João wan-tshinna yine ptowruneka: — Hita honhayma n-batiz-jethi. Seyni runanu hita yohnik-kahwakpiratkaluru. Hita hi tsru hixikatshriwano nkochpirojyawakaplu h-sapato-tetslu. Wale batiza-tanhi Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluruyma hiyrun-koxa tshitshmeroyma.
Ruplokapre himyo hwa hkotspalaxyawakaplu hitataji hipatayma. Rapatjetanru hitataji hihruko rutakanru seyni hipata hyoxikanu tshitshmeroya hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatuya.
Hiyrun-koxa hixo pimri piranayma ruykotna yine runkaklewaxini.
Seyni rapatlu phuru Herodes klu tshinanu hhanunrotlo himole Filipe tshinkaluru hnunro, Herodias tshinkaluro. Hiyrun-koxa rapatlu phuru Herodes pimri hixoluru hektutu hkamhaleru tshinanu.
Wane pnutetka phuru Herodes hektut-potu hkamha klu tshinanu preso rutakjixlu João.
Jesus Batiza-xikolu PiranapniWaneya João hali batiz-lexinixkana yine ptowruneka hiyrun-koxa Jesus h-batiza-tatka. Waneya ranjihohnekanaxiniwa Jesus tenhohne kotpukka.
Waneya Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru motkokoji pixka rixa wale hohowaka hapokatshri. Waneya waneylu tokantshi tenhohneyalutu wan-tshinatshri: — Pixni noturyi nalukanruyi, wale poyikowkakno.
Jesus Hitsrukatenni Hiwakkaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus yinuwajinixkalu hkamrure psokaklu trinta mhaletkalu. José whene hikahwakkaluru, José hirutlu Eli.
Eli tshinkaluru hirutlu Matate, Matate tshinkaluru hirutlu Levi, Levi tshinkaluru hirutlu Melqui, Melqui hirutlu Janai, Janai hirutlu José.
José hirutlu Matatias, Matatias hirutlu Amós, Amós hirutlu Naum, Naum hirutlu Esli, Esli hirutlu Nagai,
Nagai hirutlu Maate, Maate hirutlu Matatias, Matatias hirutlu Semei, Semei hirutlu José, José hirutlu Jodá,
Jodá hirutlu Joanã, Joanã hirutlu Resa, Resa hirutlu Zorobabel, Zorobabel hirutlu Salatiel, Salatiel hirutlu Neri,
Neri hirutlu Melqui, Melqui hirutlu Adi, Adi hirutlu Cosã, Cosã hirutlu Elmadã, Elmadã hirutlu Er,
Er hirutlu Josué, Josué hirutlu Eliézer, Eliézer hirutlu Jorim, Jorim hirutlu Matate, Matate hirutlu Levi,
Levi hirutlu Simeão, Simeão hirutlu Judá, Judá hirutlu Jonã, Jonã hirutlu Eliaquim,
Eliaquim hirutlu Meleá, Meleá hirutlu Mená, Mená hirutlu Matatá, Matatá hirutlu Natã, Natã hirutlu Davi,
Davi hirutlu Jessé, Jessé hirutlu Obede, Obede hirutlu Boaz, Boaz hirutlu Sala, Sala hirutlu Nasom,
Nasom hirutlu Aminadabe, Aminadabe hirutlu Admim, Admim hirutlu Arni, Arni hirutlu Esrom, Esrom hirutlu Peres, Peres hirutlu Judá,
Judá hirutlu Jacó, Jacó hirutlu Isaque, Isaque hirutlu Abraão, Abraão hirutlu Tera, Tera hirutlu Naor,
Naor hirutlu Serugue, Serugue hirutlu Reú, Reú hirutlu Pelegue, Pelegue hirutlu Éber, Éber hirutlu Selá,
Selá hirutlu Cainã, Cainã hirutlu Arfaxade, Arfaxade hirutlu Sem, Sem hirutlu Noé, Noé hirutlu Lameque,
Lameque hirutlu Metusalém, Metusalém hirutlu Enoque, Enoque hirutlu Jarede, Jarede hirutlu Maalalel, Maalalel hirutlu Cainã,
Cainã hirutlu Enos, Enos hirutlu Sete, Sete hirutlu Adão, Adão Hoyakalu whenni.
Jesus Yohnixikolu PiranapniJesus Jordão wenne rali hichpaklexinixka, katsepoyatkalu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru. Waneya Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hanikkotlu Jesus kahnete poktshiri hyiywakpatka.
Waneya tsru kamtshi Satanás wan-tshinru: — Hoyakalu whene pixinipakni, ptowutanru xye sotlukaka pão rixinwa.
Seyni Jesus hihitlu: — Hi he Hoyakalu tokanu potukalu yonatkaluru wan-tshina: Yine hi pão mixkonu tsonu riwejyana seyni ptowruka wane htshintokanuta Hoyakalu: “Hoyakalu tokanu tshinanu riwekanu yineru.”
Waneya tsru kamtshi Satanás hanikatkalu Jesus satu himriji tenolu, pchinhohnejiji rekhitlu Jesus ptowruka tshijnekaka pohirewaxyawaka.
Waneya tsru kamtshi Satanás wan-tshina: — Xye ptowrukamka nenekanyi ptowuxyawaklu, npohirewnale koxamka pixanpatka. Klu tshinanu xye ptowruka nenekka hiyáhoni numukata henekletanru katukta naluk-henekletanu.
Xyekaka ptowruka pixanpatkani pyoptsojityehixinipno, pimalwuxinipno.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru: — Wane htshina hinkakleta Hoyakalu tokanu potukalu yonatkaluru: “Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu tsonu himalwutanu hiyrun-koxa wale tsonu pomkahitanu.”
Waneya wane pnutetka tsru kamtshi haniklu Jesus Jerusalém poktshi waneya Hoyakalupji hohwaka hwatshri tenoptajiru rimatskotlu Jesus. Waneya wane htshinru: — Hoyakalu whene pixinipakni hewi tenowaka puknojinwa,
klu tshinanu Hoyakalu tokanu potukalu yonatkaluru wan-tshina: “Hoyakalu towutna htowrene hiwejikalune tenhohne hajene hinoxyawakapyi.”
Hiyrun-koxa: “Himyoymana ruchatkapanyina, pma muphajixixyawakanupa sotlu hoho.”
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru: — Seyni Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru wan-tshina: “Hi pyahotaletanru Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu Poyakalute.”
Waneya rali yahotaletletlu Jesus xye yahotaletluya psoluka, tsru kamtshi Satanás hichomtlu. Waneya pchinhohne retachatlu.
Jesus Yinuwaka Kamrurewlexyawaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus satokanwakatlu Galileia tshijne nwaka. Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru himukatle himotsatlu. Jesus pirana wale tshijne psoluka rupalpiranyehita.
Rasruklewjekanata wanna hanjihohnewakapjikakaya. Ptowruneka himalwutlu.
Nazaré Poktshi Rawyawaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus htseruwniywaka poktshi Nazaré tshinikowaka hya. Rixjexyawaka sábado hohne hanjihohnewakapji hjihloka. Waneko hyopkaka rethaxyawakaplu Hoyakalu tokanu potukalu yonatkaluru.
Waneya renekka papel-mta Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshrini Isaías-ni yonre steno. Hkoprakatkalo. Rukchiklu wane htshin-yonhaxyawaka:
“Hita rawa Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru Hnuretno nunkaklexyawakaplu Kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana hike mwikane yehiya Runkaklewjixno ruchoxikowakapna yine pirana kachitkalune tshinanu hiyrun-koxa himrekhale pirana nunkajyawakna mayhalene, ruchotkona salewnatshine,
nunkaklexyawak-koxlu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu rayinetene riwekkajinripatka mhale pirana.”
Waneya Jesus hichyatatkalo papel-mta waneya reneklu hanjihohnewakapji kamrurewaxikatshri. Waneya htuplatatka. Ptowrunek-yine hanjihohnewakapji hwakanatatshine yopukhapotutlu.
Waneya hyinuwaka wan-tshinretna: — Xawakni hohne potuko rakanhatka xye tokantshi yonatkaluru hjemyawaka pixka.
Ptowru neruka halikakni htshinruna Jesus, rukchikhihlenutluna kihleru tokantshi Jesus hinkajyatkana. Wla htshinjekanatluna: — Hi he José tshinkaluru whenni wale?
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinna: — Hix-hetko ptowrunekhi xye yapkaklu pirana htshinanno: “Kpinrewakleru, putskalajinwa.” Wla kox-hetko htshinanno: “Cafarnaum poktshi pkamhakanaxinri hewi koxa, ptshijne potuko, pkamhinixnaklu.”
Wane htshin-koxa Jesus: — Halikaka wane ntshinhi. Hi satukna muphujewnakatuwa pirana hinkakletatshri hikchikhihlenutko waleko htshijneya.
Hjemanru: Mitshikananu hinamtatshri pirana hinkakletatshri Elias-ni tshinkaluru klu papko rawna hipnahnurutatshrone Israel tshijneya. Waneklu papko hi rinnewjekanata Israel tshijneya mapa mhale hiyrunu seis ksuru pchinika. Waneya tsru natshi potuko retna wale tshijne hajene.
Wanepnawaka hi satokna Israel tshijne hajero hipnahnurutatshro nwaka hyokanatka Elias-ni Hoyakalu tshinanuya. Seyni halikaka Sarepta tshinikowaka, Sidom tshijne hwatshri poktshi hajero hipnahnurutatshro tsonu Elias tyokananwakatka.
Hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshrini Eliseu-ni tshinkaluru klu papko koxa yeyixlu mjemtshinotkotu himwatshine híxona Israel tshijneya seyni hi satuknako wanna hitskalakka waneklu. Naamã-ni tshinkalurni, Sírio-neru tsonupka hitskalakkatka waneklu papko.
Waneya xye pirana hyijnakoxinixkana hanjihohnewakapji hwakanatatshine ramewpotutna.
Waneya hpalnamtna. Poktshi maleka sreta ranikluna hipokananu. Wale poktshi maleka tenopjitawaka potuko ranikluna hitskata hyotkajyawakapluna.
Seyni hixolune yine hanikajiteko yapamta. Hyatka.
Kkamtshiteru PiranapniWaneya Jesus jihlokamtlu Cafarnaum poktshi Galileia tshijne poktshite. Waneya sábado hohne rasruklewjeta hanjihohnewakapjiya.
Waneya kkamtshiteru koxa wane hwakanata hanjihohnewakapji. Waneya hsaplewata kkamtshiteru. Wla htshin-sapleta:
— Ya! Kluhe pixannatkawu, Jesus Nazaré hajeru? Puna pumtukapyawakapwuhe? Nimatyi katyi pixa: Potukalyi Hoyakalyi!
Seyni Jesus hi hinanchitlu. Waneya wane htshina: — Potshkepyi. Puchpakanutka wale maneya! Waneya kamtshi wanna hanikajite yawnakaklu kkamtshiteru. Waneya ruchpakamxyalu. Hi rumtukamtlu jeji.
Waneya ptowrunek-yine himyeka. Hiyáhoni repomhakakna, wane htshinna: — Klunerni xye tokantshikaka? Xye jeji tsru hitakkaluruyma hiyrun-koxa tsru himukatluyma kamtshi ruchpakjixa. Hiyrunu hjemluna wale kamtshine htshinyawakna.
Waneya hpohiwata Jesus psol-tshijne potuko wale tshijneya.
Pedro Himajiro Rutskalajyawaka Jesus PiranapniWaneya hanjihohnewakapjiya ruchpakamxinixka Jesus Simão Pedro tshinkalurupji hjihloka. Simão himajiro patshwapotuta waneya wala tshinanu ranjitluna.
Waneya walastsi hyopkaka. Waneya ruchpakjixlu patshwalu. Tutuk-patshwalemtatka. Waneya waneklukawa tyotunotatka waneya tyomhatna.
Waneya kayi rixinixka rimxijinixka tkatshi yeyixatshine ranikanwakatluna hiyrun-koxa ptowru hixatshri hahijewaktshi himwatshine. Waneya wanna ptowruneka himyo rutakhohota, rutskalakna.
Kamtshine koxa hixolune yineyma hwakanatatshine hichpakamtatka, hsaplewamtatkana. Wla htshin-saplemtna: — Pixni Cristo-yi, Hoyakalu Whenyi! Seyni Jesus hi hitshi yanumsaletna kamtshine klu tshinanu rimathetluna Cristo rixyawaka.
Jesus Yinuwaka Hinkaklewlexyawaka PiranapniWaneya rumrekpiraxinixka, poktshi ruchpakamxyatka Jesus. Potshkewaka nwaka hyatka. Waneya yine hixolune yinuwaka hijhaletlu. Hyanwakatluna. Waneya rukchijinixkaluna htshipetmakluna wanna yehi hma muchpajyawakanupa.
Seyni Jesus wan-tshinna: — Nujhalu nunkaklewaxyawak-koxa pimri poktshikakaya, Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hinatshripa pirana. Klu tshinanu wale tshinanukni nuna.
Hiyáhoni runkaklewakananumta hanjihohnewakapjikakaya Judeia tshijne hajerkakaya.
Jesus Nuretna Satkaka Rikamrurewatjenepa PiranapniWaneya wla rixa Jesus. Hipowha Genesaré wnahlu rawakanata Jesus. Ripxakjekanaxyawakluna yine Hoyakalu tokanu hjemyawakna.
Waneya hepi kanawa reta, hipowha wnaha rawakanatna. Seyni kkanawaterune mariskakanatatshine hichotlo hkanawatna klu tshinanu h-tarrafa-tkakna rerokakanatna hipowha wnahaya.
Hiyáhoni sato kanawa hpokowna Jesus, Simão tshinkaluru kanawate. Waneya Jesus hanjitlu Simão hanikajhayaka ranjiywaklu. Waneya kanawa htuplata waneya hyinuwaka hasrukletna yine hixolune.
Waneya rali hinkaklewlexinixka, Simão htowuta, wla htshina: — Kanawa xako tenohawaka panikanu. Waneya hiknok-tarrafa-tetanu chima hkachixyawakapa.
Seyni Simão wan-tshinru: — Kasruklewakleru, psol-yetshnokmaka wmariskata seyni hike wkachita. Seyni pixa tokanu tshinanu, tarraf-kaka nuknokanu.
Waneya rali wan-hixletatkana, hix-potu chima hkachitna. Haté ruskatana h-tarrafa-tkaknina.
Waneya repirenna rutsejrihjeyehitna sato kanawa hwakanatatshine, repixyawakapna. Runna. Waneya hepi kanawa htsepotna chima haté rimxikpiratna kanawane.
Waneya xye rexinixka Simão Pedro, hyoptsojityehitlu Jesus. Waneya wane htshinru: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa hit-yehi pasujini klu tshinanu hitni jejno hektuntshi hwalerno.
Klu tshinanu Simão hiyrunu pimrin-koxa himyekpotuta hixo chima hkachitanruna tshinanu.
Tiago hiyrunu João tshinkalune, Zebedeu tshinkaluru whenen-koxa, Simão tshinkaluru hepirene himyekpotuta. Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru Simão: — Hi ppikanu. Xawakni yine kmariskahohoklerunpatkahi.
Waneya tshiji hyosropkaklona hkanawatkakna. Ptowruko ruknokamtatkana waneya Jesus romkahitatkana.
Jesus Hitskalajyawaklu Hijirohitutatshri PiranapniWaneya pa katatnaka Jesus pa poktshi hwakanatatka waneylu satu jeji hijirohitutatshri hallikanatatshri. Waneya Jesus rexiniklunu hyoptsojityehitlu Jesus tshiji rutspakhojita waneya Jesus ranjita: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, palujinipa pumukata hitskalakletno.
Waneya Jesus homyokanwakatlu, hkamruklu. Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru: — Hehe, naluklu. Putskalhatka. Waneya waneklukawa potuko rujirhitle ramhiyatka, rutskalhatka.
Waneya Jesus hijretlu wla htshinru: — Petanu. Hike punkakanu seyni pyanutka. Sacerdote pekhimantapinwa putskalhinrixka. Waneya panikanru henekachalu henekawaka nwaka Moisés-ni yonreru tshinyawaka pixka pimrine himaxyawakaplu putskalhiywakatka.
Seyni pnute hya kopalpiranretlu. Hiyáhoni hixolune yine hinanwakatlu Jesus tokanu hjemyawakna hiyrun-koxa hyeyixlena rutskalajyawakapa.
Seyni Jesus kahnete sputa hya potshkewaka. Waneya wane ranjihohnexya.
Jesus Hiktehatshri Hitskalajyawaka PiranapniWaneya pa hohnetnaka Jesus hasrukakanatna. Wane koxa rawakanata satkaka fariseu hiyrun-koxa satkaka yonawahlo yonha kyimakleru Jesus-stsi htuplakanatna. Ptowru poktshi pejnu runyatkana Galileia tshijneya hiyrun-koxa Judeia tshijne hajeneya. Jerusalém poktshi koxa runyatkana. Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu himukatle Jesus-ymalu ptowru hahijewaktshi rutskalajyawaka.
Seyni hixolune yine tshinanu hi rumukata hijihlokletluna hiktehatshri. Hiyahokni ranikluna pantshi hoho hwakwatatshri. Hjihmikakwatluna waneya wane swa hkosputajyaluna yoklutsayma hiktehatshri hijeko hikoluhamtatshri, hixolune yine hanikajite Jesus hojistsi rutspakluna.
Waneya Jesus hexinri wanna halixle, wane htshinru hiktehatshri: — Nimatletleru, pektunu puknojikatka.
Waneya fariseu-ne hiyrun-koxa kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine yinuwaka hijhahchinikanretna waneya wla htshinatkana: — Katnihe xye jeji hektuwaka htshinanwakatlu Hoyakalu? Katu tsonhe himukata hiknokhektunutlu yineru? Satupkalu Hoyakalu tsonu.
Seyni Jesus himathetahchinikanutna hiyáhoni ruhitna, wane htshinatkana: — Klu tshinanhe wan-hixahchinikanuta xyekaka hektutu hichinikanrethajixyawaka?
Hanupothe kihle tshinko? Wla htshinikowaka hiktehatshri: “Pektunu puknojikatka”, ho wla htshinikowaka: “Pyotunotanu, pyanutka”?
Seyni himatjempotuxyawakaplu Jeji Whene tshinkaluru hitakkalurutkani xye tshijiya ruknokhektunuxyawakapna yine hiyáhoni wla ntshinanru hiktehatshri: — Pixa wane ntshinyi: Pyotunotanu, pkochtshekjekomtanu pyanutka pipji.
Waneya waneklukawa hyotunomtatka, hkochtshekjekomtatka ptowruneko hetanu. Hipji nwaka hyatka. Rimalwumtlu Hoyakalu.
Ptowruneka tsru himyeklu rixna. Tsru pikluyma rimalwutluna Hoyakalu. Wane htshinkakna: — Kluneru pixkalutu weta xawakni?
Jesus Tshanixyawaklu Levi PiranapniWaneya wane pnute ruchpakamta Jesus, retlu satu jijhawenrukleru, Levi tshinkaluru. Htuplakanata tuplawaka hwenuxikolu hyoptoxyawakapa. Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru: — Pomkahitanno.
Waneya ptowruka ruknokachata, hpalnamtatka waneya romkahitlu Jesus.
Jesus Hektuneyma Nijyawaka PiranapniWaneyakni Levi tshinkaluru tsru niklu hkamhiylu Jesus, waleko hipjiya. Wane rawakanatna hixolune jijhawenruklerune, pimrin-koxa wannayma tuplakanatatshine nikawakakwa yehi.
Seyni fariseu-ne hiyrun-koxa kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine kahemhayehitna Jesus hasruklene. Wla htshinna: — Kluneru tshinanhe wannayma hnika, rura wanna jijhawenruklerune, hektuneyma?
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinna: — Pomtalune hi haluklu kpinrewakleru seyni katshinomtalu haluklu.
Klu tshinanu hi nuna ntshanixyawakapna kihlerune seyni hektune ntshanixyawaka rehchinikanuxyawakapna.
Hix-hohne Mnikkatu PiranapniWaneya satkaka yineru wan-tshinru Jesus: — Haklu tshinanhe João Batista hasruklene hohajirewjeta, ranjihohnejet-koxna hiyrunu fariseu-ne hasruklene waneko pixka rixna seyni pasruklene nika, rurna?
Waneya wane htshinatkana: — Rumukata natshretnahe hnunrowlu hetatshine hnunrowatatshriymalune? Hike.
Seyni rapokhohnexinpatka hnunrowpiratatshri hixolune hetanu hkochpakkoklunpatka. Waneklu papko halikaka rohajirewatanutkana wanna.
Waneya satu yapkaklu pirana runkakkoxna, wla htshinatka: — Hi kihle hipxatkolu mkatshri hitsruka herotu samayma. Wan-rixkoklunu herotu sama hiskakkakanunru tsrutsolejipni. Hiyrun-koxa hi pixkakakluni tsrutsoleji herotu samayma.
Hi kihle tsrutsoleji mapa hitakhatkolo vinho-ha hekamhakolha. Wan-rixkoklunutka vinho-ha hipchekkakanunru sac-kakapni. Tuyokhatanuna vinho-hapni waneya sac-kaka koxapni salewnanuna.
Seyni vinho-ha herotu, saco herotu tutakhatka.
Hiyrun-koxa mitshikawlurha hiratshritka hi hannahatlo herotha. Klu tshinanu wane htshinna: “Mitshikawlurha halikaka kihlepotu.”
Jesus Hapnanuxikalur-hohne Yohnik-hijhakalurniWaneya wan-rixa. Hsana hyapakanata Jesus hapnanuxikalur-hohne. Waneya Jesus hasruklene jimlakahawamtlu hitakluhawa. Himyoyna hjijpekamtluna. Hnikamtluna.
Waneya pimrine fariseu-ne wan-tshinru: — Haklu tshinanhe wan-rixna hapnanuxikalur-hohne hinanchitkalur-hohne?
Waneya Jesus hihitna, wane htshinna: — Hikeklu hohnehe het-yonhatlu Davi-ni pirana, hnatshixinni waleni hiyrun-koxa waleymalune?
Hanu rixa jihlokletlu mitshi Hoyakalupji waneya Davi-ni niklu pão-kaka Hoyakalu henekachalurupa hiyrunu rimotsatjene koxa reneklu hnijyawakapluna? Wale hinanchitkaluru hnikni. Sacerdote-ne tsonu himukata nikletanru hnikni.
Jesus wan-tshin-koxa: — Hiyáhoni Jeji Whene hapnanuxikalur-hohne yohnik-himukatatshrini.
Jesus Hitskalajinri Hiprihamyotatshri PiranapniWaneya wan-rixa satu hapnanuxikalur-hohnepatnaka hanjihohnewakapji hjihlokatnaka. Wane rasruklewakanaxya. Wane rawakanata satu jeji hiprihamyotatshri hpotuklemyo.
Waneya satkaka wane hwakanatatshine koxa fariseu-ne hiyrun-koxa pimrine kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine ruslahpotukanatluna Jesus ho hapnanuxikalur-hohnerhe rutskalaklewatanu ho hike.
Seyni rimatatka Jesus klu ruchinikanretna. Hiyáhoni wale tshinanu wla htshinatkalu jeji hiprihamyotatshri: — Pyopkakanutshi, hewi hixa hanikajiteya potuko pyotunoxini, — htshinru. Waneya hpalnatka jeji, hyotunotatka.
Waneya Jesus heknojtayehitmakna wanna ptowruneka. Waneya wane pnutetka wla htshinatkalu jeji: — Pyosurukkanotanu. Waneya hyosurukkanotatka, ruhlewamyotatka.
Waneya hjihekanuwpotutatkana. Hiyáhoni rujhahchinikanutatkana wannakakluko hanu rixa himukata hikolukletluna Jesus.
Jesus Nurexyawakna Rasruklenepa PiranapniWaneya waneklu papko Jesus himriji hkankatka ranjihohnexyawakapa. Waneya psol-yetshnoko waneko ranjixyalu Hoyakalu.
Waneya rumrejinixka hohi htomhana rasruklene hixolune. Waneya doze hnuretatka hixolune tskalaya. Nyi doze jejine rutakhiwakatkana ‘nuretkalune’.
Hhiwaknina: Simão, wale rutakhiwakata Pedro; André, Pedro mole; Tiago, João, Filipe, Bartolomeu;
Mateus, Tomé, Tiago, Alfeu tshinkaluru whene; Simão honukla Israel tshijne haluka mixkowkakletatshri;
Judas, Tiago tshinkaluru whene; Judas Iscariotes tshinkaluru, Jesus kamnitjerupa.
Jesus Hinkaklewjeta Hiyrun-koxa Rutskalaklewjexyawaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus himriji hserpikatka rasrukleneyma waneya rutukamta kihlemta tshijiwaka pimrine hixolune rasrukleneyma. Hixolune yine hwakanata. Wannani Judeia tshijne hajene, Jerusalém poktshi hajen-koxa, hiyrun-koxa Tiro poktshi hajene hiyrun-koxa Sidom poktshi hajene mar powhastsi poktshikaka hwatshrikaka.
Runna rutskalajikowakapna ptowru hyeyixleyna hiyrun-koxa Jesus tokanu hjemyawakapna. Run-koxna kkamtshiterune. Rutskalakanna wanna ptowruneka.
Ptowruneka haluka yotnekletmaklu Jesus klu tshinanu pixkontshi hichpaka wale yehiya. Ptowrunek-yine Jesus yotnekatshri hitskalhatka.
Poyikowlu PiranapniWaneya Jesus yopukhatna rasruklene waneya wla htshinatka: — Hixa hike mwikanhi seyni poyikpotukhi. Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hixanutkani.
— Poyikowatatshinhi yahmaklu xye papko natshitatshinmakhi klu tshinanu jinan-potpákohi. — Poyikowatatshinhi yahmaklu xye papko tshiyahatatshinephi klu tshinanu hitsolhiwatatshinephi.
— Poyikowatatshinhi yahmaklu xye papko hahnanutkalunhi, malukkonhi heyikkalunhi hiyrun-koxa ptowru hektutu tshinanwakatkalunhi klu tshinanu homkahitlu Cristo, Jeji Whene tshinikatshriwa.
Ppoyikowpotutanu, puptetanu poyikowluyma rakanhinipa xyekaka pejnu klu tshinanu tsru pumlujikolu pimretahnaputka tenhohneya. Klu tshinanu wane mitshi rixkana Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine rutsrukatenniyna.
Wamonuwlu Piranapni— Seyni wamonuwatatshinenapni hixa phurunephi xye papko hajenepni klu tshinanu xawakni tsonu kihle hiweklenhi!
— Ha hixa ptowruka himwatshinhi, hnatshitanuna. — Kwamonurunhi hixa xawakni hitsolhiwatatshine klu tshinanu xekoyaka hwamonuwatanu, htshiyahatanu!
— Kwamonurunpotukni kihle piranyehiru htshinanwakatanune klu tshinanu waneko pixka htshinanwakjekanatkana Hoyakalu tokanu yahole hinkakletatshine, rutsrukatenniyna!
Hi Hahnanutanna Hmukchikhihlenutjene Piranapni— Seyni wla ntshinhi hixa njemjenhi: Hi hahnanutanru hahnanutjeru. Kihlewaka hkamhinna hahnanutjene.
Kihlewaka hanjiyehitanna hipuktshi hanjiyehitjene. Hiyrun-koxa hanjihohneyehitanna hyotnetjene.
Satu yineru himpakhojixinipyi, pa sreta hoji koxa pumpakjixachatanu. Capa pkonjeru pimkal-koxa hi ptshipexinri.
Peneklewatanu klunerukta panjitka, katuktako hanjixinri. Hiyrun-koxa pimwaleru konkoklunu hi psatkakjixanru.
Hanukta paluk-hixletko yine tshinanuya, waneko pixka pixanna wanna.
Pimrine Hichinijyawaka Piranapni— Puchinikjene tsonu pamoxinipa, ha pixa kluneru kihlerhe pkamhajeta kihleru pkahwaka yoptolexnawakwa Hoyakalu yehiya? Hi he waneko pixka rix-koxna hektune?
Hiyrun-koxa kihleru hixinipna kihleru hkamhayehitjene tsonu, ha hixa, kluneru kihlerhe hkamhajeta kihleru hkahwaka yoptolexnawakwa Hoyakalu yehiya? Hi he waneko pixka rix-koxna hektune?
Hiyrun-koxa ksatkaka tiyirotlewaklerune tsonu penektiyirotexinipa klu hikoluklehe pimalwutko? Klu tshinanu hektunkakluko koxa tiyiro renekkakjetna hpoyaho satkaklexyawakna pso.
Seyni hichinikanna hmukchikhihlenutjene. Kihleru hkamhinna, henekan-koxna wanna mwenutaklene. Waneya peneklewaxya hapnutpatka tsru potpako. Tsru Potuko Tenhohne hajeru whenenephi. Klu tshinanu kchinikanurni Hoyakalu poyahnu mtshinaklene tshinanu hiyrun-koxa hektutu kamhatshine tshinanu.
Kchinikanurunephi, Hirtshi Hoyakalu pixka kchinikanurni hixa tshinanu.
Hma Jihyehixyawakanuplu Satu Yineru Piranapni— Hi hjihyehirewatanu waneya Hoyakalu koxa hi hikolukanuwnakakanhi hixa. Hi hikolukanuwjixanru satu waneya hix-koxa hi hikolukanuwnakakko. Hi hichinikanru rektunna waneya hix-koxa hi hichinikanret-hektunutko.
Heneklewachatanu pso hix-koxa henekachatko wane pso. Waneya wan-hixatshinephi tsru potuko yoptotatshinephi, tsru potuko. Hakot-haniklexyawaka pso nenekanhi hkanpuhanru. Klu tshinanu yahotapi hixa hyahotapre, walako hyahoxika.
Hasrukkaluru hi rasrukjeru yohnik-hijhakalurni seyni rasrujikolu ptowruko riknohinixka, rasrukjeru pixkako rixanutka.
— Haklu tshinanhe petlu kapopejiru mtserutu pimole yhale hwatshri seyni piyhale hwatshri kaknalu psolutu hi pimatheta?
Hanhe pumukata wan-tshinretlu pimole: “Nomole, hitatshi pitshitanu kapopejiru piyhale hwatshri nkochpajyawakapa”, pma mimathetkanuklunru piyhale hwakanatatshri? Hixachatatshrini wan-hixatshri! Mitshikananhapka puknokanrutshi kaknalu piyhale hajeru. Waneyapa petpotutanutkalu pkochpajyaplu pimole yhale hwatshri kapopejiru.
Hahmuna Hiyrunu Hisahi Hyapkakleta Jesus— Hahmuna kihleru hi hektu sahiplu. Hiyrun-koxa hahmuna hektutu hi kihle sahiplu.
Klu tshinanu ptowru hixatshri hahmuna pejnu rimathetka hisahi tshinanu, ho kihle sahruhe ho hektutra. Klu tshinanu hi kawchipiri chehi hjijrujiko figo sahi. Hiyrun-koxa hi kawchipiri chehi hjijrujiko uva-ji.
Waneko pixka rixa yineru. Yineru kihleru raj-koxa rimrexyalu kihleru, kihlekakalu kochpakjexikowakaya. Yineru hektutu hichinikanretatshri, rimretawakle hektutu, hektutkaka wane hkochpakjexya. Namtshi yanumaxyalu hix-potu raji hajeru.
Sotlu Hoho ho Ksatu Hohowaka Panawaxikatshri Piranapni— Klu tshinanhe hixa wan-tshinno Nutsrukate, Nutsrukate, seyni hi hkamhajetlu ntokanu, ntshinyawakhi?
Hita nwaka hinatshri, hita ntokanu yijnakotatshri, nuykole kamhatshri nekhitanhi hanu rixanu wan-hixatshri.
Wan-hixatshri honra jeji kamhapjitatshri pixkalutni. Tshiji hjitota. Teno rixlu. Waneya sotlumta hoho potuko ripxakkaklu pantshi. Rapohamxinixka wenu, hyochkihamta. Seyni hi rumukata kowchiretlu klu tshinanu sotlu hoho hkamhika pantshi.
Seyni ntokanu yijnakochatatshri, hektuwaka kamhatshri, katuktako mchiko wakan-tshiji panawaxikatshri pixkalutu, mpoyehitkotupji kamhatshrini. Hyochkihamta honha. Waneyakni hyawnamtanatka pantshini. Tsru yawnalu rixana walepjini.
Jesus Hitskalajyawaklu Soldado Chefe-te Towreru PiranapniWaneya rali wan-tshinretna yine xye pirana ptowruka Jesus, Cafarnaum poktshi nwaka hyatka.
Wanekananru satu soldado-ne pohire. Htowreru ramotanru potu yeyixa. Rupnakastsitkani.
Waneya hjempiranyehixiniplu Jesus, satkaka tsrukakalune judeu-ne hyokanata Jesus nwaka. Jesus htshanixakjixna runanwakaxiniplu rutskalajyawakaplu htowreru.
Waneya hyanwakatluna Jesus, htshanixpotutluna wane hyiywakapa. Wane htshinatkana: — Pujhalu wane pyiywaka klu tshinanu xye jeji hijhalu repixikowaka.
Klu tshinanu winerune retwamonpotuta. Haté satu hanjihohnewakapji hkamhiyatkawu.
Waneya Jesus himotsatna. Seyni hi howukatkalu pantshi, soldado-ne pohire yokanatna satkaka rimatletlene Jesus nwaka wla htshinakjixna: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, hi pkojwajinwa. Klu tshinanu hike kochpakatshrino nopji potuko pjihlojyawakapa.
Hiyrun-koxa hi tsru hixikatshriwano pixa niynumsaxyawaka. Seyni pyanumanwakachatanru, ntowreru hitskalhanu.
Klu tshinanu hit-koxa k-chefe-tno, towutkalurno. Wanepnawaka soldado-ne ntowuta. Satu wane ntshina, “pyanutka”, hiyáhoni hya. Satutnaka wane ntshinru, “puna”, hiyáhoni runanwakatno. Ntowreru koxa wane ntshininri, “xye pkamhanu”, hkamhanru.
Waneya xye pirana hjemini Jesus, rimyeka. Waneya ruprotakyehitatkana hixolune yine romkahikanatjene. Wane htshinatkana: — Halikaka wane ntshinhi israel-nerune tskalaya hi nexyalu xye pixkalutu halixlu.
Waneya pantshi hsatojinixkana yokanatkalune, retluna rutskalhatka towretshri.
Hipnahnurutatshro Whene Riwekkajyawaka Jesus PiranapniWaneya pa hohnepka hiknohatka waneya Jesus pa poktshi hjihlokatnaka Naim tshinikowaka. Rasruklene hiyrun-koxa hixolune yine himotsamtlu.
Hiyáhoni poktshi jihlokawakle hiphaptotestsi rapokamtatkana, ruchpakakananumtna yomletshi nwaka yatshine. Hipnatshri ranikamtna. Waleni satupkalutnixkani toturni. Hipnahnurutatshroni wala. Hixolune yine poktshi hajene himotsamtlo.
Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus hexinixkalo, retwamonpotutlo. Waneya wane htshinatkalo: — Hi ptshiyahatanu.
Waneya rapokastsitlu. Hkamruklu rukoluhamxyawakakwa hwatshri. Waneya htunwatna hipnatshri hanikakanatatshine. Waneya wane htshinru hipnatshri: — Makluji, pixa wane ntshina: Pyotunotanu!
Waneya htuplata hipnapatshritka. Hyinuwaka yanumleta. Waneya runro renekka.
Waneyakni ptowru neruka pikatka, rimalwutluna Hoyakalu. Wla htshinatkana: — Tsru jinkaklewakleru rakanhayehikakatkawu Hoyakalu. Runa Hoyakalu hayinetene ruchokjixyawakapa.
Waneya hpohiwata Jesus kamhaleru pirana Judeia tshijne psoluka hiyrun-koxa pimri tshijnekakaya wanestsi hwatshrikaka.
João Yokanrene Jesus Nwaka Hyiywakna PiranapniWaneya João Batista runkakna rasruklene xye pirana ptowruka. Waneya htomhana hepi.
Hyokanatna Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus nwaka repomhiywakapluna: “Pixakatkalhe hinatshripyi tshinkaluryi ho satuklatshi wkahwakanu?”
Waneklu papko Jesus hixolune yine yeyixatshine, hahijewnalkaka rutskalaka hiyrun-koxa kkamtshiterune rakajya. Hixolune mayhalene retkak-koxa.
Waneya ruhitatkana. Wla htshinatkana João Batista yokanrene: — Hajewa. Hinkakapanru João xye hetanrukaka hiyrun-koxa hyijnakotanrukaka. Mayhalenekananu hetatka. Myankanekananu yanatka. Hijirhitukanatatshine hitskalhatka. Majnakonekananu jema. Hipnatshine hiwekkakka. Kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana runkakkatkana hike mwikane.
Poyikowatatshine hita tshinanu mutspetkanepa!
Jesus Hiphujtaxinri João Batista PiranaWaneya hyinixkana João yokanrene, Jesus yinuwaka João pirana hepomhaletna yine, wane htshina: — Kluhe haluk-hetletapa? Kaptsheru kanniphalu kowchirerrahe hetapa?
Klunerhe hetapa? Satu jeji kihleru mkatshri hitakatshrirhe hetapa? Hetanu kihleru mkatshri hitakjetatshine, kihle hiweklerunni, phurupjikaka rawna wan-hixatshine.
Seyni kluhe mitshi haluk-hetletapa? Satu Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshrirhe hetapa? Hehe, wane ntshinhi, Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshinni yohnik-hijhakaluru hetpatka.
Klu tshinanu João yonpiranyehitkalurni: “Hewitkalu nyokanreru, hinkaklewatatshri,” htshina Hoyakalu. “Wale nyokanatanu pixa hnapu. Ralpokohnapuxyawakaplu patnu hapote.”
Klu tshinanu wane ntshinhi João Batista ptowru matutatshri yohnik-hijhakalurumkani. Wanepnawaka mujhakon-potu Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hwatshine, João yohnik-hijhakalunetkani wanna.
Waneya jijhawenruklerune hiyrun-koxa ptowrunek-yine xye pirana yijnakotatshine Potukalu htshinruna Hoyakalu klu tshinanu h-batiza-tkana João batiz-leya.
Seyni fariseu-ne hiyrun-koxa Moisés yonreru pirana himatpotutatshine hi ralukluna João batiza-xyawakna. Hiyáhoni ruknokluna Hoyakalu halujyawaka ruchinikanreta heneklexikolmakna.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshina: — Kluneru pirana nyapkakletanna xye klu papko hwatshine? Kluneru pixka rixna?
Wanna hetko mturune niktshi hanjijexikowakaswa tuplajetatshine pixka rixna. Pa sreta tuplatatshine wan-tshinna pa sreta tuplatatshine: “Wtumlejyehithi poyikowlu hima seyni hi hahsat-hixa. Kwamonuru himamka wchikaletatka seyni hi htshiyahatatka.”
Klu tshinanu João Batista hi paõ hnika, hi vinho-ha rura seyni hixa wan-tshinru: “Waneylu kamtshi.”
Runa Jeji Whene tshinkaluru. Hnika, rura. Seyni hixa wan-tshina: “Haha hetanu, xye jeji tsru nikalu, vinho-ha jirakleru. Jijhawenruklerune hiyrun-koxa majnakowatatshine rimatleta.”
Seyni himatkaltshi potuknu ptowru wuhenetkalune tshinanni.
Simão Tshinkalurupji Rawakanaxyawaka PiranapniSatu fariseu tshanixlu Jesus waleyma hnikapyawakapa. Waneya Jesus yatka fariseu-pji nwaka. Waneya nikawaka htuplata.
Waneya wale poktshi koxa twa sato suxo hektutu kamhaklero. Waneya timaxinixka Jesus fariseu-pji rukoluhinixka nikawakakwa pa stono phamluhalo yehi tanika.
Jesus tjimne tapoka hijixistsi. Ttshiyahakananumta. Tyinuwaka hihakjixletlu toktehaya. Tojiwu chehi tcheyixyalu. Tamlujixitlu. Waneya phamluhalo tuyokjixihohotlu.
Waneya xye rexini fariseu, wla htshinahchinikanuta: “Xye jeji Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri rixkamka, rimathetanmaklo katni twu suxo hanu hixatshropotni hkamrukjero. Hektutu kamhakleroni.”
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru fariseu: — Simão, pa pirana naluk-hinkakletanyi. Waneya Simão wan-tshinru: — Hehe, kasruklewakleru.
Jesus wan-tshinru: — Rawna hepi jejine deve-tatshine. Satu jeji tiyiro hikchiklewjexikatshri h-deve-tna. Satu quinhentos proji tiyiro h-deve-kanata, satu cinquenta proji tiyiro h-deve-ta.
Seyni hi satukna himukata wenutletlu h-dev-rerna. Hiyáhoni wanna hepi jejine hichya-conta-techatkatka. Hiyáhoni xawakni, hanuru potu wanna hepi hichinikpotutanru ruchya-conta-techatjerna?
Waneya Simão wan-tshinru: — Hitaho tsru potu conta hichyachaxikalurni. Waneya wane htshinru Jesus: — Hehe, wane potuko ptshina.
Waneya ruprotakyehitlo suxo waneya wla htshinru Simão: — Petlo twu suxo. Njihlokapjityi seyni hi penekno honha nojixi herojikolu. Seyni wala hihaklu nojixi toktehaya hiyrunu tojiwu tcheyitlu.
Napojini hi pamlutno. Seyni wala njihlokkawaka hi tucho hamlurjixitno.
Hi nhihtshihako puyokjiwutno seyni twu suxo phamluhalo tuyokjixitno.
Hiyáhoni wane ntshinyi, hixo tektunu tuknojikatka. Hiyáhoni tamotpotutno. Klu tshinanu wla rixa, psotsonu hiknojikaluru psotsonu ramotlewaxya.
Waneya wane htshinatkalo: — Pektunu puknojikatka.
Waneya wale nikawakakwa rimwanune yinuwaka wan-tshinreta hihchinikanuyna: — Katnihe xye haté hektuntshikaka koxa ruknoka?
Suxone Jesus Hepixjerone PiranapniWaneya wane wkatanu, Jesus ptowru poktshi nwaka hyapa, tsru poktshi hiyrun-koxa mtserutu poktshikaka. Runkaklewakananumta kihler-potuko tokantshi Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka pirana. Waleymana rasruklene, doze-na.
Hiyrun-koxa waleymana satokaka suxo rutskalaklenetka, kamtshi ruknojinine satkaka hiyrun-koxa rutskalaklerone satkaka hyeyixlekakayna. Sato wanna hepire Maria Madalena tshinkaluro. Wala honra mitshikananu sete kamtshine takajika.
Hiyrun-koxa sato suxo Joana tshinkaluro, Cuza tshinkaluru hnunro phuru Herodes hitakanru waleyma htowuwaxyawakapa. Hiyrun-koxa Susana hiyrun-koxa pimrone hixolune. Wanna Jesus hepixjekanata hejnuyma rimwalerna.
Hitaklu Tataji Jiplaljekleru PiranapniWaneya hixolune yine ptowru poktshikaka hichpajikatshine hapatjeyehitlu Jesus. Waneya Jesus satu yapkaklu pirana runkakatkana:
— Satu jitaklewakleru hichpakamta rutaklewtapanu. Waneya ruplaljetatajitlu. Pimriji hatnu hapostsi hapoktatajita. Wane hkatsrejikatka, runna kochitshin-koxa hnikloktatajitanruna.
Pimriji sotlu hanikajite hapoktatajita. Wane ruptshejyatka riprih-hapkatanatka klu tshinanu hi khatshij-yehinru.
Pimriji kona yehi hapoktatajita. Waneya konaymakananuko htseruwna, hkakmokanatkalu.
Seyni pimriji kihle tshijiwaka hapoktatajita. Htseruwna, hjiwata. Satkakaji pejnu tshinanu cem-ji rawa. Waneya wane htshinna Jesus: — Kajnakopnahi hyijnakoxyawakapa, hyijnakotanu.
Jesus Hasruklu Klu Hyapkakleta Hitataji Jiplaljekleru PiranaWaneya Jesus hasruklene hepomhalu Jesus: — Hanhe htshina xye yapkaklu pirana?
Waneya wane htshinna Jesus: — Hixamka henekka himaxyawakaplu mimatkotu pirana Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka pirana. Seyni pimrine tshinanu yapkaklu nkamhiylu ptowru piranako. Rexinna retmakna, hi rapkathojitna; hjeminna, hjemmakna hma mimatjeminixipna.
— Xyeni yapkaklu. Hitataji Hoyakalu tokanni.
Hatnu hapostsi hapoktatajitatshri yaholni tokantshi jematshine. Seyni runa Satanás kamtshi. Hkonyana tokantshi rajiyna hitakkaluru hma malixyawakanupluna, hma miwekkajikowakanupna.
Sotlu hanikajite hiknokkalune wannani tokantshi jematshine. Tokantshi hjeminixkana hyoptotmakluna tsru rumuwleymana. Seyni hi waneyna hitskina wanna. Hiyáhoni pchini tsonu halixatshinepni. Runinipa yahtaletlewlu ramtakanruna tokantshi hjemlerna.
Kona yehi hapoktatajitatshine, wanna Hoyakalu tokanu jematshine pixkalune. Seyni kojwakahchinikanrukaka, ho pohirewnalu, ho poyikowlukaka xye hohne hexikaluru mixkowpotuta waneya xekoyaka hkakmokannatkalu. Hiyáhoni hi hjiwatanatkana.
Seyni halikaka kihle tshijiwaka hapoktatajitatshine, wannani potuk-hajirune, kihle hajirune. Hyijnakotluna tokantshi. Romkahitluna hjemlerna. Hmachiretleymana hjiwatanutkana.
Katalu Piranapni— Hike yineru lamparina nikotatshri hachhaji hpuko hitakanro. Hi hijeko hpukoko rutakanro. Seyni kihlero halikaka lamparina kihle nikotle tixyawaka tutajikowaka, ptowru yineru hapkathojixyawakapa tnikotle tshinanu.
Klu tshinanu ptowruka yohimluru ruphujetko. Ptowru tokantshi yohimatkaluru rimathetko, runkakletko.
— Hiyáhoni hislahinwa hanu pixa yijnakoletanru xye hima: Klu tshinanu hwikatshri pnute renekko. Seyni hike mwikatu haté seyo rimwaleru hkonkona.
Jesus Hinro, Himolen-koxa PiranapniWaneya Jesus hinro, himolen-koxa yanwakatlu Jesus. Seyni hi rumukata hapoklestsitluna hixolune yine tshinanu.
Waneya runkakka. Wane htshinruna: — Punro, pepurun-koxa maleka rawna. Raluk-hetletyina.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinna wanna ptowruneka: — Katnihe nunro, nomolene wannani Hoyakalu tokanu yijnakotatshine hiyrunu ntshinyawaka kamhatshine.
Jesus Kanniphalu Hitukkajyawaka PiranapniWaneya pa hohnekotnaka Jesus kanawa hpokowna rasrukleneyma. Waneya wla htshinna: — Tujra sreta wnahlu powha wyanu. Waneya hyatkana.
Seyni hkopruhatka pchinikna Jesus himkamta. Waneya hyopyoka tsru kanniphalu tsru powhaya. Htsepohjetlo kanawa hiyáhoni katsephatkalo. Tsru jhamleru potukni ptowruka.
Waneya rasruklene yanwakatlu Jesus, hkomyekluna wane htshinruna: — Kasruklewakleru, Kasruklewakleru, wupnahetkotanuna! Waneya Jesus yotunotatka htshihetjetlu kanniphalu hiyrunu tenoplojhal-koxa. Waneya rutukatka kanniphalu. Pokokha rixatka hipowha.
Waneya Jesus hepomhatkana rasruklene wane htshinna: — Hanurhe hixa halixle? Seyni hpikatkana hiyáhoni wane htshinkakna wannakakluko: — Hanu hixatshri koxni xye jeji? Klu tshinanu kanniphalu hipowha koxa yijnakotlu.
Jesus Hitskalajyawaklu Jeji Hixolune Kamtshine Himwatshri PiranapniWaneya tujra wnahlu tsru hipowha Gerasa sreta rapokna, Galileia powha wnahlu.
Waneya kanawa ruptejinixka Jesus satu jeji poktshi hajer-makni, kamtshine himwatshri yoptotlu. Hix-hohne mamkatni. Hi pantshiko rawa seyni yomletshi rawa.
Waneya Jesus rexiniklunu hsaplewata. Hyawnamta Jesus-stsi. Tsru plama rixa waneya wane htshin-saplewleta: — Jesus, Hoyakalu ten-potu hajeru whene! Kluhe pixannatkano? Nanjityi hi psaletpotutanunno.
Wale wan-tshina klu tshinanu Jesus yokanatatkalu kamtshi ruchpajyawakaplu jeji. Hixo kata kamtshi kachitlu hipokananu. Hiyáhoni rostutka. Yomuwatsamka rostutka himyonota, hihpeji koxamka. Seyni yomuwatsni hiknajromtana hmixkonu tshinanu. Waneya popriwaka ranikjekanatluna kamtshine.
Waneya kamtshine hanjitlu Jesus teno pnawaka hma yokanaxyawakanupna.
Wanekananru hixoluru porco hipjitastsi hnikakanaxyana. Waneya kamtshine hipokananu ranjitluna Jesus ritshixyawakapna porco mane hjihlojyawakanapna. Waneya Jesus hitshitna.
Hiyáhoni ruchpakamtatkana kamtshine. Waneya porco-ne mane hitokote hjihlokamtatkana. Waneya hixolunni porco-nni hipjita hijrujyanatka. Hipowha rapokanna waneya hipowha rahyejyanna.
Waneya xye rexinixkana porco-ne hinotatshine rasukamtna. Runkaklewatna tsru poktshiya, hsana hajen-koxa.
Waneya hixolune yine hinamta retapyawakanapna klu rixanna. Waneya rapokluna Jesus nwaka. Retluna kkamtshithixapatshri. Htuplakanata Jesus jixistsi. Kamkatkalu kkamtshithixapatshri, kahchinikanutkalu. Waneya rimyekatkana yine.
Waneya kkamtshithixapatshri hetakanatjene hinkakna hanu rixa hitskalakletkatka.
Waneya hpikpotutatkana ptowrunek-yine Gerasa tshiji sreta hajene. Hiyáhoni ranjitluna Jesus wanna tshijne ruchpajyawakapa. Waneya kanawa hpokownatka Jesus. Waneya hsatokhonukatka ruchpakakanaxyawaka sreta.
Seyni wale jeji kkamtshithixapatshri hanjitmaklu Jesus, waleyma rixyawakpatka. Seyni Jesus yokanatlu. Wla htshinhonuklu:
— Pipji pyanutka. Punkakanna yine Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu rix-hepixlexyawakyi pirana. Hiyáhoni ralimta. Runkaklewatatka hipoktshi hajene yehiya Jesus hixyawakatkalu.
Jesus Sato Suxo, Sato Mturo Rutskalajyawaka PiranapniWaneya pa sreta wnahlu rapojinixka Jesus, hixolune yine yoptotlu, tsru poyikowluyma. Klu tshinanu waneko hkahwakakanaxyaluna.
Waneya runa satu tsru hitakkaluru hanjihohnewakapji hajeru, Jairo hiwakatletatshri. Hyoptsojityehitlu Jesus jixistsi. Ranjitlu Jesus hipji hyiywakapa,
klu tshinanu richitsho, satopkaluto, doze mhaleruto, tupnakastsitkani. Waneya Jairo-pji hyakananumxiniwa Jesus hixolune yine hipxakjemtlu.
Waneya twa sato suxo hihrahawatatshro. Doze hwalapu hima tuhrahawatatka. Hixo kpinrewaklerunemka pinixnixkalo hiyrunu tnikatlewatanatka ptowruka twinri. Hike himukata hitskalhakakletlo.
Jesus tjimne sretako tunya waneya tkamrukamkatlu. Waneklukawa potuko tutukahrahatatka.
Waneya repomha Jesus: — Kathe kamrukamkatno? Seyni ptowru yineru hi hitni htshinna. Waneya Pedro wan-tshinatkalu Jesus: — Kasruklewakleru, hixolune yine katshnekyi ripxakjetyina.
Seyni Jesus wan-tshina: — Yineru kamrukamkatatkano. Nimata klu tshinanu ruchpakamxyatkano npixkonu.
Waneya texnawa suxo hi tumukata yohimlexnawa, hitatakatshroko yanwakatlu Jesus. Waneya Jesus jixistsi tuknojnawa. Waneya tunkaklewata ptowru yineru hetanu klu hikolukle tkamruklu hiyrunu waneklukawa tutskalhiywakatka pirana.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinro: — Chrima, palixle hitskalakyi. Pyanu kihlehchinikanpatkayi.
Waneya hyanumsakanaxiniwa Jesus, Jairo-pji hichpajikatshine htowrene hapoka. Waneya wane htshinruna: — Pchitshni hipnanatka. Hi pnute pkojwakanru hasruklewatatshri.
Wale hjemini Jesus, wane htshinru Jairo: — Hi ppikanu. Palixachatanu, pchitsho hitskalhanu.
Waneya Jesus Jairo-pji hapojinipa, hi ritshitna pimrine wanna hatjini hjihlojyawakna. Pedro, Tiago, João hiyrunu mturo hiru, tunro, wane pejnu tsonu himukata wane yaleta.
Wane pchinika ptowru yineru tshiyahata hsaplewjepotutna mturo pohwaka tshinanu. Seyni Jesus wan-tshinatkana: — Hituk-tshiyahletanutka. Mturo hi tupna seyni tumkachata.
Seyni rutsolhitatluna Jesus, wanna himata tupniywakanatka.
Waneya Jesus kosemyoxininatkalo mtúroni, wane htshinro: — Mturo, ppalna!
Waneya tiwejinri hiwekatnaka. Waneklutka mturo yotunotatka. Waneya Jesus hohlujixlo mturo.
Turu, tunro koxa himyekatka seyni Jesus hijretna hike hmunkajyawakanupluna wale pirana.
Jesus Hasruklene Kamrurepa PiranapniJesus tomhana rasruklene doze waneya renekpixkonutna kamtshine htowuxyawakapna ruchpajyawakapna yine maneya hiyrun-koxa ptowru hixatshri yeyixlu rutskalajyawakna.
Jesus yokanatna Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka pirana runkaklexyawakapna hiyrun-koxa yeyixatshine rutskalajyawakna.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinna: — Hike hanikanu xye yanre tshinanu, hi hkanojere, hi saco-ko, hi pão-ko, hi tiyiroko, hi hepi mkatshriko hanikanu.
Hma yoptotjenepa, hma jemjenepa tshinanu, hichpakamxinpatka waneya wanna hetanu hiwlihkajpatjixitanu rimaxyawakapna hi hixako htshinanni seyni hma yoptotjene malixlenu tshinanni.
Waneya hyatkana. Ptowru poktshi pejnu nwaka hyana. Runkakletluna kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana hiyrun-koxa ptowru sretaka hwatshine yeyixatshine rutskalakna.
Phuru Herodes Kojwakahchinikanuxyawaka PiranapniWaneya phuru Herodes, Galileia tshijne pohire, himatyehitlu Jesus kamhajekanatanru pirana. Waneya hkojwakahchinikanutatka Herodes klu tshinanu satkaka wan-tshinakanata: — João Batista-ni hetko hiwekatnaka.
Pimrine wan-tshina Elias-ni tshinkalurni hakanhayehihetkotwu, seyni pimrine wan-tshina satu mitshikawni Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri hiwejiklutnaka.
Seyni Herodes wan-tshina: — Hitakni kastaknojikjixatkalu João Batista-ni. Hiyáhoni katnihe xawaka xye jeji xyekaka pirana njemyehixinri? Hiyáhoni phuru Herodes haluk-hetletlu.
Jesus Hixolune Yine Rohluxyawaka PiranapniWaneya hsatojinixkana Jesus nurrene, runkakluna Jesus ptowruko hkamhapanruna. Hiyáhoni ranikna wannapka kahnete poktshiriya Betsaida poktshistsi hajeru nwaka.
Seyni hixolune yine himatyehitlu wane hyiywaka. Hiyáhoni romkahitluna. Seyni Jesus kihle yoptole rixna. Runkakletluna Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka pirana hiyrun-koxa rutskalakna ptowruneko hpinitkonnalune.
Waneya kayi rixinixka Jesus hasruklene hapyehitlu. Wane htshinruna: — Pyokanatanna yine hixolune poktshikaka nwaka hyiywakapna hiyrunu hsankaka wi potuko hwatshri nwaka hyiywakapna. Wane ruknokajinrina hoyetshno, rukchijyapluna hnikanrupna. Klu tshinanu hewi wwiywaka kahnete poktshirni.
Seyni Jesus wan-tshinna: — Hixa henekanna hnikanrupna. Waneya ruhitna: — Nijittshi wimwalerutka cinco pão hepi chima tsonu. Palukluhe wanjixyawakaplu nikkaluru nyi yine pejnu tshinanupa?
Klu tshinanu rawna cinco mil jejine. Waneya wane htshinna rasruklene: — Htuplajixanna yine pa ptohkaka, cinquenta yine pa xkehkaka rixanna.
Waneya wan-rixana. Htuplajixna ptowruneka.
Waneya Jesus kochtsheklu cinco pão, hepi chim-koxa. Tenhohne hyihata hpoyahnutlu Hoyakalu. Waneya hjiknajrotlu pão. Waneya rasruklene reneklu hixolune yine rapsaxyawakapna.
Waneya ptowruneko nikatka. Jinanutkana. Waneya hkochtshekluna hixetatshri pão psojkaka, chim-koxa, doze chiwatu htsepotana.
Pedro Jesus Hiphujtaxyawaka PiranapniWaneya pa katatnaka ranjihohnekananumta Jesus, walepka. Waneya rasruklene repomha walestsi hwakanatatshine. Wane htshinna: — Kathe rikahwaknona yine?
Waneya ruhitluna, wla htshinruna: — Satkaka yineru wan-tshina pixa João Batista-yi; satuko wan-tshina pixa Elias-yi; satuko wan-tshinyi pixa satu mitshikawni Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshriyi, hiwejiklutnakyi.
Jesus hepomhana: — Ha hixa, kathe hkahwakno? Waneya Pedro hihita: — Pixni Hoyakalu yokanreryi, Messias-yi.
Jesus Hinkakletlu Rupninri Pirana Hiyrunu Riwejyawakatnaka PiranaWaneya ruykotna hipokananu hike yineru xako hinkakanru wale pirana. Waneya wane pnute htshina:
— Jeji Whene tshinkaluru hijhalu hsalewniywaka hixo pa hixanu tshinanuya. Nuknokko tsrukakalune judeu-ne hiyrunu tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne yehiya, kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine yehiy-koxa. Nuylatko. Seyni map-hohne rixinri niwekanutnaka.
Cristo Cruz Rutaykoxinri PiranapniWaneya wane htshinna wanna ptowruneka: — Satu yineru haluk-homkahrexinno, rujhalu pa hohne pejnu wale ralujyawaka ruchoxyawaka, ptowru hohneruka rutaykopitanru h-cruz-te waneya romkahitanno hita.
Klu tshinanu katukta haluk-hiwekkakletanru riwejinrimka, ramtakanru riwekle; seyni katukta hita tshinanu hamtakanru riwekle riwekanu.
Hanhe rixa hepixletlu yineru xye tshijne hihlenu psoluka hkayaxiniklunu seyni riwejinri ramtakanuna ho hnikaxikona?
Klu tshinanu katukta hipatewatanno hita hiyrun-koxa ntokanu hipatewatatshri Jeji Whene tshinkaluru koxa hipatewatanru wale runinipa waleko royaknuyma hiyrunu Ruru hoyaknuyma rimapojinipa hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrene tenhohne hajene potukaluneyma.
Hichinikanru xye; satkaka hewi hajeru hma mupnaknukawa, retanru Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hapokatshritka.
Jesus Pnuko Hixamanexyawaka Rasruklene Hetanu PiranapniWaneya pa semana pnutejiji hiknohatka Jesus, Pedro, João, Tiago koxa ranika. Satu mriji hkankatkana ranjihohnetapyawakapna.
Waneya ranjihohnekanaxiniwa Jesus, hyokmanhojitatka. Himkal-koxa klata, klat-potuko rixa, katajru.
Waneyakni hepi jejine hakanha. Riynumsatluna Jesus. Satni Moisés-ni tshinkalurni, satni Elias-ni tshinkalurni.
Hoyaknutshi rimakanhana, Jesus hipnalepa pirana htshinjetna, Jerusalém poktshi hakanhikatshripa pirana.
Seyni Pedro-ne hixapnewpotuthonuka. Waneya ruyojinixkana, retluna Jesus hoyaknu, hiyrun-koxa hepi jejine waleymalune.
Waneya hyinixkana Jesus hiynumsakanatatshine Pedro wla tshinru Jesus: — Kasruklewakleru, kihleru wiko wutujyawaka. Hayeri wkamheru mapa pantshi; satu pixanupa, satu Moisés-nupa, satu Elias-nupa. Pedro hi himatjemnawa klukta htshina.
Waneya hohimkohi hitokote ruchpajyatka tokantshi wla tshinatshri: — Xyekni nowhene nalukleru. Hyijnakotanru hanukta htshinanhi!
Waneya rutshrojinixka tokantshi Jesus tsonu retatkana. Waneya potshkechana. Waneya waneklu papko retlerna hike runkakna.
Jesus Mturu Kamtshite Hakajyawaka PiranapniWaneya wale prika himriji hserpijyatkana. Waneya yine hixolune yoptotaplu.
Waneyakni satu jeji hixolune yin-yehi hwakanatatshri saplewata. Wane htshin-sapleta: — Kasruklewakleru, nanjityi pepixyawaklu noturu klu tshinanu waleni noturu satupkalutu.
Kamtshi kachjetlu mturu. Hsaplewjejetana, hkowchoklu mturu, kamtshi hipokananu hiknoklu, ruchpaksolnamatana. Hsaletjetanru. Kyapreru mturu ruchoxyawakanru.
Pasruklenemka nanjita ruknojyawakapluna kamtshi seyni hi rumukatna.
Waneya Jesus hihita. Wla htshina: — Yine malixaklenhi, hektutu kamhaklerunhi. Haté hi pejnu hohnekta nimwanhi hixa? Haté hi pejnu hohnekta nakotanhi? Waneya wla htshinru tsru: — Wkata panikanru pituru.
Waneya ranikatkaluna mturu Jesus nwaka kamtshi hiknokanru mturni tshij-hoho. Ruwnanakanatka. Waneya Jesus towutlu kamtshi mturu ruchpajyawakapa. Rutskalaklu mturu. Waneya ruru renekatkalu.
Hiyáhoni ptowruneka himyekahchinikanutatka Hoyakalu tsru pixkonu rixle tshinanu.Waneya rimyekahchinikanuxiniwana yine ptowruneka Jesus kamhajekanatanru tshinanu, Jesus wan-tshinatkana rasruklene:
Jesus Hinkaklewaxyawaklu Rupninri Piranapni— Hi xako hamtakanru xye tokantshi ntshinyahi. Jeji Whene tshinkaluru yine renekko.
Seyni Jesus hasruklene hi rimatjemluna klu raluka tshinreta xye tokantshi. Hi phujetanuwaka htshina xye tokantshi hma mimatjemyawakanupluna. Hiyrun-koxa hpika hepomhaletluna Jesus klumka raluka tshinreta wale tokantshiya.
Kat-pothe Hijhakaluru PiranapniWaneya rasruklene yinuwaka hihjekakleta wannakakluko katnihe hijhakalur-potu.
Seyni Jesus himatlu ruchinikanretanruna. Hiyáhoni satu mturu hkachita Jesus. Hyehistsi rutaklu mturu.
Waneya wla htshina: — Katukta hihle yoptoletlu xye mturu nhiwaka tshinanu hit-koxa hyoptotanu. Hiyrunu katukta yoptotanno hita, hyoptotanru hita nyokanatjeru. Klu tshinanu mujhakotu hikahwakleru hixa, walekni hijhakalur-potu.
Katukta Hi Kamnirewata Repixlewata Wale PiranapniWaneya João wan-tshinru: — Kasruklewakleru, wetlu jeji kamtshi hiknokatshri pixa phiwakaya seyni wimaletlu klu tshinanu hi hixa wepirni.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinna João hiyrunu pimrine rasruklene: — Hi himaletanru klu tshinanu katukta hi kamnitwu, repixwu.
Samaria-nune Tshinkalune Myoptohihlenuxyawakanru Jesus PiranapniWaneya wla rixa. Rapokpapkolupiraxinixka tenhohne hyiywakapa, Jesus hichinikanretlu Jerusalém poktshi hyiywakapa.
Waneya hepi yine hkosekakjixa ralpokohnapuxyawakapluna Jesus. Hyatkana. Waneya satu mtserutu poktshi Samaria tshijne hwatshri ralpokoxyana kihle hapokle rixyawakapa.
Seyni wane hajene hi haluka yoptotletlu Jesus klu tshinanu rimathetluna Jerusalém poktshi nwak-potu hyanu.
Waneya rasruklene Tiago, João rexinixkana wan-rixahchinikanuxyawakna wane poktshi hajene, wla htshinruna: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus, hi he paluklu tshitshmero tenhohne hajeru wtomhiywaka nyi yine hnikaxyawakapa?
Seyni Jesus hiprotakatka waneya htshihetjetna. Wla htshina: — Hi himathexnawa hanu hixa hiwekletatshinhi hixa.
[Klu tshinanu Jeji Whene tshinkaluru hi hina yine samenru hnikaxyawakapa seyni halikaka runa riwekkajyawakapna yine.] Waneya pa poktshi nwakako hyatkana.
Satkaka Jesus Homkahpiratatshinemka PiranapniHatnu hapo hyapakanaxinna, satu jeji wan-tshinru Jesus: — Kasruklewakleru, hanuktako pyanu pixa nimotsatanyi hita.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru jeji: — Kaweretshine kapna rawjetna. Kochitshin-koxa tenhohne yapatshine waneyna rawyawakna. Seyni Jeji Whene tshinkaluru tsonu hi jimkawakleru, hi rawya rapnanuwakle.
Waneya satu jejitnaka Jesus wan-tshinmaklu: — Pomkahitanno. Seyni wale wla tshinru: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, pitshitanno mitshikananhapkatshi nsatkapamtanu. Nurunitshi nkapnamtanu.
Seyni Jesus wan-tshinru: — Petachatanna hipnatshinekakluko kapnakajyawaka. Seyni pixa, punkakletanru Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka pirana.
Waneya satutnaka wan-tshinru Jesus: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, nomkahitanmakyi seyni petachahapkatanno nunhiywakapna nopji hajene.
Seyni Jesus wan-tshinru: — Katukta yochyaktshijipi yochyaktshijixikatshriko ratjini reknojini, Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka mpoyahokkakatni.
Setenta Hiyrunu Hepi Jejine Hyokanata Runkaklewtapyawakapna PiranapniWaneya Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus setenta e dois jejine hnureta. Hyokanatna hepkaka hkosejyawakapna, ptowru poktshi hiyrunu ptowru tshijnekaka hyiywakapna, Jesus yapamxyawaka pejnupa.
Hajewa. Seyni himatanu. Nyokanathi hatatjewa ovelha-nhi lobo-ne pixkalune hanikajite hyiywakapa.
Tiyiro mapa hi hanikanu, hi sacola-ko hanikanu. Hiyrun-koxa hi hanikanru sandalha. Hi halikanru hatnu hapo hyoptoxinri.
Satu pantshi hjihlojinipa, mitshikananhapka wla htshinanna pantshi hajene: “Kihlephi xyepji hwatshine.”
Hiyáhoni wanepji rawinipa satu yineru kihle hwachleru walekni kihle hwachleru htshinka. Seyni wane hmawkanuklunu jeji kihle hwachle mixkatu htshintokanuxyawaka hixa nwaka ko hsatkapanu htshinyawaka.
Walepjiko hwanu. Wane hnijini kluneruktako hohlutko. Hiyrun-koxa wanepjiko hirini klunerukta hitko. Klu tshinanu kamrurewatatshri himukata yoptoletlu hkamrure hipekole. Hi pimripjikaka hyanu.
— Hanur-poktshiktako hjihlojinipa, kihle yoptole hixkoklunupa, hnikanru kluneruktako henejikolupa.
Wane poktshi hwatshine hitskalhakakanu. Waneya wla htshinanna: “Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hapokanwakatatkahi.”
Hanu poktshikta hjihloka hma malukkonuklunupa waneya wane hichpajini. Poktshipji kaka hapotlo hyanu. Waneya wla htshinanu:
“Haté tshiji pahi xye poktshi hajeru, wijixi hipxakatshri pahi, wcheyitanu hixa hetanu. Seyni hichinikanru xye: Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hapokanwakatamkahi.”
Jesus pnuteko htshinna: — Nunkakhi, halikaka ntshina. Hapnokaxikolu hohnepa Sodoma poktshini salexikolu yohnik-hapnokatlu rixko hma yoptohihlenuxikowakanu poktshiya.
Malixkane Poktshikaka Hapnokaxikowaka PiranapniHiyrun-koxa Jesus wan-tshina: — Hapnokatkalur-potupyi pixa Corazim poktshi hiyrunu Betsaida poktshi! Klu tshinanu himyekaklewatatshrikaka hkamhakmaka Tiro poktshiya hiyrunu Sidom poktshi hix-yehi hakanhikatshri pixkalutu, waneyamka mitshikawako rehchinikanutanutkana wane poktshikak-hajene, waneyamka mkatshri saco mapa kamhikolu hmakatanutkana rimathexikowakna rehchinikanutatkana hiyrunu tshitshi pahi koxamka hpolojiwuxinwana.
Rapnokaxikolu hohnepa Tiro hiyrun-koxa Sidom poktshi hi hsaletpotukanatkona hixa salexikowaka pso.
Hiyrunu pixa Cafarnaum poktshi. Pkahwakhe patskoxyawakapa haté tenhohne? Seyni pixa halikaka puknokko tshiji hitokote hamhikowaka yehi.
Hixa yijnakotatshine hit-koxa hyijnakotna. Hixa hiknokatshine hit-koxa ruknokna. Hiyrunu hita hiknokatshine, nyokanatjer-koxa ruknokna.
Setenta Hiyrunu Hepi Satojyawaka PiranapniWaneya hsatokatkana setenta e dois jejine Jesus yokanrene. Hpoyikowpotutna. Wla htshinatkaluna Jesus: — Haté kamtshine yijnakotwu wyokanaxinna ruchpakna pixa phiwaka tshinanu!
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinna: — Hehe, hita hetlu Satanás kamtshi rujrujyawaka tenhohneya rawrakle pixka.
Hjemanno. Nenekatkahi pixkontshi himnune hkatsrexyawaka, heklone koxa. Hike rixa. Nenekatkahi pixkontshi hkamnitjene mixkonu hiknojyawakapa. Hike himtukanhi.
Wanepnawaka hi himuwatanu kamtshine yijnakoxyawakhi tshinanu seyni halikaka himuwatanu klu tshinanu hyonhiwakatka tenhohneya.
Jesus Poyikowaxyawaka PiranapniWaneya waneklu hpoyikowpotuta Jesus, Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru himukatle tshinanu. Waneya wane htshina: — Nimalwutyi, Nuru, tenhohne tshij-koxa Towutatshriyi. Klu tshinanu pyohimatlu xye pirankaka jimatkaleruneya hiyrunu kahchinikanuruneya. Seyni puphujetlu hike mimatkane hetanuya. Hehe, Nuru, xye pixa palujyawakni.
— Nuru, ptowru potuko renekno. Hike himathetlu Whentshi seyni Hirtshipka himathetlu. Hike himathetlu Hirtshi seyni Whentshipka himathetlu hiyrun-koxa katukta raluk-himatyehkakletlu Hirtshi.
Waneya Jesus hiprotakyehitna rasruklene waneya wla htshinatkana wannapka: — Kihlehchinikanhi xyekaka pejnu hexini, hiyhaleya.
Klu tshinanu wane ntshinhi hixo Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshinni hiyrun-koxa phurune haluk-hetletmaklu hixa hetanrutka. Seyni hi retluna. Raluka yijnakoletmakluna hixa yijnakotanrutka seyni hi hyijnakotluna.
Kihleru Jeji Samaria Hajeru PiranapniWaneya satu Moisés yonreru pirana himatpotutatshri palnamta hyahoxyawakaplu Jesus. Wla htshin-hepomhaletlu: — Kasruklewakleru, kluhe nkamhanu nkayaxyawakaplu hiwejikaluru hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa?
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru: — Hanhe htshina yonruru pirana? Hanhe htshin-yonhata?
Waneya jeji wla tshin-hihretlu: — “Pamotanru Tsru Hixikatshriwa Poyakalute psol-potuko pajiya, psol-potuko piwejinriya, psol-potuko pmixkonuya, psol-potuko pihchinikanuya; pamotanru pimwastsitanru pamoxnawakwa pixka.”
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru: — Hehe, wane potuko ptshin-hihreta. Wane potuko pixanu waneyapa piwekanu.
Seyni hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshri haluka powratlexnawa hiyáhoni wla htshinru Jesus: — Seyni katnihe nimwastsireru?
Waneya Jesus hihitlu: — Wanekananru satu jeji Jerusalém poktshi yopijikatshri. Jericó nwaka hyakananumta. Katshowhurune yehi rapokana. Hkomkahanruna. Ruylakanruna. Waneya hyatkana. Rupnakastsitkani ruchomtatkaluna.
Waneyakta satu sacerdote wale hapoko yopikakanaxya. Retamxininatkalu jejni pa sretatnu hapo hyapamta, hyatka.
Seyni satu Samaria tshijne hajeru wale hapok-koxa yapamtatshri hapyehixinixkalu jeji. Retlu. Retwamonutlu.
Hyanwakatlu. Hpoyichretlu. Nhihtshiha ruyokhohotlu vinho-ha koxa. Waneya hipratji hoho rutakatkalu. Ranikatkalu, himkajexikowakapji rutakatkalu. Waneko rinoxyalu.
Waneya wale prika hyatka. Seyni mitshikananhapka tiyiro hepi hohne kamrurtshi wenru pso hkochpaka waneya kapjiru reneka. Wla htshinru: — Puslahanru. Klunerukta wane pnute psaletanutka wale tshinanu, nsatkapinipa, nwenutanyi.
Hiyáhoni xawakni kathe pkahwaka pixa, nyi mapa jejine tshinanu, rimwastsirexyawakluna katshowhurune hiylakleru?
Waneya hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshri wla tshinru: — Retwamonutjeru halikaka himwastsiretlu. Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru: — Pyanu. Waneko pixka pixanu pixa.
Jesus Hetapna Marta Hiyrunu Maria Tshinkalurone PiranapniWaneya Jesus rasrukleneyma yatka. Satu poktshi nwaka hyatkana. Sato suxo Marta tshinkaluro, wale poktshi hajero yoptotlu Jesus topjiya.
Waneyatka tepuro Maria tshinkaluro Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus jixistsi ttuplakanatatka. Tyijnakokanatlu htokanu.
Seyni Marta tshinkaluro kojwakahchinikanuta hixo kamrurtshi, pantshi hajeru tshinanu. Hiyáhoni tapokanwakatlu Jesus. Waneya wla ttshinru: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, hike pix-pixa tuknokamtano nepuro, hitapkani kamrurewatana? Hiyáhoni pyokanatanro tepixyawakapno.
Waneya Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus wan-tshinro: — Marta, Marta, kojwakahchinikanutatshroyi, mimatahichinikanuwatkátoyi hixo pa hixanu tshinanu.
Satupkalu hijhakalur-potu. Maria-kni kihleru nuretatka. Hiyrun-koxa hi tkonko tnurreru.
Jesus Hasrukna Ranjihohnexyawakna PiranapniWaneyatnaka Jesus hanjihohnekanata. Rali hanjihohnerexini satu rasrukleru wla tshinru: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus, pasrukanwu wanjihohnexyawaka, hanu wtshinanu, João hasrujyawakna rasruklene pixka.
Waneya Jesus wla tshina: — Wla htshina hanjihohneretanu: “Nuru, wanjityi pohitkalurupa pixa phiwaka potukalu. Runanutka pixa ppohirewaxyawaka.
Wniklerupa xye hohne tshinanupa penekanwu.
Pamtakahchinikanyehixinwu wektunu pimrine hektunu wamtakahchinikanyehixyawaka pixka. Hi yahtalexikowaka putakanwu.”
Hapokatshri Hnapu PiranapniXye koxa htshinatkana Jesus rasruklene: — Hanurhe hixa satkakhi, hanikaj-yetshno himatletlerupji nwaka yatshripa wla tshinatshripa: “Nimatletleru, mapatshi pão penekanunno.
Klu tshinanu satu nimatletleru yanamtatshri hapyehitno. Seyni hike nimwa nohluxyaplu.”
— Ho hitokoklahe ruhjechaxini. Wla htshinanu: “Hi pkojwakanno. Hiphapto hichyatka. Nojeko nwa nowheneneyma. Hiyáhoni hi numukata hiptekleta pão nenejyawakapyi,” — hi wane htshinanu.
Wane ntshinhi, yáholu himka raluk-hiptekleta rimatletleru rixyawaka tshinanu, seyni ruptekanu renekanru ptowruka ralukanru hma mapaxyawakanuplu.
Jesus Hanjihohnekjixyawaka PiranapniHiyáhoni wane ntshinhi: Hanjitanu henekko. Hijhanu hikchikanu. Hitpehiphaptotetanu, hkotpukko hiphapto.
Klu tshinanu ptowru hanjitatshri yoptotanru. Hiyrun-koxa ptowru hijhatshri hikchikanru. Ptowru yineru hiphapto hitpetatshri hkotpukyehitko hiphapto.
Hixlahe hirtshinhi, hituru chima ranjixinhi, himnurhe henekanru?
Ho tonaji ranjixini, heklolhe henekanru?
Hixa hektutu kamhaklerunhi himata kihleru henekawheneta hiyáhoni wane yohnik-rixa heneklewleta Hirtshi tenhohne hajeru, Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru ranjitjeru.
Jesus Hiyrunu Belzebu Tshinkaluru PiranapniWaneyatnaka Jesus kkamtshiteru kamtshite maleka ruknokamta. Myanumatkatni. Seyni ruchpajinixka kamtshi myanumakanatkatu yanumatatka. Hiyáhoni rimyekahchinikanutna.
Seyni pimrine wan-tshinyehitlu Jesus: — Kamtshi pohire Belzebu tshinkaluru himukatleyma tshinanu hetko maleka ruknokna kamtshine.
Pimrinetnaka haluka yahtaletletlu Jesus hiyáhoni hetkaluru tenhohne hichpajikatshrimka ranjitluna.
Seyni Jesus himathetahchinikanutna hiyáhoni wane htshinna: — Ptowru tshijne rawa nikawnatshripa, pa hchinikanurutu hmixlenu tshinanna wane tshijne hajene. Hiyrun-koxa pantshi hajene wannakakluko pnu pejnu rixahchinikanutna hi rumukata hwachaletna wanna.
Hiyrun-koxa Satanás kamtshi hkamnixiniklunwa hanhe rumukata pnute yaletanu htowuwle? Klu tshinanu hixa wan-tshinno Belzebu himukatleyma maleka nuknokna kamtshine.
Hiyrun-koxa Belzebu himukatleyma maleka nuknokamkana kamtshine ha hixa hiwhenene katu hiwakaymahe kamtshine maleka ruknokjekanatna, kat-mixkonu tshinanu wan-rixna? Hiyáhoni hixako hiwheneneko hikolukanunhi.
— Satu Jeji kmatsyiru, ptowru rimwaleruyma ruslahapjixinwa, ptowru rimwaleru hihle hislahletkaluru.
Seyni satu wale yohnik-mixkonurutu yanwakaxiniplu, ramtakakkanunru. Waneya hkonanru kachri hmunanhalerukananu. Waneya hkaniprejetlu rejnunkate.
— Hiyáhoni hita nmepixjetu, waleni nkamnitjeru. Hitayma mapatjetkatu, hkotspallewata.
Kamtshi Satojyawakatnaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus wan-tshinatnaka: — Kamtshi yineru mane ruchpakamxini, hyanachata, popriwaka hyapachata. Rujhalu rapnanuxyawaka. Seyni hi rukchiklu. Hiyáhoni wla htshina: “Nopjitapyawaka nsatokanutnak-honuka.”
Rapoka. Rukchiklu satolotkaluru, hihlepokoluru.
Hiyáhoni wla rixa. Hya waneya ranikna pimrine waleyma sete-ne kamtshine wale yohnik-hektunu kamhatshine. Hjihlokna, wane rawna. Ralipretka rallikanatatka xye jeji rekamtshitewle pnute.
Hihlewahchinikanyehitkalun-potu PiranapniWaneya wan-rixatnaka, xye pirana htshinakanaxiniwa Jesus, sato suxo wan-tshinru Jesus, tsru tokantshiya: — Hihlewahchinikanyehitkalúroni suxo pmatnanwakaxinro hiyrun-koxa pachitnurero.
Seyni Jesus wan-tshina: — Hehe, seyni hihlewahchinikanyehitkalun-potu ptowruneka Hoyakalu tokanu jematshine hiyrun-koxa romkah-tokanutjene.
Yine Hanjixyawaklu Hetkaluru PiranapniRapatjestsitluna Jesus hixolune yine. Psal-potúkona. Waneya Jesus yinuwaka hinkaklewleta. Wla htshinatkana: — Nyi himiwekkakhohnekanatatshine hektutu Kamhatshine potu. Hetkalurkakamka ranjitna. Seyni hi satukna hetkaluru rekhitkona seyni Jonas tshinkalurni hetkalurutepka rekhitkona pa hohne.
Jonas pixka hetkaluru rixnawa Nínive poktshi hajenni tshinanu. Waneko pixka rixanu Jeji Whene tshinkaluru xawakni hohne hiwekatshinewa hetanuya.
Tsro phúroni sul sreta tshijne hajéroni howuk-tshijne tuchpajyani phuru Salomão-ni hasruklewle himatkalnu tjemyawakapa. Hiyáhoni jemahchinikanrewlu hohnepa tukolukanuna xye papko hiwekatshinepni. Haha hetanu, hewiru satu Salomão-ni yohnika kpohiru.
Hikolukanuwnalu hohnepa jejinni Nínive poktshi hajenni hikolukanna xyeklu papko hiwekatshinepni klu tshinanu Jonas-ni hinkakle tshinanu rehchinikanutatkana. Haha himatanu, hewiru Jonas-ni tshinkaluru yohnik-hijhakalurni.
Mantshi Katalute PiranapniWane koxa htshina Jesus: — Hike nikotlu lamparina tkatshpokachaxikowakapa tomero ho hachhaji hpuko tutajikowakapa. Hi wane tixko seyni phujewak-potuko tutakko rapkathojixyawakapna hihruko jihlokatshinepa.
Wimane katalute waleni wiyhale. Kihleru yhale pixini piman-koxa kat-yehi potpako. Seyni hektu yhale pixinipa waneya piman-koxa mapchah-yehipa.
Hiyáhoni hislahinwa katalu himane hwatshri hma mapchahawaxyawakanupa.
Himane psoluka katawaka hixinipa, hi psojikna mapchahalu hwa, waneya katawaka potukni hatatjewa lamparina nikoxyawakni.
Jesus, Fariseu-ne Hiyrunu Hinanchitkaluru Tokantshi Hasruklewatatshine PiranapniWaneya rali yanumlexinixka Jesus, satu fariseu tshanixlu Jesus hipji hnikapyawakapa. Waneya Jesus wan-ya. Mesa htuplata.
Waneya fariseu rexinixkalu Jesus merojikatukwa tuplachaxyawaka mes-yehi rimyeka.
Waneya Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus wan-tshinru: — Hixa fariseu-nhi, herokalu copa stono prat-koxa maleka sreta tsonuya. Seyni hitoko hixa hinanwaka katsephi hahnanuwlu, hektuntshi koxa.
Mahchinikanunhi! Maleka sreta kamhatshri hi he hitoko nanwaka kamhatshri koxni wale?
Hiyáhoni xawakni psoji himwaleru xako henekanna hike mwikane. Waneyakni wan-hixinipa ptowruko powrapatka hixa tshinanu.
— Hapnokatkalunephi hixa fariseu-nhi! Klu tshinanu hixamka ptowrukmaka himwaleru Hoyakalu psoji henekjeta. Haté phamlu sureru phuta psoji arruda sure hapikjetlu hiyrun-koxa, ptowru hejnuj-sure psojite Hoyakalu penekaphutjeta. Seyni Hoyakalu chinikannu hiyrunu ruchiniklewle hixa hiknokachata. Xyekaka himukata kamhaleta hiyrunu hi pimrikaka hiknohachatanu.
— Hapnokatkalunephi hixa fariseu-nhi! Klu tshinanu hixa haluklu tsru hitakkaluru tuplawakle tsonu htuplawaxyawaka, hanjihohnewakapjikakaya. Hiyrun-koxa hixa halukpotutlu hpotuklexikolu halijikoluyma yine hixolune tshinanu.
— Hapnokatkalunephi! Kapnatkalunenatka pixkalunhi. Metapnatkotuya. Yine wale hoho hyapmakna seyni hi rimathetluna.
Waneya satu Moisés yonreru pirana himatpotutatshri wan-tshinru: — Kasruklewakleru, wane ptshinini hix-koxa papata.
Hinanchitkaluru Tokantshi Hasruklewatatshine Rujreta JesusWaneya Jesus wan-tshina: — Hapnokatkalunephi hix-koxa Moisés yonreru pirana himatpotutatshinhi! Klu tshinanu kyapre hanikkolu pixkalutu hitjikakna yine. Seyni hixa hi himyojiknako hyotnejyalu yinni hwunutleru hinolu hepixyawakanna yinni.
Hapnokatkalunephi. Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshinni yomlekaka hihleyehijechatatshinhi. Hixa hitsrukatenni hiylalenni.
Hiyáhoni wan-hixa hiphujetlexnawa hitsrukatenni kamrure hikchikhihlenutatshinhi. Klu tshinanu wanna hiylatanna hixa hihle yomletanna.
Hiyah-koxni Hoyakalu rimatkalnuyma wla htshina: “Nyokananwakatmakna, hinamtatshri pirana hinkakletatshine, nnuretanun-koxa. Satkakapni ruylatanna. Pimrinepni hsalewnakakanna.”
Abel-ni hiylaxikolu klu haté Zacarias tshinkalurni klu papko Zacarias honira Hoyakalupji altar yehi hwatshri altar hanikajiteswa ruylaxikana. Hehe, halikakni nyi himiwekkakhohnekanatatshine rapnokatkona xyekaka hiylalewlu tshinanupa.
— Hapnokatkalunephi hixa hinanchitkaluru tokantshi hasruklewatatshinhi! Klu tshinanu hixa konru chave himatkalewaxikaluru chav-ne waneya himretlu. Hi hixako jihloklu. Hiyrun-koxa wane jihlokpiratatshine himaleta.
Rutsekletmakluna Jesus Hkachixyawakapluna Piranapni— Waneya wane ruchpakamxinixka Jesus, kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine hiyrun-koxa fariseu-ne yinuwaka tsru jhekantshi kamhaleta. Hixo pirana repomsatluna Jesus.
Rutsekletmakluna, hkachtokanuxyawakapluna hjihyehixyamkapluna.
Hislahinwa Hixachaluya PiranapniWaneya rapatjetna hixolune yine, hixo mil yine. Haté hkatsrekkakna wannakakluko. Waneya mitshikananhapka Jesus wan-tshinna rasruklene: — Hetanru xako fariseu-ne tserutjeru. Waleni rixachalna.
Ptowru potuko hichyatkaluru ruphujetko hiyrun-koxa ptowru potuko yohimluru pirana pohitko.
Hiyáhoni ptowru potuko hyanumaxinri mapchahawakaya, hyijnakotko katawak-hohne yehiya. Hiyrun-koxa ptowru potuko himsalewaxinri, hihruko hitokoteya, ptowru yineru jemanru htshinyawak-potuko.
Jesus xye koxa htshina: — Nimatletanune, wane ntshinhi halikaka: Hi hpikanna mantshi hiylatatshine klu tshinanu wane pnutetka hike rumukata kamhalexyatkahi.
Wale tshinanu nekhithi kat-potu hpikanu. Halikaka hpikanru Hoyakalu hix-mane hakot-hiylaletatshri waneya wane pnute tshitshmero ruknoklewata. Wane ntshinatnaka. Halikak-potu Hoyakalu hpikanu.
— Hi he cinco kochitshine hi kwenu hichanjika? Wanepnawaka Hoyakalu hi satukna kochitshi hma muslahanutu.
Haté wijiwutsa ptowruka hitakyahokalurni Hoyakaluya. Hiyáhoni hi hpikanu klu tshinanu hixa yáholu satupka yineru tsonu, hixo kochitshine yohnik-hijhakalurni!
Jesus wan-tshina: — Wane ntshinhi, katukta hiphujtatno hita yine jemanu, Jeji Whene tshinkalur-koxa hiphujtatanru wale hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrene tenhohne hajene hetanu.
Seyni katukta yine jemanu malukkotu htshinanwakaxinipno waneya Jeji Whene tshinkaluru koxa waneko pixka htshinanwakatanunru hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrene tenhohne hajene jemanuya malukkotni wale htshinanunna.
— Katuktako hektuwaka htshinanwakatlu Jeji Whene tshinkaluru, wanepnawakatshi ramtakahchinikanuxiko rektunu. Seyni katukta hektutu tshinanwakaxiniplu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hikeklu hohne ramtakahchinikanyehitkona rektunu.
— Hanikkoklunpatka hanjihohnewakapjikaka nwaka hjihyehixikowakapa, ho tsrukakalune hoji sreta, ho tsru hitakkalun-yehi, hi hkojwakahchinikanuxinwa hanu potu htshin-hihretanna ho hanu htshinanna.
Klu tshinanu waneklu papko potuko Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hasrukanhi hanu potu htshinanu.
Jeji Phuru Mahchinikanutu PiranapniWaneya satu jeji wan-tshinru Jesus hixolune yin-yehiya. Wla htshina: — Kasruklewakleru, ptowutanru nomole hkaniprexinmakno wurni hiknokamtanru hejnu.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru: — Jeji, kathe hitakno hapohchinikanutkaluru nixyawaka nkotspalaxyawakaplu hejnu hixa tshinanu?
Waneya Jesus wla tshinna: — Yine, hislahinwa ptowruka ksotanuru pmet-sotanuxyawakanupa. Klu tshinanu hiweklu hi hejnu hihlenu tshinanu riwekanu yineru.
Waneya Jesus xye yapkaklu rutaka: “Rawa satu jeji phuru. Htshijne rawa tsru honantshi.
Waneya hyinuwaka hichinikanuwleta: Hi kwawakleyno xye tsru honantshi nimrexyawakapa. Hanhe nixanu xawaka?
Ha! Xawakni nimatlu nkamhanrupa, — htshina wale nanwaka. — Nyotkakanru pantshi hitsruka honantshi himrexikowakapjikaka waneya herotu pantshikaka nkamhanu tsru potpaklu. Waneko nimrexinri nonanru psoluka, nimwaleru ptowruka koxa.
Waneya wla ntshinanu nohchinikanuya: ‘Jeji kihle hchinikanurno. Ptowru potuko kihleru nimwa hixo mhale tshinanu. Xawakni napnanutanu, nnikanu, nuranu, numuwatanu!’”
Seyni Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu wan-tshinru: “Jipukaleru! Xye yetshno potuko pupnanu. Ha xawakni kathe himutukanru wale ptowruka pimretanru?”
Waneya Jesus wla tshina: — Wan-rixanuna yinepni hejnu hapatjetatshinepni wannanupka hijhatshinepni seyni hike mwikanenapni Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu yehiya.
Hoyakalu Munanhikolu PiranapniWaneyakni Jesus wan-tshinna rasruklene: — Hi hkojwakahchinikanutanu hanu hixa hiwekletanu, klu hnikanu. Hi himane tshinanuko koxa hkojwakahchinikanutanu klu hmakatanu.
Klu tshinanu hiweklu, nikkaluru yohnik-hijhakalurni. Mantshi, mkatshri yohnik-hijhakalurni.
Hetanru pokotu. Hi rutaklewata. Hi ramlu. Hi honantshi himretawakako rimwa. Halikaka rohlutjeru tsonu Hoyakalu. Seyni hixa, kochitshine yohnik-hijhakalun-pothi hixa.
Hanunhe hixa satkakhi kojwakahchinikanruyma hixolethohneyehixikatshriwa rumukata hiweklexyawaka pejnu hohne?
Hetanru kahwuru. Hanhe rixa tseruwnaleta? Hi hkamrurewata. Hi rama. Seyni wane ntshinhi halikaka hi phuru Salomão-niko, phuru potukni, seyni mkatshri kihler-potuko rutakjereru hi kahwuru pa hihlenu rixa.
Hoyakalukni makawkaklu campo hwatshriptshe xawakni wetleru yetshikawa ramhannatka forno hyoxijikolu tshinanu. Hi he kchana hmakaxyawaka pnute rixa makawkakletanhi hixa malixaklenhi?
Hiyáhoni hi hijhanru klu hnikanu ho klu hiranu. Hi hkojwakahchinikanuxinwa.
Klu tshinanu xyekaka ptowruka rujhajetmakna moyakalutene, ptowru tshijne hajeneko. Hiru tenhohne hajeru himatlu xye ptowruka halukanru.
Seyni mitshikananhapka Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hijhanu. Waneyakni Hoyakalu koxa henekanhi xyekaka ptowruka.
Waneya Jesus wla tshina: — Noprane ovelha-ne mixone pixkalunmakhi seyni hi hpikanu. Klu tshinanu hixa Hiru nurehchinikanuxnawa hpohirewaxyawaka renejyawakaphi.
Ptowruka himwaleru hichankanu waneya tiyiro hyoptotanrupa henekanna hike mwikane. Hikchijinwa tsapantshikaka mimat-nikawnakatu, hpohirewninri himretanu tenhohneya. Wane hi rimata nikawniya. Klu tshinanu tenhohne katshowhurune mwiywakanni. Hi kamlako himtuklewaxya.
Klu tshinanu hanukta himrexyalu hpohirewnale wane koxlu hihchinikanu.
Towrertshi Hislahyawakapa Piranapni— Halpokoxinwa ptowru potuko hinatshripa tshinanu. Hostuskotaxinwa lamparina hnikotanru.
Towrertshine pixka hixanu, hpohirna hkahwajinna hnunrowlu nikle yehi ruchpajinpatka pixka hixatshinephi. Rutpehiphaptotexinipa hkotpukyehihapkaxyawakapluna hitowrene.
Hihlewahchinikanyehitkalunephi towrertshine hiyokatshine pixka hixini, ptowruka halpokatkalurpatka hpohire hnapu. Halikaka wane ntshinhi, hpoyiptshijixinwa phuru. Htuplajixanna htowrene. Repixanutkana wale potuko.
Hihlewahchinkanyehitkalunepni hanunektapni hiyokatshine hikchijikolune rapojinipa htowutjerna ho hanikaj-yetshno ho hoprikako rapojinipa.
Hichinikanru xye: kapjiru himatahnaputkamkalu katshowhuru, himka retachatanru hipji hyotpujyawakapa.
Hix-koxa kakonutanu klu tshinanu Jeji Whene tshinkaluru hinanu hma kakonuxinri papko.
Waneya Pedro hepomhalu: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, xye yapkaklu ptshinreru ho hixa tshinanu tsonuplahe ho pimrine tshinan-koxaplahe?
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru: — Katnihe towrertshi ptowutkolu, kahchinikanuru? Walepkani towrertshi rutakka htowutjerupji rinoxyawakapa hiyrunu pimrine towrertshine reneka niklexyawakapa niklu papkokaka.
Hihlehchinikanyehitkalurni wale towrertshi htowutjeru hininipa retamtlu wan-rixa kamrurekanata!
Halikaka wane ntshinhi, wan-hixatshri towrertshi rutakko ptowruka htowutjeru himwaleru htowuxyawakapa.
Seyni towrertshi wla htshinahchinikanuxini rajiya: “Ha hohamokpotukananutkalu ntowutjeru.” Waneya hyinuwaka hiylakletna towrertshine, towretshrone koxa. Hiyrun-koxa tsru potuko hnika, rura, rimeta.
Hiyáhoni wale towrertshi towutjeru hma kahwajinitu hohne runanu. Hma malpokoxinutu hohne runanu. Htowutjeru yostajhitutanunru towrertshipni. Malixkaneyma ruknokona waneko rapnokaxikona.
— Hiyrun-koxa htowutjeru halukleru himatatshri seyni hma muhlepokotkanuklunru hkamrure hiyrunu hma kamhaknuklunru htowutjeru halukanru, hkotshipjetko hipokananu.
Seyni towrertshi, htowutjeru halukanru mimatkatu, hpupjexini pa hixanuya, rujhalu rapnokaxikowakapa seyni psotsonu hkotshipjexiko. Klu tshinanu katukta hixo henekka, hixo koxa rujhiko. Hiyrun-koxa hixo hitajikaluru, hixo ranjitko.
Kotspalaxikatshinwa Jesus Tshinanu PiranapniJesus wla tshinatnaka: — Nuna napnokaxyawaklu xye tshijne tshitshmeroyma. Hi pso haluklekananukta nixlu ralhiywakapa xye tshiji.
Nujhalu nyoptoxyawakaplu satu batiza-xikolu pixkalutu. Hiyáhoni nkojwakahchinikanuta hmakanhaknu pchinika.
Hixlahe kahwaklu nuna kihle hwachleru nanikanwakaxyawaklu xye tshijne? Seyni hike. Halikaka wane ntshinhi, nuna hi hihle hwachlu nenejyawakaphi seyni nuna nkotspalaxyawakaphi halikaka.
Klu tshinanu xawakni potuko cinco yine papji hwatshine kotspalahchinikanutkotka. Mapa yine hkamnitanna hepi. Hiyrunu wanna hepi kamnitanna wanna mapa yine.
Hirtshi kamnitanru hwuhene hiyrunu whentshi kamnitanru ruru. Hinrotshi kamnitanro tchitsho, tchitsho kamnitanro tunro. Hiyrun-koxa himajirotshi kamnitanro tomekanunro hiyrunu mekanunrotshi kamnitanro thimajiro.
Hipapkolkaka Himaxikolu PiranapniXye koxa htshinna Jesus yine hixolune: — Hixa hohimkohi heta palnalexini tkatshi himxijyawaka sreta waneya wla tshina, “Hinhetkopatkani.” Hiyrunu wane potuko rixa.
Hiyrun-koxa tkatshi mwiywakanu sreta ruchpajini kanniphalu, hixa wan-tshina: “Hameru hohnektapni.” Hiyrunu wane potuko rixa.
Hkamnitjene Hektunu Ramtakahchinikanyehixyawaka Piranapni— Haklu tshinanhe hixa hi nurehchinikanuxinwa hanurni kihle kamruru menu?
Ho satu yineru jihyehixinipyi raluk-haniklexinipyi jemahchinikanjexikowaka yehi. Wane hyamtkako pchini puhlemtanru wale pirana jemahchinikanjexikowaka yehi pmapokkanuko pchini, hipokananu hma manikkanuklunupyi. Heta mayxaklerewatatshri kapna yochmaklewjetatshri hma menejyawakanupyi. Kapna hitaklewjetatshri kapna mutajyawakanupyi.
Hiyrun-koxa wane ntshinyi, kapna putakkoklunupa hi puchpakanu waneya tiyiro ralujyawaka pso pma menekkanuklunuko pchini.
Mehchinikanutkatu Hiylaxikowakapa PiranapniWaneklu hohne koxa satkaka yine hinkaklu Jesus Galileia hajene pirana. Phuru Pilatos hima hiylakjixanna satkakni Galileia hajenni henekachalu hiylatkaluru Hoyakalu renekakanaxiniwa.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshina: — Hixlahe kahwaklu nyi Galileia hajenni pimrine Galileia hajene yohnik-hektunu rixyawaknina tshinanu wan-rixa salewnaletna?
Seyni hita wane ntshinhi, hike. Hma mehchinikanutkanuklunupa hixa ptowrunekhi, waneko pixka hixa hiylaletkona.
Ha hiyrun-koxa dezoito yinni tenopjiru yawnahohotanunni. Ruylatkanna. Hixlahe kahwaklu wannani pimrine ptowruneka Jerusalém poktshi hajene yohnik-majnakowatatshinnixkani?
Seyni wane ntshinhi, hike. Hma mehchinikanutkanuklunu hixa, ptowrunekhi waneko pixka hixa hiylatkotanu.
Figueira Muna Masahito PiranapniWaneya Jesus yapkaklu pirana rutaka: — Satu yineru pa kata figueira muna rutaka rusanate uva-cha yehi. Waneya wane hya hisahi rujhapyawakmaka. Seyni hikta rawa.
Waneya wla htshinru uva-cha hislahatshri: “Haha hetanu! Mapa mhale pchinika nujhasahtaplu xye muna seyni haté xawakni hi kasahpirlu. Hiyáhoni xawakni pkayikanutkalu. Klu rimimaletachatlu tshiji?”
Seyni uva-cha hislahatshri wan-tshinru: “Nutsrukate, xye mhaleyakatshi wetanru. Njitoskotanrutshi waneya tshkipahitshi nutakaskotanru.
Hsahiwaxinipa kihleplu. Seyni wane hmixkanuklunupa pkayikajixanru halikaka.”
Jesus Hitskalajyawaklo Suxo Hapnanuxikalur-hohne PiranapniSatu hapnanuxikalur-hohnetnaka Jesus hasruklewakanata satu hanjihohnewakapjiya.
Waneya sato suxo satu kamtshi yeyixkaklewatatshri twiya. Dezoito mhale pchinika hyeyixkaklo wala suxo. T-satkokanatka. Hi tumukata potukawleta hi psotsonujijiko.
Waneya rexiniklunutkalo Jesus, htomhalo. Waneya wane htshinatkalo suxo: — Suxo, pyeyixale hichotanropyi.
Himyo wala hoho rutaka, waneya chinpotukawa tpotukawamtatka. Waneya timalwutatkalu Hoyakalu.
Seyni hanjihohnewakapji kosekatshri himtuwnahchinikanuta klu tshinanu Jesus pinrewata hapnanuxikalur-hohne waneya wla htshinna yine wane hapatjekanaxikatshine: — Waneru seis hohne rumukata kamrurewlexyawaka yineru. Hiyáhoni kamrurtshi hohnekaka hinanu hpinixikowaka hijhiywakapa seyni hapnanuxikalur-hohne hike.
Seyni Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus wla tshinru: — Hixachatatshinhi, hi he hixa ptowrunekhi hipra boi ho burro hkochpiroka hapnanuxikalur-hohne hiyrunu hanikna maleka sreta honha rurapyawakapna pratshine?
Hiyrunu xawakni twu suxo Abraão-ni klopicha. Satanás kachitanro dezoito mhale pchinika. Hiyáhoni kluneru tshinanhe hi tumukata hichotkota xye tkachikanaxikolu hapnanuxikalur-hohne?
Waneya Jesus kamnitjene ptowrunniko patewatana Jesus wan-tshinyawakna tshinanu. Seyni pimrine yine hixolune hpoyikowatna himyekaklewatatshrikaka Jesus kamhaleru tshinanu.
Mostarda-tataji PiranapniWaneya Jesus wan-tshina: — Kluneru pixka rixa Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka? Kluneru nyapkakletanru?
Mostarda-tataji pixka rixa. Satu jeji haniklo. Rusanate rutaklo. Ttseruwna, hahmuna tixnawa. Waneya kochitshine teno yapatshine hina, hkamhachaletna hiplu hohoya.
Chitshponatshri PiranapniHiyrunukotnaka wla htshina Jesus: — Kluneru nyapkakletanru Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka?
Tserutatshri pixka rixa. Sato suxo hwalu. Mapa chiwatupso trigo pahi tyapjetlu haté psolujpako chitshponatka.
Mtseruswa Hiphaptotetu PiranapniWaneya pa poktshikaka, tsru poktshikaka, mtserutu poktshikak-koxa hyapamtatka Jesus. Rasruklewakananumta. Jerusalém poktshi nwaka hyamta.
Waneya satu yineru hepomhalu, wla htshinru: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, mixon-koxlahe yine hiwekkako? Waneya Jesus wan-tshinna:
— Hyahot-jihlokletanu mtseruswa hiphaptotetu. Klu tshinanu halikaka ntshinhi. Hixolunemka haluka jihlokletanu seyni hi rumukatanruna.
— Kapjiru palnanu, hiphapto ruchyatanu. Waneya hixa hiphapto maleka sreta hwanu, hiphaptomka hitpetanu wla htshinreyma: “Tsru Hixikatshriwa, pjihlokkakanwu.” Seyni wale hihitanhi, wla htshinanhi: “Hi nimathi hanu sretakta hichpajikatshinhi.”
Waneya hixa wla tshinanu: “Hixa pixayma mitshi nikatshinwu. Wipoktshi mitshi pasruklewaxya.”
Hexiniklunpatkana Abraão-ni, Isaque-ni, Jacó-ni, hiyrun-koxa pimrinni Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshinni ptowrunnika Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka rawyawakna seyni hixapni maleka sreta hwininapa waneya rawanu tsru tshiyahlu haskiyhiru koxa.
Hixolune yine hinanu, tkatshi hichpajyawaka sreta, rimxijyawaka sreta, pa sta sreta hpotukle sreta ruchpajinna. Nikjexikowaka yehi Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hwatshri htuplatanna.
Himatanru xye. Rapkatle hwatshri kosekanutka. Hiyrun-koxa kosekakanatatshri hapkatatanutka.
Jesus Jerusalém Poktshi Ruchinijyawaka PiranapniWaneya waneklu satkaka fariseu yanwakatlu Jesus. Wla htshinruna: — Hewi pasujinixka klu tshinanu phuru Herodes haluk-hiylaletyi.
Waneya Jesus wla tshina: — Hajewa. Wale kaweretshi pixkalutu nwaka hyanu. “Kamtshine nuchpakkaka hiyrunu yeyixatshine nutskalakjeta xawakni hohne, yetshikawa koxa wane nixanu. Halikaka map-hohne rixinripa nali kamruretanutka.” Xye xako hinkakanru.
Klu tshinanu nujhalu natnu hapote nomkahixyawaka xawakni, yetshikawa wale pnut-hohne. Klu tshinanu halikakni Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri hi rumukata hipnaleta Jerusalém poktshi minjeya.
— Jerusalém, ha Jerusalém! Puylajetna Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine hiyrunu pimrinni pixa nwaka hyokanatanunni Hoyakalu psotlujeta! Hixo katmaka naluka kapolethi ho sapriklethi patlapa tapatjewhenexini pixka! Tomeji hpuko tutajinna pixka. Seyni pixa hi hitshitno.
Himatanru xye. Xawakni hipji hichotkalurutka. Halikaka ntshinyi. Hi hiyrunu petanutkano haté wla ptshininipa: “Hoyakalu hihlehchinikanutlu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hiwaka hinikatshri.”
Jesus Yeyixatshri Rutskalajyawaka PiranapniWaneya satu hapnanuxikalur-hohnetnaka Jesus jihloklu fariseu-pji fariseu-ne kosekatshripji wane hnijyawakapa. Ruslahluna Jesus klu hkamhanu.
Satu jeji hanokatshri walestsi hwakanata.
Waneya Jesus hepomhana Moisés yonreru pirana himatpotutatshine hiyrunu fariseu-ne, wla htshin-hepomhaletna: — Hinanchitkalurlahe hapnanuxikalur-hohne hitskalaklewlu ho hike?
Seyni potshkena. Hiyáhoni Jesus kosetlu jeji waneya rutskalaklu. Waneya hyokanatlu hyiywakapa.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinna: — Satkaka hixa ho hiwhene ho hipra boi kapna hijrujini hi he hkochtshekanru hapnanuxikalur-hohne?
Seyni hi rimat-hihitluna.
Mayohotu, Kchinikanuru PiranapniJesus hislahakanatna yine niklu hitshanixkalune ho tuplawakkaka kihleru mesa yehi hwatshrirhe hnuretanna. Waneya satu yapkaklu runkakna niklu hitshanixkalune. Wla htshinna:
— Htshanixkoklunupa hnunrowatatshri nikle yehi, hi hnuretanru tuplawaka hijhakaluru wane htuplaxyawakapa. Pa katako pixa yohnika tsru kahwakpiratkaluru koxa tshanixka.
Waneya hyanwakaxinipyi htshanixjeru waneya wla htshininipyi: “Penek-tuplawakletanru xye.” Waneyakni patewatatshrinapyi ppalnanatka tuplawaka hapkatlutu ptuplata.
Seyni ptshanixkoklunupa, hapkatlutu hapkako ptuplatanutka. Waneya runinipa ptshanixjeru, wla htshininipyi: “Nomole, kihlewakayaka ptuplatanu.” Waneklu pukchikhihlenutko ptowruneka piminkakjene.
Klu tshinanu katukta kahwakpiratkaluru hitajinwa, malukkotu rutakko wale. Seyni malukkotu hi kahwajikatshriwa, hkahwakpiratka wale.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinru htshanixjeru: — Niklu pkamhini, hanikaj-hohne ho kayi koxa, hi ptshanixanna pimatletlene, ho pimolene, ho petjejrene phurune, ho pimwastsitanune tsonu. Klu tshinanu wane pixini pa katako wanna koxa hapnutanyi pixa. Waneya kihleru pkamhaleru tshinanu rapnutankoxyina pixa.
Seyni tsru niklu pkamhinipa, hike mwikane, myapene, myankane hiyrun-koxa mayhalene ptshanixanu.
Waneya hihlewahchinikanyehitkalurupyi wanna pma poyaho hapnuretjene tshinanu. Seyni halikaka Hoyakalu hapnutanyi kihleru kamhaklerune hiwekkajikolu hohnepa.
Tsru Niklu PiranapniWaneya satu Jesus himinkakjeru jemlu xye pirana waneya wane htshina: — Kihle hchinikanurunepni Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka nikawakle tuplatatshinepa.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Satu jeji tsru niklu hkamha. Hixo yine htshanixa.
Rapokpapkoluxinixka hyokanatlu htowreru wla htshinyawakapna tshanixkalunetka mitshi: “Hinanu, ralixatka.”
— Seyni satkaka pnu pejnu hixahchinikanuta. Hyinuwaka hallikakletna. Tshanixkalurutka mitshi wla tshina: “Tshiji nanjita. Nujhalu wane nyiywakapa, netapyawakaplu. Hiyáhoni nanjityi pma mukolujyawakanupno.”
— Waneya satuko wan-tshinatnaka: “Dez boi-ne nanjita carro himat-kosetatshine. Wanna nwakakni nyamtatka netapyawakapna. Nanjityi pma mukolujyawakanupno.”
— Waneya satutnaka wan-tshin-koxa: “Nhanunrowatatka hiyáhoni hi numukata wane yaleta.”
— Waneya towrertshi satokatka. Hyokanatjeru runkakatka htshintokanuxyawakna htshanixlenemka. Waneya kapjiru jihekanuwata. Wla htshinru htowreru: “Hajewa pchiretanu. Tsru poktshi nwaka pyanu. Ptowru pantshi hapkaka tsru hapolu, mtser-hapot-koxa pyanu. Pwapanna hike mwikane, myapene, mayhalene, myankane.”
Waneya wla htshinru htowutjeru: “Haté hehe. Pyanutnaka ptowru hapokaka nwaka haté kahnete hapojijkak-koxa nwaka. Yine hipokananu pjihlokjixanu, nopji htsepoxinripna.
Klu tshinanu wane ntshinyi halikaka. Hi satukna wanna jejine mitshikananu ntshanixlenemka hetumhanru nnijitu!”
Jesus Hasruklene Haluk-hixlexikatshriwa PiranapniHixolune yine himotsakanatlu Jesus. Jesus hiprotakatka waneya wane htshinna:
— Katukta haluka nasrukleru hixletanu seyni ruru ho runro ho hhanunro ho hiwhenene ho himolene jejine ho himolene suxone ho haté waleko riwekle hmahnanutkanuklunu, hi rumukata nasrukleru hixleta.
Hiyrun-koxa katukta h-cruz-te hma mutaykopitkanuklunupa hi rumukata nasrukleru hixleta.
Kathe hixa satkakhi pantshi tenopjiru haluka kamhalexini seyni mitshikananhapka hma muchinikanuwatkanuklunu hma mutakyahokwenrutkanuklunru ho rumukata nikat-kamhaletluhe ho hike?
Wane hmixkanuklunupa, tenopjiru hkamhapirreru hyinuwakachatlu seyni hi hnikata kamhaletlu. Waneya ptowruneka hetatshine heyikanru. Wla htshinanruna:
“Haha hetanu. Xye jeji panawaphutata seyni hi hnikata kamhaletlu!”
— Ho hanukananru phuru satu phuruyma hiylalewpiratatshri, muchinikanuwhapkatkatu ho rumukata yahotletnahe hyanwakatjenepa vinte mil soldado-ne himwatshriyma, dez mil tsonu himwatshriyma?
Wla hmixkanuklunupa, howukakowana htowrene hyokanata riynumsakajyawakapna kihle hwachle rixyawakapna pirana.
— Hiyrun-koxa katukta hi hiknoklu ptowru potuka rimwaleru hi rumukata nomkahitjeru hixleta.
Hma Tuwrenuklunutka Tuwu Piranapni— Kihlemkalu tuwu. Seyni hma tuwrenuklunutka, kluneru tuwutkotka?
Hike kihleyatkalu. Hi tshijiko kihleylu, hi tshkiko kihle yapjetkotkalu. Seyni ruknokachatkatka. Katukta kajnakopnapa hyijnakoxyawaka hyijnakotanru.
Ovelha Pupjetatshro PiranapniWaneyatnaka rapokastsitluna Jesus hixo jijhawenruklerune hiyrun-koxa hektutu kamhaklerune hyijnakoxyawakapluna.
Waneya fariseu-ne hiyrun-koxa kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine jiheklu Jesus. Wla htshinanwakatluna: — Xye jeji hiyanna hektutu kamhatshine. Hiyrun-koxa wannayma hnika.
Hiyáhoni Jesus yapkaklu pirana runkakna. Wla htshinna:
— Hanurutkanhe jeji cem ovelha rimwini seyni sato ramtajini, hi he pimri hiprane noventa e nove, ruknokamtanu kahnete poktshi rujhapyawakaplo pupjetatshro haté rukchijini potuklo?
Waneya rukchijiniplo ovelha hamhakanatatshro, hpoyikowpotuta. Rutjitanro
haté hipji yehi. Htomhana rimatletanune rimwastsitanune. Waneya wla htshinna: “Himuwatanu hitayma klu tshinanu nopra ovelha hamhakanatatshro nukchikatka.”
— Hiyáhoni wane ntshinhi tenhohney-koxa rawanu tsru poyikowlu potuko satupka hektuwaka kamhatshri hehchinikanuxiklu tshinanupa noventa e nove-pna yine potuka hchinikanurune, hehchinikanru mujhakanetka.
Tiyiro Proji Hamhatshro Piranapni— Suxo dez proji prata kamhikolu himwatshro, pa projipka tamhini, hi he tujhanru? Tumukata hikchiklexyawakaplo lamparina tnikotanu, pantshi t-satolotanu, tujhapotutanro haté tukchikanro.
Waneya tukchijiniklunuplo ttshanixanna timatletanune, timwastsitanune wla ttshinna: “Himuwatanu hitayma klu tshinanu nukchiklo ntiyirote proji hamhakanatatshro.”
— Wane ntshinhi halikaka, waneko pixka rixa himuwletna hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrene tenhohne hajene, rehchinikanuxini satu yineru hektuwaka kamhatshri.
Whentshi Pupjetatshri PiranapniJesus wla tshinatnaka: — Hepi whenru satu jeji.
Waneya hepurtshi wan-tshinru ruru: “Papa, xawakni penekanutkano psoji hitanupakotka.” — Hiyáhoni tsru kanipretatkalu wanna hepi hiwhenene himlujikolu.
Waneya hi hix-hohne potuwani hepurtshi ptowruka rihnanutamtatka. Howuk-tshijne nwaka hyatka. Waneya wane hsalechaxyalo ptowruka rimwakanatanru, ptowru hixatshri poyikowluyma.
— Waneya ptowruniko hsalexinixka, tsru natshi hakanhatka rawyawaka tshijneya. Hyinuwaka yijnako mahlerewatanatka.
Waneya hyinuwaka yanretatka. Kamrurtshi rujhapyawakatka rawatshijnetanru yehiya. Waneya rukchik-kamruretka hiyáhoni campo porco-ne yehi hyokanatka porco-ne rohluxyawakapa.
Raluk-hinanutlexnamkawa porco-ne nijitumka raluka nikleta. Seyni waleni hike renekna.
Nsatkaphetkotanu nurupji nwaka. Wla hetko ntshinanru: ‘Papa, nektuwyehitatkalu Hoyakalu hiyrunu pix-yehi koxa.
Hiyáhoni hi numukatatka pituru ntshinikolpatka. Satu ptowreru pixka pixkakanno.’ ”
Hiyáhoni hpalnamta. Hsatokatka rurupji nwaka. Seyni ruru howukako rexyalu. Retwamonutlu. Rasukanwakatlu, hsapriklu, ramlutlu.
Waneya hituru wan-tshinru: “Papa, nektuwatatka Hoyakalu hetanu, pixa hetan-koxa. Hi numukata pituru tshinretkotka. Satu ptowreru pixka pixkakanutkano.”
— Seyni ruru towutna htowrene, wla htshinna: “Wuya, hchiretanu, mkatshri hopowalu kihleru hwapanu. Hyochmakanru. Hiyrun-koxa anel putakamyojitanru, sandalha hyochmakjixitanru.
Boi whene hixownakakaluru hwapanu. Hiylatanru. Tsru niklu wkamhanu. Wpoyikowatanu.
Klu tshinanu xye noturu nupnaholerutka hiwekhonukatnaka, hamhakanatatshri hiphujewnatka.” — Waneya hyinuwaka poyikowletna.
— Wane pchinika hituru tsrujru hsana hwakanata. Waneya pantshistsi rapojinixka hjemlu tokluru, hahsalu.
Hiyáhoni satu towrertshi htomha. Repomhalu klunerni.
— Waneya wale wla tshinru: “Pepuru hapokatka. Pantshitkalu kihle hapokle rixa. Hiyáhoni puru boi whenni hixownakakaluru ruylakjixa.”
— Seyni whentshi tsrujru jihekanuwata. Hi hjihlokpirata. Hiyáhoni ruru hichpakanwakatlu. Hjihlokjixlu.
Seyni whentshi tsrujru wla tshinru tsru: “Ha, hi pejnu mhalekananu nepixyi, towutachatkaluru pixka. Hikeklu ptokanu nmajnakowaxya. Wanepnawaka hikeklu penekno carneiro whene nimatletanuneyma npoyikowaxyawakapa.
Seyni xye pituru pnikat-hejnunkatetjeru, suxone jejiheroneya, runatka pumuylatlu boi whene hixownakakaluru.”
— Waneya tsru wan-tshinru whentshi tsrujru: “Noturu, pixa ptowru hohneka himwanno. Ptowru potuko nimwaleru pixanni.
Seyni wujhatkalu xye poyikowlu wkamhiywaka, wpoyikowaxyawaka. Klu tshinanu xye pepuru hipnatshrikananni hiwekatka. Hamhakanatatshrini seyni hikchikalurutkani.”
Pantshi Muhle Hislahletkatu PiranapniWla koxa htshinatkana rasruklene Jesus: — Rawa satu jeji phuru. Ktowreru pantshi hinotatshri. Xye towrertshi jihyehitkatka, hsalethimatlu rutsrukate hejnunkate.
Hiyáhoni htomhalu waneya wla htshinru: “Klunhe xye njempiranyehityi? Puhlepokotanru pantshi pinotjexyawaka pirana. Klu tshinanu hewi hi pumukata hinotlepjitatka.”
— Waneya pantshi hinotakanatatshri wan-tshina hitoko hchinikanuya: “Klu nkamhanutka xawakni? Klu tshinanu ntowutjeru yokanatno. Hi kmixkonno njitoxyawaka. Npatewata tiyiro nanjijechaxyawaka.
Hehe, nimata klu nkamhanu, nuchpajinpatka xye kamrurtshi pantshi ninoxyawaka, nyoptohihlenutkoklunupa pimrine yehiya.”
— Hiyáhoni repukna satkaka htowutakanatjeru deve-tatshine. Wla htshinatkalu mitshikananu hapokatshri: “Hi pejnuhe p-deve-tlu ntowutjeru?”
— Waneya wale wan-tshina: “Cem stono nhihtshi n-deve-tlu.” — Waneya pantshi hinotatshri wan-tshinru: “Xyetkani papel-mta p-conta-te pirana. Ptuplatanu waneya cinquenta stono pejnu tsonu pyonatanu.”
— Waneya pantshi hinotatshri wla tshinru satu deve-tatshritnaka: “Ha pixa, hi psolhe p-deve-ta?” — Waneya wale hihitlu: “Cem chiwatu trigo-ji n-deve-ta.” — Waneya pantshi hinotatshri wan-tshinru: “Wuya, oitenta chiwatupso pyonatanu.”
— Waneya phuru hikchikhihlenutatkalu pantshi muhle hislahletkatu rimatkalnu tshinanu. Waneya Jesus wla tshina: — Yine, xye hohne hwatshine, yine katawaka hwatshine yohnik-jimatkalerunni xye tshiji hajeru piranaya.
Hiyáhoni wla ntshinhi: Hikchikanru himatletleru xye tshijne pohirewnaleyma. Waneya wale pohirewnalu nikawninipa, hyoptotkona hwikowaka hikeklu mnikawnakatu yehiya.
Katukta psotsonuyaka kihle kamrureya, tsrur-tshinan-koxa kihle kamrurru. Hiyrun-koxa katukta hi kihle hislahle psotsonu tshinanu, tsrur-tshinan-koxa waneko pixka rixa.
Klu tshinanu muhle hislahletkane hixini xye tshijne pohirewnale tshinanu, kathe xawaka munanhanhi pohirewnalu halikakalutu tshinanu?
Hiyrun-koxa pimrine hejnunkateyma mpoyahokaka kamruretkane hixini, kathe henekanhi hixanpako?
— Hi satukna yineru towrertshi walerutu himukata kamhaletlu hepi phurune kamrure. Klu tshinanu rahnanutanru satu, satu ramotanu; ho satu repiretanu, satu reyikanu. Hixa hi himukata kkamrurewaklerune hixleta Hoyakalu tshinanu hiyrunu pohirewlu tshinanu.
Jesus Hichinikakjetna Yine Satkaka Hiykolu YonatkaluruSeyni fariseu-ne xye pirana jematshine heyiklu Jesus klu tshinanu ramotlona tiyiro.
— Moisés hiykole pirana yonatkaluru hiyrun-koxa mitshikawlunni Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshinni hinkakle hwatka haté João Batista klu papko. Waneya waneklukananuko, kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka pirana, hinkakletka. Ptowrunek-yine yapretaklu wane hjihlojyawakapna.
— Myapretpotni tenhohne hiyrunu tshiji nikawniywakapa seyni Moisés hiykole pirana yonatkaluru yáholu pa yonhajiji hi nikawnanu.
— Ruchohnunroxini jeji, satoko hhanunroxini rimopatatkalo. Hiyrun-koxa katukta hanunrotlo, hichotkaluro rimopatlewata.
Phuru Hiyrunu Lázaro Piranapni— Rawa satu jeji phuru. Kihleru mkatshri rutakjetatka ptowru hohneruka kihleru hiweklu rimwa.
Raw-koxa satu jeji hike mimwakatu kachreru, Lázaro hiwakatletatshri. Phurupji hiphaptotestsi rutakka.
Waneya Lázaro haluka nikletlu phuru nijitu h-mesa-te hijrujikatshri. Haté kawene hapokastsitlu Lázaro, remrotluna rutsreru.
Waneya wan-rixatka. Lázaro-ni kwamonurni hipnanatka waneya hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrene tenhohne hajene hanikatkalu Abraão-ni nwaka. Waneya phurni koxa hipnanatka. Waneya hkapnatka.
Phurni salewnapotutana tshitshmeroya. Retlu Abraão-ni howuk-potuko rawa, retkoxlu Lázaro Abraão-nistsi.
Waneya hsaplewata phurni: “Nutsrukatni Abraão-ni, petwamonutanno! Pyokanatanru Lázaro-ni, himyoji ruhakamtanu waneya runanu ruhakanrutanunno klu tshinanu nsalewna hewi tshitshmeroya!”
— Seyni Abraão-ni wan-tshinru: “Noturu, puchinikanru piwekakanaxini ptowruka kihleru pimwakanata seyni Lázaro salewnajekanata. Hiyáhoni xawakni wale hewiru hpoyikowahchinikanuta seyni pixa salewnanu.
Hiyrun-koxa hewi hixa hanikajite rawa tenotlowaka hiyáhoni wanna hewi hajene pixa nwaka yapiratatshinemka hi rumukata koprurenwakatyina hix-yehi, hi koxa hix-yehi hajene himukata koprurenwakatwu hixa.”
— Waneya phurni wan-tshina: “Wan-rixini Nutsrukatni Abraão-ni, nanjityi Lázaro-ni xako pyokanatanu nurupji nwaka hyiywakapa.
Klu tshinanu kamolno cinco jejine. Pitshitanru Lázaro-ni wane hyiywakapa ruykoxyawakapna wanna hma munyawakanupna hewi salewnikowaka.”
— Seyni Abraão-ni hihitlu: “Pimolene himwalu Moisés tokanu hiyrun-koxa pimrine Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine hiykoxyawakapna. Hiyáhoni wannako hyijnakotanna.”
— Seyni phurni hihitlu: “Hike, Nutsrukatni Abraão-ni, seyni satni yinerni hiwejinpatnaka waneya wan-hixatshri hiykoxinipna waneya rehchinikanhetkotanumkana rektunnuyna.”
— Seyni Abraão-ni wan-tshinru: “Moisés yonreru hiyrunu pimrine Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine hma malixkanuklunna, hi koxa ralixanruna yinerni hipnatshri yotunoxiklu.”
Hektuntshi Hiyrunu Ramtakahchinikanyehixikolu PiranapniWaneya Jesus wla tshinna hnurrene: — Hi rumukata himaletkota hitspetkalurukaka hma wiywakanupa. Seyni hektumkalu wale yineru kojwakahchinikanrewatatshri!
Kihlepotmaklu tsru sotlu rostunojixikowaka waneya mar powha ruknojikowaka hma pupjekajyawakanupna mtserkakanewa.
Hixanuko hislahinwa! Pimwastsireru hektuwaxini punkakanru jikolukanuru rixyawaka. Rehchinikanuxinipa hamtakahchinikanuxinri rektunu.
Sete kata rektuwyehixinipyi pa hohne tshinanu seyni sete katako rapokanwakaxinipyi wla htshininipyi: “Nehchinikanutatka”, waneya pamtakahchinikanutanru rektunu.
Halixlu PiranapniWaneya nuretkalune wla tshinru Jesus: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, ptserut-halixletanwu.
Waneya Jesus wla tshina: — Mostarda-tataji pso rixiniklunu halixle waneya himukata xye figueira muna wla tshinreta, mutakkotu muna, “Pkopkolijinwa. Mar powha putajinwa.” Waneyamka wane potuko rixanu.
Towrertshi Kamhalerupa PiranapniWaneya Jesus wla tshina: — Hixa satkakhi htowreru hsana yochyakakanatatshri, ho campo kamrurewakanaxikatshri pantshi rapojini hixa hi wla tshinru: “Punanu ptuplatanu nikawaka yehi.” — hi htshinru.
Hi he wla htshinhonuklu: “Nijittshi pkamhanu. Mkatshri nijittshi hikamhapi pmakatanu waneya punanu nijittshi putajinno. Nnikka pchinika nurka pchinika pinotanno. Nali niklexini tsonu pnikanu, puranu”? Hi he xawaka wlako htshinru htowreru?
Towrertshirhe xawaka poyahnutka ruhlenu kamrure tshinanu? Hike.
Hiyáhoni hix-koxa ptowru potuko htowuxikowaka hali kamhalexini, wla htshinanu: “Hixa towrertshinwu hike hepixatshinwu. Klu tshinanu wtowuxikolupka wkamha.”
Jesus Dez Hijirohitutatshine Rutskalajyawaka PiranapniWaneya wla rixatka Jesus. Jerusalém poktshi nwaka hyamxini Samaria hiyrunu Galileia tshinikowaka tshijne hyapamtatka.
Waneyakta satu poktshi hjihlokamxinixka dez jejine hijirohitutatshine yoptotaplu. Howukako hyopkakna.
Hsaplewatna: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus, petwamonutanunwu!
Waneya satu wanna, Samaria-nerni, rexinixkawa rutskalhiywakatka, hsatoka, tsru tokantshiyma rimalwumtlu Hoyakalu.
Waneya Jesus jixistsi hyoptsojitamta waneya hpoyahnutlu.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Hatshni dez-na hitskalakalune? Seyni ha pimrine nove, hanhe hyatkana?
Klu tshinanhe xye jeji tsonu, pa neruko satoka Hoyakalu rimalwuxyawakapa?
Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Ppalnanu. Pyanutka. Putskalhatka palixle tshinanu.
Hoyakalu Pohirewaxyawaka Hapojinri PiranapniWaneya satkaka fariseu-ne hepomhalu Jesus hikluplu Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka. Waneya Jesus hihitna, wla htshinna: — Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hapojiklu hi phujetkalurupa yine yhaleya.
Hike yineru himukata wan-tshinretlu: “Hetanu, hewitkalu”, ho “Hawlalu”. Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hixa hitokote rawa.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinatkana rasruklene: — Rapokpapkoluxinipa hixa haluk-hetletanru Jeji Whene tshinkaluru klu papkopa yáholu pa hohnejiji. Seyni hi hetanru.
Wla htshininiphina: “Hetanu, wanetkalu” ho “Hewiru”. Hi wane hyanu. Hi homkahitanna.
Klu tshinanu rawrakle pixka rixanu, pa sreta hyinuwaka hawraklexini haté pa sreta hohne rapokhawrakletsatanu. Waneko pixka rixanu Jeji Whene tshinkaluru hapojinri hohnepa.
Seyni mitshikananhapka rujhalu hsalewniywaka hiyrun-koxa ruknokko xye hohne hiwekatshine klu papko.
Noé klu papko pixka rixanu Jeji Whene tshinkaluru hapojinri papkopa.
Klu tshinanu ptowrunniko yinni hniknina, rurnina, hhanunrowatnina, hhanuruwatnina, Noé-ni tsro kanawatlo jihlojinriklu potukananuko. Waneya runatka hahyekachalu, ptowrunnika yinni hnikata.
Ló tshinkalurni klu papko koxa waneko pixka rixa. Hniknina, rurnina, hmaronewatnina, rutaklewatnina, hpanawatnina.
Ló tshinkalurni hichpajin-hohne potuko, Sodoma poktshiya wan-rixanixkana. Waneya hina pixka rixa hijrukleta tenhohneya tshitshmero hiyrun-koxa enxofre. Ptowrunnik-yinni hnikata.
Waneko pixka rixanu Jeji Whene tshinkaluru ruphujewnin-hohnepa.
Waneklu hohnepa katukta pantshi hoho hwatshripa, rasukhapkatanu. Hi pantshi hjihlokanu rejnunkate pantshi hwatshri rawapyawakapa. Katukta campo hwanu, hi hsatkapanu hipji nwaka.
Hichinkapanro Ló tshinkaluru hnunroni.
Katukta haluk-hiwekkaklexinwa, ramtaklewatanun-honuka. Katukta hamtakanru riwekle riwekanu halikaka.
Wane ntshinhi: Wale yetshnopa hepi himumkakakatshinepni walerutu chetshiya. Satu hanikko, satupni hiknokamtkona.
Hepi suxone trigo-ji yojitatshinepa, sato hanikko, satopni hiknokamtkona.
Waneya rasruklene hepomhalu, wla htshinna: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus, hanhe rakanhini xye ptshinreru?
Waneya Jesus wla tshinna: — Hanukta rawamanetanuna hipnatshripni wane rapatjexinna maylune.
Hipnahnurutatshro Hepixikolu PiranapniWaneya Jesus satu yapkaklu pirana runkakna ranjihohnexyawakapna, hma muhrojyawakanupna.
Wla htshinatkana: — Pa poktshi rawa satu hetamayxaklerewatatshri. Wale hi piklu Hoyakalu. Yine koxa hi hkahwakpirata.
Wale poktshi twakanat-koxa sato hipnahnurutatshro. Waneya wale yehi tya. Wla ttshinru hetamayxaklerewatatshri: “Papnuyehitanno nkamnitjeru tshinanu!”
— Seyni hix-hohne hi repixlo. Waneya wale pnutetka wane htshinahchinikanuta: “Himka npiklu Hoyakalu. Hiyrun-koxa hi nkahwakpiratlu yineru.
Seyni twu hipnahnurutatshro kojwakjepotutno hiyáhoni napnuyehitanutkalo. Wane nmixkanuklunupa nupukalewatanutka wala hinjetatshro tshinanu.”
Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus wla tshin-koxa: — Hyijnakotanru klu htshina hetamayxaklerewatatshri mpomunanukotu.
Seyni wane ntshinhi, repixanna halikaka! Seyni rapojinipa Jeji Whene tshinkaluru halixlerhe rukchikanu xye tshijiya?
Fariseu Hiyrun-koxa Jijhawenrukleru PiranapniWaneya Jesus xye yapkaklu pirana htshin-koxa, yine kihle hikahwajikatshinwa hiyrunu pimrine reyikjetna.
Waneya wla htshina Jesus: — Hepi jejine yanwakatlu Hoyakalupji ranjihohnexyawakapna. Satu jeji fariseu hiyrunu satu jeji tiyiro kyoptokleru.
Waneya fariseu yotunotatka ranjihohnetatka walepka. Wla htshinnawa: “Ha, Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu npoyahnutyi hita hi pimrine pixka hixatshrino, wanna katshowhurune, hektutu kamhajetatshine, suxohewatatshine, haté xye tiyiro kyoptokleru pixka hi nix-hita.
Pa semankaka hepi kata hita hi nika hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu nenekjetlu psoji ptowruka nu.”
— Seyni tiyiro kyoptokleru howuka hyotunoxyatka, hi tenoko hyihatatka. Seyni rutpestaxnawa wane htshina: “Ha, Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu, petwamonutanno hitni hektuwaka kamhatshrino!”
Waneya Jesus wan-tshina: — Wane ntshinhi jeji mitshikananu hanjihohnetatshri hi ruhlehchinikanutka seyni hapkat-hanjihohneretatshri kihle hchinikanutka hsatkapa hipji nwaka Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakaluyma. Klu tshinanu katukta kihle rixahoxnawa mtserutu rixinixkawa seyni katukta mtserutu hixakanaxinwa htserutkotka.
Jesus Hiyrunu Mturune PiranapniWaneya mturunemka ranikanwakatka Jesus, kihle hwachalerunephi htshinikowakamkapna mturune seyni Jesus hasruklene hi hitshitna.
Waneya Jesus tomhana rasruklene. Wla htshinatkana: — Hetachatanna mturune hyanwakaxyawaknona. Hi himaletanna. Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hayinetene mturune pixkalune koxni wanna.
Wla ntshinhi halikaka: Katukta hi yoptotanru Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka mturu pixka, hi hjihlokanru.
Jeji Phuru PiranapniWaneya satu judeu tsrukakalu hepomhaplu Jesus, wla htshina: — Kasruklewakleru kihleru, klunerhe nkamhanu niwejinri hikeklu hohne nma nikawniywakanupa?
Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Haklu tshinanhe wane ptshinno kihle nixyawaka? Hikeni yineru kihleru, Hoyakalu tsonu kihleru hikeni hiyrunu.
Pimathonru hiykolu pirana: “Hi hapoklewatanu, hi puylalewatanu, hi ptshowhuwatanu, hi pimrine pweyatanu, pkahwakpiratanru puru, punro.”
Waneya phuru hihita: — Nmatureyakawa haté xawakni nomkahitlu xye hiykolu ptowruka.
Waneya hjeminixkalu Jesus xye ptowruka wla htshinatkalu: — Seyni satu pa hixanu pmaha kamhaletawa. Puchankanru ptowruka pimwanru, penekanna ptowruka mahaxikatshine. Wane pixa pohirewnaletanu tenhohneya. Waneya punanu, pomkahitanno hita.
Waneya wale pirana hyijnakoxinixka phuru, hwamonuwnapotuta klu tshinanu phurupotukni.
Waneya rexinixkalu Jesus hwamonuwnapotuxyawaka phuru, wla htshinru Jesus: — Hi pa yaprenukananru phurune Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hjihlojyawakapna!
Kyapreru camelo tsapujripna hjihlojyawaka seyni wane yohnik-yapren-potu phuru Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hjihlojyawaka.
Waneya wale pirana yijnakotatshine wla tshina: — Ha han-hixatshri hiwekkakko?
Waneya Jesus wla tshina: — Yine mumukatanutu, wale rumukata Hoyakalu.
Waneya Pedro wla tshina: — Petanu, ptowruka wuchota, pixa womkahixyawakatka.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinna: — Nmunanhalu ptowru yineru hipji hichotatshri, ho runro, ho ruru, ho himolene ho himolerone ho hhanunro, ho hiwhenene hichotatshri Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka tshinanu.
Wale yoptotanru yohnik-potu xawakni riwejinri hiyrun-koxa xye riwejinripa hinatshri hyoptotanru riwejinri hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa.
Jesus Hinkaklexyawaklu Rupninri PiranapniWaneya Jesus hanikna kahnete doze rasruklene, waneya wla htshinatkana: — Jerusalém poktshi nwaka wyamtanu. Wane poktshikni rakanhini ptowruka yonatkaluru tshinyawaka mitshi Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshinni yonre tshinyawaka pixka Jeji Whene pirana.
Klu tshinanu judeu mixkane renekko. Reyikko, rapnokatko, rutskahjetko.
Hkotshipjetko waneya ruylatko. Waneya map-hohne rixinri riwekanutnaka.
Seyni wanna hike pirana rimatjemna. Wanna rinanchixika xye pirana hiyáhoni hi rimatjematkaluna klu raluka tshinreta Jesus xye pirana tshinanu.
Jesus Mtsawa Hitskalajyawaka PiranapniWaneya Jericó poktshistsi rapojinixka Jesus satu mayhaletu hatnu tnumne tuplakanatatshri. Tiyiro hanjijetatshri.
Waneya hixolune yine hjema hiknohlexinixka, repomha: — Klunernihe?
Hiyáhoni hyinuwaka saplewleta, wla htshinjeta: — Jesus, phuru Davi-ni whene, petwamonutanunno.
Waneya kosekamtatshine hiykotlu potshke rixyawaka mtsawa; seyni wale wane pnute hsaplewjepotuta: — Phuru Davi-ni whene, petwamonutanunno hitni!
Waneya Jesus yopkaka. Waneya ranikjixlu wale nwaka. Waneya mtsawa Jesus-stsi rapojinixka repomhalu.
Wla htshinru: — Klunerhe paluka nkamhiywakyi? Waneya mtsawa hihitlu: — Kasruklewakleru, naluk-hetletatnaka hiyrunuko!
Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Petanutka. Palixle tshinanu putskalhatka.
Waneya waneklukawa retatka. Waneya mtsawakananu homkahitatkalu Jesus, Hoyakalu rimalwumta. Hiyrun-koxa ptowrunek-yine xye hetatshine yinuwaka himalwuretlu Hoyakalu.
Jesus Hiyrunu Zaqueu Tshinkaluru PiranapniWaneya Jesus Jericó poktshi hjihlokamta waneya hkoprutlu.
Waneya wanekananru satu jeji Zaqueu tshinkaluru. Waleni jijhawenruklerune chefe-te. Phurni wale.
Raluk-hetletlu Jesus hanu hixatshrini seyni hi rumukata hetletlu hixolune yine tshinanu klu tshinanu mtseruwnakatni.
Hiyáhoni pnuteyaka hya hasukleta. Waneya satu hahmuna ratskotatka rexyawakaplu Jesus. Klu tshinanu wane hyapamtanu.
Waneya rapojinixka Jesus wale yehi, teno hyihata Jesus. Waneya wla htshinru: — Zaqueu, hajewa pserpikhapkatanu klu tshinanu xawakni pipji naluk-hapokleta.
Hiyáhoni hchireta serpikleta Zaqueu. Hyoptotlu Jesus hpoyikonuyma.
Seyni pimrine hetakanatatshine kahemha. Wla htshinna: — Hektutu kamhatshripji rawanu.
Waneya ptowru yine hetanu hyopkaka Zaqueu tshinkaluru. Waneya wla htshinru Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus, petanu, hanikaji nimwaleru nenekanna hike mwikane. Hiyrun-koxa katuktako pa hixanu ntshowhuxya nyokwijreymalu, quatro kata pnute nsatkajinri.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Xawakniko hiweklu jihlokatkalu xyepji. Klu tshinanu Abraão-ni when-koxni wale.
Klu tshinanu Jeji Whene tshinkaluru hina hamhakanatatshri rujhiywakapa riwekkajyawakaplu.
Dez Ouro Proji PiranapniWaneya Jesus yapkaklu pirana runkakna, tokantshi jemakanatatshine. Klu tshinanu hi howukatkalu Jerusalém poktshi hiyrunu wanna kahwakatkalu Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hakanhahapkaxyawakpatka.
Hiyáhoni wla htshina Jesus: — Satu jeji phuru hijhalu pa tshijne hyiywakapa wale tshijne pohire rutajikowakpatka. Waneya hima hsatkapanu.
Seyni mitshikananhapka htomhanna hkamrurewkakjetanune dez-rune. Waneya pa projkaka ouro renekna satkaka. Waneya wla htshinna: “Hetanu hi psokta tiyiro himukata kamhaletanu wale projiyma haté napojini.”
— Seyni rawyawaka tshijne hajene hahnanutlu. Hiyáhoni hyokanatna wale hatjini tokantshi hanikatshine. Wla tshinatshine: “Hi walukyi pixa wwiywaka poktshi pohire pixyawaka.”
— Waneya rali yoptolexinixkalu hpohirewaxyawaka pa tshijneya, htshijne nwakako hsatokatnaka. Waneya hkamrurewkakjetanune ouro proji renekamtanune htomha rimaxyawakaplu hi psokta tiyiro hkayatatkana walaya.
Mitshikananu jeji hapokatka waneya wla htshina: “Nutsrukate, pa proji ouro penekamxyano, dez proji ouro wanetka.”
— Waneya phuru wan-tshinru: “Poyahnu, kihleru towrertshiyi. Psotsonu tshinanu kihle hislahlu pixlu. Hiyáhoni dez poktshi pohirepyi.”
— Waneya satu hinatnaka. Waneya wla htshina: “Nutsrukate, pa proji ouro penekamxyano, cinco proji ouro-tkalo.”
— Waneya wale koxa wla htshina phuru: “Pix-koxa cinco poktshi pohirepyi.”
Waneya satu hinatnaka, wla htshina: “Nutsrukate, xyetkani ouro proji penekamxyano, satupkalutu. Nimretlo, mkatshri sama npoyitlo.
Klu tshinanu npikyi, pix-honra jeji menekachalewakletyi. Pwiya pma kamhanutuko. Mutakatúkoyi hamlu.”
— Waneya wla htshinru: “Hektutu towrertshiyi. Pixako ptokanuko nukolukkakanunyi. Pimatnohe jeji menekachalewakletu nixyawaka? Nma kamhanutuko nimwiywaka hiyrun-koxa mutakkatukno hamyawaka?
Haklu tshinanhe hi banco putaklo ntiyirote tatskoxyawakapa? Wane pixkamka napojinitka nyoptotanmaklo tiyiro tsroyakalotka.”
— Seyni wanna wla tshina: “Seyni Tsru Hixikatshriwa, wale honra dez projine ouro rimwa!”
— Waneya wla htshina phuru: “Wla ntshinhi, tsru himwatshriko pnute renekko. Hiyrun-koxa hike mwikatu seyo rimwalerujiji hkonko.
Hiyrun-koxa nmalukjene hpohirna nmaluk-hixletjene hanikanna hewi. Hita hetanuko hiylatanna.”
Jesus Jerusalém Poktshi Jihlojyawaka PiranapniWaneya rali wan-tshinretatka Jesus, hyatka. Hkosekamtna Jerusalém poktshi nwaka.
Waneya Betfagé hiyrunu Betânia poktshikaka rapokastsixinixka, himriji Oliveiras tshinikowakastsi hyokanatna hepi rasruklene.
Wla htshinna: — Poktshi pnute hajeru nwaka hyanu. Waneya chinpotukawa hjihlokanru, hetanru jumento whene tsatkaluru hikeklu myapatjitkotuwa. Hkochpirokanru wale, hanikanru wkata.
Seyni satu yineru hepomhiniphi haklu wla himixa waneya wla htshinanna: “Kasruklewakleru haluklu.”
Waneya hyatkana Jesus yokanrene. Rukchikluna htshinakanaxyawak-potuko.
Hkochrijinixkaluna jumento whene kaprane hepomhana, Haklu hikochriklu jumento whene?
Waneya wane htshinna: — Kasruklewakleru haluklu.
Waneya rasruklene Jesus nwaka ranikluna jumento whene. Waneya himkalna jumento-tji hoho rutakna. Waneya Jesus waletji rutakatkana.
Riknohamtka pchinika Jesus, yine koprakamkata hatnu hapo.
Waneya Jerusalém poktshistsi rapojinixka, Oliveiras-pjita yopikjexikowaka, hixolune yine romkahitjene himuwata. Hyinuwaka himalwuretluna Hoyakalu. Hsaplew-himalwuretluna ptowru retakanatanruna, hetkalurkaka tshinanu.
Wla htshinna: — Himalwutkalurni Pohirtshi, Tsru Hixikatshriwa hiwaka hinikatshri! Kihle hwachalu rixanu tenhohneya! Tenoya hoyakawaxikowaka!
Waneya satkaka fariseu-ne hixolune yine himwakanatatshine wan-tshinru Jesus: — Kasruklewakleru, putshrokjixanna pasruklene.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinna: — Halikaka wane ntshinhi, nyi potshke hixinipa seyni sotlune saplewatanu.
Jesus Tshiyahaxyawaka Jerusalém Poktshi Tshinanu PiranapniWaneya Jerusalém poktshistsi rapojinixka Jesus, rexinixkalu htshiyahata wale poktshi tshinanu.
Wla htshinakteta Jesus: — Ha! Himatkamka, haté xawakniko, himukata hikchikletlu kihle hwachalu! Seyni xawakni hi pumukata hetletlu.
Klu tshinanu pa hohne runanna pkamnitjene, tshiji hjitotanna hkamnixyawakyina papkopa. Hsajrukanyina. Ptowru sretako rerutanyina.
Hyotkakanyina hiyrun-koxa pixa hitokote hwatshinepni. Hi satukna sotlu hwahohokakanu klu tshinanu hi pimathetlu Hoyakalu hepixlepir-hohne.
Jesus Hoyakalupji Rapkapyawaka PiranapniWaneya Hoyakalupji hjihlokamta Jesus. Hyinuwaka maleka yokanretna hichanrewatatshine.
Wla htshinna: — Wla htshina yonatkaluru Hoyakalu pirana: “Nopji hanjihohnewakapjini.” Seyni hixa katshowhurune hwiywaka hkamhiyatkalu!
Jesus ptowru hohneruka hasruklewjekanata Hoyakalupjiya. Tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne, kasruklewaklerune, hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine hiyrun-koxa judeu-ne tsru hixikatshinwa haluk-hiylaletmaklu Jesus.
Seyni hi rukchikluna hanu potu rixa hiylaletanruna. Klu tshinanu ptowrunek-yine haluka jemlepotutlu Jesus tokanu.
Jesus Tsru Potu Hitakkalurni PiranapniWaneya pa hohne Jesus Hoyakalupji hasrukakanaxyana yine, kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana, tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne, kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine, hiyrun-koxa tsrukakalune judeu-ne hapokanwakatlu.
Waneya repomhaluna: — Punkakanwu hanhe ruchpajya ptowutjeru xyekaka pkamhiywaka? Kathe henekyi xye tsru hitakkaluru?
Waneya Jesus wan-tshin-hihretna: — Hit-koxa satu hepomhalu nixanhi hixa. Hinkakanno xako.
Kathe xawaka towutlu João h-batiz-lewaxyawaka? Ho Hoyakalu ho jeji?
Waneya hyinuwaka hiynumsakakletna wannakakluko. Waneya wla htshinkakna: — Wla wtshininri Hoyakalu, waneya repomhanunwu: “Haklu tshinanhe hi halixlu João?”
Wale tshinanu wanna wla tshina hi hima rimatna hanu ruchpajyatka wale towuwlu.
Hiyáhoni Jesus wla tshinna: — Hit-koxa hi hinkakanhi hanukta ruchpajya xyekaka ntowuxijeru.
Hsana Kamrurewaxikatshine Hektu Kamrurerune PiranapniWaneya Jesus yinuwaka hinkakletanna yine satu yapkaklu pirana: — Satu jeji yinuwaka hitakletlu uva. Waneya hsana hislahatshine renekamta. Waneya pa tshijne howuka hya. Hix-hohne ramha.
Waneya rapokpapkoluxinixka ramikolu, jitakleru yokanatlu satu htowreru hitaklucha hislahatshine nwaka honantshi rawapyawakapa. Seyni hitaklucha hislahatshine kachitlu htowreru hkotshipjetluna. Hike manikamtkatuko hsatkakna.
Waneya jitakleru yokanatatnaklu satu htowreru. Seyni ruylakluna wale koxni. Wan-rixa kamhalpatetanruna. Hike manikamtkatuko hsatkakna.
Hiyrunuko wane hyokanatlu satu mapa rixinri seyni hitaklucha hislahatshine wale koxni ruylakna. Waneya uva-cha malekate ruknokanruna.
Waneya jitakleru wla tshina hihchinikanuya: “Kluhe nkamhanu? Nyokanahetkotanru noturu namotleru. Wale hetko hkahwakpiratanna.”
— Seyni rexinixkaluna hitaklucha hislahatshine, riynumsakakna wannakakluko, wla htshinna: “Ha xyekni jitakleru whene. Hayeri wuylateru. Waneyakni hitaklu hixanpatka!”
— Hiyáhoni kahnete ruknokluna jitakleru whenni hitaklu mwiywakanu. Waneya ruylatanruna. Hiyáhoni klunerhe hkamhinna jitakleru?
Runanu ruylatanunna hitaklucha hislahatshinepni. Waneya pimrineko hitaklucha hislahatshine renekanu. Waneya xye pirana hjeminixkana, wla htshinatkana: — Ha, Hoyakalu, hi wane pixkakanru!
Seyni Jesus yopukhatna waneya wla htshinna: — Klunerhe xawaka raluka tshinreta Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru wla htshinini: “Sotlu kpanawaklerune malukkotu rikahwakluna hepixlewatatshri potukni, psolupjiko poyehitatshrini wale.”?
Katupnikta xye sotlu hoho hijrukanuna rumlokanuna. Hiyrun-koxa katupnikta xye sotlu hapokhohotanu, hipahi tsonunapni.
Repomhaluna Jesus Ho Tiyiro Raluka Wenutletluna César Ho Hike PiranapniTsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hiyrun-koxa kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine himatlu Jesus kamnitna yapkaklu piranaya runkakletleru. Raluka kachretmakluna Jesus seyni hpikna yine.
Hiyáhoni hyinuwaka hislahletluna. Hwenutluna satkaka yineru waneya hyokanatluna rumlukanta hepomhalexyawakapluna Jesus. Kihle hchinikanune rixahoxnawana Jesus rumlukanuxyawakna. Wan-hixatshri hkachitko wale tshijne tsrukakalutene renekko.
Waneya repomhatkaluna, wla htshinna: — Kasruklewakleru, wimatyi pixa halikaka pirana ptshinjeta, pasrukjetkoxna. Hiyrun-koxa hi yine hixachatatshineko yokwityi seyni pasrukle halikakalutu Hoyakalu halujyawaka pirana.
Hiyáhoni wepomhanyi minanchitkotlahe psoji tiyiro wenejyawaklu César Roma hajeru tsru hixikatshriwa? Ho wenejerhe ho hike?
Seyni Jesus himathetahchinikanutna waneya wla htshinna: — Haklu tshinanhe haluk-himlukantaletno?
Hanikanro proji tiyiro. Netanro. Katu yaholunhe kat-hiwaknihe toproji hwatshri? Waneya ruhitluna: — César-ni.
Waneya Jesus wla tshina: — Henekanru César kluneruktapni César-nu henekanru hiyrun-koxa kluneruktapni Hoyakalunu waleko henekanru.
Hi rumukata kachretluna tokantshiya yine hetanu. Hiyáhoni potshkena klu tshinanu rimyekna Jesus hihixya tshinanna.
Repomhaluna Yineru Hiwejyawakpatnaka PiranapniWaneya satkaka saduceu Jesus-stsi hipnatshri mkahwak-hiwekletkane hapoka. Waneya wla htshinna:
— Kasruklewakleru, Moisés-ni yonaxyawu xye hiykolu pirana: “Jeji hipninipa ruknokamtanro hhanunro mwuhenetoko, walen-moleko hnunrotanro waleni hnunro. Twuhenewatanu hipnatshrini whenene hkahwajikowakapna.”
Wan-rixa hahijewakatanna sete-ni jejinni moletkakatshinni. Tsrujruni hnunrowatni rupnana mwuhenetniko.
Waneya repurni hnunrotlo hipnahnurutatshro. Rupnana mwuhenetniko.
Waneko pixka rixa hahijewakatan-koxa satni mapa rixinri. Sete-ni hnunrotlewatni walaluto suxo. Rupnanna mwuhenenniko.
Waneya suxni koxa hipnanatka.
Xawakni hiwejikalur-hohnepatnaka, hanurpatkanhe thanuru? Klu tshinanu ptowruneko hnunrotaplo.
Waneya Jesus hihita: — Jejine, suxone xye tshijne hajene, hhanunrowjetna, hnuruwjetna.
Seyni tujra hohne mnikawnakatupa himukata hwaletatshinepa, hiweklu yoptotatshinepa, hi hnunrowatanu hiyrunu hi hhanuruwatanna.
Moisés-ni hekhipotutlu hipnatshine hiwejyawakpatnaka halikaka. Klu tshinanu kamxihiru ruchpakmeroxini Moisés-ni wla htshinyawaka Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu pirana “Abraão-ni Hoyakalutno, Isaque-ni Hoyakalutno, Jacó-ni Hoyakalut-koxno.”
Wale hekhitlu Hoyakalu hiwekatshine Hoyakalutni seyni hi miwekkanepa Hoyakalutni. Klu tshinanu ptowrunek-yine hiweka wale tshinanu.
Waneya satkaka kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine wan-tshina: — Wane potuko ptshina, Kasruklewakleru!
Waneya wane pnute ptowru yineru pa pirana pika hepomhaletlu.
Cristo Davi-ni Klopichni Rixyawaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus hepomhana yine: — Hanhe rumukata wla tshinretna yine, Messias klopichnixkani Davi-ni?
Davi-ni potuko wan-tshina yonawahlo papel-mta, Salmos stenoya: “Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu wan-tshinno Tsru Hixikatshriwa: Ptuplatanu npotukle sreta,
haté pkamnitjene pijixi hpuko nutakanu.”
Davi-ni potuko Rutsrukate tshinru Hoyakalu hiyáhoni hanhe rumukata Davi-ni klopicha hixleta Messias?
Jesus Hikolujyawakna Hinanchitkaluru Pirana Hasruklewatatshine PiranapniWaneya ptowru yineru jemanu Jesus wla tshinatkana rasruklene:
— Xakoka hi kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine yokwijetanhi. Rukchikhihlenutluna mkatshri hopowalu riyanyawakna. Rukchikhihlenutluna ralijikowakna hixowaka hetanu. Hnuretluna tuplawaka tsru hixikatshriwa tuplaxyawakapa ptowrupjika hanjihohnewakapji, kihleru niklur-yeh-potuko htuplatna.
Hipnahnurutatshroni hkonahejnunkatetna. Seyni wanepnawaka hohanjihohneru rixjetna kihleru hkahwajikolupna. Seyni wanepnawaka tsru hapnokatlu rixkona.
Hipnahnurutatshro Hike Mwikato Henekachle PiranapniWaneya Jesus hislahakanatna phurune henekachal-paji hitak-tiyirotetatshine.
Hiyrun-koxa retlo sato hipnahnurutatshro hike mwikato, tutaklo tiyiro seyojiji hepi proji.
Waneya Jesus wla tshina: — Halikaka wane ntshinhi, twu hipnahnurutatshro hike mwikato pimrine yohnik-tutaka wala.
Klu tshinanu nyi pimrine hixetatshro tsonu rutakna henekachawaka Hoyakalunupa. Seyni wala, hike mwikato, teneklu psoluka timwakanatanru, tyoptojetanru tenekatka.
Jesus Himatahnaputlu Hoyakalupji Kopalaxikowakapa PiranapniWaneya satkaka Hoyakalupji pirana htshinakanatna. Hi pa hihlenukananru pantshi sotlukaka kwenur-koxa hewi, hiyrunu henekachlukaka Hoyakalupji henekkaluru. Waneya Jesus wla tshina:
— Rapokpapkoluxinipa xyekaka ptowruka hetleru hkoptalhako hi satukna sotlu hwahohokakanu.
Salewaktshi, Kojwaklewatatshri PiranapniWaneya repomhatkaluna Jesus, wla htshinna: — Kasruklewakleru, hikluhe wan-rixanu? Klunerhe rakaxrikletanu rekhixyawakaplu xye ptowru potuko hakanhapiraxinpatka?
Waneya Jesus hihitna, wla htshina: — Xakoka hike yokwijetanhi. Klu tshinanu hixo hiphujewnanu hita hiwakaya wla tshinatshripa, “Hita Cristo-no”, ho, “rapokpapkolutatka”. Seyni wan-tshinatshri hi homkahitanru xako.
Hjeminiplu hiylakaklu ho pa tshijnekaka yahotkakle pirana hi hpikanu. Klu tshinanu xye ptowruko hakanhanu seyni hi hnikawnalepnitshi.
Waneya xye koxa htshinatkana: — Pa neruymako hyahotkakanu satu neruko. Pa tshijneko yahotanru satupni.
Hix-poktshi hiyolikanu. Natshipni. Yeyixlukakapni. Hetkalurkaka himyekaklewatatshripni, tsru hetkalurkakapni tenhohneya.
— Seyni xye ptowruka hnapu, preso hitakko, hsalewnakakko. Hanjihohnewakapjikaka hajene henekko, hjemahchinikanyehitko waneya preso hiknokko. Tsru hixikatshinwa hiyrunu tsrukakalune nwaka hanikko hita hiwaka tshinanu.
Wan-hixatshinhi hinkaklewatanu kihler-pirana Cristo pirana.
Hiyáhoni hi hkojwakahchinikanutanu himat-hihitanna hjihyehitjen-yehi hapojinipa.
Klu tshinanu hita henektokanutanhi hiyrunu himatkalewlu. Hma mumukata hihretanutna hkamnitjene, hma mumukata yoptoletanutna tokantshi.
Hixako hirune preso hitakanhi. Hiyrunu himolene pirana haté himolene potuk-koxa hiyrunu himatletanune preso hitakjixanhi. Satkaka hixa hiylajixko.
Ptowru yineru hahnanutanhi hixa, hita tshinanu.
Seyni hi pa jiwutsakna hamhini.
Tsru Salewaktshi PiranapniJesus pnute hya hinkakleta: — Hexinpatkalu soldado-ne Jerusalém poktshi sajrukatshine hkamnixyawakaplu, himatanutkalu hi howukatkalu hyotkajikowakanpatka poktshipni.
Waneyakni katukta Judeia hwanu, rasukanu, hipjita hyanu. Katukta poktshi hwanu, ruchpakhapkatanu. Katukta campo hwanu, hi hjihlokanru poktshi.
Klu tshinanu waneklu papkopa hapnokatlu hohnepatkani, rakanhiywakapa ptowru potuka yonatkaluru Hoyakalu piranaya.
Hi pa himtukalutu retanna suxone kamchirone waneklu hohnepa, hiyrun-koxa hachiwhenetatshinepni! Klu tshinanu tshiji rawanu salewaktshi tsrupotpákolu. Hoyakalu hapnokatanna nyi yinepni.
Hixolunepni hiylatkona yohlolewapiya, pimrinepni hanikkona ptowru tshijne ranikkona preso rutakkona. Hiyrun-koxa judeu mixkane Jerusalém poktshi hkapnikapahitanna haté rapokpapkoluxinpatka ruchoxikolna papko.
Jeji Whene Hininri PiranapniWaneya Jesus wan-tshina: — Waneplu hetkalurkaka tkatshiya, ksuruya, katahirin-koxa. Hiyrun-koxa tshijiya ptowru tshijne hajene tsru kaheknanuwlu retanna, mar powha hiyrunu tenoplojhalu honha sejire hamlenu tshinanu.
Psol-tshijne hajenepniko hitshpokhojitanuna hpiklena tshinanu, hkahwaklu retlerna tshinanu, salewnalu xye psol-tshijneko hinatshripa tshinanu. Klu tshinanu poyehirkaka tenhohne hajeru kowchitkotka.
Waneya Jeji Whene tshinkaluru hiphujewnanu, hserpikanu hohimkohiya tsru hpixkonu ratnuyma.
Hyinuwaka hakanhalexini xyekaka, poyehi yopkaklephi. Teno hiyhatanu klu tshinanu chinpotukawa hiwekkakkotka.
Figueira PiranapniWaneya Jesus satu yapkaklu pirana runkakna, wla htshina: — Hetanru figueira muna hiyrunu ptowru hahmuna hanu rixna.
Hyinuwaka hiptsheklesurexinixka, himatlu hi howukatkalu mhalu.
Wane koxa rixanu, hexinpatkalu xyekaka himatanutka hi howukatkalu rakanhiywakapa Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka.
Halikaka wane ntshinhi, xyekaka wan-hixa hiphujewnaletanu hmupnaknuhnapukawna xawakni mupnakanewa.
Tenhohne, tshij-koxa nikawnanu seyni ntokanu hikeklu nikawnanu.
Hiyokanu, Hanjihohnetanu PiranapniJesus wan-tshina: — Hislahinwa! Hi hyokwixinwa tsru nikluyma ho himruya ho xye hiwejinri kojwakle tshinanuya. Hma mimyejyawakanupa himnanhakanatatshine pixka rakanhinpatka xyekaka.
Klu tshinanu ptowrunek-yine xye tshijne hajene hkachitanu hitseklu pixkalutu.
Hiyáhoni hi himnanhinri, hanjihohnejetanu, hi hituk-hanjihohneretanu, himukata hasuklexyawakaplu ptowruka xyekaka hinatshripa. Hpaklu poyehiwlehchinikanuta Jeji Whene tshinkaluru hetanuya.
Jesus Hoyakalupjiya hasruklewjekanaxya, ptowru hohneko. Halikaka hoyetshno himriji Oliveiras tshinikowaka hyajekanata. Wane rawjekanata.
Ptowru prikaka, yetshpotukawa ptowrunek-yine yanwakjetlu Jesus Hoyakalupjiya hjemyawakapluna htokanu.
Hjemahchinikankakyehitluna Jesus Ruylaxyawakapluna PiranapniWaneya hi hix-hohne mahatatka Páscoa hohne tshinkaluru rexyawakapa. Waleni pão myapjetu nijikolu hohne.
Hiyáhoni tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hiyrunu kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine hijhahchinikanuta hanu rixa himukata hiylaletanruna Jesus.
Judas Tshinkaluru Kamnixyawaklu Jesus PiranapniWaneyakni tsru kamtshi Satanás jihloklu Judas tshinkaluru. Hyokle hiwakni Iscariotes. Judas tshinkalur-honra satu doze Jesus hasrukleru.
Judas yatka, riynumsaxyawakapna tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalupji hinotatshine hanu potu rixa hiphujetletanru Jesus wanna yehiya.
Wale hjeminixkana poyikpotukna. Waneya tiyiro renekpiratluna Judas.
Waneya Judas hinkakletlu Jesus renejyawakapna. Hiyáhoni rujhalu hiklukta hpoyaho hekhiretanna, hixolune yine himnanhinri papko Jesus rekhixyawakapna.
Jesus Páscoa Hohne Hichinijyawaka PiranaRapokatka pão myapjetu hnikjexinrina hohne, carneiro-ne ruylajexinrina judeu-ne Páscoa hohne ruchinikjexinrina hohne.
Waneya Jesus yokanatna Pedro, João tshinkalune, wla htshinatkana: — Hajewa. Halpokotanru hixa tshinanupa Páscoa hohne nikle wnijyawakapa tshinanu.
Waneya repomhaluna: — Hanhe paluka wutajyawaklu?
Waneya Jesus wan-tshina: — Tsru poktshi hjihlojinipa wane hyoptoxinri satu jeji honha hachhaji hanijikatshri. Homkahitanru. Hanupjiktako hjihlokamxini jeji wane koxa hjihlokanu.
Hiyáhoni wale hekhitanhi tsru hihruko pantshi hohwaka hwatshri, ralpokotka ptowruka hwiywaka. Wane halpokoxini.
Waneya wane hyana. Waneya rukchikluna Jesus tshinyawaka pixka potuko. Waneya ralpokotluna hniklerupna Páscoa hohne kayno hnijyawakapna.
Jesus Hipninri Yapkakle PiranapniWaneya rapokpapkoluxinixka, Jesus mesa htuplata hnurreneyma.
Waneya wla htshina: — Naluk-himinkalepotuthi xye Páscoa hohne, nsalewninri wkatanuko.
Klu tshinanu halikaka wane ntshinhi hikeklu hohne nnikanru xye Páscoa hohne tshinanupa haté rakanhanu Páscoa hohne potu Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawakaya.
Waneya copa stono hkochtsheka. Hpoyahnutlu Hoyakalu. Waneya wla htshina: — Xye copa hyoptotanu. Himurkakanu.
Klu tshinanu wane ntshinhi: Hi nuranutnaklu xye vinho-ha haté rapojinipa Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka.
Waneya pão hkochtsheka. Waneya hpoyahnutlu Hoyakalu. Hjiknajrotlu pão waneya rasruklene reneklu. Waneya wla htshina: — Xyeni hatatjewa nomane. Hixa tshinanu renekka. Xye pixkalutu hkamhajetanu hita hichinijikolupa.
Waneyatnaka rali niklexinixkana waneko pixka rixa, copa stono hkochtsheka, waneya wla htshina: — Twu copa stonha nunkakletleru, waleni herotu nohraha piranni. Xye nohraha hixa tshinanu hiyokkalurupa.
Seyni hetanu! Hewitkalu nkamnitjerupa! Hitayma hewi nikjexikowaka rawa.
Klu tshinanu Jeji Whene tshinkaluru halikaka hipnanu Hoyakalu hixahchinikanuxyawaka pixka. Seyni hektu potlu wale jeji, Jeji Whene tshinkaluru kamnitatshri!
Waneya hyinuwaka hepomhakakletna wannakakluko, kathe xawaka kamnitanru?
Katpothe HijhakaluruSeyni Jesus hasruklene hihjekaka wannakakluko katpotnihe hijhakaluru.
Hiyáhoni Jesus wan-tshina: — Phurune xye tshijne hajene towutjetna yine. Hiyrun-koxa towutatshine ralukluna kihlewaka htshinanwakaxikowakna.
Seyni hixa hi wan-hixanu. Seyni hijhakalur-potni mujhakot-potu hikahwajikatshriwa. Hiyrun-koxa tsru towutatshri hijhalu towrertshi pixka rixyawaka.
Klu tshinanu katpothe hijhakaluru? Ho nikjexikowaka tuplatatshri ho nijittshi hitakatshri? Hi he nikjexikowaka tuplatatshri potu hijhakaluru? Seyni hix-yehiya towrertshino Hita.
— Hixa himwatkano ptowruka nsalewnale tshinanu.
Hiyáhoni towuwlu, Nuru henejyano pixkalutu, wale towuwlu pixkalutu nenekanhi hixa.
Halikaka himinkanno, himuranno nikjexikowakaya npohirewaxyawaka hwatshri. Hiyrun-koxa phuru tuplawakle htuplatanu hikolukanuwnakakanna israel-nerune doze ptohkakapni.
Jesus Hinkaklu Pedro Wkatakluyakawa PiranaWaneya Jesus wan-tshina: — Simão, Simão. Hetanu, Tsru kamtshi Satanás-mka halukyi pixa. Raluk-hixirikletmakyi hahosu hixirijikowaka pixka.
Seyni nanjihohneyehityi palixle hma mahaxyawakanupa. Pehchinikanuxinpatka pmixkowkakahchinikanutanna xako Hita tshinanu pmoletanune.
Waneya Simão Pedro wan-tshinru: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, halpokotatshrino preso nutajikowakapa pixayma. Haté pixayma nupniywakapa halpokotatshrino.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru: — Halikaka wane ntshinyi, Pedro. Xye yetshno hma yanumatkanuklunuwa patlapa hepi kata, pixa map-kata pweyawatanu. Pma mimatletanutu ptshinanno.
Hepi Yohlolewapi PiranapniJesus wan-tshinatnakna: — Pa kata mitshi nyokanathi tiyiro manikkanhi, tsapantshi, sandalha koxa manikkanhi. Kluhe mitshi hmahaxyatka? Waneya wanna wan-tshina: — Hike wmahaxyatka.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinna: — Seyni xawakni wane ntshinhi, tiyiro mapa himwatshri ranikanru. Hiyrun-koxa tsapantshi himwatshri, ranikanru. Yohlolewapi mimwakatu, ruchankanru himkalu, yohlolewapi ranjixyawakapa.
Klu tshinanu halikaka wane ntshinhi: Xye nopirana, yonatkaluru Hoyakalu tokanuya haluk-hiphujewnaletanu hitayma. Wla htshina yonatkaluru, nopirana: “Hektutu kamhatshine yehi nwanu.” Xye tokantshi yonatkaluru hitayma ruphujewnanu.
Waneya rasruklene wan-tshina: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa petanu. Hewitkalu hepi yohlolewapi. Waneya Jesus wan-tshina: — Hehe hpoyahota.
Jesus Himriji Oliveiras Tshinikowaka Hyiywaka PiranapniWaneya hyatka Jesus. Himriji Oliveiras tshinikowaka hya, rixjexyawaka pixka. Rasruklen-koxa homkahitlu.
Waneya wane rapojinixkana, Jesus wan-tshinna: — Hanjihohnetanu hmallixikowakanupa.
Wla htshina hanjihohnereta: — Nuru! Palujinipa putneprikkajinno twu copa salewaktshi yehi. Seyni hi hitako nalujyawaka pkamhanu halikaka.
Satu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru hiphujewnayehitlu. Hmixkowkaklu.
Jesus salewnahchinikanuta tsru potuko hiyáhoni hmixkowa hanjihohnereta wane pnute. Ruhkokha hrahtshi pixka rixa. Rutspihle tshiji rapoka.
Waneya rali hanjihohnerexini, hpalna hsatoka rasruklene nwaka. Retamtna himkatshine. Hwamonuymana.
Waneya wane htshinanna: — Haklu tshinanhe himkakanata? Hpalnanu. Hanjihohnetanu hmallixikowakanupa.
Jesus Kachixikowaka PiranapniHyanumakanatawa Jesus runatkana hixolune yine. Judas tshinkaluru, satu doze rixinri, kosekamtna hixolune yine. Waneya rapokastsitlu Jesus ramluxyawakaplu.
Seyni Jesus wan-tshinru Judas: — Judas, pkamnitluhe Jeji Whene satu hamluruyma?
Waneya Jesus-ymalune rexinrina riknohjerutka wane htshinruna: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, yohlolewaplahe wustaklewaxini?
Waneya satu repirna kastakjepitlu tsru sacerdote towrer-jepi. Hkastaklu hpotukle jepi.
Seyni Jesus hitukjixna, wla htshina: — Hitshi hi wan-hixanu. Waneya hkamruklu hijepi hwakanaxyawaka. Waneya ruhlewata.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinna tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne, Hoyakalupji hinotatshine chefe-tene, tsrukakalune judeu-ne koxa hkachpiratjene: — Ha hixa wkata hina yohlolewapikakayma, hahajekakayma koxa hkachixyawakapno? Hatatjewa katshowhurlanohe?
Hixayma nwakanata ptowru hohneruka. Hoyakalupji nasrukjekanaxyahi. Seyni hi hkachitno. Seyni xawakni hipapkolutkani Hoyakalu hitshixyawaklu hixa tshinanu. Xawakni pixkontshi mapchahawaka hwatshri papkolni.
Pedro Wan-tshina Hi Rimathetlu Jesus PiranapniWaneya hkachitluna Jesus. Ranikluna tsru sacerdote-pji nwaka. Seyni Pedro hohatjini hwamta romkahyehitlu Jesus.
Waneya hiputu hanikajite hpawatna, rituplakakna. Waneya Pedro tshinkalur-koxa wannayma htuplata.
Seyni sato towretshro hetlu Pedro tshitshmero rolkakanaxyawaka. Tyopukhatlu, waneya wane ttshina: — Xye jeji koxa Jesus-ymakakalutu.
Seyni wale weyawata, wane htshina: — Suxo, hi koxa nimathetlu.
Waneya pchini hohnejiji satutnaka hetlu waneya wla htshina: — Pix-koxa satu wannaymalutyi. Seyni Pedro wan-tshinru: — Jeji, hita hi wannaymalutno.
Waneya satu hora hetko hiknohatka waneya satu hipokananu wan-tshinru: —Ha hi wkaheklu, wimatlu xye jeji satu Jesus-ymalutni klu tshinanu wale Galileia tshijne hajerni.
Waneya Pedro wan-tshinru: — Jeji, hi nimata klukta ptshina. Waneya waneklukawa potuko, hyanumaxiniwa Pedro, patlapa yanumatatka.
Waneya Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus heknokyehitlu Pedro. Waneya Pedro hichinkaplu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus tokanu, htshinakanaxyawaklu: “Xawakni hma yanumatkanuklunuwa patlapa, pixa map-kata hi pimathetno ptshinanu.”
Waneya Pedro wane hichpajya, kahnete hya. Waneya hyinuwaka tshiyahlepotuta.
Soldado-ne Hapnokaxyawaklu Jesus PiranapniWaneya soldado-ne Jesus kachitatshine yinuwaka heyikletlu. Ruylakluna.
Ruchyahojitluna. Waneya repomhaluna. Wla htshinna: — Pmetanutu punkaklewatanu, kathe hiylakyi?
Hi heppik-pirana htshinruna, hektuwaka potuko htshinruna.
Tsrukakalune Jemahchinikankakyehixyawaklu Jesus PiranapniWaneya hohi rixinixka rapatjetna tsrukakalune judeu-ne, tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne, kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshin-koxa. Waneya ranikjixluna Jesus jemahchinikankakjexikowakaya, judeu chefe-tene hapatjewakle.
Waneya repomhaluna Jesus, wane htshinna: — Punkakanwu. Pixlahe Messias tshinkaluryi? Waneya wale wan-tshinna: — Hehe ntshininiphi hi hetko halixanno.
Hiyrun-koxa hixa pa pirana nepomhiniphi hi hetko hihitanno hita.
Seyni xawaknikotka Jeji Whene tshinkaluru, Hoyakalu ptowru potuko himukatatshri potukle sreta htuplatanu.
Waneya wanna ptowruneka hepomhatkalu: — Hiyáhoni, pixlahe Hoyakalu Whenyi? Waneya wale wan-tshinna: — Htshinyawakno, hitakni.
Pilatos Yehi Ranijyawakluna Jesus PiranapniWaneya hpalnatkana wanna ptowruneka, waneya phuru Pilatos tshinkaluru nwaka ranikluna Jesus.
Waneya hyinuwaka jihyehretluna, waneya wane htshinyehitluna: — Xye jeji wukchika winerune pupjekakatshri. Hyokchajetna yine phuru César hma wenuxyawakanupna. Hiyrun-koxa wale hima Messias-ni, Pohirtshini.
Waneya phuru Pilatos wan-tshinru: — Pixlahe judeu-nerune pohiryi? Waneya Jesus hihitlu, wane htshina: — Pixako wan-tshina.
Waneya phuru Pilatos wan-tshinna tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hiyrun-koxa pimrine yine: — Hi psojikna hikolukanuwnalu nukchika xye jeji tshinanu.
Seyni wanna mixkowa yanumletatka, wla htshinna: — Xye komyekahchinikanutna yine. Judeia tshijne psoluka hya rasruklewle. Galileia tshijne hyinuwajya. Xawakni hewi rapokatka.
Waneya hjeminixkalu phuru Pilatos, Galileia tshijne hkochtshejyawakna, repomhana ho Galileia tshijne hajerlahe xye jeji.
Waneya rimaxinixka phuru Herodes hinoxyawaka sreta hajeru rixyawaka Jesus, phuru Pilatos yokanatlu phuru Herodes nwaka. Klu tshinanu phuru Herodes koxa Jerusalém poktshi rawakanata waneklu papko koxa.
Herodes Yehi Ranijyawakluna Jesus PiranapniWaneya phuru Herodes, Jesus rexinixka hpoyikowpotuta. Klu tshinanu hix-hohne tshinanu raluk-hetletmaklu Jesus. Klu tshinanu hixo pirana hjemyehitlu Jesus. Hiyáhoni hiyakolumka raluk-hetleta, Jesus kamhalerupa.
Waneya phuru Herodes hixo hepomhalu rixmaklu Jesus. Seyni Jesus hike tshinru.
Waneya tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne, hiyrun-koxa kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine yotunota. Hjihyehitatkaluna Jesus. Hipokananu hyanumatna.
Waneya phuru Herodes, soldado-neyma heyiklu. Rapnokatluna. Waneya mkatshri kihler-potuko hmakatluna Jesus. Wan-hixatshriko phuru Pilatos nwaka ranikluna hiyrunukotnaka.
Wale hohnetka rimatletkakatkana phuru Herodes hiyrunu phuru Pilatos-yma. Klu tshinanu mitshikananu hkamnikakjekanatna.
Ho Jesus Ho Barrabás PiranapniWaneya phuru Pilatos hapatjekjixna tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne, tsrukakalune judeu-ne hiyrun-koxa yine pimrine.
Waneya wla htshinna: — Hixa xye jeji hanikanwakatno, yine himtukahchinikanutatshri phuta. Seyni hixa hetanuko nepomsatlu. Hi satuknako jikolukanuru nukchika xye jeji hjihyehixyalu tshinanu.
Phuru Herodes koxa hike hima rukchika jikolukanuru wale tshinanu. Klu tshinanu hsatkakjixlu hixa nwaka. Halikaka hike hkamha ruylaxikowakapa.
Hiyáhoni nkotshipjejixachatanru. Waneya wan-hixatshri nyakjixanu.
Tsru niklu hohne tshinanu Phuru Pilatos hijhalu satu preso hajeru hichoxyawaka, yine nurrer-potuko.
Waneya ptowrunek-yine yinuwaka saplewleta: — Pixrikkakanru xye, seyni Barrabás tshinkaluru puchoxinwu!
Barrabás preso hitakka klu tshinanu poktshi tsrukakalutene hkamnikanaxyawaka tshinanni. Ruylale tshinanu kapna rutakka.
Seyni Pilatos haluk-hicholetmaklu Jesus. Hiyáhoni yinemka hixolune repomhatnaka.
Seyni wanna wane pnute rixa saplewlepotutna: — Cruz putakanru! Cruz putakanru!
Waneya phuru Pilatos wan-tshinna map-kata rixinri: — Seyni klunerhe hektutu hkamha xye? Hi satukna jikolukanuru nukchijyalu rupninripa. Hiyáhoni nkotshipjejixanru waneya wan-hixatshri nuchotanu.
Seyni wanna hixko rixa saplewlepotuthonukna. Ranjitluna cruz rutajikowakatka. Hiyáhoni wanna tokanu hallirewata.
Waneya phuru Pilatos, Jesus ruylakjixa, ranjixyawakna yine pixka.
Ruchoxyana jeji kkamnirewakleru, hiylalu tshinanu preso hitakkaluru. Ranjixyawakna yine pixka rixyana. Hiyahokni renekna Jesus wanna ralujyawakna hkamhiywakapna Jesus-yma.
Jesus Calvário Tshinikowaka Ranjikowaka PiranapniWaneya ranikakanaxinixkaluna Jesus hatnu hapoya, satu jeji yoptotna Simão tshinkaluru Cirene poktshi hajeru. Campo ruchpakamxya. Hkachitluna. Waneya cruz rutjikakluna, Jesus hatjini ranijyaplu.
Hixolune yine homkahimtlu. Wannayma hyana suxone, kaheknanuwatatshrone, wamonuwatatshrone Jesus tshinanu.
Waneya Jesus hiprotakyehitna suxone. Waneya wane htshinna: — Jerusalém poktshi hajerone hi hitshiyahatanno hita. Seyni halikaka htshiyahatanu hixako htshinanu hiyrun-koxa hixako hwuhenene tshinanu.
Klu tshinanu halikaka rapokhohnetanu wla htshininri hohnepna, hihle hchinikanyehitkalunepni mwuhenewatkane, mmatuwhenetkane hiyrun-koxa tnutshkaka machitkotuwa.
Klu tshinanu rapnokaxinipnona hita, herot-muna pixkalutukno, klunerhe hkamhikatka popri rixinixka?
Waleyma ranikka koxna hepi hektutu kamhatshine, Jesus-yma ruylaxikowakapna.
Jesus Cruz Hitajikowaka PiranapniWaneya rapokluna Calvário tshinikowaka. Wale tokantshi yokakkaluru, yineru jiwuta pixkalutni. Wane potuko cruz rutajyaluna Jesus. Hiyrun-koxa hektutu kamhaklerune, hepi wan-rutakna. Satu Jesus potukle sreta rutakka. Satu pa sta sreta hitakka.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshina: — Nuru, pamtakahchinikanyehitanru nyi yine hektunu. Klu tshinanu hi rimatna klukta hkamhana. Waneya hiknokkaluru ruknokna rimaxyawakapna katu kayatanru Jesus-ni mkalu.
Retakanatluna Jesus. Tsrukakalune judeu-ne wannaymalune koxa heyiklu, wla htshinna: — Pimrine riwekkaka, rumukaxinipa riwekkajinwa wale nanuko, halikaka Messias tshinkaluru rixinpakni, Hoyakalu nurreru.
Soldado-ne heyik-koxlu. Jesus-stsi rapokamtna, renekmakluna kapsahalu.
Wla htshinruna: — Judeu pohire pixini halikaka, pkochpajinwa cruz-ya!
Cruz hoho teno nwaka raw-yonhata, Jesus jihyehixikolu pirana. Wla htshin-yonhata: “Xye judeu-ne pohire.”
Hepi Hektutu Kamhatshine PiranapniWaneya satu wanna hepi hektutu kamhaklerune, Jesus-yma cruz hitakkalune, heyik-koxlu Jesus: — Hi he Messias-yi? Hiyáhoni piwekkajinwa pixa, hiyrunu hix-koxa piwekkakanu.
Seyni satu hiykotlu, wane htshinru: — Hi he Hoyakalu ppika? Hixa ptowrunekwu hapnokatkalunwu pixkakaklunwu.
Seyni hix-hepwu halikaka wane potuko wixka. Klu tshinanu wkamrure hapnute pixkalutu potuko wyoptota. Seyni xye hike hektutu hkamha.
Waneya wane htshina: — Jesus, puchinikanunno hitni, ppohirewaxyawaka papojinipa.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru: — Halikakni wane ntshinyi. Xye hohneko hitaymapyi kihlewak-potuko, tenhohne wyanu.
Jesus Hipninri PiranapniWaneya hanikaj-hohnestsi rutshpokatka. Hiyáhoni psol-tshijneka rutshpokapya mapa hora.
Waneya mkatshri sama, Hoyakalupji hwatshrini hiskakana hepi tshraj-samanru.
Jesus hipokananu saplewatatka: — Nuru, pimyo nutaklu niwejinri. Waneya rali wan-tshinretatka rupnanatka.
Waneya romano-neru soldado-ne pohire rexinixkalu, wan-rixikowaka Jesus-ni, Hoyakalu rimalwutatka, wla htshina: — Halikakni xye jeji honnira, jeji potukalni.
Hiyrun-koxa ptowrunek-yine, wane hapatjexikatshine, hetapatshine, rexinixkaluna wan-rixikowaka Jesus-ni, rutpestaxnawana. Waneya hsatokna.
Hiyrun-koxa ptowruneka rimatletanune suxon-koxa romkahitjene Galileia rumuchpajinine, hyotunotna howukaya. Retakanatluna xyekaka.
Jesus Kapnaxikolu PiranapniWanekananru satu jeji José hiwakatletatshri. Wale tsru jemahchinikankakatshine yehi hajerni. Hiyrun-koxa jejni kchinikanuru, potukalu.
Wale honra hi hehe htshinatkana pimrine repirene hijhahchinikanutatshineya Jesus jihyehixikolu piranaya. José tshinkaluru Arimateia tshinikowaka hajerni, judeu poktshi. Hiyrunu Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka kahwakatshrini, wale koxa.
Xye jeji Pilatos nwaka hya. Jesus-ni mane ranjitlu.
Waneya José tshinkaluru Jesus-ni mane hkochtsheka cruz-ya. Waneya mkatshri sama, linho sama, ruwtoklu. Waneya kapna, sotlu jitoxikolu hipjitaya, rutakmanetlu Jesus-ni. Satukna mutajikowakanuwa rutaklu.
Wale hohne halpokotkalur-hohneni. Hiyrun-koxa hi howukatkalu hapnanuxikalur-hohne hyinuwajyawakapa.
Hiyrunu suxon-koxa, Jesus himotsatatshine, Galileia tshijne rumuchpajinine, retkapnatkotapluna. Retkoxluna hanu potu rixa kapnakota Jesus-ni mane.
Waneya hsatokatkana. Ralpokotluna phamlu pahiru hiyrun-koxa phamluhalo. Seyni rapnanutatkana hapnanuxikalur-hohne Moisés-ni hiykole yonatkaluru tshinyawaka pixka.
Jesus Hiwejyawakatnaka PiranapniWaneya hyinuwakle seman-hohne, yetshpotukawa yomletshi nwaka hyana. Raniklona phamluhalo hkamhahnapuxyaluna.
Seyni retluna rerutkatka sotlu yomletshi hajeru.
Hjihlokyomletluna. Seyni hi rukchikmanetluna Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus-ni mane.
Hpikatkana suxone. Tshiji hyohimhojitna. Waneya jejine mkatshri katajiru hitakatshine, wan-tshinna: — Klu tshinanhe hipnatshri hwawakle hijhiylu hiwekatshri?
Hi hewitkalu seyni riwekatnaka halikaka. Hichinkapanru runkajyapiranhi mitshikananu Galileia tshijne rawakanaxiniwa.
Wla htshinatkahi mitshikananu: “Jeji Whene tshinkaluru hijhalu renejikowakapa hektune myoya. Rujhalu ruylaxikowakapa cruz-ya. Waneya map-hohne rixinri rujhalu riwejyawakatnaka.”
Waneya suxone hichinkaplu Jesus tokanu.
Hiyáhoni yomletshi nwaka ruchpajyatkana. Xye pirana ptowruka runkakmakna onze Jesus hasruklene, pimrin-koxamka.
Suxone wannani Maria Madalena, Joana, tshinkalune hiyrun-koxa Maria tshinkaluro, Tiago tshinkaluru hinro. Nyi suxone, pimron-koxa wannaymalune xye pirana ptowruka runkakletna, onze jejine Jesus nurrene.
Seyni nyi onze suxone yanumsalecha pixka rixa jemletluna. Hiyáhoni hi ralixatkana.
Waneya Pedro palna, rasukanwakatlu yomletshi. Rujnoka. Retlu mkatshri sama tsonutka. Waneya hipji hsatokatka. Rimyekahchinikanuta xye pirana tshinanu.
Jesus, Hepi Rasruklene Yehi Rakanhiywakatnaka PiranapniWaneyatnaka wale hohneko hepi pa poktshi nwaka yamtatshine, doze quilômetro pchinru Jerusalém poktshi, Emaús tshinikowaka.
Riynumsakakakananumtna ptowruka xye hiknohatshri pirana.
Waneya riynumsakakakananumxiniwana, repomsakakamxiniwana, Jesus hapokastsitna. Wannayma mnutkalu.
Rasruklene hetmaklu seyni kluneru tshinanukta hi rimathetluna katuktani.
Waneya Jesus hepomhana: — Klu pirana htshinkakakananumta hixkakluko hyanakananumxyawaka? Waneya rutuk-yanretatkana wamonuwhojitatshineko.
Waneya satu, Cleopas tshinkaluru wan-tshinru: — Jerusalém poktshi hajermakyi, seyni pixa tsonu hetko hi himatlu klu rixanatka Jerusalém poktshiya xye hohnekaka.
Waneya wale wan-tshinna: — Kluneru pirana? Waneya wanna wla tshinna: — Jesus-ni Nazaré poktshi hajerni pirana. Walenixkani jejni Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshrini. Hiyrun-koxa ptowrunek-yine hetanuya kpixkonuru hkamrureya, htokanuy-koxa.
Tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne, hiyrun-koxa wutsrukatene heneklu ruylaxikowakapa. Ruylatluna cruz-ya.
Seyni hixa kahwakmaklu walepnikni israel-nerune hepixatshripni hkamnitjeneya. Waneya xawakni, map-hohne pnutetkani wan-rixinrinatka.
Waneya xawakni pimrone suxon-koxa, hixaymalone himyekakahchinikanutwu. Yetshpotukawa yomletshi hyana.
Seyni hi rukchikmanetluna. Waneya hsatokna. Hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrene tenhohne hajen-hima retna. Runkakhimatkanna Jesus hima hiwekatnaka.
Wane hyapna pimrin-koxa hixaymalune yomletsh-yehi. Htshinakanaxyawak-potukna suxone rixa hetletkoxna wanna. Seyni Jesus potuko hi retna.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinna: — Ha, mimatjemkanhi. Hi kahchinikanhi halixhapkaxyawaka ptowru potuko pirana Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine tshinjekanaxyawakhi!
Hi he rujhalu Messias tshinkaluru hsalewniywakapa waneya hyoptoxyawakaplu tsru pixkontshi walenuko?
Waneya hyinuwaka hinkakletna Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru pirana, Moisés yonreru hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine yonrekananuko runkakna wane htshinakanaxyawakna waleko hipirana.
Waneya rapokastsitluna poktshi hyamxyawakna. Walemka pnute yapirata.
Seyni wanna tshipetlu. Wla htshinruna: — Hewipyitshi. Kayitkani, hoyetshnopatkani. Hiyáhoni Jesus jihlokapjitna. Wanna yehi rutukatka.
Waneya nikawakakwa htuplata. Pão hkochtsheka waneya hpoyahnutlu Hoyakalu pão tshinanu. Waneya hjiknajrotlu pão. Waneya reneksatna.
Waneya hyopukhatatkana hiyáhoni rimathetluna. Seyni wale hamhamtatka. Hi retluna.
Waneya wane htshinkakna wannakakluko: — Hi he hamhajitaknawu riynumsakanaxinixkawu hatnu hapoya, runkakakanaxinixkawu Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru tshinpiraxyawaka pirana?
Waneya hpalnahapkatna. Hsatokanwakatluna Jerusalém poktshi nwaka. Wane hyoptoxyaluna Jesus rasruklene onze, wannaymalun-koxa rimapatjejekanatanune.
Waneya wanna hepi jejine koxa hinkakletlu riknohjerna pirana hatnu hapoya. Runkakletkoxluna Jesus pão hjiknajroxiniklunutka rimathetluna Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus-ni.
Jesus Rasruklene Hakanhayehixyawaka PiranapniWaneya wane htshinakanatawana, xye piranaya, Jesus wanna hanikajite hyopkakatka. Waneya wane htshinna: — Kihle hchinikanuphi.
Seyni wanna himyekpotuta. Hpikpotutatkana. Wanna kahwakatkalu samentshi rexyawakna.
Seyni wale wan-tshinna: — Klu tshinanhe hkojwakahchinikanuta? Kluneru tshinan-koxhe wan-hixahchinikanhajita?
Hetamyotanno hiyrun-koxa nojixi. Hitakni. Hkamrukanno, himathexyawakapno. Klu tshinanu samentshi hi kahitlu, hi kahaplu. Hixa hi hetno wane nixyawaka.
Rali wan-tshinretatka, rekhitna himyo, hijix-koxa.
Seyni hi ralixluna tsru hpoyikowle tshinanna, hiyrun-koxa rimyekahchinikanre tshinanna. Hiyáhoni Jesus hepomhana, wla htshina: — Hi he waneyhi pa hixanu nikkaluru?
Waneya wanna heneklu psoji chima jimkaluro.
Jesus yoptotlo waneya wanna hetanuko hniklo.
Hoyakalu Tokanu Ruphujexyawaka Jesus PiranapniWaneya Jesus wan-tshinna: — Nimwakanaxiniwahi nunkakatkahi raluk-hakanhaleta ptowru potuko hita pirana yonatkaluru, Moisés yonreruya, Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine yonreya hiyrun-koxa Salmos-mta yonatkaluruya hita pirana.
Waneya hkotpukahchinikanutna rumukata himatjemletluna Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru.
Waneya wane htshina: — Hyonpiranatka Messias tshinkaluru haluka salewnaleta seyni map-hohne rixinripa riwekanutnaka hipnatshine tskalaya.
Hiyrun-koxa ptowru tshijneko runkaklexikotka hehchinikanru pirana hektuntshi hiknojikowaka pirana, wale hiwakaya. Jerusalém poktshi hyinuwaka hinkaklewlexini.
Hixakni xye pirana hiphujetatshinephi.
Hiyrun-koxa hitakni yokananwakatanhi Nuru hinkaklexyahi. Seyni hewitshi poktshi hitukanu pixkontshi klu papko hapojini, tenhohne hichpajikatshri, hixa nwaka hapokatshripa.
Jesus Tenhohne Yinri PiranapniJesus hanikatkana Jerusalém poktshi kahnete Betânia poktshistsi potuko ranikatkana. Waneya hyotukamyota. Ruhlewahchinikanyehitna.
Waneya wan-rixakanatawa, ruhlehchinikanyehitka pchinikna, wanna yehi hkochtshejikatka. Tenhohne ranikkatka.
Rimalwutluna waneya hsatokna Jerusalém poktshi nwaka tsru poyikowluyma.
Ptowru hohneko Hoyakalupji rawna. Hoyakalu rimalwutna. Hpoyahnutluna.
