Hyinuwajikolukananukotka Hoyakaluyma rawatka Tokantshi.
Hoyakalu ptowru potuko ruyakota waleyma. Hikepotukni ruyakoleru Hoyakalu wale minje.
Tokantshi hiwekluni. Xye hiweklu katalni yine nikotyehitatshri.
Katalu nikotlu mapchahawaka hiyrun-koxa mapchahawaka hi hiwakatkalu katalu.
Hoyakalu yokanatlu satu jeji João tshinkaluru.
Xye jeji hapokatka hiphujtatatshri rixyawaka ruphujexyawakaplu katalu katni wale. Wan-rixa ptowru yineru halixatshri rixinripa runkakle tshinanu.
Xye katalu hi João-kni wale. Seyni runatka João ruphujtaxyawakaplu katalu katni.
Katalu halikakalutu waleni katalu xye tshijne hapokatshri ptowru yineru hchinikanu nikotatshri.
Xye tshijne rawa hiyrunu xye tshijne hiyakotatshrini wale. Seyni xye tshijne hajene hi himathetatkalu.
Seyni ptowruneko, ralixjene pejnu rutakna Hoyakalu whenene rixyawakapna, ralix-hiwakatjene pejnu tshinanu wan-rixa.
Wanna ptowruneka hi hrahtshiyma matutatshine tsonni, hi mantshi matuxikatshine tsonni, hi yineru halujyawaka tshinanu matutatshinetkani seyni Hoyakalu tshinanu matutatshinni wanna.
Tokantshi Manewaxyawaka PiranapniTokantshi manewata. Hiyrun-koxa hixa tskala rawakanatatka. Wetlu royaknu. Hoyakalu hoyaknu pixka rixatka Hoyakalu whene satupkalutu. Hpoyahokakatkalu ptowru potuka Hoyakalu hihlenu hiyrunu halikakalutu pirana hpoyahokakatka.
João hiphujtatlu xye yineru. Tsru tokantshiyma wla htshina João: — Xyekatkani ntshinjekanatanru: “Hita natjini hapokatshripa hita yohnik-kahwakpiratkaluru klu tshinanu nma matutkanuklunuwa rawakotka wale.”
Klu tshinanu rumukatle tsru potuko hepixlewatatshri yoptotatshinwu hixa ptowrunekwu. Ruhlenu renekachale yoptotatshinwu hiyrunu ruhlenu renekachale wane pnutepa yoptotatshinepwu.
Hiykolu pirana yonatkaluru yokanatatshrini Moisés-ni seyni Jesus Cristo-kni Hoyakalu hihlenu ptowru potuka hiyrunu halikakalutu pirana hiyakotatshrini wale.
Hi satukna yineru hikeklu hetjejetlu Hoyakalu. Halikaka Hoyakalu whene satupkalutu, ruru Hoyakalusko potuko hwatshriko, walekni hiphujtatlu Hoyakalu.
João Batista Tshinkaluru Hinkaklewaxyawaka PiranapniXyekni João pirana, judeu-ne mitshi yokanatna sacerdote-ne hiyrunu levita tshinkalune, Jerusalém poktshi hichpajikatshine, João tshinkaluru nwaka repomhiywakapluna João, katnihe wale.
Waneya João hiphujexnawa. Hi pnuko htshinatka. Seyni halikaka htshina, wla htshinatka: — Hi Cristo-no hita, htshina.
Waneya repomhatkaluna: — Katpotyihe pixa? Elias tshinkalurlayihe? Waneya João hihitna, wla htshina: —Hike, hi waleno. Waneya repomhatnakna: — Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshripotuklayhe? Seyni wla htshinatka João. — Hike.
Hiyáhoni wane htshinruna: —Punkakanwu katpotyihe pixa? Waluk-himatletlu kathe pikahwajnawa wunkakapyawakapna wyokanatjene, wepomhakjixjene.
Waneya João wla tshina: —“Hitni kahnete poktshiri saplewaxikatshri tokanno, wla tshinatshri: Halpokotanru Tsru Hixikatshriwa hatnu hapotkaka. Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshrini Isaías-ni tshinkalurni tshinyawaka pixka nixa.”
Seyni João hepomhapatshine wannani fariseu-ne.
Hiyáhoni repomhaluna, waneya wane htshinruna: — Cristo pmixkanuklunu ho Elias pmixkanuklunu ho Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri koxa pmixkanuklunu kluneru tshinanhe p-batiz-lewjeta?
Waneya João hihitna, wla htshina: — Hita honha n-batiz-jexyana. Seyni hixa hanikajite rawa satu yineru hmimatyehitanutu.
Walekni hita pnute hapokatshripa hita yohnik-kahwakpiratkaluru. Hita hi tsru hixikatshriwano nkochpirojyawakaplo h-sapato-tetslu.
Xyekaka ptowruka hakanhatka Betânia poktshiya, Jordão wenne pa sreta hwatshri, João batiz-lewjekanaxyawaka.
João Batista Hiphujexyawakatnaklu Katni Jesus PiranapniWaneya wale prika João hetlu Jesus. Runamta Jesus João nwaka. Waneya João wan-tshina: — Hetanu hixa, xyekni Hoyakalu carneiro-te. Xyekni xye tshijne hektunu konatshripa.
Xyekatkani nunkakletakanatanru: Satu jeji hita pnute hapokatshripa hita yohnik-hijhakalurni klu tshinanu hi nmatutawa rawatka wale.
Hit-potuko hi nimathetatkalu katuktani seyni nuna n-batiz-lewajexyawaka honhaya rimaxyawakapluna israel-nerune katuktani wale.
Jesus Batiza-xikolu PiranapniWaneya João xye pirana hinkakletatka: — Netlu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru, motkokoji pixka rixmaneta, tenhohne ruchpajya Jesus hoho rapokatka wale hoho rutukatka.
Himka nimathetatkalu katuktani seyni Nyokanatjeru n-batiza-xyawakapa honhaya hinkakhapkatno wane htshina: — Wale jeji honra pexiniplu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hijrukhohotlu walekni batiza-tanna yine Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluruya.
Hita hetlu hiyáhoni nunkakletanru, halikakni xye jeji Hoyakalu whenni.
Jesus Mitshikananu Hasruklene PiranapniWaneya wale prikatnaka João wane hwakanata hepi rasrukleneyma.
Jesus reta yanamtatshri waneya wla htshina: — Hetanru Hoyakalu carneiro-te.
Nyi hepi João hasruklene jemlu htokanu. Waneya romkahitluna Jesus.
Waneya Jesus hiprotaka, retna romkahitjene. Waneya wla htshinna: — Kluhe hijhajeta? Wanna wla tshinru: — Hasruklewatatshri (wale Tsru Hixikatshriwa raluka tshinreta). Hanhe pwajeta?
Waneya wale wan-tshinna: — Hinanu hetapanru. Wane hyana retluna rawjexyawaka. Wale hohne rutukna wale yehi klu tshinanu kayitkani quatro horas hetkotkani.
Satu wanna hepi João tokanu yijnakotatshine, Jesus homkahitatshri, André tshinkalurni, Simão Pedro hepuru.
Waneya André hanikatkalu himole Simão Jesus nwaka. Jesus hexiniklunru wla htshinru: — Phiwaka Simão, João tshinkaluru whene. Seyni xawakni pixa hiwakatka Cefas. (Yokakkalurutka waleni sotlu.)
Jesus Nurexyawakna Filipe Hiyrunu Natanael PiranapniWaneya wale prika Jesus hichiniklu Galileia tshijne sreta hyiywakapa. Seyni mitshikananhapka Filipe rukchika waneya wla htshinru: — Pomkahitanno!
Filipe Betsaida hajerni, André hiyrunu Pedro hwajexyawaka poktshi hajerni wale.
Filipe hijhatkalu Natanael waneya wla htshinru: — Wukchikatkalu wale yineru Moisés-ni yonyehitanru yonruru piran-yehi hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine yonyehitanru. Jesus-ni wale, José tshinkaluru whene, Nazaré poktshi hajeru.
Waneya Natanael hepomhalu: — Rumukathe satu pa hixanu kihleru Nazaré poktshi hakanhalexya? Waneya Filipe wla tshinru: — Punanu, petapanru.
Waneya Jesus hexinri Natanael wale nwaka hinamta wla htshinanwakatlu: — Hetanru! Tujrapatkani jeji israel-neru halikakalutu. Waleni maylokletu.
Waneya Natanael wan-tshinru: — Hanhe pix-himathetletno? Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Filipe mtomhaknuklunuwayi netyi figueira muna hpuko pwakanaxini.
Waneya Natanael hihitlu, wla htshina: — Kasruklewakleru, pixni halikaka Hoyakalu Whenyi! Pixni halikaka israel-neru Pohireyi!
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru: — Figueira muna hpuko pwakanaxini nexyayi ntshinre tshinanrahe, palixno? Xyekaka yohnik-hijhakalurkaka petanu.
Waneya wla htshina: — Halikakni, halikakni wla ntshinhi pa hohne tenhohne hitpukatshri hetanu hiyrunu hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrene tenhohne hajene hetanu hatskomtatshine, serpikamtatshine Jeji Whene tshinkaluru hohowaka yapamtatshine.
Hnunrowlu Nwaka Hyiywaka Jesus PiranapniWaneya hepi hohne hiknohinixka rawatka hnunrowlu Caná poktshi, Galileia tshijneya. Jesus hinro koxa wane hwa.
Hiyrun-koxa Jesus hiyrunu rasruklene tshanixka hnunrowlu nwaka.
Waneya vinho-ha nikawninixka, Jesus hinro wan-tshinru: — Vinho-ha nikawnahatanatka.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinro: — Suxo, klu tshinanhe pujhano hita? Nopapkolu hi hapokawa.
Waneya wala wan-tshinna towrertshine: — Klunerukta runkajinhi, wale potuko hkamhanu.
Wanekananru seis hachhaji, sotlu kamhikolu. Judeu-nerune powratjexinriwa tshinanu. Satkaka oitenta ho cem litros honha hkachita.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinna towrertshine: — Honha htsepotanru hachhajkaka. Waneya htsepohapotutluna hachhajkaka haté hipto potuko.
Waneya wla htshinatkana: — Hsajikhatanu xawakni. Hnunrowatatshri nikle kosekatshri nwaka hanikanru. Waneya ranikanwakatluna.
Hnunrowatatshri nikle kosekatshri hi himatlu hanhe tuchpajya vinho-ha seyni towrertshine honha sajehatatshine himatlu. Waneya hnunrowatatshri nikle kosekatshri hetumhiniklunutkalu vinho-ha honha kamhikaluro, repuklu hnunrowatatshri.
Wla htshinatkalu: — Ptowru yineru niklu yinuwaklekawahapka hitakjetlu vinho-ha kihleru, waneya tnikahatkoklunutka vinho-ha kihlero waneya tutakkatka vinho-ha kayaho hihlenurutokotka. Seyni pixa vinho-ha kihleru pimreta haté xawakniwa.
Wan-rixa yinuwakletlu Caná poktshiya, Galileia tshijne hajeruya Jesus kamhalu mitshikananu hetkaluru hkamhaleru. Ruphujetlu royaknu hiyrunu rasruklene halixatkalu.
Waneya wane wkatanu, Jesus, runro, himolene hiyrun-koxa rasruklene Cafarnaum poktshi nwaka hyatkana. Wan-rutukatkana pimri hohnekaka.
Jesus Hoyakalupji Nwaka Hyiywaka PiranapniPáscoa hohne judeu kahwakpirreru hohne wkatanuko, Jesus Jerusalém poktshi nwaka hya.
Waneya Hoyakalupji hyoptoxyana boi-ne hichanretatshine, carneiro hichanretatshine, kamowane hichanretatshine hiyrun-koxa tiyiro hipekjetatshine wane tuplatatshine hyoptota.
Kotshipjerewapi hkamha katsaluya. Waneya Hoyakalupji rakajyatkana ptowrunek-yine, carneiro-ne hiyrun-koxa boi-ne Hoyakalupji maleka sreta hyiywakapna. Tiyiro hipekjetatshine tiyirote rupkaka hiyrun-koxa hyotkakanru mes-kakni.
Hiyrunu wla htshinna kamowane hichanretatshine: — Xye ptowruka hewi hkochpajini! Hi hkamhanru maronewawakapji rixyawakapa Nurupji.
Waneya rasruklene hichinikanretlu yonatkaluru wla tshinatshri: “Hoyakalu, pipji tshinanu njempotuthonuklu, naji halhapirata hatatjewa tshitshmero nwahajita.”
Waneya judeu-ne hihitlu, wla htshinruna: — Kluneru hetkaluru pekhitanwu wimaxyawakaplu towutatshriyi xyekaka pumukata kamhalexyawaka?
Waneya Jesus wla tshinna: — Xye Hoyakalupji hyotkakanu hixa waneya map-hohne pejnu nkamhanutnaklu hita.
Seyni Hoyakalupji pirana hkochtshekleru, waleni waleko himane pirana.
Hiyáhoni Jesus hipnatshine tskala riwejiniklunutka, rasruklene hichinikaplu htshinyawakna mitshi. Waneya ralixluna Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru hiyrunu Jesus tokanu htshinakanaxyawakna ralixatkana.
Jesus Himatahchinikanuxyawakna Ptowrunek-yine PiranapniJerusalém poktshi rawakanaxini Jesus Páscoa nikle hohne tshinanu, rexinixkaluna himyekaklewatatshrikaka Jesus kamhaleru, hixolune yine halixlu Jesus.
Seyni Jesus hi munanhana yine klu tshinanu rimatahchinikanutna ptowrunek-yine.
Hiyáhoni hi rujhatkalu satu yineru hasrujyawaklu hanu rixa yineru klu tshinanu rimatatkalu yineru hchinikanu hwatshri.
Nicodemos Hetapyawakaplu Jesus PiranapniWaneru satu yineru Nicodemos tshinkaluru, judeu chefe-te, fariseu-kni wale.
Waneya hoyetshno Nicodemos yanwakatlu Jesus waneya wane htshinru: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, wimatyi pixa kasruklewakleryi, Hoyakalu yokanreryi klu tshinanu hike yineru himukata kamhaletlu nyi hiyakolukaka pkamhajereru Hoyakalu mimotsatanune.
Waneya Jesus hihitlu: — Halikaka ntshinyi, hike himukata jihlokletanru Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hepi kata hma matutkanuklunu.
Waneya Nicodemos hepomhalu: — Hanu xawakhe rumukata yineru tsrutsoleji hiyrunuko hmatuxyawakatnaka? Rumukathe jeji runro nanwaka jihlokletatnaka waneya hmatutanutnaka?
Waneya Jesus wan-tshina: — Halikaka ntshina, hike himukata jihlokletanu Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hma mathapkatkanuklunu honhaya, Hiwejikaluruya koxa.
Yineru hmatuxini himaneya yinerni seyni Hoyakalu hiwejinri hmatuxyawaka yineru wale tsonu hiwekkaklewata.
Hiyáhoni hi himyekanu wane ntshinyawakhi hixa ptowruneka haluka matreta hiyrunukotnaka.
Hanukta raluka yaleta kanniphalu wane potuko hya. Hixamka jemlu kanniphalu sejire, seyni hi himatlu hyinuwajyawaka sreta hiyrun-koxa hi himatlu rutujyawaka sreta. Waneko pixka rixa ptowru yineru Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru matuxikatshri.
Waneya Nicodemos hepomhalu, wla htshina: — Hanhe rixanu xye?
Jesus hihitlu, wla htshina: — Hi he israel-nerune hasrukatshrimkayi seyni xyekaka pirana hi pimata?
Halikaka, halikaka wla ntshinyi: — Wunkakhi wimatjemle pirana hiyrunu wunkakhi wetlerutka pirana seyni hixa hi haluk-halixletlu wunkakle.
Xye tshijne pirana nunkaklexini wanepnawaka hi halixno hanhe xawaka halixanno tenhohne hajeru pirana nunkaklexini?
Hi satukna yineru tenhohne hatskoxya, seyni Jeji Whene tshinkaluru tenhohne serpijikatshri tsonupka wane ratskoxya.
Moisés popriwaka yopkaklu hahaje waleptaji hoho rutaklu himnu bronze kamhikolu hiyáhoni waneko pixka raluk-hixletko Jeji Whene tshinkaluru teno rutakko.
Hiyáhoni wan-rixakona ptowruneka wale halixatshine, riwekanna hikeklu hohne mnikawnakanepa.
Jesus Yokanatka Yine Ralixjenepa Riwekkajyawaka PiranapniHoyakalu psol-tshijneka hajene ramotle tshinanu hyokanatlu hituru satupkalutu ptowru yineru ralixjene hi rupnanna seyni riwekanna hikeklu hohne mnikawnakanepa.
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu yokanatlu hituru riwekkajyawakna ptowru neruka seyni hi hyokanatlu hituru yine rapnokaxyawakapa.
Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu whene halixatshine hi rapnokatkana seyni malixkane rapnokatkana klu tshinanu hi ralixluna Hoyakalu whene satupkalutu.
Xyekni hapnokaxikolu: Katalu hapokyehitmakna psol-tshijne hajeneko seyni yine yohnik-hamotlu mapchahawaka kataluya klu tshinanu hektutu hkamhajetna.
Ptowru yineru hektutu kamhatshri hahnanutlu katawaka hiyáhoni rasujyaluna katalu hike mexyawakanuplu hkamhalerna hektutu.
Seyni yineru, hanuruktako homkahitlu halikakalutu pirana katawaka rutajnawa, rimathexikowaka hkamhaleru Hoyakalu hikchikhihlenrerni wale.
João Batista Hinkaklexyawaklu Cristo Pirana PiranapniWaneya wane wkatanu Jesus hiyrunu rasruklene Judeia tshijne rapokatkana. Waneya wan-rutukatka rasrukleneyma. Wane h-batiz-lewjexya.
Hiyrun-koxa João tshinkaluru Enom poktshi h-batiz-lewakanaxya, Salim poktshistsi hajeruya, klu tshinanu honha wane hi hmahaxya hiyrunu wane hyajetna yine h-batiza-xikowakapna.
Halikaka waneklu papko João hi hkachitkawa.
Waneya João nwaka hyana, wla htshinruna: — Kasruklewakleru, jeji honra pimwakanatanru Jordão wenne tujra wnahlu mitshi, puphujtapiranaxinri, haha wale himakni h-batiz-lewjexya. Hiyrun-koxa ptowru yine yanwakjetlu.
Waneya João wla tshinna: — Yineru himukata himwaletlu pa hixanu Hoyakalu henejini tsonru.
Hixni nimetjenhi wla ntshinreru mitshi: “Hi Messias-no hita seyni nyokanatka wale wkatanu napojyawakpatka.
Yapkaklupa. Hnunrowatatshri yehi, waleni khanunrolu. Seyni hnunrowatatshri himatletjeru repixlu rimotsatlu hnunrowatatshri hiyrunu hyijnakotlu. Hiyrun-koxa hnunrowatatshri tokanu hjemini rumuwata. Hnunrowatatshri hepixatshri pixka nix-hita hiyáhoni numuwpotuthonuka hnunrowatatshri tshinanu.
Wale hijhalu pnut-potu hya hijhakaluru rixyawaka seyni hita kayaho hijhakalurupno.
Tenhohne Hichpajikatshri PiranapniHalikaka tenhohne hichpajikatshri ptowru neruka pnuterutni wale. Seyni xye tshijne hichpajikatshri xye tshijne hajerukni wale hiyrunu xye tshijne hajeru pirana kochtshekatshrini. Tenhohne hichpajikatshri ptowru neruka pnuterutni.
Runkakletlu retanru pirana hiyrunu hyijnakotanru pirana. Seyni hike yineru haluk-halixletanru runkakle pirana.
Hanuruktako yineru, runkakle halixatshri, rekhipotutlu halikakni Hoyakalu.
Hoyakalu yokanatanru, Hoyakalu tokanu runkakletjeta. Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu hi psotsonujiji Hiwejikaluru reneklu seyni Hiwejikaluru psoluka reneklu.
Hoyakalu Hirtshi hamotlu Whentshi tshinkaluru. Hiyrun-koxa wale towre rutajyalu ptowru potukananuka.
Wale tshinanu Whentshi tshinkaluru halixatshri himwalu hiweklu hike rixiniko mnikawnakatu. Seyni Whentshi tshinkaluru malixkatu hi rawyalu riwejinri seyni Hoyakalu hapnokaxyalu hikeklu hohne rasujinri.
Suxo Samaria-nero PiranapniJesus hima João tshinkaluru yohnik-homkahitatshine rawya hiyrunu João yohnik-hima h-batiz-jeta Jesus. Waneya fariseu-ne jemlu xye pirana.
(Seyni Jesus hi batiz-jekanata halikaka rasruklene tsonu batiz-jekanatna.)
Jesus himaxinixka wane htshinyehikanaxyawakluna waneya Judeia tshijne ruchpajyatka. Hsatoka Galileia tshijne nwaka.
Samaria tshijne raluka yaplemta.
Waneya satu poktshi Samaria tshijne hajeru poktshi rapoka, Sicar tshinikowaka, Jacó-ni mitshi hituru José-ni renektshijnererustsi.
Wanekananru Jacó-ni hakophale tshinikowaka. Hanikaj-hohnestsi hetkotkani ramanutatka Jesus hyanre tshinanu waneya hakophastsi htuplatatka Jesus.
Waneya sato suxo Samaria-nero wane tapoka t-sajkapyawakapa. Waneya Jesus wan-tshinro: — Honha putanno.
Klu tshinanu Jesus hasruklene poktshi nwaka hyatkana nijittshi ranjixyawakapna.
Waneya suxo Samaria-nero wla tshinru: — Haklu tshinanhe panjitno hita Samaria-nerno honha nuxyawakapyi klu tshinanu pixa honukla judeu-neryi pixa? (Wane ttshina suxo klu tshinanu judeu-ne hi rimatletkakna Samaria-nerune.)
Waneya Jesus hihitlo wla htshinro: — Pimatkamkalu Hoyakalu henekachle hiyrun-koxa pimatkamkalu panjitjeru wla tshinatshri, honha putanno waneyamka honha panjixinru wale waneya walemka henekanyi honha hiweklu heneklewatatshri.
Waneya suxo wla ttshinru: — Honha sajikapi hi pwiya hiyrun-koxa tenopnalu honha yehi. Hiyáhoni hanhe pixa kochpakletanru xye honha hiweklu heneklewatatshri?
Pixlahe wutsrukate Jacó-ni yohnika tsru hixikatshriwayi? Walenikni henekwu xye hakopha. Hiyrun-koxa wale potniko xye honha hirjekanatni wale, hiwhenene hiyrun-koxa hiprane.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinro: — Ptowru yineru xye honha hiratshri hiyrunukotnaka ronunnahatewatanu.
Seyni katuktako honha hita henekjexyalu hiratshri hikeklu ronunnahatewatanu. Klu tshinanu honha hita henekjexyalu hakopha rixnatkawa hisatu hitokoteya. Hiweklu hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa renekanru.
Waneya suxo wla ttshinru: — Nanjityi penejyawakapno xye honha hikeklu nonunnahatewatanutka. Wan-hixatshrono hi nujhalu hewi nsajkapyawakatka.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinro: — Ptomhapanru phanuru. Hewitshi hinanu.
Seyni suxo hihitlu wla ttshinru: — Hita hi khanurno. Waneya Jesus wla tshinro: — Halikaka ptshina, hi khanurno, ptshina.
Klu tshinanu cinco kata jejine phanurutatka halikaka xye jeji xawakni potuko pimwaleru hi phanurni wale. Hiyáhoni halikaka tokantshi ptshina.
Wutsrukatenni xye mrijiko rimalwuxyatkaluna Hoyakalu, seyni hixa judeu-nhi wane htshinjeta Jerusalém poktshi Hoyakalu himalwuxikowakni halikaka.
Waneya wla htshinro: — Suxo palixanno. Rapokhohnetanu hike yineru himalwutanru Hoyakalu hewi xye himrijiya, hi Jerusalém poktshiyako.
Hixa Samaria-nerunhi hi himatlu kluneru potu himalwujeta, seyni hixa judeu-nwu wimatlu wimalwutanru klu tshinanu judeu-ne yehi runya hiwekkaklewatatshri.
Seyni rapokhohnetanu, halikaka wale hohne hapokatka, Hoyakalu himalwutatshine potu himalwutanru Hirtshi Hoyakalu riwejinriyna hiyrun-koxa hpotuknu hchinikanuymana. Klu tshinanu Hirtshi Hoyakalu halukna rimalwutjene wane pixka hixatshine rixyawakna.
Hiwejikalurni Hoyakalu hiyáhoni rimalwutjene haluk-himalwuretlu riwejinriyna hiyrun-koxa hpotuknu hchinikanuymana.
Waneya suxo wla ttshinru: — Nimatlu Messias honukla Cristo tshinkaluru hinanu halikaka. Runiniklunu ptowru potuko ruhle hinkakletanwu.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinro: — Walekno hita, hitakni hiynumsatyi pixa.
Waneklu papko potuko rapokatkana rasruklene. Rimyekna suxo riynumsakanaxyawaka. Seyni hi satukna wanna hepomhatkalo suxo klu talukatka. Hiyrun-koxa hi repomhatkaluna Jesus klu tshinanhe riynumsakanatlo.
Waneya suxo hiknokahachhajremta. Tyatka poktshi nwaka. Yine tunkaka.
— Hinanu hetapanru satu jeji ptowruka nkamhaleru nunkakjeru. Hi he xawaka Cristo-katkani wale?
Hiyáhoni wale poktshi ruchpajyatkana. Jesus nwaka hyatkana.
Jitaklewaklerune, Hamatshine PiranapniWaneya wane pchinika Jesus hasruklene nikjixmaklu. Wla htshinruna: — Kasruklewakleru, pnikanu.
Seyni wale wla tshina: — Knijitno nniklerupa hmetjejetanutu.
Wale tshinanu rasruklene wla htshinkakna: — Hiyáhola satu yineru haniknijitutlu?
Waneya Jesus wla tshinna: — Nnijitni waleni nyokanatjeru halujyawaka nkamhiywaka hiyrunu nnikaxyawakaplu hkamrure nenejikolu.
Hix-honra hasruha wla tshinreta: “Quatro ksuru pejnu mahata wamyawakaplu.” Seyni hjemanru ntshinyawakhi, himrekhatanu hetanru hitakluchakaka, hitaklu serowata, hmahachata ramikowakatka.
Hamatshri wenuxikolu hyoptota. Rapatjeyehixnawa halukkaluru hiweklu hike rixiniko mnikawnakatu tshinanupa. Hiyáhoni hitaklewatatshri hiyrunu hamatshri himumuwatanu.
Xye tshinanni halikaka pirana htshinna wla tshinatshine: “Satni hitaklewatatshri, satni hamatshri.”
Nyokanathi hamyawakaplu hma mutakanutuko yehi. Pimrine wane kamrurewaxyatka waneya hixa wanna kamrure-ptako hjihlokachatatka.
Hixolune Samaria-nerune Halixyawaklu Jesus PiranapniHixo Samaria-nerune wale poktshi hajene halixlu Jesus klu tshinanu suxo wla ttshinakanata: “Runkakno ptowruka nkamhakanatanru.”
Waneya Samaria-nerune hapyehixinru Jesus, ranjitluna wanna yehi rutujyawakapa. Hiyáhoni hepi hohne pejnu wan-rutukatka.
Hiyáhoni pimrine hixolune halixlu waleko htokanu tshinanu.
Wla htshinrona suxo: — Hi pixa ptokanu tsonu tshinanni seyni waleko htokanu wjemyawaka tshinanu walixlu. Wimatlu halikakni Cristo-ni wale ptowru tshijne Hiwekkakatshrini wale.
Jesus Satokanwakaxyawaklu Galileia Tshijne PiranapniHepi hohne wan-rutukatka waneya wane ruchpajya. Galileia tshijne nwaka hyatka.
Jesus honra mitshi wane htshinatka, “Muphujewnakatuwa pirana hinkakletatshri hi hkahwakpiratka waleko htshijneya.”
Waneya Galileia tshijne rapojinixka Jesus, kihle yoptole rixluna wane hajene. Tsru niklu hohne Páscoa hohne tshinanu, Jerusalém poktshi hyatkana wanna koxa hiyáhoni wane rexyaluna ptowruka Jesus kamrure wane hkamhakanaxinritka.
Jesus Hitskalajyawaklu Phuru Whene PiranapniJesus satokanwakatlu Caná poktshi Galileia tshijne hwatshri Jesus mitshi honha vinho-ha kamhiywaka nwaka. Wanekananru satu phuru, yeyixawhenetatshri Cafarnaum poktshiya.
Waneya hjeminixka phuru Jesus Judeia tshijne ruchpajyawaka pirana Galileia tshijne hyiywaka waneya Jesus yehi hya. Ranjitlu Jesus hituru nwaka hyiywakapa rutskalajyawakaplu klu tshinanu hiwhene hipnakastsitkani.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Hetkaluru ho himyekaklewatatshri hma metkanuklunu, hi hetko halixanu.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Pyanutka pipji nwaka. Piwekawhenethonuka. Jeji halixtokanutlu Jesus hiyáhoni hyatka.
Hipji nwaka hyapamtawa htowrene yoptotlu. Runkakluna, wla htshinruna: — Piwekawheneta!
Waneya repomhana klu papko hyinuwaka hihlewleta. Wanna wan-tshinru: — Kapethohne, kayi sreta uma hora, rutuk-patshwaleta.
Hiyáhoni tsru himatatkalu Jesus tshinyawaklu mitshi: “Piwekawheneta” htshininiklunru klu papko potuko wan-rixatka. Waneya ralixatka wale hiyrunu hipji hajene ptowruneka halixatka.
Xyekni hepi rixinri hetkaluru Jesus kamhaleru Judeia tshijne ruchpajinixka, Galileia tshijne hyinixka.
Jesus Hiktehatshri Hitskalajyawaka PiranapniWaneya wane pnut-hohne tsru niklu hohnetnakni himretkaluru hohne judeu-neya, Jesus Jerusalém poktshi nwaka hya.
Jerusalém poktshi carneiro jihlokawakle tshinikowakastsi rawa satu honha paji cinco hiphaptoterutu. Xye paji wan-tshinka judeu tokanuya “Betesda”.
Hixolune hahijewaktshi kachitanune wane hwa. Tshiji rukoluhakanatna mtsawane, myankane, hiktehatshine. Honha hiyolikle hkahwakakanatna.
Pa katkaka hserpika hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru ruyolikkajyawaklu honha. Hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru hiyolikajinru honha, waneyakni mitshikananhapka honha katsretatshri hima kluneruktako hyeyixale rutskalhiya.
Wanekanan-koxlu satu yineru hahijewaktshi kachreru, trinta e oito mhalerutu.
Waneya Jesus hetlu hikoluhatshri hiyrun-koxa rimaxinixkalu hix-hohne wan-rixyawakatka waneya wla htshinatkalu jeji: — Paluk-hitskalhalethe?
Waneya jeji hiktehatshri wla tshinru: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, hikeni satu yineru honha nutakjeru, ruyoljinipa honha. Hiyáhoni nyahot-jihlokletka pchini satu hapka jihlojyanatkano.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Pyotunotanu, pkochtshekjekomtanu. Pyanutka.
Waneya waneklukawa rexnawa jeji rutskalajikowakatka. Hkochtshekjekomtatka hyanatka. Seyni hapnanuxikalur-hohneni wale hohne.
Hiyáhoni judeu-ne wan-tshinru hitskalakalurutka: — Xawakni hapnanuxikalur-hohneni. Hinanchitkalurni putjijekoxyawaka xye hohne.
Hiyáhoni ruhitna, wla htshinatkana: —Nutskalakjeru wan-tshinno: “Pkochtshekjekomtanu. Pyanutka.”
Waneya repomhatkaluna, wla htshinruna: — Hanurnihe jeji xye pkamhakjixjeru?
Seyni jeji hitskalakalurutka hi himathetlu rutskalakjeru katuktani klu tshinanu Jesus hixolune yine tskala ramhiyatka.
Waneya wane pnut-hohne Jesus yoptotlu Hoyakalupjiya waneya wla htshinru: — Petanu. Putskalakkatka. Hiyáhoni xawakni hi pnute hektuwaka pkamhanu, hmakanhayehixyawakanupyi hektutu wane yohnikalutu.
Wane ruchpajyatka jeji waneya runkakna tsrukakalune judeu-ne, Jesus tshinkaluru hitskalaklu.
Hiyáhoni tsrukakalune judeu-ne yinuwaka kamniretlu Jesus, hiyrunu wannamka haluk-hiylaletlu klu tshinanu xyekaka hkamha hapnanuxikalur-hohneya.
Seyni Jesus wla tshinna: — Nuru haté xawakni hkamrurewata. Hiyrun-koxa hit-koxa kamrurewjeta.
Hiyáhoni tsrukakalune judeu-ne hijha hiylaletlu wane yohnika, hi hapnanuxikalur-hohne hma kahwakpiraxyawakanu tshinanu tsonni seyni Hoyakalu pixka rixnawakwa tshinanni. Klu tshinanu wale wan-tshina, Hoyakalu potuko hima ruruta.
Jesus Hinkaklexyawaklu Hkamrure PiranapniWaneya Jesus wla tshinna: — Halikakni, halikakni wla ntshinhi: Whentshi tshinkalurno hike numukata kamhaleta Nuru mepixkanuklunno. Klu tshinanu kamrurtshi kluneruktako net-kamhaletlu Nuru waleko nkamha hita Whentshi tshinkalurno. Kluneru kamrurtshiktako hkamha Nuru wale potuko nkamhajeta hita Whentshi tshinkalurno.
Klu tshinanu Nuru hamotlu Whentshi tshinkalurno. Rekhitlu Whentshi tshinkalurno ptowru potuko hkamhaleru. Xye kamrurtshikaka yohnikalutu rekhirewatanu, himyejyawakapa hixa.
Nuru hiwekkakjetna hipnatshine, hiweklu renekjetna. Hiyáhoni waneko pixka nix-hita Whentshi tshinkalurno. Hanuruktako yineru naluk-hiwekkakleta, niwekkaklu.
Hiyrun-koxa Nuru hi satukna yineru rukolukanuwnajixa seyni renekno hita Whentshi tshinkalurno ptowru potuko nukolukanuwniywakapa.
Wan-rixa ptowru yineru kahwakpiraxyawakno hita, Whentshi tshinkalurno, Nuru hkahwakpiraxyawakna pixka. Yineru hanuruktako, mkahwakpiratkanuklunupno hita Whentshi tshinkalurno, Nuru Hoyakalu nyokanatjeru koxa hi hkahwakpirata.
Halikakni, halikakni wane ntshinhi, ntokanu jematshri, nyokanatjeru halixatshritka himwalu hiweklu hike rixiniko mnikawnakatu. Hike jikolukanuru waneylu. Seyni hipuktshi riknokajikatka hiweklu hjihlokatka.
Nuru Hoyakalu hiwekkajnawa waleko rumukatle tshinanu. Waneko pixka nix-hita Whentshi tshinkalurno renejyano niwekajnawa hitako numukatle tshinanu.
Hiyrun-koxa renekno hitakkaluru yine nukolukajyawakapa klu tshinanu Yineru Whene tshinkalurno.
Hi himyekanu xye pirana tshinanu. Klu tshinanu rapokhohnetanu yinni ptowrunnika hipuktshi yehi hwatshinni, htokanu hjeminipna waneya hipuktshi yehi ruchpajinna.
Kihleru kamhatshine, riwekkakkona riwejyawakapna seyni hektutu kamhatshine riwekkakkona rapnokaxikowakapna.
Hike numukata kamhaleta hitako nalujyawaka tsonu tshinanu. Hanuruktako Nuru Hoyakalu hikolukanuwnajixno wale nukolukanuwnakaklewaxya. Hiyrun-koxa potukalni nukolukanuwnajixle. Klu tshinanu hi nujhalu hitako nohchinikanu nomkahixyawaka seyni Nuru Hoyakalu nyokanatjeru hihchinikanuko naluk-homkahreta.
Hitapka hinkaklexinri nopirana waneya hike yineru hetko halixanru nuphujetleru pirana.
Seyni waneru satu nopirana hiphujetatshri. Hiyrun-koxa nimatlu halikakni htshinyawaka, nopirana ruphujtatanru.
Hixa yokananwakatlu João nopirana hepomhatshinepa. Hiyrunu wale hiphujtatlu halikakalutu pirana.
Halikaka hi nujhalu yinerucha hiphujtale. Seyni xyekaka pirana ntshinhi hiwekkajikolupa.
Nikotapi nikotle tsrur-potuko pixka rixatka João. Hixa hijhatkalu pchini tsonu himuwpotuxyawaka xye hnikotle tshinanu.
Seyni waneru nuphujtatjeru João yohnik-halukkaluru. Kamrurtshi Nuru Hoyakalu henejyano nnikaxyawakapa, xyekaka nkamhaleru, walekni hiphujtatlu nopirana, Nuru Hoyakalu yokanaxyawakno ruphujeta.
Nuru Hoyakalu nyokanatjeru walekni hiphujtatno hita. Seyni hix-yinhi hikeklu jematkalu htokanu hiyrun-koxa hikeklu hetatkalu himane.
Htokanu hi hixa hitokote hwa. Wan-rixa klu tshinanu hi halixatkalu hyokanatanru.
Hethapotjetlu Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru, hanu htshina. Klu tshinanu hixa kahwaklu wale yonatkaluru tshinanu hikchikanru hiweklu hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatu. Haha walekni hiphujtatlu kat-potno hita.
Hix-yinhi hi haluk-homkahretno, hiwekkajikolupa.
Hi nujhalu yineru tokanuwnale.
Seyni nimathethi hi Hoyakalu hichinikanreta haji hitokoteya.
Nuru Hoyakalu hiwaka nunya seyni hi haluka yoptoletno. Seyni satuko waleko hhiwaka runikmaka walemka halikaka hyoptohihlenutanu.
Hanhe hixa halixletlu hixa, pimrine tokanuwle hjemleru? Seyni hi hijhatkalu tokanuwnalu Hoyakalu satupkalutu nwaka hichpajikatshri.
Hi hkahwakanu njihyehixyawakhi Nuru Hoyakalu yehi. Hixa hikolukjerni Moisés-ni, hixa munanhaleru potuko, walekni hikolukanhi.
Klu tshinanu Moisés-ni halixkamka waneya hit-koxmaka halixanutka. Klu tshinanu nopirana yonatatshrini wale.
Moisés-ni yonreru hmalixkanuklunu hanu hixa halixletokanutanno hita?
Jesus Pão Hixolewkajyawaka PiranapniWaneya wane pnute Jesus kopruhatlu Galileia powha tujra wnahlu Tiberíades tshinikowaka.
Hixolune yine homkahikanatlu Jesus klu tshinanu retluna himyekaklewatatshri Jesus yeyixatshine rutskalajyawaka.
Waneya Jesus satu himriji hkankatka wane htuplata rasrukleneyma.
Páscoa hohne (waleni ruchinikanretluna Egito tshijne ruchpajinrina papko), tsru himretkaluru hohne, judeu-ne hasruha himretletanru hohne hi howukatka.
Waneya Jesus heknojtata retna hixolune yine romkahitjene. Waneya Jesus wan-tshinru Filipe: — Hanhe wanjixinri nijittshi nyi hixolune yine niklerupa?
Jesus himatlu hkamhanrupa seyni wane htshina Jesus, Filipe retumhiywakapa.
Waneya Filipe hihitlu: — Satkaka yineru yoptoxyawakaplu psotsonujiji nikluru wujhalu duzentos prata proji ho pnute.
— Hewiru satu mturu rawya cinco pão cevada kamhikolu hiyrun-koxa hepi chima whene. Seyni hanhe rixa hinanuwletanna nyi yine hixolune?
Waneya Jesus wan-tshina: — Punkakanna yine tshij-hoho htuplaxyawakapna. Wale peklo yehi waneya peklo hwiywaka potuko htuplatna. Pakat-hetkoko cinco mil jejine wane hwakanata.
Waneya Jesus pão hkochtsheka, hpoyahnutlu Hoyakalu waneya Jesus hapsatna pão ptowruneko. Waneko pixka rixlo Jesus chim-koxa. Waneya ptowruneka hi psokta raluka nikletna wane pso hnikna.
Waneya rinanuwaxinixkana yine Jesus wan-tshinna rasruklene: — Hapatjetanru hixetatshri hike hma salewniywakanupa.
Waneya rasruklene hapatjetatkalu hixetatshristsiji cinco pão tshinanu hiyáhoni htsepotatkana doze chiwatu.
Waneya Jesus hiyákole hetakanatatshine wan-tshina: — Xyekni halikaka Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri xye tshijne hinatshripa.
Waneya rimaxinipa Jesus yine haluk-hipokananu kachrexyawaklu wanna pohire rutajyawakluna hsatkapanwakatlu himriji hiyrunupatnaka. Walepka wan-ya.
Jesus Honha Hoho Hyanamxyawaka PiranapniWaneya kayi rixinixka Jesus hasruklene yanwakatlu hipowha.
Waneya kanawa hpokownatkana Jesus hasruklene waneya hyinuwaka kopruhaletatkaluna hipowha, hyanwakamtluna Cafarnaum poktshi nwaka. Waneya rutshpokatka hiyrun-koxa Jesus hi hapokawa wanna hyoptoxyawakapa.
Waneya waneklukawa potuko rakanhatka tsru kanniphalu. Waneya kanniphalu tenoplojha hixkaklu honha.
Waneya cinco ho seis quilômetros pchini ruchpajyatkana Jesus hasruklene retluna Jesus honha hoho hyanamxyawaka. Kanawastsi rapokatka. Jesus hasruklene pikpotuthonukna.
Seyni Jesus wan-tshina: — Hi hpikanu, Hitni!
Hiyáhoni hpoyikonuymana kanawa hpokotatkaluna Jesus. Waneya waneklukawa rapokna ruchinijyawakna tshiji.
Pão Hiwekkaklewatatshri Rixyawaka Jesus PiranapniWaneya wale prika yine hixolune pa sreta wnahlu hitukatshinetka hetlu pa kanawapka mtseroto tsonu wane hwa. Hixolune yine himatlu Jesus hi pokownalo kanawa rasrukleneyma klu tshinanu yine hixolune hetna Jesus hasruklene wannapka yatka.
Waneya wane pchinika pimro kanawkaka Tiberíades poktshi hichpajikatshrokaka hapokastsitlu hixolune mitshi nijyawaklu pão Jesus hali poyahnutlexinixkalu, Hoyakalu mitshi.
Waneya rexinixkaluna Jesus hiyrunu Jesus hasruklene hi wane rawna, kanawkaka hpokownatkana waneya Cafarnaum poktshi sreta hyana Jesus rujhapyawakapna.
Waneya hixolune yine yoptotlu Jesus hipowha pa sreta wnahluya. Waneya repomhaluna: — Kasruklewakleru, hikluhe hewi papokatka?
Waneya Jesus hihitna: — Hixa hi hijhajetno hiyakolukaka hexyawaka tshinanu seyni halikakni hixa hijhajetno klu tshinanu hixa nikatkalu pão, hinanuwatatka.
Xako hi hkamrurewatanu nikkaluru himat-nikawnatshri tshinanu. Seyni hkamrurewatanu nikkaluru hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa tshinanu. Yineru Whene tshinkalurno xye nikluru hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa nenekanhi klu tshinanu Nuru Hoyakalu henekno xye tsru hitakkaluru.
Waneya repomhaluna: — Klunerhe xawaka wkamhanu? Hoyakalu kamrure wkamhiywakapa?
Waneya Jesus hihitna: — Xyekni Hoyakalu kamrure yine halixyawaklu Hoyakalu yokanrerni.
Waneya wane htshinna wanna: — Klu himyekaklewatatshri pkamhanu wexyawakaplu walixyawakapyi? Klunerhe pumukata kamhaletanu?
Wutsrukatene maná hnikna popriwakaya wane htshina yonawahlo potukalu: “Reneklu pão tenhohne hichpajikatshri yine niklerupa.”
Waneya hyanumata Jesus: — Halikakni Moisés hi henekna pão tenhohne hichpajikatshri klu tshinanu pão tenhohne hichpajikatshri halikakalutni walekni Nuru heneklewjeta.
Klu tshinanu pão Nuru heneklewaxya walekni yineru tenhohne serpijikatshri xye tshijne Hiwekkaklewaxikatshrini.
Waneya wanna wan-tshinru Jesus: — Hiyáhoni penekjetanunwu xye pão.
Waneya ruhita Jesus: — Pão hiwekkaklewatatshri Hitni. Katukta yanwakaxinno hikeklu hohne hnatshitanu hiyrun-koxa nalixjeru hikeklu hohne ronunnahatewatanu.
Seyni ntshinyawakhi mitshi, hetmakno seyni hi halixno.
Ptowru pejnu Nuru Hoyakalu henejyano, hinanwakatno. Hiyrun-koxa ptowru pejnu hita nwaka hapokatshri hikeklu maleka nuknokanru.
Xyekni Nuru Hoyakalu, nyokanatjeru halujyawaka. Hi satukna hma mamhiywakanupa renejyano pejnu, ralipre hohnepatka riwekkakona hipuktshi yehiya.
Hiyrunu xyekni Nuru Hoyakalu halujyawaka, Whentshi tshinkalurno hetatshine, hita halixatshine pejnu, hiweklu hike rixiniko mnikawnakatu hkayaxyawakapna. Waneya ralipre hohnepatka niwekkakanna hipuktshi yehiya.
Jesus Tokanu Hmukchikhihlenuxyawakna Judeu PiranapniWaneya judeu-ne hihjekaka klu tshinanu Jesus wan-tshinna pão tenhohne hichpajikatshrini wale.
Waneya wla htshinna: — Hi he Jesus tshinkalurni xye, José tshinkaluru whenni, ruru hiyrunu runro wimathetanunni, xye? Hiyáhoni hanhe xawaka rumukata wan-tshinrexnawa tenhohne hichpajikatshrini wale?
Jesus hihitna, wla htshinatkana: — Hi hihjekakanu hixkakluko.
Hike yineru himukata yanwakletno Nuru Hoyakalu, nyokanatjeru mkosekkanuklunuplu hita nwaka. Waneyapa ralipre hohnepatka hipuktshi yehi niwekkajinri.
Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine yonawahle, wla htshina: “Wanna ptowruneka Hoyakalu hasrukanunepni.” Hiyahokni ptowru yineru Nuru Hoyakalu jematshri, Nuru Hoyakalu himatkalewaxikatshri, yanwakatanno hita.
Halikaka hi satukna yineru hetjejetlu Nuru Hoyakalu. Halikaka satupkalu, Hoyakalu yehi hichpajikatshri tsonu hetjejetlu.
Halikakni, halikakni ntshinhi, Hita halixatshri himwalu hiweklu hike rixiniko mnikawnakatu.
Hitni pão-no hiweklu heneklewatatshrino.
Hixa hitsrukatenni maná nikjekanatni popriwakaya. Seyni rupnanna.
Xyekni pão tenhohne hichpajikatshri. Ptowru yineru wale nikatshri hmupniywakanupa tshinanu.
Pão hiwekkaklewatatshri, tenhohne hichpajikatshri, hitni. Hiyrun-koxa yineru wale nikatshri pejnu hiwekanu, hike rixiniko mnikawnakatupni. Xye pão xye tshijne hiwekle neneklerupa, waleni nohitu.
Waneya ruhjekakpotuthonukna wannakakluko judeu-ne, wla htshinna: — Xye jeji, hanhe rumukata waleko himane henekletwu wnijyawakaplu?
Waneya Jesus hihitna, wla htshina: — Halikakni, halikakni ntshinhi, Jeji Whene tshinkaluru hitu hma mnijyawakanu hiyrunu hihraha hmuryawakanu hi hiwekanu halikaka.
Nohitu nikatshri hiyrunu nohraha hiratshri hiwekanu, hike rixiniko mnikawnakatupni. Hiyrun-koxa ralipre hohnepatka hipuktshi niwekkajinri.
Klu tshinanu nohitu halikakni nikkaluru hiyrunu nohraha halikakni hirkaluru.
Nohitu nikatshri hiyrunu nohraha hiratshri, hita riwejya. Hiyrun-koxa wale niwejya hita.
Nuru Hoyakalu hiwekatshri yokanaxyawakno pixka hiyrunu Nuru Hoyakalu himukatle tshinanu niwejyawaka pixka, waneko pixka rixa ptowru yineru hita nikatshri pejnu. Hita tshinanuko riwekanu.
Xyekni pão tenhohne hichpajikatshri. Hi maná, hitsrukatenni nikjekanatanru pixka rixa. Hnikluna seyni rupnanna wanepnawaka. Seyni xye pão nikatshri pejnu hiwekanu hike rixiniko mnikawnakatupa.
Cafarnaum poktshi rawakanaxini Jesus, hanjihohnewakapji rasruklewjekanaxini xye tokantshikaka htshinatka Jesus.
Satkaka Jesus Homkahiphutatatshri Hma Mukchikhihlenuxyawakluna Jesus Tokanu PiranapniWaneya hixolune rasruklene xyekaka tokantshi hjeminna wla htshinna: — Kyapreru xyekaka tokantshi. Kathe hakot-yoptoletlu xye?
Seyni Jesus himatatkalu waleko hihchinikanuya ruhjekakna htokanu tshinanu hiyáhoni wla htshinna: — Hixlahe himtukahchinikanuta xyekaka tokantshi tshinanu?
Ha hexiniplu Jeji Whene tshinkaluru tenhohne nwaka hsatojinipa rawakanaxyawaka yehi, hanhe hixahchinikanutanu?
Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru waleni henek-hiweklerewatatshri. Wimane hike kochpakatshrini. Tokantshi ntshinyahi waleni Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru, hiweklu reneklewata.
Seyni satkakhi hi halixno. Jesus wla tshina klu tshinanu hyinuwaklekananuko Jesus himathetatkana wanna malixlene hiyrunu rimathetlu katupni hkamnitjerupa, rekhitjerupa.
Waneya wane pnute htshina hinkakleta, wla htshina: — Wale tshinanu wane ntshinhi: Hi satuknako yineru himukata yanwakletno hita, Nuru Hoyakalu mitshitkanuklunru.
Hixolune Jesus Homkahiphutatatshine Hicho Homkahrexyawakanru PiranapniWaneya waneklukawa hixolune Jesus hasruklene hiknokatkalu hiyáhoni Jesus rucho hiyanretna.
Waneya Jesus hepomhatkana rasruklene doze, wla htshinatkana: — Ha hixa, hix-koxlahe hichotanno?
Hixa halixyi, wmunanhayi Pixni Cristo-yi, Hoyakalu hichpajikatshriyi Potukalyi!
Waneya Jesus wla tshinna: — Hi he hitakni nurethi hixa doze-runhi seyni satu hixaymalutu kamtshi pixkalutni?
Judas tshinkaluru, Simão Iscariotes whene pirana hkochtsheka Jesus. Klu tshinanu walekananukni satu wanna doze rixinri, Jesus kamnitjerupa, rekhitjerupa.
Jesus Molene Malixlenu PiranapniWaneya wane wkatanu Jesus hi Judeia tshijne hyapatka klu tshinanu judeu-ne, wane hajene, haluk-hiylaletlu. Hiyáhoni Galileia tshijne tsonu hyapjeta.
Himretkaluru hohne judeu-neya, Tabernáculos tshinkaluru hohne hi howukatka.
Waneya Jesus molene jejine wla tshinru: — Pyanutka, Judeia tshijne nwaka pyanu. Waneya pimrin-koxa pomkahitjene pkamrure retanutkana.
Klu tshinanu satu yineru ralujinri retjejpotuxikowaka, hi rumukata yohimletlu hkamhajetanru. Hiyáhoni xyekaka pkamhaleru pkamhajetanru tshinanu, ptowru yineru hetanu pkamhinri rimathexyawakapyina.
Klu tshinanu hi himoleneko halixatkalu Jesus.
Waneya Jesus hihitna, wla htshina: — Nopapkolu hi hapokawa. Seyni hixa ptowru papkoko himukatatka.
Xye tshijne hajene hi himukata hahnanutlethi hixa, seyni hita rahnanutna klu tshinanu hkamrurna phujewaka nutaklu rimathexikowaka hektutni hkamrurna.
Hiyáhoni hixa tsru niklu nwaka hyanu. Seyni xawakni hitatshi hi wane nyanu klu tshinanu nopapkolu hi hapokawa.
Hiyáhoni rali wan-tshinretatka, Galileia tshijne rutukatka.
Jesus Tsru Niklu Yehi Hyiywaka PiranapniSeyni rali yalexinixkana Jesus molene waneya wale koxa wane yatka Tsru Niklu nwaka. Halikaka hyohimta wane yaleta hmexikowakanupa.
Hiyáhoni judeu-ne hijhamkatkalu Tsru Niklu yehiya. Waneya wla htshinatkana: — Hanutkalhe wale?
Tsru hihjekaklu hkamhana yine hixolune Jesus tshinanu. Satkaka wla tshina: — Kihlerni wale. Seyni pimrine wla tshina: — Hike, wale halikaka yokwijetna yine.
Seyni hi hixolune jemanu wane htshinanwakatluna Jesus klu tshinanu hpikna judeu-ne.
Hihjekaklu Hkamhiywakna Judeu-ne PiranapniWaneya Tsru Niklu hohnekaka hanikajitetkani Jesus wane yatka. Waneya Hoyakalupji nwaka ratskota waneya hyinuwaka hasruklewleta.
Waneya judeu-ne himyekpotuta, wla htshinna: — Hanhe ruchpajya xye rimatkalnu. Klu tshinanu hikeklu ruchtotatatka.
Jesus hihitatkana, waneya wla htshina: — Nasruklewaxya hi hitako nohchinikanni wale seyni waleni Hoyakalu nyokanatjeru hchinikanu.
Satu yineru haluka kamhalexinri Hoyakalu halujyawaka, rimathetanru nasrukle hichpajyawaka pirana, ho Hoyakalu yehi hichpajikatshrira ho hitako ntokanra.
Klu tshinanu waleko hipirana kochtshekatshri, rujhalu waleko hiwaka hpohixikolupa. Halikaka hanurukta himalwutlu hyokanatjeru, wale halikaka, halikaka pirana hinkakletatshri hiyrun-koxa hi kaweylu.
Hi he Moisés-ni henekatkahi yonruru pirana seyni hi satuknako hixa homkahitlu. Hiyáhoni klu hikolukle tshinanhe haluk-hiylaletno?
Waneya yine hixolune hihitlu, wla htshinatkana: — Pix-hetko kkamtshite. Klu tshinanu kathe haluk-hiylaletanyi?
Jesus hihitna, wla htshina: — Nkamhatkalu himyekaklewatatshri hiyáhoni wale tshinanu hixa ptowrunekhi himyekatka.
Halikakni Moisés-ni henekatkahi jiprojhaptojimtaxikolu pirana (seyni hi Moisés-ni ruchpajya seyni hitsrukatenni ruchpajya halikaka). Hapnanuxikalur-hohneko hjiprojhaptojimtakjixlu jeji.
Jeji mturu honra hapnanuxikalur-hohne hjiprojhaptojimtakjixa hiyrun-koxa wan-hix-hixa Moisés-ni yonreru pirana hma mayxajyawakanupa. Hiyáhoni kluneru tshinanhe hahkanno hapnanuxikalur-hohne satu jeji mane psoluka nutskalajinixka?
Hi hikolukanuwnayehlewatanu rohocha tshinanu tsonu seyni halikaka piranayma hikolukanuwnayehlewatanu.
Jesus Hyahot-kachrexyawakna Judeu-ne PiranapniWaneya satkaka Jerusalém hajeru wla tshina: — Hi he xyekni jeji raluk-hiylaletna yine?
Hetanru. Ptowru yineru hetanu hyanumsata. Seyni hike htshinruna judeu kosekatshine. Hiyáhola rimathetluna xye jeji halikakni Cristo tshinkaluru rixyawaka?
Seyni Jesus Hoyakalupji rasruklewakanaxini tsru tokanuyma wla htshina: — Hix-yinhi himathetno hiyrunu hi wale tsonu seyni himatkoxlu nuchpajyawaka sreta. Hi nuna hitako nalujyawaka tshinanu. Nyokanatjeru halikaka halikakni, seyni hi himathetlu.
Seyni hita himathetlu, klu tshinanu wale yehi nuchpajya hiyrunu waleko yokanatno.
Waneya wannamka haluka kachretlu. Seyni hi satukna yineru yahot-kachretlu klu tshinanu Jesus papkolu hi hapokawa.
Waneya hixolune yine halixlu Jesus, wla htshinna: — Cristo tshinkaluru hapojinipa xyekaka himyekaklewatatshri xye jeji kamhaleru yohnikalutlahe hkamhanu wale?
Seyni fariseu-ne jemlu tokantshi yine hixolune tokanu Jesus piranyehi. Hiyáhoni fariseu-ne hiyrunu tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne yokanatna Hoyakalupji hinotatshine Jesus-mka hkachixyawakna.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinna: — Pchini tsonu nimwanhi waneya wane pnutepa nyokanatjeru nwaka nyanu.
Hixamka hijhanno seyni hi hikchikanno. Hiyrun-koxa nyiywaka yehi hi himukata yaleta hixa.
Waneya judeu-ne yinuwaka yanumsaleta wannakakluko, wla htshinatkana: — Hanhe xawaka hyanu wmukchijyawakanuplu? Judeu-ne hipalatkalune judeu mixkane yehi hwatshine nwaklahe hyanu xawaka? Wanerhe xawaka rasruklewtapini?
Klu xawaka raluka tshinreta wane htshinini, “Hixamka hijhinno seyni hi hikchikanno. Hiyrun-koxa nyiywakapa hi himukata yaleta hixa”?
Jesus Honha Hiweklu Heneklewatatshri Pixka Hixyawaka PiranapniTsru niklu hijhakaluru hohne potu nikawninixka Jesus palna waneya tsru tokantshiyma wla htshina: — Yineru hanuruktako honunnahatewatatshri yanwakatanno. Ruranu.
Nalixjeru, Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru tshinyawaka pixka rixanu: “Raji hitokote ruchpakhaxini honha hiweklu heneklewatatshri.”
Seyni xye htshinyawaka, Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru pirana hkochtsheka. Ptowru yineru Jesus halixatshri Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru renejikowaka piranni wale. Seyni Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hi reneklewatawa klu tshinanu Jesus hi hipuktshi yehi riwekkajikawa.
Waneya yine hixolune xye pirana hjeminiklunna wla htshinna: — Xye jeji halikakni Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri potuko wikahwaklu.
Pimrine wla tshina: — Xyekni Cristo tshinkaluru. Seyni pimrine wla tshina: — Seyni Cristo tshinkaluru hi hetko Galileia tshijne ruchpajini.
Hi he Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru wla tshinpiranyehitlu Cristo, Messias tshinkaluru Davi klopichapni hiyrunu Belém poktshi, Davi tshinkaluru poktshite hmatuxini Messias?
Hiyáhoni yine kotspalahchinikankaka Jesus pirana tshinanu.
Satkaka yine kachpiratlu Jesus seyni hi satukna yineru yahot-kachretlu.
Judeu Kosekatshine Malixyawakanru Jesus PiranapniWaneya Hoyakalupji hinotatshine satokanwakatna tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hiyrunu fariseu-ne nwaka. Waneya repomhatkana rapokyehitjene, wla htshinna: — Haklu tshinanhe hi hanikatkalu?
Waneya Hoyakalupji hinotatshine wla tshinatkana: — Hikeklu satu yineru hinkaklewata xye jeji pixka.
Waneya fariseu-ne wla tshinna: — Hix-koxlahe hyokwitatka?
Petluhe satu judeu kosekatshri ho satu fariseu halixyawaklu?
Seyni nyi yine hixolune yonruru pirana mimatkane, Hoyakalu hapnokatkanna wanna.
Nicodemos tshinkaluru, fariseu-ne hepire, Jesus mitshi hoyetshno yanwakatatshri wale wla tshinna:
— Yonruru piranrahe hikolukanuwnayehjixlu satu yineru hma jemahchinikanyehitkoklunuwa hkamhalerukaka mimatpotutkonuklunuwa?
Waneya wanna hihitlu, wla htshinruna: — Pix-koxlahe Galileia hajeryi? Petjepotutanru Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru klu potu htshina waneya pimatanru satu Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri wkahwakleru hi Galileia tshijne ruchpajini.
Waneya satkaka waleko hipji nwaka hyatka.
Himopatlewatatshro PiranapniWaneya Jesus himriji Oliveiras tshinikowaka hya.
Waneya yetshpotukawa Hoyakalupji hyatnaka. Wane hjihloka. Waneya ptowrunek-yine hapokastsitlu. Waneya Jesus tuplatatka waneya rasrukna yine.
Waneya kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine hiyrunu fariseu-ne hanikanwakatlu Jesus sato suxo, timopatlewakanaxyawaka yehi hkachixinrona. Waneya wanna hapatjetatshine hanikajite rutaklona suxo.
Moisés towutwu yonruru piranaya sotluji tunokajexikowakapa wane pixkalone. Ha pixa, hanu ptshina pixa xye pirana tshinanu?
Wane htshinna rutseklexyawakluna Jesus, rumukata jihyehrexyawakapluna. Waneya Jesus yonohita. Tshiji hyonata himyojiya.
Pnuteko hya hepomsaletluna hyotunota. Waneya wla htshinna: — Katukta hektuntshi mwikanhi, wale hapka hinokanro sotluya.
Waneya hyonohitatnaka. Tshiji hyonatatnaka.
Waneya xye hjeminixkana, hyatkana. Satkaka yatka. Tsrutsolejinkaka hapka yatka. Waneya Jesus-pka hiknokamtkatka hiyrunu suxo hanikaji hwakanatatshro.
Waneya Jesus hituka yonohletatka. Hi satukna yineru retatka. Suxo tsonupka hitukatka. Waneya Jesus wla tshinro suxo: — Suxo hanutkanhe pukolukanuwnakakjene? Hikehe hikolukanuwnayehjixatkayi?
Waneya wala wla tshina: — Hiketkani, Hasruklewatatshri. Waneya Jesus wla tshinro: — Hi hitako hikolukanuwnayehkakyi hiyáhoni pyanutka hi pektuwatanutka hiyrunu.
Jesus Xye Tshijne Nikotatshri Rixyawaka PiranapniJesus pnute hya tshinretatnaka, wla htshinna fariseu-ne: — Hitni katalno xye tshijne hajene ptowruneka tshinanu. Hita homkahitatshri hi mapchahawaka yanatshripni seyni rawanu katalu hiweklu heneklewatatshri.
Hiyáhoni fariseu-ne wla tshinru: — Pix-nanuko hiphujtaxnawakwa tshinanu hi kmixkonru ptshinyawaka.
Waneya Jesus hihitatkana, wla htshina: —Yáholu hita nanwaka hiphujtaxnawa wanepnawaka halikaka piranni ntshinyawaka. Klu tshinanu nimatlu nuchpajyawaka sreta hiyrun-koxa nimatlu nyiywakapa sreta hanu nyanu. Seyni hixa hi himatlu nuchpajyawaka sreta hiyrun-koxa nyiywakapa sreta hi himata.
Hix-yinhi hikolukanuwnakaklewata yine hixannu tshinanu tsonu. Hita hi satukna yineru nukolukanuwnakaka.
Seyni nukolukanuwnajixlewaxinmaka halikakapni wale nukolukanuwnajixlemka. Klu tshinanu hi hita tsonu hikolukanuwnajixlewata seyni Nuru, nyokanatjeruyma nukolukanuwnajixlewata.
Hiyrun-koxa yonruru pirana homkahle wla tshina, Hepi yineru hiphujtale tshinanu ralixka ruphujtalerna.
Satu nopirana hiphujtatatshri hitni hiyrunu hepi rixinri nopirana hiphujtatatshri waleni Nuru nyokanatjeru.
Waneya wla htshinatkaluna: — Hanutkalhe Puru ptshinreru? Waneya Jesus hihitna, wla htshinna: — Hi himathetno hita hiyrun-koxa Nuru hi himatheta. Hita himathetkamka Nuru koxamka himathetanu.
Xyekaka tokantshi htshinatka Jesus, tiyiro hapatjexikowaka hruko Hoyakalupji hwatshri hruko, rasruklewakanaxini Jesus. Hiyrunu hi satukna yineru yahot-kachretlu klu tshinanu Jesus papkolu hi hapokawa.
Jesus Hinkaklexyawaklu Waleko Hipirana PiranapniWaneya Jesus wla tshinna hiyrunuko: — Nyanutka. Hitamka hijhanu seyni hixannu hektunuko hipninina. Nyiywaka sreta hi himukata yaletanu.
Waneya judeu-ne wla tshina: — Walenanuklahe hiylaxinwa? Klu tshinanu wale wan-tshina, Nyiywakapa sreta hi himukata yaletanu.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinatkana: — Hixni xye tshiji hwatshinhi. Seyni hitni teno hajerno. Hixni xye tshijne hajenhi seyni hitni hi xye tshijne hajerno.
Hiyáhoni wane ntshinatkahi, hixannu hektunuko hipnanutka. Klu tshinanu halikakni hmalixkanuklunno hixannu hektunuko hipnanutka.
Waneya wanna wla tshinru: — Katyihe pixa? Waneya Jesus wla tshinna: — Ptowru papkoko ntshinyawakatkahi walekno hita.
Hixo piranamka numukata tshinrenwakathi hiyrunu hixo pirana tshinanu naluk-himlukantalethi. Seyni halikakalutni nyokanatjeru. Nyanumaxyalu nyokanatjeru tshinyawaka tsonu nunkakjetna xye tshijne hajene.
Seyni wanna hi himatjemlu ruru Hoyakalu pirana runkajyatkana.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinna: — Hixa teno hitajinpatkalu Jeji Whene tshinkaluru, waneya halikaka himatanu waleno, hita. Hiyrun-koxa himatanu hike nkamha hitako nohchinikanu halukanru. Seyni Nuru Hoyakalu hasrujyano pirana tsonu nyanumaxya.
Hiyrun-koxa hitaymalu nyokanatjeru. Nuru Hoyakalu hikeklu hiknokanno. Klu tshinanu rukchikhihlenreru tsonu nkamhajeta.
Xyekaka tokantshi hyanumaxini hixolune yine halixatkalu.
Waneya Jesus hiynumatna judeu-ne ralixjene, wla htshinna: — Ntokanu hpaklu homkahrexini waneya nasruklenepotpakhi halikaka.
Hiyrun-koxa halikakalutu pirana himatanu hiyrunu hichotkalunpatkahi halikakalutu pirana tshinanu.
Waneya ruhitluna, wla htshinruna: — Hix-honra Abraão-ni klopichwu. Hikeklu hohne satu yineru towrertshi hixkakwu. Hiyáhoni hanhe pumukata wan-tshinretwu, hichotkalune wixyawakapa?
Hiyrun-koxa towrertshi hi ptowru hohneruka himolene yehi rawa. Seyni wanepnawaka whentshi himolene sreta hajerukni.
Hiyáhoni Whentshi tshinkaluru hichokajiniphi waneya hichotkalunpotpakotkahi.
Nimata hixni Abraão-ni klopichanhi. Seyni haluk-hiylaletno klu tshinanu ntokanu hi kwawakleru hix-yehiya.
Netleru, wale ptowruka Nuru Hoyakalu hekhixyano nunkakleta. Hiyrun-koxa hixa hkamhajetanru wale ptowruka hixako hirune hasrujyatkahi.
Waneya ruhitatkaluna Jesus, wla htshinruna: — Abraão-ni honra wurni. Waneya Jesus, wla htshinna: — Abraão-ni whenene hixkamka, Abraão-ni hixjekanaxyawaka pixka hixanumka hixa.
Seyni xawakni haluk-hiylaletanno hita. Hit-honra hinkakatkahi halikakalutu pirana Hoyakalu hinkajyano pirana. Abraão-ni hi wane pixka hixatka mitshi.
Hixa kamhajetlu hiru kamrure. Waneya wla htshinruna: — Hixni whentshine potwu, hi kahnete hakanhikatshinwu hixa. Wuru satupkalutni, waleni Hoyakalu.
Jesus wla tshinna: — Hoyakalu hirutkamka, hixamka halukanno hita. Klu tshinanu Hoyakalusko hichpajikatshrino hita hiyrunu hewitkano. Hiyrun-koxa hi nyokanaxnawa seyni Nuru yokanatno.
Haklu tshinanhe hixa hi himatjemlu ntokanu? Hi himatjemlu klu tshinanu hixa hi himukata yijnakoletlu nunkakle.
Hixa hirni, Tsru Kamtshi, hichpajikatshinhi. Hiyrunu hiru hikchikhihlenreru hektutu hkamhanu. Waleni jiylalewakleru hyinuwaklekananukawa. Halikakalutu pirana mimwakatni wale. Klu tshinanu hikeklu rimwatkalu halikakalutu pirana. Hweyawaxini, waleko hihchinikanu tshinanu wan-rixa. Klu tshinanu kayloklerni wale hiyrun-koxa ruyakotlu weyawlu.
Halikakalutu pirana nunkakjexyawakhi tshinanu hixa hi halixtokanutno.
Hanurhe hixa satkakhi himukata hetlepotutno hektuwaka kamhakleru nixyawaka? Hiyáhoni halikakalutu tokantshi ntshininhi haklu tshinanhe hi halixtokanutno?
Hoyakalu yehi hichpajikatshri yijnakotlu Hoyakalu tokanu. Hiyáhoni hixa hi hyijnakotlu klu tshinanu hixni hi Hoyakalu yehi hichpajikatshinhi.
Waneya judeu-ne hihitlu, wla htshinruna: — Hi he halikaka pirana wtshina, wla wtshinanwakaxinyi, Samaria hajeru wtshininyi, hiyrunu wla wtshininyi kkamtshityi?
Waneya Jesus wla tshinna: — Hi kkamtshitno. Seyni halikaka Nuru Hoyakalu hiwaka npohita. Seyni hixa hektuwaka htshinanwakatno hita.
Hi nujhalu hita nanwaka pohixnawakwa. Seyni rawa satu nimalwutjerupa hiyrunu waleni hetamayxaklerewatatshri potuko.
Halikakni, halikakni ntshinhi, hita ntokanu homkahpotutatshri, hikeklu hipuktshi kachitanru wale.
Waneya judeu-ne wla tshinru: — Ha, xawakni wimatyi kkamtshityi halikaka. Abraão-ni hipnana hiyrunu Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine mitshikawlunni hipnana. Seyni pixa wan-tshina katukta homkahpotutlu ptokanu, hipuktshi hikeklu kachitanru wan-hixatshri, ptshina.
Pixlahe kahwajnawa hipnatshrini wurni Abraão-ni yohnika tsru pixyawaka? Hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu tokanu hinkaklewatatshine mitshikawlunni ptowrunekni hipnana. Hiyáhoni kathe pikahwajnawa?
Jesus wla tshina: — Hita nanwaka npohixiniklunwa, npohixnawakwa hike kochpaka. Npohitjeru waleni Nuru Hoyakalu. Hixa Hoyakalute htshinreru.
Hixa hi himathetlu wale seyni hita himathetlu. Hitamka wla ntshininipa, hi nimathetlu, waneyamka kaweyalno hita hixa pixka. Seyni nimathetlu hiyrun-koxa nomkahitlu htokanu.
Hirni Abraão-ni rumuwatni ret-hapoklexinno. Retlu hiyrunu rumuwatni.
Waneya judeu-ne wla tshinru: — Pix-hetko hi cinquenta mhaletkayi seyni Abraão hima peta?
Waneya Jesus wla tshinna: — Halikakni, halikakni wane ntshinhi, Abraão-ni mmatutkanuklunuwa, nwakotka.
Waneya sotluji hkochtshekna hsotlujexyawakapmakluna seyni hi retkatka Jesus. Hoyakalupji ruchpajya.
Jesus Mayhaletu Retkajyawaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus yamxini retlu satu jeji mayhaletu. Hmatuxinikawa mayhaletni.
Waneya Jesus hasruklene hepomhatkalu Jesus, wla htshinruna: — Kasruklewakleru, kathe hektuwatatka, xye jeji mayhaletu ho ruru ho runro? Klu tshinanu mayhaletuko hmatuxyatka xye jeji.
Jesus wla tshinna: — Hi rektunu tshinanu hiyrunu hi rurune hektunu tshinanu wan-rixa xye jeji mayhaletu. Seyni wan-rixa Hoyakalu kamrure himathexikolupa xye jeji tshinanu.
Nujhalu nyokanatjeru halukanru nkamhiywaka, hohi rixka pchinika. Klu tshinanu hoyetshno hapokanu. Waneya hoyetshno rixinpatka hike kamrurewatanu.
Waneya rali wan-tshinretatka, tshiji rutskahata. Waneya hitskaha ruhaklu kajpa. Waneya mayhaletu yhale hsahajpatlu kajpa.
Waneya wla htshinru mayhaletu: — Hajewa. Honha himrexikowaka Siloé tshinikowaka pyanu wane perokayhalexinwa. Siloé, raluka tshinreta ‘yokanatkaluru’. Hiyáhoni hyatka, wane hya. Rerokayhalexnawa waneya hsatokatka retatka.
Waneya rimwastsirene hiyrunu pimrine mayhaletukananu himathetatshine wla htshinyehitluna: — Hi he xyekni tuplajekanatatshri, hanjijekanatatshri?
Satkaka wla tshina: — Hehe walekni. Seyni pimrine wla tshina: — Hike, seyni wale pixkalutni. Seyni waleko wla tshina: — Hitakni.
Hiyáhoni wla htshinruna: — Hanhe pixa himrekhaletatka?
Waneya ruhitatka wla htshina: — Satu jeji Jesus tshinkaluru kajpa hkamha waneya noyhale hsahajpatlu. Waneya rerokayhalekjixno honha himrexikowaka yehi Siloé tshinikowakaya. Hiyáhoni wane nya, nerokatkalu noyhale, netatka.
Waneya repomhatkaluna, wla htshinruna: — Hanurnihe? Waneya wale wla tshina: — Hi nimata.
Fariseu-ne Mayhaletukananu Repomhiywakna PiranapniWaneya repomhakjene haniklu jeji mayhaletukananu fariseu-ne nwaka.
Hapnanuxikalur-hohneni Jesus hitskahayma kamhalu mayhaletu rumrekhakajinrijpa.
Waneya hiyrunukotnaka repomhaka mayhaletukananu hanu rixa hetkakletkatka. Fariseu-ne hepomhalu. Waneya mayhaletu wla tshinna: — Kajpa hsahayhaletno, waneya nerokayhaletatka, netatka.
Waneya fariseu-ne wla tshina: — Ha wan-hixatshri jeji hi hetko Hoyakalu hichpajikatshrini klu tshinanu hi hkahwakpiratlu hapnanuxikalur-hohne. Seyni pimrine wla tshina: — Hanu xawakhe rumukata hektuwaka kamhatshri xye pixkalutu himyekaklewatatshri kamhaleta? Hiyáhoni hkotspalahchinikanutatkana yine.
Waneya wla htshinatnakluna mayhaletukananu: — Ha pixa hanu pixahotlu jeji piyhale himrekhakakatshri? Waneya wale wla tshinna: — Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshrini wale.
Seyni judeu kosekatshine hi halixlu mayhaletu rixakanaxyawaka, waneya retkakkatka, haté hetkakkaluru hirune mtomhaknuko pchinika.
Waneya judeu kosekatshine hepomhatkana tsrune, wla htshinna: — Xyerhe hituru, hixa wan-tshinru, mayhaletu matuxikatshri? Halikaka rixini hanhe rixa hetletatka xawakni?
Waneya ruru, runro hihitna, wla htshinna: — Wimatlu xyeni wwuhene jeji hiyrun-koxa wimata mayhaletu hmatuxyatka.
Seyni hi wimata hanukta rixa hetletatka. Hiyrun-koxa hi wimatlu katukta himrekhakaklu. Seyni tsru yinerutkani hiyáhoni wale potuko hepomhanu. Waleko hinkaklexinwa.
Xye tokantshi htshinatka ruru, runro klu tshinanu judeu kosekatshine hpikatkana. Klu tshinanu judeu kosekatshine wane htshinna mitshi pa hchinikanurunepni, katukta yineru hiphujtaxinri Jesus, Cristo tshinkaluru rixyawaka, wale tokantshi tshinatshri hanjihohnewakapji hkochpajiko.
Hiyáhoni wale tshinanu ruru, runro wane htshinna: — Tsru yinerutkani wale, hiyáhoni waleko hepomhanu.
Waneya mayhaletukananu htomhatnakna waneya wla htshinruna: — Hoyakalu tsonu himalwutanu klu tshinanu wimathetlu putskalakjeru ptshinreru hektuwaka kamhatshrikni wale.
Waneya mayhaletukananu hihitna, wla htshina: — Hi nimata ho halikaklahe hektuwaka kamhatshrini xye jeji ho hike. Seyni satu pirana nimata, mayhaletukananno seyni xawakni netatka.
Waneya wla htshinatnakluna mayhaletukananu: — Kluhe rixyi? Hanhe rixa himrekhakakletyi?
Seyni wale wla tshinna: — Nunkakatkahi seyni hi haluk-halixletno. Haklu tshinanhe haluka yijnakoletatnaklu? Hix-koxa haluk-homkahretluhe?
Waneya wanna heyikatkalu mayhaletukananu, wla htshinruna: — Pixa halikaka homkahitlu seyni hixni Moisés-ni tshinkalurni homkahitatshinwu.
Wimata Hoyakalu hiynumaxyawakniri Moisés-ni seyni xye jeji hi wimata hanu potu ruchpajya.
Waneya mayhaletukananu hihitna, wla htshinna: — Halikaka himyekaklewatatshri piranni xye hixa tokanu, klu tshinanu rumrekhakakatkano seyni wanepnawaka hi hima himata hanu ruchpajya.
Ha, wimatlu Hoyakalu hi repixna hektune. Seyni Hoyakalu homkahitatshri hanuruktako yineru hiyrunu ralujyawaka kamhatshri hanuruktako yineru repixa halikaka.
Xye tshiji hiyakotkoklunukawa hikeklu hetko hjempiranyehitka satu yineru himrekhakajyawakatkalu hmatureyakawa mayhaletu.
Klu tshinanu xye jeji Hoyakalu yokanreru hma mixkanumka hikemka rumukata kamhaletanu.
Waneya wla htshinruna mayhaletukananu: — Pixa halikaka hektuntshi matuxikatshriyi, seyni paluk-hasrukletwuhe wanepnawaka? Waneya hanjihohnewakapji hkochpajyaluna hipokananu.
Waneya wale wla tshina: — Nutsrukate, waletshi pekhitanno, hanurni wale, nalixyawakaplu.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Pali hetletatkalu. Walekni piynumsatjeru.
Waneya mayhaletukananu wla tshinru: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, nalixa. Waneya Jesus rimalwutatka.
Waneya Jesus wla tshina: — Nuna xye tshiji, yine hektunu nuphujexyawaka. Yine metkane netkajyawakapa. Hetaphutatatshine hma mexyawakanupna.
Waneya satkaka fariseu Jesus-stsi hwakanatatshine jemlu xye tokantshi waneya repomhaluna: — Hix-koxlahe mayhalenwu?
Jesus wla tshinna: — Mayhalene hma mikahwajiknumkawa, himka hektuntshi hwalerunephi. Seyni hixa wan-tshinnawa, ‘hetatshinwu’ htshina, hiyáhoni hektunu hi hkonka halikaka.
Jesus Carneiro Suslahakleru Pixka Rixyawaka PiranapniJesus wla tshina: — Halikakni, halikakni wla ntshinhi, hanuruktako yineru carneiro himjiywaka hruko hiphaptote hma yapkanuklunu seyni pnuko hyapini, waleni katshowhuru ho ktshowhuwakleru.
Seyni hiphapto jihlojikatshri halikakni carneiro suslahaklerni.
Hiphapto hinotatshri hiphapto hkotpukyehitanru hiyrun-koxa carneiro-ne himat-tokanutlu. Waleko hiprane htomha satkaka thiwakaya. Hkosekna ruchpajyawakna.
Waleko hiprane hkochpajinixka, hkosekna. Carneiro-ne homkahitlu klu tshinanu rimat-tokanutluna.
Carneiro-ne hi homkahitanru satuko yineru hmetjejetanutu seyni rasujyaluna wan-hixatshri klu tshinanu hkahimtatokanutluna.
Jesus-mka hinkakna xye yapkaklu pirana seyni hi rimatjemluna klu pirana raluka tshinreta xye yapkaklu tshinanu.
Waneya wane pnute htshina hinkakleta Jesus: — Halikakni ntshinhi, Hitni hiphaptono carneiro jihlokawakleno.
Wanna ptowruneka hita pnute hapokatshine wannani katshowhurune, ktshowhuwaklerune seyni carneiro-ne hi rimatjemtokanutkana wanna.
Hitni carneiro jihlokawakleno hiyáhoni katukta hita hiknohanu riwekanu, hjihlokanu, ruchpakanu, rukchikanru hnikleru.
Seyni katshowhuru xye tshinanu tsonu runa htshowhuxyawakapna, ruylalewaxyawakapa, hnikaxyawakapna carneiro-ne. Seyni hita hina carneiro-ne jiwekle hixyawakpatka hiyrunu hiweklu hike mmahaxikatutka nenejyawakapna.
Hitni carneiro suslahakleru kihlerno; carneiro suslahakleru kihleru hamtaka hiwekletanu pratshine tshinanu.
Seyni pratshine kamrurewyehichatatshri, carneiro suslahakleru potuko hmixkanuklunu, pratshi mpuratkatu rixini, lobo rexini wale nwaka yamtatshri, ruknokachatna pratshine carneiro, rasuka honuka. Waneya lobo hakakna pratshine hiyrunu rupalkakna.
Pratshine kamrurewyehichatatshri hasukachata klu tshinanu pratshine kamrurewyehichatatshrini wale hiyáhoni hi ramotna pratshine carneiro-ne.
Hitni carneiro suslahaklerno kihleru hiyrunu nimatna noprane carneiro-ne. Hiyrun-koxa noprane himatno hita.
Waneko pixka Nuru Hoyakalu himatno hiyrunu hita himatlu Nuru Hoyakalu. Niwekle namtakanu noprane carneiro-ne tshinanu.
Pimrine pratshine carneiro-ne pixkalune nwiya hi xye carneiro himjiywaka hruko hajenni wanna. Wanna koxa nujha hwapleta. Ntokanu hjemanna. Pa xkehipkapna hiyrun-koxa carneiro-ne suslahakleru satupkaplu.
Wale tshinanu Nuru Hoyakalu hamotno. Klu tshinanu niwekle namtaka numukata kochtshekletatnaklu niwekle.
Hike yineru himukata kochtsheklexyano niwekle seyni namtakanru niwekle hitako nalujyawaka tshinanu. Numukata hamtakletlu niwekle hiyrun-koxa numukatle tshinanu numukata kochtshekletatnaklu niwekle. Nuru Hoyakalu towutno xye nkamhiywaka.
Judeu-ne Kotspalahchinikanuxyawaka PiranapniWaneya hkotspalahchinikanutatnakna judeu-ne xye pirana hjemakanaxyawakna tshinanu.
Waneya yine hixolune wla tshinanwakatlu Jesus: — Wale hetko kkamtshiterni, mahchinikanutni wale. Ha, klu tshinanhe hyijnakjetokanutlu xye?
Seyni pimrine wla tshina: — Htokanu, hi kkamtshiteru tshinyawaka pixka, htshina xye. Hiyrun-koxa rumukathe kamtshi rumrekhakajyawaklu mayhaletu?
Jesus Hoyakalu Rutajnawa PiranapniJerusalém poktshi tsru niklu hohneni, Nurexikolu hohne tshinkaluru hohneni. Katshikleru klu papko.
Waneya Jesus Hoyakalupji psojite, Salomão tshinikowaka hyapamta.
Jesus wla tshinna: — Nunkakamkatkahi seyni hi halixa. Kamrurtshi, nkamhaleru Nuru Hoyakalu towuwle tshinanu, wale hiphujtatno.
Seyni hixa hi halixa klu tshinanu hixa hi n-carneiro-tene hwawakle hajenhi.
Noprane carneiro-ne pixkalune jemtokanutno, nimatna hiyrunu romkahitnona.
Nenekanna hiweklu hike rixiniko mnikawnakatu. Hikeklu rupnanna hiyrun-koxa hi satuknako yineru himukata ninotle yehi kochpaklexyana.
Nuru Hoyakalu pratshine carneiro-ne pixkalune nenekjeru, ptowru potuko tsru potni wale. Hi satuknako yineru himukata Nuru Hoyakalu hinotle yehi kochpaklexyana.
Hita hiyrunu Nuru Hoyakalu satupkalunwu.
Waneya judeu-ne sotlumka hkochtshekatnakna hsotlujexyawakamkapluna.
Waneya Jesus wla tshina: — Hixo kamrurtshi kihleru, Nuru Hoyakalu kamhakjixleru, nekhithi. Hiyáhoni hanuru kamrurtshi xyekaka nkamhaleru tshinanu hsotlujetanmakno?
Waneya judeu-ne kosekatshine hihitlu, wla htshinruna: — Ha, hi satu kamrurtshi kihleru pkamhaleru tshinanu wsotlujetyi seyni hektuwaka ptshinanwakaxyawaklu Hoyakalu tshinanni. Klu tshinanu pixa yineruchayi seyni putajnawa Hoyakalu pixka pixnawa.
Jesus hihitna, wla tshinna: — Yonatkaluru homkahjereru pirana, wla htshin-yonhata, “Hita wane ntshinhi, Hixni hoyakalunhi.”
Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru hi hiknokko hiyrunu htokanu henekkalune hoyakalune htshinna.
Seyni wanepnawaka hixa wan-tshinanwakatno hita Hoyakalu Nurrerno, Hoyakalu yokanreno xye tshiji napojyawaka seyni wanepnawaka hektuwaka ptshinanwakatlu Hoyakalu, htshinjetno. Seyni wane htshina klu tshinanu wla ntshinnawa Hoyakalu Whenno, ntshina.
Nuru Hoyakalu kamrure nma kamhaknumka waneya hi halixanno halikaka.
Seyni Hoyakalu kamrure nkamhini halikaka, yáholu hi hita halixini seyni kamrurtshi nkamhaleru halixanu. Himaxyawaklu hiyrunu halixyawaklu Nuru Hoyakalu himwano hita hiyrunu hita himwalu wale.
Hiyáhoni wannamka hiyrunukotnaka haluka kachretlu Jesus seyni wanna rasujyatka.
Waneya Jordão wenne pa sreta wnahlu, João mitshi batiz-jekanaxyawaka yehi hyatnaka Jesus. Waneya wan-rutukatka.
Hixolune yine hapatjeyehitlu Jesus waneya wla htshinkakna: — João tshinkaluru hikeklu hiyákolu hkamha seyni ptowru xye jeji pirana runkakletahnapuxyalu mitshi halikakni.
Waneya wane hajene hixolune yine halixatkalu.
Lázaro Tshinkaluru Hiwekkajikolu PiranapniLázaro hiyrun-koxa himolerone Maria, Marta, Betânia poktshi hajenni. Seyni Lázaro yeyixakanata.
Twu Maria, yeyixatshri Lázaro mole, honra suxo phamluhalo tuyokjixitlu Jesus Tsru Hixikatshriwa jixi hiyrunu Jesus tojiwu chehi tcheyijixixya.)
Waneya Lázaro molerone hinkakjixlu Jesus: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, pimatletleru pamotleru yeyixa!
Seyni Jesus xye pirana hjemini wane htshina: — Xye yeyixlu hakanhatka hi rupniywakapni Lázaro tshinanni seyni hyeyixle hakanhamta Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu pohixikowakapa hiyrunu hpoyahnutko koxa Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu whene.
Hetanu, Jesus hamotatkana Marta, Maria, Lázaro koxa.
Waneya Jesus jemnixkalu Lázaro yeyixle pirana waneya hi hchireta seyni waneko rutukawa hepi hohne.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinna rasruklene: — Hayewa Judeia tshijne wsatkapanu.
Seyni wanna wan-tshina: — Kasruklewakleru, xawakni potuko judeu-ne wane hajene haluka sotlujrekanatyi seyni wanepnawaka paluka satkapleta wanna nwaka?
Waneya Jesus hihita: — Hi he satu hohne tshinanu waneru doze horas katawaka? Hiyáhoni hohohne hyanini yineru hi rutspetanu klu tshinanu katyehiru.
Seyni hoyetshno hyanini yineru rutspetanu klu tshinanu hi katyehiru.
Hiyrun-koxa wane htshina Jesus: — Wimatletleru Lázaro himkatka seyni wane nyanu nkomyejyawakaplu.
Seyni Jesus haluka tshinreta rupnanatka Lázaro. Seyni Jesus hasruklene kahwakatkalu Jesus wan-tshina rumkachata Lázaro.
Waneya Jesus hinkakna phujewak-potuko: — Lázaro-ni hipnanatka.
Hiyrunu numuwata hi wane nwakanata waleyma hixa tshinanu, hixa halixyawakapa tshinanu. Hayewa wetapanru.
Waneya Tomé, hepirune tshinkaluru, wan-tshinna rimotsatanune: — Hayewa wane wyanu hix-koxa Kasruklewakleruyma wupniywakapa!
Waneya rapojinixka Jesus Lázaro yehi quatro hohnetkani hkapnatkanatka Lázaro-ni.
Hi howukatkalu Betânia poktshi Jerusalém poktshiya, três quilômetros hetkoni.
Hiyáhoni híxona judeu-ne hinanwakatlo Marta, Maria koxa hyokwihchinikanuxyawakapna himolni hipniywaka tshinanu.
Waneya Marta himatyehixinixkalu Jesus runamxyawakatka, tyanwakatlu tyoptoxyawakaplu. Seyni Maria pantshiko tutukatka.
Waneya Marta wan-tshinru Jesus: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, hewiko pwakmaka himka rupnanni nomolni.
Wanepnawaka nimatlu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hikchijinyi klunerukta panjitanru.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinro: —Pimole hiwekanutnaka.
Waneya Marta hihitlu: —Hehe, nimatlu riwekanutnaka hnikawnapiraxin-hohnestsi.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinro: — Hitni hiwekkakatshripno. Hitni hiwekluno. Ptowruka Hita halixatshripa yáholu rupnanu riwekanutnaka.
Hiyrun-koxa ptowruneka hiwekatshine, hita halixatshinetka hikeklu rupnanna. Palixluhe xye?
Waneya wane ttshina: — Hehe Tsru Hixikatshriwa, nalixyi Messias pixyawaka Hoyakalu whenyi xye tshiji hinatshriyi.
Waneya tali tshinretatkalu xye, Marta yatka, ttomhanatkalo tomole Maria waneya wane ttshinro tumsalexyawaklo: — Rapokatka Kasruklewakleru hiyrunu repukyi.
Waneya Maria jeminixkalu xye, tpalnahapkatatka, tyanwakatlu Jesus.
(Jesus hi hapokawa pantshi seyni wanekowalu Marta yoptoxyawakawalu).
Pantshi rawakanatna satkaka judeu, Maria yokwihchinikanupiratatshine. Waneya rexinrona Maria palnahapkaxyawaka pantshi tuchpajyawaka, rimotsatatkalona klu tshinanu wanna kahwakatkalo Maria yomletshi nwaka tyamta waneko ttshiyahaxyawakapa.
Waneya tapojinixka Maria Jesus yehi, tuknojnawa Jesus jixistsi, wane ttshina: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, hewiko pwakmaka himka rupnanni nomolni!
Waneya Jesus hetlo Maria ttshiyahata, ret-koxna timotsatjene koxa htshiyahakanatna. Hiyáhoni hwamonuwatatka Jesus, htshiyahpiratatka Jesus.
Waneya repomhatkana: — Hanhe hkapnatanatkalu? Ruhitna: — Hinanu hetapanu.
Waneya Jesus tshiyahata.
Waneya judeu-ne wan-tshina: — Haha hetanu hi pa hamotlekananukta rixanru Lázaro-ni.
Seyni satkaka wanna judeu-ne wan-tshina: — Xye jeji hitskalaklu mayhaletu. Hi he xawaka rumukatatka kamhaletlu pa hixanu hma mupniywakanu Lázaro?
Waneya Jesus tshiyahpiratatnaka. Hyanwakatlu yomletshi. Hipjita rawa yomletshi. Tsru sotlu hichyapnatlu yomletshi.
Waneya Jesus towutna: — Herutanru sotlu! Waneya Marta Lázaro-ni mole wan-tshinru: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, wale xawaka posunatka klu tshinanu quatro hohne kapnanatkalu!
Ruhita Jesus: — Hi he wane ntshinyi palixinri petanru Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu pixkonu?
Waneya rerutluna sotlu. Waneya Jesus teno yihatatka wane htshina: — Nuru, poyahnu klu tshinanu pyijnakotatkano.
Rali wan-tshinretatka waneya hsaplewatatka: — Lázaro, puchpakanu waneya!
Waneya Lázaro hichpakatka. Lázaro jixi, himyo koxa ruwtoka mkatshri sama, hihoji koxa mkatshri sama sapowakatka. Waneya Jesus wan-tshina: — Hkochpirokanru, petachatanru hyanyawakpatka.
Waneya híxona judeu-ne, Maria himotsatatshine, retluna Jesus kamhanru waneya ralixatkaluna Jesus.
Seyni pimrine yanwakatna fariseu-ne. Waneya wanna hinkakletlu Jesus kamhaleru.
Raluk-hiylalexyawakluna Jesus PiranapniWaneya tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hiyrun-koxa fariseu-ne hapatjeta judeu tsru hitakkaluneyma. Waneya wane htshinna: — Hanhe xawaka wixanu? Xye jeji híxolu hiyakolukaka hkamhajeta!
Wetachaxinri wan-rixyawaka ptowru yine halixanru. Waneya romano chefe-tene hinanwakatanwu, Hoyakalupji hyotkakanna hiyrunu wtshijne hkonanwuna.
Waneya satu wanna, tsru sacerdote hitakkaluru wale mhale potuko, Caifás tshinkaluru wla tshina: — Ha hixa hike himata.
Hi hetko himat-hichinikanuwata, kihlewu satu yineru rupniywakapa hixolune yine tshinanu hma nikaxikowakanupa wtshijne.
Wale wan-tshina xye, hi waleko hihchinikanni wla htshinya, seyni tsru sacerdote rixyawaka wale mhale tshinanu runkakletlu hinamtatshri pirana. Jesus rupniywakapa htshijnena tshinanu pirana.
Hiyrunu hi wale tshijne tsonu tshinanu rupnapini seyni rapatjexyawakapna Hoyakalu whenene ptowru tshijne hipalaxikatshine pa nerunepka rixyawakapna.
Waneya waneklukananuko rujhahchinikanutna hanu rixa himukata hiylaletluna Jesus.
Hiyáhoni Jesus hi phujewaka judeu-ne yehi hyanya. Seyni hyatka pa tshijne nwaka, kahnete poktshiri yine mwiywakanustsi hajeru nwaka hya. Satu poktshi, wale tshijne hajeru Efraim tshinikowaka, rutukatka Jesus rasrukleneyma.
Waneya hi hix-hohne mahatatka Páscoa hohne tshinkaluru rexyawakapna judeu-ne. Hiyáhoni hixolune yine wale tshijne ruchpajyatkana Jerusalém poktshi hkanjiywakapna, runkajikowakpatkana powralune rixyawakatkana Páscoa hohne wkatanu.
Waneya rujhaluna Jesus. Hoyakalupji rawna yine waneya repomhakakna Jesus pirana, wla htshinna: — Ha hixa hanu hixahotlu Jesus, ho runewhe tsru niklu hohne tshinanu ho hike?
Mitshikananu tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hiyrun-koxa fariseu-ne towutna yine, katuktako Jesus yehi himatatshri runkaklewaxinripa, klu tshinanu raluka kachretluna.
Maria Tshinkaluro Phamluhalo Tuyokjixixyawaklu Jesus PiranapniWaneya seis hohne tsonu mahaxinixkalu Páscoa hohne, hipnakanatatshri Lázaro tshinkaluru, Jesus hipuktshi hiwekkajinri, hwajexyawaka poktshi, Betânia tshinikowaka poktshi, rapokatka Jesus.
Waneya wane natshnewlupa hkamhinrina. Marta tshinkaluro nijittshi hitajyana nikatshine. Lázaro satu wanna Jesus-yma tuplatatshine mesa yehi.
Waneya Maria haniklo hanikaji litro phamluhalo kwenuro potu, nardo tskihi kamhikolni. Wala-ha tuyokjixitlu Jesus. Waneya tcheyijixitlu Jesus tojiwuchehiyma. Waneya phamluhalopha pantshi psoluka tupalata.
Waneya satu Jesus hasrukleru, Jesus hekhitapatshri, Judas Iscariotes tshinkaluru, Simão tshinkaluru whene, wla tshina:
— Haklu tshinanhe hi tuchankaka twu phamluhalo trezentos proji tshinanumkapa waneya hike mwikanemka tenekko?
Seyni wane htshina hi hike mwikane ruchinijyawaka tshinanni seyni katshowhuru rixyawaka tshinanu wane htshina. Klu tshinanu k-saco-ne maplu, tiyiro mapa ranikjeta hiyrunu rawjetlo tiyiro wane hitakjetkaluro. Wale tshinanu, wane htshinatka.
Waneya Jesus wla tshina: — Hetachatanro. Klu tshinanu timretlo twu phamluhalo nkapnaxikol-hohne tshinanupa.
Klu tshinanu hike mwikane himwahohnekanatanu seyni hita hi himwahohnekanatanu.
Lázaro Ruylapiraxyawakna Tsru Sacerdote-ne PiranapniJudeu-ne hixolune himatlu Jesus wane rawyawaka. Hiyáhoni wane hyatkana seyni hi Jesus rexyawakapna tsonu tshinanu wane hyana seyni Lázaro, Jesus hipuktshi hiwekkajinri rexyawakapna tshinan-koxa wane hyana.
Seyni rujhahchinikanutna tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hanu rixa himukata hiylaletluna Lázaro tshinkaluru koxa.
Klu tshinanu Lázaro pirana tshinanu hixolune judeu-ne hichotatkana wanna tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne. Jesus ralixna.
Jerusalém Hajene Yoptoxyawaklu Jesus Tsru Poyikowluyma PiranapniWaneya wale prika hixolune yine, Jerusalém poktshi hapokatshine tsru niklu hohne tshinanu, Jesus Jerusalém poktshi rapojyawakapa pirana hjemna.
Kyawe sure ranikamtna waneya hyatkana Jesus hyoptoxyawakapna. Hsaplew-himalwuretluna, wla htshin-sapletna: — Hamotkaluru Hoyakalu! Himalwutkalurni israel-neru Pohire, Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hiwaka hinikatshri!
Waneya Jesus, jumento whene rukchijinixka ratskotjihohotlu, Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru tshinyawaka pixka, rixa.
Mitshikananu Jesus hasruklene hi himatjematkalu xyekaka pirana. Seyni Jesus hipuktshi riwejinixka waneya ruchinikapluna wane potuko hixkaluru Jesus yineya, yonatkaluru mitshikawluru tshinyawaka pixka, Jesus pirana, hinatshripa pirana.
Hixolune yine, Jesus-stsi hwakanatatshine mitshi, Lázaro-ni yomletshi htomhiylu mitshi, hipuktshi riwekkajyalu mitshi, ruphujtatluna Lázaro pirana.
Hiyáhoni xye pirana tshinan-koxa hyoptotapluna hixolune yine, klu tshinanu hjemluna xye hiyákolu hkamha Jesus.
Waneya fariseu-ne wla htshinkakna: — Haha hetanu, hike wkochpaka! Hetpotutanu, ptowrunek-yine homkahitlu.
Satkaka Grego-neru Haluk-hetlexyawaklu Jesus PiranapniWanekananna wannayma satkaka grego-neru Jerusalém poktshi hapokatshine Hoyakalu rimalwuxyawakapna tsru niklu hohne tshinanuya.
Hiyáhoni nyi yine Filipe tshinkaluru, Betsaida poktshi, Galileia tshijne hajeru nwaka rapokna. Waneya ranjitluna, wla htshinna: — Wutsrukate, hixamka haluk-hetletlu Jesus.
Filipe yanwakatlu André tshinkaluru, waneya runkaklu. Waneya wanna hepi, André hiyrunu Filipe hinkakletlu Jesus.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinna: — Rapokpapkolutatka Jeji Whene tshinkaluru royaknu ruphujexikolupa.
Halikakni, halikakni wane ntshinhi, Chijiji tshiji hmapokkanuklunu, hmupnaknuklunupa, wane rawachatanu. Seyni rupninipa, hixo jiplu.
Yineru hamota hiwekletatshri, riwejinri ramtakanu. Seyni hiweklu xye tshijne hajeru mamotkatu, riwejinri rihnanutanu hike rixiniko mnikawnakatupa.
Satu yineru kamrurewyehixinno, romkahitanno. Waneya hanukta nwanu hita wane koxa rawanu nkamrurewyehitjeru. Ptowru yineru hit-yehi kamrurewaxikatshri pejnu Nuru Hoyakalu kihler-pirana htshinanwakatanru.
Xawakni nkojwakahchinikanuta. Klu pirana numukata tshinreta? Numukata wla tshinrethe, Nuru Hoyakalu xye salewaktshi kochpajinno? Hike, klu tshinanu xye papko potuko tshinanu nuna xye tshijneya.
Nuru Hoyakalu, Pixa phiwaka puphujexini. Waneya waneylu tokantshi tenhohneyalutu wan-tshinatshri: — Nuphujetatkalu hiyrunu nuphujetanru hiyrunupakotnaka.
Waneya yine wane hwakanatatshine, xye tokantshi jematshine wane htshinna: — Rutlohleni. Seyni pimrine wla tshina: — Satu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru hiynumatlu.
Seyni Jesus wla tshinna: — Xye tokantshi hi hina hita tshinanu seyni hix-yinhi tshinanupa runatka.
Xawakni rapokpapkolutatka xye tshijne rukolukanuwnayehixikolupa. Xawakni kamtshi xye tshijne towutatshri hallitkotka.
Hita teno nutajikolupa, xye tshijiya, ptowru yineru nkosekanu hita nwaka rapojyawakapna.
Xye tokantshi htshina rimaxikowakapa hanu rixa hiylatkotanu.
Waneya yine wla tshinru: — Hixa jemlu Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru, Cristo tshinkaluru hima hwahohnekanatanu. Hiyáhoni hanhe pukchijyalu wane ptshinyawaka, Jeji Whene tshinkaluru hijhalu teno rutajikowakapa? Hanurnihe Jeji Whene ptshinreru?
Waneya Jesus wla tshinna: — Pchinhohnejiji rawanu katalu hix-yehi hwatshri. Hiyáhoni katawaka hwaka pchinika hyananu, hma kayixyawakanupa. Klu tshinanu mapchahawaka yanikatshri hi himatlu hanu sreta hyamta.
Katalu hwaka pchinhi halixanru. Katalu hajene hixyawakapa. Jesus xyekaka pirana runkakleta waneya hyatka. Wanna yehi ramhiyatka.
Judeu-ne Malixlenu PiranapniHixo himyekaklewatatshri hkamha wanna hetanu seyni wanepnawaka hi ralixluna.
Wan-rixna hpoyahokajyawakapa Isaías tshinkalurni, hinatshripa pirana hinkakletatshri tokanu, wla tshinatshri: “Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu katnihe satu wunkakle halixatshripa? Katu nwakhe ruphujexiko Hoyakalu himukatle?”
Wale tshinanu hi rumukata halixletna, klu tshinanu satu yonhatnaka, wla htshinya Isaías-ni:
“Hiyhalna ruchyatatka hiyrun-koxa hihchinikanna rimaletatka. Hma mexyawakanupna hiyhaleyna hiyrun-koxa mimatjemkanepni hihchinikanuyna, hma mehchinikanuxyawakanupna wan-hixatshine nutskalajyawakamkapa.”
Isaías-ni xyekaka tokantshi htshina mitshi Jesus hoyaknu rexini mitshi waneya wale pirana runkakletatka.
Wanepnawaka hixolune wanna judeu kosekatshine halixlu. Seyni fariseu-ne hpijyawaka tshinanna hi rumukata hiphujetletluna Jesus, hanjihohnewakapji hma kochpajikowakanupna tshinanu.
Klu tshinanu yine hikchikhihlenreru potu rujhatkana, Hoyakalu hikchikhihlenreru pnute.
Jesus Tokanu Hikolujyawakna Yine PiranapniWaneya Jesus tsru tokantshiyma wla htshina: — Hita nalixjeru, hi hita tsonu ralixa seyni wale nyokanatjeru koxa ralixa.
Nuna katalu nixyawaka xye tshijne tshinanupa, mapchahawaka hma wyawakanupa nalixjeru.
Satu yineru ntokanu jematshri hmalixkanuklunupno hi nukolukanuwnakakanru. Klu tshinanu hi nuna xye tshijne nukolukanuwnakajyawaklu seyni nuna xye tshijne niwekkajyawakaplu.
Hita malukkatu hiyrunu ntokanu malukkatu rawya rukolukanuwnayehitjerupa. Ntokanu nunkakletleru walekni hikolukanhi ralipre hohnepa.
Klu tshinanu hi hitako ntokanu nunkakatkahi seyni Nuru Hoyakalu yokanatno wane ntshinyawakapa, nunkakletanrupa.
Hiyrun-koxa nimatlu tokantshi htowuxyano waleni hiweklu hike rixiniko mnikawnakatupa. Hiyáhoni ptowru potuko nunkakletleru pirana wale Nuru Hoyakalu hinkakletjixyano tokanni.
Jesus Herokajixixyawakna Rasruklene PiranapniTsru niklu hohne Páscoa tshinkaluru hohne wkatanu Jesus himatatka rapokatka hipapkolutka xye tshijne ruchpajyawakapa, Ruru Hoyakalu nwaka hyiywakapa. Ruchinikatkana yine walenune xye tshijne hwatshine. Ruchinikhohnekanatna rupninri hohne potuko.
Jesus hiyrunu rasruklene hali nikletatka. Kamtshi koxa hali hitakahchinikanretatkalu Simão whene, Judas Iscariotes tshinkaluru, Jesus rekhixyawakapa hkamnitjeneya.
Jesus himatatkalu ptowru potuko reneklu Ruru Hoyakalu htowuxyawakapa Jesus. Hiyrun-koxa Jesus himatlu Hoyakalu yehi hichpajikatshrini hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu nwaka yatshripni wale.
Waneya nikjexikowaka yehi hpalniyatka. Himkalu roho hajeru kahnete rutaklu. Satu cheymanepi hkochtsheka. Rostuptshijita.
Waneya wane pnute bacia rutakhatlu honha waneya hyinuwaka herokajixletna, rasruklene hiyrunu cheymanepi hiptshiji hostutatshri hcheyijixixyana.
Waneya Pedro-stsi rapoka. Pedro wla tshinru: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa perokajixitenohe?
Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Nkamhanru hi pimatjema xawakni seyni xekoyakpatka pimatjemanru.
Waneya Pedro wla tshinru: — Pixa hikeklu perokajixitanno hita. Waneya Jesus hihitlu, wla htshinru: — Nma merokakanuklunupyi hi psojikna hit-yehi pwini.
Waneya Pedro wla tshinru: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa hi nojixi tsonu perokanu seyni perokanru nomyo koxa hiyrun-koxa nojiwu.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Hijixi tsonu herojikalurutka. Wan-hixatshri powratka psoluka. Hixa powralunhi seyni satu hixa tsonu hi powra.
Klu tshinanu wale honra himathetatkalu rekhitjerupa. Hiyáhoni wale tshinanu wane htshina, “Satupkahi hi powra.”
Han-hixatshrihe Yineru Potu Tsru Hixyawaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus rali herokajixletatkana, himkalu roho hajeru rawatka, htuplatatnaka. Waneya wla htshinna: — Himatjemluhe klu kamrurtshi nixhi?
Hixa wan-tshinjetno, Kasruklewakleru ho Tsru Hixikatshriwa htshinno. Kihleru, wane potuko htshinno klu tshinanu halikakni, wan-hixatshrino.
Hita, Kasruklewaklerno hiyrunu Tsru Hixikatshriwano nerokajixithi hix-koxa hijhalu herokajixkajyawaka, nixakanaxyawakhi pixka.
Klu tshinanu satu hyimlerupa nekhithi hixa. Hiyáhoni hix-yinhi haluka wan-hixletna pimrine hita hixyawakatkahi pixka.
Halikakni, halikakni wane ntshinhi, Towrertshicha hi htowutjeru yohnik-himukatatshrini wale. Hiyrun-koxa yokanatkaluru hi hyokanatjeru yohnika tsruni wale.
Xyekaka pirana himatatshri, kihle hchinikanurupni xyekaka hasrujikolu hkamhini.
Seyni hi hixa ptowruneka nkochtsheka wane ntshinini. Klu tshinanu nimatna nnurrene hanu hixatshinetkani. Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru tshinyawaka hpoyahokajyawakapa tshinanni. Wla htshina yonatkaluru: “Hitayma nijittshi nikatshri pnut-hohne hkamnitanno.”
Hiyáhoni nunkakhapkathi rakanhinipa ntshinyawakhi pirana, halixyawakapno hita nixyawaka.
Halikakni, halikakni ntshinhi, Katuktako yoptoxinri nyokanatanru hit-koxa hyoptotatka. Hiyrun-koxa nyoptojerupa nyokanatjeru koxa hyoptotanu.
Jesus Hinkaklexyawaklu Satu Rasrukleruko Kamnixyawakaplu PiranapniWaneya Jesus hali wan-tshinretatka hkojwakahchinikanuxnawa waneya ruphujetpotutlu wla htshina: — Halikakni, halikakni wane ntshinhi, satu hixa nkamnitjene hekhitanno.
Waneya rasruklene yopukhakaka, hi rimatahchinikanutna katu pirana hkochtsheka.
Wanekananru satu Jesus hasrukleru, ramotleru potuko, Jesus sta hinaple hikoluhatshri.
Waneya Simão Pedro hitsejrihjeta Jesus-stsi hikoluhatshri repomhiywakaplu Jesus katu piranrahe hkochtsheka.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Walepakni hijpa pão yotshmoluru psoji nenekanu. Waneya pão psoji hyotshmota. Waneya Simão whene, Judas Iscariotes tshinkaluru reneklu.
Pão yotshmoluru hnika waneya chinpotukawa Satanás kamtshi jihloklu. Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Wuya pkamhalerupa pkamhahapkatanu.
Hetanu, hi satukna yineru nikawakakwa hwakanatatshine himatlu klu pirana hkochtsheka Jesus wane htshininri Judas.
Klu tshinanu satkaka wanna kahwaklu Jesus hanjikjixlu pa hixanu hmahaxinrina tsru niklu tshinanupa ho tiyiro renekakjixlu hike mwikane, klu tshinanu Judas tshinkaluru honukla hinotjekanatlo tiyiro mapa yehi.
Hiyáhoni rali yoptolexinixkalu pão psoji, hyatka. Hoyetshnotkani.
Herotu Towrexikolu PiranapniWaneya rali yalexinixka Judas, Jesus wla tshina: — Xawaknitka Jeji Whene tshinkaluru hoyaknu hiphujetka. Hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu hoyaknu hiphujetka wale tshinanu.
Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu hoyaknu hiphujexika wale tshinanu. Xawakni Hoyakalu tshinan-koxa ruphujexika wale hoyaknu. Chinpotukawa ruphujexikolupa royaknu.
Nowhenene mtserunhi pchini tsonu nimwanhi. Xekoyaka hijhanumkano seyni judeu-ne ntshinakanaxyawaka pixka koxa ntshinanhi hixa, nyiywakapa nwaka hi himukata yaleta.
Nowhenene mtserunhi herotu towrexikolu nunkakanhi. Waleni hamotkajyawaka. Namotjekanaxyawakatkahi pixka, waneko pixka hix-koxa hamotkajyawaka.
Xye tshinanu ptowru yineru himathetanhi nomkahitjene hixyawaka, hamotkajini.
Jesus Hinkaklu Pedro Wkatakluyakawa PiranapniWaneya Simão Pedro hepomhalu, wla htshinru: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa hanhe pyanu? Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Nyiywakapa nwaka hi pumukata himotsletanno xawakni. Seyni xye pnutpatka pomkahitanno.
Waneya Pedro wla tshinru: — Seyni Tsru Hixikatshriwa, klu tshinanhe hi numukata homkahretanyi xawakni? Klu tshinanu haté niwejinri nuknokanu pixa tshinanupa.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Halikaklahe, haté piwejinri puknokanu hita tshinanupa? Klu tshinanu halikakni, halikakni ntshinyi, hma yanumatkanuklunuwa patlapa, pixa map-kata pweyawatanu. Pma mimatletanutu ptshinanno.
Jesus Hatnu hapo, Halikakalutu, Hiweklu Rixyawaka PiranapniWaneya Jesus wan-tshina: — Hi hwamonuwatanu; hi hkojwakahchinikanutanu. Hmunanhanru Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu, Hit-koxa hmunanhanu.
Nuru Hoyakalupji hixo hwikowaka hwa. Wane hmixkanumka nunkakanmakhi. Wane nyanu nalpokoxyawakaplu hwiywaka hixa tshinanu.
Waneya nyinpatka, hixa hwiywakapa nalpokoxyawakapa, nunanutnaka. Hitako hwapanutkahi, hixa hita hwiywaka hwanutka.
Nyiywakapa nwaka himata hiyrun-koxa hyapawakle himata.
Waneya Tomé tshinkaluru wla tshinru: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, hi wimatlu hanu pyanu hiyáhoni hanhe wumukata himatletlu hatnu hapo?
Waneya Jesus hihitna: — Hitni hatnu hapno, Hitni halikakalutno, Hitni hiwekluno. Yine Hita tshinanu tsonu rumukata hapokanwakletluna Nuru Hoyakalu.
Hita himathexinmaka, Nuru Hoyakalu koxa himathetanu. Hiyáhoni xawaknikananuko himatlu hiyrun-koxa hetatkalu.
Waneya Filipe tshinkaluru wla tshinru: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, hixatshi Puru pekhitanwu waneya hike pnuteko wujhanutka.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Hix-hohne nimwatkayi seyni wanepnawaka hi pimathetawanhe Filipe? Hita netjeru Nuru Hoyakalu koxa reta. Hiyáhoni xawakni haklu tshinanhe wla ptshina, Puru Hoyakalu pekhitanwu?
Hi he palixlu Nuru Hoyakalu hwatshrino hita hiyrun-koxa Nuru Hoyakalu hita hwatshrini wale? Tokantshi nunkaklexyahi hi hita nnurrerni wale nunkakletanru. Seyni Nuru Hoyakalu hita hwatshri, waleni ptowru potuko kochpakatshrini.
Halixanno Nuru Hoyakalu hwatshrino nixyawaka, hiyrunu halixanru Nuru Hoyakalu hita rawa. Ho halixanno kamrurtshikaka nkamhalerutka tshinanu tsonu.
Halikakni, halikakni ntshinhi, Kamrurtshikaka nkamhaleru, hita nalixjeru koxa kamhanru. Xye kamrurtshikaka wale yohnik-hkamhanu klu tshinanu Nuru Hoyakalu nwaka nyiywaka tshinanni.
Hiyáhoni kluneruktako hanjixini hita hiwaka tshinanu, wale nkamhanu halikaka, Nuru Hoyakalu himalwuxiko Whentshi tshinkalurno tshinanu.
Kluneruktako hanjixini hita hiwaka tshinanu, nkamhanru.
Hamoxinipno, ntowuxyahi hkamhanu.
Jesus Hinkakletlu Satu Hapnanuhchinikankaklewatatshri Hyokanaxyawakapa PiranapniJesus pnute hya tshinreta, wla htshina: — Hita hanjitanru Nuru Hoyakalu wale satu hapnanuhchinikankaklewatatshri renejyawakaphi, hix-yehi rawhohnekanaxyawakapa.
— Hi nuknokanhi hi muslahkonephi. Seyni nsatokanu hixa nwaka.
Pchini tsonu yine xye tshijne hajene hi hetanutnakno. Seyni hixa hetanutnakno. Klu tshinanu niwekanutnaka hita hiyáhoni hix-koxa hiwekanu.
Wale hohnepa hixa himathetanru Nuru Hoyakalu hwatshri nixyawaka hita. Himathetanru hixni hita hwatshinhi hiyrun-koxa hita hixa hwatshrino hita.
Ntowuxyahi tokanu himwatshri, wale tokantshi homkahitatshri, walekni nalukjeru. Nalukjeru, hanuruktako yineru, Nuru Hoyakalu koxa halukanru. Hit-koxa halukanru wale hiyrunu wale yehi nuphujexinwa kat-potno hita.
Waneya Judas tshinkaluru, hi Judas Iscariotes tshinkalurni seyni satuko, wla tshinru: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa hanhe pixa hiphujetlexinwa hix-yehi tsonu seyni yine xye tshijne hajene yehi hi puphujexinwa?
Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Yineru hita nuchinikjeru, ntokanu koxa romkahitanu. Hiyrun-koxa Nuru Hoyakalu hamotanru wale. Wale yehi wyanu. Wale yehi wwanutka.
Seyni nmalukjetu hi homkahitlu ntokanu ntowuxyalu. Hjemanru tokantshi ntshinyahi. Wale tokantshi ntshinyahi hi ntokanni wale seyni Nuru Hoyakalu nyokanatjeru tokanni wale.
Xyekaka tokantshi ntshinyahi hix-yehi nwaka pchinika.
Hiyrunu Hapnanuhchinikankaklewatatshri ptowru potuko hasrukanhi. Walekni hepixanhi hichinijyawaklu ptowru potuko nunkaklexyatkahi. Xye Hapnanuhchinikankaklewatatshri, Hoyakalu Hiwejikalurni. Walekni Hoyakalu yokanatanrupa Hita hiwakaya.
— Hapnanuhchinikanrewlu hix-yehi nutakanu nuhlehchinikanyehixikolu nenekanhi. Xye tshijne hapnanuhchinikanre phuta pixkalutu hi nenekanhi. Hiyáhoni hi hkojwakahchinikanutanu. Hi hpikanu nyiniklunpatka.
Hjempiranatatkalu wane ntshinyawakatka mitshi: “Nyanutka seyni nunanutnaka hix-yehi.” Halikaka hitamka halukatka, hpoyikowatanumka klu tshinanu wane ntshina, Hirtshi Hoyakalu nwaka nyanu. Klu tshinanu Nuru Hoyakalu hita yohnika Tsru Hixikatshriwani wale.
Xawakni nunkakatkahi hmapokkanuwa xye, rapojinpatka halixyawakaplu.
Xawakni pnutpatka hi hixo pirana nunkakanhi klu tshinanu xye tshijne towutatshri hinanu. Hike htowutanu hit-yehiya.
Seyni xye nkamha xye tshijne hajene himaxyawakaplu Nuru Hoyakalu nuchinijyawaka pirana hiyrunu xye nkamha htowuxyawakno pixka. — Hajewa hpalnanu, hewi wuchpajinitka.
Uva-tsa Halikakalutu Piranapni— Hitni uva-tsa halikakalutu pixkalutno. Nuru Hoyakalu uva-cha hislahatshrini.
Ptowruka hita hwatshri plukaka masahitu Hoyakalu kastakanru. Hiyrun-koxa ptowru plukaka kasahiru wale hihletlu hsahiwpotuxyawakapa.
Hixni hihletkatka ntokanu nunkajyatkahi tshinanu.
Hita hwanu hiyrunu nwanhi hixa. Klu tshinanu uva plu hi himukata sahiwleta waleko hmixkonu tshinanu tsonu seyni rujhalu hiptshe hyokajikowaka. Waneko pixka hixatshinhi hixa. Klu tshinanu hixa hike himukata kochpakleta hita hma yokakkanuklunu.
— Uva-tsa pixkalutno hita. Hixni hiplu. Hiplu hita hwatshripa hiyrunu hita nimwaleru-plu pixkalutu, hixo sahiplu. Seyni hita mwakatu hikeko hkochpaka.
Katukta hi himwano, hiplu hiknokkaluru pixkalutupni. Riprihanu hiplu hiyáhoni rapatjetka yineya waneya tshitshmero ruknokkana. Hyoxikka hiplu.
Hita himwini hiyrunu ntokanu hixa hitokote hwanu, halukanru kluneruktako hanjixini, wale hyoptotanu.
Nuru Hoyakalu himalwutko hix-potu sahi pixkalutu hsahiwaxini. Wan-hixatshinephi nasruklene.
Nuru Hoyakalu hichinijyawakno pixka waneko pixka nixa hichiniklethi hixa. Hi hasujinri nuchinikle hixa tshinanu.
Ntowuxyahi homkahixini hi nutuk-hichiniklethi. Nuru Hoyakalu tokanu nomkahjexyawaka pixka. Hiyáhoni hi rutuk-hichinikletno.
— Xye pirana nunkakhi, numuwle himwatshine himukatatshinephi, hiyrun-koxa hpoyikowaxyawaka hike mahatatka.
Xyekni ntowuxyahi pirana, hichinikakjexyawaka, hita hichinijyawakhi pixka.
Hikeni xye yohnik-hichiniklewatatshri, satu yineru rimatletanune kachrijru rupniywaka.
Nimatletanunephi, ptowru tokantshi ntowuxyahi homkahixini.
Hi towrertshine ntshinatkahi klu tshinanu towrertshinecha hi himatlu towutatshri, htowutjerna hchinikanu. Seyni nimatletanune ntshinatkahi klu tshinanu ptowru tokantshi Nuru Hoyakalu tshinyano njemleru, nunkakatkahi.
Xyekaka pirana ntowuthi, Hichinikkakanu.
— Xye tshijne hajene hahnanuxiniphi, hichinikanru hit-hapka rahnanutatkana.
Xye tshijne hajeneymalune hixkamka waneyamka hamotko hixa wannanu pixka. Seyni xye tshijne hajeneymalune hma mixyawakanu tshinanni, hiyrunu nurethi xye tshijne hajene hmixyawakanu tshinanu, xye tshijne hajene hahnanuthi.
Hi hamtakanru tokantshi ntshinyatkahi. Xyekni wale: “Towrertshi hi htowutjeru yohnik-himukatatshrini wale”. Hiyáhoni hita hsalexinixka, hix-koxa hsaletanna yine. Hita ntshinyawaka rimrexinna waneya hixa tshinyawaka koxa rimretanna.
Hiyáhoni xyekaka ptowruka hkamhinna hixa, nhiwakaymalunhi tshinanu. Xye hkamhanna klu tshinanu hi rimatluna nyokanatjeru.
Hita nma munkanumka hiyrunu nma miynumatkanumkana yine waneyamka hi hektuwaka kamhatshinetkani. Seyni xawakni hi rawyana rektunna mimathexikowakanu.
Hita nahnanutjeru, Nuru koxa rahka.
Kamrurtshi nkamhaleru satukna yineru mkamhanutu, nma kamhaknumka wanna hetanu, himka hektuwaka kamhatshinetkani. Seyni xawakni retluna nkamrure wanepnawaka rahnanutnona hiyrunu Nuru koxa rahnanutna.
Seyni xye hakanhatka hpoyahokajyawakapa tokantshi yonatkaluru wanna yonre hwatshri, wla tshinatshri: “Rahkanona hike mixkatukno.”
Seyni Hapnanuhchinikankaklewatatshri, Hiwejikaluru halikaka pirana hiphujetatshri, Nuru Hoyakalu yehi hichpajikatshripa, nyokanatanrupa, rapojinipa hixa nwaka, waleko hiphujtatanno.
Hiyrunu hix-koxa hiphujtalewatanu klu tshinanu nehapoklekananuko hitaymalunekananhi.
Jesus Hinkaklexyawaklu Salewaktshi Hinatshripa PiranapniJesus wane pnute wan-tshina: — Xyekaka nunkakhi hma malixyawakanupa.
Hanjihohnewakapjikaka hkochpajikolupa hixa hiyrun-koxa rapokpapkolutanu hiylaxikowaka Hoyakalu halukanru hkamhahoxinwa.
Xyekaka hkamhinhina hixa klu tshinanu hi rimatluna Nuru Hoyakalu, hi hitako rimatna.
Seyni xyekaka nunkakhi, rakanhinipa xyekaka, hixa hichinikanru xyekaka nunkakakanaxyahi. Hiyrunu Jesus wan-tshina: — Seyni mitshikananu xyekaka hi nunkakatkahi klu tshinanu hix-yehi nwawa.
Seyni xawakni nyokanatjeru nwaka nyanu. Seyni hixa hi satukna hepomhano: “Hanhe pyanu?”
Hiyrun-koxa xyekaka nunkajyahi tshinanu, hixa wamonuwhajita tsru potuko.
Seyni halikaka nunkakhi, kihlepotlu nyinripa klu tshinanu nma yaknuklunupa hapnanuhchinikankaklewatatshri hi hapokanu; seyni nyinipa nyokanatanru hix-yehi.
Seyni rapojinipa Hiwejikaluru, wale hichinikkakanna xye tshijne hajene hektuntshi pirana, potukalu pirana hiyrun-koxa hikolukanuwnalu pirana.
Hektuntshi tshinanu hjihyehitkanna klu tshinanu hi ralixnona.
Potukatlewlu pirana tshinanu hjihyehitkona klu tshinanu Nuru Hoyakalu yehi nyanutka. Hi hetanutkano.
Hikolukanuwnalu klu tshinanu xye tshijne yokanatatshri hikolukanuwnatka.
— Waneyno pimri pirankaka nunkajyawakapmakhi seyni hixa hi himukata hakotletlu xawakni.
Seyni runinpatka Hiwejikaluru halikakalutu, waleko kosekanhi ptowru piranako halikaka piranaya. Klu tshinanu hi waleko hihchinikanu runkakletanu seyni runkakletanru ptowruka hjemlerutka, runkakletanru hinatshripa pirana.
Hiwejikaluru halikakalutu hita hpoyahnutanu. Hita hinkakle runkakanhi.
Ptowruka Nuru himwaleru hitanni. Wale tshinanu wane ntshinatkahi, Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru nunkakle psoluka runkakanhi.
— Xekoyakapa hi hetanno seyni hi howukchini hetanutnakno.
Hiyáhoni satkaka wanna hasrukkalune wla htshinkakna: — Klunernihe xye pirana htshinatkawu? “Xekoyakapa hi hetanno seyni hi howukchini hetanutnakno?” Hiyrunu xye, “Nuru Hoyakalu nwaka nyiywaka tshinanni”?
Hiyáhoni wla htshinna: — Hi wimatjemlu klunerukta raluka tshinreta wla htshinini, “Xekoyakapa”.
Halikaka, halikaka ntshinhi. Hixa wamonuwatanu, htshiyahpotutanu seyni pimrine xye tshijne hajene poyikowatanu. Hixa wamonuwatanu seyni hwamonuwle hiprotakanu, himuwlupatkani.
Suxo honra mturu tshino tjemini, tkaheknanuwata klu tshinanu rapokatka topapkolu. Seyni hajeyri tali matuwhenrexinixka, hi tuchinikanretatkalu katshinolukananu tpoyikowata satu mturu xye tshijne tmatkajini tshinanu.
Hiyáhoni xawakni hwamonuwata seyni netanutnakhi hiyrunuko waneya himuwatanu. Hiyrun-koxa himuwle hike yineru himukata kochtsheklexyahi.
— Hinatshri hohnepa hike pirana hijhayehitanutkano. Halikaka, halikaka wla ntshinhi, Kluneruktako hanjixinri Nuru Hoyakalu hita hiwaka tshinanu, renekanhi.
Haté xawakni hike hanjitawano. Hanjirewatanu, hyoptoxyawakaplu himuwle hike mmahaxyawakanupa.
Jesus Tokanu Hinhale— Xyekaka pirana nunkakhi yapkaklu piranayma seyni hinatshripa hohne hi yapkaklu piranayma niynumatanhi. Wale hohnepa Nuru Hoyakalu piran-yehi nekhipotutanhi.
Wale hohne hinatshripa hita nhiwakayma hanjirewatanu. Hiyrunu wane ntshinhi wale hohnepa hi Nuru Hoyakalu nanjitanu hixa tshinanupa.
Klu tshinanu wale, Nuru Hoyakaluko hichinikhi klu tshinanu hixa hichinikno hita hiyrunu klu tshinanu halixno Nuru Hoyakalu yehi hichpajikatshrino.
Nuru Hoyakalu nunya. Xye tshijne hapokatshrino. Waneyapa xye tshijne nuchpajini. Nuru Hoyakalu nwaka nyanu.
Waneya rasruklene wla tshinru: — Xawakni halikaka pekhixnawa puchinikanretler-potuko. Hi yapkaklu tsonu ptshina.
— Ha xawakni wimatyi pixa ptowru potuko himatatshriyi. Hi rujhalu yine hepomhiywakyi. Hiyáhoni walixyi Hoyakalu yokanreryi pixyawaka.
Waneya Jesus hepomhana, wla htshinna: — Halikaklahe halixno xawakni?
Hetanu rapokpapkolutanu, rali hapoklepapkotatka hipalaxyawakapa hixa satkakhi waleko hyawakle yanu, hita hichomtanu. Seyni hi hichotkalurno halikaka klu tshinanu Nuru Hoyakalu hitaymalutni wale.
Xyekaka pirana nunkakatkahi kihle hchinikanurunephi hita tshinanu. Xye tshijne salewnikatshinephi. Seyni kihle hchinikanurunephi klu tshinanu xye tshijne namtakakatka.
Jesus Hanjihohnere PiranapniXyekaka pirana htshinatka Jesus. Tenhohne hyihata waneya wla htshina: — Hoyakalu, Nuru rapokpapkolutatka. Piwhene puphujetanu, ruphujexyawakapyi pix-koxa.
Peneklu towuwlu ptowru yineru htowuxyawaka, hiweklu hike rixiniko mnikawnakatuko renejyawakapna yine ptowruneka penejyatkalu.
Pixa Hoyakalu halikakalutu rimaxyawakapna yine, hike pixka hixatshriyi, hiyrunu Jesus Cristo, pyokanatanru rimaxyawakapna yine, xyekni hiweklu hike rixiniko mnikawnakatupa.
Nuphujetatkayi pixa hewi xye tshijneya. Nnikatatkalu kamrurtshi ptowuxyano nkamhiywakapa.
Hiyáhoni xawakni Nuru Hoyakalu, pix-potuko puphujetanno. Xye tshijne myinuwakkanuklunuwa pixayma nwajekanaxini hoyaknutshi netleru penekanno.
— Nuphujetatkalu pixa phiwaka yine penejyano xye tshijne hajene yehiya. Payinetene penejyano. Hiyrun-koxa pixa ptokanu romkahjetna.
Xawakni rimathetluna ptowruka penejyano, pix-yehi hichpajikatshri rixyawaka.
Klu tshinanu tokantshi punkajyatkano, wanna nunkakatka. Hiyrun-koxa wale tokantshi ralixna. Pix-yehi hichpajikatshrino halikaka rimathetna hiyrun-koxa rimathetnona pixa yokanatanruno nixyawaka.
— Nanjihohneta wanna tshinanu, hi xye tshijne hajene tshinanu nanjihohneta. Seyni nanjihohneyehitna yine penejyano klu tshinanu pixanunni wanna.
Hiyrun-koxa hitanunni, pixanun-koxni wanna. Waneko pixka rixa pixanunni hitanun-koxni wanna. Wanna tshinanu rawa noyaknu.
Pixa nwaka nyanu, hatatjewa hi hewi tshijne nwawa seyni nyi yine hewi tshijne hwawa. Nuru Hoyakalu Potukalu, nyi yine penejyano pihnanutanu pixa hiwaka himukatle tshinanu. Pa hchinikanurune rixyawakapna hixa pixka.
Wannayma nwakanaxini xye tshijneya pixa hiwaka himukatleyma nihnanutatkana. Yine penejyano nihnanutatka hi satukna hamha seyni hamhatshri tsonupni tshitshmero yatshripa tsonu. Wan-rixatka hpoyahokajyawakaplu Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru tshinyawaka.
Hiyáhoni pixa nwaka nyanu. Hiyrun-koxa xyekaka tokantshi xye tshijne hajene nunkakatka, numuwle nenejyana hpoyahokajyawakapa wanna yehi.
Pixa tokanu nunkakatkana seyni xye tshijne hajene hahnanutna klu tshinanu hi xye tshijne hajenetkani, hita xye tshijne hajeru nmixyawakanu pixka.
Hi nanjityi xye tshijne pkochpajyawakapna seyni nanjityi pinoxyawakna kamtshi hma kojwajyawakanupna.
Ppotukatanna halikaka piranayma. Halikakalutni ptokanu.
Pyokanaxyawakno xye tshijne pixka, wanna koxa nyokanata xye tshijne hyiywakna.
Wanna tshinanu pixa nenejnawa. Wanna koxa ptokanu halikakalutu tshinanu pixa renejinwana.
— Hiyrun-koxa hi nyi tshinanu tsonu nanjihohnetanu seyni nanjihohneyehitanna koxa hita halixatshinepa runkakle tshinan-koxna.
Nanjityi pa hchinikanurune rixyawakapna, hixa pixka Nuru Hoyakalu pa hchinikanurunwu pixa hitayma hiyrunu pa hchinikanurunwu hita pixayma. Nanjityi pa hchinikanurune pixkakanna hixayma, xye tshijne hajene halixyawakaplu pyokanatanruno nixyawaka.
Hiyrunu hoyaknutshi penejyano, wale nenekatkana wanna. Pa hchinikanurune rixyawakapna, pa hchinikanurune wixyawaka pixka.
Hita wannayma hiyrunu pixa hitayma hike mmahaxikane rixyawakapna pa hchinikanurune rixyawakapna. Xye tshijne hajene himaxyawakaplu pixa yokanatno hiyrunu rimaxyawakapna puchinikna puchinikjexyawakno pixka.
— Nuru Hoyakalu nanjityi yine penejyano hita nwiywakapa rawyawakapna wanna koxa. Npohirewnale penejyano rexyawakapna. Klu tshinanu xye tshijne hma kamhakonuklunuwa puchinikatkano.
Ha, Nuru Hoyakalu Potukalu, xye tshijne hajene hi himatatkayi. Seyni hita himatatkayi hiyrunu nyi yine himatatkalu pixa yokanatno hita.
Pixa nimatkakatkana wanna hiyrunu pix-pirana nunkakjetawana. Hichiniklewlu puchinijyawakno pso, wannayma rawyawakapa hiyrunu hita wannayma nwiywakapa.
Jesus Getsêmani Tshinikowaka Hyiywaka PiranapniWaneya rali hanjihohnerexinixka, Jesus rasrukleneyma yatka waneya hkoprutluna Cedrom tshinikowaka tskata. Rapokluna oliveira-cha wane sreta hwatshri.
Waneya Judas, Jesus hiphujetatshri, himathetlu oliveira-cha wane hajeru klu tshinanu hixo kata wane rapatjexya Jesus rasrukleneyma.
Hiyáhoni Judas koxa oliveira-cha hya, hkosekamtna soldado-ne hiyrun-koxa satkaka tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hiyrunu fariseu-ne yokanatanune. Ranikluna lamparina, kolhamero koxa hiyrunu hiylalewapkaka.
Ptowruka riknohjerupa rimatahnapuxyawaka tshinanu, Jesus yanwakhapkatna waneya repomhatkana: — Kathe hijha?
Waneya ruhitluna: — Jesus, Nazaré hajeru. Waneya Jesus wla tshinna: — Hitakni. (Wannayma koxlu Judas, Jesus kamnitjeru.)
Waneya Jesus wla tshininiklunu, “hitakni”, ratjini hyoxiritna hnakhamtna.
Hiyáhoni rimepe hepomhaletatnakna: — Kathe hijha? Waneya wanna wla tshina: — Jesus, Nazaré hajeru.
Waneya Jesus hihitna: — Nunkakatkahi hitakni. Hiyáhoni hita hijhini, hetacha yaletanna nyi.
Wane htshina hpoyahokajyawakapa tokantshi htshinyawaka mitshi, wan-tshinatshri: “Yine penejyano hi satukna namtaka.”
Simão Pedro yohlolewapi himwakanata, waneya hkochpaklu hyohlolewapre, hkastakjepitlu tsru sacerdote towrer-jepi. Hkastaklu hpotukle jepi. (Wale towrertshi hiwakni Malco.)
Seyni Jesus wan-tshina hiykoletlu Pedro: — Pihnanutanru hipaji pyochmakanru pyohlolewapre! Pixlahe hi halukno twu copa salewaktshi yehi Nuru henejyano nuryawaka?
Anás Yehi Ranijyawakluna Jesus PiranapniWaneya soldado-ne h-chefe-tnayma hiyrunu judeu-ne tsru hixikatshinwa kachitlu Jesus. Rostutluna.
Mitshikananhapka ranikluna Anás yehi. Caifás tshinkaluru himatjirni Anás. Caifás tsru sacerdote wale hwalapu tshinanu.
Caifás honra wla tshinatkana judeu-ne kihleru satupka jeji hipniywaka yine tshinanu.
Pedro Wan-Tshinyawaka Hi Rimathetlu Jesus PiranapniSimão Pedro hiyrunu satu Jesus hasrukleru homkahitlu Jesus. Tsru sacerdote hetjejreru potuko xye Jesus hasrukleru Jesus-yma jihloklu tsru sacerdote-pji hiputre.
Seyni Pedro hiphapto maleka sreta hitukatka. Waneya Jesus hasrukleru, tsru sacerdote himathetleru, hsatkapa waneya riynumsatlo suxo hiphapto hislahatshro waneya hjihlokaklu Pedro.
Waneya suxo hepomhalu Pedro: — Hi he pixa xye jeji hasrukler-koxyi? Waneya ruhitlo, wla htshina: — Hita hike.
Katshikleru tshinanu towrertshine hiyrunu soldado-ne holkakanata tshitshi hpawlerna yehi. Pedro koxa wannayma yopkaka rolkakanata.
Tsru Hixikatshriwa Sacerdote Hepomhiywaklu Jesus PiranapniWaneya tsru sacerdote hepomhalu Jesus. Repomhalu rasruklene pirana hiyrunu Jesus hasruklewle pirana.
Klu tshinanhe hita pepomha? Pepomhanna njemakanatjene. Wanna halikaka himatlu nunkakjekanaxyana.
Seyni wane htshininixka satu soldado Jesus-stsi hwatshri himpakhojitlu Jesus. Waneya soldado wla tshinru Jesus: — Wanerhe ptshin-hihretlu tsru sacerdote?
Waneya Jesus hihitlu, wla htshinru soldado: — Hektuwaka ntshinini, puphujetanru ntokanu hektutu. Seyni halikaka ntshinini, klu tshinanhe pumpakhojitno?
Waneya Anás yokanatlu Jesus hostutkaluruko tsru sacerdote Caifás tshinkaluru nwaka.
Pedro Hiyrunuko Wan-tshinyawaka Hi Rimathetlu Jesus PiranapniWaneya Pedro holkakanaxiniwa repomhaluna: — Hi he pix-koxa Jesus hasrukleryi?Seyni Pedro weyawata, wla htshinna: — Hi hitni.
Waneya tsru sacerdote towreru Pedro kastakjepitanru mole wla tshinru: — Hi he netyi Jesus-yma oliveira-chaya?
Hiyrunuko hweyawata Pedro waneya waneklukawa potuko hyanumatatka patlapa.
Jesus Pilatos Yehi Hapojyawaka PiranapniWaneya judeu-ne haniklu Jesus. Caifás yehi ruchpajyana phurupji ranikluna. Yetshpotukawa. Judeu-ne hi haluka jihlokletlu phurupji hma pitshoxnawakanupwana Páscoa hohne nikle rumukata niklexyawakapna.
Hiyáhoni Phuru Pilatos hipji hichpajya waneya repomhana: — Klu tshinanhe hjihyehitlu xye jeji?
Waneya ruhitluna, wla htshinruna: — Hektutu hma kamhaknumka, himka pixa wenekanru.
Hiyáhoni Phuru Pilatos wla tshinna: — Haté hisatkapanru. Hjihyehitanru hixanu yonreru pirana tshinyawaka pixka. Waneya judeu-ne wan-tshinru Phuru Pilatos: — Seyni hixa hi rawyawu hinhatshri wuylaxyawaklu satu yineru.
Wan-rixluna Jesus hpoyahokajyawakapa htshinyawaka rixa hipnalexyawakapa salewaktshiyma.
Phuru Pilatos Hepomsaxyawaklu Jesus PiranapniWaneya Phuru Pilatos jihlokapjita, htomhalu Jesus waneya repomhalu, wla htshinru: — Pixlahe judeu-nerune pohiryi?
Waneya Jesus hihitlu: — Pixako pihchinikanrahe ptshina ho pimrine hchinikanra ptshina?
Seyni Phuru Pilatos wla tshinru: — Ha, judeu-nerlahe pkahwakno hita? Pineruneko hiyrunu tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hita hsamyokyina. Kluhe pkamha pixa?
Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Npohirewaxyawaka hi xye tshijne hajerni. Xye tshijne hajeru rixkamka, ntowrerune yahotkakanmaka nma kachixikowakanupa judeu-neya. Npohirewaxyawaka hi hewi hajerni.
Waneya Phuru Pilatos wla tshinru: — Hiyáhoni pixlahe phuryi? Waneya Jesus hihitlu, wla htshina: — Pixako wan-tshina. Halikaka wale tshinanu nmatuta hiyrunu xye tshijne napoka nuphujtaxyawakaplu halikakalutu pirana. Ptowruneka halikakalune yijnakotlu ntokanu.
Waneya Phuru Pilatos hepomhalu: — Ha klunernihe halikakalutu pirana? Wane htshininixka ruchpakatka judeu-nerune nwaka hya. Waneya wla htshinna judeu-nerune: — Hi psojikna hikolukanuwnalu nukchijyalu xye jeji.
Seyni ptowru Páscoa hohne tshinanu nuchojetlu satu preso hajeru. Hi he haluklu nuchoxyawakaplu judeu pohire?
Seyni ptowrunek-yine wla tshin-sapleta: — Hike, hi walepni seyni Barrabás tshinkaluru puchoxinwu! Barrabás tshinkaluru honukla katshowhuru.
Hiyáhoni Pilatos haniklu Jesus waneya hkotshipjejixatkalu.
Waneya soldado-ne kawchiriplu hsaxpatna sahyi hkamhiywakapna waneya Jesus jiwu rutakatkaluna. Waneya mkatshri sama serolu hmakatluna Jesus.
Hiyrunu walestsi rapokjejetna, wla htshina halikletluna: — Hali judeu-ne Tsru Hixikatshriwate! Waneya rumpakhojitluna Jesus.
Hiyrunuko ruchpakatka Pilatos waneya wla htshinatkana judeu-ne: — Hetanu! Jesus nanikanwakathi himaxyawakapa hi psojikna hikolukanuwnalu nukchijyalu xye jeji.
Waneya Jesus himuchpakkatka serolu mkatshri hitakamtatshri hiyrunu kawchiri sahyetamtatshritka, Pilatos wla tshinna: — Xyetkani jeji!
Waneya tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hiyrunu soldado-ne hajeyna retawaluna Jesus, hyinuwaka saplewletna, wla htshinna: — Cruz puylaxinri! Cruz puylaxinri! Seyni Pilatos wan-tshinna: — Hixako hanikanru, Cruz hiylaxinri! Klu tshinanu hitaho hike hikolukanuwnalu nukchijyalu xye jeji.
Waneya judeu-nerune hipokananu wla tshinru: — Hixanu yonreru pirana tshinanu rujha hipnaleta klu tshinanu wale wan-tshina, Hoyakalu potuko hima ruruta.
Waneya xye hjeminixka Pilatos, pnute hpikatka.
Hiyáhoni hjihlokatnaklu hipjiru. Waneya repomhalu Jesus: — Hanhe puchpajya? Seyni Jesus hike tshina.
Seyni Jesus hihitlu, wla htshina: — Hike ptowuta pixa hita tshinanu Hoyakalu menekkanuklunyi. Wale tshinanu hita nsamyokjeru pixa pnute hektuwatatka.
Hiyáhoni waneklukananuko Pilatos haluk-hicholetmaklu Jesus seyni judeu-ne saplewata, wla htshinruna: — Xye jeji puchoxinipa, hi César himatletlerupatkayi klu tshinanu katukta pohirtshi tshinnawa hkamnitlu César.
Wale hjemini Pilatos, maleka raniklu Jesus. Hikolukanuwnayehjexikowaka htuplata “Sotlumta tshinikowaka”, ( waleni “Gabatá” judeu tokanuya).
Hiyáhoni Páscoa hohne halpokotkaluru hohnestsitkani, hanikaj-hohnestsitkani. Waneya Pilatos wan-tshinna judeu-ne: — Haha xyetkani hpohire.
Seyni judeu-ne wan-tshin-sapleta: — Puylatanru, puylatanru. Cruz putakanru. Waneya Pilatos wla tshin-hepomhaletna: — Hpohirrahe cruz nutakanu? Waneya tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne wla tshinru: — César-pkani wpohire.
Hiyáhoni renekatkana Jesus cruz rupniywakpatka.
Cruz Rupniywaka Jesus PiranapniWaneya soldado-ne hanikatkalu Jesus. Waneya cruz rutjitatka Jesus, hyatka, Calvário tshinikowaka, wale tokantshi yokakkaluru, yineru jiwuta pixkalutu yehi, hya.
Wane cruz rutajyaluna hiyrunu hepi yine. Satkaka pa sreta hwa. Jesus hanikaji hwa.
Pilatos yonakjixlu hjihyehixikolu pirana tábua hoho, rutakjixlu cruz-stsipto. Wane htshin-yonhata: “Jesus, Nazaré hajeru, judeu-ne pohire”.
Hiyáhoni hixo judeu-ne het-yonhatlu xye pirana klu tshinanu cruz rutajikowaka Jesus hi howukaylu tsru poktshi. Hiyrun-koxa mapa nru hyonaxika, judeu tokanu, latim tokanu hiyrunu grego tokanu.
Waneya tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne wan-tshinmaklu Pilatos: — Hi wane ptshin-yonhakakanru: “Judeu-ne pohire rixyawaka”, seyni wla ptshina yonretanru waleko htshinyawaka pixka: “Hitni judeu-ne pohirno”.
Seyni Pilatos wla tshina: — Nyonakjixlerutka hyonatkatka.
Soldado-ne Hiknojyawaka Jesus Mkalu Hkayaxyawakna PiranapniWaneya soldado-ne cruz rutakatkaluna Jesus, ranikatkaluna himkalu. Quatro hkaniprexyatkaluna satkaka soldado-ne. Satu himkalu myotsletu hixeta. Teno ruyak-saxpalexika haté tshiji sreta.
Waneya wannakakluko wla tshina: — Hi wsuskakanru seyni hiknokkaluru wuknokanu wimaxyawakapa katu kayatanru Jesus-ni mkalu. Wan-rixa hpoyahokajyawakapa Hoyakalu tokanu mitshikawluru yonatkaluru tshinyawaka, wla tshinatshri: “Nomkalu hkanipretna wannakakluko, hiknoklu rikamhaluna rimaxyawakapna katu kayatanru nomkalu.” Hiyáhoni wan-rixatkana soldado-ne.
Cruz-stsi hyopkakna Jesus hinro, nato htshinrero, Maria, Clopas tshinkaluru hnunro hiyrunu Maria Madalena.
Waneya Jesus hexinro runro hiyrunu rasrukleru ramotleru runrostsi hwakanatatshri, wla htshinro runro: — Suxo, klalutkani pituru.
Wane pnute wla htshinru rasrukleru: — Klalotkani punro. Waneklukawa rasrukleru hanikatkalo waleyma twiywakpatka.
Jesus Hipnale PiranapniWane pnute, rimaxinixka Jesus ptowruka rali kamhalexinixka hiyrun-koxa hpoyahokajyawakapa Hoyakalu tokanu mitshikawluru yonatkaluru, Jesus wla tshina: — Honunnahno.
Wanekananro pa stonha vinagre-ha. Hiyáhoni wanna kamkolu ruhakluna vinagre-ha. Hissopo tshinkalurujestsipto rutakluna waneya Jesus nama rutakluna.
Waneya rurinixkalo vinagre-ha Jesus, wla htshina: — Ralixatka. Waneya hyonohjiwutatka, rupnanatka renek-hiwekletatka.
Hyohlokwansataxikowaka Jesus PiranapniSábado hohnepatkani wale prika. Tsru kahwakpiratkaluru hohnepatkani. Judeu-ne hi halukatkalu hipnatshinni mane cruz rutujyawakatka haté sábado hohne. Hiyáhoni judeu-ne hanjitlu Pilatos hitpali hapu ruknahjixyawakapa. Waneya hiknahatpalitkalunni mane hanikjixkatka.
Hiyáhoni runna soldado-ne. Mitshikananu cruz hwatshri Jesus hinaple hwakanatatshri hitpali hapukaka ruknahna. Waneya Jesus pastate hwakanatatshrini koxa ruknajrotpalitna.
Seyni Jesus nwaka rapojinixkana soldado-ne retluna rali hipnaletatka Jesus-ni. Hiyáhoni hi ruknahatpalitluna Jesus.
Seyni satu soldado wane hwakanatatshri yohlokwansatatlu Jesus harpão-ya. Chinpotukawa hrahtshi hichpaka honhayma.
(Xye hetatshri hinkaklewata. Halikaka htshina. Rimata halikakni htshinyawaka. Runkakletlu hix-koxa himukata halixlexyawakaplu tshinanu.)
Xyekaka wan-hixatka Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru tshinyawaka himukata poyahokaklexyawakapa. Wane htshina: “Hi satukna hihapu hiknahko.”
Hiyrunuko wane htshinatnaka Hoyakalu tokanu mitshikawluru yonatkaluru: “Hyopukhatanruna hyohlolerna.”
Jesus Kapnaxikolu PiranapniWane pnute José tshinkaluru, Arimateia hajeru, hanjitlu Pilatos Jesus-ni mane renejikowakapa. José Jesus hasrukler-koxni seyni yohimaxikatshriwani judeu-ne hamlenu tshinanu. Waneya Pilatos hitshitlu hiyáhoni runa ranijyawakaplu Jesus-ni mane.
Waleymalu Nicodemos tshinkaluru, mitshikawa Jesus yehi hapkapyetshnotatshri. Nicodemos haniklu phamlu pahiru mirra tshinkaluru hiyrunu aloés tshinkaluru yapjetkaluro, quarenta e cinco kilos hetkolu.
Cruz rutajikowakastsi rawa satu hitaklucha. Wane hitaklucha rawa satu jitopnatkaluru herotu hike mutajikowakanuwa.
Judeu-ne halpokohnaputanru hohnestsi potuko rixyawaka tshinanutka hiyrun-koxa hejitotkolu wanestsiko hwatka, wan-rutakmanetanatkaluna Jesus-ni.
Jesus Hiwejyawakatnaka PiranapniWaneya hyinuwakle seman-hohne, mapchahakowalu, Maria Madalena yanwakatlu yomletshi. Tetlu rerutkatka sotlu yomletshi hichyale.
Hiyáhoni tasukamta Simão Pedro hiyrunu satu rasrukleru Jesus hamotleru yehi tya. Waneya wla ttshinna: — Yomletshikta hkochpajyanatkaluna Tsru Hixikatshriwani. Hi wimata hanukta rutakanatkaluna.
Hiyáhoni Pedro hiyrunu satu rasrukleru yomletshi nwaka hyana.
Wanna hepi hasukamta seyni satu kapnuhamtlu Pedro. Wale hapka hapoklu yomletshi.
Waneya ripyoka, retlu mkatshri sama seyni hi hjihloklu yomletshi.
Waneya Simão Pedro hapkatamtatshri hapoka. Hjihloklu kapna. Retlu mkatshri sama wane hwakanatatshri.
Ret-koxlu kasamalu Jesus-ni jiwu hiwtokakanatatshri. Hi pimri sama yehi rawakanata seyni pa sreta rawakanata rixannu hiwtokleko.
Wane pnute satu rasrukleru hapokhapkatatshri jihlok-koxlu kapna. Retlu waneya ralixatka.
(Seyni wanepnawaka hi rimatjemawaluna Hoyakalu tokanu Jesus hiwejinritnaka tshinanu hipnatshine tskalaya.)
Waneya rasruklene hipjina hyatkana.
Jesus Hakanhayehixyawaklo Maria Madalena PiranapniSeyni Maria yomletshistsi tyopkakakanata, ttshiyahakanata. Ttshiyahakanaxiniwa, tipyoka texyawakaplu kapna.
Waneya tetlu hepi hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrene tenhohne hajene klatpowalune tuplakanatatshine Jesus-ni mane hwakanaxyawaka. Satu hijiwu hwakanaxyawaka sreta hwa, satu hijixi hwakanaxyawaka sreta hwa.
Waneya repomhalona: — Suxo, kluhe pitshiyahjeta? Waneya tuhita, wla ttshinna: — Klu tshinanu hanukta ranikanruna Nutsrukatni, hi nimata hanukta rutakanatkaluna.
Wane ttshininixka, tuprotaka. Tetlu Jesus, hyopkakakanata seyni hi timathetlu Jesus rixyawaka.
Waneya Jesus hepomhalo, wla htshinro: — Suxo, klu tshinanrahe ptshiyahata? Kathe pujha? Seyni wala hitaklucha hislahatshri tikahwaklu hiyáhoni wla ttshinru: — Hitsrukatshi, pixa hanijiniplu, punkakanno putajyawaklu waneya nwapanru.
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinro: — Maria. Waneya tuprotaka, hipokananu wla ttshinru judeu-ne tokanuya: — Rabôni! (wale haluka tshinreta kasruklewakleru.)
Waneya Jesus wan-tshinro: — Hi pkachitanno klu tshinanu Nuru yehi hi nyawa. Seyni nomolene yehi pyanu, punkakanna: “Teno nyanu Nuru yehi hiyrunu hixa Hiru yehi, Noyakalute yehi hiyrunu hixa Hoyakalute yehi nyanu.”
Waneya Maria Madalena yanwakatna rasruklene tunkajyawakapna Tsru Hixikatshriwa texyawakatka. Hiyrunu tunkakatkana ptowru pirana runkajyatkalo.
Jesus Rasruklene Hakanhayehixyawaka PiranapniWaneya hyinuwakle seman-hohne kayno, Jesus hasruklene hapatjetatka ruchyatka hiphaptokaka judeu-ne hamlenu tshinanu. Waneya Jesus hapokatka wanna hanikajite hyopkakatka. Waneya wane htshinna: — Kihle hchinikanuphi.
Rali wan-tshinretatka, rekhitna himyo, hikwansat-koxa. Waneya hpoyikowpotutna rasruklene Tsru Hixikatshriwa rexyawakna.
Waneya Jesus rimepe wan-tshinretna: — Kihle hchinikanuphi. Nuru xye tshijne yokanaxyawakno pixka nixa yokanrethi hixa.
Waneya wane htshininixka, rajpokanwakatna waneya wla htshinna: — Hyoptotanru Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru.
Hixa hamtakahchinikanyehixinri pimrine hektunu waneya Hoyakalu koxa hamtakahchinikanyehitanru wanna hektunu. Seyni hixa hma mamtakahchinikanyehixiniklunru pimrine hektunu, wanna hektunu hi ramtakahchinikanyehitka rektunna.
Jesus Tomé Hakanhayehixyawaka PiranapniTomé, walekatkani Dídimo tshinkaluru, satu Doze Jesus hasrukleru, hi wannayma rawakanata, Jesus hakanhayehixiniklunna rasruklene.
Hiyáhoni pimrine hasruklene wla tshinru: — Wetatkalu Tsru Hixikatshriwa. Seyni Tomé wan-tshinna: — Nma metkanuklunuplu prego yohloxyawaka marca-te himyo hiyrunu nomyoji nma yochmakkanuklunuplu prego yohloxyawaka hiyrun-koxa nomyo nma yochmakkanuklunuplu hikwansata yohloxikolu, hi nalixanru.
Jesus Hiyrunuko Hakanhayehixyawakna Rasruklene PiranapniWaneya pa semana hiknohinixka, wanepjitnakna Jesus hasruklene Tomé-yma. Waneya yáholu hiphaptokaka hichyaluru potuko, Jesus jihlokatka wanna hanikajite hyopkakatka, waneya wla htshinna: — Kihle hchinikanuphi.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinru Tomé: — Pimyoji nomyo putakanu, petamyotanno. Pomyokanu, nokwansata pyochmakanru. Hi malixakletupyi seyni halixatshripyi.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Pexyawakno tshinanu palixatka seyni himuwatatshinepni yine yáholu himka retannona seyni ralixannona.
Klu Riyonatka Xye PiranaHixo pimri hetkalurkaka hkamha Jesus rasruklene hetanuya, twu papel-mta mutak-yonhatkotu.
Seyni xyekaka yonatka hixa halixyawakaplu Jesus, Hoyakalu Whene Cristo (Messias) rixyawaka hiyrun-koxa halixinri waneyaphi hiwejinri wale hiwaka tshinanu.
Jesus Sete Rasruklene Hakanhayehixyawaka PiranapniWane pnute Jesus hakanhayehitatnakna rasruklene Tiberíades powha tshinikowakaya. Wan-rixa hakanhaleta:
Rapatjekanatna Simão Pedro; Tomé, walekatkani Dídimo tshinkaluru; Natanael, Caná poktshi Galileia tshijne hajeru; Zebedeu whenene; hiyrunu pimrine hepi hasruklune.
Waneya Simão Pedro wla tshinna: — Hita mariskatapanu. Waneya wanna wla tshinru: — Pixaymapwu. Waneya hyatkana. Kanawa hpokownatkana seyni wale yetshno, hi satukna hkachitna.
Waneya yetshpotukawa rixinixka, Jesus hipowha wnaha hyopkaka seyni rasruklene hi himathetlu Jesus rixyawaka.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinna: — Maklujine, hi he chima hkachita? Ruhitluna Jesus, wla htshinruna: — Hike, hi satukna.
Hiyáhoni wla htshinna: — H-tarrafa-te kanawa potukle sreta hiknokanu waneya hikchikanro. Hiyáhoni ruknokatkaluna h-tarrafa-tna. Waneya hixo chima rixyawaka tshinanu, hi rumukata kosretluna h-tarrafa-tna.
Waneya hasrukluru, Jesus hamotleru, wla htshinru Pedro tshinkaluru: — Tsru Hixikatshriwatkani tujra! Waneya Simão Pedro jeminixkalu Tsru Hixikatshriwa hapojyawaka hmakawatatka klu tshinanu mamkatukananni hmariskaxyawaka tshinanu. Waneya ruptekhamtlu hipowha.
Pimrine hasrukkalune kanawa runyana hwanha nwaka. Hi howuk-potutkalu hwanha. Cem metros pchini hetko hya kosretluna tarrafa hixo chima yehi.
Waneya hiwnaha rapojinixkana, wane rexyaluna tshitshipawa wane twatka chima jimluro hiyrunu pão koxa.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinna: — Pimro chima hkachrero hanikanu wkata.
Waneya Simão Pedro pokownatka. Waneya tarrafa hixo chima tsrokakalo hwaleru hkoseta hiwnaha. Chimane cento e cinquenta e três pejnu. Katseplu chima wanepnawaka hi ruskata tarrafa.
Waneya Jesus wla tshinna: — Hinanu, hnikanu. Hiyrunu hi satukna hasrukaluru haluk-hepomhaletlu Jesus, katni wale. Klu tshinanu rimathetluna Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus rixyawaka.
Waneya Jesus pão hkochtsheka waneya wanna rapiklu. Waneko pixka rixlo chim-koxa.
Jesus hipuktshi riwejinritka wkatanu, map-kata rasruklene yehi ruphujewniyatka xawakniymakananuko.
Jesus Hepomhiywaklu Pedro PiranapniWaneya rali niklexinixkana, Jesus wla tshinru Simão Pedro: — Simão, Jonas whene, puchinikanretnohe hita nyi pimrine pnute? Waneya Pedro wla tshinru: — Hehe Tsru Hixikatshriwa, pimatlu nuchinijyawakyi. Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Pohlutanna noprane carneiro whenene pixkalune.
Waneya rimepe wane tshinretatnaka: — Simão, Jonas whene, puchiniknohe hita? Waneya Pedro wla tshinru: — Hehe Tsru Hixikatshriwa, pimatlu nuchinijyawakyi. Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Puslahanna noprane carneiro-ne pixkalune.
Waneya map-kata rixinri wla htshinru: — Simão, Jonas whene, puchiniknohe hita? Seyni Pedro wamonuwata klu tshinanu map-kata wla htshinru: “Puchiniknohe?” Hiyáhoni wla htshinru: — Nutsrukate ptowru potuko pimata, pimatlu nuchinikyi. Waneya Jesus wla tshinru: — Pohlutanna noprane carneiro-ne pixkalune.
Halikaka, halikaka wla ntshinyi: — Makluji pixakanaxini palpokoxnawa, hanuktako paluka yaletatka wane pyatka. Seyni tsrutsoleji pixinpatka pkanrakanu. Satu tsatanyi, pmaluka yalexyawakanu ranikanyi.
Wane htshina, rimaxyawakaplu han-hixatshri hipuktshi retanu Pedro hiyrunu Hoyakalu ruphujexyawakapa. Waneya rali wan-tshinretatka Jesus, wla htshinru: — Pomkahitanno hita.
Waneya Pedro hiprotakatka, retlu Jesus hasrukleru ramotleru potuko hapakamnu. Xyekni Jesus sta hinaple hikoluhakaynokanatatshri hnikakanaxinna mitshi wla tshinakanatatshri mitshi: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus kathe hekhitanyi?
Waneya Pedro rexiniklunru wla htshinru Jesus: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus, ha xye jeji, hanu hixatshripnihe?
Seyni Jesus wla tshinru: — Pomkahichatanno pixa. Seyni nalujiniplu riwejyawaka xye haté nsatojinipa kluhe rixyi?
Wale tshinanu xye pirana hipalatatka Jesus halixatshine yehiya, xye Jesus hasrukleru hima hi hipnanu. Seyni Jesus-mka hi wan-tshinru hma mupniywakanupa seyni wla htshinru: Nalujiniplu riwejyawaka haté nsatojinipa, kluhe rixyi?
João Hiphujexyawaklu PiranapniXye honukla hasrukaluru xyekaka pirana hiphujetatshrini hiyrunu xyekaka pirana yonatatshri. Wimatlu halikakni ruphujtaleru pirana.
Hiyrun-koxa hi heppiklu pimri Jesus kamhaleru. Seyni ptowru piranako yonatkomka hitaho hi hetkomka xye tshijneko poyahotanro papel steno ptowruka Jesus kamhaleru pirana yonatkomka.
<font color=teal>Atos</font>Jesus Nurrene Kamrure PiranapniTeófilo tshinanupni twu yonawahlo, yonawahlo mitshikananu nyonreru, nyonatlu Jesus pirana, ptowruka Jesus kamhanru pirana hiyrunu runkakle pirana psoluka, Jesus hasruklewle yinuwaklekananuko;
Rali hipnalexinixka Jesus, riwekatnaka waneya quarenta hohne pejnu tsonu ruphujewnayehjekanatatkana hnurrene hiwekatshriko rixyawakatka, hiyrunu rekhipotutna hiwekatshri rixyawakatka. Wane pchinika Jesus hiynumsatna hnurrene Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka pirana.
Jesus wannayma rapatjekanaxini ruykotna hnurrene Jerusalém poktshi hma muchpajyawakanupna seyni hkahwakanruna haté Hirtshi henejyana wale runkaklexyatkana. Wane htshinatkana Jesus: — Hita hinkajyatkahi.
Klu tshinanu halikaka João batiza-thi honhaya, seyni hi hix-hohnepnitshi hixa batiza-tko Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluruya.
Jesus Tenhohne Hanijikowaka PiranapniWaneya hapatjekanatatshine hepomhalu Jesus. Wane htshinruna: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, xawakniktshikla puhletanru Israel mitshikananu pixka rixyawakapa psol-tshijneko htowuxyawakatnaka?
Seyni Jesus hihitna: — Hixa hi hijhalu himaxyawaklu wale hohnekaka, hi hipapkoluko. Hirtshi nuretanru waleko hihchinikanuya.
Seyni Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hix-hoho rapojinipa hyoptotanru pixkontshi hiyáhoni nuphujtatjenephi Jerusalém poktshiya hiyrunu Judeia tshijne psoluka, Samaria tshijneya, haté hmahaxyawaka tshiji nuphujtatjeneyaphi.
Waneya wane rali tshinrexinixka, Jesus teno ranikkatka wanna hetanuya. Waneya satu hohimkohi katshpoklu Jesus haté hi rumukata hetletatkaluna.
Seyni wanna teno hyihakananumtawana Jesus hatskotka pchinika. Waneya chinpotukawa hepi jejine klatalu mkatshri hitakatshine wannastsi potuko hakanhiyatka.
Waneya wane htshinna: — Jejine Galileia hajene, klu tshinanhe wane hwa hixa teno hyihjeta? Xyekni Jesus hixayma hwakanatatshri, tenhohne yatshritka waleko satkapanu hanukta rixa hatskoletatka hixa hetanuya wane potuko rixa hapokletanutnaka.
Jerusalém Poktshi Rawyawakna Jesus Nurrene PiranapniWaneya nuretkalune satokanwakatlu Jerusalém poktshi. Oliveiras mriji runyatkana satu quilômetro pchini.
Waneya Jerusalém poktshi rapojinixkana, hihruko nwaka hyamtna, pantshi teno hwahrukotatshri. Wane rawjexyawakna Pedro, João, Tiago, André, Filipe, Tomé, Bartolomeu, Mateus, Tiago, Alfeu whene, Simão honra Israel tshijne tshinanu mixkowatatshrini, hiyrun-koxa Judas, Tiago whene.
Nyi yine ptowruneka pa hchinikanurune hi rucho hanjihohneretna, wannaymalune Jesus molene jejine, Jesus hinro, hiyrun-koxa pimrone suxone.
Matias Nurexikowaka PiranapniWaneklu papko Pedro yopkaka Jesus hasruklene hanikajite (cento e vinte yine hapatjetatka) waneya wane htshina:
— Jejine, nomolene hpoyahokakatkalu Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru Davi-ni nama hinkakletakanatatkalu Judas tshinkaluru.
Waleni wepir-potuko. Wale hepixjekanatwu wkamrure tshinanu seyni walekni hanikna Jesus kachitjenepa.
Waneya htiyirote tshiji ranjixya hkamrure himtuknu tshinanu. Seyni waneko hyawniyanatka, himane rupchejyanatka, rixkapi hichpajyanatkalu.
Jerusalém hajene ptowruneka jempiranyehitlu, wale tshinanu wale tshijne rutakhiwakatluna “Aceldama” tshinikowaka, wannanruya wla htshina “Jratshijneru”.
Waneya pnute hya hinkakletna Pedro: — Hoyakalu pirana yonatkaluru Salmos steno rawa: “Malepjiplu, hike wane hwanu.” — Hiyrunu wane koxa htshina yonretka: “Satuko jeji wale kachrijru jihlokanu nuretkaluru rixyawakpatka.”
— Wale tshinanu xawakni wnuretanru satu jeji hixa wepire rixyawakapa, Jesus Cristo hiwejinritnaka pirana wumuphujtatjeru rixyawakapa. Rujhalu wiyanjereru rixyawaka Jesus hix-yehi rawakanaxini,
João batiza-xinri Jesus hohnekananuko haté tenhohne ranikkoklunutka papko.
Hiyáhoni hepi jejine htomhana. Satu jeji hepi hiwaklu José Barsabás. Satu hhiwakni Justo. Satu jeji Matias tshinkaluru.
Waneya wanna ptowruneka hanjihohnetatka wane htshinna: — Hoyakalu, pixa tsonu himathethajitna yine. Pekhitanwu hanuru nyi hepi pnuretatka
xye kamrurtshi hkamhiywakapa. Judas tshinkaluru hichotlu kamrurtshi hiyáhoni hyatka rawyawakpatka. Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu, pekhitanwu katukta jihlokanru wale kachrijrupatka.
Waneya satu hiknoklu hkamhana hnurexyawakapluna hiyáhoni hiknoklu hekhitlu Matias-patkani. Waneya repiretna onze Jesus nurrene.
Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru Hapojinri PiranapniRapojinixka Pentecostes hohne, wanna ptowruneka pa hruko rapatjekanaxyatkana.
Waneya waneklukawa potuko, hjemluna sejirtshi tenhohne hichpajikatshri, tsru kanniphalu pixka rixa hajpoleta htsepotlu htuplakanaxyawaknapji psoluka.
Waneya satkaka ruphujewnayehita tshitshmero katmerolkaka pixkalutu. Satkaka wanna tseptahi rapokmerotatka.
Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru Yanumkakatkana Jesus Nuretanune Pa Nerunru Pejnu Hyanumaxyawakatkana PiranapniWaneya wanna ptowruneka, katsepoyatka Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru. Waneya hyinuwaka yanumlexyaluna pa nru pejnu, hyanumanruxinine nru pejnu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru yanumkakatkana wannanruya.
Jerusalém poktshi rawakanatna judeu-ne Hoyakalu hamotatshine ptowru tshijnekaka hichpajikatshine.
Waneya hapatjemtatshine himyeka, hpikna. Waneya wane htshinna: — Hetanu! Nyi jejine yanumatatshine ptowruneka Galileia hajene.
Hanhe xawaka wixa yijnako yanumletna hixa satkakwu wunru potuko?
Hixa Pártia tshijne hajenwu, Média tshijne hajenwu, Elão tshijne hajenwu, Mesopotâmia tshijne hajenwu, Judeia tshijne hajenwu, Capadócia tshijne hajenwu, Ponto tshijne hajenwu, Ásia tshijne hajenwu,
Frígia tshijne hajenwu, Panfília tshijne hajenwu, Egito tshijne hajenwu, Líbia tshijne psojite Cirene poktshistsi hwatshri hajenwu. Satkakwu Roma poktshi hichpajikatshinwu.
Satkakwu judeu-nerunwu, satkakwu hiprotaka judeu rixnatkawa. Satkaka Creta tshijne hichpajikatshine pimrine Arábia tshijne hichpajikatshine. Hanhe xawaka wixa himatjemletna nyi yine hixa satkakwu wunru potuko, Hoyakalu kamrure kihler-potuko pirana runkaklexyawakna?
Hiyáhoni rimyekna wanna ptowruneka. Hi rimata klu ruchinikanretna hiyáhoni repomsakakna wannakakluko: — Klunernihe xawaka xye ptowruka?
Seyni pimrine hitsolhitatna, wane htshinna: — Nyi jejine himetatshine, vinho-ha rurna.
Pedro Hinkakle PiranapniSeyni Pedro yopkaka pimrine onze Jesus nurreneyma waneya hyanumata hipokananu, hixolune yine jemanu: — Nimatletanune judeu-ne hiyrun-koxa hixa ptowruneka Jerusalém hwatshin-koxa hislahtokanutanno:
Hixa kahwakna nyi jejine himetatshine rixyawakna seyni hi koxa rimetna klu tshinanu tumakananustsikowani.
Seyni Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshrini Joel tshinkalurni yonahnaputlu xye hohne wet-hiknohlexyawaklu. Joel-ni wan-hixa yonreta:
“Hoyakalu wan-tshina: Hmahaxinri hohne Hita henekanna hitanuko Hiwejikaluru ptowru neruka. Hixa whenene jejine suxon-koxa hinkakletanru hinamtatshriwa. Tsrutsolejine hipnawatanu. Maklujine hetanru hetkalurkaka.
Waneklu papko nenekanna ntowrene jejine, suxon-koxa Hiwejikaluru Hitanu. Hiyáhoni wanna hinkakletanru hinamtatshriwa.
Nekhitanru himyekaklewatatshrikaka tenhohneya tshijiya; hrahtshipni, tshitshmeropni hiyrunu tshitshiphapni hixko sajnuru.
Rutshpokanu tkatshi. Jraplu ksuru, hma mapokkanuko pchini Hoyakalu Tsru Hixikatshriwa hohneru hijhakaluru hiyrunu hoyaknutshi.
Waneya katukta hanjitanru Tsru Hixikatshriwa hepixyawaklu riwekkakko.”
Waneya Pedro pnute hinkakna: — Jejine, israel-nerune, hyijnakotanru xako xye tokantshi: Hixa himatlu xye jeji Jesus Nazaré hajeru, Hoyakalu nurreru rixyawaka. Xye rekhitatkahi Hoyakalu ruyakolekakayma, tsrukaka himyekaklewatatshriyma, Jesus kamhaleru hixa tskalaya.
Seyni Hoyakalu waleko ralujyawaka tshinanu Jesus renekhi hixa myoya. Waneya hixako hiylatlu. Jejine hektune cruz hiylaxyalu Jesus hixako tshinanu.
Seyni Hoyakalu hiwekkakatnaklu Jesus, hipuktshi mixkonu hkochpajyalu Hoyakalu klu tshinanu hipuktshi hi himukata kachretlu Jesus.
Klu tshinanu Davi-ni wan-tshinyehitatkalu: “Netlu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu nohoji hinaple rawhohnekanaxyawaka klu tshinanu npotukle sretako rawhonuka wale tshinanu hike npikanu.
Hiyáhoni naji himuwata, nonru poyikowata haté noman-koxa hapnanuhchinikanutatka;
Klu tshinanu hi puknokachamtanno hipuktshi yehiya. Hi koxa puchochatanru palukleru potukalu rujpahachaxyawakapa.
Pasrukatkano hanu nixa hiwekletanu Hoyakalu halujyawaka tshinanuya. Pixayma nwiniklunu pixa tsepoxinno poyikowlu.”
Waneya Pedro wan-tshinna: — Nonerune! Hitshitanno nunkajyawakaphi phujetanuru wutsrukatni Davi-ni pirana. Rupnanatka waneya hkapnatka haté xawakni wimwalu hewi hkapnaxikowakana.
Davi-ni Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshrinixkani hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu hinkaklexyalu pirana himatatshrini. Hoyakalu hinkaklexyatkalu Davi-ni, satu waleko hiklopichane phuru hixyawakapa waleni pixka.
Hma mapokkanuklunuwa wale seyni Davi-ni himatakanatatka. Wale tshinanu wane htshina: “Hi ruknokachamtkotka yomletshiya, wale mane hi hijpahanu.” Davi-ni hinkakletlu Cristo hiwejyawakatnaka pirana.
Hoyakalu hiwekkakatnaklu xye Jesus hiyrunu hixa ptowrunekwu wale pirana hiphujetatshinwu.
Hiyáhoni Jesus hanikkatka, Hoyakalu potukle sreta rawyawakpatka hiyáhoni hyoptotlu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru htshina hinkaklexyawakpotuklu Jesus. Hiyáhoni xye hixa hetanru hiyrunu hjemanru waleni Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hiyoklerni.
Davi-ni hi hanikkatka tenhohne seyni wane htshina: “Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu wan-tshinru Nutsrukate — ‘Hitastsi ptuplatanu npotukle sreta
haté nenekanyi pkamnitjene ptowuxyawakapa.’ ”
Waneya xye pirana hjeminna yine, ptowruneka kojwakahchinikanutatka. Hiyáhoni repomhana Pedro hiyrun-koxa pimrine nuretkalune: — Wimolene, kluneruktshika wkamhanutka xawakni?
Waneya Pedro wan-tshinna: — Hehchinikanutanu hixa satkakhi Jesus Cristo hiwakaya h-batiza-xikowakapa hixa himtukjetatshrikaka hiknojikowakapa; wan-hixatshripa Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hyoptotanu Hoyakalu henekanhi.
Klu tshinanu xye pirana Hoyakalu hinkaklexyatkahi hixa, hixa whenen-koxa runkaklexyalu hiyrun-koxa wanna ptowruneka hi hixastsi hwatshine tsonu runkaklexya. Tsru Hixikatshriwa Woyakalute tomhanune pejnu runkaklexyalu.
Waneya Pedro hihle hinkakletna yine. Ruykotna, wane htshinna: — Hiwekkajikolupa hixa xye papko hiwekatshinetka hektutu kamhatshine tskalaya.
Hiyáhoni Pedro hinkakle halixatshine pejnu batiza-tkatka. Waneklu hohneni mapa mil yohnikna Jesus halixatshine.
Hehchinikanutatshine Hiwekle PiranapniHiyrun-koxa nuretkalune hasruklewle romkahitna. Hapatjeru romkahitna hiyrunu rapatjetna hnijyawakna hiyrun-koxa hanjihohneru hi ruchotna.
Wanna ptowruneka kahwakpiratatkalu Hoyakalu. Hiyrun-koxa nuretkalune kamhalu hixo hiyakolukaka hiyrun-koxa hetkalurkaka.
Cristo halixatshine ptowruneka himwakaka. Ptowruko rejnunkatna ptowruneko himwalu.
Ruchankaluna rejnunkatna rimwalerna. Hkotspalkajyana ptowruneka satkaka hmahaxinrina.
Ptowru hohneruka Hoyakalupji rapatjexyana pa hchinikanurunni. Pimrinkaka papji pejnu nijya. Pa nikkalunni himuwatatshinni pixkakaklune hkahwajnawana.
Rimalwutluna Hoyakalu. Rumutkana ptowru neruneka. Wane pchinika Hoyakalu hixoletna pa hohnekaka wanna Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine pimrineyma hiwekkakkalunepa.
Myankatu Hitskalajikolu PiranapniPa hohne kayi nwaka três hora hanjihohneru papko, Pedro, João Hoyakalupji nwaka hyana.
Ptowru hohneruka satu jeji hmatureyakawa myankatu Hoyakalupji hiphaptote kihlewaka tshinkalurustsi rutakjetka. Wan-rutakluna myankatu tiyiro ranjixyawakapna hiphapto jihlokatshinepa.
Waneya myankatu hetna Pedro, João Hoyakalupji hjihlokamxyawakna. Tiyiro ranjita renejikowakapa.
Waneya Pedro, João-yma yopukhatlu waneya Pedro wan-tshinru: — Petanwu!
Waneya myankatu hetpotutna. Hkahwakakanatlu pa hixanu hkayaxyawaka.
Waneya Pedro wan-tshinru: — Tiyiro hi nwiya seyni pa hixanu nimwa. Wale nimwaleru nenekanyi. Xawakni Jesus Cristo Nazaré hajeru hiwakaya tshinanu ppalnanu! Pyanu!
Waneya Pedro myankatu myo hpotukle hkachita. Hpalnakaklu. Waneklukawa hixkojixitkalu hiyrun-koxa hihpeji hixkoyatkalu.
Waneya ruptemta, hyotunota waneya hyinuwaka yanretatka. Waneya Hoyakalupji hjihlokatka wannayma. Hyanamtatka, ruptemtatka. Rimalwumtlu Hoyakalu.
Ptowru yineru het-yanretlu, rimalwumtlu Hoyakalu.
Waneya rimathexinixkaluna, Hoyakalupji Hiphaptote Kihlewaka tshinkalurustsi tuplajekanatatshri rixyawaka, tiyiro hanjijekanatatshri rixyawaka rimyekna. Rimyekpotutna wan-rixinixka.
Pedro Hoyakalupji Hinkaklewaxyawaka PiranapniWaneya myankatukananu hihlexikolutka himotsatna Pedro, João. Ptowrunek-yine himyeka. Hixolune hasukamta wanna nwaka Hoyakalupji psojite Salomão tshinikowaka nwaka hya hasuklexkehimtna.
Waneya rexinna Pedro wan-rixyawakna yine, wane htshinna yine: — Jejine israel-nerune, haklu tshinanhe himyeka? Haklu tshinanu hixa yopukhatwu hatatjewa hixako wpixkonu tshinanu ho wuhlenu tshinanu wyankakatkalu xye jeji?
Wutsrukatenni Hoyakalute, Abraão-ni, Isaque-ni, Jacó-ni Hoyakalute, walekni tsru hitakkaluru reneklu htowreru Jesus. Seyni hixa nomolenhi hkamnitlu Jesus hiyrunu Jesus Pilatos tshinkaluru hoji sreta rawakanaxini, Pilatos kaspukpiratmaklu Jesus seyni hixa nomolenhi hi hinanchitlu.
Hiyáhoni hixa nomolenhi hi halixlu Potukalu Poyahokakatshri, seyni hixa Pilatos hanjita jiylalewakleru ruchoxyawakapa.
Hixa nomolenhi hiylatatkalu hiweklu heneklewatatshri seyni Hoyakalu hiwekkakatnaklu hiyrunu hixa hetpotutlu xye ptowruka.
Jesus hiwaka ralixyawaka tshinanu rutskalakkatka xye jeji hiyrun-koxa xye hiwaka pixkonu tshinanuko renek-mixkonutlu xye jeji myankatukananu hixa hetamtanru, himatanru hyanyawaka. Hehe, Jesus ralixyawaka tshinanu renekkatka pomtalu rixyawakpatka hixa hetanuya.
Seyni xawakni, nomolene, nimatlu hixa hiyrunu hixa tsrukakalutene wan-hixlu Jesus hma mimatkan-tshinanna.
Seyni Hoyakalu kamhalu wale runkaklewjixanru ptowruneka Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine namaya, Messias hijhalu hsalewniywaka.
Hiyrun-koxa rapojinipa pixkontshi papko Hoyakalu yokanre, Jesus yokanatko, mitshikananu hixa tshinanu rutakka Messias rixyawaka.
Jesus hijhalu tenhohne rutujyawaka haté rapokpapkoluxini ptowruka herotetko wane htshina hinkakleta Hoyakalu mitshikawako nuretkalune Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine namaya.
Klu tshinanu Moisés-ni wan-tshinatka: “Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu yokanatanru hixa tshinanu satu Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri, hita pixka rixanu pimolene ruchpajini. Hyijnakotanru xako wale ptowruko runkajyahi.
Katukta hi yijnakotanru wale, Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri, hkotspalatko yine tskalaya hiyrunu hnikatko.”
Ptowruneka Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine Samuel-ni klukananuko haté hapkatatatshine ptowruneka hinkakletpiranatlu wale pirana, hinkaklewatatshine runkakletpiranatluna xye hohnekaka pirana.
Hipirana psoluka Hoyakalu hinkaklexyana Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine hix-koxa runkaklexyatkalu. Hix-koxa hkojireta Hoyakalu, Hoyakalu hkojirexinnina hixa hitsrukatenni wane htshinniru Abraão-ni: “Ptowru tshijne hajene hihlewahchinikanyehitko piklopichane tshinanu.”
Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu hali hiwekkaklexinixkalu Hituru, Hoyakalu yokanhapkatlu hix-yehi, ruhlewahchinikanyehixyawakaphi, hixa satkakhi hichoxyawakaplu hektuntshi hwaleru.
Pedro João-yma Preso Rutajikolu PiranapniRunkaklewakanatawana Pedro, João yin-yehiya, rapokatkana sacerdote-ne hiyrunu Hoyakalupji hislahjetatshine chefe-te hiyrunu saduceu-ne hapoka.
Hjihekanuwatna klu tshinanu nuretkalune hepi hinkakletlu Jesus hiwejinixnaka pirana hiyáhoni rekhihimatluna hipnatshinetka koxa hiwekkakko.
Hiyáhoni hkachitna Pedro, João waneya preso rutakna haté wale prika klu tshinanu kayixkani.
Seyni hixo yine tokantshi yijnakotatshine halixlu Hoyakalu tokanu. Waneyakni Cristo halixatshine pejnu rixolewnana cinco mil yine hetko.
Pedro, João Jemahchinikankakatshine Hoji Sreta HitakkaWaneya wale prika rapatjetna Jerusalém poktshi hajene judeu-ne tsrukakalutene, yine chefe-tene hiyrun-koxa kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine hapatjeta.
Wane koxa rawakanata tsru sacerdote Anás wannayma, hiyrun-koxa Caifás, Anás mekanuru, João, Alexandre, hiyrunu pimrine Anás molene.
Wanna hoji sreta rutakkana Pedro, João waneya wanna hepomhana Pedro, João: — Hanhe ruchpajya xye hpixkonu, kat-hiwaka tshinanhe hkamhalu xye hiyakolukaka?
Waneya Pedro Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru katsepoyalu wan-tshinna: — Tsrukakalune judeu-ne hiyrunu yine chefe-tenhi!
Xawakni hixa hepomhawu klu hixlu xye jeji myanakanatkatu hiyrun-koxa hanukta rixa hitskalakkota.
Hiyáhoni himatanru xako hixa hiyrun-koxa israel-nerune ptowruneka, Jesus Cristo, hixa hiylaleru cruz-ya seyni Hoyakalu hiwekkakatnaklu waleko hpixkonu tshinanu rutskalhapotutatka xye jeji myanakanatkatu hixa hetanuya.
Walekatkani Jesus Yonawahlo Potukalu wan-tshinyehita: “Xye Jesus wale honukla sotlu, hixa panawatatshinhi, malukkotu rikahwakluna hepixlewatatshri potukni, psolupjiko poyehitatshrini wale.”
Hiyáhoni Jesus tsonu hiwekkaklewata klu tshinanu tshiji psoluko hikeni satu hiwaktshi yine tskalaya yine hiwekkakatshri.
Waneya hixolune hetna Pedro, João hi hpika hinkaklewletna. Waneya rimathetkoklunutkana Pedro, João muchtotkakkone rixyawakna hixolune himyekpotuta hiyrunu rimathetna Jesus-yma yanjejekanatatshine rixyawakna Pedro, João.
Hiyrunu hixolune hetlu jeji hitskalakkaluru João, Pedro-yma hyopkajyawaka wale tshinanu hike rumukata tshinretna.
Waneya hyokanatatkana Pedro, João jemahchinikankakjexikowakapjiya maleka hyiywakapna waneya tsrukakalune hjemahchinikankakatkana wannakakluko.
Wane htshinkakna: — Kluhe wixanutkana nyi jejine? Klu tshinanu ptowru yine Jerusalém poktshi hajene himatlu tsru hiyákolu hkamhana hiyrunu hi wumukata malixlenutlu.
Seyni hma mupalaxyawakanupa hipirana yin-yehiya wuykotanna hipokananu hma munkaklewaxyawakanupna hiyrunuko yin-yehiya Jesus hiwakaya.
Waneya tsrukakalune hepukatnakna Pedro, João waneya ruykotna hma munkaklewaxyawakanupna hi psojikna Jesus hiwakaya, hi koxa rasruklewatanna Jesus hiwakaya.
Waneya Pedro, João hihitna: — Haté hixa hinkakanwu katpothe xawaka wyijnakotanu ho hixa ho Hoyakalu?
Klu tshinanu hi koxa wumukata wma munkaklexyawakanuplu wale wetanru, wyijnakotanru.
Waneya rali hiykoletatnakna João, Pedro ruchochatna klu tshinanu hike rumukolujtatkana Pedro-ne yine tshinanu. Klu tshinanu ptowru yineru himalwutlu Hoyakalu wan-rixikolutka.
Xye jeji hitskalakkalurutka hiyákolu tshinanu quarenta mhale pnutetkalu.
Waneya Cristo halixatshine rali yijnakolexinixkana, wanna pa hchinikanurune rimalwutluna Hoyakalu, wane htshinruna: — Pixa Hoyakalu Ptowru Himukatatshriyi tenhohne hiyrun-koxa tshiji pkamha, mar powha koxa pkamha hiyrun-koxa ptowruka mar powha hitokote hwatshri, tenhohne hwatshri, tshiji hwatshri kamhatshriyi.
Pixa hinkakletatkalu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluruya wutsrukatni Davi-ni ptowrerni namaya, wane htshina: “Klu tshinanhe rahnanuwatna yine panerkaka, hiyrunu jipukaleru pirana ruchinikanretna yine?
Ptowru tshiji hajene phurune hiyrun-koxa tsrukakalune hapatjetna pa hchinikanurune hkamnixyawakluna Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus, Hoyakalu nurreru.”
Klu tshinanu halikaka phuru Herodes hiyrun-koxa Pôncio Pilatos hapatjeta xye poktshiya, judeu-neyma hiyrun-koxa pimri tshijnekaka hkamnixyawakluna Jesus, pnurreru potukalu.
Rapatjetna hkamhiywakapluna wale mitshikananu punkakletleru pmixkonu tshinanu, pihchinikanu tshinanu hakanhatshripa.
Hiyáhoni xawakni Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu, hetanu hi pso hamlenukananu htshinanwakatwu. Penekanna ptowrene hmixkowahchinikanuxyawakna runkaklexyawakluna ptokanu.
Seyni wanepnawaka Hoyakalu pomyokanu wan-hixkalurkakapa hitskalhalkaka, hetkalurkaka, himyekaklewatatshrikaka, pnurreru potukalu Jesus hiwaka tshinanu.
Rali hanjihohnerexinixkana, waneya ruyolikatka rapatjekanaxyawakna. Ptowru neruka katsepoyatka Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru. Hoyakalu tokanu runkakletna hike pikanu.
Cristo Halixatshine Hwiywakni PiranapniPtowuneka Cristo halixatshine pa hajipkana, pa hchinikanurunni. Hi satukna wan-tshina: Nimwaleru pejnu hitanu. Seyni wanna ptowruneka hapiklu rejnunkatkakna psoluka rimwastsireneyma.
Tsru pixkonuyma nuretkalune hiphujetlu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus hiwejinixnaka pirana, hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu hihlenuymatkana.
Klu tshinanu hi satukna wanna mahaxya pa hixanu klu tshinanu katukta himwalu tshiji ho pantshi, ruchankanru waneya ranikanru ruchankaleru wenru.
Waneya nuretkalune jixistsi ruknokluna ruchankalerna wenru. Hiyáhoni satkaka rapikna wan-rixa mahlexyana.
Barnabé Henekachale PiranapniHiyáhoni José, nuretkalune yokmakhiwakleru rutakhiwakatatkaluna, Barnabé. Waleni yokakkaluru hiykolewatatshri. José Levita, Chipre tshijne hichpajikatshrini.
Waneyakananru tshiji. Hiyáhoni ruchankalu. Raniklu hwenru. Nuretkalunesko rutakwenrutlu.
Ananias Hiyrunu Safira PiranapniSatu jeji Ananias hiwakatletatshri hhanunro Safira-yma hichankatkalu psoji tshiji.
Seyni psoji tshiji wenru Ananias himutuka hhanunro koxa himatyehitatkalu. Seyni tshiji wenru psojite tsonu ranikatka Ananias waneya renekna nuretkalune.
Waneya Pedro wan-tshinru: — Ananias, haklu tshinanhe pitshitlu Satanás htowuxyawakyi pihchinikanuya pweyawyehixyawaklu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru pumutujyawaklu psoji tshiji wenru?
Pma muchankakanuklunuwalu tshiji, hi he pixanu rixapa? Haté pali hichankalexinixkalu tshiji, hi he pixanni tiyiro? Haklu tshinanhe paluka wan-hixletatka? Hi yineru pweyawyehita seyni halikaka Hoyakaluko pweyawyehita.
Xye tokantshi hjeminixka Ananias waneya waneklukawa hyawnanatka rupnanatka. Hiyáhoni tsru piklu rixna jempiranyehitatshine ptowruneka.
Hiyáhoni rapokna maklujine hpoyitatkaluna himanni waneya maleka ranikluna hkapnatatkaluna.
Waneya mapa hora rixini tjihlokatka Ananias-ni hnunro seyni hi timatakanata wan-rixyawakanatka Ananias-ni.
Waneya Pedro hepomhalo: — Punkakanno, wla pso wenrurhe pyoptoxyalu tshiji?Waneya tuhitlu: — Hehe, wane pso wenru wyoptota.
Hiyáhoni Pedro wan-tshinatkalo: — Haklu tshinanhe pixa phanuruyma pa hchinikanurutu hixa yahotletlu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru? Petanna! Hiphaptostsitkana maklujine phanurni kapnatapatshine hiyrunu pix-koxa hkochpakanna.
Waneklukawa Pedro jixistsi tyawnamtanatka. Tupnanatka. Waneya hjihlojinixkana maklujine, hipnatshroni rukchijyalona waneya hkochpaklona thanurnistsi hkapnatanatkalona.
Hiyáhoni Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine hiyrunu ptowru jempiranyehitatshine koxa pikpotutatka.
Hixo Himyekaklewatatshrikaka Hkamhana Nuretkalune PiranapniNuretkalune kamhalu hixo hetkalurkaka, himyekaklewatatshrikaka koxa yine tskalaya hiyrunu rapatjejetna Hoyakalupji psojite Salomão tshinikowaka.
Pimrineko pika hepiretletna seyni wanepnawaka yine kahwakpirpotutna nuretkalune.
Híxona jejine, suxon-koxa halixlu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Cristo hiyáhoni rixolewnamtatkana Jesus halixatshinetka.
Haté yine koxa hanikna yeyixatshine hatnu tnumne rutakkana. Hijekoymana ho rukwereyma rutakkana pa katako Pedro wane hyapamxinipa wale mayawle katshpokanna.
Nuretkalune Kachixikowaka PiranapniWaneya hpalnatka tsru sacerdote hiyrunu waleymalune saduceu-ne mkoje hajenni, wanna ptowruneka hahxatna nuretkalune.
Hkachitna nuretkalune waneya preso rutakkatkana.
Seyni wale yetshno potuko satu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajene kotpukatkalu preso hiphaptotkaka waneya ranikna nuretkalune maleka waneya wane htshina:
— Hyanutka, Hoyakalupji hyopkakanu waneya hinkakanna xye herotu hiweklu pirana.
Xye tokantshi hyijnakoxinixkana, yetshpotukawa rixini hjihlokatkaluna Hoyakalupji waneya runkaklewatna. Seyni tsru sacerdote hiyrunu waleymalune hapatjejixatkana tsrukakalune judeu-ne hiyrunu tsrune judeu-ne ptowruneka. Wane pnute rawapjixatkana nuretkalune preso hwatshine.
Seyni preso yehi rapojinixkana soldado-ne, hi wane rukchijikatkana hiyáhoni hsatokatkana waneya runkaklewatna,
wane htshinna: — Preso yehi wapoka wetlu hihle hichyaletatshri hiyrunu hinotatshine soldado-ne hiphapto hinaple hyopkakakanatna. Seyni wkotpujinixkalu preso hike yineru wane wukchijyatka.
Waneya xye pirana hjeminiklunu Hoyakalupji kosekatshri hiyrunu tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne, hi rimat-hichinikanuwatatkana klukta rixatkana nuretkalune.
Waneya pchini tsonu satuko hapoka, runkakna wane htshina: — Hjemanu! Preso hitakanune jejine Hoyakalupji hyopkakna runkakna yine.
Hiyáhoni soldado-ne pohire h-soldado-teneyma Hoyakalupji nwaka hyana. Rawapna nuretkalune seyni hi hipokananu hkachitna klu tshinanu hpikna hixolune sotlujexyawakna wanna soldado-ne.
Waneya soldado-ne hjemahchinikanyehitjene hoji sreta hitakna nuretkalune waneya tsru sacerdote wan-tshina:
— Hi he wuykothi xye hiwaktshi pirana hmasruklewaxyawakanu? Seyni hetanu Jerusalém psoluyaka hyapiranata xye hasruklewlu hiyrunu hixa haluka hikolukletwu xye jeji hiylaxikowaka tshinanu.
Pedro hiyrunu pimrine nuretkalune wan-tshin-hihretatkana: — Hoyakalu halujyawak-potu wujha homkahretanu seyni yine halujyawaka hike.
Wutsrukatenni Hoyakalute hiwekkakatkalu Jesus hixa hiylaleru hahmuna skita hixpaleru.
Seyni Hoyakalu hitaklu Jesus hpotukle sreta Tsru Hixikatshriwa rixyawakapa yine hiwekkakatshri rixyawakapa. Renejyawakna judeu-ne rehchinikanuxyawakapna hiyrunu rektunna ruknojyawakapna.
Hixa hiyrunu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru koxa hiphujtatatshinwu xye pirana tshinanu. Hoyakalu henekna ralixjene Hiwejikaluru Potukalu.
Gamaliel Hiykole PiranapniWaneya hjemahchinikanyehitjene jeminiklunru xye pirana hjihekanuwatna hiyáhoni raluk-hiylaletna nuretkalune.
Seyni satu fariseu, Gamaliel hiwakatletatshri, yopkaka wanna hanikajite. Wale, hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshrini, ptowru yineru kahwakpirpotutlu. Wale maleka hkochpakjixna nuretkalune pchini tsonu.
Waneya Gamaliel wan-tshina: — Israel-nerune! Xakoka kluhe hkamhinna nyi jejine.
Klu tshinanu mitshikawa ruphujewnatka Teudas tshinkaluru. Tsru rutajnawa hiyáhoni psokaklu quatrocentos jejine hepiretlu seyni ruylatkatka waneya ralixjene ptowruneka hipalatatka hiyáhoni hike hkamhatkana wanna.
Waneya wane pnute rutakyahojikolhohnena yine rixinixka ruphujewnatka Judas tshinkaluru, Galileia hajeru. Hixo yineru homkahitlu waneya wale koxa hipnana waneya romkahitjene ptowruneka hipalatatka.
Hiyáhoni xawakni nunkakhi: Hetachatanutkana nyi jejine hichochatanutkana klu tshinanu yinenu rixini xye chinikantshi, xye kamrurtshi pa hohne nikawnachatanu.
Seyni Hoyakalunu rixinipa, hixa hi himukata himaletletanru. Pa katako haté Hoyakalu wyahota hixa. Waneya wanna halixlu Gamaliel tokanu.
Hiyáhoni htomhatkana nuretkalune waneya rali kotshipjerexinna ruykotna Jesus hiwaka hma munkaklexyawakanpatkana waneya ruchotatkana.
Hiyáhoni nuretkalune hjemahchinikanyehixikowakna yehi ruchpajyana. Rumuwamtna klu tshinanu rutakyahokkana rumukata salewnalexyawakna haté reyikkana Jesus hiwaka tshinanu.
Ptowru hohneruka Hoyakalupjiya haté pa pjikakaya hi rutuk-hinkakletletluna Jesus Cristo pirana hi rutuk-hasrukletna yine.
Halixatshine Hapatjetatshine Hepixatshine Hitajikolu PiranapniHiyáhoni wale hohnekaka rixolewnatkana Cristo halixatshine. Seyni hejnu hima hakanhatka grego-nerune, hebreu-neruneyma. Klu tshinanu grego hipnahnurutatshrone hi hima hislahka heneksajexikowakaya pa hohne pejnu.
Hiyáhoni doze nuretkalune rapatjetkana yine waneya wane htshinna: — Hi kihleru wuknojyawakaplu wunkaklexyawaklu Hoyakalu tokanu nikkaluru tshinanu.
Hiyáhoni, nomolene, hnuretanna sete jejine hixa tskalaya, jejine kihle piranyehirune, Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru katsepoyalune, kahchinikanerune. Wanna wutakanu xye kamrurtshi hkamhiywakapna.
Waneya ptowru yineru hikchikhihlenutlu wane htshinyawakna nuretkalune. Hiyáhoni hnuretluna Estêvão, jeji Cristo halixatshri potuka hiyrun-koxa katsepoylu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru. Hiyrun-koxa hnuretna Filipe, Prócoro, Nicanor, Timom, Pármenas, Nicolau Antioquia hajerni. Walemka hi judeu-neru seyni judeu halixyawaka homkahitatshrini.
Nyi jejine nuretkalune hoji sreta yine hitakna. Waneya nuretkalune hanjihohnetatka, rutakamyotna jejine jiwu hoho.
Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu tokanu mixkowatatka. Rixolewnatkana Cristo halixatshine Jerusalém poktshiya. Hiyrun-koxa hixo sacerdote-ne homkahitlu halixlewlu.
Estêvão Hapatjehchinikanutatshine Hoji Sreta Hitajikolu PiranapniWaneya Estêvão Hoyakalu hamotanru potuko katsepoylu hpixkonu. Xye jeji tsru himyekaklewatatshrikaka tsru hetkalurkaka koxa hkamha yine tskalaya.
Seyni satkaka yineru hanjihohnewakapji hislahatshine Libertos tshinkalune, Cirene, Alexandria, Cilícia, Ásia hichpajikatshine, ruhjekakna Estêvão-yma.
Seyni hi rumukata halliretlu Estêvão rimatkalnu tshinanu hiyrun-koxa Hiwejikaluru hyanumkakjeru tshinanu.
Hiyáhoni Estêvão kamnitjene hyohniyehitluna satkaka jeji wane htshinyawakapluna Estêvão: — Ha hixa wjemlu xye jeji hektutu htshinyehixyawaklu Moisés hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu yehi.
Estêvão kamnitatshine jihekna hixolune yine, judeu-ne tsrukakalutene koxa hiyrun-koxa kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine. Rapyehitluna Estêvão. Waneya ranikluna jemahchinikanyehixikowakapji.
Hiyáhoni ranikluna weyawatatshine hweyawyehixyawakapluna Estêvão: — Xye jeji hi hituka hektutu tshinrenwakatlu Hoyakalupji potukalu hiyrunu Moisés yonreru koxa.
Klu tshinanu wjemlu wane htshinyawaklu: Xye Jesus Nazaré hajeru nikatanru Hoyakalupji hiyrun-koxa pnuko rixkakanwu wixjexyawaka Moisés yokanre hixa tshinanu.
Waneya ptowru yineru tuplatatshine jemahchinikankakjexikowakapji yopukhapotutlu. Rethojitluna Estêvão. Hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hichpajikatshri hoji pixka rixhojita Estêvão.
Estêvão Kojiretna Hjihyehitjene PiranapniWaneya tsru sacerdote hepomhalu Estêvão: — Waneklahe?
Waneya Estêvão wan-tshina: — Nomolene hiyrun-koxa hitsrukatshine, hyijnakotanu. Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hiphujewnayehitniri wutsrukatni Abraão, Mesopotâmia rawakanaxinni Harã hma yaknuklunuwa.
Hoyakalu wan-tshinru: “Ptshijne puchpajini pimolene tskalaya. Pyanwakatanru tshiji nekhitanyi.”
Hiyáhoni Abraão hichpajyalu htshijne Caldeia, Harã poktshi rapoka. Waneya rupninixka Abraão hirni Hoyakalu hanikatkalu Abraão hewi tshijne hixa wwiywakatka xawakni.
Seyni Hoyakalu hi psojikna xye tshiji reneklu Abraão waneklu papko hi pa kochtsheklu jixikna renekniri. Seyni Hoyakalu hinkaklexyalu xye tshiji psoluka renejyawakaplu Abraão hiyrunu Abraão klopichanepa. Hoyakalu xye pirana runkaklexyalu Abraão hi kwuhenewalu Abraão.
Seyni koxa Hoyakalu wla tshinru Abraão: “Pixa klopichane mtshijnene pixka rixanna pa nerkaka tshijne rawanna. Wanna towutkalune pixka rixanna, hsaletkona quatrocentos mhale pchini hohne.”
Waneya wane htshina Hoyakalu: “Hita hapnokatanna yine hixa saletatshine. Waneya wane pnute wale tshijne ruchpajinna wanna hsatkapanna xye tshijne hita towutanunepni.”
Hoyakalu hinkaklu Abraão hjiprojhaptojimtaxyawaka pirana, hkojirexyalu wale pirana mnukawa runkaklexyalu Hoyakalu. Wale tshinanu Abraão histaklu Isaque ptojimta hmatuxini Isaque oito hohne rixini. Isaque wuhenetlu Jacó. Jacó wuhenetna wutsrukatene doze.
Waneya wutsrukatene hahxatlu José hiyáhoni ruchankatkaluna José Egito ranikkatka. Seyni Hoyakalu hislahatkalu.
Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu kochpaklu José hsalewnale psoluka. Hiyrun-koxa José Faraó hoji sreta rapojini Hoyakalu wan-hixkaklu José Faraó poyikowaxyawaka hiyrunu Hoyakalu heneklu José kahchinikanu rixyawaka. Hiyáhoni Faraó hitaklu José Egito tshijne htowuxyawaka hiyrun-koxa phurupji ruslahyawaka.
Seyni rakanhatka tsru natshi hiyrunu tsru salewaktshi Egito tshijneya, Canaã tshijneya koxa. Waneya wutsrukatenni hike hnikleru hwiynina.
Waneya hjeminri Jacó Egito tshijne hima rawa trigo, hyokanatna wutsrukatenni Egito tshijne nwaka mitshikananu kata.
Hepi kata rixinri José hinkakatkana himolene José rixyawaka waneya Faraó himathetlu José kluneru nerni.
Waneya José hepuklu ruru Jacó hiyrun-koxa himolene ptowruneka setenta e cinco yineru.
Waneya Jacó yanwakatlu Egito. Hix-hohnetkani wane rupniyanatka Jacó-ni wutsrukatenni koxa.
Wane wkatanuko ranikkana wannani mane Siquém tshinikowaka hkapnatkanna. Siquém Abraão mnukawa ranjixyana Hamor klopichane tiyiroya waneko hkapnatkana.
Rapokpapkolutatka Hoyakalu kamhiywaklu Abraão runkaklexinri hkojirexyalu pirana, wane pchinika rixolewnatkana yine Egito tshijneya.
Waneya satu phuru hiphujewnatka José metjejetkatu.
Seyni waneklu papko hmatutatka Moisés mturu pomtalu kihleru. Tsrune hislahatkalu mturu Moisés hipjikona hyohimaxika mapa ksuru pchinika.
Seyni hma mumukata yohimletkanuklunutkaluna mturu phuru whene suxo himutukatkalu, tkammanetatkalu Moisés towhene rixyawakapa Moisés.
Wale tshinanu Moisés hasrukkatka Egito hajene himatkale hiyrun-koxa tokantshi hiyrunu kamrurtshi tsru himukatatshrini.
Waneya quarenta mhale rixinixka Moisés ruchinikatkalu himolene israel-nerune retapyawakapa.
Wane retlu satu egito-neru yotnemtlu israel-neru. Hiyáhoni repixlu himole hiyrunu Moisés hiylatanru egito-neru.
Moisés kahwaklu himolene himatlu Hoyakalu hepixanna wanna Moisés tshinanu. Seyni hi rimatjematkaluna.
Waneya wale prika Moisés hetna hepi yahotkakatshine israel-nerune. Raluk-hiykoletmakna wane htshina: “Jejine, hyijnakotanu, hixa moletkakatshinhi klu tshinanhe hyahotkaka?”
Seyni yinuwaka yahotkakletatshri herutlu Moisés waneya wane htshina: “Kathe xawaka hitakyi pixa ptowuxyawakwu ho hixa puykoxyawaka?
Paluk-hiylaletannohe hita kapethohne egito-neru puylatanruni pixka?”
Waneya Moisés xye hima hjemini rasujyatkalu Egito tshijne, Midiã tshijne hya rawyawakapa. Hepi jejine hwuheneta Moisés wale tshijneya.
Waneya quarenta mhale hiknohatnaka. Satu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru hakanhayehitlu Moisés, popriwaka Sinai mrijistsi kawchipiri halhatshri mero hitokote rakanhiya.
Seyni Moisés himyeka retanru tshinanu hiyáhoni hkayehikatkalu kawchipiri retpotuxyawakaplu. Waneya Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu plama hjema, wla htshina:
“Hitni putsrukatenni Hoyakalutno, Abraão-nni, Isaque-nni hiyrunu Jacó-ni Hoyakalut-koxno.” Seyni Moisés hitataka hpikle tshinanu haté hpika wane yihleta.
Waneya Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu wan-tshinru: “Pkochpakanru p-sandalha-te klu tshinanu xye tshijne pyopkajyawaka Hoyakalu hwiywaka tsonu.
Netna nonerunni Egito tshijne hwatshine salewnale, njemlu wanna tshiyahle hiyáhoni nuna nkochpajyawakapna. Xawakni pixa nyokanatanu Egito tshijne pyiywakapa.”
Seyni israel-nerune hi yoptotlu Moisés. Waneya wane htshinruna Moisés: “Kathe hitakyi ptowuxyawakwu, puykoxyawakwu?” Seyni Hoyakalu yokanatlu xye Moisés chefe hiyrunu kochpaklewatatshri rixyawakapa, hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru hepixleyma kawchipiri hoho hakanhikatshri.
Walekni kochpakna israel-nerune Egito tshijne ruchpajyawakna. Hiyakolukaka hkamha hiyrun-koxa himyekaklewatatshrikaka hkamha Egito tshijneya hiyrun-koxa Mar powha Seroluya hiyrun-koxa popriwakaya quarenta mhale pchinika.
Xyekni Moisés wan-tshinatkana israel-nerune: “Hoyakalu yokanatanru satu Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri hita pixka hixatshripni Hoyakalu yokanatanrupni. Hixako himolepni wale.”
Moisés israel-neruneyma rawakanata popriwakaya hapatjexikowaka. Wane rawakanata Moisés wutsrukatenniyma hiyrun-koxa hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru Sinai mriji popriwaka riynumsaxijeruyma. Moisés yoptotlu tokantshi hiwekkaklewatatshri hixa runkajyawakaplu.
Seyni wutsrukatenni hi haluka yijnakoletlu Moisés hiyáhoni rerutluna hiyrunu rujhahchinikanutna Egito nwaka hsatkapyawakna.
Wane htshinruna Arão: “Pkamhinwu hoyakalune hixa wkosekjenepa. Hi wimatlu klukta rixanatka xye Moisés hixa Egito tshijne wkochpajijeru.”
Hiyáhoni Arão kamhiyna satu mayawletshicha boi whene mayawle waneya ruylatluna satkaka nikalu henekachalu renekluna. Waneya poyikowlu hkamhana mayawletshicha hkamhalerna himyoyna tshinanu.
Seyni Hoyakalu hiknokatkana retachatna, wutsrukatenni katahirine tenhohne hajene hmunanhiywakna. Klu tshinanu wane htshina yonawahleta Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine yonawahleya: “Israel-nerune, hi koxa hita tshinanu hixa hiylajekanatlu nikalune henekachalkaka tshinanu quarenta mhale pchinika popriwakaya.
Hixa hanikakanatlu nikalumtapji, hoyakalu minje Moloque tshinkalurupji hiyrun-koxa katahiri mayawle Renfã tshinkaluru hixa hoyakalute yapere. Hixa kamhatkalu xyekaka mayawletshichakaka hmunanhalerupa. Wale tshinanu nakakanhi Babilônia tshijne pnute hyiywakapa.”
Wutsrukatennimka rawya nikalumtapji Hoyakalu hwiywaka popriwaka yehi. Xyepji kamhakatka Hoyakalu tshina hinkaklexyawak-potuklu Moisés hiyrunu Hoyakalu hekhixyawak-potuklu Moisés rixa kamhaletlu nikalumtapji.
Wanna yoptotlu nikalumtapji rutsrukatenniyna waneya xyepji ranikjekanatna Josué-yma, pa tshijnekaka hajene rakakjekanaxinna Hoyakalu hakakanunetka pejnu. Waneya nikalumtapji wale tshijne hitukatka haté Davi papkolutka.
Davi hihlehchinikanutka Hoyakaluya waneya Davi hanjitlu Hoyakalu ritshixyawakaplu papji hkamhiywakapa Jacó Hoyakalute tshinanupa.
Makakta Salomão kamhanru Hoyakalupji.
Seyni Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu tenhohne hajeru hi pantshi yineru kamhalerupji rawa. Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri tshinyawaka:
Hi he hitakni kamhalu xyekaka ptowruka?”
Waneya Estêvão wan-tshinatnakna hjihyehitjene: —Chiko hchinikanurunhi, chiko hajirunhi hektuwaka kamhatshinhi. Hixa hi yijnakotlu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru, hixa wutsrukatenni pixka hixa.
Hanutkalhe Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri hitsrukatenni mkamnikanatkotu? Hixa wutsrukatenni mnukawa hiylajekanatanna potukalu hinatshripa pirana hinkakletatshinni. Hiyrunu hixa samyoklu hiyrunu hiylatlu xye kihleru.
Hixmaka yoptotlu yonruru pirana hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrene tenhohne hichpajikatshineya seyni hixa majnakowaxyalu.
Estêvão Hipninri PiranapniWaneya hjihyehitjene yijnakotlu Estêvão. Hjihekanuwpotutna. Raskiyhiyehitluna.
Seyni Estêvão katsepoylu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru, tenhohne hyihatatka, retlu Hoyakalu hoyaknu hiyrun-koxa retlu Jesus, Hoyakalu potukle sretaya.
Waneya wane htshina: — Hetanu! Netlu tenhohne hitpukatshri, netlu jeji whene Hoyakalu potukle sreta yopkakatshri.
Seyni hixolune katshpokajnakopnamta. Hsaplewpotutna pa kaphohotkolutu rixluna Estêvão.
Waneya ruknokluna Estêvão poktshi kahnete waneya hsotlujetanatkaluna. Hetakanatatshine satu makluji jixistsi rutakamkalutna. Wale hiwakni Saulo.
Estêvão hsotlujetna. Seyni Estêvão hanjitlu Jesus wane htshina: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus, pyoptotanru niwejinri.
Waneya hyoptsojitamta Estêvão. Tsru saple rixa. Wane htshin-sapleta Estêvão: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu, hi papnokatanna nyi jejine hmajnakonuna tshinanu! Waneya rali wan-tshinretatka rupnanatka.
Saulo Kamnixyawakna Cristo Halixatshine Hapatjetatshine PiranapniHiyrun-koxa Saulo hikchikhihlenutlu Estêvão-ni ruylaxyawakatkana. Wale hohne Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine Jerusalém poktshi hajene yinuwaka salewnaleta tsru potuko. Hiyáhoni hkopalatkatkana halixatshine Judeia tshijneya psoluka, Samaria tshijneya psoluka. Seyni nuretkalune tsonu Jerusalém hitukatka.
Satkaka jejine kahchinikanurune kapnatlu Estêvão manni. Htshiyahpotutna Estêvão-ni tshinanu.
Seyni Saulo hijhalu Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine hnikaxyawakna. Papji pejnu hjihloka, hkochtshekna jejine, suxon-koxa waneya kapna ruknokanatkana.
Filipe Hinkaklewaxyawaka Samaria Tshijneya PiranapniHiyáhoni hipalatatshine ptowruchaka hyana, runkakletluna tokantshi Hoyakalu pirana.
Waneya Filipe Samaria poktshi nwaka hya. Runkaklewyehitna Cristo pirana.
Hapatjetatshine hixolune yijnakpotutlu Filipe tshinyawaka. Ptowru yineru yijnakotlu, retakanatluna himyekaklewatatshrikaka Filipe kamhaleru.
Klu tshinanu kamtshine hichpajyatkana hixo yine, tsru saple rixna kamtshine ruchpajinixkana. Hiyrun-koxa hixo hiktehatshine myankane koxa hitskalhatka.
Hiyáhoni rumuwatna Samaria poktshi hajene.
Kahontshi Simão PiranapniWale poktshi koxa rawakanata satu jeji Simão hiwakatletatshri. Mitshikawa kahontshitkani wale poktshiya. Rimyekjekanatna Samaria hajene. Tsru potu rutajnawa,
hiyáhoni wale poktshi hwatshine ptowruneka tsrukakalune, hike mwikane koxa hislahpotutlu htokanu. Wane htshinna: — Xye jeji Hoyakalu pixkonu himwatshri, “Tsru Pixkonurutu” tshinkalurni.
Ruslahpotutluna klu tshinanu hix-hohnepotukananu rimyekakatkana kahontshi rixle tshinanu.
Seyni Filipe hinkaklexinixkalu kihler-potuko tokantshi Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka pirana hiyrunu Jesus Cristo pirana. Jejine, suxon-koxa halixatka waneya h-batiza-tkatkana.
Simão koxa halixatka. Rali batiza-letkoklunutka, Simão himotsatlu Filipe. Rimyekatka Simão klu tshinanu retlu hetkalurkaka, himyekaklewatatshrikaka Filipe kamhalerkaka.
Pedro Hiyrunu João Samaria Tshijne Rawyawakna PiranapniNuretkalune Jerusalém hitukatshine jempiranyehixinna Samaria hajen-koxa yoptoxyawakatkalu Hoyakalu pirana hyokananwakatna Pedro, João.
Waneya rapojinixkana Pedro, João, ranjihohnetna Samaria hajene yoptoxyawakaplu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru.
Klu tshinanu nyi yine batiza-tkatka Jesus Cristo hiwakaya tsonu seyni Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hi wanna hoho rapokawa.
Waneya Pedro, João himyona hitakhohotna Samaria hajene hiyáhoni wan-rixa yoptoletluna Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru.
Seyni rexinixka Simão nuretkalune himyona hitakhohoxinixkana Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru renejikowakpatkana waneya tiyiro ranikanwakatna Pedro, João.
Seyni Pedro wan-tshinru: — Pixa ptiyiroteymako tshitshmero yanu klu tshinanu pkahwaklu Hoyakalu henekachale hanjitka tiyiroyma.
Pixa hi himukata hapaka hepixletwu xye kamrurtshiya klu tshinanu hi potuk-hajyi Hoyakalu hetanuya.
Pehchinikanutanu xye hektutuya waneya Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu panjitanu pa katako xye hektutu chinikantshi paji hwatshri ruknojinyi.
Klu tshinanu hitaho katsepoyyi hahxalu hiyrunu hektutu hostutatkayi.
Waneya Simão wan-tshinna Pedro, João: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hanjiyehitanno hixa xye ptowruka htshinyawaka hma makanhayehixyawakanupno.
Hiyáhoni Pedro, João hali hinkakletatkana yine Hoyakalu pirana hiyrunu rali hiphujtaletatkaluna Jesus kamrure pirana, hsatokluna Jerusalém nwaka waneya pa poktshikaka Samaria tshijne hyapamxyawakna runkaklexyaluna kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana.
Filipe Hiyrunu Phuro Hislahjetatshri PiranapniWaneya hiwejikaluru Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru hiynumatlu Filipe: — Ppalnanu sul sreta pyanu hatnu hapo Jerusalém Gaza yapatshri, kahnete poktshi hatnu hapote. Waneya hpalnatka Filipe, hyatka.
<sup>(27-28)</sup> Hatnu hapo hyoptoxyalu satu jeji Etiópia hajeru, htshijne nwaka yamtatshritka. Etiópia hajero suxo phuro Candace hislahatshrini wale. Tpohirewle psoluka hislahatshrini wale. Jerusalém rapkapatka Hoyakalu hpoyahnuxyawakapa waneya h-carro-te, cavalo kosleru hsatojya rethakananumtlu Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri Isaías-ni yonawahle.
(-)
Waneya Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru wan-tshinru Filipe: — Pyanwakatanru, pomkahitanro twu carro.
Hiyáhoni Filipe hasukanwakatlu, hjemlu rethakanaxyawaklu Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshrini Isaías-ni yonre. Waneya repomhalu: — Pimatjemluhe pethatanru?
Waneya ruhitlu: — Hanhe numukata himatjemletlu nethatanru hike masrukanutno? Waneya htshanixlu Filipe ratskoxyawaklo carro waleyma htuplaxyawakapa.
Xyekatkani Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru psojite rethakanatanru: “Hatatjewa carneiro hiylawaka hanikkaluru pixka hiyrunu carneiro jiwjitkaluru pixka rixa hike htshina waneko pixka rixanu, hi hyanumatanu.
Reyikkatka rapnokkatka. Hi kaklopichlu hma pohixikowakanupna hiklopichane klu tshinanu hkona hiwekletkatka xye tshijneya.”
Waneya phuro hislahatshri hepomhalu Filipe, wane htshina: — Nepomhanyi, punkakanno katu piranrahe hkochtsheka Isaías ho walenrahe ho satuko?
Hiyáhoni Filipe yinuwaka hinkakletlu. Xye pirana yonatkaluruko hyinuwaka hihle hinkaklepotutlu kihler-potuko tokantshi hiwekkaklewatatshri Jesus pirana runkaklu.
Waneya hatnu hapo hyapamtawana honha yehistsi rapokna. Phuro hislahatshri wan-tshina: — Petanru honu, klu himaletno n-batiza-xikolupa?
Waneya Filipe wan-tshina: — Palixiniplu psoluka pajiya pumukata.Waneya ruhitlu: — Nalixlu Jesus Cristo Hoyakalu whene rixyawaka.
Hiyáhoni htowutlu rutukajyawaklo h-carro-te waneya hyopikatkana wanna hepi honha hjihlokna waneya Filipe batiza-tlu phuro hislahatshri.
Hkanijiniklunna Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru kochtshekamtlu Filipe hiyáhoni phuro hislahatshri hikeklu hetatnaklu Filipe seyni phuro hislahatshri yatnaka poyikowamtatshritka.
Chinpotukawa Azoto poktshi rakanhiyatka Filipe, runkaklewamta kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana ptowru poktshikaka hyapamxyawaka Cesareia poktshi rapojyawakatka.
Saulo Hehchinikanre PiranapniWane pchinika Saulo hinkakletatkalu ruylaxikowakna Jesus halixatshine. Tsru sacerdote, Hoyakalu kamrure kamhatshri, nwaka hyatka Saulo.
Ranjitlu yonawahlo Damasco poktshi hanjihohnewakapji hajene tshinanu, yonawahlo hinhatshri tshinanu Saulo himukata kachretatkana wane hajene Jesus halixatshine rukchijinipna jejineko ho suxoneko, wan-hixatshine rumukata hanikleta Jerusalém poktshi nwaka hostutkalunetka.
Seyni hatnu hapo hyapamtawa, Damasco-stsi rapokatka. Waneklukawa potuko tsru katalu tenhohne hichpajikatshri hatawnayehitlu Saulo.
Saulo yawnamtatka tshiji. Hyijnakotlu satu tokantshi wane htshinjeru: — Saulo, Saulo, haklu tshinanhe pkamnitno?
Waneya Saulo wan-tshina: — Katyihe pixa Tsru Hixikatshriwayi? Waneya wane htshinru: — Hita Jesus-no pkamnijetanruno.
Seyni ppalnanutka. Tsru poktshi pyanu. Waneko pimrine hinkajinyi nalukleru pkamhinripa.
Seyni Saulo himotsane jejine hitukatka. Hike rumukata tshinretna. Tokantshi halikaka hjemna seyni hike yineru retna.
Hiyáhoni Saulo palnatka. Rumrekhatmakatka seyni hi rapkathojitatka. Hiyáhoni hkanojimtluna Saulo Damasco poktshi rutakatkaluna.
Ananias Hapkapyehixyawaklu Saulo PiranapniDamasco rawakanata satu jeji Jesus halixatshri Ananias tshinkaluru. Hoyakalu pixkonu tshinanu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus hepomhalu: — Ananias! Waneya Ananias hihitlu: — Hewno, Tsru Hixikatshriwa.
Waneya Tsru Hixikatshriwa wan-tshinru: — Ppalnanu. Hatnu hapo Direita hiwakatletatshri pyanu, Judas-pji nwaka. Wane pujhinri satu jeji Saulo tshinkaluru, Tarso poktshi hajeru hanjihohnetatshri.
Saulo satu jeji rupjeta Ananias tshinkaluru. Xye rupjereru jihlokhipnayehitlu, himyo rutakhohotlu rexyawakpatnaka.
Waneya Ananias hihitlu wane htshina: — Tsru Hixikatshriwa, hixo yine njempiranyehixyalu xye jeji hi psokananu hektutu hkamhiyatkana potukalune Jesus halixatshine, Jerusalém hajene.
Hiyrun-koxa xawakni hewi rapoka tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hinhatshriyma hkachixyawakapna wanna ptowruneka pixa hiwaka munanhatshine.
Waneya Tsru Hixikatshriwa wan-tshinru: — Seyni wane pyanu klu tshinanu nnuretlu xye jeji hkamru-rewaxyawakpatka hita tshinanu. Hita hiwaka hpohixinripa judeu mixkane yehiya, pohirtshinyehiya, israel-nerune klopichane yehiya.
Hitako hekhitanru Saulo ptowruka hsalewninripa Hita hiwaka tshinanu.
Hiyáhoni Ananias yatka, Judas-pji hjihloka waneya Saulo hoho rutakamyotatka. Waneya wane htshina: — Nomole Saulo, Tsru Hixikatshriwa hewi nyokanatjeru walekni Jesus pixa hetleru hatnu hapoya. Wale yokanatno pexyawakpatnaka hiyrun-koxa ptsepoxikotka Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru.
Waneya waneklukawa potuko rujrukhichyaleyhaletatka chimatataji pixkalutu. Retatka. Waneya hpalnatka, h-batiza-tkatka.
Waneya rali niklexinixka hjemlu hixko rixyawakatnaka. Waneya Damasco rutukatka pa hohnekaka Jesus halixatshineyma.
Saulo Damasco Rawyawaka PiranapniWaneya waneklukawa hanjihohnewakapjikaka Jesus pirana runkakleta Saulo. Wane htshina: — Jesus, Hoyakalu whene rixyawaka.
Waneya ptowruneka Saulo jematshine himyeka. Wane htshinna: — Hi he xyekni Jerusalém hajene, Jesus munanhatshine hiylajetatshrikni wale? Hi he walekni hanikna Jesus halixatshine hostutkalune tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne yehi?
Seyni Saulo pnute mixkowahchinikanutatka haté judeu-ne Damasco hajene hi rimatahchinikanutluna Saulo hiphujexyawaklu Jesus, Cristo rixyawaka tshinanu.
Waneya hix-hohne hiknohinixka judeu-ne hapatjehchini-kanutatka ruylaxyawakapluna Saulo.
Seyni Saulo jempiranyehitna. Judeu-ne hislahpotutlu poktshi hiphaptotkaka hohohne hoyetshno koxa ruylaxyawakapluna Saulo.
Seyni hoyetshno rixini Saulo homkahitatshine satu chiwatu hitokote rutakluna Saulo. Waneya wan-hixatshri hkaplakkakluna Saulo poktshi cerca-te.
Saulo Jerusalém Hiyrunu Tarso Rawyawaka PiranapniWaneya Saulo yanwakatlu Jerusalém. Rujhalu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus halixatshine rimotsaxyawaka. Seyni wanna ptowruneka pikatkalu. Hi ralixluna Saulo halixatshri rixyawakatka.
Hiyáhoni Barnabé hwaplu. Waneya raniklu Saulo nuretkalune yehi. Waneya Barnabé hinkakna nuretkalune Saulo pirana, Jesus hiynumsaxyalu pirana. Hiyrun-koxa Barnabé hinkakna hanu rixa Saulo hinkaklewle Jesus hiwakaya, hi hpika hinkaklewleta, Damasco poktshiya.
Waneya Saulo wannayma rutukatka. Jerusalém poktshi psoluko hyajeta runkaklewjeta Jesus hiwakaya hike hpika.
Hiyrun-koxa ruhjetna judeu-ne, grego-nru yanumaxikatshine. Seyni wanna hijhalu ruylaxyawakapluna Saulo.
Waneya wale pirana rimatyehixinna halixatshine hapatjetatshine ranikluna Saulo haté Cesareia poktshi. Waneya hyokanatluna Saulo Tarso poktshi nwaka hyiywakapa.
Cristo Halixatshine Hapatjetatshine Hixolewnakajikowaka PiranapniHiyáhoni Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine xkehkaka Judeia tshijneya, Galileia tshijneya hiyrun-koxa Samaria tshijne psoluyaka hihlewahchinikanutatka. Htseruwahchinikanutatkana hiyrunu hkahwakpiratluna Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus hiyrunu rixolewnatkana, Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hislahle tshinanu.
Enéias Hitskalajikowaka PiranapniPtowru poktshikaka hyapamxyawaka Pedro hiyáhoni rapyehitkoxna potukalune Cristo halixatshine Lida poktshi hwatshine.
Wane rexyalu satu jeji Enéias tshinkaluru. Oito mhale pchinika hi ruchpajyalu hijeko klu tshinanu hi rumukata yanreta.
Waneya Pedro wan-tshinatkalu: — Enéias, Jesus Cristo hitskalakyi. Ppalnanu, pihnanutanru pijeko. Waneya waneklu papko potuko hpalnatka.
Hiyáhoni Lida poktshi hajene hiyrunu Sarona poktshi hajene hichinhatlu xye jeji waneya wanna ptowruneka halixatkalu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu.
Dorcas Hiwekkajikowaka PiranapniWaneya Jope poktshiya twa sato suxo Jesus homkahitatshro Tabita tshinkaluro. (Grego-nruya Dorcas ttshinka.) Ptowru hohneruka kihleru tkamhajekanatni hike mwikane tepixjekanatni.
Waneya waneklu papko tyeyixanatka, tupnanatka. Teromanetkana waneya teno hwahrukotatshri tutakkanatka.
Lida poktshi hi howukaylu Jope poktshi. Hiyáhoni Cristo halixatshine jempiranyehixinri Pedro Jope rawyawaka, hepi yine hyokananwakatluna Pedro. Ranjipotutluna Pedro chinpotukawa hyanwakaxyawakapna.
Waneya Pedro yokanatna ptowru yineru waneya hyo-ptsojita ranjihohnetatka. Waneya ruprotakyehitlo Dorcas mane waneya wane htshina: — Tabita, ppalnanu xako! Waneya tumrekhata, tetlu Pedro waneya ttuplatatka.
Romyokanwakatlo waneya hyotunkaklo. Hiyáhoni potukalune Jesus halixatshine hiyrunu hipnahnurutatshrone htomhatka Pedro waneya rekhitna Tabita hiwejyawakatka.
Waneya wale pirana himatka psoluyako Jope poktshiya. Hiyáhoni hixo halixlu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Cristo.
Waneya hix-hohne Jope poktshi rutukatka Pedro. Simão-pji rawakanata. Waleni couro-mta jihlekleru.
Hoyakalu Towreru Hakanhayehitlu Cornélio PiranapniCesareia poktshi rawakanata satu jeji Cornélio hiwakatletatshri. Xye romano soldado-ne pohire italiano tshinkalune.
Cornélio powra hchinikanuru hiyrunu Hoyakalu homkahitatshri rixyawaka. Wale hiyrun-koxa wanna ptowruneka hipji hajene. Cornélio henekachajetna judeu-ne hike mwikane hiyrun-koxa hanjihohneru ranjijexyalu Hoyakalu.
Pa hohne kayi nwaka três hora hetko Cornélio Hoyakalu pixkonuya retpotutlu satu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hichpajikatshri. Waneya hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hichpajikatshri yanwakatlu Cornélio. Waneya Hoyakalu towreru wan-tshinru: — Cornélio.
Cornélio hetpotutlu. Hpikatka. Waneya Cornélio wan-tshinru: — Klunerni, Tsru Hixikatshriwa? Waneya wane htshinru Hoyakalu towreru: — Hoyakalu hoji sreta rapokatka panjihohnere hiyrun-koxa petwamonrekaka. Hoyakalu hichinikyi.
Hiyáhoni xawakni jejine pyokanatanu Jope poktshi hyinripna htomhiywakapluna satu jeji Simão tshinkaluru. Wale yokle hiwaka Pedro.
Pedro Simão-pji rawjeta. Waleni couro-mta jihlekleru. Mar powhastsi hwapjitatshrikni.
Waneya hyinixka hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hichpajikatshri, Cornélio hiynumsatatshri, htomhatkana hepi htowrene hiyrun-koxa htomhalu satu soldado kahchinikanuru.
Waneya Cornélio hinkakna wale pirana psoluka waneya Jope poktshi hyokanatna.
Hoyakalu Powraxyawaklu Ptowru Nikkaluru PiranapniWaneya wale prika hanikaj-hohnestsitkani, Pedro teno hruko ratskota ranjihohnexyawakapa. Wane pchinika runamtna Cornélio yokanatanune hatnu hapo. Jope poktshistsi rapokna.
Hnatshita Pedro. Raluka nikleta. Hnijituwatka pchinikna pimrine Pedro Hoyakalu pixkonu tshinanu retatkalu.
Retlu tenhohne hitpukatshri. Waneya ret-hijrukletlu tsru mkatshri sama pixka hixatshri. Quatro tsojri hostuxikaluru hijrukatshri. Tshijistsi rapoka.
Wane hitokote rawamta ptowru hixatshri niktshine, quatro jixirune, niktshine yosrolotatshine, kamejirune koxa.
Waneya Pedro yijnakotlu satu tokantshi wan-tshinatshri: — Ppalnanu, Pedro. Puylatanru, pnikanru.
Hiyáhoni Pedro wan-tshina: — Hike, Tsru Hixikatshriwa. Hita hikeklu hohne niklu pa hixanu kaptsholu ho tshipetkaluru.
Seyni tokantshi hinatnaka Pedro yehi wan-tshinatshri: — Kluneruktako Hoyakalu powratanru hi kaptsholu ptshinanru.
Map-kata wan-rixatka. Waneya mkatshri sama tenhohne hanikkatka.
Pedro Yoptotna Cornélio Yokanatanune PiranapniPedro hi himatahnaputlu wale nanwaka klukta xawaka reta Hoyakalu pixkonu tshinanu. Waneklukawa Cornélio yokanatanune jejine Simão-pji repomsayehitna waneya Simão-pji hiphaptote rapokna.
Htomhana kapjirune waneya repomhana: — Hi he hewi rawjeta Simão, Pedro yoklethiwakletatshri?
Seyni Pedro hichinikanretakanaxiniwalu Hoyakalu pixkonu tshinanu retleru, Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru wan-tshinru: — Hetanu, mapa jejine hijhayi.
Hiyáhoni palpokoxinwa, pserpikanu. Pimotsatanna. Hi pkojwakahchinikanutanu klu tshinanu Hitako yokanatna.
Hiyáhoni Pedro serpikatka. Waneya wane htshinatkana jejine: — Hitakni hijhanruno. Klu tshinanhe hina?
Waneya wanna wan-tshina: — Soldado-ne pohire Cornélio yokanatwu. Cornélio jeji kihle hchinikanuru, Hoyakalu kahwakpiratatshri, kihle piranyehiru ptowruneko judeu yehiya. Satu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru towutlu Cornélio rawapakjixyawakyi Cornélio-pji pyiywakapa pyijnaktokanuxyawaklu.
Hiyáhoni Pedro tshanixna hjihlojyawakapna. Renekna rumjiywakna. Waneya wale prika hyotunota Pedro. Wannayma wane hyatka. Pimrin-koxa Hoyakalu halixatshine mkoje Jope hajene himotsatlu.
Cornélio-pji Rapojyawaka Pedro PiranapniWaneya wale prika Cesareia poktshi rapokna. Cornélio kahwakakanatna. Rapatjetanunetka himolene hiyrun-koxa rimatletanunepotu.
Waneya Pedro pantshi hjihlokpiraxinixka, Cornélio yoptotaplu. Tshiji rapokamta Cornélio Pedro jixistsi. Hyoptsojita Pedro-stsiya. Hpoyahnutatkalu Pedro.
Waneya riynumsakakakanaxiniwana Cornélio-yma, Pedro pantshi jihlokatka hyoptotna hixolune yine wane hapatjexikatshine.
Waneya Pedro wan-tshinna: — Hixa himatlu hinanchitkalurni judeu hapyehixyawakaplu pa neruko ho rimapatjexyawakapna. Seyni Hoyakalu hekhitatkano hikeni yineru malukkotu, kaptsholu Hoyakalu yhaleya.
Hiyáhoni nepukkatka hi nkojwakahchinikanutatka seyni nunhapkata. Xawakni naluk-himatleta kluneru tshinanhe hixa hepukno?
Waneya Cornélio wan-tshina: — Quatro hohne xye hohneymakananuko nanjihohnekanata nopjiya, kayi nwaka três horas-tkani. Waneya waneklukawa potuko satu jeji yopkakhinapletno katajiru hitakatshri.
Waneya wane htshina: “Cornélio, Hoyakalu yijnakotatkalu panjihohnere hiyrun-koxa penekachalkaka hike mwikatu tshinanu ruchinikyi Hoyakalu.
Hiyáhoni pyokanatanru satkaka yineru Jope poktshi nwaka repujyawakaplu jeji Simão Pedro hiwakatletatshri. Wale Simão couro-mta jihleklerupji rawa, mar powhastsi hwapjitatshri.”
Hiyáhoni waneklukawa nyokanrewata pix-yehi. Kihleyi pixa punyawaka. Xawakni hixa ptowrunekwu hapatjetatshinwu hewi Hoyakalu hetanuya, wkahwakachatlu wyijnakoxyawaklu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hinkaklewjixatkayi.
Waneya Pedro yinuwaka yanumleta wane htshina: — Xawakni nimata Hoyakalu kahwaklu satkaka yineru pixkakaklu rixyawaka.
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu hihlehchinikanutlu ptowru yineru Hoyakalu kahwakpiratatshri hiyrunu Hoyakalu halujyawaka kamhatshri, hanuruneruktako rixini.
Xyekni tokantshi Hoyakalu yokanatanru israel-nerune nwaka, kihler-potuko tokantshi ruhlewahchinikanuxyawaka pirana, Jesus Cristo-ya. Xyekni ptowru potuko Tsru Hixikatshriwa.
Hixa himatlu tokantshi pohitkaluru Judeia tshijne psoluyako hapokatshri Galileia tshijne yinuwajya. João Batista batiza-xyawaklu Jesus waneya hyinuwaka hinkaklewletatka.
Hiyrun-koxa hixa himatlu Jesus Nazaré hajeru pirana. Hoyakalu hipkakhohotlu Jesus Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hiyrunu tsru pixkonu reneklu Jesus. Waneya Jesus ptowru sretako hyapakananumta. Kihleru hkamhakananumta Jesus. Rutskalakna ptowruneka tsru kamtshi himwakanatatshine klu tshinanu Jesus-ymalu Hoyakalu.
Hiyrunu hixa hiphujtatatshinwu wale ptowruka Jesus kamhanru, judeu tshijneya hiyrun-koxa Jerusalém poktshiya. Seyni wanna hiylatlu Jesus, cruz rixpatluna.
Seyni Jesus-ni Hoyakalu hiwekkakatnaklu map-hohne rixinri. Hiyrunu Hoyakalu hitshitlu Jesus hix-yehi rakanhiywaka.
Hi ptowru yineru rakanhayehimta Jesus seyni hixa tsonu mnukawa Hoyakalu nurrenwu. Hoyakalu hali hiwekkaklexinixnaklu Jesus waneya wkatanu waleyma wnika wura.
Hyokanatwu yin-yehiya wunkaklexyawakaplu, wuphujtaxyawakaplu Jesus-kni, Hoyakalu hitakanru towutatshri rixyawakapa hiwekatshineya, hipnatshineya koxa.
Ptowruneka Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine hiphujtatlu Jesus pirana, satkaka yineru Jesus hiwaka hmunanhiywakapa ruknojikowakapa rektunna.
Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru Hapokhohotna Judeu Mixkane PiranapniWaneya xye pirana hyanumsaxiniwa Pedro Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hapokhohotna wanna ptowruneka tokantshi yijnakokanatatshine.
Waneya rimyekna Cristo halixatshine judeu-ne, Pedro himotsatatshine klu tshinanu judeu mixkane hoho koxa rapokatka henekachalu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru.
Klu tshinanu judeu-ne yijnakotatkana judeu-ne mixkane hyanumsaxyawakna, rimalwuxyawakluna Hoyakalu hoyaknu tshinanu panrukakaya waneya Pedro wan-tshina:
— Nyi yine yoptotatkalu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hixa pixka. Hiyáhoni kathe xawaka tshipetna nyi yine h-batiza-xikowakna honhaya? Hikeni.
Hiyáhoni Pedro batiza-jixatkana Jesus Cristo hiwakaya. Waneya ranjitluna Pedro pimri hohnetshi wanna yehi rawyawakapa.
Pedro Hinkajyawakna Jerusalém Hapatjexikatshine PiranapniWaneya nuretkalune hiyrun-koxa Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine Judeia tshijne psoluyako yijnakpiranyehitna judeu mixkane koxa yoptotlu Hoyakalu tokanu.
Hiyáhoni Pedro Jerusalém yanwakaxinixka judeu-ne yanhaklu Pedro.
Wane htshinna: — Pixakni jihlokyehitna mjiprojhaptojimtatkane neru yehi. Wannayma pnika.
Waneya Pedro hinkakna wanna wale pirana psoluka hyinuwakleya haté hmahaxyawaka. Waneya wane htshina:
— Jope poktshi nwakanaxini nanjihohnekanaxini waneyakta Hoyakalu pixkonu tshinanu nexyalu tenhohne hichpajikatshri jijrukaluru quatro tsojri rostuxika. Hit-yehi rapoka.
Waneya nyopukhatlu, netpotutlu. Netlu quatro jixirune tshiji hajene hiyrunu nikalu kmatsyirune hiyrunu yosrolotatshine hiyrun-koxa kamejirune tenhohne yapatshine neta.
Hiyrun-koxa tokantshi njema wane ntshinjeru: “Pedro, ppalnanu, puylatanru waneya pnikanru.”
Waneya rimepeta tokantshi tenhohne hichpajikatshri wan-tshina: “Wale honra Hoyakalu hihlelerutka hi wane ptshinanru malukkotni.”
Waneya map-kata wan-rixatka waneya wale ptowruka tenhohne hya satokletatka.
Waneya waneklukawa potuko pantshi nwakanaxini rapokna mapa jejine. Wanna Cesareia poktshi hyokanaxikatkana hita nwaka.
Waneya Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru towutno nyiywakhapkapatka wannayma hike npikanu. Hiyrunu nyi seis jejine Cristo halixatshine hitaymatka hita hapakatka. Waneya Cornélio-pji wjihlokatka.
Waneya wale hinkakwu hanu rixa hakanhalyehitatkalu satu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru hipjiya hyotunota waneya wane htshina: “Jope poktshi pyokanaxinna jejine Simão htomhiywakapa wale yokle hiwakni Pedro.
Walekni hinkakanyi tokantshi hiwekkaklewatatshri tokanu piwekkakko pixa hiyrun-koxa ptowruneka pipji hajene.”
Waneyakta hajeyrino nyinuwaka yanumletawa, rapokhohotatkana Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru, hixa mitshikananu pixka rixa rapokhohokanaxinwu.
Waneya nuchinikatkalu Tsru Hixikatshriwa tokanu wan-tshinyawaka: “Halikaka João batiz-jekanatna honhaya seyni hixa batiza-tkotka Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluruya.”
Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu henejinna waleko renekachaleko koxa hixa pixka rixa henekletna Wutsrukate Jesus walixiniklunu hiyáhoni hanhe nixa himaletletanru Hoyakalu?
Waneya xyekaka tokantshi hyijnakoxinixkana nuretkalune rutshrokna. Ranjitluna Hoyakalu wane htshinruna: — Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu henekkoxna judeu mixkane riwejyawakna rehchinikanre tshinanna.
Cristo Halixatshine Hapatjetatshine Antioquia Poktshi Hajene PiranapniWaneya Estêvão hiylatkoklunutka Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine hipalatatka salewaktshi tshinanu. Hiyáhoni Fenícia poktshi rapokna, Chipre poktshi, Antioquia poktshi koxa rapokna runkaklewatna hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana seyni judeu-ne tsonuko runkakna.
Seyni satkaka wanna Chipre poktshi hajene hiyrunu Cirene poktshi hajene Antioquia poktshi hapokatshinetka hinkakkoxna judeu mixkane. Runkakletluna kihler-potuko tokantshi Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus pirana.
Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus mixkowkakatkana hiyáhoni hixo yine halixatka, rehchinikanutna. Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu romkahitatkana.
Waneya Jerusalém poktshi hwatshine Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine yijnakpiranyehitna hiyáhoni Barnabé tshinkaluru yokanatka Antioquia poktshi.
Waneya rapojinixka Barnabé retlu Hoyakalu ramoxyawakna hiyáhoni rumuwata. Waneya Barnabé mixkotahchinikanutna psoluka rajiyna Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu romkahixyawakna hiyrunu hi ruchotanruna Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu.
Barnabé honra kihle hchinikanuru, katsepoylu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru, ralixle koxa. Hiyáhoni Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus ralixyawakna tshinanu hixolune yine hapatjetka.
Waneya Barnabé Tarso poktshi yatka Saulo tshinkaluru rujhapyawakapa.
Waneya rukchiklu Saulo waneya ranikatkalu Saulo Antioquia poktshi nwaka. Waneya satu mhale psoluka wane rawna rapatjejetna Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshineyma. Rasrukna hixolune yine. Jesus homkahitatshine yinuwaka hiphujewnahiwakleta halixatshine htshinikowakna Antioquia poktshiya.
Ágabo Hinkakletahnapuxyawaklu Tsru Natshi PiranapniWaneya waneklu papko satkaka Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine Jerusalém hichpajya Antioquia poktshi rapokna.
Satu wannaymalutu Ágabo tshinkaluru yopkaka, waneya Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hepixle tshinanu hyanumata. Wane htshina: — Tsru natshipni psol-tshijne hajeneko tshinanu. Hiyrunu phuru Cláudio-klu papko wane potuko rixatka.
Hiyáhoni Antioquia hajene Cristo halixatshine wan-rixa hichinikanuwletna hyokanaxyawakna repixikolna Judeia hajene Cristo halixatshine. Satkaka yokanatlu hpoyaho yokanrexyawaka pso.
Waneya tiyiro rapatjetna waneya renekluna Paulo, Barnabé hiyáhoni wanna hanikanwakatna tiyiro Judeia hajene Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine kosekatshine.
Herodes Kamnixyawaklu Tiago Hiyrunu Pedro PiranapniWaneklu papko phuru Herodes yinuwaka kachretna satkaka yineru Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine hkamnixyawakna.
Waneya Herodes hiylakjixlu hiylalewapiya, espada tshinkaluru, Tiago, João mole.
Waneya Herodes rexiniklunna wale poyikowkakatkana judeu-ne, Pedro koxa hkachijixatka. Xye wan-hixatka himretkaluru hohne pão myapjetkotu kamhikolu hohne.
Waneya rali kachretatkalu Pedro, Herodes preso rutaklu. Soldado-ne quatro ptohkaka quatro-kaka satkaka ptohkaka hislahakanatlu Pedro. Herodes honra haluka Pedro hkochpakhetanuxyawakna judeu-ne Páscoa hohne wkatanuko.
Waneya Pedro preso hwa ruslahkatka seyni Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine psol-mixkonuko Hoyakalu ranjihohneyehitluna Pedro.
Waneya Herodes haluka kochpaklexinixkalu Pedro rekhixyawakapna, wale yetshno Pedro himkakanata hepi soldado-ne hanikajiteya. Pedro hostutka hepi sretkanoko soldado-neya. Soldado-ne hinotatkalu preso hiphaptote.
Waneya chinpotukawa rakanhayehitlu Pedro satu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hichpajikatshri katalu hatatlu preso hruko. Waneya Pedro-thana rutpeta hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hichpajikatshri. Hkomyeklu. Waneya wane htshina: — Wuya chinpotu pyotunotanu. Waneya yomuwatsa hijrukatka himyo hwatsakanatatshri.
Pedro Preso Hichpajyawaka PiranapniWaneya preso yehi ruchpakamxya Pedro. Romkahimtlu Hoyakalu towreru. Seyni Pedro hi himatatka ho halikakla hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hichpajikatshri kochpaklu ho rupnawlechala. Hoyakalu pixkonu hetkaluru rikahwaklu.
Waneya riknohamtluna mitshikananu soldado-ne xkehi yehi hiyrun-koxa wale hapkatatatshri soldado-ne xkehi yehi riknohna. Waneya rapokna hiphapto yomuwa kamhikaluru poktshi jihlojikowaka yehi. Seyni hiphapto hitpukamta wale nanwaka wanna tshinanu. Waneya ruchpakamtna satu hapo hyapamtna waneya chinpotukawa hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hichpajikatshri hichomtlu Pedro waneya.
Waneya Pedro hichinikanuwpotutatka. Waneya wane htshina: — Xawakni nimatlu halikakni. Halikakni Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu yokanatlu htowreru hiwejikaluru tenhohne hichpajikatshri hkochpajyawakapno Herodes-myoya hiyrun-koxa wale ptowruka judeu-nerune haluk-hixlexyawakmakno.
Rimatjeminixka Pedro wan-rixyawakatka hyatka, Maria, João Marcos hinropji nwaka hyatka. Hixo yine wane hapatjekanaxya. Ranjihohnekanatna.
Waneya Pedro hitpetlu hiphapto pantshi yoptowaka sreta. Maria towrero Rode hiwakatletatshro hetaplu katnihe.
Waneya timatjemtokanuxinixkalu Pedro, tumuwpotuthonuka haté hi tkotpuklu hiphapto seyni t-satokhonukatka tasukamxyawaka. Tunkaklewata Pedro hiphapto maleka sreta hwa.
Waneya wane htshinrona: — Pix-hetko hipukalewata! Seyni wala hinkakletlu halikaka pirana rixyawaka. Waneya wanna wan-tshina: — Wale hetko Pedro-ni samenrutka.
Seyni Pedro pnuteko hixa hitpereta. Hiyáhoni hiphapto hkotpukna retluna Pedro-katkani. Rimyekna.
Waneya Pedro hekhitna himyoyma potshke rixyawakna waneya runkakna hanu rixa kochpakletlu preso yehiya Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu. Waneya wane htshina: — Xye pirana Tiago hinkakanu hiyrun-koxa wimolene Cristo halixatshine. Waneya wane ruchpajyatka pnuko hyatka.
Waneya wale prikatkani tsru kaheknanuwlu rixna soldado-ne klukta rixanatka Pedro-ni.
Ptowru sretaka rujhiylu Herodes seyni hi rukchikatkalu. Hiyáhoni repomsatna soldado-ne Pedro hinotatshine waneya ruylajixatkana soldado-ne. Waneya Herodes Judeia tshijne hichpajyatka Cesareia poktshi rapokatka. Wane rawatka pchini hohnejiji.
Herodes Hipninri PiranapniPhuru Herodes hahkajetna hepi poktshi hajene, Tiro poktshi hiyrunu Sidom poktshi hajene. Seyni wanna hepi poktshikak-hajene ptowruneka yanwakatlu Herodes. Mitshikananhapka rukchiklu Blasto hepixlewle, walekni Herodes towreru. Wane pnute Herodes nwaka hyanna hiyáhoni ranjitluna hmahnanuwaxyawakanupa klu tshinanu hyoptotluna nikkaluru htshijneyna Herodes tshijne hichpajikatshri.
Waneya h-marca-xikolu hohne Herodes makatlu phuru mkalu kihleru. Phuruko htuplawakle htuplata Herodes waneya runkaklewyehitna.
Waneya hsaplewatna yine: — Tukwala hoyakalu plama potuko hi yineru plamatkani.
Hiyáhoni waneklu papko potuko hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru himtukatkalu Herodes-ni klu tshinanu hi hpoyahnutakjixlewatni Hoyakalu potu. Waneya homawlu nikanru waneya rupnanatka.
Seyni Hoyakalu tokanu tseruwnatka hiyrunu rixolewnatka rupalatatka.
Waneya hnikaxinixkaluna hkamrurna Barnabé hiyrunu Saulo Jerusalém poktshi hsatokna, ranikluna João Marcos tshinkaluru.
Barnabé Hiyrunu Saulo Yinuwaka Kihler-pirana Runkaklexyawakna PiranapniCristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine Antioquia poktshiya rawakanatna satkaka Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri hiyrun-koxa satkaka hasruklewatatshri. Waneru Barnabé, Simeão, Níger hiwakatletatshri; Lúcio, Cirene hichpajikatshri; Manaém, Herodes-yma kammanetkalurni hiyrunu Saulo.
Waneya pa kata Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu rimalwujekanaxinna hiyrunu rohajirewakanaxinna, Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru wan-tshina: — Xawakni Barnabé hiyrunu Saulo hkotspalaxinno kamrurtshi tshinanu. Nnuretna satu kamrurtshi tshinanu.
Hiyáhoni rohajirewatna. Ranjihohnetna. Waneya Barnabé hiyrunu Saulo hoho rutakamyotna waneya hyokanatatkana hyiywakapna.
Kahontshi Elimas PiranapniHiyáhoni Barnabé hiyrunu Saulo Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru yokanre tshinanu, Selêucia nwaka hyana. Waneya waneko hpokowniyna hyahap-hatna. Chipre rapokna. [Wale mar powha hanikajite hwatshijitatshri.]
Waneya Salamina poktshi rapojinixkana hyinuwaka hinkakletletlu Hoyakalu tokanu judeu hanjihohnewaklepjikakaya. João Marcos hapaka repixyawakapna.
Waneya hkoprutna psoluka mar powha hanikajite hwatshijitatshri haté Pafos poktshi rapokna. Wane rexyaluna satu kahontshi judeu-neru halikaka tokantshi minje hinkakletatshri. Wale hiwakni Barjesus.
Tshiji towutatshri Sérgio Paulo tshinkaluru repireta. Jimatkaleru potu Sérgio Paulo tshinkaluru. Waneya Sérgio Paulo tomhakjixna Barnabé, Saulo klu tshinanu Hoyakalu tokanu raluka jemleta.
Seyni kahontshi Elimas tshinkaluru kamnitna. (Elimas, walekni Barjesus hiwakni grego-nruya.) Raluk-himaletletlu tshiji towutatshri Jesus hma malixyawakanupa.
Waneya Saulo, walekni Paulo tshinkaluru, katsepoylu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hyopukhapotutlu Elimas.
Paulo wan-tshinru: — Pixa Satanás whenyi! Pkamnitlu ptowru halikakalutu. Katsepoyyi yokwijrewlu hiyrunu weyawlu. Hi he putukanu Hoyakalu tokanu halikakalutu pkoprotajyawaka weyawlu pikahwajyawaklu?
Xawakni Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu yotnekanyi mayhaletu pixyawakapa. Pimri hohnekaka hike pa hixanu petanutka, hi koxa katalu tkatshi hichpajyawaka petanutka. Waneklu potuko ptowruka ruwnayhalexyatka Elimas tshinkaluru. Hyanachata, rujhamkalu satu yineru kanojixyawaklu himyoya.
Waneya xye rexinixka tshiji towutatshri, ralixatka. Rimyejyatkalu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Cristo hasruklewleya.
Seyni wanna Perge hyahap-haxyana haté Antioquia poktshi, Pisídia tshijne sreta rapokna. Waneya hapnanuxikalur-hohne rixini hyanwakatluna judeu hanjihohnewaklepji. Waneya wane htuplatna.
Rali hethaletkoklunutka Moisés yonre hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine yonawahle waneya hanjihohnewakapji chefe-tene hinkaklewjixna Paulo-ne: — Wimolene, waneyhi satu tokantshi hiykolu pirana yine tshinanupa? Rawini hinkaklewatanu.
Paulo Hinkaklewata Antioquia Poktshiya PiranapniWaneya Paulo yotunota, rekhitna himyoya potshke rixyawakapna. Waneya wane htshina: — Jejine, israel-nerune hiyrun-koxa hixa ptowruneka Hoyakalu kahwakpiratatshine, hyijnakotanu.
Israel Hoyakalute nuretna wutsrukatenni. Tsru potu rixkajyawakna yine Egito tshijne rawakanaxinna. Waleko kochpakatkana Egito-ya tsru hpixkonuyma.
Waneya quarenta mhale pchinika retachatna rixjexyawakna popriwakaya.
Hoyakalu nikatna sete nerunkaka Canaã tshijneya hiyáhoni Hoyakalu rayinetene henektshijita.
Quatrocentos e cinquenta mhale pchinika wan-rixna. Wane pnute Hoyakalu henekna jemahchinikanyehirewatatshine haté Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri Samuel-klu papko.
Waneya hixolune yine hanjitlu satu phuru htowuxyawakna. Hoyakalu henekna Saulo, Quis whene, Benjamim-neru. Quarenta mhale pchinika phuru rixatka Saulo.
Waneya rali kochpakletkatka Saulo, Hoyakalu henekna Davi hpohirna rixyawakapa. Hoyakalu wan-tshinanwakatlu Davi: “Netlu Davi, Jessé whene, wale poyikowkakno hiyrunu ptowruka nalujyawaka hkamhanu.”
Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu hanikyehitna Israel satu Davi klopichane wanna hiwekkakatshri rixyawakapa, hanu rixa kojiretletna mnukawa, walekni Jesus.
Hma mapokkanuklunuwa Jesus, João hinkaklewyehitna Israel whenene. Runkakna satu batismo hehchinikanru pirana, ptowru israel-nerune tshinanupa.
Waneya ralipiraxinixkalu hkamrure João wan-tshina: “Kathe pkahwakno? Hita hi waleno hkahwaklerno! Seyni hita pnute, waleko hinanu. Hita hi tsru hixikatshriwano h-sandalha-tetslu nkochpirojyawaka.”
— Jejine, nomolene, Abraão klopichane whenene hiyrun-koxa katukta kahwakpiratlu Hoyakalu hixa tskalaya hyijnakotanno: Hixa tshinanu hyokanatka xye Hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana.
Jerusalém hajene haté htsrukakalutene koxa hi rimathetluna Jesus yine Hiwekkakatshri rixyawaka. Yáholu ptowru h hohne rethata hi rimatjemluna Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri tokanu. Seyni wanepnawaka mitshikawako yokanatkaluru hakanhatka Jesus jihyehixikolu hohne.
Hike rukchijyaluna ruylaxikolupa seyni wanepnawaka Pilatos ranjitna ruylaxikowakapa.
Waneya rali kamhalexinixkaluna ptowruka Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru tshinyawaka pixka mnukawa, cruz hoho hkochtshejyanatkaluna waneya yomletshi rutakanatkaluna.
Seyni Hoyakalu yotunkaklu hipuktshiya.
Wane wkatanu hix-hohne retkatnaka rimotsaneyma Galileia Jerusalém yapatshine. Wannakni Jesus hiphujtatatshine ptowru yineru tshinanu.
Hiyáhoni hewiwu wunkakhi kihler-potuko tokantshi hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana Hoyakalu mitshi hinkaklexyana wutsrukatenni.
wale renekatkawu hixa, wutsrukatenni whenenwu Hoyakalu hiwekkajinixkalu Jesus. Wane potuko htshina yonawahleta Hoyakalu pirana yonatkaluru hepi rixinri Salmo: “Pixni Noturyi. Xawakni nwuhenetyi.”
Hiyrunu Hoyakalu wan-tshinanwakatlu Jesus hiwejinixnaka pirana, hikeklu hohne hipuktshi nikatanru. Hiyáhoni mnukawa wane htshinatka Hoyakalu: “Nenekanhi hihle hchinikanrewlukaka potukalni ntshina hinkaklexyatkalu Davi.”
Wane koxa htshina satuko Salmo-mtaya: “Hi pucho hijpahlechatanru Pixanu Potukalu.”
Waneya Paulo pnute hya hinkakleta: — Davi kamhalu Hoyakalu halujyawaka riwejinri pchinika. Waneya rupnatka, rutsrukatenni yehi hkapnaxika waneya himane hijpahatka yomletshiya.
Seyni Hoyakalu yotunokajinri, wale hi hijpaha yomletshiya.
Hiyáhoni jejine, nomolene, hixa ptowrunekhi himatanu xako, Jesus tshinanu runkakletka hektuntshi hiknojikolu pirana.
Moisés yonreru pirana hi powratlewata seyni Jesus tshinanu ptowru Cristo halixatshripa powratko ptowru potuyako.
Xakoka! Hislahinwa hma makanhayehixyawakanuphi Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine hinkajyatkawu mitshi:
“Hjemanu, jeyikaklerune! Hixa himyekachatanu wane pnute hipnanuna, klu tshinanu satu kamrurtshi nkamhanu hixa hiwekka pchinika seyni hixa hi halixanru yáholu hinkakka.”
Judeu-ne Heyijyawakna Paulo, Barnabé PiranapniWaneya hanjihohnewakapji ruyakamxyana Paulo, Barnabé, ranjitkana hapnanuxikalur-hohne hinatshripa wale pirana runkajyawakapna hiyrunukotnaka.
Paulo Barnabé Hiknokamxyawakna Judeu-nerune PiranapniWaneya rapojinixka hapnanuxikalur-hohne, psokaklu tsru poktshi hajene ptowruneka hapatjeta hyijnakoxyawakapluna Hoyakalu tokanu.
Seyni retkoklunutkana judeu-ne hixolune yine hapatjetatka wanna hahxapotutna Paulo-ne. Waneya judeu-ne heyiklu Paulo-ne raluk-hiknokletluna Paulo hinkakle.
Seyni Paulo, Barnabé htsernu hchinikanuyma runkaklewatna wane htshinna: — Raluk-hinkaklehapkatna hixa judeu-nhi Hoyakalu tokanu. Seyni hixa malujyawakanru tshinanu hiyrunu hiwejinri hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa hixa malujyawakanru tshinanu hixa wuknokanu xawakni judeu mixkane wunkakanu.
Klu tshinanu xyekni htowutwu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu mnukawa: “Hixa nutaka katalu hixyawakapa judeu mixkane tshinanu hiyrun-koxa hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana hanikajyawakapna psol-tshijne hajeneka haté hmahaxyawaka tshiji.”
Waneya judeu mixkane xye hjeminiklunna hpoyikowatna hiyrunu rimalwutluna Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu tokanu. Hiyáhoni ralixna ptowruneka nuretkalunetka hkayaxyawakapna hiwejinri mnikawnakatupa.
Waneya Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu tokanu hipalaxyalu wale tshijne psoluyaka.
Seyni judeu-ne yokchatna suxone tsrokakalone Hoyakalu himalwutatshrone hiyrun-koxa tsru hitakkalune tsru poktshi hajene. Hiyáhoni wanna yinuwaklu salewaktshi Paulo, Barnabé tshinanu haté hkochpakna wale tshijneya.
Seyni Paulo, Barnabé sandalha pahi ruploka rimaxikowakapa ruknokatkana waneya Icônio poktshi nwaka hyatkana. [Judeu-ne hasruha wan-hixleta.]
Seyni Cristo halixatshine poyikpotukna katsepoyna Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru.
Icônio Rawakanaxyawakna Paulo, Barnabé PiranapniWaneya Icônio poktshiya waneko pixka potuko rixatkana Paulo, Barnabé. Hjihlokluna hanjihohnewakapji. Waneya wan-rixa hinkaklewletna haté hixo yine judeu-nerune hiyrun-koxa grego-nerune halixatka.
Seyni judeu-nerune malixkanetka komyekahchinikanutna judeu mixkane hyokchatna Paulo, Barnabé hma malixyawakanupna.
Seyni wanepnawaka Paulo, Barnabé hix-hohne Icônio poktshi rawna. Runkakletluna Jesus Cristo pirana hike pikanu. Hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu hekhitlu halikaka pirana rixyawaka Hoyakalu chinikannu pirana klu tshinanu renekpixkonutna hetkalurkaka hiyrunu himyekaklewatatshri hkamhiywakna.
