Tiro Poktshi Rapojyawaka Paulo PiranapniWunhamxinixkana wane wuchpajya mar powha hanikajite hwatshijitatshri Cós hiwakatletatshri wyahapkata. Wale prika Rodes yopjewakle wutspaka waneya pnute wyatka haté Pátara poktshi wapoka.
Wane wukchijyalo sato tsro kanawa Fenícia poktshi yamtatshro hiyáhoni wpokownatka pnute wyahap-hata.
Waneya wali hichinhalexinixkalu Chipre tshijne wpastate sreta wiknohamxyalu waneya Síria nwaka wyamtatka. Tiro poktshi wutspakyehita klu tshinanu wane tkowunuxiko kanawa.
Wale poktshi wukchijyana satkaka Hoyakalu homkahitatshine hiyáhoni pa semana wannayma wutukatka. Waneya wanna hiykotmaklu Paulo Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluruya Jerusalém hma yiywakanupa.
Seyni rapojinixka wyinri hohne, wyatka. Waneya Hoyakalu homkahitatshine, hhanunronna koxa hiwhenennaymakananuko himotsatwu tsru poktshi malekate. Ksatu wnahlu wyoptsojixya hixa ptowrunekwu, wanjihohnetatka.
Waneya wunhamxinixkana tsro kanawa wpokownatka. Hoyakalu homkahitatshine hsatokanwakatluna rawyawakna.
Cesareia Poktshi Rawyawaka Paulo PiranapniPnute wyatka. Tiro poktshi wuchpajyatka Ptolemaida poktshi wapokatka. Wane wyoptoxyana pimrine Hoyakalu homkahitatshine, wannayma wutukatka pa hohne.
Waneya wale prika wyatnaka Cesareia poktshi wapokatka. Waneya Filipe Hoyakalu pirana jinkakletaklerupji wjihloka wane wutukatka. Filipe satu Jerusalém Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine hepixatshrini pimrine jejineyma sete-tkana.
Quatro whenru Filipe maklojine hinamtatshri pirana hinkakletatshine.
Hix-hohne wane wwa waneya satu hinamtatshri pirana hinkakletatshri Ágabo tshinkaluru hapoka, Judeia tshijne ruchpajya.
Waneya xye pirana wyijnakoxinixka, hixa hiyrunu wane hajen-koxa, hanjitlu Paulo Jerusalém hma yiywakanupa.
Seyni Paulo hihitna: — Kluneru tshinanhe htshiyahata, klu tshinanhe hwamonuwkakno? Hita halpokoxnawa nostuxikolupa seyni hi wale tsonu, nalpokoxnawa nupninripa Jesus Cristo hiwaka tshinanu.
Hiyáhoni hi wumukata tshipetletlu wale tshinanu wutuk-kojiretletlu waneya wane wtshinru: — Hoyakalu halujyawaka rixkotka.
Wale hohnekaka hiknohinixka wuprukatka Jerusalém nwaka wyamta.
Satkaka Hoyakalu homkahitatshine Cesareia hajene himotsamtwu. Ranikwuna Menasom-pji, wale Chipre hajeru, walepji wutukanutka. Mitshikawako ralixatkalu Hoyakalu pirana.
Jerusalém Rapojyawaka Paulo PiranapniWaneya Jerusalém wapojinixka Hoyakalu homkahitatshine hyoptotwuna. Hpoyikowpotutna.
Wale prika Paulo hixayma hapaka Tiago wetapyawakapa. Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine kosekatshine ptowruneka wane hapatjexya.
Waneya Paulo halikna wanna waneya runkakatkana psol-piranako Hoyakalu hixkajyawakna judeu mixkane waleko hkamrure tshinanu.
Hyijnakoxinixkaluna hpoyahnutluna Hoyakalu waneya wane htshinruna: — Petewa wimole, hi pejnu mil kananu judeu Cristo halixatshinetka hiyrunu wanna ptowruneka Moisés yonreru pirana homkahpotutatshinetkani.
Wanna jempiranyehityi pasrukjexyawakna judeu-ne pa yine tskala hwatshine Moisés hiykole yonatkaluru pirana ruchoxyawakna haté pasrukjexyawakhimna hma jiprojhaptojimtawhenexyawakna hiyrunu hma kahwakpiraxyawakanruna judeu-ne hixjexyawaka.
Hiýahoni kluhe wixanu? Wanna himatanu punyawaka.
Hiyáhoni wane pixanu wtshinyawakyi. Hewina quatro jejine Hoyakalu runkaklexyaluna rixannuna. Xawakni rujhaluna wane potuko htshinyawakna rixyawakna.
Panikanna waneya wannayma powratlewlu pirana pixinwa. Wanna tshinanu pwenutanru jiwjirewatatshri ptowruneka pekhixyawakapa hi halikakni htshinanwakaxyawakyina hiyrunu pekhixyawakapna pix-koxa homkahitlu Moisés yonreru pirana piwekleya.
Ha judeu mixkane Cristo halixatshine tshinanu wali yokanrenwakatna yonawahlo wan-tshinatshri: Hi hnikanru mayawletshicha henekkaluru nikalhitu, hi hihrahako, hi koxa hostuplatkalurniko hnikanu. Hiyrun-koxa hi hapoklewatanu.
Hiyáhoni Paulo hiynumatna quatro jejine waneya wale prika wannayma powratlewlu pirana hpohixnawana. Waneya wane pnute Hoyakalupji hjihlokna runkaklexyawakapluna klu hohne hnikatanruna powratlewlu hohnekaka. Wale hohne rixinipa satkaka wanna hanikanru henekachalu hiylatkalurupa.
Hkachixikowaka Paulo PiranapniWaneya wale sete hohne nikawnapiraxini satkaka judeu-ne Ásia tshijne hichpajikatshine malixkane hetlu Paulo Hoyakalupji rawakanata. Waneya wanna jihekna hixolune yine Paulo tshinanu hiyáhoni hkachitluna Paulo.
Hsaplewatna wane htshin-sapletna: — Jejine, israel-nerune hepixanwu! Xyekni jeji ptowru poktshikaka yapatshri runkajyawakapna yine Moisés yonreru pirana wuchoxyawakapa, wimolene koxa wuchoxyawakapa haté xye Hoyakalupji wuchoxyawakapa htshina. Hiyrunu xawakni satkaka judeu mixkane ranika Hoyakalupji nwaka hiyáhoni rumtukachtaplu Hoyakalupji walenukotkani hikenutkani hiyrunu.
Wane htshinatkana wanna klu tshinanu retluna Trófimo tshinkaluru Éfeso hajeru tsru poktshiya Paulo-ymalu. Wannamka kahwaklu Paulo hanikatkalu Trófimo tshinkaluru Hoyakalupji. Seyni hike.
Waneya ptowru poktshi hajene jihekanuwatatka. Rasukamtna, hkachitluna Paulo waneya hkosemtluna Hoyakalupji malekate ranikluna. Waneya chinpotukawa ruchyatluna Hoyakalupji hiphaptotkaka.
Waneya hixolune hiylapiraxinixkalu Paulo, romano soldado-ne pohire Jerusalém poktshi hajeru jempiranyehitlu tsru sejirtshi hakanhatka Jerusalém poktshiya.
Waneya waneklu potuko wale pohire, soldado-ne chefe-tekaka hiyrun-koxa soldado-ne hmaklutene ranika waneya rasukanwakatna hixolune yine nwaka. Waneya hixolune hexinixkana soldado-ne rutuk-hiylakletluna Paulo.
Waneya soldado-ne pohire yanwakatlu Paulo. Hkachitlu waneya rostukjixlu hepi corrente-tsaya. Waneya repomhayehitlu Paulo hiyrunu repomhalu kluhe hkamha wale.
Pimrinkaka hixolune saplewata, satkaka pnuk-tshin-sapleta. Tsru saple tshinanu soldado-ne pohire hi himatyehitlu klukta hikoluklu. Wale tshinanu soldado-ne pohire towutna soldado-ne ranijyawakapluna Paulo soldado-nepji nwaka.
Hatskowakastsi rapojinixkana soldado-ne rutjitluna Paulo hixolune jihekle tshinanu.
Klu tshinanu hixolune yine homkahimtlu hsaplewatna wane htshin-sapletna: — Hiylatanru xako! Hiylatanru xako!
Waneya hyochmakpiraxinixkaluna Paulo soldado-nepji Paulo wan-tshinru soldado-ne pohire: — Numukata hiynumletyihe? Waneya soldado-ne pohire hepomhalu: — Pimatluhe grego tokanu?
Hi he Egito hajeryi mitshikawa pkamhalu tsru sejirtshi quatro mil jejine tshiji towutatshine kamnitatshine kosekatshriyi potshkewakaya?
Seyni Paulo hihitlu wane htshina: — Hita judeu-nerno Cilícia tshijne tsru poktshite Tarso tshinikowaka hajerno. Pitshitannotshi hixolune yine niynumatanu.
Waneya soldado-ne pohire hitshitlu Paulo riynumsaxyawakna yine. Hatskowaka hyopkakatka Paulo waneya romyokatka potshke rixyawakna hixolune yine. Potshke rixinixkana hixolune Paulo hiynumsatna judeu tokanuya wane htshinna:
Hjeminixkaluna judeu tokanu riynumaxyana, potshkepotukna. Wane htshina Paulo:
— Hita judeu-no Tarso poktshi Cilícia tshijne hwatshri hajerno seyni halikaka hewi Jerusalém poktshiya ntseruwniya Gamaliel hasrukanruno. Wale hasrukatkano ptowru pirana wutsrukatenni yonreru pirana hiyrunu nomkahpotutlu Hoyakalu hixa pixka ptowrunekhi hewi hwatshinhi.
Hita, Paulo-no, kamnijekanatna Cristo halixatshine ruylaxikowakapna. Nkachitna jejine, suxon-koxa waneya kapna nyochmakna.
Tsru sacerdote hiyrunu judeu-ne tsrukakalutene ptowruneka himukata hiphujtaletlu halikaka pirana ntshinyawaka klu tshinanu wanna yonawahlotekaka nyoptotatka Damasco poktshi hajene judeu-ne yokananwakaxikolu. Wane nixa hapoklexyalu Damasco wane hajene nkachixyawakapa Jerusalém nwaka nanijyawakna hostutkalune rapnokatkonna.
Waneya hanikaj-hohnetkani hatnu hapo nyapamtawa Damasco-stsitkano. Waneklukawa potuko tsru katalu tenhohne hichpajikatshri hatawnayehitno.
Nyawnatka tshiji, nyijnakotlu satu tokantshi wan-tshinatshri: “Saulo, Saulo, haklu tshinannihe pkamnitno?”
Waneya nepomhalu: “Katyihe pixa Tsru Hixikatshriwayi? Ruhitatkano: — “Hita Jesus-no pkamnijetanruno.”
Nimotsatanune koxa hetlu katalu hiyáhoni hpikna seyni hi hjemluna niynumsatjeru tokantshi.
Waneya nepomhalu: “Klu pothe nkamhanu, Tsru Hixikatshriwa?” Waneya Tsru Hixikatshriwa wan-tshinno: “Ppalnanutka Damasco nwaka pyanu. Wane punkajiko nalukleru pkamhinripa.”
— Wale tsru katalu tshinanu hi netanatka, hike potuko. Wale tshinanu nimotsatanune hkanojimtnona waneya Damasco napokatka.
Hiyáhoni wane rawakanata satu jeji Ananias tshinkaluru, Moisés yonreru pirana homkahitatshrini wale. Judeu-ne Damasco hajene ptowruneka kahwakpiratlu Ananias.
Ananias yanwakatno, hitastsi hyopkaka waneya wane htshinno: “Nomole Saulo, petanutnaka.” — Waneklukawa potuko netatnaka waneya netatkalu Ananias.
Waneya wane htshina: “Wutsrukatenni Hoyakalute nuretatkayi pimaxyawakaplu waleko ralujyawaka hiyrunu pexyawakaplu Jesus Potukalu hiwakatletatshri.
Klu tshinanu ptowru yineru puphujtaxinri ptowru petanru pirana pyijnakotanru pirana koxa pjemyawaklu htokanu Jesus namaya.
Ha xawakni, kluhe pkahwakjeta? Ppalnanu, p-batiza-tkotka, pmunanhanru Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu ruknojyawakaplu pektunu.”
— Waneya Jerusalém nsatojinixka, nanjihohnekanatawa Hoyakalupjiya netlu satu hetkaluru Hoyakalu pixkonu tshinanu.
Netlu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hita riynumata: “Pchiretanu. Jerusalém puchpajini klu tshinanu wane hajene hi halixanyi hita pirana punkaklexinipa.”
— Waneya wane ntshinru Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu: “Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu, wanna himatlu hanjihohnewakapjikaka nujhajekanaxyana, kapna nyochmakjekanatna haté nkotshipjekanatna pixa Cristo-yi halixatshine.
Hiyrunu puphujtatjerni Estêvão ruylaxinruna hit-koxa wane hwakanata. Nukchikhihlenutlu wan-rixyawakluna. Hiylalewatatshine mkalu ninota.”
— Waneya wane pnute Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu wan-tshinno: “Pyanutka, howuk-tshijne nyokanatanyi judeu mixkane tskalaya.”
Hi Hkotshipjetluna Paulo Klu Tshinanu Romano-nerni PiranapniHyijnakokanatluna haté wale tokantshi htshinini waneya hsaplewpotutna waneya wane htshinna: — Wan-hixatshri yineru xye tshijne hnikaxika klu tshinanu hi rumukata hiwekleta xye tshijiya.
Hsaplewjetna hkowchomkatna hiyrunu ruknopxepahitluna tshiji pahi. Rahnannuna.
Waneya soldado-ne pohire yokanatna soldado-ne Paulo ranijyawakna soldado-nepji. Waneya hkotshipjexikowaka hyokanatluna klu tshinanu raluk-himatletlu klu tshinanu wan-rixa saplewjeryehitluna.
Seyni rostukanatawaluna soldado-ne, Paulo wan-tshinru satu soldado-ne pohire wanestsi hwatshri: — Pumukathe kotshipjeretluhe satu jeji romano-neru mjihyehitkotu?
Waneya xye hjeminixka soldado-ne pohire, hyatka soldado-ne pohire runkakapa, wane htshinru: — Pimatluhe klu pkamhinri? Xye jeji romano-nerni.
Waneya soldado-ne pohire yanwakatlu Paulo wane htshinru: — Punkakanno, halikaklahe pixa romano-neryi? Waneya ruhitlu: — Hehe!
Waneya soldado-ne pohire wan-tshina: — Tsru tiyiro nwenuta romano-neru nixyawaka. Seyni Paulo wan-tshina: — Hita wane tshijiko nmatuxya.
Waneklukawa potuko hsaletjenemka hitspalamtatka. Hiyáhoni hpikpotuthonuka soldado-ne pohire klu tshinanu rali hosturetatkalu Paulo klu tshinanu romano-nerni wale.
Waneya soldado-ne pohire haluk-himatletlu halikaka klu tshinanni hjihyehitluna judeu-ne. Hiyáhoni wale prika htowutna tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hiyrunu tsrukakalune judeu-ne ptowruneka rapatjexyawakna. Waneya hkochpirokatkalu rostuxikolu waneya wanna hoji sreta ranikatkaluna Paulo.
Seyni tsru sacerdote Ananias towutna Paulo-stsi hwatshine hkotshipinamaxyawakapluna.
Waneya Paulo wan-tshinru Ananias: — Hoyakalu hiylakanyi pixa, yanumachatatshriyi. Wane ptuplata pjemahchinikanyehixyawakno Moisés yonreru tshinyawakyi seyni yonruru hinanchityi puylakjixyawakno.
Paulo-stsi hwatshine wan-tshinru: — Pyanhakluhe tsru sacerdote Hoyakalu nuretanru?
Hiyáhoni Paulo wan-tshina: — Nomolene, hi nimatakanata tsru sacerdote rixyawaka, klu tshinanu hyonatkatka: “Hi hektutu tokantshi ptshinanwakatanru pinerune hitsrukate.”
Seyni Paulo himaxinitka satkaka wanna saduceu-ne rixyawakna seyni pimrine fariseu-ne rixyawakna, tsru htokanuyma riynumatna hjemahchinikanyehitjene waneya wane htshinna: — Jejine, nomolene, hita fariseu-no, fariseu when-koxno. Hewi nyopkaka klu tshinanu nalixlu pa hohnepa hipnatshine hiwekanutnaka.
Wane htshininiklunu Paulo ruhjekakna fariseu-ne saduceu-ne wannakakluko hiyáhoni satkaka wane hajene satu pejnu halixa.
Klu tshinanu saduceu-ne wan-tshina hi hkahwakna rawyawakna hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrene tenhohne hajene, hi koxa rawa hiwejikaluruko hiyrun-koxa hi hima ralixna hipnatshine hiwekanutnaka pa hohnepa. Seyni fariseu-ne hima halixlu wale ptowruka.
Waneya tsru sapletshi rixna wanna. Satkaka kasruklewaklerune hinanchitkaluru pirana hasruklewatatshine, fariseu-ne hajene yopkaka waneya hipokananu wane htshinna: — Hike hektutu wukchijyalu xye jeji. Pa katako satu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru ho satu hiwejikaluru hiynumatlu.
Waneya hixolune jihekanuwpotutatka waneya soldado-ne pohire kahwaklu hixolune jiknahmanexyawakaplu Paulo wale tshinanu htowutna soldado-ne rawapyawakapluna Paulo hiyrunu htowutna ranijyawakapluna soldado-nepji nwaka.
Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu Hakanhayehitlu Paulo PiranapniWaneya wane pnut-yetshno Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hapoka, Paulo-stsi hyopkaka. Wane htshina: — Papohchinikanutanno! Jerusalém hajene yehi punkakletpiranyehixyano hiyáhoni wane potuko pixanutnaka Roma poktshiya.
Satkaka Judeu-ne Nurexnawa Paulo Ruylaxyawakapa PiranapniWale prika satkaka judeu-nerune nurexnawa Paulo ruylaxyawakapa hiyáhoni wla htshinna wanna: Paulo wma muylatkanu pchinika hike wnikanu hike wuranu.
Quarenta pnutna jejine xye kamrurtshi haluka kamhaletatshine.
Waneya tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hiyrunu tsrukakalune judeu-ne yehi hyanwakatna waneya wane htshinna: — Hixa wan-tshinanwakatlu Paulo wma muylatkanuko pchinika hike wnikanu hike wuranu.
Hiyáhoni xawakni hixa hiyrunu hjemahchinikanyehitjene pyokantokanunwakatanru soldado-ne pohire Paulo kochpakko rexikowakapa. Hinkakanru hixa haluk-hepomsalexyawaklu Paulo waneya hmapokkanuklunuwa hixa hiylatanru.
Waneya Paulo palikleru himatyehixinri wane raluk-hixlexyawakluna, hyatka. Soldado-nepji hjihlokamta, runkakatkalu Paulo.
Hiyáhoni Paulo tomhalu satu soldado kosekatshri, wane htshinru: — Panikanru xako xye makluji soldado-ne pohire nwaka klu tshinanu rawya pa pirana runkakletlerupa.
Waneya soldado kosekatshri hanikatkalu makluji, soldado-ne pohire nwaka rapokna, wane htshinna: — Hostutkaluru Paulo tomhano waneya ranjitno xye makluji nanikanwakaxyawakapyi pa pirana hima runkakapanyi.
Soldado-ne pohire kanojimtlu waneya ranikatkalu potshkewaka. Repomhalu makluji: — Klunerhe paluk-hinkakletno?
Waneya makluji hihitatkalu: —Judeu-ne haluk-hanjiretyi yetshikawa pkochpajyawakaplu Paulo jemahchinikanyehixikowaka hatatjewa pnute raluk-himatlexyaluna Paulo pirana.
Seyni hi palixanna! Quarenta pnute jejine yohimahnaputlu Paulo ruylaxyawakapluna. Wanna hinkaklewata Paulo hma muylatkanuko pchinika hike hnikanna hike ruranna. Xawakni ralpokotatkana hkahwakachatluna ptokanu.
Hiyáhoni soldado-ne pohire yokanatatkalu makluji seyni hkojiretatkalu: — Hike punkakanu xye pirana punkajyapiranno.
Waneya soldado pohire tomhana hepi soldado kosekatshine waneya wan-rixa towutletna: — Halpokotanna duzentos soldado-ne Paulo ruslahyawakapna, setenta cavalo yapatshine koxa duzentos yohlolewapi hanikatshine koxa waneya xye yetshno nove hora rixini Cesareia nwaka hyanutka.
Halpokotanru cavalo Paulo yaplerupa kihle rixa hapoklexyawakapa Félix tshinkaluru yehi (waleni Cesareia poktshi towutatshri).
Waneya yonawahlo hyonata wla htshinyawaka:
Cláudio Yonawahlo Yokananwakatlu Félix Piranapni“Hita, Cláudio Lísias-no, yonanwakatyi kchinikanuru governador Félix. Nalikyi.
Judeu-ne kachichatanru xye jeji ruylaxyawakamkapluna. Seyni nimaxinixka romano-neru rixyawaka, hita soldado-neyma hwapatkalu.
Waneya naluk-himatlexini klu tshinanu hjihyehitluna judeu-ne, nanikanwakatna wannani kjemahchinikanyehrewaklerune.
Seyni hi nukchijyalu tsru jikolukanuru hipuktshi kayatatshri ho rostuxikolupa. Hjihyehitluna wannani yonreru piranaya tshinanu.
Waneya nimaxinixkalu judeu-ne hiylapiraxinixkalu Paulo waneklukawa potuko nyokanatatkalu pix-yehi. Nunkakkoxna hjihyehitjene runkajyawakapyina klu potu hjihyehitluna. Seyokatkani.”
Wale prika soldado-ne hichomtna cavalo yapatshine himotsaxyawaklu Paulo waneya soldado-ne satokanwakatlu soldado-nepji.
Waneya cavalo yapamtatshine hanikatkalu Paulo haté Cesareia poktshi rimapluna. Waneya yonawahlo renekatkaluna Félix hiyrun-koxa Félix renekapluna Paulo.
Waneya rali hethalexinixkalu yonawahlo, Félix hepomhalu klu tshijne hajerni wale. Waneya rimaxinixka Cilícia hajeru rixyawaka,
wane htshinru: — Rapojinipna pjihyehitjene njemanyi. Waneya Félix himretjixatkalu Herodes-pji tsrupjiwakaya.
Judeu-nerune Jihyehitlu Paulo PiranapniCinco hohne hiknohinixka Cesareia poktshi nwaka hyatka. Tsru sacerdote Ananias tshinkaluru, pimrine tsrukakalune judeu-neyma hiyrunu satu himat-yanumsatatshri Tértulo tshinkaluruyma wane hya. Félix hjihyehitluna Paulo.
Waneya htomhaka Tértulo hiyáhoni hyinuwaka jihyehletlu Paulo, wane htshina: — Kchinikanuru Félix! Hix-hohne nonerune ruhlewahchinikanutna pixa tshinanu haté hixo pirana hihlepokotka yin-yehiya pixa tsru pimatkale tshinanu.
Ptowru hohneruka hiyrunu ptowru papkoluka wepixka xye ptowruka pixa tshinanu wepixka hiyáhoni wale tshinanu wpoyahnutjetyi.
Nma mimalexyawakanyi nanjityi pchini tsonujiji pyijnakoxyawakwu pchinikannu tshinanu.
Klu tshinanu wukchiklu xye jeji kojwaklewjetatshri rixyawaka, ptowru tshijne hajene judeu-ne hjihekkakjeta. Waleni nazaré-ne mkoje kosekatshri.
Hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalupji rumtukachtapa. Wale tshinanu wkachitlu. Waluka hikolukletmaklu hixa judeu-nwu hixikowakamka rixko.
Seyni soldado-ne pohire Lísias tshinkaluru hapyehitwu waneya psol-mixkonuyma wimyo hkonyawu Paulo.
Waneya Lísias yokanatna hjihyehitjene pix-yehi hyiywakapna hjihyehixyawakapluna. Pix-potuko hepomsaxinri waneya wale namako pimaxinri ptowru pirana wjihyehixyawaklu.
Waneya judeu-ne pa jihyehitkolu rixluna Paulo hiyrunu wane htshinna wanna, halikakni xye ptowruka.
Paulo Hihitna Hjihyehitjene PiranapniWaneya Félix-mka hanjitlu Paulo hyanumaxyawakapa. Waneya Paulo wan-tshina: — Nimata hixo mhale pchinika judeu-nerune jemahchinikanyehilewatatshri pixatka. Wale tshinanu npoyikowata pixa hoji sreta numukata hinkakletlexinwa.
Klu tshinanu pixa himukata himatletlu doze hohne tsonu hiknohatka Jerusalém nyiywakatka Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu nimalwuxyawakapa.
Seyni judeu-ne hi hikchijyano satu yineruyma nuhjekajyawaka Hoyakalupjiya hi koxa rukchijyanona pimrine njihejyawakna hanjihohnewakapjikakaya hi koxa tsru poktshi hajeneko nyotnekanata.
Hi koxa rumukata hekhiretnona halikakni rixyawaka hjihyehixyanona.
Seyni halikaka xye nuphujtaxnawa pix-yehiya. Hita himalwutlu Wutsrukatenni Hoyakalute, Jesus hatnu hapote homkahitatshri nixjexyawaka tshinanu. Judeu-ne wan-tshina, hi hima halikakni Jesus hatnu hapote. Seyni hita halixlu wale ptowruka Moisés yonreru pirana hiyrunu Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine yonre koxa nalixa.
Judeu-ne pixka nixahchinikanuta, Hoyakalu nkahwajyalu hipnatshine riwekkajyawakna Cristo halixatshine haté malixkane koxamka hiwekanu.
Wale tshinanu psol-hohneruka kihleru nyahot-kamhaleta Hoyakalu hetanuya, yine hetanuya koxa.
Hiyáhoni xawakni hixo mhale hiknohatka waneya nsatokanwakatlu Jerusalém tiyiro nenejyawakapna nonerune hiyrunu henekachal-koxa nanijyawakapa.
Xye nkamhakanatawa waneya satkaka judeu-ne Ásia tshijne hichpajikatshine hikchikno npowraxnawakwa Hoyakalupjiya. Seyni hi hixoluneymano hi koxa nkojwakakanatna yine.
Wannamka hewi pix-yehi rapokamkana rumukata jihyehletanmaknona satu pa hixanu nkamhakmaka halikaka.
Ho haté nyi judeu-ne pepomhanu ho satu tsru jikolukanuru rukchijyanona judeu-ne njemahchinikanyehixikowakapa yehi nyopkakanu.
Seyni halikaka wanna hanikajite nyopkajiniklunu satu tokantshi tsonu ntshin-sapletatka: “Hixa jihyehitno xawakni klu tshinanu nalixlu pa hohnepa hipnatshine hiwekanutnaka.”
Paulo, Félix Hiyrunu Drusila Hoji Sreta Rapojikowaka PiranapniWaneya xye pirana hyijnakoxinixka Félix hkahwakjixna klu tshinanu rali himatjemletatkalu Jesus hatnu hapote pirana. Hiyáhoni wane htshina: — Soldado-ne pohire Lísias hapojinipa tsonu hjemahchinikanyehitanyi.
Waneya Félix satu soldado-ne pohire towuta Paulo rinoxyawaka seyni hi rostujixpotutatkalu haté rimatletlene himukata hanikanwakletlu hmahaxinri.
Pa hohnetnakni runa Félix hhanunroyma Drusila, judeu-nero. Paulo htomhatka waneya hyijnakyehitatkalu Cristo Jesus halixikolu pirana.
Paulo Félix riynumsakanatawa runkakna yineru hiwejinri potukaxikolu pirana, yineru mmunanhinynawakanupwa pirana hiyrunu hapnokaxikolu hinatshripa pirana. Waneya Félix pikatka. Waneya wane htshinru: — Pyanutka xawakni, numukaxinipa pa hohne nepukanyi.
Waneya hepi mhale hiknohinixka Pórcio Festo tshinkaluru Félix kachrijru hjihlokatka, Cesareia poktshi htowuxyawakatka. Seyni Félix himretawalu Paulo preso-ya klu tshinanu raluka poyikowkakletna judeu-nerune.
Paulo Hanjitlu César Rexyawakapa PiranapniHiyáhoni wale tshijne rapokatka Festo tshinkaluru. Waneya map-hohne hiknohinixka Cesareia poktshi ruchpajyatka Jerusalém nwaka hyatka.
Waneya tsrukakalune sacerdote-ne hiyrunu judeu-ne chefe-tene hinkakletlu Paulo pirana. Hjihyehitluna Paulo.
Ranjitluna Festo hyokanaxyawakaplu Paulo Jerusalém nwaka, klu tshinanu wanna hichinikanretlu Paulo ruylaxyawakluna hatnuya.
Seyni Festo hihitna wane htshinna: — Cesareia poktshi rutukawa Paulo hiyrunu xekoyaka wane nsatkapanu Cesareia nwaka.
Waneya wane htshinna Festo: — Hitshitanna satkaka hixa chefe-tene himotsaxyawakapno wjihyehixyawakaplu Paulo Cesareia poktshiya. Wetanu ho rawyahe jikolukanuru ho hike.
Waneya ho oito ho dez hohne Jerusalém poktshi rutukatka Festo waneya Cesareia nwaka hyatnaka. Wale prika rawapakjixlu Paulo, jemahchinikanyehixikowaka yehi htuplakanata Festo.
Waneya rapojinixka Paulo, judeu-ne Jerusalém hichpajikatshine Paulo hsajrukna waneya hyopkakna hweyawyehitluna seyni hike himukata hekhiretlu halikakni htshinyehixyawakluna.
Waneya Paulo wan-tshin-hihretna: — Hike nmajnakowaxyalu Moisés yonreru, hi koxa Hoyakalupjiko hi koxa ptowru yine towutatshri César yehiya.
Waneya judeu-ne hpoyikowkajyawakapa tshinanu Festo hepomhalu Paulo: — Pixlahe haluka Jerusalém nwaka pyiywakapa njemahchinikanyehixyawakapyi xyekaka tshinanu?
Waneya Paulo wan-tshina: — Romano-ne hoji sreta nyopkaka hjemahchinikanyehixyawakapnona klu tshinanu numukata hijhahchinikanyehletka hewiya. Klu tshinanu hike hektutu nkamhiyna judeu-ne, haté pixa himata halikaka ntshina.
Pa hixanu nmajnakowaxikmaklu hinanchitkaluruya hipuktshi hijhatshri haté hi nanjitlu niwejyawakapa seyni hweyaxiniklunnona hike himukata wannamyo henekletno. Hiyáhoni naluklu César tshinkaluru rujhahchinikanyehixyawakapno ho napnokatjewhe ho hike.
Waneya Festo hiynumsatna ruykotjene waneya wane htshinru Paulo: — Panjitlu César pexyawakapa wale tshinanu César yehi potuko pyanu!
Festo Hinkajyawaklu Agripa Tshinkaluru Paulo PiranaPa hohnetnakni phuru Agripa tshinkaluru hiyrunu hhanunro Berenice tshinkaluro Cesareia poktshi hapoka rapyehixyawakaplu Festo.
Pimri hohnekaka wan-rutukatkana waneya Festo hinkaklu phuru Paulo pirana, wane htshina: — Hewi rawa satu jeji Félix hiknokamtanru hostutkaluru.
Jerusalém poktshi napkapinixka tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hiyrunu judeu-ne tsrukakalutene hinkakno Paulo pirana. Hjihyehitluna Paulo. Ranjitnona ruylaxikolupa.
Seyni nuhitna: Romano-ne hi hasruhlu preso rutakhapkaxyawakaplu satu yineru kjihyehrewaklerune jihyehre hma muhitkonuklunuwa.
Waneya nyi judeu-ne hapojinixka Cesareia poktshi hi nkahwakachata seyni wale prikako yine jemahchinikanyehixikowaka yehi ntuplatatka waneya ntomhakjixatkalu xye jeji.
Waneya rapojinixkana hkamnitjene hyopkakna waneya hjihyehitluna Paulo seyni hikeni tsru jikolukanuru pirana rukchijyaluna Paulo, hi nixahchinikanuxyawaka pixka rixa pupjereta.
Seyni satu hjihyehixikolu tsonu ranikanwakatluna Paulo wannako royakalutna pirana tshinanu hiyrunu satu hipnatshri Jesus pirana hkochtshekna seyni Paulo hiphujtatlu Jesus riwejyawaka pirana.
Seyni hi nukchikahchinikanuta hanu nixa himatletanru xye pixkalutu pirana hiyáhoni Paulo nepomhatka: Hi he Jerusalém nwaka paluka yaleta pjemahchinikanyehitko xye pjihyehixikolkaka tshinanu?
Seyni ranjitlu César rujhahchinikanyehixyawakaplu hiyáhoni nimretjixatkalu haté César yehi nyokanaxiniplu hohne.
Waneya phuru Agripa wan-tshinatkalu Festo: — Hitamka koxa haluka jemletlu xye jeji. Waneya Festo wan-tshinru: — Haté hehe, yetshikawa pjemanru.
Festo Hinkakatnaklu Agripa PiranapniHiyáhoni wale prika Agripa hiyrunu Berenice tsru hpohirewleyma rimapokanna. Jemahchinikanyehixikowakapji hjihlokna soldado-ne chefe-teneyma hiyrunu tsrukakalune poktshi towutatshineyma. Waneya Festo tomhakjixatkalu Paulo.
Festo wan-tshina: — Phuru Agripa hiyrun-koxa hixa ptowrunekhi hixayma hapatjetatshine, hetanru xye jeji. Judeu-nerune ptowruneka, hewi hwatshine haté Jerusalém hwatshine koxa wale pirana hinkakatkano. Hsaplewyehitluna ruylaxikowakapa.
Seyni nimaxinixkalu hike tsru jikolukanuru hkamhatka ruylaxikolupa hiyrun-koxa waleko hanjitlu César rexyawakapa, nuchinikanuwata nyokanaxyawakaplu.
Seyni hi nimata hanhe nixa yonreyehitanru Paulo tshinanu César nwaka nyokanreru. Hiyáhoni hewi nanikatkalu hix-yehiya, pix-yehiya potuko phuru Agripa pepomsaxyawaklu waneya numukata pa pirana yonrexinri.
Klu tshinanu nkahwaklu hi kihleru hostutkaluru César yehi hyokanatkoklunu munkaklewyehitkotu klu potu hjihyehixika.
Paulo Hinkaklexnawa Agripa Yehiya PiranapniHiyáhoni Agripa wan-tshinatkalu Paulo: — Pumukata hinkakletlexnawa. Waneya Paulo romukamyota hyinuwaka yanumletatka.
Klu tshinanu pixa himatyehpotutna judeu-ne hanu rixjetna haté klu pirana rimaletkakjetna hiyáhoni nanjityi puhle yijnakoleyehixyawakno.
Judeu-ne ptowruneka himatyehitno nmatureyakawa. Rimatna nmatureyakawakananuko ntshijne potuko Jerusalém poktshi nwajekanata.
Wanna himatakanatatkalu hiyáhoni ralujinipna rumukata hinkakletyina neyinuwaklekananuko fariseu kihleru nixapa, hiyrunu fariseu-ne homkahpotutlu judeu hoyakalute.
Hiyáhoni hewi nyopkaka klu tshinanu nkahwakjetlu Hoyakalu hixa kojiretlexyawaknina wutsrukatenni mitshikawni.
Ptowru nonerunkaka hohi hoyetshno Hoyakalu hichinikanretatshine hiyrun-koxa hkahwakjetluna hyoptoxyawakapluna xye hkojirexikolna. Phuru Agripa, xye kahwakaluru pirana tshinanu judeu-ne jihyehjetno.
Haklu tshinanhe hixa, judeu-nhi, kahwaklu kyapreru rixyawaka halixyawaklu Hoyakalu himukata hiwekkakletna hipnatshine? Waneya wane pnute htshinatkana Paulo:
— Hit-koxa wane nixahchinikantapatka ptowruka nyahot-kamhaleta nkamnixyawaklu Jesus Nazaré hajeru.
Hiyáhoni wane potuko nixpatka Jerusalém poktshiya. Tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne hitshitno preso nutajyawakna hixolune potukalune Jesus halixatshine. Waneya ruylatkoklunutkana hit-koxa hikchikhihlenutlu wan-rixikowakanna.
Hix-hohne potuko napnokatatkana ptowru hanjihohnewakapjikakaya haté nyapretakatkana ralixlena ruchoxyawakna. Nahkatkana haté pa poktshikaka napkapa napnokaxyawakapna.
Wale tshinanukni pa kata Damasco nwaka nyatka, tsru hixikatshinwa sacerdote-ne yokanatno tsru hitakkaluru rixkaknona.
Waneya, Phuru, hanikaj-hohnetkani hatnu hapo nyapamtawa netlu katalu tenhohne hichpajikatshri. Tkatshi mero pnute hatajniru. Xye katalu hatawnayehitno nimotsatanune koxa ratawnayehita.
Waneya hixa ptowruneka tshiji yawnamtatka. Waneya tokantshi njema, judeu tokanu riynumaxyano, wan-tshinatshri: “Saulo, Saulo, haklu tshinanhe pkamnitno? Pkamnijetno seyni halikaka pumtukachaxnawa.”
— Waneya hita Paulo-no hihitlu: “Katyihe pixa Tsru Hixikatshriwayi?” — Waneya ruhitatka Tsru Hixikatshriwa: “Hita Jesus-no pkamnijetanruno.”
Ppalnanu pyotunotanu xako! Nnuretyi ntowreru pixyawaka hiyrunu ptowru yineru puphujtaxinri ptowruka petanru haté ptowruka nekhixyapyi. Wale tshinanu nyanwakatatkayi xye hohne.
Nkochpakanyi pa hohne judeu-myoya hiyrun-koxa judeu mixkanemyoya. Wanna yehi nyokanatanyi
pumrekhakajyawakna rumukata hichpaklexyawakna mapchahawakaya katalu romkahixyawakapna hiyrunu Satanás towre ruchpajyawakna Hoyakalu romkahixyawakapna. Waneya ralixlena tshinanu rektunna ruknojikona hiyrunu Hoyakalu nuretanune rixyawakapna.”
— Hiyáhoni, Phuru Agripa, hi nmajnakowaxyalu hetkaluru tenhohne hichpajikatshri.
Seyni Damasco poktshi hajene hapka nunkaklexyalu xye pirana waneya Jerusalém poktshiya wane pnute Judeia tshijne psoluyaka haté judeu mixkane tskalaya nunkaklexyalu. Nunkakna rehchinikanuxinripna rektunna tshinanu Hoyakalu yehi hsatojinripna hiyrunu hkamhiywakapluna kamrurtshikaka rekhixnawakapwana rehchinikanutatkana.
Wale tshinanukni judeu-ne kachitno Hoyakalupjiya hiyáhoni raluk-hiylaletnona.
Seyni Hoyakalu hepixatkano hiyáhoni hewi nyopkaka xawakni nunkajyawakapna ptowru yineruka, tsrukakalune yanachalune koxa, netanru pirana psoluka. Seyni Moisés-ni hiyrunu tokantshi hinkakletatshinni tshinyawakna hinatshripa tokanu tsonu ntshina hita:
Cristo haluka salewnaleta hiyrunu walepni mitshikananu yotunotatshripa hipnatshine tskalaya, katalu pixkalutu rekhixyawakapna judeu-ne hiyrunu judeu mixkane.
Festo Hiynumaxyalu Paulo PiranapniWaneya Paulo hinkaklexnawa seyni Festo tsru htokanu wane htshinyalu: — Paulo, pixlahe hipukalewatatka? Tsru pimatkallahe himtukatkayi?
Seyni Paulo wan-tshinru: — Kchinikanuru Festo, hi nupukalewata. Ntokanu halikakni hiyrunu hpoyaho himatjemletlu.
Klu tshinanu Phuru Agripa, pimatlu xyekaka hiyáhoni numukata phujewaka hiynumsaletyi. Hita nkahwaklu pimatyehitlu xyekaka klu tshinanu hi kahnete poktshi kamhikalurni xye.
Phuru Agripa, palixluhe Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshinni tokanu? Nimatyi palixyawaklu.
Waneya Phuru Agripa wan-tshinatkalu Paulo: — Psokakno puykoxyano tshinanu halixatshrino.
Waneya wane htshina Paulo: — Nanjitlu Hoyakalu ho xawakni ho howukchinipa pixa hiyrun-koxa xawakni nyijnakotjene ptowruneka hita pixka rixyawakapna Jesus Cristo halixatshinepni seyni corrente mostutkonepni.
Paulo Ruchotkamka Seyni Ranjitlu César Rexyawakapa PiranapniWaneya rali wan-tshinrexinixkalu xye pirana, Phuru Agripa, Festo, Berenice hiyrunu wannaymalune ptowruneka palnatka.
Waneya ruchpajinixkaluna wanna riynumsakakna wannakakluko waneya wane htshinna: — Hike hkamha xye jeji ruylaxikowakapa hi koxa hkachixikowakapa.
Paulo Roma Poktshi Hyokanaxikolu PiranapniWaneya wale nuretkatka Itália tshijne wyiywakapa. Satu soldado-ne pohire hiwakni Júlio, waleni psol-tshijne hislahatshine towutatshrikni wale. Hiyáhoni wale henekkatka Paulo hiyrunu pimrine preso hajene ruslahyawakpatka.
Waneya tsro kanawa Adramítio poktshi hichpajikatshro wpokowninixka wyotspehatka Ásia tshijne yopjewaklekaka wyapamxyawakapa. Hixaymalu Aristarco tshinkaluru, Tessalônica poktshi Macedônia tshijne hajeru.
Wale prikatkani Sidom yopjewakle wapokatka. Júlio hihle hislahletlu Paulo hiyáhoni ritshitlu Paulo retapyawakapna rimatletlene hmahaxinri hyoptoxyawakapa.
Waneya wane wutspajinixka Chipre hanikajha hwatshijitatshristsi wyapamta klu tshinanu kanniphalu yoptotwu.
Mar powha wkopruhaxyawaka Cilícia Panfília hinaple wyapamta waneya Mirra poktshi Lícia tshijne hwatshri wapokatka.
Waneya soldado-ne pohire wane hikchijyalo sato tsro kanawa Alexandria hichpajikatshro, Itália tshijne yatshropa. Waneya wala hpokotakjixamtwuna.
Waneya hix-hohne wuhlepotuko yahap-hata. Kyaprepotuklu wyahap-haxyawaka seyni Cnido poktshi hinaple wapokatka. Waneya kanniphalu yoptoxyawakwu tshinanu hi pnute wyatka seyni Creta tshijne hinaple sul sreta hapka wyatka hiyáhoni Salmona-stsi wyapamtatka.
Waneya wane wixa yahap-haletatka hiwnahastsi potuko wyapamta seyni wanepnawaka kyaprepotuklu wapojyawaklu Kihleru Yopjewakle tshinikowaka yehi. Wane hi howukaylu Laseia poktshi.
Tsru Kanniphalu Mar powha Hakanhiywaka PiranapniHix-hohne wane wutukatka hiyáhoni xawakni jhamlepotuklu wyahap-hale klu tshinanu majnákolu hiknojikol-hohne rali hiknohletatka. Hiyáhoni Paulo hiykotna.
Wane htshinna: — Jejine, xye yahap-halu tshinanu netlu hixo jhamleru wetanu. Pa katako ramhanu kanawa, hwunru haté wiwekle koxa hamhanu.
Seyni soldado-ne pohire halixna tsro kanawa hanikatshri hiyrunu kkanawateru seyni Paulo tshinyawaka hi ralixpotuta.
Wale yopjewakle hi kihleru katshikleru ruknokajyawakna. Wale tshinanu hixolune hyokmanayakatanu pa katako Fênix poktshi rapokanna. Xye yopjewaka Creta poktshi yopjewakle kihleru klu tshinanu kanniphalu hichpajyawaka sreta hi hyoptokajya. Wanna kahwaklu xye yopjewakle kihleru riknokajyawakapluna katshikleru papko.
Waneya kanniphalu sul sreta hajpokatshri yinuwajinixka wanna kahwaklu waneyatkana ruchinikanretlerna. Waneya hkosetatkaluna htsatjererna waneya Creta wnahastsi potuko wyapamta.
Waneya chinpotukawa rajpokatka tsru kanniphalu Nordeste hiwakatletatshri mar powha hanikajite hwatshijitatshri ruchpajya.
Hiyáhoni kanniphalu kachitlo tsro kanawa, hi tumukata pnute yaleta. Waneya wetachatlo hiyáhoni kanniphalu hanikachatwu.
Waneya mar powha hanikajite hwatshijitatshri Cauda hiwakatletatshri wiknohamxinixka psokaklu hi wkachitlo mtseroto kanawa pokotkaluro.
Waneya rali kachrexinixkalona mtseroto kanawa pokotkaluro, waneya tsro kanawa rostukwanapatna kapotsa tma mupojyawakanupa. Hpikluna tsro kanawa ksatu tutshlixyawaka Líbia wnaha hwatshri, wale tshinanu hkochpirokluna mkatshri sama kanawa herutatshri hiyáhoni retachatluna kanniphalu hanikachaxyawaklo.
Wale prika tsru kanniphalu herutpotutwu wale tshinanu jejine psoji hwunru ruknokhatna.
Waneya map-hohne rixinri hixa wimyo potuko wuknokhaxyalu tsro kanawa wunru.
Hix-hohne hi phujru tkatshi, katahiri hiyrunu tsru kanniphalu hi hitukpirata wale tshinanu hi wkahwaklu wiwejyawaka.
Waneya hix-hohne hike wnikanatka wane pnute Paulo yopkakatka wanna hanikajite waneya wane htshinna: — Jejine, hixamka hyijnakotkamkano Creta tshijne hi wuchpajya hikemka kojwaklu wetanu.
Seyni xawakni nkojirethi hihlehchinikanutanu klu tshinanu hi satukna hixa hipnanu. Tsro kanawa tsonu hamhanu.
Klu tshinanu xye yetshno satu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru hapyehitno, walenutkano wale nkamrurewaxya.
Wane htshinno: “Paulo, hi ppikanu! César-stsi pyanu hiyrunu petanu, Hoyakalu henekyi pimotsane ptowruneka.”
Hiyáhoni jejine, hihlehchinikanutanu. Hoyakalu nmunanha wale tshinanu nimat-hita runkajyano hiyrunu wane potuko rixa hakanhaletanu.
Seyni halikaka satu mar powha hanikajite hwatshijitatshri wyosropyehitanunatka.
Tsro Kanawa Hipojyawaka PiranapniHepi semana hiknohinixka seyni tsru kanniphalu herutatkawu Mediterrâneo powhaya. Waneya hanikaj-yetshno rixinixka kanawa hanikatshine kahwaklu hi howukatkalu tshiji.
Hiyáhoni ruknokhatluna kapotsa hinolu htsatlerna waneya retluna honha trinta e seis metros pa tennuhlu. Waneya pnutejiji hyahothatatnakna retluna vinte e sete metros tennuhatkalu.
Hpikluna tsro kanawa sotlu hwiywaka tutshlixyawaka wale tshinanu tostsi sreta ruknokhatluna quatro hinolu htsatlerna waneya ranjihohnetna rumrerejinripa hohi.
Waneya Paulo wan-tshinna soldado-ne hiyrunu soldado-ne pohire: — Tsro kanawa hma mutukkanuklunupna kanawa hanikatshine hixa hi himukata hiwekkakletko.
Hiyáhoni soldado-ne hkastakatsatatkalona mtseroto kanawa pokotkaluro waneya retacha hijrukhaletatkalona.
Hohistsitkani Paulo tshanixna ptowruneka hnijyawakapna wane htshinna: — Hepi semana pchinika hixa kahwakachatlu hike mnikkanhi.
Xawakni nkojirethi pa hixanu hnijyawakapa klu tshinanu hixa haluka nikleta hiwejyawakapa klu tshinanu hi pa jiwutsakna hamhini hixa ptowrunekhi.
Waneya wane pnute Paulo kochtsheklu pão, hpoyahnutatkalu Hoyakalu wanna hetanu. Waneya hjiknajrotlu pão hyinuwaka nikletatkalu.
Waneya hmixkowahchinikanutatkana hiyáhoni wanna koxa nikatka.
Kanawa yapatshine ptowrunekwu duzentas e setenta e seis yine.
Waneya rali nikletatkana ptowruneka trigo pahi hixetatshri ruknokhatna minotu tixyawakapa tsro kanawa.
Hohi rixinixka kanawa hanikatshine hetlu tshiji. Hi rimathetluna klu tshijneni seyni retluna pokokhawaka hiyáhoni wane raluk-hitspakletmakna rumukaxinipna.
Hiyáhoni hkastakatsatatkaluna hinolu htsatlerna waneya mar powha ruchomtatkaluna. Hiyrunu waneklukawa koxa hkochpirokatkaluna kanawa hpotukataprekakna. Waneya romukatnakluna mkatshri sama tojri sreta hwatshri ksatu nwaka rumukata yalexyawakapna.
Seyni ksatumtaha tachtsheka tsro kanawa hiyáhoni tachtshekajritanatka hi tuyoljetatka kanawa seyni tostsi sreta hyinuwaka hiknahleta tenoplojhalu tshinanu.
Waneya soldado-ne haluk-hiylaletna hostutkalune ptowruneka hmanojiywakanupna hmasujyawakanupna.
Seyni soldado-ne pohire Júlio tshinkaluru haluk-hiwekkakletlu Paulo hiyáhoni hi ritshitna soldado-ne hostutkalune ruylaxyawakna. Waneya hyokanatatkana himat-hanokatshine hapka rujrukhaxyawakna tshiji rapojyawakapna.
Ha hixetatshine kanawa chpata ho kluneruktako kanawa hajeru hoho hyapamtanna. Hiyáhoni wan-rixa hapokletluna tshiji ptowruneka. Riwekatkana ptowruneka.
Malta Tshinikowaka Rapojyawakna PiranapniWaneya tshiji wapojinixka wimatatka xye mar powha hanikajite hwatshijitatshri Malta tshinikowaka rixyawaka.
Wane hajene hihle yoptoletwu. Hpawatatkana klu tshinanu hinatkani hiyrunu katshiklerni waneya hyoptotwuna hixa satkakwu.
Paulo hapatjetlu kapluru tshitshmero hoho ruknoklu waneya himnu hichpakamta hameru tshinanu Paulo rachkamyotatka.
Waneya wane hwatshine hexinixkalu himnu Paulo-myo rachtshekayhixyawaka wane htshinna wannakakluko: — Jiylalewakleru hetkoni xye jeji. Seyni hi rupna mar powhaya seyni hapnokatatshri hi haluk-hiwekkakletlu wanepnawaka.
Seyni Paulo hiwlipatlu himnu tshitshmero hyana hiyáhoni hike rixatka Paulo.
Seyni wanna kahwaklu ranojiywaka Paulo ho hyawnanuna. Howukchini ruslahluna seyni hike rixa. Hiyáhoni ruprotakahchinikanutatkana waneya wane htshinna: — Hoyakalu hetkoni.
Públio Haniklu Paulo Hipji Rutujyawaklu PiranapniWanestsi rawa psoji tshiji, Públio tshinkaluru tshijneni, waleni tsru poktshi chefe-te. Hyoptohihlenutwu, hipji nwaka ranikatkawu waneya map-hohne pchinika ruslahhihlenutwu.
Públio hiru yeyixakanata, htseruhata. Waneya Paulo jihlokyehitlu, ranjihohneta waneya wale hoho rutakamyota rutskalaklu.
Waneya ralixinixka Paulo ptowru tshijne hajene yeyixatshine yanwakatlu hiyáhoni wanna koxa rutskalaka.
Waneya wane hajene kahwakpirpotutwu. Waneya wuchpakpiraxinixka renekwuna ptowruka wmahaxinri.
Hyatnaka Paulo PiranapniWaneya mapa ksuru katshikleru papko hiknohinixka tsro kanawa Alexandria hichpajikatshro wpokownatka. Katshikleru papko pchinika hewi tshijne hitspakjekanatatshrotlo. Kanawajri hwa yonhatatshri wane htshina: Hoyakalune hepirune.
Waneya Siracusa poktshi wapoka map-hohne wane wutukatka.
Waneya wsajrukapa hiyáhoni Régio poktshi wapokatka. Wale prika kanniphalu yinuwakatka sul sreta ruchpajya hiyáhoni wale prika Pozuoli poktshi wapokatka.
Wane wukchijyana pimrine Hoyakalu halixatshine waneya ranjitwuna pa semana wutujyawaka wannayma. Wane pnut-hohne tsonu Roma poktshi wapokatka.
Waneya Hoyakalu halixatshine Roma poktshi hwatshine jempiranyehixinixkawu wunamxyawakatka, hyanwakatwuna Praça de Ápio poktshi hiyrunu Três Vendas poktshi hyoptoxyawuna. Waneya Paulo hexinixkana Hoyakalu halixatshine hpoyahnutlu Hoyakalu hiyrunu hmixkowahchinikanutatka.
Map-hohne rixinixka Paulo tshanixna judeu chefe-tene. Waneya rapatjexinixkana judeu chefe-tene Paulo wan-tshina: — Nonerune, hike hektutu nkamhiyna wimolene, hiyrun-koxa hi psojikna nmajnakowaxyalu Wutsrukatenni Abraão-ni, Isaque-ni, Jacó-ni hasrujyawu pirana. Seyni wanepnawaka judeu chefe-tene kachikjixno Jerusalém poktshiya waneya nenekkatka romano-myoya.
Waneya romano-ne hepomsatno hiyáhoni raluk-hicholetno klu tshinanu hike nkamha nuylaxikowakapa.
Seyni wane hajene judeu-ne hi haluklu ruchoxyawakapnona romano-ne. Wale tshinanu nanjitlu Roma poktshi nyiywakapa César tshinkaluru rujhahchinikanyehixyawakapno. Seyni wanepnawaka hike ntshinanwakatna nonerune.
Wale tshinanu naluk-hetlethi niynumsaxyawakaphi. Xye corrente-kaka nostuxikolu israel-nerune kahwakleru nalixyawaka tshinanu.
Waneya ruhitluna Paulo: — Hike yonawahlo wyoptota Judeia tshijne hichpajikatshri pixa pirana. Hiyrun-koxa hi satukna wimole wane hichpajikatshri hanikpiranyehityi, hi koxa pnu pejnu htshinanwakatyina.
Seyni waluka jemletlu pihchinikanu klu tshinanu wimata ptowru sreta hajene pnu pejnu htshinanwakatyina pixa hiyrunu pixa pixka hixatshine.
Paulo Hinkaklewata Roma Poktshiya PiranapniWaneya Paulo hiyrunu judeu-nerune marca-hohnetlu hapatjeru hkamhiywakapna. Wale hohne rixinixka hix-potuko judeu-ne hapatjeyehitlu Paulo hwiywaka. Psol-hohneruka Paulo hiynumsatna. Hkochtsheklu Moisés yonreru pirana hiyrunu Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshinni tshinre yonatkaluru runkajyawakapna Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka pirana. Waneya htowutna Jesus pirana ralixyawakapna.
Satkaka halixlu hanu htshina Paulo seyni pimrine hi halixlu.
Wale tshinanu malixkane yinuwaka hihjekakleta wannakakluko hiyáhoni hyinuwaka hichpakletna. Seyni hma muchpajyawakanupna wanna, Paulo wan-tshinna: — Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hinkakna hixa hitsrukatenni Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshriniya, Isaías tshinkalurni tokanu tshinanu, wla htshina:
<sup>(26-27)</sup> “Pyanwakatanna nyi yine waneya wla ptshinanna: Hixa yijnakochatanu seyni hi himatjemanu. Hixa hijha himatjemletanru seyni hikeklu himatanru, klu tshinanu nyi yine chiko hchinikanna. Hike hjemna hijnakopnaya hiyrunu ruchyayhalexnawana. Wane hma mixkanumkana pa katako rapkathojitna hiyhaleya, pa katako hijnakopna tshinanu hyijnakotanna hiyrunu rimatjemanna hihchinikanuya waneya rehchinikanutanna nutskalakanna.”
(-)
Waneya Paulo wan-tshina: — Himatanu, Hoyakalu yokananwakat-koxna judeu mixkane hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana hiyáhoni wanna yijnakotanru hyoptotanruna wale pirana.
Waneya rali wan-tshinretatkalu Paulo, judeu-nerune hichpakamta ruhjekakna wannakakluko.
Hepi Mhale Hostutkaluru Rixatka Paulo PiranapniWaneya wan-rutuka Paulo hepi mhale. Pantshi wenutkaluru rawakanata. Katukta hapyehitlu Paulo hyoptohihlenutlu.
Tsru hihchinikanuyma runkaklewata Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka pirana, Jesus Cristo pirana koxa hiyrunu hike himaletpiranatlu.
<font color=teal>Romanos</font>Hita, Paulo-no, Jesus Cristo towrerno, yonatlo twu yonawahlo. Hita Jesus nurrerno, nnuretka, ntowutka Hoyakaluya nunkaklexyawakaplu kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana.
Kihler-potuko tokantshi hiwekkaklewatatshri piran-honra Hoyakalu mitshikananuko hinkakletlu Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshineya hiyrunu Hoyakalu tokanu potukalu yonatkaluru rawa wale pirana.
Xye yonatkaluru hinkakletlu Wutsrukate, Jesus Cristo, Hoyakalu whene. Himane Davi klopichani.
Seyni rimaxikowaka potukalu rixyawakatka, Hoyakalu ruchpajya, retka hpixkonu tsru potuko. Klu tshinanu hipuktshi riwekkajika, rimathexikowaka Hoyakalu whene rixyawakatka.
Hiyáhoni Jesus Cristo tshinanu Hoyakalu henekno xye hitakkaluru, hnurreru nixyawakatka, Cristo tshinanu, nalixkajyawakapna, kajnako nixkajyawakapna yine psol-tshijne hajeneko.
Hixa Roma poktshi hajenhi ptowrunekhi Jesus Cristo tshanixlenhi.
Hiyáhoni nyonanwakathi hixa ptowrunekhi Roma poktshi hwatshinhi, Hoyakalu hamotanunhi, htomhaka Hoyakalu kotspalatanune hixyawakapa; waneyaphi Hoyakalu hihlenu hiyrun-koxa hihlehchinikanrewlu Wuru Hoyakaluya hiyrunu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus Cristo-ya.
Paulo Hichinikjexyawakna Cristo Halixatshine Hiyrunu Rexyawakapna PiranapniMitshikananhapka npoyahnutlu Noyakalute, Jesus Cristo-ya hixa ptowruneka tshinanu; klu tshinanu hixa halixle pirana ptowruchaka hjemika.
Hoyakalu nomkahitanruni psoluka nmixkonuya hiwhene Jesus, kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana nunkakletjereru hetanu, hi nweyawata. Hoyakalu himata ptowru hohneka nuchinikjethi nanjihohnereya.
Hiyrun-koxa nanjijetlu Hoyakalu, ralujinipno, ritshixiniklunupno hita xekoyaka hixa napyehitanu.
Klu tshinanu halikaka naluk-hetlethi klu tshinanu naluk-hapiklethi hixa satkaka himutlewlu henekachalu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluruya hmixkotahchinikanutjerupa.
Waleni hixa ptowrunekwu, hixa hiyrun-koxa hita walerutu papkoko wepixko; hixa hepixko nalixle tshinanu hiyrunu hita hepixko hixa halixle tshinanu.
Hiyáhoni Cristo tshinanu nmoletanune, nalukhi hixa himaxyawaklu hixo katamka nalpokotatkalu hix-yehi napojinripa seyni ptowru katako satu pa hixanu himaletno wane nma yiywakanupa. Klu tshinanu naluk-halixkakletna yine hixa tskala hwatshine nixa halixkaklexyawakpotukna pimrine judeu mixkane pixka nkamrure tshinanu.
Klu tshinanu naluk-hinkakletna ptowru neruka, yáholu yine ho kajitune, yáholu jimatkalerune ho hike mimatkane seyni nujhalu nunkajyawakna.
Hiwekkaklewatatshri Pirana Wale Pixkonu PiranapniHi npatewyehitlu kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana klu tshinanu nimatlu waleni Hoyakalu pixkonu ptowru Cristo halixatshripa hiwekkakkalurupni; mitshikananhapka judeu-nerune tshinanupni waneya wane pnute judeu mixkane tshinanupni.
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu hekhixnawa potukalu rixyawaka yineru hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana tshinanu, hyinuwaklekananukawa haté wetpotutanhonuklu. Hiyáhoni wane ttshina yonawahlo potukalo: “Katukta Hoyakalu potukata, ralixle tshinanu riwekkakko.”
Yine Hektunu PiranapniHiyáhoni Hoyakalu tenhohne hwatshri hekhixnawa hjihekannu ptowru yine hektunu tshinanu, halikakalutu tokantshi yohimpiratatshine tshinanu.
Klu tshinanu wale Hoyakalu himatyehixikaluru phujetkalu; phujetkalu klu tshinanu Hoyakalu potuko phujewak-potuko hitakatkalu.
Hoyakalu xye tshiji ruyakoxiniklunukananukotka haté xawakni, Hoyakalu metkotni seyni wale hpixkonu mnikawnakatni hiyrunu royaknu retpotutkahonukatka. Xye ptowru potuka hetka Hoyakalu kamhalerutka tshinanu hiyáhoni wannako htshinanupnina hmalixlenna tshinanupni.
Rimathetmakluna Hoyakalu seyni hi hkahwakpiratluna Hoyakalu, Hoyakalu rixkal-tshinanu hiyrunu hi hpoyahnutluna Hoyakalu. Hiyáhoni hike muchinikanretkanni raj-koxna mapchahayna.
Jimatkalerune hkahwajnawana seyni halikaka jipukalerunni.
Hi Hoyakalu hoyaknu, hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupni hkahwakpiratna seyni mayawletshichakaka hkahwakpiratluna yine moyaknuko pixka hixatshri hkahwakpiratna ho kamejirune mayawle ho niktshine quatro jixirune mayawle ho niktshine yosrolotatshine mayawle.
Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu hichochatna hektut-potuko hkamhiywakna hektu haji rixle tshinanna, kapatmenuru hkamhakajyawakna wannakakluko.
Ripekotluna halikakalutu Hoyakalu tokanu weyawluya. Hiyáhoni rimalwutluna, romkahitluna Hoyakalu kamhaleru seyni Hoyakalu potuko ptowru potuko hiyakotatshri hi romkahitna. Hiyrunu Hoyakalutkani himalwuhohnekanatkalurupa hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa. Amém.
Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu hichochatna hektutu haluklu hkamhachaxyawakapna. Haté hsuxonerna suxo mixyawakanu kamha suxonkakluko pnu hixkakjeta.
Waneko pixka rixkakna jejine, suxoneyma ruchotna wane rixjexyawakna seyni jejinekakluko het-sotankakjeta, jejinekakluko pnu hixkakjeta Hoyakalu mukchikhihlenutanutu hkamhana hiyáhoni hyoptotluna rapnokaxikolna rujhalerna rumtuknu tshinanna.
Hi raluk-himretahchinikanretluna Hoyakalu. Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu henekatkana hektu hchinikanu rixyawakna, malukkotu hkamhiywakna.
Katsepoyna ptowru muhlentshi, himtuklewatatshri, hektutuya, hahxalewluya, ruylalewleyna, tokantshiya, yokwirewluya, hma hchinikannuymana, hapatlewluya,
kapatlewaklerune, Hoyakalu kamnitatshine, malixletu, tsru rikahwajnawana, tserpiranawlu, hektutu hakanhakakatshine, tsrune majnakowyehitatshine,
mahchinikanune, kyokwijeklerune, mamotlewatkane, chikohchinikanrune, metwamonrene.
Hiyrunu rimatjemmakluna Hoyakalu hitakanru, ptowru pejnu wan-hixkalune hijhalu rupninripna, wanepnawaka wan-rixjetna seyni hi wane tsonu rixjetna; rukchikhihlenutluna haté pimrin-koxa wan-hixatshine.
Hoyakalu Hapnokatlewle PiranapniHiyáhoni hi pkahwakanru powra pixyawaka wane ptshininri satu hektutu kamhatshri. Klu tshinanu peyijinri satu hektutu kamhatshri, wane potuko pixa heyiklexnawa. Klu tshinanu waneko pixka hixatshri koxyi pixa, pixa wan-tshina rukolukanuwninripa.
Seyni wimatlu potukalni Hoyakalu wan-rixa hikoluklexnawana xyekaka kamhatshine.
Ha pixa, yineryi, rukolukanuwnana ptshinanwakatnahe xyekaka kamhatshine seyni waneko pixkalutu pkamhajeta. Pkahwakluhe pasujyalu Hoyakalu hapnokatlewle?
Ho peyikluhe xawaka Hoyakalu potshwanu, wale hchinikanu, hkahwakhohnekanaxyawakyi? Hi he puchiniklu Hoyakalu hihlenu kosejyawakyi pehchinikanuxyawakapa?
Seyni chiko haji pixini, pma mehchinikanhajitkanu tshinanu papatjeyehixnawa tsru jhekantshi hapnokaxikolu hohne tshinanu Hoyakalu hekhitlu hchinikannu potukal-potuko.
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu henekanru yineru waleko hkamrure wenru kihleru ho hektutu.
Hoyakalu heneklewatanu riwejinri hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa hanunektako hi hituka kihleru kamhaleta hiyrunu Hoyakalu hpoyikoxyawakna hijhatshine. Hoyakalu honra rumuwkakpiratna hiyrunu riwejinrina mnikawnakatuko hijhatshine.
Seyni halixkoxikatshinwa, halikakalutu tokantshi majnakowyehitatshinewa hektutu romkahixyawakna, wanna hoho rapokanu Hoyakalu jhekanu hiyrun-koxa rapnokaxikolna.
Tsru salewaktshipni hiyrun-koxa wamontshi hapokhohotanru satkaka yineru riwejinri hektutu kamhatshriwa. Mitshikananhapka judeu-nerunepni waneya wane pnute judeu mixkane wan-hixko.
Waneya himalwutkalurupni, kahwakpiratkalurupni, kihlehchinikanrupni satkaka yineru kihleru kamhatshri wan-hixkomka, mitshikananhapka judeu-nerunemkapni waneya wane pnute judeu mixkane wan-hixkomka.
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu hike yineru hkahwakpirata.
Hiyáhoni ptowruneka hektune Moisés yonreru mwikane wan-hixatshinepniko, Moisés yonreru mwikanepniko hamhanuna. Hiyrunu ptowruneka Moisés yonreru majnakowaxikatshine rukolukanuwnanna Moisés yonreru tshinanu.
Klu tshinanu judeu mixkane, Moisés yonreru mwikanemkani, seyni wane potuko rixinna ruphujetluna wannako rimwalerna htowutjerna yáholu Moisés yonrerumka hi rimwana.
Wan-hixatshinekni hekhitlu wan-rixna yáholu Moisés yonrerumka hi rimwana seyni rajiyna hiyrunu hihchinikanuyna rawa wale yonreru pixkalut-potuko. Hiyáhoni rimat-hichinikanuwatna ho kihlerahe hkamhana ho hike.
Waneklu hohnepa Hoyakalu hapnokatanru ptowru yine hchinikanu mimatyehikanatkotu ntshinyawaka kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana tshinanu Jesus Cristo tshinanuya.
Rapnokaxikowakna Judeu-ne Wannako Htshinanu PiranapniHa pixa xawaka? Judeu-neru ptshininwa, Moisés yonreru munanhatshriyi hiyrunu palixkoxnawa Hoyakaluneru ptshininwa.
Pixamka judeu himatlu Hoyakalu halujyawaka. Hiyrunu Moisés yonreru tshinanu ppoyaho himatletmaklu kihleru pnurexyawaka.
Pkahwajnawa mayhalene kosekatshriyi hiyrunu mapchahawaka hwatshine tshinanu, katalu pikahwajnawa pixa, judeu
mahchinikanune hasrukatshriyi pkahwajnawa, mturune yimanruyi ptshinnawa. Pkahwaklu Moisés yonreru tshinanu pimwalu ptowru potuko himatkaltshi hiyrunu halikakalutu pirana.
Pimrine pasruka, haklu tshinanhe hi pasrujinwa? Punkakna hi htshowhuwatanu seyni pixa xawaka ptshowhuwatewhe?
Pixa wan-tshina: Hi himopatlewatanu, seyni pixa xawaka pimopatlewathe? Peyikjetlu mayawletshichakaka seyni wanepnawaka hinkaklewawakapjikaka hajeru ptshowhuxini.
Palixkoxnawa Hoyakalu pirana pimwiywaka seyni pma mimretkanuklunru yonruru pirana hi he ppatetjetlu Hoyakalu?
Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru wan-tshina: “Hixa judeu-nhi hektunu tshinanu judeu mixkane hektuwaka htshinanwakatluna Hoyakalu.”
Judeu Halikakalune PiranapniMoisés yonreru pirana pomkahixini, pujhalu judeu jiprojhiynawakwa pixka pixyawaka hijhakalurni wale. Seyni yokanruru pmajnakowaxini, hi psojikna repixatkayi pjiprojhikolu.
Klu tshinanu judeu mixkatu hi jiprojhiynawa seyni Moisés yonreru pirana potukalu romkahixini, hi he xawaka Hoyakalu kahwaklu hatatjewa hjiprojhiynatkawa?
Hiyáhoni hixa judeu-nerunhi heyikanwakatko judeu mixkaneya klu tshinanu hixa himwalu yonatkaluru hiyrunu hjiprojhajexnawa wanepnawaka hixa majnakowaxyalu yonruru pirana seyni judeu mixkane homkahitlu Hoyakalu hiykole pirana yáholu hi hjiprojhiynawana.
Hiyáhoni hanu pothe rixa judeu? Roho mane hi judeu hixkaklu yineru. Hiyrun-koxa hi jiprojhaptojimtaluko judeu hixkaklu yineru.
Seyni judeu pixkalut-potni yineru hitokote hwatshri, waleni hihchinikanu histakkaluru seyni hi kotshiroyni, xyekni Hoyakalu kamrure hi yineru mixkonuyni yonatkaluru homkahitatshri tshinanni. Wan-hixatshri yineru Hoyakalu rimalwuxiko, hi yineruyapni.
Hoyakalu Hi Yohikanru Htokanu PiranapniHiyáhoni klunerhe rawyana judeu-nerune, judeu mixkane pnute? Klunerhe repixlewaxya jiprojhalu?
Tsru potuko repixlewaxya judeu rixkaklewaxyawaka. Mitshikananhapka klu tshinanu Hoyakalu henekna judeu-ne htokanu rimwiywakna.
Ha xawakni, hanhe rixna satkaka hma malixlenna tshinanu? Ha xawakni Hoyakallahe yohikanru htokanu?
Hike, hi psojikna. Hoyakalu hikeklu hweyawata yáholu yine ptowruneko kayloklerunemkani seyni Hoyakalu hike. Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru wan-tshina: “Pimathexikowakapni pixa Hoyakalu potukalyi kluneruktako ptshina hiyrun-koxa pimalwutko yahmaklu pweyawyehitko.”
Seyni hi he xawaka wektunu hiphujetlu Hoyakalu hihlenu? Hanu wtshin-hihretanru xye? Wumukata wla tshinrehetkota, Hoyakalu hetko pupjeta rapnokaxyawakwu. (Seyni hewiya yine hchinikanu pixka ntshinachaxya.)
Maka hike! Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu mpotukatu rixkamka himka rimat-hikolukanuwnayehijixanna ptowruneko yine.
Hiyáhoni nmajnakowaxini hi he xawaka rimalwutko Hoyakalu pimrineya? Klu tshinanu rimathexikowaka potukalu rixyawaka Hoyakalu nektunu tshinanu. Hiyáhoni kluneru tshinanhe napnokatko nektunu tshinanu, wtshinjeta?
Wan-rixkamka wlamka wtshinanu: “Wuya, hektututshi wkamhanu kihleru hakanhiywakapa.” Wane htshina hapatlexinnona pimrine seyni wane ntshinjenepni rapnokatkonna halikaka.
Ptowru Yineru Hektuwaka Kamhatshri Hixyawaka PiranapniHiyáhoni ha wanna judeu-ne xawaka hixa yohnik-hihlenurunrahe? Hike, hi psojikna klu tshinanu wekhixnatkawa judeu-neru hiyrun-koxa judeu mixkane pixkakakanni klu tshinanu rektunna tshinanu.
Wla htshina yonatkaluru tshinyawakakotnaka: “Hi satukna yineru potukalu.
Hi satukna himatjematshri. Hi satukna Hoyakalu homkahitatshri.
Wanna ptowruneka howuka hwa Hoyakaluya. Pupjetatshinni wanna ptowruneka. Hi satukna kihleru kamhatshri, hi satuknako.”
Hiplamna hatatjewa yomletshi hihpukatshri. Hinruna hweyawaxyana tokantshi hipnakaklewatatshri. “Himnu kamaklewatatshri pixka rixa hinamna hichpajikatshri.”
“Hchiretna yine hsalexyawakna hiyrunu ruylalewaxyawakna.
Hanukta hyapna ranikluna himtuklewlu, tsru saletlewlu.
Hi rimatluna hapnanuhchinikankaklewlu pirana.”
“Hiyrun-koxa hi hpikluna Hoyakalu.”
Moisés Hiykole Yonatkaluru Miwekkaklewatkatu PiranapniSeyni wimata Moisés yonreru tshinyawaka wan-tshinanwakatna Moisés yonreru pirana homkahitatshine. Wan-rixa klu tshinanu hike yineru himukata powratlexinwa seyni ptowru tshijne hajeneko hikolukanuwnatka Hoyakalu hetanuya.
Seyni hike yineru Moisés yonreru kamhatshri powratko Hoyakalu hetanuya. Klu tshinanu Moisés yonreru pirana rimathexikatka muhletu rixyawaka yineru.
Jesus Cristo Halixatshri Tsonu PiranapniSeyni Hoyakalu hali hiphujetletatkalu Moisés yonreru mwaknuklunuwa rawapiranatatka hpowraxikowakna yine Hoyakalu hetanuya. Xye pirana rekhita Moisés yonreru pirana hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine hiphujetlu.
Wpowratjerni Hoyakalu walixle Jesus Cristo tshinanuya. Ptowru halixatshri pejnu wan-hixka; klu tshinanu hikewani yineru pnuko hixatshriwa,
seyni ptowru potuko yineru hektuwaka kamhatshrini hiyáhoni Hoyakalu hoyaknu hpupjexyana.
Seyni Hoyakalu powratachatlu yineru, hi rujhalu hwenuxikowaka, Hoyakalu henekachalewata klu tshinanu Cristo Jesus wenutatkalu.
Hoyakalu heneklu Cristo henekachaluru hiylatkaluru rixyawakapa hiyáhoni cruz rupniywaka tshinanu, yineru hektunu hiknokatshri rixyawakatka Cristo, ptowru yineru munanhalerutkani Cristo. Hoyakalu wan-hixa rekhixyawaklu potukalu rixyawaka. Mitshikananu Hoyakalu hetachatna hektuwaka kamhatshine, hmachiretannu tshinanu; hiyáhoni hi rapnokatna rektunna.
Seyni xawakni Hoyakalu henekatkalu Cristo rekhixyawakaplu potukalu rixyawaka. Potukalni Hoyakalu hiyáhoni hpotukatanru Jesus halixatshripa.
Hiyáhoni wumukata tserpiranatlexnawhe hix-nanuko? Hike! Kluneru tshinannihe? Moisés yonreru pirana womkahixyawakatka tshinanrahe? Hike, seyni Jesus walixyawaka tshinanni.
Hiyáhoni wimatjemlu Hoyakalu powratlu yineru ralixle tshinanu tsonu seyni Moisés yonreru pirana romkahixyawaka hi powratlu yineru.
Hkahwakhe judeu Hoyakalute tsonni, hi he judeu mixkane Hoyakalut-koxni wale? Hehe, halikakni, judeu mixkane Hoyakalut-koxni wale.
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu satupkalu. Hiyáhoni wale powratlu judeu-neru hiyrun-koxa judeu mixkane ralixlena tshinanu.
Ha xawakni, wuknokachatatjerhe Moisés yonreru walixle tshinanu? Hike, hi psojikna wuknojinri seyni wpoyahokakanru Moisés yonreru.
Abraão-ni Wyiminri PiranapniHanhe wumukata tshinyehretanru Abraão-ni wutsrukatni? Klunerhe xawaka rukchika Abraão-ni Hoyakalu hetanuya?
Abraão-ni hkamrure tshinanu hpowratkonimka Hoyakalu hetanuya waneyamka tsru pirana htshinyehixiniwa wale nannuko seyni Hoyakalu hetanuymaka hike.
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru wan-tshina: “Abraão-ni halixtokanutlu Hoyakalu hiyáhoni ralixle tshinanni Hoyakalu powratniru Abraão-ni, potukalu rixyawakni.”
Kamrurewatatshri wenutka. Hiyrun-koxa wenutkaluru hi kahwaklu renekachaxikowaka seyni hkamrure tshinanu hkaylerni.
Klu tshinanu katukta hi munanhanru hkamrure seyni Hoyakalu potukatlewatatshri hmunahanu, ralixle tshinanu hpowratko Hoyakaluya.
Wane potuko raluka tshinretni Davi-ni wane htshinyawaknixka hihlehchinikanyehitkalunetkani Hoyakalu powratanune ralixle tshinanu tsonna hiyrunu hi hkamrurna tshinanu hpowratkona;
wane htshinna: “Hektune powraxikolunetka hihlehchinikanyehitkalune hiyrunu rektunna ruknojikatkana.
Hihlehchinikanyehitkalune yine hektune mtshinkonpatkani Hoyakalu hektuntshi hiknojyawaka tshinanu.”
Ha xye poyikowlu Davi-ni hinkakletleru yineru jiprojhikatshriwa tshinanu tsonrahe? Hike, seyni yineru mjiprojhikatwa tshinan-koxni. Klu tshinanu yonatkaluru tshinyawaka wunkakleta: “Abraão halixtokanutlu Hoyakalu hiyáhoni ralixle tshinanni Hoyakalu hitaklu Abraão potukalu rixyawakatka.”
Hanu rixatka Abraão waneklu papko? Hjiprojhakoklunu wkatanrahe hpotukatka ho wane pnut-hohneko hpotukatkatka? Abraão hi hjiprojhakawa seyni Hoyakalu potukatatkalu.
Wane wkatanutka hjiprojhakjixnatkawa Abraão ralixle hiphujetatshrini wale. Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu hiphujetlu, Hoyakalu potukatatkalu Abraão ralixle tshinanu tsonu seyni hi hiptojimta tshinanni. Hiyáhoni Abraão rurutna wanna ptowru neruka Hoyakalu potukatanune ralixlena tshinanu yáholu hi hjiprojhakjixnawana.
Hiyrun-koxa Abraão rurutna jiprojhakjixikatshinwa seyni hi wale tshinanu tsonni seyni ralixlena tshinanni Abraão hma jiprojhaknuklunuwa pixka.
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu wla htshinkamka Moisés yonreru homkahitatshine tsonu himukata yoptoletlu runkaklexyana waneya himka rawanu halixlu hiyrunu hike mkochpakatshrimkapni Hoyakalu hinkaklexyana yine.
Yonruru tshinanu rawanu hapnokatlewlu Hoyakaluya majnakowatatshine tshinanu. Seyni yonruru mwaknumka himka rawanu majnakowlu.
Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu hinkakletlu halixatshine tshinanu. Wan-rixa Hoyakalu rimaxikowaka Hoyakalu hinkakletanru renekachatanna Abraão-ni klopichane ptowrun-potuka, hi Moisés yonreru pirana homkahitatshine tshinanu tsonu seyni ptowru yineru pejnu halixatshri Abraão-ni pixka hixa halixletatshri tshinanni. Klu tshinanu Abraão-ni wuruta hixa halixatshinwu ptowrunekwu.
Wane htshina yonatkaluru: “Wane nixkakatkayi Abraão-ni rurutyina hixo nerkaka hirutanru.” Hoyakalu hinkaklexyalu hakanhanu klu tshinanu Hoyakalu honra hinkakletlu. Xyekni Hoyakalu Abraão-ni munanhaleru. Hoyakalu walekni hipnatshri hiwekkakatshri hiyrunu htokanu tsonu tshinanu ptowruka mwakatuwa hakanhakakatshri.
Hiyáhoni Abraão-ni halixachata, hkahwakachata yáholu yine yhale hetanu hmahijer-kahwaklechatanru. Hiyáhoni ralixle tshinanu Abraão-ni wuhenetna hixo nerune. Wane potuko htshinatka yonatkaluru: “Piklopichane wla pejnupna.”
Abraão-ni psokakniru cem mhale rixyawaknixka. Seyni hi ruhroka halixlewletni yáholu rimathetlu himane hipnatshri pixka rali hixletatka hiyrunu Sara-ni hi wuhenewpiratni.
Seyni hi rutuk-halixletni Abraão-ni hiyrunu hi ruhrok-halixletlu Hoyakalu hinkaklexyanru. Ralixle mixkotnixkalu, Hoyakalu rimalwutnixka.
Abraão-ni himatlu psolu hchinikanuyako Hoyakalu himukata kamhaletlu wale runkakletanru.
Wale tshinanukni Abraão-ni ralixle tshinanu Hoyakalu potukalu htshinniru Abraão-ni.
Xye hima yonatkaluru wan-tshinatshri “Hoyakalu potukalu htshinniru” hi Abraão-ni tshinanu tsonu hyonatka.
Seyni hixa tshinan-koxa hyonatka. Potukalune tshinikatshinwu, hixa ptowrunekwu Hoyakalu, Wutsrukate Jesus hiwekkakatshri halixatshinwu.
Jesus, hixa hektunu tshinanu renekka rupniywaka seyni riwekkaka wuhleyehitka Hoyakaluya.
Halixlewlu Tshinanu Hpowraxikowaka PiranapniWpowratka, halixlewlu tshinanu hiyrunu hihlehchinikanyehitkalunwu Hoyakaluyma. Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus Cristo kamhaleru tshinanu.
Walixle tshinanu Cristo wan-hixwu Hoyakalu hihlehchinikanrewle henekachalu wyoptoxyawaka. Wane wixa haté xawakni. Wale tshinanu wpoyikowata klu tshinanu Hoyakalu hoyaknu wkahwakanu.
Hiyrun-koxa wpoyikowata salewaktshi tshinanu klu tshinanu wimatlu salewaktshikni hasruklu yineru kahwakachatatshri rixinripa.
Hoyakalu hikchikhihlenutlu salewaktshi wakotachaxyawaka hiyáhoni Hoyakalu hikchikhihlenreru tshinanu Hoyakalu hihlenu wkahwakanu.
Hiyrunu hi wmahijeruchata xye wkahwakle tshinanu. Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu wajkaka hipkaklu ramotlewle Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru, Hoyakalu henekachale tshinanu.
Klu tshinanu hi wumukata hepixlexnawa, wumtuknu tshinanu hiyáhoni rapokpapkoluxinixka Cristo hipnapatka hixa tshinanu.
Kyaprehetkolu satu yineru haluk-hipnalexyawaka satu yineru kachrijru rixyawakapa. Rumukata hiphujewnaleta satu yineru rupniywaka satu yineru kihleru hkachrihyawakapa.
Seyni Hoyakalu wla rixa hekhiretlu hi pa hamotlekananu rixwu klu tshinanu hektune wixakanaxiniwa Cristo hipnapa hixa kachrijru.
Hiyáhoni Cristo tshinanu hi wetanru Hoyakalu hapnokatlewle klu tshinanu Cristo hraha hiyokle tshinanu wpowratka Hoyakaluya.
Wkamnitmaklu Hoyakalu seyni rimatletawawu hituru hipnal-tshinanu. Rimatletatkawu hiyáhoni wane pnuteyaka wiwekkakko Cristo hiwekle tshinanu.
Hi wale tsonni seyni xawakni koxa wumuwata Hoyakalu tshinanu hiyrunu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Woyakalute Jesus Cristo tshinanu. Klu tshinanu Jesus Cristo tshinanu wimatletatnaklu Hoyakalu.
Adão, Cristo PiranapniHektuntshi jihlokatkalu xye tshijne satupka jeji majnákonu tshinanu. Hiyrunu hektuntshi yma rapokatka hipuktshi. Wale tshinanu ptowru yineru hipnanu klu tshinanu ptowru yineru hektuwatatka.
Hma mapokkanuklunuwa Moisés yonreru rawakanatakotka hektuntshi. Seyni hanukta hi rawa yonruru yine hi himathetlu hektuntshi.
Hiykolu mwaknu pchinika Adão-ni haté Moisés-ni klu papko hipuktshi hiykole yine towutakanatatka. Wan-rixa towutletkanatkana Adão-ni hektunu pixka mixkannitka Adão-ni hinatshripa yaholuni.
Seyni Hoyakalu henekachale hi Adão-ni hektunu pixka rixa. Halikaka ptowru yine hipna satupka yineru hektunu tshinanu. Seyni Hoyakalu ramotle renekachalewaxya tsru mixkon-potukni klu tshinanu ptowru nerukmaka henekka riwejyawakapna satupka yineru tshinanu. Walekni Jesus Cristo.
Hiyrunu Hoyakalu ramotle henekachalewaxya hi satni yinern-hektunu pixka rixa. Satupka majnákonu tshinanu rapokatka jikolukanuru seyni hix-potuko hektuntshi wkatanuko rapokatka ptowru hektuntshi hiknokatshri hiyrunu renekachalewat-koxa.
Halikakni satupka yineru majnákonu tshinanu hipuktshi towutlewata. Seyni hakanhatshritka satupka yineru tshinanu, Jesus Cristo hektuntshi yohnik-himukatatshrini. Klu tshinanu ptowru neruko Hoyakalu hihlenu yoptotatshine, Hoyakalu henekachale potukatlewatatshri yoptotatshine pohirewnanu Cristo pixkonu tshinanu.
Satupka jeji majnakowaxyalu Hoyakalu hiyáhoni hixolunni hektune rixkakatka. Seyni satupkani yineru kajnakolu Hoyakaluya hiyáhoni hixolune hihletko.
Moisés yonreru hakanhatka rekhixyawaklu hektuntshi hektupotuko rixyawaka. Seyni hektuntshi hallikanaxinixka Hoyakalu hiknojyawaklu hektuntshi koxa mixkowatatka.
Hektuntshi mitshikananu hipuktshiyma towutatkawu. Seyni Hoyakalu mixkowata hektuntshi ruknojyawaka yine tshinanu. Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu hiknojyawaklu hektuntshi himukata hihleretna yine Hoyakaluya. Xye hiwekkaklewata hiweklu hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa Jesus Cristo Wutsrukateya.
Hektuntshi Hi Towutlu Cristo MunanhatshriHa hkahwaklu wan-hixini yohnik-kihle hixyawaka wektuwatanu waneya Hoyakalu pnute powratachatanwu?
Hike, hikeklu! Klu tshinanu hektuntshi hetanuya hipnatshine pixka hixatshinetkawu hanhe xawaka wixa himukata hwaletanutnaklu hektuntshi?
Hi he hichiniklu w-batiza-tkoklunu Cristo Jesus hipnale wyima? Hiyáhoni Cristo Jesus hipnale w-batiza-xikatka.
W-batiza-tkoklunu Cristo kapnaxikolu wyimatka, hatatjewa waleyma wupnatka. Hiyrunu Cristo hiwekatnaka hipuktshiya Hirtshi hoyaknu tshinanu hiyáhoni wale pixkonu herotu hiweklu henek-koxwu hixa.
Cristo hipnatka hiyáhoni hatatjewa hix-koxa hipnatka waleyma. Cristo hiwekatnaka hiyáhoni hix-koxa hiwekanu Cristo-yma.
Hiyáhoni wimatanru wiwekle mitshikawlurni hipnanatka Cristo-yma cruz-ya hnikawniywakapa hektuntshi mixkonu, hektuntshi mtowuxyawakanupwu.
Klu tshinanu hektuntshi hi himukata towutletlu hipnatshritka.
Waneya Cristo-yma wupninixka, wimata waleyma wiwekanu.
Cristo hipuktshi hiwekkajikatka hiyrunu wimatlu Cristo hi himukata hipnaleta hiyrunukotnaka. Xawakni hipuktshi hi himukata kachretlu Cristo.
Hiyáhoni rupninixka Cristo, rupnatka pa katapka hektuntshi mixkonu hkonyawaka hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa tshinanu. Seyni Cristo hiweka hiyrunu hpaklu hiwekleta Hoyakaluya.
Wane pixka potuko hixanu hixa. Hipnatshinetka hkahwajinwa hektuntshi mixkonu tshinanu seyni hiwekatshinephi Hoyakaluyma Cristo Jesus tshinanu.
Hiyáhoni hi hitshitanru hektuntshi towuxyawaklu himane moyakatu, himane het-sotanre hma kamhiywakanupa.
Hiyrun-koxa hi henekanru himane psojite hektuntshi towuxyawaklu, muhlentshi kamhatshri rixyawaka. Seyni henejinwa Hoyakaluya hatatjewa hipnakanatatshine pixka hixa seyni xawakni hiwekatshinetkahi. Hiyáhoni himane psojite Hoyakalu henejinri kihleru kamhatshri rixyawakapa.
Hi hetachatanru hektuntshi towuxyawakhi klu tshinanu htowutjeru hi Moisés yonreru seyni Hoyakalu hihlenu tsonu halikaka towutanhi.
Potukatlewatatshri Towutanru PiranapniHa xawakni? Wektuwatewhe klu tshinanu yonruru hi towutwu seyni Hoyakalu henekachale yoptotatshinwu wixyawaka tshinanu? Hike, hikeklu wane wixanu.
Hixa himatlu katukta henejinwa towrertshi rixikowaka rujhalu hyijnakoxyawaklu htowutjeru. Hiyáhoni hixa hijhalu hkamhiywaklu htowutjeru towuxyahi. Hektuntshi towuxinhi hipuktshi hkayatanu seyni kajnako hixini Hoyakaluya, hiyáhoni hihletko Hoyakaluya.
Seyni poyahnu Hoyakalu! Klu tshinanu mitshikananu hektuntshi towutjekanathi seyni wkatanuko hixa homkahitatkalu psol-mixkonuyako halikakalutu pirana Hoyakalu hiykole pirana hixa henejikolu.
Hixa hektuntshi towuxyawakhi hkochpajika hiyáhoni hpotukaxikolu pirana towutjethi.
Yineru pixka ntshina, yine hchinikanu hihrokle tshinanu. Mitshikawni hixa mpotukanhi hixapa hiyrunu hektutu hyijnakjekanata, ptowru hixatshri hektutu hkamhajekanaxyawaka. Hiyáhoni xawakni waneko pixka hixanu henejinwa psoluyako potukatlewlu pirana towuxyawakhi, kihleru hkamhiywakapa.
Hixa hektuntshi towrerune hixjekanaxiniklunu hi yijnakjekanatlu potukal-towutlewle pirana.
Klunerhe xawaka repixatkahi kapatmenuru hkamhajekanaxini? Wan-hixatshri kamhatshri kayatanru hipuktshi.
Seyni xawakni Hoyakalu kochpakatkahi hektuntshi mtowuxyawakanutkahi. Hiyáhoni hixa kayatatkalu hiwejikaluru hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa.
Klu tshinanu hektuntshi wenru walekni hipuktshi. Seyni Hoyakalu henekachale hiwekluni hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa Wutsrukate, Jesus Cristo-ya.
Hnunrowlu Yapkakle PiranapniCristo tshinanu nmoletanune, hixa Moisés yonreru himatheta. Hiyáhoni hixa himatkoxlu Moisés yonreru homkahitatshine tsonu rumukata towutleta.
Klu tshinanu suxo thanuru hiwekka pchinika hi titshitka thanuru tuchoxyawaka. Seyni rupninipa thanuru, Moisés yonreru towre tuchpajyatka.
Seyni satuko thanuruxini riwekka pchinika thanuru Moisés yonreru wan-tshina, timopatlewata. Seyni rupninixka thanuru waneya tuchpajyatkalu Moisés yonreru. Hiyáhoni hi himopatlewatatshrotkani, satu thanuruxini.
Klu tshinanu wimane halujyawaka womkahjekanaxiniklunu, hektuntshi het-sotanrewle mixkowatatka wimaneya, yonruru tshinanu. Wkamrure hipuktshi renekwu.
Seyni xawakni yonruru hi towutjetwu klu tshinanu wupniyatkalu Moisés yonreru wkachikanatjeru. Xawakni wumukata homkahretlu Hoyakalu, herotu hiwejikaluruya. Waleni Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru towutlewleya. Hi mitshikananu yonruru womkahjekanatanru womkahitatka mitshikananu pixka.
Hiykolu Yonatkaluru Hiphujexyawaklu Hektuntshi PiranapniHa xawakni hanhe wtshinanu? Wlalhe wtshinanu, Yonruru hetko hektuntshi? Hike, hikeklu! Seyni Moisés yonreru tshinanu nimathetlu hektuntshi. Himka nimatatkalu het-sotanuhonutshi, Moisés yonreru wane hma tshinkanumka: “Hi pet-sotanrewatanu.”
Yonruru tshinanu hektuntshi hikchiklu ptowru hixatshri het-sotanuhonutshi rekhixyawakno. Klu tshinanu yonruru mwaknumka hi kmixkonru hektuntshi.
Hetanno hita, mitshikananu yonruru hi nimatyehitatka seyni niwekatka. Seyni nimatyehixinixkalu hiykolu pirana, rakanhahapkatatka hektuntshi.
Waneya nupnapatka. Hiyáhoni hiykolu hiphujewnal-tshinanu, hipuktshimka renekno.
Hiykolu tshinanu hektuntshi hikchikatkalu hyokwijexyawakno. Hiyáhoni hiykolu tshinanu hektuntshi hiylatapno.
Hiyáhoni halikakni Moisés yonreru kihleru potukalni hiyrun-koxa hiykolu potukalni, halikakni, kihlerni.
Hiyáhoni wkahwakhe hiykolu kihleru rumukata hipuktshi henekletno? Hike, hikeklu! Seyni hektuntshi kamrurni wale. hektuntshi kihleru hyapa ruylaxyawakapno rimathetka hanu potu rixa hektuntshi. Hiyáhoni hiykolu tshinanu hektuntshi hekhixnawa hektuntshi hektupotukananu rixyawaka.
Klu tshinanu wimatlu Moisés yonreru Hoyakalu runya seyni hitni xye tshiji hichpajikatshrino hektuntshi towreru nixapa.
Hi nimatjemlu nkamhajetanru klu tshinanu naluka kamhaletanru hi nkamha seyni neyiklewle nkamha.
Hiyáhoni nmalukanutuko nkamhajeta, nuphujtatanru Moisés yonreru kihleru rixyawaka.
Hiyahokni hi hita kamhalu seyni halikaka hektuntshi nimwaleruko kamhalu.
Klu tshinanu nimatlu hita hitokote hikeni kihleru, walekni, nomane hi rawa kihleru. Klu tshinanu hitamka haluka kihleru nkamhiywaka seyni hi nkamhalu.
Hiyáhoni kihlerumka hi nkamha seyni halikaka hektutu nma malukanutuko nkamha.
Hiyáhoni nkamhinri wale nma malukanutu hi hita kamhalu seyni hektuntshi hita hitokote hwatshriko kamhalu.
Hiyáhoni nukchiklu xye yonruru, kihleru naluka kamhalexinimka hektutu tsonu nnureta.
Nohchinikanuyma nuphujetlu Hoyakalu yonreru kihleru.
Seyni netlu satuko yonruru nomaneya ntowutjeru. Walekni kamnijetlu yonruru nohchinikanu hikchikhihlenutanru. Yonruru kamnitatshri walekni hektuntshi ntowutjeru hiyáhoni hektuntshi hosturerno.
Kwamonurpotukno! Katnihe nepixjeru xye nomane hipuktshi heneklewatatshri tshinanu?
Npoyahnutanru Hoyakalu niwekkakjeru Jesus Cristo wutsrukate tshinanu. Waneya nohchinikanuyma ntowutjeru waleni Hoyakalu yonreru seyni nomane towutatshri waleni hektuntshi yokanreru.
Kajnakopwu Xako Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru PiranayaHiyáhoni Cristo Jesus munanhalene hi hjihyehitkona Hoyakaluya.
Hiwejikaluru hiykole Cristo Jesus tshinanuya, hiwekkaklewatatshri kochpakno hektuntshi towre pixkonuya hiyrunu hipuktshi heneklewatatshri pixkonuy-koxa.
Moisés yonreru hi kmixkonu klu tshinanu hektuntshi hihrokahchinikankaklewatatshri himaletlewata. Seyni Hoyakalu hituruko hyokanatatka yineru hektuntshi hwaleru pixka rixyawakapa hektuntshi hkamnixyawakapa hiyáhoni ruylatlu hektuntshi yineru mane hwatshri.
Hiyáhoni Moisés yonreru potukalu wpoyahokaka, wale hiykole wkamhiywaka, hixako walujyawaka wma kamhiywakanupa seyni Hiwejikaluru halujyawaka wkamhiywakapni.
Katukta waleko ralujyawaka homkahita waleko hihchinikanu towutanru. Seyni katukta Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru halujyawaka homkahita Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hchinikanu towutanru.
Klu tshinanu hixako wihchinikanu towuxinwu, hipuktshipni seyni Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hiwekluni hiyrunu hapnanuhchinikanru reneklewata.
Hiyáhoni waleko ralujyawaka kamhatshri Hoyakalu hkamnita. Klu tshinanu wan-hixatshri hi yijnakotlu Hoyakalu yonreru. Halikaka wan-hixatshri hi himukata homkahretlu Hoyakalu.
Yineru waleko ralujyawaka romkahixini hi rumukata poyikowkakletlu Hoyakalu.
Hiyáhoni Cristo hixa hitokote hwini, wimane hipnatka hektuntshi tshinanu halikaka Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hiwekkaklewata. Klu tshinanu Cristo potukatatkawu Hoyakaluya.
Hixa hitokote rawini Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru, Jesus manni hiwekkakjeru, Cristo mane hiwekkakatshri hix-manen-koxa riwekkakanu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru tshinanu hixa hitokote hwatshri.
Hiyáhoni Cristo tshinanu nmoletanune, towutkalunwu seyni hi hixako halujyawaka wtowuxika.
Klu tshinanu hixako halujyawaka hkamhinipa, hipnanu; seyni Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru mixkonuyma hixa hiylaxinri hektuntshi himane hwatshri, hiwekanu.
Klu tshinanu ptowrunek-yine Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru kosekanna, Hoyakalu whenene rixyawakna tshinanna.
Klu tshinanu Hiwejikaluru honra Hoyakalu henekanwu, hi jhamleholune rixkakanwu. Seyni Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru wan-hixkakwu Hoyakalu whenene wixyawaka. Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru pixkonu tshinanuya hipokananu wane wtshinanu: Hirtshi! Nuru!
Hiyrunu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hixa wiwejinri repixa wla wtshinyawaka Hoyakalu whenenetkawu.
Hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu whenene wixini, wyoptotanru Hoyakalu himwaleru. Cristo-yma wyoptotanru. Halikaka Cristo pixka wixa salewnalexini wimatan-koxa Hoyakalu hoyaknu wyoptotanu Cristo pixka wixa yoptoletanru.
Hoyakalu Hoyaknu Wyoptotanrupa PiranapniKlu tshinanu nimatlu salewaktshi xye hohnekaka hwatshri hi hpoyaho yapkakletletlu hoyaknutshi hix-yehi hakanhikatshripa.
Ptowru potuko Hoyakalu kamhaleru chiretmaklu rakanhiywakna Hoyakalu whenene.
Klu tshinanu ptowruka Hoyakalu kamhaleru hiprotakatka moyakatu rixyawakatka, hi waleko ralujyawaka tshinanni seyni Hoyakalu haluklu wan-rixyawaka. Klu tshinanu rawa xye kahwakachalupa:
pa hohnepa ptowru Hoyakalu kamhaleru kochpakko moyaknutshi mtowuxyawakanuplu. Waneya ruchotkoklunpatka kihler-potuko hkayatanna, Hoyakalu whenene kayatanrupa.
Klu tshinanu wimatlu haté xawakni ptowru Hoyakalu kamhaleru hotshhita tsru katshinoluyma hatatjewa mturu tshino hjemna.
Hi Hoyakalu kamhaleru msamenrutu tsonu hotshhita seyni hix-koxa wan-hixa. Hiwejikaluru Potukalu Hoyakalu henekachale himwatshinwu. Wotshhita hitoko maneya haté Hoyakalu hali wan-hixlexinipwu wale whenenepotpakotkawu. Waleni wimane hiwekkajikol-potuko.
Wiwekkakka kahwakachaluya seyni wexinpatkalu wkahwakakanatanru hi wkahwakanutkalu. Klu tshinanu kathe kahwakachatanru retanru?
Seyni wma metkanuklunru wkahwakachaleru, wkahwakachatanru.
Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru Hanjihohnere PiranapniHoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hepixjetwu klu tshinanu himka wimata klunerukta wanjita. Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluruko hapohchinikanutlu Hoyakalu hixa tshinanu. Tsru hotshhiruyma ranjitlu Hoyakalu haté tokantshi hi poyaho yanumleta.
Hoyakalu himathethajitlu yineru. Hiyrunu Hoyakalu himatlu Hiwejikaluru hchinikanu. Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru, Hoyakalu halujyawak-potuko ranjijetlu Hoyakalu, Hoyakalu kotspalatanune tshinanu.
Wimatlu ptowru potuyako Hoyakalu kamrurewata hixa hihlenu tshinanu, ptowrunek-yine Hoyakalu hamotatshine, Hoyakalu nurrenni. Hoyakalu nuretatkana waleko hkamrure hkamhiywaka tshinanupna.
Hoyakalu himathetatkana nuretkalunepa xye tshiji hiyakotkoklunu pnutekananuko. Hiyrunu hnuretna hituru pixka rixyawakapna hiyáhoni Jesus himukata mitshikananu matutatshri rixyawaka himolene hixolune tskalaya.
Hoyakalu hitakna hituru pixka rixyawakapna hiyrunu wanna koxa hnureta. Hiyrun-koxa hnurrene hpotukatatka. Hiyrunu potukatkalunetka royaknu reneka.
Hoyakalu Hamoxyawakwu Jesus Tshinanu PiranapniHiyáhoni hanhe wtshina xye chinikantshi tshinanu? Hoyakalu hixa sreta hwini, kathe xawaka himukata kamniretwu?
Hoyakalu hi tshipetawheneta seyni hyokanatlu hixa ptowrunekwu tshinanu. Hiyáhoni hi he Jesus-yma renekanunwu ptowru potuko?
Kathe xawaka himukata kahekletna Hoyakalu nurrene? Hikeni klu tshinanu Hoyakalukni potukatatkana.
Kathe xawaka jihyehitwu? Hikeni, klu tshinanu Cristo Jesus hipnapatka waneya riwekatka hipnatshine tskalaya. Hiyáhoni xawakni Hoyakalu potukle sreta rawa, hixa tshinanu Hoyakalu ranjita hipokananu.
Rawhe xawaka satu Cristo hamotle konatshri? Rumukathe kojwawnalu, ho kojwakahchinikanutatshri, ho kamnirewlu, ho natshitatshri, ho mamkatu ho kyowikolu ho hinokakaklu hamlenrahe himukata hitspalkakletlu Hoyakalu hamotlewle?
Hiyahokni wane htshina yonatkaluru: “Hoyakalu, pixa hiwaka tshinanu ptowru hohneruka hipuktshi hamlenu wwa. Carneiro pixka hiylatkalunepwu.”
Seyni xyekaka yohnik-hiknohatshinwu wamotjeru tshinanu.
Hiyáhoni nimatlu hi hipuktshiko, hi hiwekluko, hi hiwejikalurune Hoyakalu towrene tenhohne hajeneko, hi kamtshineko, hi xawakniko, hi hinatshripako, hi towretshriko,
Hoyakalu Hiyrunu Yine Malixlena PiranapniCristo himatlu halikaka pirana ntshina. Hi nweyawata. Nohchinikan-koxa hiphujtatno Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluruya hi nweyawata.
Wane nixa. Nwamonuwpotuta. Katshino hajno ptowru hohnekananuko.
Repixkamkanna nomolene hitamka hiknokakjixinwa Cristo yehiya, nonerune nomane nmoletshinine tshinanu.
Wannani israel-nerune Hoyakalu nurrene hiwhenene rixyawakna. Hoyakalu hoyaknu hetatshinetka hiyrunu wale ptowruka Hoyakalu hinkaklexyana himwatshinetka. Hoyakalu henekatkana Moisés yonreru pirana hiyrunu Hoyakalu rimalwuxyawakna renekna. Waneyna Hoyakalu hinkaklexyana.
Hitsrukatshinnixkani wannani Cristo molennixkani himaneyna. Waleni Hoyakalu ptowru potuko towutatshri. Himalwutkalurni wale ptowru hohnekananuko mnikawnakatupni. Amém.
Hoyakalu Ptowru Potuko Towutatshri Rixyawaka PiranapniHimka hmahijer-tokanutatka Hoyakalu israel-nerune tshinanu. Seyni hi ptowru israel-nerune Hoyakalunerune potuko hixnawa.
Hiyrun-koxa hi ptowru Abraão-ni klopichane halikaka Hoyakalu whenene hixnawa klu tshinanu Hoyakalu wan-tshinru Abraão-ni: “Piklopichane potuko Isaque klopichanepni ntshina hinkaklexyawakatkayi pixka.”
Hiyáhoni hi ptowru Abraão-ni klopichane Hoyakalu whenene hixnawa. Seyni Hoyakalu whenen-potuko wannakni wanna ptowruneka Hoyakalu whenenepa Hoyakalu Abraão-ni hinkaklexinritka.
Hoyakalu wan-tshina hinkakletniru Abraão-ni: “Rapokpapkoluxinipa nsatokanu waneya Sara jeji matkakanu.”
Hiyrunu hi wale tsonupni seyni Rebeca wuhenetanna hepi, pa hirupkana, waleni wutsrukatni Isaque-ni.
<sup>(11-12)</sup> Waneya hi hmatutawana hepi mturune seyni Hoyakalu wan-tshinatkalo Rebeca: “Hepurtshi towutanru tsrujru.” Hiyrunu mturune hi kihleru hi hektutuko hkamhawana. Seyni Hoyakalu wan-tshina hnurrerupni waleko ralukanru hnurrene rixyawakapna. Hnuretka klu tshinanu Hoyakaluko tomhanru, hi jejiko hkamrure tshinanni.
(-)
Wane htshinyawaka yonatkaluru: “Jacó namota seyni Esaú nahnanuta.”
Hoyakalu Hetwamonrewle PiranapniHanhe wtshinanu xye tshinanu? Hoyakallahe mpotukatu? Hike, hikeklu!
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu wan-tshinru Moisés: “Nepixanru katuktako naluk-hepixleta hiyrunu katuktako naluk-hetwamonreta, netwamonutanru.”
Hiyáhoni Hoyakaluko nuretanru katukta raluk-hetwamonreta. Waneya Hoyakalu nuretanrupa hi yine kamrure hi yineru halujyawaka tshinanu.
Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru wan-tshinru Faraó Egito pohire: “Xye tshinanu nutakyi phuru pixyawaka, npixkonu nuphujetanru pixa tshinanu hiyáhoni nhiwaka pohitko psol-tshijneyako.”
Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu hetwamonutlu katukta raluk-hetwamonreta seyni katukta raluka chikhajiwkakleta, hchikhajiwkaklu.
Hkamhaleru Hi Hallitanru Hoyakalu PiranapniHiyáhoni satu wan-tshininno: “Klu tshinanhe hkahekwuna? Kathe himaletlu Hoyakalu halujyawaka?”
Seyni pixa yineruchayi. Hanhe xawaka pixa kahekletlu Hoyakalu? Hachhaji kamhakaluru hi kaheklu hkamhakjeru wane htshinyawaka: Klu tshinanhe wane pixa kamhaletno? hi htshina.
Hi he rumukata kkamhakleru wale jpako kamhalexyalu satu kihleru, satu hektutu?
Wan-rixa Hoyakalu. Rahkalene ralpokohnaputatka ramhiywakapna Hoyakalu tsru hakotlu rixachakananyehitna klu tshinanu Hoyakalu haluk-hekhirexnawa hjihekannu, yine himukata hetlexyawakaplu hpixkonu.
Hkahwakhohnekanatna Hoyakalu yine, retwamonre yoptotatshinepa tshinanu rekhixyawakna royaknu tsrur-potuko tshinanu. Nyi yine Hoyakalu halpokotatka royaknu yoptotatshinepa.
Nyi yine htshanixlene hixakni. Hi judeu-nerune tsonni seyni judeu mixkan-koxa htshanixatka Hoyakalu.
Wane htshina yonawahlo Oseias-mta: “Wanna nonerune mixkanekananu, nonerune ntshinanna. Hiyrunu nma mamotakanatanutu nalukanru ntshinanru.”
Mitshikananu wla htshinanwakatka: “Hixa hi nonerunhi seyni wanepnawaka Hoyakalu Hiwekatshri whenene htshinkona.”
Hiyrunu Isaías-ni wla tshinanwakatna israel-nerune, hipokananu wane htshina: “Yáholu hixpotpakhi, ksatuji mar powha hwatshri pejnuphi seyni satkaka tsonu hiwekkakko.
Klu tshinanu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hi hix-hohne hkahwakanu hkamrure psoluka ralixyawaka seyni hnikathapkatanru.”
Wane potuko htshinnitka Isaías-ni: “Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu ptowru potuko himukatatshrini, hma mixetkanumka satkaka klopicha waneyamka Sodoma, Gomorra poktshinni pixka hixatshinemkapwu.”
Seyni israel-nerune yahot-homkahretmakluna Moisés yonreru pirana hpotukaxnamkawana Hoyakalu yhaleya seyni hpupjetna.
Haklu tshinanhe wan-rixna? Klu tshinanu hi halixlu hmunanhatkana hpotukaxyawakna seyni rujhaluna Hoyakalu yhaleya hpotukaxnawakwana Moisés yonreru pirana romkahre tshinanu phutna. Hiyáhoni rutspetanna sotlu hitspetkaluru pixka.
Wane htshina Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru: “Sião poktshi nutakanru sotlu hitspetkaluru, sotlu yawnakaklewatatshri seyni xye sotlu munanhatshripa hi hmahijerutanu.”
Judeu-nerune Hi Halixlu Hpowraxikowakna PiranapniNomolene, hitamka psoluka nmixkonuyma nalukmaklu nonerune hiwekkajikowaka. Wanna nanjiyehjeta Hoyakaluya.
Klu tshinanu nuphujtatlu judeu-nerune yapretakmaklu Hoyakalu halujyawaka hkamhiywakna. Ralukmakna seyni hi rimatyehpotutluna Hoyakalu.
Hi rimatjemluna hanu rixa potukatletna Hoyakalu yine hiyáhoni hmunanhiynawana yine Hoyakalu hihlenu hpoyahokajyawakna. Ruknokluna Hoyakalu powratlewle pirana.
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu hitneprijyatkalu Moisés yonreru pirana Cristo tshinanu hiyáhoni ptowru Cristo halixatshinepa himukata powratletka Hoyakalu hetanuya.
Klu tshinanu Moisés yonatlu Moisés yonreru pirana homkahitatshri powraxikowaka pirana, wla htshina: “Yonruru homkahitatshri riwekkako romkahle tshinanu.”
Seyni Hoyakalu powratanru yineru ralixle tshinanu wane htshina yonatkaluru: “Hi pepomhinwa: Kathe tenhohne hatskotanu?” Waleni hwapkalurupa tshijiya Cristo tenhohne hajeruya.
“Hi pepomhan-koxa: Kathe serpikanu haté tshiji hitokote?” Wale piranni Cristo hatskokakatshripa hipnatshine tskalaya.
Seyni wla htshina yonatkaluru: “Hi howuklu tokantshi. Pinama rawa, paj-koxa rawa.” Walekni tokantshi halixlu pirana, wunkakletanru pirana.
Wane ptshininri pinamaya, “Jesus Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hixyawaka” ptshinini hiyrunu palixinri pajiya Hoyakalu hiwekkajyawaklu Jesus, piwekkakko.
Klu tshinanu walixinri wajiya, Hoyakalu potukatwu. Winamayma wunkakletlu Cristo walixyawaka hiyáhoni wiwekkakka.
Klu tshinanu wane htshina Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru: “Ptowru yineru wale munanhatshri hi hmahijerutanu.”
Yonatkaluru wan-tshina ‘ptowru yineru’ wane htshina klu tshinanu hi rawa kakojeru, yáholu judeu-neru, yáholu judeu mixkatu. Walerutu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu rutsrukatetna hiyrunu Hoyakalu hihlehchinikanutna ptowru yineru hanunektako munanhinri.
Wane htshina yonatkaluru: “Katukta hanjitlu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu riwekkakko.”
Seyni hanhe rixa hanjiretanruna Tsru Hixikatshriwa Cristo hma malixkanuklunruna? Hanhe xawaka rixa himukatle halixletluna hma yijnakpiranyehitanutna? Hanu rixa yijnakoletanruna hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana hike munkakkanuklunna?
Satu hinkaklewatatshri myokanatkonuklunu, hanhe xawaka rixa himukata hinkaklewleta? Wane htshina yonatkaluru: “Hi pa hihlen-jixikananuktana kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana hihlehchinikanrewatatshri pirana hinkakletatshine!”
Israel-nerune Majnákonu Wannako Htshinanna PiranapniSeyni hi ptowru israel-neru halixatkalu kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana. Klu tshinanu Isaías yonreru wan-tshina: “Ha, Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu, kathe halixlu wunkakle?”
Hiyáhoni kihler-potuko tokantshi jemikowaka ruchpajini halixlu. Hiyrunu yine jemanru kihler-potuko tokantshi satu hinkaklexinri Cristo pirana.
Seyni nepomhanhi: Hi he hyijnakotluna kihler-potuko tokantshi? Hehe, hyijnakotmakluna wane htshinyawaka yonatkaluru: “Psol-tshijneko hpohiwaxya runkaklena. Htokanna haté xye tshijne mahahijhakalur-potuko rapokhimata.”
Seyni wane ntshinatnaka: Ha israel-nerune, hi he xawaka rimatjematkaluna? Mitshikananhapka Moisés wan-tshina: “Hita het-sotankakanhi yine hike mkahwakpiratkane hetanuya. Pahnanutkolunephi pa nerune mchinikanune tshinanu.”
Hiyrunu Isaías hi pika wane htshinyawaka: “Nukchikna nma mujhanuneko hiyrunu nakanhayehitna nma mepomhayehitanuneko.”
Seyni israel-nerune pirana Isaías wan-tshinyehitna: “Psol-hohneruka naluk-himatletletmakna yine hektune, chikohajirune.”
Hoyakalu Hetwamonuxyawakna Israel-neru PiranapniHiyáhoni wane ntshina: Hiyáhola Hoyakalu hiknokachatna hinerune potuko? Hike, hikeklu, hi psojikna ruknojikna. Klu tshinanu hit-koxa israel-ner-potukno, Abraão-ni klopichno, Benjamim-nerno.
Hoyakalu hi koxa ruknokachatanna hinerune hnurrene mitshikawlune. Hixa himatlu wane htshina Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru Elias-ni tshinyawaka, Hoyakalu rapohchinikanuta israel-nerune tshinanu:
“Ha Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu, ruylatkana ptokanu hinkakletatshinni hiyrunu altar-kaka hyotkakna. Hita tsonu hitukatka hiyrunu xawakni hit-koxa raluk-hiylaletna.”
Waneya hanhe htshin-hihretniru Hoyakalu? Wla htshina Hoyakalu: “Waneyawano sete mil yine Baal momkahitkane.”
Waneko pixka rixna haté xawakni rawna yine hi híxona Hoyakalu nurrene Hoyakalu hihlenu nuretanune.
Ha xawakni hanhe wtshinanu? Israel-nerune hijhalermaka hi rukchikluna seyni Hoyakalu nurrene hikchiklu. Hiyáhoni pimrine chikohajiwata.
Wane htshina yonatkaluru: “Hoyakalu hixkajyawakna chikohajiwatatshine rixyawakna, mchinikanune rixyawakna hiyáhoni haté xawakni kayhalmakna seyni hi retna hiyrunu kajnakmakna seyni hi hyijnakotna.”
Hiyrun-koxa Davi-ni wla tshinnixka: “Wla hixkalunepni nikjexikowaka hkachixikona hiyrunu hyokwijetkona; hiyrun-koxa rallitkonna, rapnokatkonna.
Ruchyayhaletkana hma mexyawakanupna; hiyrunu hi kmixkonutskijinapna hsaptshohikanuna kojwaklewlu tshinanu.”
Hma Muchopotuxikowakanna Judeu-ne PiranapniWaneya wane ntshin-hepomhalethi: Ha judeu-nerune, hpupjerna tshinanrahe ruknokkana? Hike, hikeklu. Seyni hpupjerna tshinanu hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana hakanhayehitatkana judeu-nerune minje. Hiyáhoni judeu-nerune het-sotanutna judeu mixkane.
Hiyáhoni judeu-nerune pupjere wan-hixkaklu Hoyakalu hihlehchinikanre hapokanwakatna xye tshiji hajene hixolune. Judeu-nerune hamtakleru rukchikatkana judeu mixkane. Waleni Hoyakalu pohirewle. Hiyáhoni rehchinikanuxiniklunpatkana judeu-nerune yohnikpatkalu Hoyakalu pohirewle wanna yehiya.
Hixa nunkaka, judeu mixkanhi. Hit-honra nuretkalurno judeu mixkane tshinanu hiyáhoni nuslahpotutlu nkamrure.
Hiyáhoni pa katako numukata het-sotankakletanna nomolene, nonerune. Hiyáhoni pa katako Hoyakalu satkaka wanna hiwekkakanu nkamrure tshinanu.
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu hiknokanutkana judeu-nerune, rimatletatkana psol-tshijne hajeneko. Ha xawakni, hanu rixkonna judeu-nerunepni rimatlexikowakpatnaka Hoyakaluya? Wla rixkona, hipnatshinetka hiwekkakko.
Hijpa psojite Hoyakalunu rixini hiyáhoni psolujpako Hoyakalunni. Hiyrun-koxa hahmuna tskihi Hoyakalunu rixini waneya hiplukak-koxa Hoyakalunni.
Hatatjewa oliveira muna hislahluro plukaka kastakka. Waneya hixa judeu mixkanhi hatatjewa oliveira muna kahnete hwatshri pixka hixatshinhi waleplu kastajikolu hislahkaluru muna yokakkalunetkahi. Hiyáhoni hixa yoptotlu judeu-nerune mixkonu hiyrunu riweklena.
Hiyáhoni hi halixkoxinwa klu tshinanu hiplukakachanhi. Hixa hi hiwekkaklu hitskihi seyni halikaka hitskihi hiwekkakhi hixa.
Seyni hixa pa katako wane htshina: Hehemka seyni hislahkaluru plukaka kastakkatka wale ptaklu hyokakkatka hixa.
Hichiniklu xawaka judeu-nerune kastakaplutka klu tshinanu hmalixlenna tshinanni. Seyni hixa wane hyokakkatka halixle tshinanu. Hiyáhoni hi halixkoxinwa seyni halikaka hpikanu.
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu hi hetachatatkana judeu-nerune hiplukak-potu pixka hixatshine seyni rapnokatatkana. Hiyáhoni hixlahe kahwaklu Hoyakalu hi hapnokatanhi hix-koxa? Wane.
Hislahanu hanu potu rixa Hoyakalu. Kchinikanru seyni kapnokatle koxlu. Wale hapnokatanunna hektuwaka kamhatshinepni seyni hixa tshinanu kchinikanurni, Hoyakalu hchinikanu homkahixini. Wane hmixkanuklununapa hix-koxapni kastakkona.
Hiyrun-koxa judeu-nerune hichoxiniplu hmalixlenna ruchpajyawakna munako hyokakkotnakna klu tshinanu Hoyakalu kpixkonru hyokajyawakpatnakna.
Hixa judeu mixkanhi hatatjewa oliveira muna kahnete hwatshri plu kastajikolu oliveira muna hislahkaluru yokakkalune pixka hixatshinetkahi. Hi he xawaka myapretpotni Hoyakalu yokajyawaklu wale munako hyokakapluxyawakatnaka?
Israel-nerune Hiwekkajikolu PiranapniCristo tshinanu nmoletanune, naluklu hixa himaxyawaklu pa pirana yohimluru pirana. Himaxyawakaplu hi ptowru potuko himatawa. Judeu-nerune hi ptowru hohnekananuko chikohajirunepni seyni wan-rixachatna judeu-ne judeu mixkane hma poyahokajiknu pchinikwana hi ralixanna judeu-ne.
Waneya wane pnute ptowru judeu-neru hiwekkakko klu tshinanu wane htshina yonatkaluru: “Hiwekkaklewatatshri Sião poktshi ruchpajini, waleko hektuntshi konanu Jacó klopichaneya.”
Hiyrunu wane htshina Hoyakalu: “Ntshinyawak-potuko nixanu. Rektunna nkoninna.”
Judeu-nerune hiknokatkalu kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana hiyáhoni Hoyakalu kamnitna, hixa judeu mixkanhi hpoyaho hepixlexyawakapa. Seyni Hoyakalu nurexyawaka tshinanna, Hoyakalu himatletatkana judeu-ne, rutsrukatenna tshinanu.
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu hi yokmakahchinikanyehitlu katuktako raluka nurreta hiyrunu katuktako raluk-hihlehchinikanyehreta, hi hyokmakahchinikanuta.
Seyni hixa judeu mixkanhi mitshikananu majnakowaxyatkalu Hoyakalu. Seyni judeu-nerune majnákonu tshinanu Hoyakalu hetwamonutatkahi.
Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu hetwamonuxyawakhi tshinanu, judeu-nerune majnakowaxyalu Hoyakalu, wanna koxa himukata yoptolexyawakpatnaklu Hoyakalu hetwamonre.
Ptowruneka hektuntshi towre mixkonu hitakka Hoyakaluya. Hiyáhoni xawakni Hoyakalu himukata hetwamonretna ptowru neruka.
Hoyakalu HimalwuxikoluHa hi psokananru Hoyakalu hihlenu. Hanhe ruchinixya hihchinikanu hiyrunu rimatkalnu! Kathe xawaka himatjemlu Hoyakalu hixjexyawaka?
Wane htshina yonatkaluru Hoyakalu pirana: “Kathe xawaka himatlu Hoyakalu hchinikanu? Kathe xawaka himukata hasrukletlu?”
Hike deve-kaklu Hoyakalu satu pa hixanu renekkoklunu.”
Hoyakalu Wenejnawakwa PiranapniHiyáhoni Cristo tshinanu nmoletanune, Hoyakalu hetwamonre tsru potuko rixyawaka tshinanu nanjithi henejinwa Hoyakaluya himane henekachalu rixyawaka. Hoyakalu tshinanu kotspalatkalunhi hiwejinri powraluya, Hoyakalu hikchikhihlenrerutka. Wane potuko rimalukyi Hoyakalu.
Hi hewi tshijne hiwejikatshine pixka hixanu seyni hitshitanru Hoyakalu herotexyawaklu hixa hchinikanu psol-potuko. Wan-hixatshinephi himatanru Hoyakalu halukanru kihleru hiyrunu hikchikhihlenruru hiyrunu ruhleretanru potuko.
Cristo Halixatshri Cristo Mane Psojitekni PiranapniRenekachale Hoyakalu hihlenu Hoyakalu henekachaxyano tshinanu, wla ntshina hixa satkakhi tshinanupa: Hi hkahwajinwa pimrine yohnik-hihlenhi hixyawaka. Seyni halixlewlu Hoyakalu henekachaleyma hyahoxinwa hanu hixatshinhi.
Klu tshinanu wan-rixa yineru, pa manepkalu seyni híxolu himane psojitkaka hiyrunu satkaka wimane psojitkaka pnu pejnu rixa kamrureta.
Hiyáhoni hix-koxa, yáholu hixomnuwu seyni pa manepkawu Cristo-ya. Hiyrunu ptowrunekwu pa manepka psojitwu pimrineymakananuko.
Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu henekachale kakojerni, hpixkonu reneksatwu, womkahitanru. Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu pixkonu renekachale Hoyakalu pirana wunkaklexyawaka rixini waneya wane potuko wixanu, hi psokta wixa halixleta, wane wixanu.
Seyni Hoyakalu henekachale wepixkakjexyawaka rixini waneya wepixkakjetanu; seyni wasruklewaxyawaka rixini waneya wasruklewatanu;
seyni pimrine wuykoxyawaka rixini waneya wuykolewatanu. Katukta henekhejnunkatrewata poyikowluyma renekanru. Towutatshri rixini waneya ruslahpotutanu. Jetwamonukleru rixini poyikowluyma repixanru.
Hoyakalu Halujyawaka Wkamhiywaka PiranapniHamotlewatanu halikak-potuko. Muhlentshi hahnanutanu seyni homkahitanru kihle hixatshri.
Hamotkakanu hixkakluko, moletkakatshine pixka. Hkahwakpiratanru hixa satkakhi.
Hkamrurewatanu, hi xako hmernu. Hoyakalu halujyawaka hkamhanu hixako hmixkonu psoluyako.
Himuwpotutanu klu tshinanu hiwekkakkalunhi kahwakkalunhi. Hakotachatanru salewaktshi. Hi hituk-hanjihohneretanu.
Henekachalewatanu mahaxikatshine moletkakatshine Jesus tshinanu. Yanamtatshine hapojini kihle yoptole hixanna.
Hoyakalu hanjitanu kihleru hixa hapnokatjene tshinanu. Hihlewahchinikanyehitanna, hi hkamakatanna.
Himuwatanu himuwatatshriyma. Hwamonuwatanu tshiyahatatshineyma.
Pa hchinikanurunephi. Hi halixkoxinwa seyni haté malukkotu hitajinwa. Hi hkahwajinwa jimatkalerun-potuko hixyawaka.
Satu yineru yotnexinhi hi hapnutanru wale. Hijhalu kihleru hkamhiywaka ptowru yineru hetanuya.
Hixako himukaxyawaka ptowru potuko hixanu pa hchinikanupka hixanu hixkakluko.
Nomolene, hi hix-nanuko hapnuyehixinwa seyni hetachatanru Hoyakalu hapnuyehixyawakhi. Klu tshinanu yonatkaluru wan-tshina: “Hitako hapnutanru. Napnokatanru htshina Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu.”
Seyni yonatkaluru tshinyawaka hixanu: “Hnatshixini pkamnitjeru, pohlutanru; ronunnahatewaxini, putanru; wane pixa hepixlexinri hpatewatanutka hatatjewa tshitshime ppokotlu hijiw-hoho hwaprotatshri.”
Hi hetachatanru hektutu hihrokkajyawakhi seyni hektutu hkamnitanu kihleruyma.
Cristo Halixatshine Hijhalu Tsru Hitakkalune HyijnakoxyawaknaPtowrunek-yijnakotanna tsru hitakkalune.
Hiyáhoni hitakkalune kamnitatshine Hoyakalu halujyawak-koxa hkamnitna. Katukta wan-hixa rukolujinwa.
Hektutu kamhatshri tsonu pikanna tsru hitakkalune seyni kihleru kamhatshine hi pikanna. Tsru hitakkalune hmaluka pikletkanuklunupa, kihleru hkamhanu. Waneya tsru hitakkalune himalwutanhi.
Klu tshinanu walekni Hoyakalu towutle kihleru hexikolupa. Seyni pmajnakowaxini, ppikanu. Klu tshinanu hitakkaluryi pixa papnokaxikowaka. Walekni Hoyakalu towre hektutu kamhatshine hapnokaxikowakapa.
Wale tshinanu hixa hijhalu tsru hitakkalune hyijnakoxyawaka. Hi hapnokaxikolu hkahwakpiraxyawaka tshinanu tsonu hyijnakotanna seyni hihchinikanu himaxyalu hanur-potni kihleru tshinanu.
Hiyáhoni wale tshinan-koxa xye tshijne yokanatatshri koxa hwenutanu klu tshinanu Hoyakalu halujyawaka hkamhajetna tsru hitakkalune. Ruslahpotutanruna Hoyakalu kamrure.
Katukta h-deve-tanu hwenutanru. H-deve-xinru xye tshijne tsru hitakkalune hijhawenuyehixikolu, hwenutanru. Hkahwakpiratanna kahwakpiratkalune ptowruneka.
Pimrine Wixyawaka PiranapniHike yineru h-deve-tanu tiyiroya seyni deve-tatshinephi hamotkakleya. Katukta hamotlu rimwastsireru romkahitlu Moisés yonreru pirana psoluka.
Klu tshinanu katukta hamotanru rimwastsitanru hi psojikna himtukanru. Hiyáhoni pimwastsitanru pamoxyawaka poyahokaklu Moisés yonreru pirana psoluka.
Hi Wumnanhinri KihleruHiyáhoni wan-hixanu klu tshinanu hipapkolutkani hiyojyawaka klu tshinanu hi howukatkalu wiwekkajikolu, wehalixletka hohne pnute.
Hatatjewa hoyetshno nikawnapiratatka, hohi hi howukatka. Hiyáhoni wuknokanru mapchahawaka kamrure seyni wkochtshekanru wyahotkakapre katawaka wyahotkajyawakpatka.
Katawaka pixka wixa yanretanu kihleru xako wkamhanu. Hi himru ptowru hixatshri womkahitanu, hi suxohewluko, hi patewahonutshiko, hi yanhakakluko, hi sotanuhonutshiko womkahitanu.
Seyni Wutsrukate Jesus Cristo wutajinwa. Hiyrunu hi wujhanru wimane halujyawaka wkamhiywaka.
Hi Heyikanru Hmoletanru Jesus Tshinanu PiranapniHihroka halixletatshri hjihlokkakanu hixa tskalaya. Seyni hi hihjekakanu wale hihchinikanu tshinanu.
Satuko yineru ralixle tshinanu ptowru potuko hnika. Seyni satuko hihroka halixletatshri kasureru tsonu hnika.
Katukta ptowru nikalu hnika hi heyikanru ptowru mnikole nikatshri. Hiyrun-koxa ptowru mnikole nikatshri hi hiykotanru ptowru nikalu nikatshri klu tshinanu Hoyakalu hi heyiklu.
Han-hixatshriyihe pixa satu yineru towreru peyijyawaka? Waleko htowutjeru hetahchinikanutlu ho kihlerhe htowreru ho hektutrahe htowreru. Klu tshinanu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu towreru himukata hepixletlu htowreru kihleruya.
Satuko yineru kahwakpiratlu satu hixatshri hohne seyni satutnaka kahwaklu ptowru hohne pixkakakluni. Hiyáhoni satkaka yineru hijhahchinikanutanu hanu potu rixahchinikanuta.
Hiyáhoni katukta kahwakpiratlu satu hixatshri hohne Hoyakalu tshinanu wan-rixa. Hiyrunu katukta nika, Hoyakalu tshinanu hnika, klu tshinanu hpoyahnutlu Hoyakalu hnijitu tshinanu. Hiyrunu katukta hi ptowruka nika Hoyakalu tshinanu wan-rixa klu tshinanu Hoyakalu hpoyahnuta.
Hi satukna towuxnawa riwejyawaka hiyrunu hi satukna towuxnawa rupniywaka.
Wiwejini, Hoyakalu tshinanu wiwekanu. Wupninipa, Hoyakalu tshinanu wupnanu. Hiyáhoni ho wiwejini ho wupninipa Hoyakalununwu.
Klu tshinanu Cristo hipna riwekatnaka rekhixyawakna hiwekatshinewa Tsru Hixikatshriwatni hiyrunu hipnatshinetka Tsru Hixikatshriwatni wale.
Hiyáhoni klu tshinanhe pixa hikolukanuwnayehitna pimrine pimolene Cristo tshinanu? Klu tshinanhe peyiklu Cristo tshinanu pmoletanru? Klu tshinanu pa hohne Hoyakalu hetamayxaklerewatatshri sreta wyanu hixa ptowrunepnikwu.
Klu tshinanu wane htshina Tsru Hixikatshriwa yonatkaluruya: “Wane htshina Tsru Hixikatshriwa, niwejyawaka tshinanu ptowru yineru yoptsojityehitanno hiyrunu ptowru yineru hiphujetanru Hoyakalu nixyawaka.”
Waneya waneklupa ptowrunekwu hinkaklexinwa Hoyakalu yehiya.
Hi Pujrukkakanru Cristo Tshinanu PmoletanruHiyáhoni hi wane pnuteko heyikakanu hixkakluko. Seyni halikaka hijhahchinikanutanu hitspetkaluru pma mutakyehixyawakaplu Cristo tshinanu pmoletanru hma mujrujyawakanupa, hma majnakowaxyawakanupa.
Jesus nalixyawaka tshinanu nimatpotutlu hikeni himtuklewachatatshri. Seyni katukta pa hixanu himtuklewatatshri rikahwaklu waneya waleko htshinanu rumtujnawa.
Pkojwaka halixlexinri Cristo tshinanu pmoletanru nikluru tshinanu hiyáhoni hi puchinikanretlu Cristo tshinanu pmoletanru. Hiyáhoni hi hetachatanru hnijitu jijruk-halixletna yine Cristo hipnayehitanune.
Hi pitshitanru kihleru pkahwakleru hektutu htshinikowaka.
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hi niktshi ho hirkaluru tshinanni seyni halikaka kihlerukni, hapnanuhchinikanruni hiyrunu poyikowluni Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru heneklewleni.
Hiyáhoni katukta homkahjetlu Cristo xye hichinikantshiya, Hoyakalu poyikowanwakatanru hiyrunu yine hikchikhihlenutanru wan-hixatshri.
Hiyáhoni womkahitanru xako wale ptowruka hapnanuhchinikanru heneklewatatshri hiyrunu wujhanru hanu potu wumukata mixkotkakleta hixa satkakwu.
Hi nikalu hikolukle tshinanu himtukanru Hoyakalu kamrure. Hikemkani nikalu tshipetkaluru seyni wpupjeta wnikanru tshinanu yineru wumtukahchinikanuxini.
Hiyáhoni kihle koxlu hi nikaluko hnijyawaka, hi vinho-hako ruryawaka hiyrunu hi kluneruktako poyaho himtukahchinikanrewletatshri Cristo tshinanu pmoletanru tshinanuya.
Nikalu hiyrunu hirkaluru pirana hanukta pixa hetletanru, waleni pixanu tsonni Hoyakaluyma. Yineru hkamhaleru kihleru hkahwajinri hi hkojwakahchinikanuxnawa seyni hpoyikowahchinikanuta.
Seyni kojwakahchinikanutatshriko yineru nijinri, Hoyakalu yehi rukolujinwa nikatshri. Klu tshinanu hi ralixle tshinanu hnika. Klu tshinanu kluneruktako hkamha yineru hmalixlenuyma waleni hektuntshi.
Cristo Wyimyawaka PiranapniHixa hixkolunwu halixlewluya wujhalu wepixyawakna hihroka halixletatshritka hinolu ranijyawakna xye riwejinriyna. Hi wumukata hixako walujyawaka tsonu wuchinikanrexyawaka.
Klu tshinanu Cristo hi wale nanwaka tsonu hichinikanrexnawa. Seyni wan-rixa Jesus htshinyawakakotnaka yonatkaluru potukalu, wan-tshinatshri: “Heyiklewlu htshina heyiklexyawakyina pixa, hita hoho rapoka htshina heyiklexyawakyina pixa.”
Psoluka yonatkaluru potukalu pirana yonatka hixa wasrujikolu tshinanu ruchinikanuwkakwu wkahwakachaxyawakaplu Hoyakalu hihlenu hiyrunu repixlewle. Xye wukchika Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru piranaya.
Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu wmixkotjeru hiyrunu wpoyikotahchinikanutjeru hepixanwu pa hchinikanurunwu wixyawakapa hixkakluko, womkahixinri Cristo Jesus hixjexyawaka.
Pa hchinikanurunhi pa tokanurunhi himalwutanru Hoyakalu, Jesus Cristo Hitsrukate.
Hiyáhoni hyoptokakanu kihlehchinikanurunhi Hoyakalu himalwuxikolu tshinanu klu tshinanu wan-rixa yoptoletatkawu hixa Cristo.
Klu tshinanu wane ntshinhi Cristo hepixatkana judeu-nerune rekhixyawakna Hoyakalu munanhakalurni klu tshinanu Cristo poyahokaklu wale pirana psoluka judeu-nerune hitsrukatenni Hoyakalu mitshi hinkaklexyanna.
Hiyrun-koxa repixatkana judeu mixkane rimalwuxyawakapluna Hoyakalu retwamonre tshinanu. Wane htshina yonatkaluru potukalu: “Hiyáhoni nuphujtatanyi judeu mixkane yehiya. Pixa hiwaka nimalwutanu chikaltshiya.”
Hiyrunu wane htshina: “Himalwutanru hixa judeu mixkanhi Hoyakalu nurreneyma.”
Hiyrun-koxa wane htshina: “Ptowruneka judeu mixkane himalwutanru Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu. Ptowru neruka himalwupotutanru Hoyakalu.”
Hiyrunuko Isaías-ni wan-tshinni: “Runinipa satu Jessé klopicha hajerupa runanu judeu mixkane htowuxyawakapa. Hiyrunu wanna kahwaklerupni wale.”
Nanjitlu Hoyakalu wkahwakleru hpoyikowkajyawakwu wajiya, wapnanuhchinikanuxyawaka walixle tshinanu. Waneya hixa kahwakachale pnute hya tseruwnaleta Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru pixkonu tshinanu.
Paulo Hinkaklexyawaklu Waleko Hipirana PiranapniNmoletanune walixle tshinanu, nimatlu hixa katsépolu ptowru kihleruya hiyrunu katsepoyhi himatkalewlu hiyáhoni hixa himata hiykokaka hixkakluko.
Seyni twu yonawahlo phujewaka nutaklu satkaka pirana wane nixa hichinikkaklethi. Phujewaka nutaklu klu tshinanu Hoyakalu henekno xye kamrurtshi nepixyawakhi.
Cristo Jesus towrerno judeu mixkane nepixyawaka. Sacerdote kamrure pixka nixa hiyáhoni nkamrurni Hoyakalu pirana, kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana nunkaklexyawaka nkamhajeta. Wane nixa judeu mixkane henekachalune rumukata hixlexyawakapna Hoyakalu hikchikhihlenreru potukatlewatatshri Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluruya.
Hiyáhoni Cristo Jesus nimwale tshinanu, npoyikowahchinikanuta nkamrure Hoyakalu tshinanu.
Hiyáhoni hi npika hinkakletletanru wale ptowruka Cristo wan-rixa kamrureta hita tshinanuya. Walekni nunkakle hiyrunu nkamrure tshinanu wane nixkakna judeu mixkane Hoyakalu romkahixyawakna;
