Wane htshinatnaka mitshikawlur-pirana: “Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu himatahchinikanutna jimatkalerune mahijeru hchinikanutatshine.”
Hiyáhoni hi satukna yineru halixkowatanu klu tshinanu ptowru potuko hixanni.
Paulo, Apolo, Pedro, xye tshijne, hiweklu, hipuktshi, xye papko, hinatshripa, xye ptowruka hixanni.
Cristo-nunhi hixa. Hiyrun-koxa Cristo Hoyakalunni.
Nuretkalune Cristo Pirana Hiphujetatshine PiranapniHixa hijhalu Cristo-yma kamrurewatatshinwu hikahwajyawakwu. Hoyakalu pirana yohimakanatkaluru pirana hiphujetatshinwu.
Xye pirana hislahatshine rujhaluna Royakalutna halujyawaka kamhatshine potuko rixyawakna.
Halikaka ho hixa hexyawakno ho hapatjehchinikanutatshine hexyawakno hike rixa. Haté hi hitako jihyehixnawa.
Klu tshinanu hikeni hektutu nuchinikanretleru nukolujnawakwa. Seyni hi koxa wane nma mixyawakanu tshinanu powrano. Nutakyahokjerni Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu.
Hiyáhoni xawakni hike hikolukanuwnanu hma mapokkanuko pchini hipapkolu. Hkahwakanu Wutsrukate Cristo hapojinipa papkopa waneya ptowru pirana potuko rutakyahokanu. Ruphujetanru ptowru pirana yohimatkaluru pirana, ruphujetanru ptowru yineru hichinikanretanru pirana. Waneklu satkaka halixkotko Hoyakalu tshinanu.
Cristo tshinanu nmoletanune, hixa nasrujyawaka tshinanu xye hasruklewlukaka nutajnawa hiyrun-koxa Apolo. Hix-hepwu wyapkaklexnawa kajnakolune hixyawakapa yonatkaluru piranaya. Wane htshina: “Hixa hma malixkoxyawakanuplu satu yineru pimrine pnute.”
Kathe wan-hixkakyi halukkaluru potu pixyawaka pimrine pnute? Hi he Hoyakaluko henekatkayi ptowru potuko pimwaleru? Hiyáhoni klu pimalixkoxinwa pma yoptotanutu pixka?
Hixa ptowru potuko himwatshinetkahi! Phurunetkahi. Hixa phurunhi seyni hixa hike. Kihlemkahi phurune hixyawaka Hoyakalu yhaleya. Wan-hixatshinemkahi hixayma wpohirewatanumkatka.
Klu tshinanu hitaho Hoyakalu hitakwu hixa nuretkalunwu Cristo pirana hiphujetatshinwu hapkatatatshine pot-wixyawakatka. Hixa hatatjewa hiylajixkalunepwu ptowru hetanuya, hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrerune tenhohne hajene hetanuya hiyrun-koxa yine hetanuya.
Cristo pirana tshinanu hike mimatkanwu seyni hixa jimatkalerunhi hixahoxnawa Cristo halixyawaka tshinanu. Hixni hihrokatshinwu seyni hixni hixkolunhi hkahwajnawa. Hixa kahwajnawa kahwakpiratkalunhi seyni hixa hike pikwu.
Haté xawakni pa katkaka natshwu, wonunnahatewata. Mkatshri hiskatatshri wmakatjeta, kotshipjerunwu, pa pji pejnu wumkamxya.
Wkamrurewpotuta. Wimyoko wkamrurewaxya. Yanhakkalunwu seyni wuhlewahchinikanyehlewata. Wyotnejetkamka seyni wakotachatlu.
Pa katkaka hektuwaka wtshinka seyni wuykotna. Malukkotu hiknokkaluru xye tshijne hajeru pixka wixa. Kaptshowaka hajeru malukkotu wkahwakka haté xawakni potuko.
Hi nyonanwakathi hixa nma patetjechaxyawakanuphi seyni nowhenene nalukanune pixka nixa hiykolethi.
Klu tshinanu yahmaklu mil Cristo pirana hasruklewatatshine himwinimka seyni halikaka hi híxona hirune. Klu tshinanu kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri piranaya nwuhenethi Jesus Cristo-ya.
Hiyáhoni nanjithi hita pixka hixanu.
Wale tshinanu Timóteo tshinkaluru nyokananwakathi. Timóteo-ni noturu pixkalutu nalukanru potuko, poyahokakatshri Wutsrukate Jesus-ya. Wale hichinkapkakanhi nixjexyawaka Cristo Jesus-ya. Wane nixa hasruklewleta ptowru sretako ptowru potuko Cristo halixatshin-yehi hapatjexikowakaya.
Satkakhi hixa halixkoxnawa klu tshinanu hkahwakhetkotlu klanu nma yiywakanupa.
Seyni chinpotukawa hix-yehi nyanu, Tsru Hixikatshriwa hitshixinipno klanu nyanu. Waneya nimatanru ho tokantshichalhe ho halikaklahe Hoyakalu pixkonu halixkoxikatshinwa tskala hwa.
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hi tokantshichani seyni himukatluni.
Hanuru pot-haluka? Ho kotshipjerewapiyma nyanwakaxyawakhi ho kihle hchinikanurno nyanwakaxyawakhi, hixako hichinikanretatshrino?
Wanepnawaka hixa halixkoxnawa! Seyni hixamka hijhalu hwamonuwpotuxyawaka hiyrun-koxa wan-hixatshri hijhalu hixa tskala hkotspalaxikowaka.
Hektuwaka Kamhatshri Salexikolu PiranapniKlu tshinanu hita yáholu hi hix-yehi nwapotuta seyni hixa nimwa nohchinikanuya. Hiyáhoni hatatjewa hix-yehi nwapotuta, njihyehitatkalu xye tsru hektutu kamhatshri Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus hiwakaya.
Hixa hapatjexinipa wane nwanu hita nohchinikanuya. Hiyáhoni Wutsrukate Jesus yokanre tshinanu Hoyakalu hitshithi.
Satanás renekko, wale saletmanetanru seyni riwejinri hiwekkakko Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus hapojinipa.
Hi kihleru halixkoxnawakwa. Hix-hetko jematkalu wane htshinyawakna yine: “Psotsonujiji chitshponatshri psolujpako hchitshponkaka.”
Hiyáhoni hixa hijhalu hiknojyawaklu kchitshponkaklewakleru mitshikawluru. Waleni hektuntshi. Wan-hixinpatka powraphi psoluyako. Waneyakni herotujpa chitshponatshri myapjetkone pixkalunpatkahi. Wan-hixatshinetkahi xawakni. Klu tshinanu ralpokotka poyikowlu hohne, Páscoa hohne, klu tshinanu Cristo carneiro whene pixkalutni ruylatka hixa kachrijru.
Hiyáhoni wuchinkapanru Páscoa hohne hi nikkalurujpa chitshponatshri yapjetkaluru pixka hixatshinepwu, waleni hektuntshi hiyrun-koxa ptowru hektutu tserutatshri. Seyni wuchinkapanru Páscoa hohne hatatjewa hijpa myapjetkotu pixkalunepwu, waleni wiwekle powralu hiyrun-koxa halikak-potu.
Mitshikananu yonawahlo nyokananwakathi nuykothi kapoklewakleruneyma hma yanjexyawakanupa.
Seyni hi ptowrun-potuko xye psol-tshijneko hajene kapoklewakleruneyma ntshina. Hiyrun-koxa hi ptowru ksotanuholuneyma, hi ptowru katshowhuruneyma, hi ptowru mayawletshicha kkahwakpirakleruneymako ntshina. Klu tshinanu wan-hixinipa, hixa hijhalu xye psol-tshijneko hichpajyawaka.
Seyni xawakni nyonanwakathi hi hepiretanru moltshi tshinkaluru Cristo tshinanu kapoklewakleru rixini ho ksotanuholu rixini ho mayawletshicha kkahwakpirakleru rixini ho jejnuhimakleru rixini ho jimekleru rixini ho katshowhuru rixini. Wan-hixatshriyma hi hnikanu.
<sup>(12-13)</sup> Katnohe hita njihyehixyawakapna malixkane, hix-yehi mwakane? Halikaka Hoyakalu jihyehjetna wanna. Seyni hixa Cristo halixatshinhi hapatjetatshinhi hi he hixa hijhalu hjihyehixyawakna hektutu kamhatshine hixa tskala hwatshine? Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru mitshikawlur-pirana wan-tshina: “Xye hektutu kamhatshri hix-yehiya kahnete hyokanatanru.”
(-)
Wla Raluk-hixletna Halixatshine Hapatjetatshine Hikolukanuwnalkaka Tshinanu PiranapniKlu tshinanhe hixa tskala hwatshri halixatshri hikolukanuwnalu kamhatshri hixa hijhahchinikanjixyehitlu tsrukakalune malixkane yehi seyni hi potukalune Cristo halixatshine hijhahchinikanjixyehitlu hikolukanuwnalkaka tshinanu?
Hi he himata xawaka hixa Cristo halixatshinhi potukalunhi psol-tshijne hajeneko hikolukanuwnalkaka tshinanu hixa hijhahchinikanyehjixkona? Psol-tshijne hajeneka tshinanu hixa hijhahchinikanyehjixkona. Hiyáhoni kluneru tshinanhe xawaka hi hixako himukata hijhahchinikanyehretlu hikoluklu mpomuklukanutpotu tshinanu?
Hi he himatlu haté hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrerune tenhohne hajene tshinanu wujhahchinikanyehjixko? Hi he wane pnute wujhahchinikanyehjixanna xye hohne hajeru hikoluklukaka?
Hiyáhoni hixa hijhahchinikanyehjixiniplu jikolukanuru xye hohne hajeru tshinanu seyni haklu tshinanhe hixa hi hitakna rujhahchinikanyehixikowakna Cristo halixatshine mpomujhakon-potu Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine yehiya?
Hixa patetjexnawa! Hi he rawa satu hix-yehi jimatkaleru himat-hichinikanuwyehrewatatshri hixa halixatshine hapatjetatshine yehiko?
Wane. Wanepnawaka Cristo hiwaka moletkajikatshinepnawakhi hijhahchinikanyehjixlu. Hiyrunu malixkane hijhahchinikanyehjixlu.
Hixa hikolukakjeta hixkakluko hiyáhoni hixa pupjeta. Hi he xawaka kihlepotlu hetachaxyawaklu jikolukanurkaka? Klu tshinanu kihle potlu htshowhuwachaxinixka.
Seyni hixa hi wan-hixa. Hixa himtukkakjeta hixkakluko. Cristo hiwaka tshinanu moletkajikatshinekhi wan-hixa.
Hi he himatlu hektutu kamhatshri hi Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hyoptotanu? Hi hyokwijexinwa. Hi kapoklewakleruneko, hi mayawletshicha homkahitatshineko, hi jimopatakleruneko, hi suxonkaklu yamankakjetatshineko, hi jejineko perepnakakjetatshineko.
Hi katshowhuruneko, hi ksotanuholuneko, hi jimekleruneko, hi jejnuhimakleruneko, hi ktshowhuwakleruneko, hi hyoptotanruna Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka.
Mitshikananu satkakhi hixa wan-hixjekanatatshinhi. Seyni hixa hektuntshi herojikatka, Hoyakalu yoptolenetkahi, hi jihyehitkalunetkahi Hoyakaluya, Wutsrukate Jesus Cristo tshinanu hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru tshinanu.
Hoyakalu Himalwuxikolu Mantshiyma PiranapniHiyáhoni satuko wan-tshinanu: “Kluneruktako naluka kamhaletanu, nkamhanru.” Hehemka seyni hi ptowru potuko paluka kamhaletanru hepixanyi. Numukata wan-tshinreta: “Hehe, numukata nalukanru ptowru potuko kamhaletanu.” Wanepnawaka hi nitshitanru nkamhaleru towuxyawakno.
Satukotnaka wan-tshinanu: “Nikkaluru nosatu tshinanupa hiyrun-koxa sattshi tshinanu rawa nikkaluru.” Wanemka seyni Hoyakalu pa hohne nikatanru nosatu hiyrun-koxa nikkaluru. Wimane hi hapoklewlu tshinanni seyni wimane Hoyakalu yokanrerupni. Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu wimane hyapa wale halukanru hkamhiywakapa.
Hoyakalu hiwekkakatkalu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus hiyrun-koxa hix-koxa riwekkakanu waleko hpixkonuyma.
Hi he himata hixa hix-mane Cristo psojitni? Kihlehohihe Cristo mane psojite kapoklewaklero mane nipxakkajyawaka? Hike.
Hiyrun-koxa hi he himatlu katukta kapoklewaklero hapokmanexini, pa manepka rixatka walayma? Klu tshinanu wane potuko htshina Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru mitshikawlur-pirana: “Hepikananna, pa manepka rixkakna.”
Hiyáhoni katukta Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hipxakanu satupkalututkani hiwejikaluruya.
Hi he himatlu wimane Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hwiywakni hixa himane hitokote hiwejikatshrini, Hoyakalu henejyawu? Wale waneyhi Hoyakalu tshinanu. Hi hixanukni hixa.
Klu tshinanu kwenuru hanjixikalunhi. Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu himalwutanu himaneyma.
Hnunrotshine, Hnurtshine Hiykoxikolu PiranapniXawakni hixa yonyehixyano pirana nkochtshekanu. Kihlepotlu jeji suxo hma yotnexyawakanu.
Seyni hapoklewlu tshinanu satkaka jeji hijhalo waleko hhanunro rimwiywakapa. Hiyrun-koxa satokaka suxo hijhalu walako thanuru timwiywakapa.
Hnurtshine haluklu hhanunrone halujyawaka romkahixyawakna. Waneko pixka tixanru suxo thanuru.
Wala suxo hi towutmanexinwa wala nanuko seyni halikaka thanuru towutleropni. Waneko pixka rixa thanuru. Hi htowutmanexinwa seyni hhanunro halikaka towutmanetanru.
Wanna hepi, jeji hhanunroyma hi htshipetmankajinna ho pchinhohnejiji tshinanu tsonu mimaletkonepni ranjihohnexyawakna tshinanu tsonu. Waneyakni himumkakakanutnaka Satanás myahtalexyawakanupna hmakoxikowakanupna tshinanu.
Seyni pchinhohnejiji htshipetmankajyawakna jeji hhanunroyma pirana hi ntowuxikolni wale pirana. Wale hitshitkaluru piranni.
Nalukmaklu ptowruneko halixatshineko hita pixkamka rixanna hi khanunrophi, hi khanuruphi. Seyni satkaka wan-rixa Hoyakalu henejyalu. Satu wane potuk-hixa. Satu pnuko hixa.
Wane ntshinna mhanunrone hiyrun-koxa hipnahnurutatshrone wane ntshina. Hita pixka rixhohnekanatanmakna.
Seyni hma makotkanuklunupluna wan-rixyawakna hhanunrowhapkatanna, hhanuruwhapkatanna. Klu tshinanu kihleru halikaka hanunrowhapkaxyawakna, hanuruwhapkaxyawakna hma kaheknanuwaxyawakanupna.
Hnunrotshi, Hnurtshi Hma Muchoxikowakanu PiranapniSatu yokanruru waneyno hixa himwakakatshine tshinanu. Halikakni hi hitako nanikpiranachalerni seyni Tsru Hixikatshriwa Cristo yokanrerni. Suxo khanururo hi hichohnurutanu.
Tuknokahnuruxinipa, mhanuruthohnekananpatkani ho wannako hihlekakanu. Hiyrun-koxa jeji hi hichohnunrotanu.
Waneya wane pnute hita wan-tshina, hi Tsru Hixikatshriwa Cristo wan-tshina: Cristo halixatshri malixkato hnunroxini taluk-himwalhohnekanaxinri, hi ruchotanro.
Hiyrun-koxa suxo Cristo halixatshri hmixkanuklunu thanuru raluk-hohnekanaxinro, hi tuchotanru thanuru.
Klu tshinanu hnurtshi malixkatu hihlehchinikanutka Hoyakaluya hhanunro halixatshro tixini. Waneko pixka tixa hnunrotshi malixkato hihlehchinikanutka Hoyakaluya thanuru halixatshri rixini. Wane hmixkanuklunna hwuhenenna hi ruhlehchinikanutkana Hoyakaluya. Seyni xawakni ruhlehchinikanutkana Hoyakaluya.
Malixkatu haluk-hicholexinro hhanunro Cristo halixatshro hyachatanu malixkatu. Wan-rixini malixkatu hike rixa halixatshine tshinanu ho jeji ho suxo. Hoyakalu honra tshanixatkahi kihle hwachale hixinripa.
Klu tshinanu pixa suxyi halixatshroyi hi pimatlu phanuru malixkatu xawaka palixkakanu, waneko pixka rixa jeji halixatshri ho phanunro malixkato xawaka palixkakanu.
Seyni riwejinri Tsru Hixikatshriwa Cristo heneksaxya tshinanhi satkakhi hixa wanekananuko hixa hiwekletanutka Hoyakalu tshanixiniklunutkahi pixkako hixhohnekanatanutka. Wane nixa hasrukletna ptowruneka Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshin-yehkaka.
Satu yineru judeu-neru jiprojhaptojimtatatshri htshanixkoklunutka Hoyakaluya hi rujhalu mjiprojhaptojimtatkotu pixka rixyawaka. Hiyrun-koxa ho pa neruko mjiprojhaptojimtatkotu htshanixkoklunutka Hoyakaluya hi rujhalu hjiprojhaptojimtaxikowaka.
Jiprojhaptojru hike repixa Hoyakalu hetanuya hiyrun-koxa hma jiprojhaptojimtatkanuklunu yineru hike repixa Hoyakalu hetanuya. Hepixlewatatshri potni Hoyakalu yokanatanru homkahixikolu.
Hanukta rixakanatatka yineru Hoyakalu tshanixinixkalu waneko rixanutka.
Hiyáhoni towutachatkaluryi pixakanaxini ptshanixkoklunutka, hike rixa seyni pumukata hichpaklexiniplu ptowuxikolu puchpakanu halikaka.
Klu tshinanu towrertshicha htshanixka Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakaluya hiyáhoni mtowretkotuko hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalunutkani. Waneko pixka rixa towrertshicha mixkatu htshanixkoklunutka Cristo towrerni wale.
Hixa kwenuru hanjixikalunhi. Hi yine towutanunephi.
Cristo tshinanu nmoletanune, hanukta hixakanata satkakhi htshanixkoklunu Hoyakaluya, waneko hixanu Hoyakalu hetanuya.
Maklojine Hiyrunu Mhanunrone Hiyrun-koxa Hipnahnurutatshine PiranapniMaklojine jejine mapokmanetanunewa tshinanu, Tsru Hixikatshriwa Cristo hike hyokanaxyano seyni Hoyakalu hitakno halixatshine ninoxyawaka halikaka pirana hinkakletatshrino, waleko retwamonre tshinanu, hiyáhoni wane nixa himatjemletlu xye pirana.
Hitaho kihleru xye papko kaheknanuwle tshinanu hanukta rixakanata jeji waneko rixanu.
Suxlahe pimwa? Hi pujhanru puchoxyawakaplo. Mhanunrotu pixinrahe? Hi pujhanro suxo.
Cristo tshinanu nmoletanune, wane ntshina, hi hohohneru Cristo hapojinripa. Hiyáhoni khanunrolune mhanunrone hiwekle pixka rixanna.
Tshiyahatatshine mtshiyahatkane pixka rixanna. Ho himuwatatshine mpoyikowatkane pixka rixanna. Maronewatatshine malechayalune pixka rixanna.
Xye tshijne hajerkaka hikamrurewatatshine hi wan-hixatshine pixka rixpotukanatanna. Klu tshinanu xye hohne hixjexyawaka nikawnanu.
Naluk-hepixletmakhi hma kojwakahchinikanuxyawakanupa. Klu tshinanu jeji mhanunrotu hijhahchinikanuxinwa hanu pot-xawaka rumukata homkahretlu Nutsrukate Tsru Hixikatshriwa halukanru.
Seyni khanunrolu haluk-himatletanru xye tshijne hajerkak-pirana hanu pot-rumukata kamhaleta hhanunro halujyawakako.
Hiyáhoni wan-hixatshri hepi hchinikanru. Suxo mhanuruto hiyrun-koxa suxo jeji mapokmanetanutowa Tsru Hixikatshriwa halukanru pirana tuchinikanretjeta. Rujhaluna suxone powra rixyawakna himaneymana hiyrun-koxa riwejinriyna. Seyni suxo khanururo thanuru halujyawaka pirana tuchinikanretanu tpoyikowkajyawakaplu thanuru.
Wane ntshina hiykolethi klu tshinanu naluk-hepixlethi. Hi naluklu nkotspehchinikanuxyawakhi. Seyni naluklu halikakalutu potukalu pirana homkahixyawakapa hiyrun-koxa Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu halujyawaka henejinwa ptowru hmixkonuyma.
Xyekni ntshina hiykoletna mhanunrone. Satu mnukawa hnunrowpiratatshri hyokmanahchinikanuxini, hmaklojite hma hnunrotpiraxyawakanu wla ntshina hiykoletlu. Hyokmanahchinikanuxinixnaka mhanunrotu klu tshinanu hi rukchikhihlenutlu tuchochaxikowaka makloji ho ralukpotutawalo hiyrun-koxa raluk-hnunrotlexinro hiyáhoni wane ntshina kihleru hhanunroxyawaklo. Wan-hixatshri hi hektuntshi hkamha.
Seyni hmixkowahchinikanuxini hihchinikanuya hma hnunrowaxyawakanu klu tshinanu hi rujhalu hanunrowaxyawaka hiyrun-koxa rakotlu mhanunrotu rixachaxyawaka hiyáhoni kihleru hma hnunroxyawakanro hmaklojite.
Hiyáhoni katukta hmaklojite hhanunrota kihleru hkamha. Seyni katukta hmaklojite hi hnunrota kihler-potu hkamha.
Suxo tiwekahnurutka pchinika tinanchitka. Seyni tupnahnuruxinixka waleni towre tuchpajyatka. Hiyáhoni tumukata hnurutletlu talukanru katuktako. Seyni Cristo halixatshri tsonupni halikaka.
Seyni hitaho tma hnuruwatkanuklunupa tumuwatanu. Hiyrun-koxa nkahwaklu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru himwano hit-koxa.
Mayawletshicha Heneknijituxikowaka PiranapniXawakni mayawletshicha heneknijituxikowaka pirana nkochtshekanu. Hehe, hixa ptowrunekwu hixo pirana wimata. Hiyáhoni wimatkale tshinanu tsru hchinikanu wixnawa. Seyni pimrine wuchinijyawaka tseruwnakaklu halixlewlu.
Ho satu kahwajnawa pa hixanu rimata hike rimata rumukata himatletanrukmaka.
Seyni Hoyakalu himatlu ruchinikjeru.
Hiyáhoni mayawletshicha heneknijituxikowaka pirana wimatlu wale mayawletshicha wale hikeni. Mayawletshichani. Wimatlu Hoyakalu satupkalutu. Wale tsonni.
Klu tshinanu wanena hoyakalune tshinkalune tshijiko hwatshine hiyrun-koxa tenhohne hwatshinemka. Wan-rixkalukni hixo hoyakalune hwaklukni híxona hitsrukatshi tshinkalune.
Seyni hixa tshinanu waneru satupkalutu Hoyakalu. Waleni Wuru Hoyakalu ptowru potuko hiyakotatshri. Wiweka wale halujyawaka wkamhiywaka. Hiyrun-koxa Wutsrukate Hoyakalu satupka. Waleni Jesus Cristo. Ptowru potuko hkamhaka Jesus Cristo tshinanuko. Haté hix-koxa hwa Jesus Cristo tshinanu.
Seyni xye pirana halikakalutu hi rimata satkaka yineru. Satkaka hasruhlu mayawletshicha hpijyawakna hiyáhoni haté xawakni hnijinna hkahwakluna mayawletshicha nijitu hnikna. Mchikohalixlene kahwaklu mayawletshicha nijitu himtuka hiweklehotna.
Halikaka hi nikkaluru tshinanu wkayehiklu Hoyakalu. Wnijini ho wma nikkanuklunu psokakluni. Hi hkaykakanwu hiyrunu hi ramtakkakanwu.
Wanepnawaka nujrethi. Xako hi hihrokatshinephi hi hitspehchinikankakanu hixa himatkalewle tshinanu.
Klu tshinanu nijittshi mayawletshicha henekachaluru pirana hihrokahchinikanutatshri hexiniklunupyi, pixa jimatkaleryi, nikjexikowaka ptuplaxiniklunu mayawletshichapjiya, hi he hkojwakahchinikanutanu hihrokahchinikanutatshri pnijiniplu mayawletshicha henekachaluru?
Pimatkalewle tshinanu ramhanuna hihrokahchinikanutatshripni. Waleni pimole Cristo tshinanu hiyrun-koxa wale tshinanu rupna Cristo.
Wane pixini, pimole Cristo tshinanu pektuwanwakata pumtukahchinikanutlu hiyáhoni Cristo-ko pektuwanwakata.
Hiyáhoni nikkaluru hitspehchinikankajiniplu Cristo tshinanu nmoletanru hikeklu hohne nnikanutkalu nikalhitu nma mumtujyawakanuplu nomole.
