Himka pimrine tshinanu nuretkalurno seyni hixa tshinanu halikakni. Klu tshinanu hixakni ntowuxikolu nimaxikolenhi Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus tshinanu.
Pimrine reyiknona. Wane ntshin-hihretna nepomsatjene.
Hi he nitshitka nnijyawaka, nuryawaka nkamrure nenejikolu tshinanu?
Hita hiyrun-koxa Barnabé tsonrahe hijhalu hkamrurewaxyawaka wnijyawakapa, wmakawaxyawakapa?
Kathe pa kata soldado-tapa waneya wale nanwaklahe wenuxnawa yineru? Kathe hsana hitakatshriko waneyapa hi hnikanru? Kathe pratshi katsohatatshriko waneya hi ruratnuhatanro?
Xye pirankaka ntshina yapkakleta wane potuko htshina Moisés yonreru.
Moisés yonreru mitshikawlur-pirana wan-tshina: “Hi postuptotanru boi hitaklu tataji pjiplokkajiniplu.” Boi-ne ruchinikanrexyawaka tshinanrahe wane htshina Hoyakalu?
Ho hixa tshinanukla wane htshina Hoyakalu? Halikaka hixa tshinanu wane htshina. Hiyáhoni hitataji hitakatshri hiyrun-koxa hitaklu hamatshri pixkakaklune klu tshinanu wanna hepi kahwaklu honantshi psoji wannanuko hkayaxyawakna hkamrurna tshinanu.
Hiyáhoni xawakni hitataji Hoyakalu yehi hichpajikatshri pirana wutajinri hix-yehi, hi he xawaka wumukata yoptoletanru wmahaxinri xye tshijne hajeru hix-yehiya?
Pimrinemka himukata wan-hixleta hix-yehiya, hi he xawaka wane pnute wumukata hixleta hixa? Wanepnawaka hi wumukaxyawaka wixjeta. Seyni ptowru potuko wakotachata wma mimalexyawakanuplu kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana, Cristo pirana.
Hixlahe xawaka himatlu Hoyakalupji kamrurewaxikatshine nikjetlu Hoyakalupji hiylajexikalurkaka. Hiyrun-koxa hixa himatlu nikalni altar hoho hiylaxikalurni psojni hyoptotna altar yehi kamrurewaxikatshine.
Waneko pixka rixa hitakletna Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus, kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana hinkakletatshine, hmahaxinrina hkayaxyawakapna kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana runkaklexyawakna tshinanu.
Seyni hita hikeklu wane nixa. Xye pirana hi nyonatlu wan-hixyapno hit-koxa. Kihlemkano nupniywakhapkatka. Satukna yineru malecha hma mixinutupa nkamrure kihleru.
Klu tshinanu nunkaklexinri kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana, hi ntserpiranawaxinrini. Halikaka ntowutka nunkaklexyawaklu. Hektu potukno nma munkakletkanuklunru kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana!
Klu tshinanu hitako nalujyawaka nkamhakmaka nwenuxikolumka nujhanu. Seyni ntowuxikoluyma nkamhiywaka tshinanru xye kamrurtshi renekno Hoyakalu.
Hiyáhoni klunernihe nwenuxikolu? Waleni npoyikowle kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana nunkaklexyawaka hiyrunu hike nujhayehita nwenuxikowaka xye nkamrure tshinanu.
Hichotkalurno. Hike yinerumka towutno. Wanepnawaka ptowruneko towrerno klu tshinanu wane nixa heneklexnawa hixolune yine nehchinikankajyawakapa.
Hiyáhoni judeu-ne tshinanu, judeu-neru pixka nixnawa, judeu-ne nehchinikankajyawaka tshinanupa. Hiyrun-koxa Moisés yonreru pirana homkahitatshine tshinanu, Moisés yonreru homkahitatshri pixka nixnawa, nehchinikankajyawakapna. Himka nmunanhanru Moisés yonreru pirana.
Hiyáhoni judeu mixkane yiminno hi Moisés yonreru nkochtsheka niwejinri tshinanu. Wane nixa judeu mixkane nehchinikankajyawakapa. Himka Hoyakalu hiykole nmajnakowaxya klu tshinanu Cristo hiykole hwikatshrino.
Hihroka halixletatshine tshinanu hihrokatshri pixka nixnawa hihrokatshine naluk-hikchikletkal-tshinanu. Ptowruneka tshinanu, ptowrukakako nixnawa, satkaka numukata hiwekkaklexyawakapa.
Kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana tshinanu, xye ptowruka nkamha. Naluka yoptoletanu halixatshineymapa Hoyakalu hihlenu wanna tshinanupa.
Hixa himatlu hasuklu kamhatshine pirana. Hasuklu kayaxikatshri tsonu yoptotanru rumlujikolu. Wan-hixa hasuklepotutanu hyoptoxyawakaplu himlujikolu.
Ptowruneko hasuklu kaypiraxikatshine ruslahmanexnawana. Wanna halikaka wan-rixna klu tshinanu satu sahyi hyochmakjiwuxikolupnina, rimathexikowakapa hasuklu kayaxikatshri rixyawaka. Halikaka wan-hixatshri sahyi nikawnanu pa hohne. Seyni hixa Hoyakalu homkahitatshinwu yoptolerupa satu sahyi hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupni, rimaxikowaka kayatatshinwu wixyawaka.
Halikaka hita wane nixa hasuklemta, npoyehitahchinikanuta hasuklu hichinixyawaka napojyawakapa. Hiyrun-koxa yahotkaklu pirana pixka nixa. Hi malechawaka hiylakatshri pixka nixa.
Seyni nsaletmanexnawa. Ntowutmanexnawa. Pimrine nunkaklewyehixinixka hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana, hit-koxa nma mahijeruxyawakanupa.
Israel-nerune Henejikolu PiranapniCristo tshinanu nmoletanune, hichinikanru xako hanu rixnixkana ptowrunniko wutsrukatenni Moisés homkahikanatatshinni. Wanna ptowrunniko Hoyakalu hoji hetakanaxinnina hohimkohi hpuko rawakanaxinnina waneklu papkolunni. Hiyrun-koxa Mar powha Serolu hyapamxinnina.
H-batiza-tkanna wanna ptowrunnika hohimkohiya hiyrun-koxa mar powhaya klu tshinanu Moisés homkahitatshine rixakanaxinnina.
Wanna ptowrunnika niklu walerutu nikkaluru Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru henejyana.
Wanna ptowruneka hirlu walerutu hirkaluru Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru henejyana. Klu tshinanu sotlu honneha hiwekkaklewatatshri rurhatna, sotlu rimotsatjerna Cristo.
Seyni hixpotna Hoyakalu mpoyahonutkane hiyáhoni popriwaka ruylaxikanna wannani. Rupalmankakanna popriwakaya.
Xye pirana psoluka hakanha hixa rasrujyawaka tshinanu. Ruykotwu wmalujyawakanuplu hektuwaka. Wannani pixka wma mixyawakanapa.
Hiyrun-koxa hi mayawletshicha kahwakpiratatshinephi, wannani satkakni pixka. Wane htshina Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru mitshikawlur-pirana wannani pirana: “Htuplatna yine. Hnikna, rurna. Waneya hpalnana hahsalu hkamhiywakapna.”
Hiyrun-koxa hi wyahotanru Tsru Hixikatshriwa Cristo hi wkahwakanru wektunu hma mapnokaxyawakanupa satkakni israel-nerunni pixka. Himnune hiylakanna wannani.
Hiyrun-koxa hi hihjekakanu hixa wannani satkakni pixka. Hiyáhoni hiylalewatatshri Hoyakalu yokanreru nikatanna yinni.
Xyekaka hakanhayehitnina wutsrukatenni yapkaklu rixyawakapa pimrine tshinanupa. Hiyrun-koxa hixa ruykoxyawakapa tshinanu hyonatka walekaka pirana. Klu tshinanu wiwekle hmahle hohnestsi hwatshritkani.
Hiyáhoni poyehi yopkakle hixahoxikatshriwa ruslahinwa hma yawniywakanupa.
Yahotaletlukaka hix-yehi hwatshri pimrine yahotjeru pixka potuko rixa. Seyni Hoyakalu htshinyawak-potuko hkamha. Hiyáhoni hi retachayehitanhi hma makoxyawakanu pnute hma mixyawakanupa yahtaletlewlu. Seyni yahtaletlewluko repixinhi hiknohyawakaplu hixa himukata hakotlexyawakaplu.
Mayawletshicha Kahwakpiraxikolu Hasujikolu PiranapniHiyáhoni nuchinikanune Cristo tshinanu, hasujinri mayawletshicha kahwakpiraxikolu.
Niynumathi kahchinikanurune pixka. Hixako hijhahchinikanutanu ho halikaklahe ntshinyawaka ho hike.
Copa stono hwatshri wurrerha pirana wuchinijyalu Jesus hipnale hixa tshinanu, wuhlewahchinikanutjeru wpoyahnuthaleru pirana. Xye copa stonha wurini, hi he xawaka Cristo hraha wapikka? Hiyrun-koxa pão wjiknajroxinri wnijinri, hi he Cristo mane wapijikolukatkani wale?
Klu tshinanu hixwu pão nikatshinwu. Seyni wale pão satupkalu, walerutu pão wnika. Hiyáhoni hixa hixolunwu pa manepkawu.
Judeu-nerune pirana hichinikanretanu. Henekachalu hiylaxikolu nikatshine hi he wannan-koxatkani henekachalu?
Klu piranhe naluka tshinreta xyekaka yapkaklu piranayma? Hixlahe kahwaklu wla ntshinyawaka kahwakpiratkalurni mayawletshichakaka ho hijhakalurni nikkaluru mayawletshicha renekachaxikowaka wanerhe htshinahotno?
Hi koxa wane ntshina hasruklethi. Halikaka xyekni ntshina. Kluneruktako nikalu renekka mayawletshicha hiylatkalurupa tshinanu, kamtshine renekka hi Hoyakalu renekka. Hi nalukhi hixa kamtshineyma htsaklawniywaka.
Hixa hi himukata hirrexyalu hepi hirapi Wutsrukate Cristo tshinanu hiyrun-koxa kamtshi tshinanu. Hiyrun-koxa hixa hi himukata niklexyalu hepi nikawaka Cristo pão nikawakle hiyrun-koxa kamtshine nikawakleya tshinanu.
Ho whahxakajerhe Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu? Hixlahe kahwajnawa Hoyakalu yohnik-mixkonu hixyawaka?
Hektuwaka Wuchoxyawaka Tshinanu Hiyáhoni Wuchinikkajyawaka PiranapniSatkaka yineru wan-tshina: “Ptowru walukanru wumukata kamhaleta.” Hehemka seyni hi ptowruka wkamhapiratanru kihlerni. “Wumukata kamhaletlu ptowru waluka kamhaletanru,” htshina satkaka yineru. Seyni satuko wkamhapiratanru hi ptowruko tseruwnakaklewata.
Hi satukna hijhanru kihleru walenupka tshinanu tsonu seyni pimrine tshinan-koxa halikaka rujhanru.
Ptowru nikkaluru hichankajexikowaka hanjixinri hnikanru, hike rixa. Hi hkojwakahchinikanutanu.
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu tokanu mitshikawlur-pirana wan-tshina: “Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalunni xye psol-tshijneko hiyrun-koxa ptowru potukananuko tshiji hajeru walenukni.”
Hiyáhoni satu yineru malixkatu tshanixiniphi himinjiywaklu halujinipa wane hyanu. Ptowru henejikolu hnikanu, hike rixa. Hihchinikanu tshinanu hi hepomhanna hanu ruchpajyatka nikalu.
Seyni satu wane tshininiphi: “Xye nikalni mayawletshicha henekalurni” htshininipa, hi hnikanru hinkaklewatatshri tshinanu, hiyrun-koxa hma kojwakahchinikanuxyawakanupa tshinanu.
Hi hixako hihchinikanu tshinanni seyni hinkaklewatatshri hchinikanu tshinanu. Pa katako satuko hepomhinwa: “Haklu tshinanhe satu yineru hchinikanu himaletno nma kamhiywakanru nmimalexikotu?”
Hiyrun-koxa wane htshina: “Hoyakalu npoyahnuxini nikkaluru tshinanu, kluneru tshinanhe napatko npoyahnutanrutka tshinanu?”
Hiyáhoni hnijini, hirini, kluneruktako hkamhini, ptowru potuko hkamhanu Hoyakalu himalwuxikolu tshinanu.
Hike hkamha rumtukahchinikanutjerupna judeu-ne, judeu mixkane koxa, hi Hoyakalu homkahitatshine hapatjetatshineko.
Hita pixka hixanu. Naluklu ptowruko nkamhaleru ptowruneka hpoyaho hichinikanuwkaklexyawakapa. Hi hitapka nepixjeru nujha seyni ptowru neruka hepixjerupa nujha, rumukata hiwekkaklexikowakapna.
Hita yimjetatshinephi hita pixka Cristo yimjetatshrino.
Suxone Halixatshrone Hixjexyawaka PiranapniKihleru ntshinanwakathi klu tshinanu hita hixjexyawaka hichinikjeta hiyrun-koxa nuykoxyahi pirana homkahjexyawaka tshinanu.
Naluklu himatjemyawaklu Cristo pirana ptowruneko yokanatatshrini. Hiyrun-koxa jeji suxo yokanatatshrini. Hoyakalu koxa Cristo yokanatatshrini.
Jeji ranjihohnexini ruchyajiwuxini ho Hoyakalu tokanu runkaklexini hi hkahwakpiratlu Cristo hyokanatjeru.
Suxo tma muchyajiwutkanuklunupa kihlero tchichyatlahixikowaka. Hiyáhoni tipatewaxinri tchichyajiwuxikolu ho tastakjiwuxikolu waneklu tuchyajiwutko.
Jeji hi rujhalu ruchyaljiwu klu tshinanu Hoyakalu yaholukni wale hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu hpoyahnuta. Seyni suxo jeji tpoyahnuta.
Klu tshinanu jeji hi suxo psojite hkamhika seyni suxo halikaka jeji psojite.
Jeji hi suxo tshinanu hkamhaka seyni suxo halikaka jeji tshinanu tkamhaka.
Hiyáhoni suxo hijhalu tojiwu tuchyaxyawaka tekhixyawaklu thanuru towutle tshijicha hwatshroni, hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrerune tenhohne hajene hetanu tshinanu.
Seyni wiwejinriya Cristo tshinanu hi rawa jeji tsonu, hi koxa twa suxo tsonu seyni ptowruneko hwa.
Klu tshinanu halikakni suxo jeji tuyakaxya seyni jeji koxa suxo matkaklu. Seyni ptowru potuko Hoyakalu hichpajya.
Hijhahchinikanyehkakanu hixkakluko. Kihle hetkolhe suxo muchyaljiwuto Hoyakalu tanjixini?
Hi he hixako hixannu hasrukhi jeji rojiwuwaxini, mkahwakpiratkotu rixlu rojiwuwle?
Seyni Hoyakalu heneklo suxo tojiwutsa. Tojiwutsa tuchyatjerupa tenekka.
Seyni satu yineru kahwajinri xye pirana npupjexyawaka waneya wla ntshinanru. Hikeni hiyrunuko xye pixkalutu womkahleru hiyrun-koxa Cristo halixatshine Hoyakalu hapatjetanune xyekaka tsonu romkahitna.
Jesus Cristo Hipnale Hichinijikowaka PiranapniXyekaka hiykolu nunkajinhi, hi nimalwuthi. Klu tshinanu hixa hapatjeru hkamhini hi repixna hapatjetatshine seyni rumtukna.
Klu tshinanu mitshikananhapka nyijnakotlu Cristo halixatshine hapatjexikowaka hapatjexini, hixa ptohkaka hitspaljexini waneya hima hkamnikakjeta. Hiyrunu xye pirana nalixa psotsonu.
Klu tshinanu rujhaklu hkaniprexikowakna hixkakluko ruphujewniywakapa halikaka pirana homkahitatshine hixa tskalaya.
Klu tshinanu hixa hapatjexini, hi Tsru Hixikatshriwa Cristo hipnale hichinijyawaka tshinanu hnika.
Klu tshinanu satkaka kochtshekhapkatlu hnikanrupa. Waneya pimrine hike nikatka seyni pimrine himetatka.
Hi he kapjihi hnijyawaka hiryawaka? Hixlahe heyikna Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine Hoyakalunune? Hiyahokni hixa patetjetna hike mwikane hixa tskala hapatjexikatshine. Ha xawakni klu pirana ntshinanhi? Numukathe kihler-pirana ntshinanwakaxyawakhi? Hike, wale pirana tshinanu hi nimalwuthi.
Klu tshinanu walekni Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus hinkajya piranno, walekni hix-koxa nunkakanu. Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus hkachixikolu yetshnopa, pão hkochtsheka.
Hoyakalu hpoyahnuta Jesus waneya hjiknajrotlu pão waneya wane htshina: “Xyekni nomane, hixa tshinanu jiknahkaluru. Xye pixkalutu hkamhajetanu hita hipnale hichinijikowakapa.”
Waneya waneko pixka rixlo copa stono, rali niklexinixkana. Wane htshina Jesus: “Twu copa stonha nunkakletleru waleni herotu nohraha piranni. Ptowru katako turiko copa stono wan-hixjetanu hita hipnale hichinijikolupa.”
Klu tshinanu ptowru katako xye pão hnijini hiyrunu twu copa stonha hirini, waleni Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus hipnale runkakleta haté rapojinpatnaka.
Hiyahokni katuktako Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus mane muchinikanretkatuko nijiniplu xye pão ho ruriniplo twu copa stonha Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus mane hiyrunu wale hraha hmajnakowaxya.
Hiyáhoni rujhahchinikanuxinwa satkaka wale nanwaka. Wan-hixatshinhi nikanru xye pão hiyrunu hirinro twu copa stono.
Klu tshinanu satu xye pão nijini ho twu copa stonha rurini hma muchinikanretkanuklunru Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus mane pirana waneya hnijinri hiyrunu rurinro waleko rapnokaxikolu yaholuni.
Wale tshinanukni hixa hixolunhi hyeyixjeta, hihrokjeta hiyrun-koxa satkaka hipnatka.
Mitshikananhapka wujhahchinikanuxinwa hix-nanuko hi rawanu jikolukanuru Hoyakaluya.
Klu tshinanu hikolukanuwnatshinepwu, wapnokatko Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakaluya wma mapnokaxikowakanupa xye psol-tshijneko hajeneya.
Hiyáhoni Cristo tshinanu nmoletanune, hixa hapatjexini Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus hipnale hichinikanrexyawaka hkahwakkakanu.
Satu yineru natshixinipa, hipjiko hnijini. Hiyáhoni hixa hi hikolukanuwnanu Hoyakaluya hapatjexinipa. Pimri pirankaka wane napojinipa nuhletanu.
Hixa himatlu, malixkane hixakanaxiniwa mayawletshichakaka mimat-yanumatkatu homkahjekanatatshinhi. Waneklu papko weyawlu homkahjekanatawa.
Hiyáhoni himatjemanru xye pirana, hike yineru htowuta Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru wla htshinyawaka — “Hamhatshripni Jesus.” — Hiyrun-koxa hike yineru himukata wla tshinreta: —“Jesus-ni Nutsrukate” — Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru masrukkanuklunru hi rumukata wan-tshinreta.
Kakojru Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru henekachale seyni Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru henekachalewatatshri satupkalu.
Kakojru Hoyakalu kamrure seyni Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu wtowutjeru satupkalu.
Himatkaltshi koxa kakoje seyni walerutni Hoyakalu himatkalnutshi heneklewatatshri Hoyakalu kamrure hkamhiywakapa satkaka.
Hoyakalu ptowru yineru repixyawaka tshinanu satkaka yineru reneklu hiphujewnakaklewatatshri pirana rimathexikowaka Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hixayma.
Wan-rixa. Satu yineru renek-himatkalnuta Hiwejikaluru potukalu Hoyakalu pirana runkaklexyawaka. Waneya walekotnaka satu yineru henek-himatkalnuta Hoyakalu pirana rimatjemyawakapa.
Walerutu Hiwejikaluru satu yineru reneka halixleta. Satuko yinerutnaka pixkontshi renekka yeyixlu rutskalajyawakapa.
Satuko yineru yoptotlu Hiwejikaluru potukalu pixkonu himyekaklewatatshri hkamhiywaka seyni satuko yineru renekka himatkalnutshi Hoyakalu pirana runkaklexyawaka. Satuko renekka himatkalnutshi rimathexyawakaplu pixkontshi renekachaxikolu Hoyakalu henejyalu ho satuko pixkontshi pnuko hichpajikatshri rimatheta. Satuko renekka pa nrukaka hyanumaxyawaka. Seyni satuko renekka pa nrukaka hyokajinripa.
Xyekaka ptowru potuko hkamha walerutu satupkalutu Hiwejikaluru. Satkaka reneka himatkalnuta waleko raluk-heneklexyalu pejnu.
Hi Heppika Psojitlu Cristo Mane SatupkalutuKlu tshinanu Cristo mane satupkalutu híxolu wale psojitenkaka. Hiyrun-koxa nyi Cristo mane psojite pixkalune, hixolune pa manepkana.
Hiyrun-koxa hixa ptowrunekwu ho judeu-nerunwu ho judeu mixkane ho hixa towretshinwu ho hixa hichpakatshinwu, wutakka hixa ptowrunekwu pa manepka wixikowaka walerutu Hiwejikaluruya. Hiyrun-koxa wutka hixa ptowrunekwu satupkalutu Hiwejikaluruya.
Klu tshinanu mantshi hi satupka rixka seyni hixo psojitlu mantshi.
Jixtshi wla tshinini — “Myotshi nmixkanu tshinanu hi mantshi psojitno.” — Seyni hi wale tshinanni hi mantshi psojite hma mixyawakanutkani.
Jeptshi wla tshinini — “Yhaltshi nmixkanu tshinanu, hi mantshi hajerno.” — Seyni hi wale tshinanni hi mantshi psojite hma mixyawakanutkani.
Mantshi psoluka yhaltshi tsonu rixkamka, hanhe xawaka rixa jemletanu? Ha psoluka hijnako tsonu rixkamka hanhe xawaka rixa hamluretanu mantshi?
Hiyáhoni xawakni Hoyakalu kamhalu mantshi psojitkaka kakojeru raluyjawak-potuko rixlu.
Himane psojitkaka mwaknumka, hi mantshini.
Hiyáhoni mantshi psojitkaka híxolu seyni pa manepka ruchpajya.
Hiyáhoni yhaltshi hi rumukata wan-tshinretlu: “Myotshi, hi hijhakaluryi.” Jiwtshi koxa hi himukata wan-tshinretlu: “Jixtshi hi hijhakaluryi.”
Seyni halikaka mantshi psojite mixahotkotu hijhakalurni mantshi psoluk-tshinanu.
Hiyrun-koxa mantshi psojite mkahwakpirpotutkotu walekni wuslahpotutanu. Walekaka hipatewluru walekni winotpotutanhonuka.
Wimane psojitkaka kihle hixahotkaluru hi rujhalu hislahikowaka. Hoyakalu wan-rixa kamhaletlu mantshi. Mantshi psoji mahaxikatshri hijhapotutlu repixikolu.
Wan-hixatshri hi hkamnikakna wimane psojitkaka seyni wannakakluko psojitkaka hepixkaka.
Satupka wimane psojite salewninipa, ptowruko wimane psojitkaka waleyma salewnanu. Satu wimane psojite himalwutkoklunu ptowruko wimane psojitkaka waleyma rumuwatatkana.
Hiyáhoni hixa ptowrunekhi Cristo manenhi. Hiyrun-koxa hix-satkakhi wale mane psojithi.
Wale tshinanu Hoyakalu satkaka himukatatshinhi rutaka Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshineya. Mitshikananhapka nuretkalune rutaka. Waneya wane pnute Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine rutaka. Wane pnutetnaka halixatshine hapatjetatshine hasrukatshine rutaka. Waneya wane pnute koxa halixatshine hapatjetatshine hepixatshine kakojerune rutaka. Wannani hiyákolu kamhatshine, yeyixlu hitskalaklewaxikatshine, kosekatshine, kakojeru nrutshi himat-yanumaxikatshine, hapkata hitakletkalunetkani wanna.
Ptowruneklahe nuretkalune? Ptowruneklahe Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine? Ptowruneklahe halixatshine hapatjetatshine hasrukatshine? Ptowruneklahe himyekkaklu kamhatshine?
Ptowruneklahe renekka yeyixlu rutskalajyawakna? Ptowruneklahe pa nrukaka himat-yanumaxya? Ptowruneklahe pa nrukaka himat-yokakatshri? Hike.
Hichiniklewlu PiranapniNumukatkamka yine nrukaka ho hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrerune tenhohne hajene nrukaka nyanumaxinimka seyni nma muchinikkanuklunru nimwastsireru hatatjewa hita ferro chpata ho lata-mta hitpetkaluro pixka nixa tsne, tsne, tsne hixatshro pixka nixachata.
Hoyakalu tokanu numukata hinkakletletkamka hiyrun-koxa nimatkamkalu ptowru piranako yohimatkaluru pirana hiyrun-koxa ptowru potuko himatkalewlu pirana nimatkamka, hiyrun-koxa nalixle pixkonu tshinanu haté teno mriji numukata yokmanjixleta seyni nma muchinikanretkanukluna nimwastsirene waneya hikepno hita.
Yáhomaklu ptowru potuko nimwaleru nenekachaxinna hike mwikane nohluxyawakapmakna ho nomane nenekachaxinna hyoxijikowakapa seyni nimwastsirene nma muchinikkanuklunu hike potuko nkochpaka hita.
Hanhe rixa hichiniklewlu? Waleni mchiretanutu, kihle hchinikanru. Hi hhahxalewata. Hi htserpiranaxnawa hiyrun-koxa hi ralixkoxnawa.
Hi hektutu hkamha. Hi walenupka rujha. Hi hjihekanuwhapkakanata. Hi rujhalu hektutu.
Hichiniklewatatshri hi hektutu tshinanu rumuwata seyni halikak-halikaka pirana himutlu wan-hixatshri.
Ptowru potuko rakota. Hikeklu rutuk-halixleta. Hoyakalu ralixa ptowruy-potuko. Ptowru potuko rakotachata.
Hichiniklewlu hi himat-nikawna. Halikaka Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletlu himat-nikawna. Pa nrukaka hyanumaxyawaka yineru koxa himat-nikawna. Himatkalewlu pirana koxa nikawnanu pa hohne.
Klu tshinanu wimatkale Hoyakalu henejyatkawu hiyrunu Hoyakalu tokanu wunkakletleru wale hi psolukni.
Seyni rapojinipa hike mmahaxikatu, wale psojitekananu nikawnanu.
Mturu nixakanaxini, mturu pixka nixa yanumleta, mturu pixka nixa himatjemleta hiyrun-koxa mturu hchinikanu pixka nixa. Seyni tsru nixinixka mturu hixannu nuchotatka.
Klu tshinanu xawakni hi wuhle hetlepotutlu Hoyakalu hatatjewa hanihapi rexika. Seyni pa hohnepa hihoj-potuko wexinri. Xawakni psotsonu nimata seyni pa hohnepa nimathetpotutanru, wale rixa himathetlexyawakno pixka.
Xawakni rawa Hoyakalu walixyawaka hiyrunu Hoyakalu wkahwakachaxyawaka hiyrun-koxa pimrine wuchinijyawaka. Xye mapa. Seyni nyi mapa pimrine wuchinijyawaka waleni tsru potuko.
Hoyakalu Tokanu Hinkakletatshri Potu Hijhakaluru Seyni Pa Nrukaka Himat-yanumaxikatshri Hi Hijhakalur-potu PiranapniPimrine hichinijyawak-potu homkahitanu. Hoyakalu henekachalkaka Hiwejikaluruya koxa hikamtu seyni Hoyakalu tokanu hinkaklexyawakapa jmereypotpakhi.
Klu tshinanu pa nru yanumaxikatshri Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru pixkonuyma tshinanu hi yine riynumsata seyni Hoyakalu riynumsata. Klu tshinanu hike himatjemlu. Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru pixkonuyma hyanumaxyalu halikaka pirana yine mimatanutu.
Seyni halikak-potu Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri hyanumaxini jematshine tshinanukni runkaklewata. Tseruwakahchinikanru pirana runkakna. Ruykotna hiyrun-koxa hapnanuhchinikanru pirana runkakna.
Pa nru yanumaxikatshri, Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru pixkonu tshinanu wale nanwaka htseruwakahchinikanuxnawa. Seyni Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri htseruwakahchinikanutna Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine.
Hitamka halukhi hixa ptowrunekhi pa nrukaka hyanumaxyawaka Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru pixkonu tshinanu. Seyni wane pnute naluklu Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine hixyawaka. Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri potu hijhakaluru seyni pa nrukaka himat-yanumaxikatshri Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru pixkonu tshinanu, hi hijhakalur-potni wale pa nrukaka himata yokakatshri mwaknuklunu. Halikaka rawini pa nrukaka yanumaxikatshri tokanu hiphujetatshri htserutahchinikanutna Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine.
Hiyáhoni xawakni hixa napyehixini waneya pa nru nyanumyehixinhi, hanhe xawaka rixa hepixletanhi nma munkakkanuklunhi Hoyakalu hinkajyano pirana ho himatkalewlu pirana Hoyakalu heneklewaxya, ho satu hinkaklu Hoyakalu piranaya, ho satuko hasruklewlu?
Waneko pixka rixa, yine tokanu mpohijetanhimatu. Hetanru tokluru ho tumleji ho violão. Hanhe xawaka rixa himatjemletluna jematshine klu hima htokatna phujewaka hma tshina tokletkanuklunna?
Tpohinewaxini kowi seyni tma pohinewpotutkanuklunu katu halpokoxinwa hiylalu hnapu?
Hix-koxa waneko pixka hixa, phujetanuwak-potuko hma tshina yanumletkanuklunu htokanuya. Kathe himatjemanru hixa htokanu? Halikaka hike mimatjemkanuklunru hixa htokanu, hatatjewa hihimachani.
Hi pejnu himakananru pnu pejnu tshinhimatatshri xye psol-tshijneko hwatshri. Hiyrun-koxa satkaka xye tokantshi hi htshinachata.
Seyni hita nmimatjemkanuklunru hanukta htshina niynumsatjeru, waneya pa neruko nkahwaklu. Hit-koxa pa neruko hkahwakanno wale.
Jmerpotuphi henekachalkaka tshinanu Hoyakalu henejyawu walenuko Hiwejikaluruya. Hiyáhoni xawakni hijhapotutanru satkaka henekachalu Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine hchinikanu hepixatshri potuko.
Hiyáhoni katukta pa nru yanumaxini rujhalu Hoyakalu ranjixyawaka rumukata hiphujtalexyawakaplu htokanu htshinakanaxyawaka.
Klu tshinanu pa nru nanjihohnexini Hoyakalu pixkonu tshinanu, halikaka niwejinriymamka nanjihohneta seyni hi nohchinikanuko himatjemlu nanjihohnere.
Hiyáhoni wla nixanu. Niwejinriyma nanjihohnetanu hiyrun-koxa nohchinikanuyma nanjihohnetanu. Nchikalewatanu niwejinriyma hiyrun-koxa nohchinikanuyma nchikalewatanu.
Wane hmixkanuklunu Hoyakalu himalwuxini hiwejinriyma hanhe xawaka rixa hixayma hapatjeretna herone wla htshinyawakapna hehe wane potuko ptshinru xye pirana hma mimatjemkanuklunupluna ptshinakanaxyawaka.
Npoyahnutlu Hoyakalu pa nrukaka nyanumaxyawaka hixa ptowrunekhi pnute.
Seyni Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine tskalaya nalukmaklu yáholu cinco tokantshi nyanumaxyawaka nohchinikanuyma pimrine nasrujyawaka. Klu tshinanu yahmaklu dez mil tokantshi pnute pa neru tokanu nyanumaxikmaka hi repixlewata.
Pa Nru Hyanumaxyawaka Waleni Hetkaluru Malixkane Tshinanu PiranapniCristo tshinanu nmoletanune, hi mturune pixka hixanu hihchinikanuya seyni halikaka hektutu hmasatanu. Halikaka hihchinikanuya tsrune hixinwa.
Wane htshina tokantshi yonatkaluru Hoyakalu henejyawu: Wane htshina Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu: “Nyi yine niynumatanu. Niynumatanna pa neru namaya hiyrun-koxa pa nrukakayma nunkakjixinna. Seyni hi wanekluko hyijnakotannona nonerune”, htshina Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu.
Klu tshinanu pa nrukaka hyanumaxyawaka Hoyakalu pixkonu tshinanu, waleni hetkaluru malixkane tshinanni, hi Cristo halixatshine tshinanni. Seyni Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletlu, waleni hetkaluru Cristo halixatshine tshinanu, hi malixkane tshinanni.
Satu yapkaklu, Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine ptowruneka hapatjexini wannapka waneya ptowruneka pa nru pejnu hyinuwaka yanumlexinipna. Waneya hjihlojinipna herone ho malixkane hi he jipukalerune rikahwakkona?
Seyni ptowruneka Hoyakalu tokanu hinkaklexini waneya hjihlokamxinipa satu malixkatu ho herotu, hjemamxiniplu hixa tokanu waneya rimathexinwa muhletu rixyawaka hiyrun-koxa tokantshikaka hjemanru tshinanu hiykotatkalu.
Hihchinikanu hichinikanretlerkaka yohimatkaluru ruphujetko. Waneya ruphamtanu Hoyakalu hetanuya, rimalwutanru Hoyakalu. Waneya wane htshinanu: “Halikakni hix-yehi rawa Hoyakalu.”
Kihle Rixpotuxikowaka Hapatjexikowaka PiranapniCristo tshinanu nmoletanune, xyekni naluka tshinreta. Hixa hapatjexini satkaka waneylu chikaltshi. Satu waneylu hasruklewlu. Satu waneylu hiphujetkaluru Hoyakalu piranaya. Satu waneylu pa nru hyanumaxyawaka Hoyakalu pixkonuyma, raw-koxa himata yokakatshri. Ptowru potuko hkamhanu halixatshine hapatjetatshine repixyawakapa.
Satu yineru pa nru hyanumaxini, Hoyakalu pixkonu tshinanu, hepipka yanumatanu. Hi mapa pnute yanumatanu. Satkaka hapka yanumatanu. Waneya satu yokakanru.
Seyni yokakatshri mwaknuklunu potshkeplu pa nru yanumpiraxikatshri Cristo halixatshine hapatjexyawakaya. Wale nanwaka tsonu hiynumsaxinwa hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu riynumatanu.
Hiyrun-koxa wan-hixanu, ho hepi ho mapa yine Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletanu, waneya pimrine hijhahchinikanutanu.
Seyni satu yineru wane tuplakanatatshri koxa pa pirana hyoptoxinipa Hoyakaluya hinkaklewakanatatshritshi potshkepa.
Klu tshinanu hixa ptowrunekhi himukata hinkakletletlu Hoyakalu tokanu hiyáhoni ptowrunekhi hasrukkalunephi hiyrun-koxa hapnanuhchinikankakkalunephi.
Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri runkaklewaxini rimatan-koxa, runkakle hi towutanru seyni halikaka wale towutanru runkaklewle.
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu hi sejirewnakjixa seyni raluklu kihlepoko rixyawaka. Wan-rixanna ptowruneka Jesus halixatshine potukalune hapatjetatshine hapatjexikowakkakaya.
Suxone potshkepa Cristo halixatshine hapatjexikowakkakaya. Klu tshinanu hi ritshitkana hyanumaxyawakna seyni hyijnakotanna. Moisés yonreru wan-tshina suxone hi towutlewatanu.
Seyni suxone raluk-himatlexinipluna pa pirana, hipjina wannako hhanurna repomhinna. Klu tshinanu kapatmenro Cristo halixatshine hapatjexikowaka tyanumaxini suxo.
Hixaklahe hakaniklu Hoyakalu tokanu? Hi he xawaka hix-yehi rapokachata halikaka Hoyakalu tokanu?
Satu yineru Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri rikahwajinipwa hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru himwatshri rixahoxinipwa, rimathetanru xye nyonaxyawaka pirana waleni Hoyakalu yokanreru piranni.
Seyni satu yineru haluka majnakowlexiniplu xye nyokanre pirana, hike yijnakotan-koxlu wale.
Hiyáhoni Cristo tshinanu nmoletanune, jmererunpotuphi Hoyakalu tokanu hinkaklexyawaka. Hiyrun-koxa hike xako himaletanru Hoyakalu pixkonu tshinanu pa nrukaka himat-yanumaxikatshri.
Ptowru potuko kihlerupni hixa tskalaya hiyrun-koxa hihlepokotkalurutkani.
Cristo Hiwejinixnaka PiranapniCristo tshinanu nmoletanune, nuchinikkakhi kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana, nunkakle pirana. Hixa nunkakatkalu. Hixa yoptotatkalu hiyáhoni xawakni hixa poyehi halixlerunetkahi wale pirana tshinanu.
Wale pirana koxa hiwekkakhi, hixa himrexinri kihler-potuko tokantshi nunkaklewyehixyatkahi. Ho hmahijeru halixlexini tsonni.
Mitshikananhapka nunkajikolu pirana nunkakatkahi. Walekni, Cristo hipnapya wektunu tshinanu yonatkaluru Hoyakalu tshinyawaka pixka.
Waneya hkapnatka Cristo. Waneya map-hohne rixinri riwekatnaka, Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru tshinyawaka pixka.
Waneya Pedro tshinkaluru hetlu waneya pimrine riyanjerene koxa doze hetlu.
Waneya wanna quinhentos pnute hetlu wanna ptowruneka Cristo homkahitatshinni. Pa hetkolutu rixluna. Hixo Cristo hetatshine hiwekawa seyni pimrinni hipnanatka.
Waneya rapkatlepapkotka hita ruphujewnayehitatka. Hita hatatjewa pa papkoko matutatshrino.
Klu tshinanu ptowruneka nuretkalune pnute mujhakotno hita. Himka npoyahotlu Hoyakalu nuretanru ntshinikowaka klu tshinanu Hoyakalunerune Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine nkamnijekanata.
Seyni Hoyakalu hihlenu tshinanu, hitatkani hita. Hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu hihlenu hi mahijerutatka hita tshinanu. Klu tshinanu nuretkalune kamrurewle pnute nixa kamrurewleta hita. Halikaka hi hit-potni seyni Hoyakalu hihlenu hitaymalutu kamrurewata.
Hiyáhoni ho hita tshinanu ho wanna tshinanu hike rixa. Seyni hixa ptowrunekwu hinkaklewata. Wale piranakni halixatka hixa.
Halixatshine Hiwejinixnaka PiranapniHi he wunkakle Cristo hipuktshi hichpajyatka riwejyawakatnaka piranni? Klu tshinanhe xawaka hixa satkaka wan-tshina hipnatshine hi hiwekanutnaka?
Hipuktshi hichpajikatshri mwaknumka Cristo-mka koxa hi hiwekanu.
Cristo hma miwekkanumka waneyamka wmahijeru hinkaklewletanu hiyrun-koxa hixamka mahijeru halixletanutka.
Hiyrun-koxa wane pnute wan-rixkamka Hoyakalu wweyata. Klu tshinanu wunkajyapiranhi Hoyakalu hipuktshi riwekkajyawaklu Cristo pirana. Hipnatshine miwejyawakanutnaka pirana halikaka rixkamka Hoyakalumka hi hiwekkakanru Cristo hipuktshiya.
Klu tshinanu hipnatshinetka hma miwekkanumkana, Cristo koxamka hi hiwekanutnaka.
Hiyáhoni Cristo miwekkanumkatnaka walixlemka mahijerutanu. Hiyáhomakni hixa hamhatshinenaphi hektunu tshinanu.
Wan-rixkamka Cristo halixatshineko hipnikanemka hamhachatatshinepmakni.
Xye wiwejinri tsonu tshinanu riwekkakkamkawu Cristo, hikemka pnute wkahwakanutka, waneyamka ptowru yinni pnute wamonnu wuchpajini.
Hipnatshine Tskalaya Mitshikananu Hiwekatshrini Cristo PiranapniSeyni halikaka Cristo hiwekatnaka hipnatshine tskalaya. Cristo hiwejyawaka tshinanu rimatka hipnatshine hiwekanutnaka.
Satupka yineru tshinanu rawa hipuktshi. Waney-koxa satupka yineru tshinan-koxa rawa hiweklutnaka.
Hiyáhoni Adão tshinanu ptowru neruka hipnanu. Waney-koxa Cristo tshinanu ptowru neruka hiwekkakko.
Seyni satkaka yineru hiwekkakko waleko hipapkolu. Cristo-ni mitshikananu hiwekatshri. Waneya hapkata hiwekletatshinepni Cristo-nune runinipa wale.
Waneya wane pnute xye hohne nikawnanu. Cristo nikaxiniplu ptowru hiweklunkaka towutle, ptowru towutatshine towutle, ptowru himukatlu koxa waneya ruru, Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka renekanru.
Klu tshinanu Cristo hijhalu htowutlewaxyawaka haté ptowruneka hkamnitjene hkatsretanu Hoyakalu.
Hapkatatatshri potukni hipuktshi wkamnitjeru. Hoyakalu nikatanru wale.
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru wan-tshina: “Hoyakalu ptowru potuko hijixi hpuko rutakanru.” Seyni wimatjemyawaklu wla htshinini ptowru potuko htshinini, hi Hoyakalu kojeru hkochtsheka. Ptowru potuko Cristo reneka Hoyakalu htowuxyawakaplu.
Ptowru potuko Cristo renekko htowuxyawakaplu waneya waleko whentshi, Hoyakalu towutlewle hpuko rutajinwa. Xye Cristo ptowru potuko htowuxyawaka renekjerni Hoyakalu. Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu towutanru ptowru potpako.
Hma Miwekkajikowakanumkapna Hipnatshine PiranapniXawakni nepomhanhi hipnatshinni tshinanu batiza-tkalune pirana tshinanu. Hipnatshinni hi hiwekahotna seyni haklu tshinanhe satkaka yineru batiza-tka hipnatshinni tshinanu?
Ha hix-koxa, haklu tshinanhe ptowru hora-ko kyowikowaka wwahohnekanata?
Cristo tshinanu nmoletanune, ptowru hohneruka hipuktshistsi nwa. Xye ntshinhi nunkakhi. Cristo Jesus Wutsrukate tshinanu nalixkothi.
Hewi, Éfeso poktshi, hejnune kmatsyirune nyahotkamka. Hiyáhoni xye niwekle tsonu nkahwajini kluhe repixinno? Hipnatshinetka hikeklu hma miwekkanumkatkana wlamka wtshinanu wuya wnikanu, wuranu klu tshinanu yetshikawa wupnanutka.
Hi yokwijetkalunephi. Klu tshinanu hektutu himatletkaluru himtuklu hixannutshi kihleru.
Hsatokanu, hihlepokoxinwa. Hi Hoyakalu tokanu hmajnakowaxini. Klu tshinanu satkaka hi Hoyakalu halukleru rimata. Wane ntshina npatetjexyawakaphi.
Hipnatshri Hixmanexyawakpatka PiranapniSeyni satu hetkoko wla htshinanu: “Hanhe xawaka rixa hipuktshi hiwekkajikaluru? Hiyrun-koxa hanhe rixmanetna wan-hixatshine?”
Mimatkat-potukni wale pirana hepomhatshri. Hitataji honra putajinri rupnahapkatanu wan-rixini tsonu ruptshekanu.
Seyni Hoyakalu henekmanetlu hitataji hanu pot-raluk-hixkakletlu. Pa neru tataji pejnu waleko himane renekka.
Kahituru hi pa hiturutni. Seyni pnuko rixhituta yineru, nikalune pnuko hixhituta, chimane pnuko hixhituta, kochitshine pnuko hixhituta.
Wanetkalu tenhohne hajeru mantshi sahikaka hiyrun-koxa xye tshiji hajeru manekaka. Seyni tenhohne hajeru mantshi sahikaka hihlenu satuko hiyrun-koxa xye tshiji hajeru manekaka hihlenu satukotkani wale.
Tkatshi pnuko rix-hatnutka, ksuru pnuko rixhatnutatnaka, katahiri hatnu satuko. Haté katahirkaka kakoj-hatnu rixna satkaka.
Waneko pixka rixanna yine Hoyakalu, hipnatshine riwekkajinipa. Mantshini himat-hijpahatshri kapnatko, hitataji pixka, seyni wale riwekkakko hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupni.
Mantshi kapnatka rumtuknu tshinanu. Seyni riwekkakko kihlepotpaklu. Hiyrun-koxa hihropowatatshri hkapnaxika seyni hixkolu hyotunokajikotka.
Mantshi xye tshijikni. Hkapnatka seyni riwekkakkoklunpatka Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru mantshi mixkotatshri tshinanu. Rawa xye tshiji hajeru mantshi hiyáhoni raw-koxa Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru mantshi mixkotatshri.
Wane htshina Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru: “Hoyakalu hiyakotlu Adão waleni mitshikananu yineru mantshi hiwekatshri rixyawakapa.” Seyni hapkatatatshri Adão waleni hiwejikaluru hiwekkaklewatatshrini.
Halikaka mitshikananu hakanhatshri hi hiwekatshrini. Seyni xye tshijneko kamhikolni. Waneya wane pnute rakanhatka hiweklu mnikawnakatu.
Mitshikananu Adão waleni tshiji hajeru tshiji kamhikolni. Seyni hapkatatatshri Adão waleni Tsru Hixikatshriwa tenhohne hajerni.
Xye tshijne hajene, xye tshiji kamhikolu pixka rixna. Hiyrun-koxa tenhohne hajene tenhohne hichpajikatshri pixka rixna.
Hiyáhoni tshiji hajeru pixka wixyahluta hiyahok-koxni Tenhohne Hajeru yáholu pixka wixan-koxa.
Hiwekatshineko Hemanexikowaka PiranapniNmoletanune Cristo tshinanu, xyekni naluka tshinrethi hixa. Hittshi hiyrunu hrahtshi kamhakaluru hi himukata jihlokletlu Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka. Hiyrun-koxa himat-nikawnatshri hi renekka hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatu rixyawaka.
Hyijnakpotutanru xye hima yohimakanatkalur-pirana. Hi ptowrunekwu hipnanu seyni hixa ptowrunekwu hemanetko.
Pchini tsonujiji himruklu pa teyaknuplu hapkat-himpotutatshro kowiklu wan-hixko. Kowi hajpokko waneya hipnakanatatshinetka hiwekanutnaka, hikeklu hohne mnikawnakanpatkani. Ptowrunekwu hemanetanutka.
Klu tshinanu mantshi himat-nikawnatshri hijhalu hyochmajyawaklu hikeklu hohne mnikawna menu. Hiyrunu hipnatshripatka hijhalu mimat-hipnakatu hyochmajnawakwa.
Hiyáhoni himat-nikawnatshri hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatu hyochmakkoklunutka. Hiyrun-koxa himat-hipnatshri mimat-hipnakatu hyochmakkoklunutka, rakanhanutka Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru hiwekkaklewatatshri tshinyawaka: “Hipuktshi nikatkatka. Kayatkaluru psoluko!”
“Hipuktshi, ha hanurhe pkayleru? Hanurhe ppixkonu yine pumtujinri?
Hipuktshi mixkowkakatshrini hektuntshi. Hiyrun-koxa hektuntshi mixkowkakatshrini yonruru pirana.”
Seyni Hoyakalu wimalwutanu, wale honukla ptowru potuko wiknohkakjeru Wutsrukate Jesus Cristo tshinanu!
