Judeia Hajene Tshinanu Hapatjetkaluro Tiyiro PiranapniXawaknipa hapatjetkaluro tiyiro Jesus halixatshine potukalune Judeia tshijne hajene tshinanu pirana. Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshin-yehkaka Galácia tshijne hajene nixakjixyawaka pixka potuko nixakjixhi.
Ptowru domingo hohne hkanipretanru tiyiro psoji waneya himretanru. Satkaka yineru rumukata hikchiklexyawaka pso tiyiro rutakanu. Wan-hixinpatka hi nujhalu tiyiro napatjexyawakpatka hita hix-yehi napojinpatka.
Wane napojinpatka nyokanatanna hixa nuretanunetka Jerusalém poktshi nwaka hyiywakapna tiyiro henekachluro hixa henekachale ranijyawakapna. Yonawahlo koxa nyokanatanu kihle yoptole rixikowakapna pirana.
