Kayatatshinwu Cristo Tshinanu PiranapniSeyni nimalwutlu Hoyakalu Cristo-ymalunwu wixyawaka tshinanu kayatatshine rixkakjexyawakwu ptowru hohneruka tshinanu. Hiyrun-koxa Cristo himatyehixikolu pirana kihlephalu pixkalutni wan-rixkaklu hixaya ptowru sretako hyakaklu.
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu renekanwu Cristo hatatjewa kihlepha hixatshinwu hiwekkakkalune yehiya hiyrun-koxa hamhatshine yehiya.
Yine hiwekkakkalunetka tshinanu kihlephalu pixka rixa hiweklu heneklewatatshri seyni hamhatshine tshinanupa hijpahlupha pixka rixa ruylatjerupna. Rawhe yineru xyekaka poyahkakatshri?
