Klu tshinanu wiwekka pchinika jhamlewaka wwahnapuwakata Jesus pirana tshinanu Jesus hiwekle koxa hiphujetkalurupni wimane himat-hipnatshri hetanuya.
Hiyahokni ptowru hohneruka hipuktshi hetumhawu seyni wanepnawaka hixa riwekkakhonuka.
Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru mitshikawlur-pirana wan-tshin-yonhata: “Nalixa hiyáhoni nyanumata.” Hiyáhoni hix-koxa himwalu walerutu walixle hchinikanu. Cristo walixa hiyáhoni wyanumata.
Klu tshinanu wimatlu Hoyakalu honra Wutsrukate Jesus hipuktshi yehi riwekkajyatkalu, hix-koxa hipuktshi yehi riwekkajinwu Jesus pixka. Hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu Jesus yehi ranikanwu hixaymakananuko.
Xye ptowruka hakanhatka hixa hepixikowaka tshinanupa. Wale tshinanu Hoyakalu hihlenu himukatatshri potuko hapokyehitna hixolune yin-yehi. Hiyáhoni nyipa yine himalwutanru Hoyakalu hanjihohneruya, hpohixikowakapa Hoyakalu.
Xye papko salewaktshijiji wetjereru pchini hohnejiji tsonu hkojwakanwu. Seyni xye salewaktshijiji hapnutpatka yohnika tsru potuko hoyaknutshi hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupni.
Klu tshinanu hi wkahwakpirpotutlu hetjejrurkaka seyni ptowruka metkotkaka halikaka wkahwakpirata. Klu tshinanu ptowru hetjejrurkaka pchini tsonu nikawnanu. Seyni metkotkaka hikeklu hohne nikawnanu.
Pantshi Myotshi Mkamhanutu PiranapniKlu tshinanu hewi tshiji wwaka pchinika wimankaka himajetshrikaka pixka hixatshrini. Seyni wimatlu xye wimajeru pixkalutu nikatkoklunupa wenekko pantshi Hoyakalu kamhaleru. Hi yinemyo kamhapjitanruni seyni wale hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupni tenhohne hajerupjini.
Wiwekka pchinika wimane hitokote kaheknanuwata wchireta. Walukpotutlu wjihlojyawaklu tenhohne hajerupji.
Hiyáhoni tenhohne hajerupji wjihlojinpatka hi mapjine pixka wixanutka.
Klu tshinanu xye wimane himajertshi pixkalutu wwaka pchinika, wkaheknanuwata wchireta. Himka waluklu wimane hkomkahikowaka seyni walukpotutlu wmakaxikowaka tenhohne hajeruya. Waneyapa hiwejikaluru nikatanru himat-nikawnatshri.
Hoyakalukni wyokmanakjixjeru. Hiyrun-koxa renekwu walenuko Hiwejikaluru rimaxikowaka ptowru potuko wenekka.
Hiyáhoni hi wutuka munanhaletlu. Wimatlu xye wimane wwaka pchinika howukawalu wwiywakapa, Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu yehi hajeru.
Klu tshinanu walixle wiwejya. Seyni hi wetjereru wiwejya.
Poyikolun-potukwu. Xyemka wimane waluk-hiknokleta Tsru Hixikatshriwa Cristo-yma wiwejyawakapa.
Seyni ptowruka pnute kihlerni hpoyikoxikowaka Tsru Hixikatshriwa Cristo, ho xye wimane wwaka pchinika, ho Tsru Hixikatshriwa Cristo-yma wiwejyawakapa.
Klu tshinanu hixa ptowrunekwu Cristo hoji sreta wuphujewnini. Cristo hijhahchinikanyehitanwu hixa ptowrunekwu. Waneya satkaka yoptotanru hkayleru xye tshiji hajeru mantshi kamrure wenru ho kihlerhe hkamhaleru ho hektutra.
Wimatletlu Hoyakalu, Hituru Cristo Tshinanu PiranapniTsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hamlenu pirana wimata. Hiyáhoni wujhalu walixkajyawakna yine halikakalutu pirana. Hoyakalu himathetwu psol-potuyako. Hiyrun-koxa nkahwaka hix-koxa himathetahchinikanutwu.
Himka waluklu hixa nanwaka kihle piran-yehi hixnawakwa. Seyni waluklu hix-yehi htseruwpiranaxyawaka wipirana. Waneyapa hix-koxa kapiranayaphi kihler-pirana himat-hinkajyawakapna wipirana pimrine rohocha tsonu hikchikhihlenuxikatshine seyni hi rajiynina.
Klu tshinanu mahchinikanune wkahwakkoklunu, Hoyakalu tshinanu wane wixa. Hiyrun-koxa kahchinikanurune wikahwakkoklunu hixa tshinanukni wane wixa.
Klu tshinanu Cristo hichinijyawakwu tshinanu wihchinikanu hkoseta. Klu tshinanu wimatlu satupka yineru hipnatka ptowrunek-yine tshinanu. Hiyáhoni hatatjewa ptowrunekwu hipnatka waleyma.
Ptowrunek-yine tshinanu rupnatka Cristo hiyáhoni hiwekatshine hi wannako ralujyawaka hkamhanna seyni halikaka riwekanna Cristo halujyawaka hkamhinipna, wanna tshinanu hipnapatshri, hiyrun-koxa wanna tshinanu hipuktshi hiwekkajikatshriwa.
Hiyáhoni xawakni hike yineru hchinikanu wetanu yine hchinikanu hixjexyawaka. Mitshikananu wane wixjejtaplu Cristo seyni xawakni hi wane wixa himatletanutkalu.
Cristo-yma hwatshritka herotu yinerutkani. Mitshikananu rixjekanaxyawaka nikawnatka. Hiyáhoni xawakni herotutkani.
Xye ptowruka Hoyakalu kamrurni. Hoyakalu wan-hixkaklu Cristo. Wale tshinanu hixa Cristo kamnikanatatshinwu hiprotaka rimatletanune wixyawaka. Hiyrun-koxa renek-kamruretwu pimrine wimatletkajyawaklu Hoyakalu.
Xyekni wunkakle: Hoyakalu hi hitajyana yine rektunna. Hoyakalu Cristo hoho hyapa ptowrunek-yine rimatlexyawakapa. Hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu henekwu xye hinkaklu, Hoyakalu himukata himatletlexyawakapna yine pirana, wunkakletjeta.
Hiyáhoni xawakni Cristo hitshre tshinanu wunkaklewjeta, hatatjewa Hoyakalu tshanixhi hixa wunkakle tokanuya. Cristo hitshre tshinanu nanjithi hixa Hoyakalu kamnikanatatshinhi himatletkotka Hoyakaluya.
Hektuntshi mimwakatni Cristo seyni wanepnawaka Hoyakalu hapnokatlu Cristo wektunu tshinanu, wpoyaho potukawnalexyawaka Hoyakalu hetanuya.
Hiyáhoni hixa rikamrurewatanunwu hanjithi Hoyakalu kamrureya: Hi himnanhinri Hoyakalu hihlenu wale honukla renekatkahi Hoyakalu.
“Hyijnakotanru Hoyakalu tshinyawaka: Hijhiniklunru hohneno nyijnakothi, Nepixatkahi hiwekkajikolu hohne tshinanuya.” Hyijnakotanu. Xawakni halikaka hipapkolutkani hyoptoxikowaka Hoyakalu hepixle. Xawakni potuko hihohnerutkani hiwekkajikowaka hixa.
Hi waluklu satu yineru het-himtuknuxyawaklu wkamrure hma mukolukanuwniywakanupa wkamrure tshinanu.
Seyni ptowru piranako wekhithi Hoyakalu kamrurewyehitatshinwu wixyawaka. Hi wkaheknanuwata wsalewnini, wmahaxinri tshinanuya hiyrun-koxa wkojwawninri tshinanuya.
Wuylakjetka, kapna wyochmakjetka, sejirtshiyma wsaletjetka. Wkamrurewpotjeta, mamkanwu, wnatshita.
Wuphujetlu Hoyakalu kamrurewyehitatshinwu wixyawaka. Wpotuknu tshinanuya, wimatkalnu tshinanuya, wsalewaklu wakotle tshinanu hiyrun-koxa wuhlenuhchinikanu tshinanu. Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hoho wyapa hiyrun-koxa hichiniklewlu halikakalutu potuko tshinanu wane wixa.
Kihle piranyehirunwu hiyrun-koxa hektu pirana yehirunwu. Kihle piranalu wtshinanwakatka, weyikka koxa. Halikaka pirana hinkakletatshinwu seyni kayloklerune wkahwakka.
Mimatletkone pixkalunwu hiyrun-koxa himatletkalune pixkalun-potwu. Hipnatshine pixkalunwu seyni hetwu hiwekatshinewawu haté xawakni. Hapnokatkalunwu seyni hi wuylatka.
Wamonuwnatshine hikahwakkalunwu seyni hi wutuk-poyikowleta. Hike mwikane pixkalunwu seyni hixolune yine wpohirewnakaka. Hatatjewa mejnunkatenwu seyni halikaka ptowru potuko wimwa.
Wuchinikanune wimatletanune Corinto poktshi hajene, wunkakpotuthi hixa, wuchinikpotuthi.
Hi hkahwakanu wma muchinijyawakanhi seyni hix-hetko halikaka hi hichinikjetwu hixa.
Nowhenene pixka nixa yanumsayehrethi. Wuchinijyawakhi pixka hixa hichinikletanwu hixa.
Malixkane Wma Miyanyawakanupa PiranapniHi malixkaneyma hyananu. Hanhe xawaka rumukata pixkakaklu hixleta halikakalutu pirana weyawluyma? Hanhe xawaka rumukata pixkakaklu hixleta katalu, mapchahaluyma?
Hiyrun-koxa hanhe xawaka rumukata Cristo-yma pa hchinikanurutu rixyawaka kamtshi? Hanhe xawaka rumukata pixkakaklu hixleta Cristo halixatshri malixkatuyma?
Hanhe xawaka rumukata pixkakaklu hixleta Hoyakalupji mayawletshichayma malixkane munanhaleru? Klu tshinanu hixakni Hoyakalu Hiwejikalurupjiwu. Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu potuko hali wan-tshinretatka: “Wanna hitokote nwanu, wanna nyanini. Royakalutepnona. Wannapni nayinetene.”
Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu wan-tshina hiyrunukotnaka: “Hiyáhoni wanna yehi hichpajini Wanna yehi hkotspalaxinwa. Kaptsholu, himtuklewatatshri hi hyotnekanu. Wan-hixatshri kihle yoptole nixanu.
Hirpakno hita, hixpakni nowhenene hiyrun-koxa nwuheneronephi — wane htshina Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu ptowru potuko himukatatshri.”
Nuchinikanune nimatletlene, xye ptowruka Hoyakalu hinkaklexyapiranwu hixanni. Hiyáhoni xawakni hpowraxinwa ptowru hixatshri wimane pitshotatshriya hiyrun-koxa wsamenru. Potukalun-potu wixinwa ptowru hohneruka Hoyakalu kahwakpiraxikol-tshinanu.
Paulo Hichinijyawakna Corinto Poktshi Hajene PiranapniHikchikahwawakletanwu hihchinikanuya wwiywakapa. Hi satukna hixa wyotneta. Hi satukna hixa wumtuka. Hike yineru wkonapahixanutechata.
Hi wane ntshina, njihyehixyawakaphi. Klu tshinanu wane mitshi ntshinatkahi hixakni wuchinikpotutanunhi hiyáhoni hike kotspalkakanwu ho wupnini ho wiwejini.
Hixa nmunanhapotuta hiyrun-koxa ntserutahchinikanuxnawa hixa pirana tshinanu. Napnanuhchinikanuta hiyrun-koxa numuwpotuthonuka ptowruka wsaletjeru tshinanuya.
Macedônia tshijne wapokkawaka hi wapnanuta. Ptowru sretako wexyalu kojwaklu, yahotkaklu hiyrun-koxa wpikle weta hitok-hajiya.
Seyni Hoyakalu honukla kojwakahchinikanutatshri hepixatshri, Tito tshinkaluru hapokle tshinanu htserutahchinikanutatkawu.
Hi Tito hapokle tshinanu tsonni seynikta hixa Tito hpoyikotahchinikanuxyawaka pirana tshinan-koxni. Runkakno hixa pirana. Hix-hima hichinikno. Hix-hima wamonuwata hita nopirana tshinanu haté hit-hima himatshwahpirata. Hiyáhoni xye pirana tshinanu xawakni pnut-potu numuwata.
Hi nehchinikanuta yonawahlo hixa nwaka nyokanreru tshinanu. Netkamkalo yonawahlo nyokanatanro pchini hohnejiji twamontakamkahi nehchinikanutanmaka.
Seyni xawakni npoyikowata yonawahlo nyokanatanro tshinanu hi twamontakhi seyni halikaka hwamonnu hehchinikankakatkahi. Hoyakalu hixkajyawaklu hwamonnu tshinanu hehchinikanutatka hiyáhoni hi psojikna wumtukatkahi.
Klu tshinanu wamonuwnalu Hoyakalu henejyahi hehchinikankaklewata riwekkakko pupjekanatatshri. Wale tshinanu hi wwamonuwnanu hixa. Seyni wamonuwnalu xye tshijne heneklewle hipuktshi reneklewata.
Haha hetanu hanu rixhi Hoyakalu hwamonuwnal-tshinanu: mchikohchinikanune rixkakhi, hiyáhoni hijhahapkatatkalu hekhixyawaklu hi ntshinyawaka mitshi pixka hixatshinhi. Hi psokananru hamlehonutshi, hi psokananru hetwamonuxyano, hi psokananru hixa hichiniklewle. Hekhixnawa hapnokathapkaxyawaklu hektutu. Ptowru potuko hekhixnawa potukalunetkahi hixyawaka xye piranaya.
Hiyáhoni xawakni yonawahlo nyonanwakathi seyni hi nyonatlo hektutu kamhatshri tshinanni, hi koxa rumtuklerutka tshinanu nyonatlo. Halikaka nyonatlo Hoyakalu hekhipotuxyawakaphi hi psokananru hichinijyawu.
Hiyáhoni xye pirana tshinanu wpoyikowata. Hi xye tshinanu tsonni seyni wumuwata Tito tshinkaluru poyikowle tshinanu. Klu tshinanu wjempiranyehithi hanu hixa poyikowkakletatkalu Tito hiyrun-koxa hixa hapnanuhchinikankaklexyawaklu pirana.
Tito nunkakatka hixa pirana kihlewaka ntshinanwakathi. Hiyrun-koxa hi npatewata kihlewaka pirana ntshinanwakathi. Ptowru hohneruka halikaka pirana wunkakhi. Hiyáhoni hixa pirana kihleru wunkaklu Tito halikaka piranni.
Pnut-potu ruchinikhi ruchinijinri kajnakolunhi hixyawaka pirana hiyrun-koxa tsru pikluyma hima hyoptotatkalu kahwakpirruyma koxa.
Hiyáhoni npoyikowata klu tshinanu psol-potuko nmunanhiyhi.
Henekachalewatanu Ptowru Poyikowluyma PiranapniHiyáhoni wmoletanune Cristo tshinanu, wimatkakpirathi Hoyakalu hihlenu henekachalewle pirana, Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshin-yehkaka Macedônia tshijne poktshikak-hajene tshinanu.
Halixatshine wane hajene tsru salewaktshikaka riknohna. Seyni hpoyikonu tshinanna hike mwikanmakni seyni henekachalu renekachalewatna ptowru rumukata hikchiklelerna.
Ranjipotutwuna renekachalna wyoptoxyawaka rumukata hepixlewlexyawakapsona Hoyakalu kotspalatanune Judeia hajene tshinan-koxa.
Wpoyahohoxyawaka pnute rixna Macedônia tshijne hajene halixatshine. Mitshikananhapka Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu renejnawana waneya wane pnute Hoyakalu halujyawaka hkamhapiraxyawaka tshinanna hix-koxa Paulo-nwu renejnawana.
Hiyáhoni wanjitlu Tito tshinkaluru xye kamrurtshi yinuwakatshri wane hyiywakapa repixyawakaphi hix-koxa xye kihle piranaluya hpoyahokajyawakaplu.
Hekhixnawa ptowru pirana potuyako hixa kosejyana pimrine, halixlu piranaya, hinkaklewlu piranaya, himatkalnuya, pimrine haluk-hepixlexyawaka pirana, hixa hichinijyawaka piran-koxa. Henekachalu heneklewlu piran-koxa hijhalu hkosejyawaka.
Hi nujhalu nyokanrewaxyawaka seyni naluk-himatkaklethi pimrine hmernu pirana xye henekachlu hapatjexikolu tshinanu. Hiyáhoni himathexinwa ho halikaklahe pimrine hichinika ho hike.
Klu tshinanu hixa himatpiranatlu Wutsrukate Jesus Cristo hihlenu henekachalewle pirana. Phurukananni Cristo seyni hixa tshinanu hike mwikatutkani, hike hmimwalnutka pohirewkakatkahi hixa.
Xyekni nohchinikanu xye pirana tshinanu: Hitaho kihle potlu hpoyahkajyawaklu kapeta mhalni hyinuwaka kamhalleru. Hi koxa hyinuwaka kamhalechatlu seyni haluka koxlu.
Hiyáhoni xawakni wale kamrurtshi hpaklutanru haté hnikatanru. Jmererunephi xawakni mitshikananu pixka. Hiyáhoni hpoyaho hikchiklexyawaka pso heneklewatanu.
Klu tshinanu henekachalu raluk-heneklewlexini yineru, Hoyakalu yoptotlu renekachale rumukata hikchikleleru tshinanu. Hoyakalu hi haluklu yineru hma mimwanutuko renekachlewaxyawaka.
Hi pimrin-potu hihlewaxyawaka tshinanupni waneya hixapni mahaxinnatka. Seyni pixkakakane hixinripni.
Xawaknikawa hixetleru himukata hepixlexinna wanna hmahaxinriyna. Hiyáhoni hixa hmahaxinri pa hohne wanna himukata hepixlexinhi wanna rixetlerna tshinanu. Hiyáhoni pixkakakanephi.
Wane htshina Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru: “Hix-potuko nikkaluru hapatjetatshrimka, hi rixexya. Hiyrun-koxa psotsonu hapatjetatshri hike hmahaxya.”
Tito Tshinkaluru Hiyrun-koxa Rimotsane PiranapniNimalwutlu Hoyakalu klu tshinanu Tito tshinkaluru renekahchinikanuta hixa Corinto hajenhi repixyawakapa. Hixa Paulo-nwu pixka rixa hichiniklethi.
Klu tshinanu halikakni Tito yijnakotlu wtshinyalu. Seyni jmerpotuklu Tito hixa repixyawaka hiyáhoni waleko hihchinikanu tshinanu hixa nwaka hyahapkatatka.
Waleyma wyokanatlu satu wimole, ptowruneko Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshin-yehkaka kihle piranyehiyalu, Jesus Cristo pirana kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana tshinanu.
Hi wale tshinanu tsonu Tito rimotsatanu seyni Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshin-yehkaka hnurexika hixayma rixyawakapa xye kamrurtshi halukkaluru hkamhiywaka tshinanupa. Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu himalwuxikowaka tshinanu. Wekhixnawa wepixlewpiraxyawaka.
Hiyáhoni wane wixa hike yineru mjihyehixyawakanupwu henekachalu wapatjemxyawakapa.
Klu tshinanu waluka kamhaletlu kihleru hi Wutsrukate Hoyakalu hetanu tsonu seyni ptowru yine hetan-koxa.
Wannayma wyokanatanru Cristo tshinanu wmoletanru. Hixo kata wetlu jmere kamrurewle rixyawaka. Waneya xawakni pnut-potu jmeretkalu klu tshinan-hima hixa hmunanha.
Tito tshinkaluru pirana haluk-himatlexini waleni wikamrurewatanru repixyawakaphi. Hiyrun-koxa pimrine rimotsane pirana haluk-himatlexini wannani Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshin-yehkaka yokanatanunni Cristo himalwuxikolu tshinanu.
Hiyáhoni pimrine Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshin-yehkaka himatpiranyehixiniphi hekhitanna nyi Cristo tshinanu moltshine hichinijyawaka hiyrunu hi wmahijerutanu kihle piranyehirune pirana wunkaklexini.
Paulo-ne Hanijyawaklu Henekachlukaka Judeia Hajene Tshinanu PiranapniHoyakalu kotspalatanune Judeia tshijne hajene hepixikolu piran-halikaka xawakni hike pirana mahata nyonyehixyawakhi.
Klu tshinanu nimatlu jmerhi wanna hepixyawaka. Ntserutpiranathi Macedônia tshijne hajene tshinanuya. Nunkakletlu hixa halixatshine Acaia tshijne hajenhi pirana kapeta mhalni kananuko rujhaluna repixlewaxyawakna ntshina mitshi. Hiyáhoni hixo yineru jmere kamhaletka hixa hmernu pirana hjeminixkana.
Hiyáhoni nyokanatna Cristo tshinanu wmoletanune wma muhlepiranyehichaxyawakanuphi kihlewaka henekachlu hapatjexikolu pirana tshinanu. Wane mitshi ntshinapna hixa halpokoxyawaklu hepixlewaxyawakapa.
Klu tshinanu Macedônia hajene himotsaxinipno waneya rukchikanunhina malpokotkanepnihi waneya wpatewatanu. Hix-potu patewatanu klu tshinanu wmahijeru munanhaletatkahi.
Hiyáhoni wale tshinanu hijhakalurni Cristo tshinanu wmoletanune nyokanhapkaxyawaka hixa nwaka hyiywakapna. Ralpokokjixyawakapluna henekachale hinkakletleru mitshi. Hiyáhoni wane napojinpatka ralpokotkotka henekachalu waneya ptowru yineru himatanru henekachalewle hi htowuxikowakni hixako hmernu tshinanni.
Xyekni naluka tshinreta, psotsonu hitaklu hitakatshri psotsonu rama seyni tsru hitaklu hitakatshri tsru potuko rama.
Satkaka yineru hihchinikanuyma potuko renekachalewatanu. Hi mpomaluklenurutuko hi koxa htowutko henekachluya. Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu hikchikhihlenutlu popoyikoner-potuko heneklewaxiklu.
Hiyrun-koxa hmahakanaxinrikaka pnut-potu rumukata heneklethi Hoyakalu hike hma mujhiywakanpatka haté hixetatshri himukata hwalexya klu kamrurtshi kihleruktako tshinanu.
Hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalukni hitataji heneklewatatshri rutajikowakapa. Hiyrun-koxa pão nikkalurupa heneklewatatshrini. Waneko pixka rixanhi hix-koxa ptowru hitataji halukkaluru pixkalutu renekanhi. Htseruwnakakanru tsrupotpákolu honantshi, hixa henekachale tseruwnaleko pixka.
Ptowru potuko hepixiko, jeneklewaklerune hixyawakapa. Hiyáhoni hixolune himalwutanru Hoyakalu henekachle waniklerupa tshinanu.
Klu tshinanu xye hkamhaleru hi Hoyakalu kotspalatanune hike mwikane repixyawaka tshinanu tsonni seyni wan-rixkakhi Hoyakalu hpoyahnuxyawakapluna wanna koxa.
Wanna himalwutanru Hoyakalu hixa hepixle tshinanu hiyrun-koxa henekachle tshinanu kajnako hixle tshinan-koxa hiyrunu Cristo pirana kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana homkahixyawaka tshinan-koxa. Hiyrun-koxa rimalwuhetkotanruna Hoyakalu hixa henekachlepa tsrur-potuko tshinanu wannako htshinan-koxna hiyrun-koxa pimrine ptowruneka tshinanupa.
Hiyrun-koxa ranjihohneyehihetkotanhina tsru hichinijikoluyma Hoyakalu henekahchinikanuxya tshinanhi.
Hoyakalu wpoyahnutanu renekachale tsrur-potuko hike pixka mixkatu tshinanu.
Paulo Towutlewle PiranapniHitakni, Paulo-no, wla mitshi ntshinnawa, hixastsi nwiniklunu kpoyikonerno seyni howuka nwiniklunu ktokanno. Hitakni hanjithi Cristo mayohnuyma hiyrun-koxa hchinikannuyma,
wane napojinipa hi ktokanu hixkakanno. Klu tshinanu nimatlu numukata tokanuwnalyehitna pimrine wla tshinatshine xye tshijne kamrure homkahitatshinni wtshinjene.
Halikakni yinwu seyni hi wyapretaklu hixako wihchinikanu halujyawaka.
Klu tshinanu wyahotkakapreni wimuylalewapre hi yine kamhalerni seyni waleni hiyahotkakapi hixkolu Hoyakalu kamhalerni wkamnitjeru munanhapre yotkakatshri. Chinikantshikaka muhletu wnikata,
hiyrun-koxa ptowru yine halixkowle pirana Hoyakalu himatyehixikowaka himaletatshri wnikata. Ptowru yine hchinikanu wyokanata, Cristo hchinikanu walixkajyawakna yine.
Waneya hixa hali hekhirexnatkawa halikaka hixatshine hixikatshinetkawahi, halpokotatshinepwu ptowru hixatshri hektuntshi wapnokaxyawakapa.
Kkahwaklu retachaklerunhi. Satu yineru Cristo himwatshri rikahwajiniklunwa hyahoxinwa hihchinikanuya klu tshinanu hix-koxa Cristo-nunwu wale pixkalunek-koxwu hixa.
Hi npatewata seyni ntserutahchinikanuxnawa Tsru Hixikatshriwa Cristo towutle henejya tshinanwu. Xye towutlu wenekka hixa wepixyawakapa htseruwnahalixlexyawakapa Cristo piranaya hi wenekka wnikathalixlexyawakaphi.
Hi nimyekakpiratkalhi hkahwajinno, yonawahlokaka nyokananwakaxyawaka tshinanhi.
Satkaka hetko xawaka wla tshinjeta: “Paulo yonawahle halikaka hixko towutlewle, htowutlewata seyni hewi potuko rawini hi kmixkonru hiyrun-koxa htokanu hike kochpakatshrini.”
Wan-tshintokanutatshri himatanu wyonawahle howuka wwakanaxiniko pixka wixa kamruretanu wane wapojinipa.
Hi wujhalu pixkakakanwu wixyawaka ho pimrine hijhakalune hikahwajikatshinwa wikahwajikowaka. Mahchinikanunni wan-hixatshine. Klu tshinanu wanna wannakaklukokni hyahotapre pixkalune rimathetkajyawakapna ho pixkakakanrahe ho hike.
Hixa hi koxa myahoxikowakanu tokanuwnikatshinwu. Seyni Hoyakalu henejyawu kamrurtshi pso potuko waneko pso potuk-koxlu wtokanuwninri. Haté xye kamrurtshi wkamrurewyehixyahi wale psojitek-koxatkani wale.
Klu tshinanu hi Hoyakalu towuxyawakwu pnute wkamha. Waneya mitshi hix-yeh-potu wapkapatka Cristo pirana, kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana wunkakapyawakaphi.
Hiyáhoni hi wtokanuwnanu yahoxikowakatka hichinixyawaka pnuteya satuko yineru kamrurewaxyawakaya. Hiyáhoni xawakni wkahwaklu hixa halixle htseruwnanu. Hiyrun-koxa wujhalu pnut-potu wkamhiywaklu kamrurtshi Hoyakalu henejyawu hix-yehiya.
Waneya wujhakoxlu wunkaklexyawaklu Cristo pirana, kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana, hixa sreta pnute hwatshin-yehiya. Hiyáhoni hi wtokanuwnanu kamrurtshi pimrine hali kamhallerutka wma kamhanutuko tshinanu.
Wane htshina Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru: “Katukta haluka tokanuwnaletanu, Tsru Hixikatshriwayma htokanuwnanu.”
Klu tshinanu kihle kamrureru tshinikatshriwa hi ralukko seyni halikaka Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hikchikhihlenreru tsonu hiknohkakko.
Paulo Hiyrun-koxa Mnuretkone Minje PiranapniNalukmaklu hakotachaxyawakno pchini tsonu mchinikanutu pixka nixyawaka. Halikaka xako hakotachatanu hitayma.
Klu tshinanu nhokothi. Hoyakalu henekno nhokoxyawakaphi. Klu tshinanu hixa hatatjewa makloji hike myanwakatanutowa hike mixkotowa pixka hixatshinhi. Nunkaklexyahi satupka hhanuruxyawakapa walekni Cristo.
Seyni npiklu himnu yokwijexyawakanro Eva-ni kihlewaka htshinreyma pixka hixikowaka, waneko pixka hixa himtuklehchinikanutkonmaka hixapni. Wan-hixkanmaka hiknoklewatanuna hihchinikanu halikakalutu, potukalu Cristo hichpajikatshri chinikantshi.
Klu tshinanu hixa kihle yoptole hixinri poyikowluyma hanu hixatshriktako satu yineruko Jesus pirana hinkakletatshri, hi Jesus piran-potuko wunkakletleru pirana munkakletkatuko. Hiyrun-koxa hyoptoxiniplu satuko hiwejikaluru, hiyrun-koxa satuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana pnuko hixatshri hi Hoyakalu Hiwejikalurni, hiyrun-koxa hi Cristo pirana, kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana wunkajyatkahi walekni halixpiranatanrutka.
Klu tshinanu hi nkahwajnawa wanna nuretkalune yokanatkalune tshinikatshinwa kayahoko hitakkalurno nixyawaka.
Kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana, Hoyakalu pirana nunkajinixkahi, hi nujhawenrutlu. Nmasaxnawa hixa tsrun-potu hixyawakapa. Hixlahe kahwaklu numtukhi wane nixyawaka tshinanu?
Hix-yehi nkamrurewakanaxika pchinika pimrine Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshin-yehkaka hepixjekanatno tiyiroya. Hatatjewa pimrine nkontiyirotekanata hixa nepixyawakapa.
Hiyrun-koxa hix-yehi nwaka pchinika, tiyiro nmahaxinri tshinanu hi nkojwakna wane hajene. Halikaka Cristo tshinanu wmoletanune Macedônia tshijne hichpajikatshine henekno ptowru nmahakanaxinri. Waneklu ptowru nmahakanaxinri tshinanu hi nkojwakatkahi hiyrun-koxa xye pnut-hohnepatka hi nkojwakanhi nmahaxinri tshinanu.
Cristo pirana halikakalutu nimwaleru tshinanu wane ntshina hinkaklethi. Hike yineru konanno xye npoyikowle Cristo pirana nunkaklexyawaka mujhawenutkatno ptowru Acaia tshijneya.
Kluneru tshinanhe wane ntshina? Hixlahe kahwakno nma muchinijyawakanhi? Hoyakalu himatlu nuchinikhi.
Nasruha hixlexyawaka nixanu nimalexyawakapna nuretkalune yokanatkalune tshinikatshinwa hma tserutpiranyehixnawakanupwana wane hma tshinyawakanupna Paulo-ne pixka wixa kamrureta.
Wanna jejine nuretkalune yokanatkalune minjenni hixachatatshinni. Hi halikakalunni. Hkamrurna pirana weyatatshinni hiyrun-koxa Cristo nuretanune yokanatkalune hixachatatshine rixnawana.
Hiyrun-koxa hi wimyekanu, Satanás honra hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru hatawnatshri kohetkowakhatshri.
Hiyáhoni hi koxa kyapreru Satanás towrene, kihleru kamhatshine rixnawakwana. Hmahlepa hyoptotanruna rujhalerna.
Paulo Salewnale PiranapniWane ntshinanutnaka: Hike kahwakanno mahchinikanutu nixyawaka. Seyni wan-hikahwajinipno mahchinikanutu pixka hixa yoptoletanno waneya numukata tokanuwnaleta.
Halikaka wla ntshinyawaka hi Wutsrukate Jesus Cristo towuxyano. Seyni tokanuwnalu nyanumaxinri pirana mahchinikanutu pixka ntshinya.
Hi heppiklu tokantshi xye tshijne hixjexyawaka pirana. Hiyáhoni hit-koxa tokanuwna.
Hixa jimatkalerunekhi hakotachatna mahchinikanune.
Hix-hetko hikchikhihlenutlu satu yineru towutachaxyawakhi ho hkonhejnunkatechaxyawakhi ho hyokwijexyawakhi ho hi hkahwakpiratanhi ho rumpakhojixyawakaphi.
Npatewa hiphujetlepiranatlu klu tshinanu hi tsru hchinikanwu wanna pixka wixyawaka. Seyni satu yineru klu pirana tshinanuktako htokanuwnini, hit-koxa tokanuwnanu. Mahchinikanutu pixka ntshina yanumsaletanu.
Hebreu-nerunrahhe? Hit-koxa hebreu-nerno. Israel-nerunrahhe? Hit-koxa israel-nerno. Abraão klopichanrahhe? Hit-koxa Abraão klopichno.
Cristo-yma kamrurewatatshinrahhe? Seyni hit-potu kamrurewatatshrino Cristo-yma. Hatatjewa mahchinikanutno wane ntshinyawaka. Klu tshinanu wanna yohnik-kamrurewle nixa. Hiyrun-koxa wanna yohnik-kata kapna nyochmakka. Hixo kat-koxa wanna pnute nuylakka hiyrun-koxa hixo kata psokaklu nupniywaka.
Cinco kata judeu-ne kotshipjetno trinta e nove kotshipjeru rixnona.
Map-kata romano-ne hiylakno hahajeya hiyrun-koxa pa kata nsotlujetka. Map-kata nupkata. Pa yetshno, pa hohne honha nwa mar powhaya.
Hixo kata yanru nkamha. Honha nyapini honha hamlenu neta. Hiyrun-koxa katshowhurune hamlenu neta, nonerune judeu-ne yowiknuya hiyrun-koxa judeu mixkane yowiknuya. Tsru poktshi hixowaka yowiknu, kahnete poktshikaka yowiknu, mar powha yowiknu, himatletkalune hixachatatshine yowiknuy-koxa.
Tsru kamrurtshi potu neta hiyrun-koxa hamanru tsru potuko neta. Hixo kata hi numka, nnatshita, ntshiklehowata, nmahamkata.
Hiyrun-koxa xyekaka pnute ptowru hohneruka nuchinikanretler-potni ptowruneka Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshin-yehkaka ninotlene tshinanu.
Kathe yijnak-hihrokleta? Hit-koxa yijnak-hihrokleta. Satu yineru himtuwnini hi he nwamonuwnahchinikanuta?
Numukata tokanuwnalexini, nuhrokle pirana hiphujetatshri tshinanu halikaka ntokanuwnanu.
Wutsrukate Jesus Cristo Hoyakalute ptowru hohneruka himalwutkaluru hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa himatlu hi nweyawata.
Damasco poktshi nwakanaxini, wale tshijne yokanatatshri, phuru Aretas tshinkaluru hitakleru, tsru poktshi hiphaptotkaka rinotjixna soldado-ne hkachixyawakamkapnona.
Seyni nimatletlene pantshi hiphaptoteswa tshiji rutajyanona chiwatuya. Cerca tenolu sotlu kamhikolu malekate nutakka. Hiyáhoni wane nixa hasuklexyatkana.
Hiphujetkalurkaka Hoyakalu Hekhixyalu Paulo PiranapniWanepnawaka ntokanuwnanu yahmaklu hike hkochpakanu. Hiyáhoni xawakni nunkakletanru Tsru Hixikatshriwa Cristo hekhixyano nupnaleya hiyrun-koxa pimri hiphujetkaluru rekhixyano.
Nimatlu satu yineru Cristo halixatshri. Tenhohne rankapka quatorze rixinri mhalni. Hi nimatlu ho halikaklahe wane rapkapa himaneyma ho riwejinri tsonrahe wane rapkapya. Hoyakalu tsonu himata.
Hkochtshekka. Kihlewaka potuko rankapka. Waneya hyijnakotlu tokantshi mpoyaho hinkakletletkotu.
Xye pirana nitokanuwnanu. Wan-hixatshri jeji pirana tsonu nitokanuwnanu seyni hitako nopirana hi nitokanuwnanu seyni nuhrokle pirana halikaka nitokanuwnanu.
Ntokanuwninmaka hi mahchinikanutu pixka ntshinanu klu tshinanu halikaka pirana tsonmaka ntshinanu. Seyni hi ntokanuwnanu klu tshinanu hi naluklu yine kahwakpiraxyawakno nkamrure pnute ho ntokanu pnute.
Hoyakalu hekhixyapirankakno kihle pirankakal-potuko tshinanu nma malixkoxnawakanupwa nenekka satu nkojwajikolu nomaneya. Hatatjewa Satanás towreru hapokyehitno ruylajyawakapno nma malixkoxnawakanupwa.
Waneya map-katamka nanjitlu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Cristo xye kojwaklu yehi nuchpajyawakapa.
Waneya wane htshinatkano. Nuhlenu henekachle poyahoxyatkayi klu tshinanu numukatle pot-hixko puhrojini. Hiyáhoni nkopalpiranatlu nuhrokle piranapnawaka klu tshinanu nuhrojiniklunu Cristo pixkonu hit-yehi rawanutka.
Hiyáhoni kihle hchinikanno hihroklukaka tshinanu, hektuntshi, mahaxikalurkaka, kojwawaktshikaka, xyekaka salewaktshi Cristo tshinanni. Klu tshinanu nuhrojini halikaka kpixkonno.
Nuretkaluru Yokanaxikolu Himathexikowaka PiranapniMahchinikanutu pixka nixa seyni hixakni wan-hixkakno. Hixakmakni haluklu kihlewaka htshinanwakaxyawakno. Klu tshinanu yáholu mujhakotno hita seyni hi psojikna napkataxyana mitshikananu nuretkalune yokanaxikolune.
Halikaka ptowru hixatshri hetkaluru nkamha rimathexikowaka nuretkalurno. Hixa tskala nkamhiylu ptowruka nma chiretannuyma, hetkalurkaka, himyekaklewatatshrikaka, hiyakolukaka.
Klu tshinanu hanhe xawaka hixa hapkatleta pimrine Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshin-yehkaka hetanuya? Xye tsonu pnuko hixika hi nepixikowaka nanjijekanathi. Xye pirana tshinanu nanjithi hi hichinikanru xye numtuknu.
Hetanu. Map-kata rixinri nupruka hixa nwaka nyiywakamkapa. Hike nalujyahi. Htiyirote hi nalujyahi nuchinikhi hixa halikaka. Klu tshinan-honra tsrune hijhanro tiyiro rapatjexyawakna hiwhenenna tshinanu, hi whentshine hijhanro tiyiro rurunna tshinanu.
Hiyáhoni numuwatanu psoluka nimwaleru nsalexyawaka hixa tshinanu. Haté nujhalu nsalexnawakwa psol-potuko hixa tshinanu. Hiyah-koxla nuchinikpotukanaxyawaka tshinanni hixa hi hichinikanretpotutatkano hita?
Haté hehe, hixa himatatkalu hike nepixikolu nujhiyhi. Seyni satkaka hetko xawaka wan-tshinno nimatkalnukni nyokwijexyahi.
Satkaklahe xawaka hixa nwaka nyokanreru tshowhuxyahi pa hixanu hita tshinanu?
Nanjitlu mitshi Tito tshinkaluru hixa nwaka rapkapyawaka. Hiyrun-koxa nyokanatlu satu Tito-yma Cristo tshinanu wmoletanru. Tito-lahe xawaka pa hixanu htshowhuxyahi? Hi he pixkakakanwu waleyma hiyrun-koxa pa hchinikanurunwu hixa tshinanu?
Hixlahe kahwakwu wpowratpiraxnawakwa hix-yehiya? Seyni hike. Cristo tshina hinkaklekjixyawakwu potuko wtshina hinkaklethi Hoyakalu hetanuya. Nuchinikanune, ptowru potuko wkamhaleru wkamhalu hixa wepixyawakamkapa tshinanu.
Npiklu wane napojini pnuko hixatshinetkahi hixyawaka, nma muchinikanrexyawakanu pixka nixa yoptolexyawakatkahi. Hiyrun-koxa hix-koxa pnuko hixahotanno hmalujyawakanu pixka hixahotanno. Npik-koxlu wane napojini hejnu hima njemyawaka, hahxalu, jhekantshi, tserpiranawlu, hektuntshi, hapatlewlu, halixkoxikatshriwa, sejirewnalu.
Npiklu wane napojinpatnaka Noyakalute mturu hixkajyawakno hix-yehiya. Hiyrun-koxa pa katako nujhalu ntshiyahaxyawakapa hixolune hektuwaka kamhatshine mehchinikanutkanewa tshinanu, hektutu hkamhalerna tshinanu, rapoklewlena, hiyrun-koxa pimrikaka hma poyaho hicholetanutna tshinanu.
Majnakowatatshine Hiykoxikowakatka PiranapniXawakni pa katatkani map-kata rixinri hixa nwaka nyanutka. Wane htshina Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru: “Hepi ho mapa yine hektutu hiphujetatshine tokanu hpoyehixika ptowru piranako.”
Wla ntshinanwakathi hixa, mitshikananu majnakowatatshinhi hiyrunu pimrine hektuwaka kamhatshin-koxa. Hepi kata rixinri hixa nwaka napkapinixka wane ntshinatkahi hiyáhoni xawakni howukmakno seyni wane ntshina hiyrunukotnaka. Xeyrunu hike yineru netwamonutanutka.
Klu tshinanu hixa haluk-himatlepotuxinri Cristo halikakakni hita nama hyanumaxyawaka. Cristo-ni muhrokkatu seyni halikaka tsru pixkonru hixa tshinanu.
Klu tshinanu yáholu cruz ruylaxika Cristo ruhrokahotko tshinanu seyni xawakni riweka Hoyakalu pixkonu tshinanu. Waneko pixka wix-kox-hixa. Hixa wale hihrokahoxikoluymalunwu seyni pa hchinikanurunwu waleyma wiweka Hoyakalu pixkonu tshinanu, wepixyawakaphi tshinanu.
Hetjexinwa, hyahoxinwa ho halikaklahe poyehi halixlehi. Hi he himatlu Jesus Cristo hwamanethi halikaka minjenhi hma mixyawakanupa?
Nkahwaklu himatyehitwu hixa hi halikaka minjenwu.
Hoyakalu wanjiyehithi hike hektutu hma kamhiywakanupa seyni hi koxa wanjiyehithi kihlewaka wtshinanwakaxikowakapa seyni potukawaka hkamhiywaka tshinanupni halikaka. Hike rixa yáholu halikaka minje pixkalune wikahwakko.
Klu tshinanu hike wumukata kamhaleta halikakalutu tokantshi wkamnixyawaka seyni halikaka halikakalutu tokantshi wimatshwaha.
Hiyáhoni wale tshinanu wpoyikowata wuhrojinmaka seyni hixa mixkowata. Hiyrun-koxa wanjitlu Hoyakalu potukalune hixyawakapa.
Hiyahokni xyekaka pirana nyonata, wane nma yaknukawa, wane nyinipa hi nujhalu hipokananu ntowuxyawakaphi nutajikolu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Cristo henejyanoyma. Xye towutlu nenekka hixa nepixyawakapa ntseruwnakajyawakaphi Cristo piranaya seyni hi hixa wnikawnakajyawaka tshinanu nenekka.
Hiyáhoni Cristo tshinanu nmoletanune, nunhahi. Hihlexinwa. Hyijnakotanru nuykole. Pa hchinikanurunephi. Kihle hwachalephi. Hoyakalu hixa ruchinijyawaka hiyrun-koxa ruhlehchinikanrewle hix-yehi hwanu.
Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus Cristo hihlenu henekachale hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu hichinijyawakhi hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru himatkaklewle hixa ptowrunekhi yehi rawanu.
