Katshowhurukananu hi wane pnuteko htshowhuwatanutka seyni hkamrurewatanu. Waleko himyoya kihler-kamrurtshi hkamhanu hkayaxyawakapa. Wan-hixatshri himukata hapikletanna mahaxikatshine.
Hi satukna tokantshi hektutu himtuklewatatshri hyanumaxini seyni kihleru tokantshi halukkaluru, tseruwaka hchinikanrewatatshripa tokantshi tsonu hyanumaxini. Yijnakotatshine hepixatshri tokantshi yanumaxiko.
Hi hwamontakanru Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru. Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru himaxikolexikalunhi. Hoyakalununhi hi ruknokanhi haté rapojinipa hiweklu hohne potuko Hoyakaluyma.
Hiknokanru ptowru hchikohajiwaxinri, ptowru himtuwnalu jhekantshi, ptowru sapletshkaka, ptowru heyiklewlu, ptowru hixatshri hahnantshi hiknokanu.
Seyni hichinikanuwyehkakanu. Hetwamonkakanu. Hixkakluko hamtakahchinikankakyehitanu hektutuya Hoyakalu hiknokhektunuxyawakhi Cristo tshinanu pixka.
