Xye chinikantshi ptowru wiwejinri htowuta. Hichinikanuwyehkakanu. Hixa hichinikanuwkakleyehixyawaka pixka rixa Cristo, renejyanawa rupniywaka hixa tshinanu renekachaxnatkawa henekachaluru rixnatkawa hatewa phamluhalo phamluro pixka potuko hixatshritkani Hoyakalu hetanuya hiyrun-koxa henekachaluru hiylatkaluru Hoyakalu hikchikhihlenutanru potuko.
Hoyakalunerunhi hixyawaka tshinanu, hi hapoklewatanu hiyrun-koxa ptowru kaptsholu, hiyrun-koxa ptowruka het-sotanuhowlu hikeklu hohne hpohiwkakanhi.
Hi hektutu tokantshi kapatmenuru hyanumaxinixka, hi tokantshichako, hi koxa hixpirannutshi tokantshiko. Klu tshinanu wan-hixatshri hi kihleru seyni halikaka himalwutanru Hoyakalu.
Klu tshinanu himatanru xye: hi satukna yineru kapoklewakleru, hi mpowratuko, hi ksotanuholuko — waleni mayawletshichako munanhatshri — hi satukna wanna yoptotanru rawyawakna Cristo pohirewaxyawaka, Hoyakalunu.
Xako hike yineru yokwijetanhi tokantshi mal-himaluya. Klu tshinanu xyekaka ntshinakanatanru kamhatshine Hoyakalu hapnokatanna wanna hektuwaka kamhatshine.
Hiyáhoni hi yokwijrewpiratatshineyma hyananutka.
Klu tshinanu hix-koxa mapchahawaka yapjekanata mitshikananu seyni xawakni Hoyakalunerune hixyawaka tshinanu katawaka hyaninixka. Hiyáhoni hiwekanu katawaka hiwejikatshine pixka.
Klu tshinanu katal-hixlu ptowru hixatshri hihlentshi poyahokakleni, halikak-potu.
Hijhanru klunerukta rukchikhihlenreru Wutsrukate Hoyakalu.
Hi himotsatanna malechawaka kamrurewaxikatshine. Waleni mapchahawaka hajeru kamrurtshi. Seyni halikaka xye kamrurtshikaka phujewaka hitakanru.
Halikaka wunkaklexinri wanna kamrure hektutu hyohimpirrerna pirana hpatetjetanna.
Ptowru potuko katawaka rekhixiko rimathexikowaka hanu potu rixa.
Klu tshinanu ptowru potuko hiphujetkalurni katawakaya. Hiyáhoni mitshikawlur-pirana wan-tshina: “Pixa himkatshriyi, puyokanu xako! Hipnatshri yehi puchpajinixka, Cristo Katalu nikotyehitanyi.”
Hiyáhoni xakoka. Hislahpotuxinwa hanu hixa hiwekletanu. Hi mimatjemkane pixka hixa hiwekletanu seyni jimatkalurune pixka hixa hiwekletanu.
Hiwekka pchinika hi hetachaxinwa, klu tshinanu xye hohnekaka katsepna yine hektutu kamhatshine.
Hiyáhoni hi mahchinikanunephi seyni Wutsrukate Cristo halujyawaka himatjematshinephi.
Hi katshwuhalo himetatshinephi. Klu tshinanu himru towutle himtuklewata. Seyni halikaka hitshitanru Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru towuxyawakhi.
Hiynumsakakanu Hoyakalu tokanu chikaleya, himalwuru chikaleya, pimrikaka chikaltshi Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluruya. Himalwutanru Wutsrukate Cristo, himalwutanru hihchinikanuya.
Ptowru hohneruka himalwutanru Hoyakalu, Hirtshi Hoyakalu, ptowru potuko tshinanu, Wutsrukate Jesus Cristo hiwakaya.
Hanu Rumukata Hixa Hiwekleta Hnurtshi, Hhanunroyma Cristo Halixatshine Rixyawaka Tshinanna PiranapniSuxone hyijnakotanna hixako hhanuru. Tsru Hixikatshriwa Cristo hixa yijnakolexyawakako pixka.
Klu tshinanu suxo thanuru tojiwukni wale. Waneko pixka rixa Cristo. Cristo towutna halixatshine hapatjetatshine. Cristo-katkani halixatshine hapatjetatshine hiwekkakatshri. Wannakatkani Cristo mane.
Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine yijnakotlu Cristo hiyáhoni waneko pixka raluk-hixletna hnunrotshine. Hhanurna hyijnakotanna ptowron-potuko suxone.
Hixa jejinhi hamotanna hhanunrone, Cristo pixka. Cristo hichinikna hapatjetatshine Cristo halixatshine. Hiyáhoni renejnawa rupniywaka wanna kachrijru.
Wan-rixa Cristo, hapatjetatshine Cristo halixatshine hatatjewa Cristo hnunropni, kanipretkalurotkani Hoyakaluya. Cristo herokalo honhaya, htokanuya hpowratlo.
Xye hkamha Cristo, rumukata heneklexnawakwa hix-yehiya, hixa hatatjewa hhanunrone, kihleron-potpakwu, maptsholemtatopni potukalo hike mukolukanutopni, hixa hapatjetatshine Cristo halixatshinwu.
Waneko pixka raluk-hixletna hnurtshine. Rumukata hichinikletna hhanunrone wannako himaneko pixka. Jeji hanuruktako hijhalu ruchinijyawaklo hhanunro walenanuko ruchinijnawakwa pixka.
Klu tshinanu hike yineru wale nanuko hayehixmanexnawa. Seyni halikaka ruslahmanexnawa. Cristo waneko pixka rixna ralixjene hapatjetatshine.
Klu tshinanu hixa satkakwu Cristo mane psojitwu.
Wane htshina yonatkaluru potukalu mitshikawlur-pirana: “Wale tshinanu jeji hichotlu ruru, runro, hiyáhoni satu manepkalu hhanunroyma.”
Halikakalutu hijhakaluru pirana runkakleta xye hima. Waleni Cristo, hiyrun-koxa Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine mkoje pejnu piranni.
Hiyrunu hixa tshinan-koxni wale pirana. Satkakhi hixa jejinhi hijhalu hhanunro ruchinijyawaka wale nanuko ruchinijnawakwa pixka. Hiyrunu suxo hijhalu tkahwakpiraxyawaklu thanuru.
Paulo Hiykotna Tsrune Hiyrunu Mturune Ruykoxyawaka PiranapniWhentshinhi Wutsrukate Cristo homkahitatshine hixyawaka tshinanu hixa hijhalu hirtshine hyijnakoxyawaka klu tshinanu xyeni kihleru wan-hixyawaka.
Pyijnakotanru puru, punro. Xye yonatkaluru yokanatkaluru mitshikananu hinkakletkaluru. Runkakletluna kihleru hakanhayehixyawakapna kajnako rixyawakapna.
Kihle hixinripa. Hohiwekle hixinripa.
Hiyrun-koxa hixa hirtshinhi hi himtuwnakakanna hwuhenene seyni hislahanna, htseruwnakakanna Wutsrukate Cristo haluklewleya hiyrun-koxa Cristo hiykolewleya.
Hiykolu Ktowutlewakleru Tshinanu Hiyrun-koxa Kkamrurewaklerune Tshinanu PiranapniTowrertshine xako yijnakotanna htowutjene xye tshijne hajene. Hkahwakpiratanna htowutjene hiyáhoni hyijnakotanna ptowru potuko hjemleru. Wane potuko hixatshinephi kihle hchinikanuphi hatatjewa Cristo towutanunhi.
Hi htowutjene hetanu tsonu kajnakophi hyokwijechaxyawaka tshinanupna htowutjene seyni Cristo towrene hikahwajinwa hiyáhoni psoluka hihchinikanu mixkonuyma hkamhanru Hoyakalu halujyawaka.
Kihle hchinikanurunhi kamrurewatanu hatatjewa hi yine towutlenhi seyni Wutsrukate Cristo towutlenhi.
Hichinikanru xye, satkaka yineru, yáholu towrertshi ho mtowutkotu seyni hyoptotanru hkamrure wenru Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu henekanhi hkamhiniplu ho kihleru ho hektutu.
Hixa ktowutaklerunhi waneko pixka hixanna hkamrurewkakjetanune. Hi hyanhakkakanna htowrene. Seyni hichinikanru xako hixa tsru hixikatshinwahi hiyrun-koxa hixa towrertshine hitsrukate satupkalu Hoyakalu tenhohne hajeru. Payakalunephi Hoyakaluyma.
Kamtshi Kamnirewle Wuknojyawaka PiranapniHiyáhoni xawakni hixkolunephi klu tshinanu Wutsrukate Cristo-ymalunwu hiyrunu hpixkonu wmixkotjeru tshinanu.
Ptowruk-xako hyochmakanu hinokakoklunu himaletyehitjerupa Hoyakalu henekanhi hixa himukata poyehi yopkakle hixyawakapa, tsru kamtshi kakonre hixa hma kachixyawakanupa tshinanu.
Klu tshinanu wkamnitjene hi yinni kahiturune, hi kahrahalune seyni wkamnitjene wannakni kamtshine hmuhlenuymana xye psol-hohneko yapatshine hiyrunu tsrukakalune, tsru hitakkalune, malehohnewaka hwatshine tsru pixkontshiyma yine yokwijpiratatshine, kamtshi yokwijpiratwu towutlewpiratatshineya.
Hiyáhoni ptowruko hyochmakanu hinokakoklunu himaletyehitjerupa Hoyakalu henekanhi hixa himukata hiknohletanru hektutu pa hohne hinyehitjerupa tshinanu. Hkamnitkoklunupa hixa himukata poyehi yopkakle hixleta haté rasujinipa hkamnitjeru hpaklu yopkakletanutshi.
Hiyáhoni xawakni chikpok-yopkaklerunephi. Halikakalutu pirana halixpotutanu wan-hixini hostuptshijitkalunhi pixka hixatshinetkahi. Potukalunephi hatatjewa statshi hislahatshri hitakastatka.
Kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana hapnanuhchinikankaklewatatshri tokantshi hpoyehixinwa hiyáhoni hatatjewa hislahjixitjeru hyochmakka.
Hiyrun-koxa ptowru hohneruka hiyrunu ptowru papkoluko halixpotutanu wan-hixatshri hatatjewa katshralu himaletapichpata ranikamta pa myoya. Hiyáhoni hixa himukata hiwakletlu ptowru hatatkaluru katshralkaka Satanás yokananwakaxyahi.
Hoyakalu henekanhi hiwekkaklewatatshri hyoptotanrupa wan-hixatshinhi hislahjiwutjeru hitakatshinhi. Hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu tokanu hanikanu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru henejyahi waleni hatatjewa yohlolewapi hkachimta.
Hit-koxa hanjihohneyehitanu, nunkaklewaxini, Hoyakalu henektokanuxyawakapno hiyrun-koxa nunkaklewaxini nma pijyawakanupa, nunkakle pirana rimatjemikowakap-koxa kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana npohitakanatanru pirana.
Kihler-potuko tokantshi hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana pohitatshrino yahmaklu kapna nutakka. Hiyáhoni hanjihohneyehitanno phujetanuwaka potuko ntshina hinkakletlexyawakaplu hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana rixpiranaxyawak-potuko.
