<font color=teal>Filipenses</font>Paulo Yonre Halixatshine Filipos Hajene TshinanuHita Paulo-no hiyrun-koxa Timóteo Jesus Cristo towrenwu yokanatlo twu yonawahlo ptowruneka Hoyakalu hayinetene Filipos poktshi hajene tshinanupa. Jesus Cristo-ymalune tshinanupni. Hiyrun-koxa wyokanatlo twu yonawahlo halixatshine hapatjetatshine kosekatshine hiyrun-koxa halixatshine hepixatshine tshinan-koxa.
