Hiyrun-koxa ptowru katako nanjihohneyehixinhi numuwa hanjihohnerejeta,
hixa hepixle tshinanu kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri piranaya, mitshikanan-hohne Filipos poktshi nwakanaxini haté xawakni.
Xye nimata. Hoyakalu yinuwaka kamhaletlu satu kihler-kamrurtshi hixa hiwekleyma, hnikata kamhaletanru haté hnikaxinpotúkolu Cristo Jesus hapojinri hohne potuko.
Hixa ptowrunekhi nuchinikanretahohnejeta. Kihleru wane nixa hichinikanretlexyawakhi klu tshinanu hixa nitsaklawnakjenhi xye kamrurtshi honukla Hoyakalu henekatkano. Hixa haté xawakni wan-hixjetno yahmaklu preso nutakka hiyrun-koxa wan-hixjekanatno mkachitkotu nixjekanaxini. Waneklu papko hike himaletakanatno kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana nimatshwahyawakapa hiyrun-koxa npoyehiwkajyawakpotuplu.
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalni nuphujtatjeru, hi nweyawata wane ntshininhi hixa nuchinijyawaka tsru potuko Cristo Jesus hchinikanu hichpajikatshrini.
Nanjitlu Hoyakalu hixa himukata pnute hya hichinikanretlexyawakaplu himatkalewlu halikakalutuya hiyrun-koxa psoluka himathetlewluya,
hpoyaho himatlexyawaklu hnurexyawaklu kihler-potuko. Waneyakni ptowru Hoyakalu malukanutuko hiyrunu patewahonutshi hi hix-yehi rukchijinru Cristo hapojinri hohnepa.
Waneya hixa hiwejinri katsepopatkalu ptowru chinikantshi kihleru, Jesus Cristo tsonu hakanikleru, ralixkoxikolupa hiyrunu rimalwuxikolupa Hoyakalu.
Paulo Preso Hitajikolu Cristo Tshinanu PiranapniCristo tshinanu nmoletanune, naluklu hixa himaxyawakaplu niknohjerkaka napyehitjerkaka repixyawakaplu kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana hinkajikolupa.
Klu tshinanu xye tshinanu soldado-ne phurupji hinotatshine ptowruneka hiyrunu pimrine hewi hajene ptowruneka himatlu Cristo towreru nixyawaka tshinanu kapna nyochmakka.
Kapna nyochmajikowaka tshinanu hixolune Wutsrukate Cristo tshinanu wmoletanune mixkowahchinikanutatka runkaklexyawakluna halikakalutu tokantshi hike hpikna.
Halikakni satkaka hinkakletlu Cristo pirana hahxale tshinanu tsonu hiyrun-koxa hyanhakleyma tshinanu. Seyni pimrine kihle hchinikanuruneko hinkakletlu Cristo pirana.
Nyi wan-rixna klu tshinanu ruchiniknona. Klu tshinanu rimatluna xye kamrurtshi renekno Hoyakalu kihler-potuko tokantshi hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana nimatshwahyawakapa.
Pimrine hahxatatshine hi runkakletluna kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana hkamhiywakapna. Seyni wannako raluklerna rujhana. Wanna kahwaklu pnute rixa salewnakakletnona hewi kapna nwakako pchini.
Hiyáhoni klunerni? Hikeni. Xye tsonupni. Numuwata hiyrunu numuwatanu han-hixatshriktako hinkaklewatatshri ho hixachatatshrini ho halikakalutni, Cristo hinkakletpiranaxikolni.
Klu tshinanu nimatlu hixa hanjihohnere tshinanu hiyrun-koxa Hiwejikaluru Jesus Cristo hepixle tshinanu nuchotko.
Nalukpotutlu hiyrun-koxa nkahwakpotutlu hikekni nipatewatanu seyni ptowru hohneruka xawakni potuk-koxa halikakalutu pirana hi nmayxakanu. Cristo pohixikolupa hita nomane tshinanuya ho niwejinri ho nupninriyapa.
Klu tshinanu hitaya kluneruktákoni kihleru niwejyawaka? Klu tshinanu niwejini Cristo tshinanu niweka. Seyni nupnini waleni kihler-potuwa hitaya.
Xye nomane riwejinipatshi pnut-potu hkamhanru kamrurtshi. Hi nimata nurpotutlu halikakalutu.
Klu tshinanu hepi hchinikanno. Nalukpotutmaklu nupnale Cristo nwaka nwinripatka klu tshinanu walekni kihler-potuko.
Ha nimatlu niwekanu hixa ptowrunekhi nimwinripa. Pnute hya halixletanu hiyrunu himuwaxinripa halixleya.
Hiyáhoni hix-yehi napojinpatnaka pnut-potu hixa halixkotletko Cristo Jesus hetanuya hita tshinanu.
