Hi psojikna hpikanna hkamnitjene. Seyni tsru hchinikanurunephi. Waneyakni rimathetanna ramtakanna halikaka seyni hixa hiknohatshinephi halikaka. Hiyrunu Hoyakalukni hixa hiknohkakjeru.
Klu tshinanu hixa henekka xye halukkaluru Cristo tshinanupa seyni hi koxa wale tsonu halixyawakapni seyni wale hikolukle tshinan-koxa hsalewnakakko.
