Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine kosekatshri hi hajeyri halixatshripni, klu tshinanu wan-hixatshri ralixkotachaxnawa, hiyahokni hjihyehitko Satanás pixka.
Rujhalu kihle piranyehiru rixyawaka malixkane yehiya, klu tshinanu hma muhlepiranyehixiknuklunwa rutsekko Satanás-ya.
Waneko pixka rix-koxna Cristo halixatshine diácono-ne. Kihle piranyehirunepni, hi kachrijtatokanutatshinepni. Hi katsholu jiraklerunepni. Hi tsru tiyiro himtuklewatatshri kaypiratatshinepni.
Halixlewlu pirana halikakalutu Hoyakalu hekhirewle hinotatshinepni powratahchinikanuxikatshinepwa.
Nyi mitshikananhapka ret-hixanutkona. Waneya riknohinipna, waneyakni Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine kosekjetatshinepatkani, hike mixkanepa.
Hhanunronna waneko pixka rixanna kihle piranyehironepni. Hi jejnuhimakleronepni. Ptowru potuyako muhrokahchinikanutkanepni potukalonepni.
Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine kamrurewyehitatshinepa sato suxopka hhanunrotanu. Himat-hijretawhenetatshinepni hiyrunu hipji hajeru himat-kosekatshinepni.
Klu tshinanu kihle kamrureru yoptotanru kihle piranyehi rixinripna yine tskalaya. Hiyáhoni rumukata hiwekletanna halixlewlu pirana Jesus Cristo tshinanu pirana hike hpikanna.
Seyni hohamok-nixinipa, nyonanwakatanhi hixa het-yonhaxyawakaplu Hoyakalupji hajeru himata kosejyawakapa. Hoyakalupji, wannani yine Hoyakalu hiwekatshri hapatjetanune Cristo halixatshine. Halikak-potukananu tokantshi yoptowaka hwastsihitatshri, hwahoholeru pixkalunni.
Tsru mimat-hinkakletkotu waleni potuknutshi hchinikanu piranni klu tshinanu: “Jesus hiphujewna yineru mane rixnawa seyni riwejinriya potukalni. Hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrene tenhohne hajene hetatkalu. Ruphujtatka psol-tshijneya. Xye tshijne halixlerni. Ranikka tenhohne.”
Runkakletahnaputna Hasruklewatatshine Yáhole PiranapniHoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hinkakpotutwu hnikawnahohnexini klu papko satkaka hiknokanru halixlu pirana. Wanna hiwejikalurune yokwijetanunepni hiyrun-koxa kamtshine hasruklewle hyijnakotanna.
Xyekaka kayloklerune hasruklewleni, weyawachatatshine tokanni. Hihchinikanna rupniyatkana hatatjewa yomuwa hameru ho tshitshime yoxjehchinikanutatkana.
Nyi jejine himaletlu hnunrowlu. Rinanchitluna nikkaluru. Seyni Hoyakalu hiyakotlu xyekaka nikkaluru wniklerupa rixyawaka hiyrun-koxa wale wpoyahnuxyawaka. Hixa Cristo halixatshinwu, halikaka pirana himatatshinwu wane wixanu.
Hoyakalu kamhaleru ptowruka kihlerni. Hikeni Hoyakalu kamhaleru hiknokko seyni ptowru potuko hyoptotanu hihlenu hchinikanuyma, Hoyakalu hpoyahnutanu.
Klu tshinanu ptowru potuko powratka Hoyakalu tokanuya hiyrun-koxa hanjihohneruya.
Kamrurewhihlenutatshri Jesus Cristo Kamrure Tshinanu PiranapniNyi hiykolukaka puchinikkajinna wmoletanune Cristo tshinanu. Kihleru kamrurewatatshripatkayi Jesus Cristo kamrureya. Wane pixini ptseruwakahchinikanutanu tokantshi halixkaluruya hiyrun-koxa hasruklewlu halikakalutuya pomkahitanru pirana.
Seyni hinkaklucha hike mkochpakkatu pirana, tsrotsolejine hinkaklecha hi hyijnakotanu. Halikaka pasrujinwa Hoyakalu halujyawaka pkamhiywakapa.
Klu tshinanu wimane hasrujikowaka psotsonu repixlewaxya. Seyni Hoyakalu halujyawaka homkahixikowaka ptowru potuko repixlewaxya. Klu tshinanu repixlu wiwekle xawakni papko hiyrun-koxa hiweklu hinatshripa Hoyakalu hinkaklexyawu.
Halikaka piranni xye hima. Hiyáhoni rujhalu ralixkoxikowaka psolu hchinikanuymako.
Wale tshinanu wyapretaklewata hiyrun-koxa wkamrurewpotuta wale piranaya klu tshinanu wmunanhanru Hoyakalu Hiwekatshri, ptowru yinerumka hiwekkakjerni, wale halixatshine halikakalun-potni.
Xyekaka pirana pasruklewatanu xako. Hiyrun-koxa punkakanna ptowruneka puykole hkamhiywakna.
Hi pitshitanna yine reyijyawakyina makluji pixyawaka tshinanu. Seyni Cristo halixatshine tshinanu pyimakko tokantshi pyanumaxinri tshinanu, pixjexyawaka tshinanu, hichiniklewluya pyimakko, halixlewluya pyimakko, powralu pixjexyawaka pyimakko.
Nma mapokkanuko pchini hi pucho hethaletanu, hi putuk-hiykolewletanu, hi putuk-hasrukletanna yine nmapokkanuko pchini.
Hi petachatanru pixkontshi penejikolu pixa hwatshri pyoptoleru, hinamtatshri pirana hinkakletatshine punkakletahnaputjene. Xye honra pyoptotatka mitshikananu tsruneya hapatjetatshine kosekatshine himyona rutakhohoxinixkayina.
Xye kamrurtshikaka puslahanu hiyrun-koxa wale penejinwa. Wane pixjetanu ptowruneka yehi rimathetko ptseruwniywaka Cristo piranaya.
Puslahinwa pixa nanwaka hiyrun-koxa pasruklewle. Pomkahitanru. Klu tshinanu wane pixini papnokaxikowaka yehi piwekkajinwa hiyrun-koxa pyijnakotjene.
Tsrune Kahwakpiraxikowaka PiranapniHi ptshihetjetanru tsru yineru seyni puykotanru hatatjewa hirtshi henekahchinikanrewaxyawaka pixka. Maklujine puykotanu hatatjewa pepurune puykoxyawaka pixka.
Tsrone puykotanu punro puykoxyawaka pixka. Maklojine puykotanu pepurone puykoxyawaka psol-powranuymako pixka.
Hipnahnurutatshrone Hislahikowaka PiranapniHislahana hipnahnurutatshrone, halikaka hipnahnurutatshrone rixinna.
Seyni sato hipnahnurutatshro kwuhenero tixini ho tomekahine twini wannakni hapka rujhaluna Hoyakalu halujyawaka hkamhiywakna wannako hipjina repixyawakna tshinanu. Rutsrukatenna rapnutanna ruslahikolna tshinanu. Klu tshinanu kihleru wan-rixyawakna hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu hikchikhihlenutlu wan-hixjetatshri.
Xawakni halikaka hipnahnurutatshro pirana hapaluchatatshro potu, Hoyakalu munanhatshro tixini, tma mutuk-hanjiretkanuklunru Hoyakalu hiyrun-koxa tanjihohnejexini hoyetshno, hohohne koxa.
Seyni tiwekka pchinika poyikowlu tsonu tomkahixini hipnatshro pixkalutotkani.
Xyekaka hiykolu ptowuxinna hma muklujikowakanupna.
Seyni katukta hi hislahanna waleko himolene, hipjiko hajenewa, walekta hichotatkalu halixlewlu pirana romkahixyawaka. Wan-hixatshri malixkatu pnute hektutu kamhatshrini.
Hipnahnurutatshro, sessenta mhaleruto ho pnute mhaleruto tsonu tuslahikowaka tutakko Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshineya. Hiyrun-koxa pa katapka hnuruwtapatshro tixinipni.
Hiyrun-koxa kihle piranyehiropni. Mturune ttseruwaka tuykohihlenutna hiyrunu kyoptohihlenrewakleropni ho Cristo halixatshine Hoyakalu homkahitatshine jixi terokajexini ho salewnatshine tepixini ho ptowru kamrurtshi kihleru hepixlewatatshri tomkahpotuxini, tuslahko Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshineya.
Seyni hipnahnurutatshrone tsrotsolejine hmixkanuklunupna hi putakanna repixikowakapna Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshineya. Klu tshinanu Cristo homkahixikowaka hyinuwaka hayoklexinipna hhanuruwatanutnakna.
Hiyrun-koxa rasruhinpatkana mmerenpatkani. Pa pji pejnu hyapachatanutkana. Hi hma mernu tsonupnina seyni hyanumsalepotukananna ptowru pirana halikaka pirana pot-minje htshinapanna. Muhlepiranatu jinkakletaklerone rixnawana.
Hiyahokni hipnahnurutatshrone tsrotsolejine minje pirana hitaho hhanuruwahapkatanna. Kwuhenepna. Ruslahapjitanna. Hiyáhoni wan-hixatshronepa hike hikoluklu hkamhinwuna wkamnitjeru hektutu hma tshinanwakaxyawakanupwuna.
Klu tshinanu satkaka hipnahnurutatshro pupjeta Satanás kamtshi romkahixyawakapna.
Sato suxo Cristo halixatshro kamolero hipnahnurutatshro, walako hepixanro. Wanna Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine hi hepixanro wan-hixatshro hiyáhoni rumukata hepixletanna hipnahnurutatshrone halikak-potu halixatshrone.
Cristo Halixatshine Hapatjetatshine Kosekatshine PiranapniCristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine kosekatshine kihle hinotlerune, kahwakkalunepni. Wan-hixatshine hijhalu hwenuthihlenuxikowakna. Wanna honukla hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana jinkakletaklerune potuko hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu hasrukle hasruklewatatshine potu wan-hixko.
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru wan-tshina: “Boi hitaklu tataji hkaplokkakkoklunu hi rostunamatko boi.” Hiyrun-koxa wane htshina yonatkaluru: “Kkamrurewakleru himukata yoptoletlu hkamrure wenru.”
Hi pyijnakotanru Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine kosekatshri jihyehixikolu. Seyni hepi ho mapa hiphujtaxiniplu halikaka pirana rixinipa. Waneya pyijnakotanru halikaka.
Halikaka hektuwaka kamhatshri ptowruneka jemanu rujretko. Waneyakni pimrin-koxa pik-majnakowletanu.
Hoyakalu hetanu, Cristo Jesus hetanu, hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrerune tenhohne hajene potukalune hetan-koxa, ntowutpotutanyi nomkahjixanyi: Ptowru potuko pixinipa xye hiykolukaka pomkahpotutanu hi kakoje pixa hichinikletanna yine seyni ptowruneko pixkakaklu hixa hetjeretatshripyi.
Hi pchireta hitakletanru Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine kosekatshinepa. Hi hektune majnákonu pyoptotanu seyni powralu pimrexinwa.
Hi honhapka puranu seyni vinho-ha psohajiji puranu pisatu tshinanu, hixo kata pyeyixjexinri tshinanu.
Satuko yineru hektunu hi pyohimlu, rimapatjetkoklunutka wkatanu hohnekananuko. Seyni satuko hektutu kamhatshri hi pimathetkohapkalu.
Waneko pixka rixa kihleru kamhalu. Pimrinenu hiphujetka. Waneya pimrinenu hi himukata yohimletko.
Towrertshine, Towuwatatshine Hiykoxikolu PiranapniTowrertshine kahwakpiratanna htowutjene ptowru potuko tshinanu. Waneyakni hike yineru hapatanru Hoyakalu hi koxa wasruklewleko towrertshine tshinanu.
Hiyrun-koxa hitowrene hi heyikanru htowutjerna Cristo homkahitatshri rixini klu tshinanu Cristo tshinanu moletkakatshinni. Seyni pnute hkamrurewatanna klu tshinanu hkamrurna kihleru yoptotatshinepni Cristo halixatshine hiyrun-koxa hichinikkalunni. Xyekaka pirana pasrukjetanna, puykolewatanu. Hoyakalu Pirana Hasruklewatatshinemka Piranapni
Satu yineru pnu pejnu htshina hasruklewlexini, halikaka tokantshi Wutsrukate Jesus Cristo hasrukle hma momkahitkanuklunu, Hoyakalu homkahru pirana,
wan-hixatshri yineru halixkoxikatshriwa. Hike rimata. Seyni ralukpotutlu hepomsalkaka, hihjekaklu mujhakotu. Wla hakanhakaklu hahxalu, yahotkaklu, mkahwakpirlentshi, hektu piranalu kamhachalu,
hihjekaklu mmahletu hkamhana yine mahchinikanune, halikaka pirana mimatkanetkani. Wanna kahwaklu Hoyakalu homkahlu pirana tshinanu tsru tiyiro rumukata kayletna.
Seyni halikakni tsru kayluni Hoyakalu homkahlu pirana tshinanu rapnanuhchinikanuxinna yine Hoyakalu homkahlu pirana tshinanu.
Klu tshinanu hikeko wimapoka xye tshijne wmatuxiniklunu hiyrun-koxa hikeko wumukata hanikleta xye tshijneya.
Hiyáhoni wnikanru, wimkalu wimwini kihlehchinikanupwu.
Halikakni tsru tiyiro kaypiratatshine hyahotalexikowakna hyana. Ptowru hixatshri hike mkochpakkatu halujikolu hektutu hyohnixnawa yineru. Xyekaka heneklu yineru salewaktshi hiyrun-koxa hamhikowaka raniklewata.
Klu tshinanu tiyiro halujikolu waleni ptowru hixatshri hektutu yinuwakatshri. Pimrine tiyiro ramotlerna tshinanu halixlewlu pirana hpupjexyana. Hiyrun-koxa hixo katshinolu hkamhiynawana hyohloxnawana.
Timóteo Htserutahchinikanuxyawaka Paulo PiranapniSeyni pixa, jejyi, Hoyakalu homkahitatshriyi wale chinikantshikaka pasujini. Pomkahitanru poyahokaklewlu, Hoyakalu homkahlu potuko, halixlewlu pomkahitanu, hichiniklewlu koxa. Pomkahitanru Hoyakalu pkahwakhohnekanatanru hiyrun-koxa pmasaxinwa.
Kihle yahotlewleru pixka pixanu halixlewluya. Hiweklu hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatu pkachixinwa klu tshinanu xye tshinanu tomhakaluryi. Peyinuwakle pixka pixanu kihlewaka ptshina hiphujtalexnawa hixolune hetanu mitshi.
Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu hetanu ptowruka hiwekatshri hiyrunu Cristo Jesus hetanu, ntowutanyi. Cristo pixka pixanu Pôncio Pilatos hoji sreta rawakanaxini, kihle hiphujetle rixnawa.
Kajnakopyi Hoyakalu yokanre tshinanuya. Powralupyi, potukalu potpakyi haté rapojinpotuko Wutsrukate Jesus Cristo.
Rapokpapkolupotuxinipa Hoyakalu wan-hixkakanru. Hoyakalu honra Hoyakalu satupkalutu, Tsru Hixikatshriwani, himalwutkalurni. Waleni pohirtshine pohire hiyrun-koxa tsru hixikatshinwa hitsrukatni.
Wale tsonni mupnakatu, Hoyakalu katawaka riwejya. Hike himukata hapoklestsitanru. Hike yineru hetlu Hoyakalu, hi koxa rumukata hetletanruna. Walepni kahwakpirhohnekanatkalurupa hiyrun-koxa tsru pixkontshipa hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa. Seyoka.
Ptowutanna kihle rixyawakapna pimrine, phurune hixkakanna kihler-kamrurtshiyma. Ptowutanna jenekaklerune rixyawakna, kapikaklerunepni.
Hiyáhoni wan-hixatshinepa halukkaluru rapatjeyehixinwana ptowru potuko poyehitatshri hinatshripa tshinanu hiweklu halikakalutu hkayaxyawakapna tshinanu.
Timóteo Ruykoxyawakatnaka Paulo PiranapniTimóteo, puslahinwa pmunanhikoluya. Pkotspalaxinwa hektut-pirana hipiranachakaka tshinikoluya. Hiyrun-koxa yanumsalkaka hike mkochpakkatu pirana, himatkaltshi pirana htshinka seyni hike pkotspalaxinwa.
Satuko yineru xye himatkaltshi himwatshine htshinnawana waneyakni hpupjexyaluna halixlewlu pirana romkahixyawakna. Hoyakalu hihlenu renekachale pixaymapa.
<font color=teal>2 Timóteo</font>Paulo Halijyawakna Yine PiranapniTwu yonawahlo Paulo yokanrerni, Cristo Jesus nurreru, Hoyakalu halujyawaka tshinanu. Nyokanatka nunkaklexyawaklu hiwejikaluru hikeklu mnikawnakatu pirana Hoyakalu hinkakletleru pirana Jesus Cristo-ya.
Twu nyonata Timóteo tshinanupa, noturu pixkalutu nuchinikanru. Nanjiyehitanyi Hoyakalu hihlenu henekachalu, hetwamonutkalurupyi, hapnanuhchinikanutatshripyi, Hoyakalu Wuru yehiya hiyrun-koxa Wutsrukate Cristo Jesus-ya.
Himalwuru Hiyrunu Hiykolukaka PiranapniNimalwutlu Hoyakalu, htowre kamhatshrino nutsrukatenni pixka. Powra hchinikanurno. Hoyetshno, hohi koxa hi nutuk-hichinikanretletyi pixa nanjihohnereya.
Nuchinikaktehaxinyi. Naluk-hetlepotutmakyi. Waneyamka numuwpotutanu.
Nuchinikanretlu palixle halikak-potu. Mitshikananhapka pajiro Lóide wan-hixa halixleta hiyrun-koxa punro Eunice. Nimatlu pix-koxa wanna pixka pixa halixleta.
Hiyáhoni naluk-hichinikkakletanyi hi petachatanru xye pixkontshi Hoyakalu henekachaxyayi pyoptotlu nomyo nutakahohoxinixkayi mitshi.
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru renejyawu Hoyakalu, hi jhamleholu hchinikanni. Seyni halikaka Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru pixkontshi renejyawu, pimrine wuchinijyawaka, hixko hchinikanu rixkakwu.
Hiyáhoni hi pipatewatanru Wutsrukate Jesus pirana puphujexyawaka. Hiyrun-koxa hi pipatewatanno hita, kachitkalurno Cristo tshinanu. Seyni Hoyakalu pixkonu pixa henekkaluru psolutu tshinanu ptsaklawna nsalewniywaka kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana punkajikolu pirana tshinanu.
Hoyakalu hiwekkakwu hiyrun-koxa htshanixwu wale hinerune wixyawakatka. Hi hixako wkamhanru tshinanu htshanixwu seyni waleko hihchinikanu tshinanni. Hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu hihlenu renekachale tshinanu htshanixwu. Hmawkanuklunuwa hyinuwakle papko Hoyakalu henekwu xye kihleru renekachale Jesus Cristo tshinanuya.
Hoyakalu hihlenu renekachale rimathetka Wiwekkakjeru Jesus Cristo hiphujewnale tshinanu. Walekni hipuktshi nikatatka hiyrunu ruphujetlu hiweklu, hiweklu mnikawnakat-koxa kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri piranaya.
Hoyakalu nuretno, rutakno jinkaklewakleru nixyawaka, judeu mixkane nasrujyawakapa.
Hiyáhoni wale tshinanu wla nixa salewnaleta. Wanepnawaka hi nuhrokahchinikanuta. Klu tshinanu nimatlu nmunanhalerni Cristo. Hiyáhoni hi nkaheklu himukatatshri potukni wale rimretjixikolu ruslahyawaka haté rapokhohnexinipa rapkatle hohne potuko.
Halikak-potuk-tokantshi, pixa nasrukjekanatanru tokantshi pomkahitanu. Pmixkota halixletanu wale tokantshiya hiyrun-koxa hamotlewlu piranaya, wimwaleru Jesus Cristo-ya.
Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru, hixa himwatshri pixkonu tshinanu puslahanru pmunanhikolu kihleru.
Hixa ptowrunekhi himatlu halixatshine Ásia tshijne hajene hiknojyawakno pirana. Nuknokjeneymalunni Fígelo tshinkaluru hiyrun-koxa Hermógenes tshinkaluru.
Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hetwamonutanna Onesíforo-pji hajene. Klu tshinanu hixo kata rapnanuhchinikankakno. Hi ripatewatno hita, hostutkalurno.
Seyni Roma poktshi rapojinixka rujhapotutno haté rukchikno.
Nanjitlu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu renejyawakaplu kihle hchinikanu rixyawakapa Hoyakalu hetwamonutanru wale hohnepa. Pixa himatpotutlu hi pejnu kata kananu repixno Éfeso poktshiya.
Jesus Cristo Soldado-te Kihler-piranapniHiyáhoni pixa, noturu pixkalutu, pmixkotahchinikanuxinwa Hoyakalu hihlenu renekachale Cristo Jesus-ya.
Pirankaka pjemakanatanru, nunkakle hixo hetatshine yehi, xyekaka pirana pasrukanna jejine pmunanhalene. Waneyakni pimrin-koxa rumukata hasrukletanna.
Hita pixka pixanu salewnalu pakotachatanu. Jesus Cristo soldado-te kihleru pixka pixinwa.
Kyahotkakakleru haluka poyikowkakletlu htowutjeru. Hiyáhoni wan-hixatshri soldado hi rujhalu hma towuxikowakanuko hkamhiywaka.
Hasuklu hasukamxikatshri hi yoptotanru rumlujikolupa hma momkahitkanuklunru hasuklu hixannu.
Susanateru hijhalu rusanate hajeru hnijyawaka wale hapka.
Pujhahchinikanutanu wane ntshinyawakyi. Klu tshinanu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu himatjemkakanyi ptowru pirana potuko.
Xye tshinanu nsalewna. Kachitkalurno hektutu kamhatshri pixka. Seyni Hoyakalu tokanu hi kachitkaluru.
Hiyáhoni nakotachatlu ptowru potuko Hoyakalunerune nuretkalune tshinanu. Wane nixjeta rumukata hiwekkakletkona Jesus Cristo-ya hiyrun-koxa rumukata Hoyakalu yehi hwalexyawakapna hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa.
Xye tokantshi potukalni: “Cristo-yma wupnini, waleyma koxa wiwekanu.
Salewnalu wakotachaxini, Cristo-yma wpohirewatanu. Hi nimathetlu, wtshinanwakaxiniplu Cristo, hi himathetanunwu hixapni.
Cristo wpupjehetanuxini, hi ruknokanwu wale. Klu tshinanu hi rumukata yohikletokanuta htshinyawakatka tshinanu.
Kamrurewatatshri MpatewatkatupaXyekaka pirana puchinkapkakanna pkoseklene. Hoyakalu hetanu tshinanu pujretpotutanna hma yanhakkajyawakanupna tokantshikaka tshinanu. Yanhaklu tokantshikaka tshinanu hikeko hkochpaka seyni rumtukachatna yijnakotatshine.
Pujhahchinikanutanu Hoyakalu ppoyahnuwkajyawaka. Kamrurewatatshri mpatewatkatupyi. Hoyakalu tokanu halikakalutu mpupje hasruklewletkatupyi.
Tokantshi muhletu, yanumsalu tshinachatatshri pkatjixini. Klu tshinanu xye pixkalutu herutna yine Hoyakalu halujyawaka hma momkahixyawakanna.
Xye pixkalutu hasruklu chretshi tseruwnapiratatshri pixkalutni. Himeneu hiyrunu Fileto tshinkaluru hasruklewle wan-hixatshri.
