Wla htshininniri mitshi Abraão-ni: “Nunkaklexyayi halikaka nuhlewahchinikanyehitanyi hiyrun-koxa nixolewnakakpotutanyi.”
Waneya Abraão-ni hmachiretannu tshinanu hyoptotlu Hoyakalu hinkaklexyanri.
Klu tshinanu yine hasruhlu wanna pnute himukatatshri hiwaka hkochtshejyawakna ralixpotuxikolupa runkakle piranna. Hiyrun-koxa runkaklexyahi tshinanu hnikatko hikoluklewatatshri.
Hoyakalu haluk-hekhirpotutna runkajya piranna yoptotatshinepa hi hkachrijetanru runkajya piranna. Hiyáhoni runkajya pirannayma waleko hiwaka hkochtshekatka.
Xye hepi pirana mmayxakatu tshinanu, hi rumukata weyawleta Hoyakalu, hiyáhoni wimwalu hixko hchinikanu wixle Hoyakalu tshinanu. Hiyáhoni wumukata hikchikletlu tsru hepixlewlu, hixa Hoyakalu nwaka hasukatshine pixkalunwu, wunkaklexikolu kahwakatshinpotwu.
Xye wkahwakachale waleni wihchinikanu tsatapre munanhakaluru, poyehiru pixkalutu. Wkahwakachale hiknokakwu mkatshri sama himaletlewatatshri yehiya.
Wane hjihlokatka Jesus wkosekjeru. Hixa tshinanu Tsru Sacerdote rixnawa hike rixiniko mnikawnakatupa, Melquisedeque tshinkaluru hitajikolu pixka.
Melquisedeque Tshinkaluru Phurukananu Hiyrunu Sacerdote-kananutkaniMelquisedeque tshinkaluru Salém tshinikowaka poktshi pohire hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu ten-potu hajeru Sacerdote-tetkani. Abraão-ni mitshi hiylakaklu nwaka ruchpajinnixka pohiruneyma xye Melquisedeque yoptotapniru mitshi. Kihlewaka htshinanwakatniri Abraão-ni.
Waneklu papko Abraão-ni ptowruka hkonreru hkamnitjene hejnunkate psojkaka reneklu hiylakaklu yehi hkoninri. Melquisedeque wla raluka tshinreta ‘Pohirtshi Kihle Kamrureru’. Hiyrun-koxa Salém poktshi pohire rixyawaka tshinanu wale hiwaka wla htshin-koxa, ‘Pohirtshi Kihle Hwachaleru’.
Hike ruruta. Hike runrota. Rutsrukatene hi kapiranyehna. Hi kyinuwakle piranru. Hiyrun-koxa hi kapiranyehru hnikawninri. Hoyakalu whene pixka rixatka. Sacerdote rixhohnekanaxinripni. Levi Sacerdote Hitajikolu Koxa Yohnik-himukatatshri Cristo Sacerdote Hitajikolu
Haha hetanu hi pa himukatlekananru Melquisedeque tshinkaluru klu tshinanu haté Abraão-ni, judeu-nerune hitsrukate potuko, rejnunkate hkonreru hiylakaklu tshinanu, wale hejnu psoji reneklu Melquisedeque.
Halikaka Moisés yonreru towutlu Sacerdote Levi tshinkaluru klopicha Sacerdote-ne hijhawenruyehixyawakapna yine ptowruka rimwalerna psoji renejyawakapna. Waleko hinerune tsonu rujhawenruyehita, yahmaklu Abraão-ni rurutna wanna.
Melquisedeque hi Sacerdote Levi tshinkaluru klopichni wale, wanepnawaka rujhalu Abraão-ni wenuxyawaklu, psoji hejnu hkonreru hiylakaklu tshinanuya. Waneya Melquisedeque hihlewahchinikanutlu Abraão-ni. Kihlewaka htshinanwakatniri Abraão-ni Hoyakalu hinkaklexinri potnikni.
Halikakpotni, kihle hwachalepyi tshinrewatatshri potu, yohnik-himukatatshriwani wale.
Sacerdote-ne, tiyiro psoji yoptotatshinekananu, yinechakananni hiyáhoni hipnatshinepni. Seyni Melquisedeque mitshi hejnu psoji yoptotatshritka, Hoyakalu tokanu hiphujetlu, xye hpaklu hiwekletawa.
Hiyáhoni wane ntshina, sacerdote Levi tshinkaluru, yine himwaleru psoji yoptojekanatatshri, hatatjewa hwenut-koxlu Melquisedeque mitshi, Abraão-niyma.
Klu tshinanu yáholu hi hmatutawa Levi tshinkaluru, seyni hatatjewa Abraão-ni mane rawakanatatka Levi, Melquisedeque yoptotapinri Abraão-ni mitshi klu tshinanu Abraão-ni hichpakatshripni wale, Levi.
Klu tshinanu satuko sacerdote hitakkoklunupa, waneya htowuwle piran-koxa satpako.
Klu tshinanu xyekaka pirana tshinanwakatkaluru, pa nerukni. Hiyrun-koxa satu neruko yineru hi himukata xye altar yehi kamrurewlexikatshri hixleta.
Klu tshinanu himatpotutkalurni Judá klopichni Wutsrukate Jesus. Hiyrunu Moisés sacerdote pirana htshinini mitshi hi xye Judá-nerune tshinanni.
Satu Sacerdote Melquisedeque Pixkalutu PiranapniHiyáhoni phujetanur-potni satu hixatshri sacerdote hiphujewnatshritka Melquisedeque tshinkaluru pixkalutu.
Hi Moisés yonreru tshinanu, hi yineru halujyawaka tshinanu sacerdote rutakka seyni sacerdote rixinwa hiweklu mnikawnakatu himukatle tshinanu wan-rixa.
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru wan-tshina: “Pixni Sacerdote hohnekananyi, Melquisedeque hitajikolu pixka.”
Hiyáhoni Moisés yonreru mitshikawluru hi towuwatatka, klu tshinanu hi kpixkonru wale.
Klu tshinanu Moisés yonreru towre hike hpotukata. Seyni kahwakkaluru wane pnute himukatatshri hakanhatka. Hiyáhoni xye kahwaklu tshinanu Hoyakalustsi wapokanu.
Jesus-yma Rawa Hoyakalu Hinkajya Piranwu PiranapniHiyrun-koxa rawa Hoyakalu tokanu runkaklexyalu pirana. Pimrine sacerdote-nekananu sacerdote-ne rixapna seyni Hoyakalu hike pirana runkakletahnapuxyana.
Seyni Jesus sacerdote rixyawakapa mitshi Hoyakalu hinkaklexyalu, wla tshinatshri mitshi: “Hitni Hoyakalno Tsru Hixikatshriwano hinkakletlu, hiyrunu hi nyokmakahchinikanuta. Pixni Sacerdote hike rixiniko mnikawnakatupyi”, htshina.
Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu hinkaklexyalu tshinan-koxa, rimaxikowak-potupa Jesus-yma rawa Hoyakalu hinkajya piranwu himukatatshri potuko.
Klu tshinan-koxa sacerdote-ne hixo rixapna klu tshinanu rupnajekanatna hiyáhoni hi rumukata paklu kamruretna hipuktshi rimaletjerna tshinanu.
Seyni Jesus hiweka hike rixiniko mnikawnakatupa. Hiyáhoni sacerdote rixyawaka hi himat-nikawna satuko kachrihyawakaplu hkamrure.
Hiyáhoni rumukata hiwekkaklepotutna yine, wale yapatshine pejnu Hoyakalu nwaka yatshinepa. Klu tshinanu riwekhohnekanata ranjijexyawakaplu Hoyakalu wanna tshinanupa.
Wale tshinanu Jesus-kni W-sacerdote-te Tsru Potuko, wujhaleru potuko! Potukal-potukni wale hike mmahaxikatni, powralu. Hiyrun-koxa hektune yehi kotspalaxikalurni wale, tenhohne ten-potu hajerni wale.
Pimrinni tsru sacerdote-nni pixka hi rixa. Hi ptowru hohneruka henekachalu hiylatkaluru rujha kamhaleta, mitshikananhapka waleko hektunu tshinanu wane pnute yine hektunu tshinanu rujhatnaka, hi rixa wale. Klu tshinanu Jesus pa katapka wale nanuko henekachaxnawa henekachlu hiylatkaluru rixnatkawa.
Tsru sacerdote-ne Moisés yonreru pirana hitakanune yine mpotukane rixapna. Seyni Hoyakalu hinkajya piranru, Moisés yonreru wkatanu, hnuretlu Whentshi tshinkaluru hike mmahaxikatu rixyawaka hike rixiniko mnikawnakatupni.
Jesus W-sacerdote-te Tsru Potuko PiranapniXye pirana ptowruka wtshinakanatanru haptowruxikolni xye. Waneywu xye pixkalutu Tsru Sacerdote. Ptowru Potuko Himukatatshri tenhohne hajeru tuplawakle, hpotukle sreta hwatshrini wale.
Hoyakalu yehi kotspalaxikowaka kamrurewaxikatshrini, Hoyakalupji potu kamrurewyehixikatshri. Hoyakalu kamhapjitanru yehi. Hi yineru kamhapjitanruni.
Klu tshinanu ptowru tsru sacerdote hitakka henekachalkaka hiyrunu niktshi hiylatkalurkaka renekjexyawaka. Hiyáhoni hijhakalurni xye W-sacerdote-te Tsru Potuko himukatatshri rixyawaka henekachalu pirana tshinan-koxa.
Hewi, xye tshijne hajeru rixkamka Jesus, himka sacerdote-pni, klu tshinanu rawna sacerdote-ne xye tshijne hajene henekachlukaka heneklewatatshine, Moisés yonreru towre kamhatshine.
Sacerdote-ne kamrure halikaka tenhohne hwatshri yaperechani hiyrunu tenhohne hwatshri kamrure yapkaklechani. Hiyáhoni wale tshinanu Hoyakalu wan-tshinru Moisés, Hoyakalupji nikalumta kamhikolu hkamhakjixlu Moisés mitshikananu, wla htshininri: “Xako puslahanru pekhixikolu, teno mriji petakanaxinri potuko mayawle, pkamhanu xako ptowru potuko. Hi psojikna pmayxajinri.”
Seyni halikaka Jesus yoptotlu satu kamrurtshi sacerdote-ne kamhajekanatanru yohnik-hijhakaluru kamrurtshipa. Hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu yine runkajya pirana Jesus-ya, wale hijhakalur-potni klu tshinanu Hoyakalu hinkajya piranwu, kochpakatshri pirana potukni.
Klu tshinanu mitshikananu Hoyakalu hinkakletlewaxya pirana hike hma mahaxiknumka waneyamka hi rujhanutkalu hepi rixinri.
Seyni Hoyakalu hetna hinerune jikolukanuru hkamhiywakna hiyáhoni wla htshina mitshi: Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu wla htshina: “Hetanu, rapokhohnetanu herotu pirana nunkaklexyana israel-nerune, Hiyrunu wale piranako nunkaklexyana judá-nerune.
Hi rutsrukatennina nunkaklexinri pixkalutu nunkaklexyanna, wannani Egito tshijne nkosemyoxinnina nkochpajinnixkana mitshi. Klu tshinanu wannani hi homkahitlu nunkajya piranna. Hiyáhoni nuknokatkana — htshina Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu.
Hinatshripa hohne nunkaklexinna israel-nerune, wla ntshinanna — htshina Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu: Nyonreru pirana wanna hchinikanu nutakanru, hiyrun-koxa wanna hajkaka nyonaxinri. Hitapni Royakalutnona, hiyrun-koxa wannapni, nayinetene.
Waneklupa hike yineru hijretanru rimwastsireru ho himole wla tshinreymapa: “Pimathetanru Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu,” hi htshina. Klu tshinanu ptowru neruka himatanutkano, mujhakone himatanutkano haté tsru hijhakaluru potuko himatanutkano.
Waneya netwamonreyma namtakahchinikanuxinna rektunna. Hiyrun-koxa hi nuchinikanretanutnaklu hmajnakonuna.”
Hoyakalu Himalwuxikolu Potuko PiranapniMitshikananu Hoyakalu tshinyawaka hanu rumukata hixletna yine Hoyakalu himalwuxikolu pirana hiyrun-koxa himalwuxikowakapji yineru kamhaleru hixikowakapa pirana.
Pantshi kamhakaluru hwapa. Yoptowaka hruko rawa nikotapi hitakawaka, mesa hiyrun-koxa pão projkaka hwiywaka. Xye hruko Hoyakalu tshinanu kotspalatkaluru htshinka.
Hepi rixinri mkatshri sama hiwrolekatshri, himalexyawaka hruko, Hoyakalu hwiywak-potuko, tshinkaluru.
Wkatanu hruko rawa kapajiru phamluru yoxikawaka ouro-mta hwahoholeru paji. Hiyrun-koxa pnute hruko rawa kapajiru Hoyakalu hwiywaka, ouro-mta hwahoholeru paji. Xye paji hitokote rawa Arão kanojere surewatatshri hiyrunu kolpeto ouro kamhikolu, nikluru maná hitakluru hiyrunu Hoyakalu tokanu yine kojiretatshri pirana, sotlu tshrajkaka hwatshri yonawahlo kapajiru hwakanatatshri pejnu.
Xye kapajiru hoho rawna mayawletshine Hoyakalu towrene tenhohne hajene mayawle, hektuntshi hiknokawaka yehi katshpokatshine. Seyni xyekaka yapkaklu pirana hi wumukata kochtsheklepotuta xawakni.
Halikaka rali halpokletkoklunutka xyekaka ptowruka, waneya sacerdote-ne Hoyakalupji jihlokawakle putu hkamrurewjekanaxyatkana hkamrurna Hoyakalu towuxyana.
Seyni hepi rixinri hruko, tsru sacerdote tsonu jihlokjeta, pa katapka pa mhalekaka tshinanu tsonu. Nikalu hraha manikkatu tsru sacerdote hi jihloklu klu tshinanu rujhalu hrahtshi renekjexyawaka waleko hpupjere tshinanu hiyrun-koxa yine pupjere tshinanu.
Xye hasruklu hkochtsheka Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru rekhipotuxyawakapwu Hoyakalupji hiputre hruko hwaka pchinika, hi kyapawaklewalu Hoyakalu hwiywak-potuko hjihlojyawakapna yine.
Xye pirana yapkaklu piranni xawakni papko tshinanu. Wimaxyawakaplu henekachlukaka hiyrunu henekachalu hiylatkalurkaka renekjekanaxyawakna yine mitshi hi rumukata powratletlu yine hchinikanu.
Xye nikkaluru pirana, hirkaluru pirana, ptowru hixatshri herojikolu pirana, waleni mantshi hijrexikolkaka piranni. Xyekaka mitshi hkamhajixkana yine haté rerotexikolu hohne hapojinpotpako.
Cristo-ni Herotu Jihlepokoyehlewakleru PiranapniSeyni Cristo hapokatka Tsru Sacerdote rixyawakapa kihler-kaka hinatshripa tshinanu. Cristo kamrurewaxikowaka kihler-potukni hiyrunu hi psojikna hmahaxyatka. Hiyrun-koxa hkamrurewjexikowaka hi yinerumyo kamhalerni, hiyahokni hi xye tshijne hajeru hwatshrini.
Hjihloklu Hoyakalu tsonu hwiywak-potuko yehi. Hi raniklu bode hraha, hi boi whenene hrahaymako hjihlokyehitlu seyni waleko hihrahayma hjihloklu. Rukchijyatkawu hixa yinwu hektunu wenuxikolu hike rixiniko mnikawnakatupni yáholu pa katapka hjihloklu Hoyakalu tsonu hwiywaka potuko yehi.
Klu tshinanu boi jeji hraha ho bode hraha ho vaca yoxikaluro pahi hpolhohoxikolna, poyaho powratletkamkana hektuntshi pitshotanune, hpowratkomkatkana yine.
Hiyáhoni wane pnut-potu himukatatshrini Cristo hraha. Cristo honukla Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hike rixiniko mnikawnakatupa himukatleyma, walenuko renejnawa Hoyakalu yehiya henekachlu hi psojikna mahaxikatshrini, hixa hchinikanu hpowraxyawakapa hike mkochpakkatu kamrurtshiya, Hoyakalu hiwekatshri wkamrurewyehixyawakapa.
Hiyáhoni wale tshinanu Cristo-ni herotu jihlepokoyehlewakleru. Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu tshanixlene pejnu rumukata yoptoletluna hyoptotanrupna hike rixiniko mnikawnakatupa pirana Hoyakalu hinkaklexyana pirana. Rumukata wan-hixletna klu tshinanu Jesus hipnale hichokakatkana yine pupjetatshine mitshikananu kojiretlu hwatshri hjihyehikanatjerna yehi.
Klu tshinanu hanuktako rawa hipnatshri hiknokamtanru hejnu pirana, ralukhimatkopotuta ho halikaklahe rupnatka hejnu hiknokamtatshri ho hike.
Klu tshinanu riwekka pchinika ruknokamtanrupa hejnu pirana hike yineru rumukata hepixleta hejnu pirana. Seyni hejnu hiknokamtatshripa hipnini tson-patka waneya halikaka repixlewatanutka hejnu hiknokamtkalurupa pirana.
Hiyáhoni wale tshinanu mitshikananu Hoyakalu yine runkaklexya pirana koxa, hrahtshi hiyokleyma tsonu hkochpaka.
Klu tshinanu mitshi Moisés hijrexinixkana yine ptowruneka hiykolu pirana yonatkaluru ptowru piranako rali hinkaklexinixkana waneya boi whenene hraha hiyrunu bode-ne hraha hkochtshekamta. Waneya honha hyapjehatlu hrahtshi. Waleha carneiro pixi seroluyma hiyrunu hitaklu hissopo chehiyma rutsalaptahjexyalu papel-mta Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru hiyrun-koxa ptowrunek-yine rutslaptahjeta.
Wla htshinreymana yine: “Xyekni hrahtshi ntshinyahi pirana hihlepokotatshri Hoyakalu hijrexyahi pirana romkahjixyahi piranhi.”
Hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalupji nikalumta kamhikolu, hrahtshi rutslaptahjetlu hiyrunu ptowru hixatshri kapajiru Hoyakalupji hwatshri kamrurewapi stono rutslaptahjetkatka hrahtshi.
Psokaklu ptowruko Moisés yonre kochtshekleru pirana hijhatkalu hrahtshi hpowraxikowakapa. Hiyrun-koxa hrahtshi hma kochpakkonuklunu, hi rawa ramtakahchinikanyehixikolu hektuntshi.
Cristo Hraha Hiknojyawaklu Hektuntshi PiranapniXyekaka yihapkakletlu tenhohne hwatshrikaka halikakalutu, hiyáhoni rujhatkalu wan-rixikowaka hpowraxikowakatka. Seyni tenhohne Hoyakalu yehi hwatshrikaka potu haluklu hiylatkaluru wale yohnik-himukatatshrini.
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu hwiywaka tshinanu tsonni, pantshi yineru kamhaler-yehi, tenhohne hwatshri yahlucha, hi hjihloka Cristo. Seyni tenhohne potuko hjihlokatka. Hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu hetanu potukawaka yehi rawa haté xawakni, hixa repixyawakapa.
Judeu-ne tsru sacerdote-te, ptowru mhaleko hjihloka Hoyakalu tsonu hwiywak-yehi nikalu hrahayma. Seyni Cristo hi hijhalu wane jihlojemnukanaxyawaka henekachalu hiylatkaluru rixnawakapwa.
Klu tshinanu wane pixka rixkamkatka waneyamka xye tshijne yinuwajinikananuko haté xawaknimkatshi wan-rixa salewakatanutshi hixo kata. Seyni xawakni Cristo hiphujewnatka xye rapkatle hohne sreta, hektuntshi ruknojyawakapa waleko rupnale himukatle tshinanu, henekachalu hiylatkaluru rixnawakwa.
Satkaka yineru hipnatshripni. Waneya wane wkatanupa rawanu hikolukanuwnalkaka.
Hiyáhoni wan-rixa Cristo. Pa katapka renejnawa hixolune yine hektunu hkonyawakapa. Hiyrun-koxa hepi kata rixinri runanu ruphujewnayehixyawakapna yine ptowruneka, hkahwakpotutjene hetanuya. Waneklupa hi hektuntshi hkonyawakapa tshinanu runanu seyni riwekkajyawakapna yine tshinanni.
Cristo Pa Katapka Renekmanexnawa Ptowru Papkoko Himukatatshripni PiranapniMoisés yonre hi ruphujetpotutlu ptowru pirana kihleru halikakalutu, hinatshripa pirana. Hiyrunu Moisés yonreru pirana hi Hoyakalu yehi hwatshri potuk-piranni seyni wale mayawle pixkalutu tsonutkani. Klu tshinanu ptowru mhal-kakako wale pixkalutu henekachlukaka hiylatkaluru renekjeta yine tshinanu. Hi rutuka henekachalu kamhaljetna seyni wanepnawaka hi hpotukatkatkana wanna yine Hoyakalu hijhatshinemka.
Seyni ptowru mhaleko xye pixkalutu henekachlukaka hichinikkakjetlu yineru hektunu pirana.
Klu tshinanu hejnune, ho boi ho bode hraha hi himukata hiknokletlu hektuntshi.
Hiyáhoni Cristo hapojiniklunutkalu xye tshijne wla htshinanwakatlu Hoyakalu: “Henekachlu hiylaxikolu hiyrunu henekachlukaka hi pujha pixa. Seyni satu mantshi palpokohnaputno.
Henekachlu yoxikalurkaka, hiylatkaluru hektuntshi wenrumka, hi poyikotyi.
Waneya wla ntshinatka: — Ha, Hoyakalu, hewno hita. Nuna palujyawaka nkamhiywakapa Moisés papel-te steno nyonpiranyehixika ptowru pirana potuka nkamhiywakapa.”
Mitshikananhapka wla htshina: “Hi paluklu hiyrunu hi hpoyikotyi henekachlukaka hiylatkaluru hi hejnune henekachalkaka poyikotyi hi henekachlu yoxikaluruko poyikotyi hi henekachlukaka hektuntshi wenrumkako poyikotyi.” Wale wan-tshinru xye pirana yáholu xyekaka henekachalkaka renekjetmakna Moisés yonreru tshinyawaka pixka.
Waneya wane wkatanu wla htshin-koxa: “Ha, Hoyakalu hewno hita. Nuna palujyawaka nkamhiywakapa”. Hiyáhoni mitshikananu rixjekanaxyawakna hnikatatka hepi rixinri rutakatka.
Jesus Cristo, Hoyakalu halujyawaka hkamhiywaka tshinanu, hpowratwu hixa ptowruka wektunuya renekachale tshinanu. Pa katapka renekmanexnawa ptowru papkoko himukatatshripni.
Hiyrun-koxa judeu-ne sacerdote-te ptowru hohnekananuko hyotunotna sacerdote kamrure hkamhiywakapna henekachlukaka renekjexyawakapna. Hiyrunu hixo kata wale pixkalut-kaka henekachlu rixjetna. Seyni xye pixkalutu henekachlu hikeklu hohne rumukata konretlu hektuntshi.
Seyni Jesus Cristo rali heneklexinixkalu renekachale satupkalutu hektuntshi hkonyawakapa hike rixiniko mnikawnakatupni waneya Hoyakalu potukle sreta htuplatatka.
Wane hkahwajyalu haté hkamnitjene hijixi hpuko rutakkoklunpatkana.
Klu tshinanu renekachle satupkalutu tshinanu hike mmahaxikane rixkakhohnekanatna yine hnurrene, walenu tsonuko rixyawakapna.
Hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru xye pirana ruphujetanwakjetwu. Hiyáhoni wla htshina mitshi:
“Xye ntshinyana wale hohnekakni wkatanu, — htshinrerutkani Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu. — Ntokanu ntowuxyana rajna nutakanru hiyrun-koxa hihchinikanna nyonaxinri.”
“Rektunna hiyrunu pnuko rixlenna hikeklu hohne nuchinikanretanutnaklu.” — htshina.
Klu tshinanu xyekaka hektuntshi hiknojikatka hiyáhoni wan-hixatshri hi hijhalu henekachlu hiylatkaluru wane wkatanu.
Hoyakalu Kayehikatshine PiranapniHiyáhoni Cristo tshinanu nmoletanune hike wpikanu Hoyakalu tsonuko hwiywak-potuko yehi wjihlojyawakapa. Jesus hraha hiyokkalurutka tshinanu wumukatlu.
Mkatshri sama hipekole, Hoyakalupji hwakanatatshri sama Cristo manekni wale. Cristo mane hiweklu heneklewatatshri wyapanu hihlepokoxikowaka wjihlojyawakapa Hoyakalu tsonuko hwiywak-potuko yehi.
Hiyáhoni waneywu satu Tsru Sacerdote Hoyakalupji towutatshri.
Xye tshinanu wkayehikanru Hoyakalu potuka hchinikanurunepwu, halixpotutatshinepwu, wajkaka hitslaptahjexikowakatka ptowru hektutu chinikantshiya hiyrun-koxa herkamanetkalune pixkalunepwu powrahalu katkalunepwu.
Chiko halixlerunepwu walixleya. Hi pnu pejnu hixahchinikanutatshinepwu. Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu htshinyawaka poyahokakatshrini.
Hichinikanretkakatshinepwu. Wepixkakanu wuchiniklewaxyawakapa hiyrunu kihleru tsonu wkamhanu.
Hi wucho hapatjeretanu pimrine hixjexyawaka pixka hi wixanu. Seyni henekahchinikankakatshinepwu pnut-potu klu tshinanu wetlu hi howukatkalu hinatshri hohnepa.
Klu tshinanu wimatjeminri halikakalutu pirana seyni wpaklu majnakowlexini wanepnawaka waneya wane wkatanu hi rawanutka henekachlu hiylatkalurupa hektuntshi tshinanu.
Seyni hapnokatlewlu kahwakatshripni tsru hpikleyma. Jhekantshi tshitshmero pa hamnurutu nikatanuna yinepni Hoyakalu kamnitatshinepni.
Moisés yonreru majnakowaxikatshri hiylatko, hike hetwamonutanru, hepi ho mapa ruphujtatjene tshinanu.
Hiyáhoni hi pso salewnalukananu rujha yineru Hoyakalu Whene heyikatshri, hrahtshi runkaklexikolna hpowratjerumkana malukkotu hikahwakatshine? Hiyrunu hi pa salewaktshikananu rapnokaxikna Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru henekachale hihlenu heyikatshine?
Klu tshinanu wimatlu wla tshinatshri: “Napnuyehixinwa. Hita hapnurewatanu.” Hiyrun-koxa wla htshina: “Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hikolukanuwnayehjixanna rayinetene.”
Tsru jhamleru potuko Hoyakalu hiwekatshri hapnokatle hapokatshripa.
Satkakhi hixa hixolune hetanu heyikkatka hiyrunu hapnokatka. Hiyrun-koxa satkakhi hixa hepiretakanatna wan-hixa saletletkalune.
Waneklu papko hixa hijha hepixlejekanatna kachitkalune. Hi htshipexyana hejnunkate seyni hsaletjekanatlu tsru poyikonutshiyma, klu tshinanu himathetlu jejnunkathi yohnikalutu mimat-nikawnakatu tenhohneya.
Hiyáhoni xawakni hi hiknokanru xye hmunanhaleru klu tshinanu wale tshinanu waneyaphi tsru himlujikolu.
Seyni hijhalu hmachiretannu waneya Hoyakalu halujyawaka hali kamhalexinipa hyoptotanru runkaklexya piranhi.
Klu tshinanu wla htshina Hoyakalu pirana yonatkaluru: “Pchini tsonujiji mahatawa hinatshripa rapojyawakapa. Hi ramhanu. Hi hohamokaplu.
Hoyakalu potukatlene hiwekanu halixlu tshinanu. Halikaka piklewtapatshinepni hi poyikotanru nohchinikanu.”
Halikaka hixa hi satkapatshine pixka wixanu, wamtajyawakaplu hiweklu. Seyni hixa Cristo halixatshinwu hiwejikowaka wwiya.
Halixlu PiranapniHalixlu waleni hinatshripa kahwajikolu hiyrun-koxa waleni metkotkaka halixikolu.
Halixlu tshinanu honukla judeu hitsrukatenni hikchikhihlenutka Hoyakalu hetanuya.
Halixlu tshinanu wimatlu ptowru tshijnekananuka hakanhatka, kihle poklu ptowruka, Hoyakalu tokanu tshinanu. Halixlu tshinan-koxa wimatlu hetkaluru ptowruka, metkotu hkamhika.
Abel, Enoque, Noé Tshinkalune Halixle PiranapniHalixlu tshinanu, Abel henekachlu halukkaluru potu, reneklu Hoyakalu, Caim henekachlu pnute hihlenurutu. Wale tshinanu Hoyakalu himatatkaklu potukalu rixyawakatka Abel. Ruphujetlu potukalu rixyawaka Abel renekachlekaka Hoyakalu yoptoxyawaka tshinanu. Hiyáhoni haté xawakni runkakletkawa Abel-ni yáholu mitshikawako rupnanatka Abel-ni.
Halixlu tshinanu Enoque tshinkaluru tenhohne ranikkatka hiwekatshriko hipuktshi hma kayaxyawakanupa. Hewi tshijne hi rukchijika klu tshinanu Hoyakalu kochtshekaplu tenhohne rawyawakapa. Wan-rixa Enoque klu tshinanu hmanikkonuklunuwa, rimathetka Hoyakalu hpoyikotjexyawaka.
Klu tshinanu halixlu minjeyma hike himukata poyikotletlu Hoyakalu. Seyni katukta haluka yanwakletlu Hoyakalu raluk-halixletlu rawa Hoyakalu. Hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu hijhatshine hkahwakan-koxluna renejikolna heneklewatatshri Hoyakalu.
Halixlu tshinanu Noé tshinkaluru jemlu jhamleru hinatshripa pirana Hoyakalu hinkajyalu. Hoyakalu tokanu hkahwakpiratatka Noé hiyáhoni tsro kanawa ralpokohnaputlu hhanunro hiyrunu hiwhenene riwekkajyawakapa. Xye pirana ptowruka romkahita Noé yahmaklu mapokatuwa pirana runkakka. Xye pirana romkahle tshinanu xye tshijne rukolukanuwnakakatka. Hiyrun-koxa Noé yoptotatkalu Hoyakalu potukatlewle halixlu tshinanu.
Abraão Hiyrunu Sara Halixle PiranapniKajnaklu mitshi Abraão, Hoyakalu towuxinri pa tshijne nwaka hyiywakapa, pa hohnepa wale tshijne renejikolupa. Ralixle tshinanu, wane hyatka hma metanutu tshijne nwaka.
Halixlu tshinanu runkaklexikolu tshijne rawjeta Abraão, hma metjejexyawakanu tshijne rawjeta. Pantshi nikalumta kamhikolupjikaka rawjeta Abraão, Isaque hiyrunu Jacó-yma. Wale tshijne yoptotatshinepa Abraão-yma Hoyakalu hinkajya pirana tshinanna.
Klu tshinanu Abraão hichinikanretakananreru poktshi hihlepokotkaluru mimat-nikawnakatu, Hoyakalu kamhaleru poktshi rukchijyawakapa.
Halixlu tshinan-koxa Sara yoptotlu tumukata michiwlexyawakapa whentshi tkayaxyawakapa yáholu tsrotsolejimkatkani seyni tmatuwhenetatka klu tshinanu talixatkalu hinkaklewatatshri himukatatshri koxni wale.
Hiyáhoni Abraão tsonu mwuhenetuko hipnahotkaluru tshinanu, yine mlejikananu hakanhiylu katahiri tenhohne hajene pejnu hiyrunu ksatuji mar powha wnahlu hajeru mpoyaho hitakyahokletkotu pejnu.
Nyi yinni ptowrunnika halixatshinni htshinikowaknina pirana metkanniko, hipnanatka. Seyni halikaka howuka tsonu rexyatkaluna runkaklexikolumkana mitshi. Rimathetluna halikaka pirana rixyawakatka, hmunanhatkaluna htshinikowakna pirana. Ruphujexnawana xye tshijne hajeru hma mixyawakanutkana seyni pa nerunekotkani. Hewi tshijne rawachakanatkalukonina.
Klu tshinanu xye pirana pixka tshinatshine rekhixnawana ruchinikanretler-potnina pa tshijneko.
Halikaka rawjekanaxyawakna tshijne ramotkamkana waneyamka pa katako rumukata satkapletanumkana.
Seyni hike, wanna halukatkalu pa tshijneko kihlewaka potuko, tenhohne hwatshri tshijne. Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu hi patewata Royakalutna htshinikowaka. Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu halpokohnaputna satu poktshi wanna tshinanupa.
Ralixle tshinanu mitshi, hyahotkoklunutka Abraão, hiwhene Isaque henekachalu hiylatkaluru rixakjixkoklunutka Abraão htshinikowaka pirana yoptotatshrini, hiwhene satupkalutu henekachalu hiylatkaluru hkamhiyamkatka.
Hiyrunu mitshi Hoyakalu wan-tshinru Abraão: “Piklopichanepa Isaque-nerune tshinkalunepa.”
Seyni Abraão munanhalu Hoyakalu himukatatshri riwekkajyawakaplu Isaque-ni yahmaklu rupninipa. Halikakni Isaque hipuktshi hiwekkajikaluru pixkalutu hyoptota Abraão. Yapkakluni wale.
Halixlu tshinanu Isaque mitshi kihlewaka htshinanwakatlu Jacó hiyrunu Esaú. Hinatshripa pirana runkaklexyana.
Halixlu tshinan-koxa rupnakastsitka mitshi Jacó kihlewaka htshinanwakatna José whenene hepi. Hyotmikleyma hkanojere ripoyehixnawa waneya wan-hixatshritka himalwutlu Hoyakalu.
Halixlu tshinanu José mitshi rupnakastsitka hkochtsheklu israel-nerune Egito tshijne ruchpajyawakapna pirana. Hiyrun-koxa ranikjixlu himanni hapu.
Moisés tsru rixinixka, ralixle tshinanu, hi ritshitlu Faraó hchitsho whene htshinikolupa.
Seyni hnurexnawa hsalewniywaka Hoyakalu nurreneyma. Hi ralukatkalu hektuntshi poyikowle phuta hi pchinhohnejijiko.
Cristo heyijikolu pixkalutu rukchikhihlenuta Moisés ptowru pohirewlu Egito tshijne hwatshri pnute. Wan-rixahchinikanuta Moisés klu tshinanu rapnutepa Hoyakalu henejyaplu hijhakalur-potu rikahwaka.
Halixlu tshinanu Egito tshijne ruknokatka Moisés mitshi. Hi hpiklu pohirtshi hahjiywaklu. Hi ruhrokatka seyni ptowruka rakotachata klu tshinanu Hoyakalu metkotu reta hihchinikanu.
Ralixle tshinanu Moisés kahwakpiratatkalu Páscoa hohne. Hrahtshi rutslaptahjekjixa, jejine mitshikananu matutatshine hiylatatshri, muylaxyawakanupna wanna koxa.
Halixlu tshinanu mar powha serolu hanikajite hyapna hatatjewa popri tshijiwaka yapatshine pixka rixna. Seyni egito-nerunnimka koxa yahot-yaplerewatni rahyekanatkana.
Hixolunni Halixatshinni PiranapniHalixlu tshinanu sete hohne pejnu hsajrurutka cerca tenolu sotlu kamhikolu tsru poktshi Jericó tshinikowaka cerca-te waneya hyawnatamatana.
Halixlu tshinanu kapoklewaklero Raabe tshinkaluro hi tupna malixkaneyma klu tshinanu kihle yoptole tixna tshiji hetapatshine.
Kluhe pnute numukata tshinretatka hixolune halixle pirana tshinanu? Hi kapapkolno xyekaka pirana nunkaklexyawakapa Gideão-ni pirana, Baraque-ni pirana, Sansão-ni pirana, Jefte-ni pirana, Davi-ni pirana, Samuel-ni pirana hiyrun-koxa pimrinni Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshinni pirana nunkaklexyawakapa.
Nyikaka halixle tshinanu pimrikaka tshijne pohirewaxyawaka yotkakka, Hoyakalu halujyawaka hkamhajekanatna hiyrunu Hoyakalu hinkaklexyana pirana hyoptotna halixlu tshinanu. Halixlu tshinanu ruchyanamatna mhenokane.
Tsru tshitshmero ruwakamtna hiyrunu rasukna hma muylaxikowakanupna yohlolewapiyma halixlu tshinanu. Hihrokatshinemkani seyni hixkolune pixka rixna. Hiylakaklu yehi himat-yahotkajikatshine pixka rixna hiyrunu pnu tshijne hichpajikatshine yahotkakatshine rakakna halixlu tshinanu.
Suxone ralixle tshinanna hiwuhenene hipnatshine hyoptotatnakna hiwekatshinetnaka. Pimrinni salewnakakkanna seyni wan-hixatshinni hi rujhaluna hipuktshi rasujyawakapna ralixlena tshinanu. Wan-rixna klu tshinanu hkahwakatkaluna riwejinritnakna xye riweklena pnute hihlenurutu.
Pimrinetnaka mturune hixkakka, hkotshipjetkatkana hiyrunu wane pnute rostutkana hiyrunu preso rutakkana.
Pimrineko sotlujetka, pimrinniko hanikaji mane serra-xikana hepi tshraji ruchpajyanatkana, pimrinniko yohlolewapiyma hiylatkana. Rawkoxna yanachalune carneiro-mta ho bode-mta tsonu hmakatna. Hike mwikanni, salewnatshinni, saletkalunni.
Xye tshijne hajene yohnik-hijhakalunemkanni. Seyni popriwaka yehi hiyrunu teno mrijiwak-yehi yapachatatshinni pupjetatshine pixkalune. Hitawakapnakaka hiyrunu kapnakaka hwajetatshinni.
Nyi ptowruneka Hoyakalu hikchikhihlenrenni ralixlena tshinanu seyni halikaka hi retlewamtanatkana Hoyakalu mitshi hinkaklexyanna.
Wan-rixa Hoyakalu klu tshinanu Hoyakalu hihlepokohnaprewata tsru hepixlewlu potuko hixa tshinanupa. Wumukata wannayma hike mmahaxikane hixletanu.
Hoyakalu Hirtshi Rixyawaka PiranapniHixa xye papko hiwekatshinetkawu wwiya hixolune potniko hiphujtatatshinni, wsajrukjenni. Hiyáhoni waluk-hicholetanru ptowruko hektuntshi hinolu pixkalutu wimaletjeru. Hiyrun-koxa ptowru hixatshri hektuntshi wkachpotutjeru werutanu honuka, waneya hasuklu kamhatshri pixka wixa hasuklemtanu mkojwakahchinikanuxikanepwu wasukachatanu xye hasuklu Hoyakalu henejyawu pixkalutu.
Jesus yehi potuko yihatatshinepwu klu tshinanu Jesus walixle yinuwakatshrini hiyrunu walixle poyahokakatshrini. Poyikpotuklu Jesus hinamtatshripa tshinanu. Cruz rupniywakapa rakotachata. Hektuwaka htshinanwakaxikolu reyikachata. Xawakni htuplatatka. Hoyakalu hetamayxaklerewatatshri tuplaxyawaka potukle sreta htuplatatka.
Hichinikanretanru hi pa salewaktshikananu hyoptota Jesus hiyrunu hi pa hahkalukananu rixluna malixkane seyni rakotlu. Hiyáhoni hix-koxa hi kaheknanuwatanu hi hma mernuwatanu.
Wuru Hoyakalu Ramotle Tshinanna Hiwhenene Cristo Halixatshine Rapnokatjexyawakna PiranapniKlu tshinanu hektuntshi kamnixikolu pirana hi hixako hihraha hkochpakatka hektuntshi hkamnixyawakapa.
Hiyáhola hamtakatkalu hijrexikolu pirana whentshine hijrexikolu pixkalutu wla tshinatshri: “Noturu, hi peyikanru Tsru Hixikatshriwa salexyayi hiyrun-koxa hi puhrokahchinikanutanu retjexya tshinanyi.
Klu tshinanu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu saletna ptowruneka ramotanune hiyrunu hkotshipjetna ptowruneka hwuhenene rutakanune.”
Hakotachatanru ptowru salewaktshi hix-yehi hapokatshri. Hiwhenene pixka rixhi Hoyakalu. Klu tshinanu hanurnihe whentshi ruru msaletanutu?
Seyni hma saletkonuklunu ptowru whentshi hihlenu salexikolu pixka, waneklu hi whentshine hihlenpothi.
Klu tshinanu wuru saletkoxwu seyni wanepnawaka wkahwakpiratatkalu. Hiyáhoni wane yohnik-wixa yijnak-tokanretanru Wuru Hoyakalu hiwejikalune kamhatshri, wiwejyawakapa.
Klu tshinanu wuru pchinhohnejiji hsaletwu raluk-hixlexyawaka pixka rixkajyawakapwu. Seyni Hoyakalu saletwu repixyawakapwu kihleruya, Hoyakalu hihlenu potukalu yehi wtsaklawniywakapa.
Halikaka hikeni salewaktshi poyikomenuru klu tshinanu katshinru. Seyni wanepnawaka repixna kihle hwachle rixyawakna hiyrunu hiweklu potukalu, saletlewlu tshinanutka.
Hiyáhoni xawakni hmixkotanru himyonota hihrokakanatatshri hiyrunu hisoji hihrokakanatatshri hmixkotanutka.
Cristo Halixatshine Hijrexikolu PiranapniHijhapotutanru kihle hwachle rixyawakapna ptowrunek-yine. Potukalunephi ptowru potuko tshinanuya. Klu tshinanu wane hmixkanuklunupa hi satuknako yineru Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hetanu.
Xako, hi satukna hicho homkahretanru Hoyakalu hihlenu wuhletjeru. Klu tshinanu wma momkahitkanuklunru rumukata hakanhaletanu hixa hitokoteya katshwu hchinikan-menu hixa kojwakatshripa, hixolunepnimka yinepni himtukahchinikanutatshripa.
Hi rawanu kapoklewakleru. Hix-yehi hi rawanu Esaú pixkalutu, Hoyakalu hikchikhihlenreru pirana heyikatshri. Esaú honukla pa niklupka ripekotlu mitshikananu matutatshri rixle pirana.
Hixa himatlu hanu rixa mitshi Esaú rali hichankalexinixkalu mitshikananu matutatshri rixle pirana waneya wane wkatanu raluka yoptoletmaklu kihlewaka htshinikolumka seyni hiknokalurutkani Esaú. Klu tshinanu hi rumukata hihlerewletanatka hkamhaleru yáholu hiktehaymamka rujhalewatnixka.
Hepi Mriji Yapkakle PiranapniHixa hi israel-nerune hinre pixka hixa Sinai tshinkaluru mriji poyaho kamrukletkaluru nwaka hyinna pixka, hi hix-hixa. Tsru tshitshmero halhatshri yehi, mapchahawaka, rutlohle yehi.
Kowi hima, tokantshi hima, hjeminixkana hi wane yohnik-rixakjixatkaluna tokantshi.
Klu tshinanu hi rumukata hakotletatkaluna tokantshi, yokanatkaluru tokantshi wla tshinatshri: “Niktshine yotnekamrijixiniplu hsotlujetkona ho katshraluyma runokakna.”
Tsru piklu potuko retna yine wale hetatshine haté Moisés koxa wla htshinatka: “Npikpotuta. Nutataka.”
Seyni hixa Sião tshinkaluru mrijiko hapokatka hiyrunu Hoyakalu hiwekatshri poktshiko Jerusalém tshinikowaka tenhohne hwatshri poktshi hapokatka hixa. Hiyrunu hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrene tenhohne hajene hixolune potu yehi hapokatka.
Hixa hapokanwakatlu poyikowlu hapatjexikowaka Hoyakalu whenene tsrujrune hapatjere nwaka, tenhohne khiwakayalune yehi. Hoyakalu, ptowru yineru hetamayxakletatshri yehi hapokatshinhi hiyrunu yine hiwejikalune potukalune, hike mmahaxikane yehi, hapokatshinhi.
Jesus herotu runkakletlewaxya poyahokakatshri yehi hapokatshinhi. Hrahtshi hitslaptahjetkaluru hektuntshi hiknokawaka yehi hapokatshinhi. Seyni Abel-ni hipnale hapnute hixa wane yohnik-kihlewaka yehi hapokatshinetkahi.
Hiyáhoni xawakni hislahinwa hmuknojyawakanuplu yanumatatshri tokanu. Klu tshinanu xye tshijne hajene hijretatshine tokanu hiknokatshine hi rasujyatkaluna rapnokaxikolna, ha wane yohnik-potu wixko hixa, tenhohne hajeru hijretlewle wkatjixini.
Waneklu papko Hoyakalu plama hiyolikkaklu tshiji. Seyni xawakni runkaklexyawu, wla htshinatka: “Xekat-patka nuyolikkakanutkalu tshiji. Seyni hi tshiji tsonu seyni tenhohne koxa.”
“Xekat-patka” htshinini rekhipotutlu ptowru kamhakalurkaka hiwchokko, rimathexikolupa muwchokkotni wale rawhohnekanaxyawakapni.
Hoyakalu wimalwutanu klu tshinanu pohirewaxikowaka muwchokkotu yoptotatshinetkawu. Poyahnuwatatshinepwu hiyrunu Hoyakalu himalwujetatshinepwu Hoyakalu halukleru pixka hixatshinepwu, Hoyakalu kahwakpiratatshinepwu tsru pikluyma.
Klu tshinanu halikakni Woyakalute tshitshmero nikatlewaxikatshrini.
Cristo Halixatshine Kamrure PiranapniHi hituk-hichiniklekakanu seyni Cristo moletanune pixka hixa hichiniklekakanu.
Hi hichochatanunna hma metjejetanunni yanachalune, hipji hitakanunna. Klu tshinanu haté satkaka hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrene tenhohne hajene hipji hitukkakatka hma metjejetanunekmaka.
Hichinikanna kachitkalune. Wannayma kachitkalune pixka hixahoxinwa. Hichinikanna salewnatshine klu tshinanu hix-koxa honra kamanerunhi.
Ptowruneka hetanu hnunrowlu kihleruni, meyikotni. Hi hma hnunrotanuto, hi hma hnurutanutu hapokletanu. Klu tshinanu hektutu kamhatshine hiyrunu hapoklewatatshine rukolujinwana Hoyakalu hetanu.
Hi tiyiro halukpotukanatatshinephi. Kihle hchinikanurunephi hejnu himwaleru tshinanu. Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu wla htshina: “Hikeklu nuchotanhi hikeklu nuknokanhi.”
Hiyáhoni kihle hchinikanurunwu wumukata wla tshinreta, hike wpikanu: “Nepixjerni Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu, hiyáhoni hi npikanu hanuktako rixinipno yineru.”
Hi Wuchotanu Kihleru Wkamhajexyawaka Hiyrunu Wepixkajyawaka PiranapniHichinikanna mitshikananu hkosekjene Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakjene. Ralixlena homkahitanu hiyrunu hetjepotutanru rixjexyawakna kamle.
Jesus Cristo rixhohnekanaxyawakni hiknohatshri hohneni, xawakni hohne hiyrunu hinatshri hohnepa mnikawnakatupa.
Hi pupjekakkalunephi ptowru hasruklewlu pejnu wma masrujyahi tshinanu. Halikakni hixa kihleylu wihchinikanu mixkoxikowaka ptowru hihlentshi Hoyakalu henekachaleyma. Hi hkahwakpiratanru nikkalurkaka hiykoyehitkaluru klu tshinanu hi repixna yine xyekaka pirana homkahitatshine.
Sacerdote-ne judeu-ne Hoyakalupji kamrurewaxikatshine hi ritshitkana hnijyawakapluna henekachalu hiylatkaluru hixa henejyana kapajir-hoho hiylaxikalurni.
Judeu-ne tsru sacerdote-te hanikjetlu nikalu hraha Hoyakalu tsonu hwiywaka yehi, henekachlu rixikowakapa hektuntshi hwenuxyawakapa tshinanu. Seyni poktshi kahnete hyoxikmanexikana nikalni.
Wale tshinan-koxa poktshi hiphaptote hichpakawaka sreta kahnete rupniyatka Jesus. Wan-rixa hpowraxyawakapna yine waleko hihrahayma.
Hiyáhoni xawakni wyanwakatanru Jesus poktshi malekateya. Jesus malujikowakanu pirana pixkalutu yoptotatshinepwu hix-koxa.
