Salewnalu hakotachatatshine kihle hchinikanurune wkahwakna wan-hixatshine. Hixa jemlu Jó tshinkaluru hakotachale pirana hiyrunu hetlu hsalewnale hali hiknohlexinixka Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hepixpotutatkalu. Hoyakalu honra kchinikanur-potni, jetwamonukleru potni.
Hanjihohneru Himukatatshri Potuko PiranapniCristo tshinanu nmoletanune hislahpotuxinwa hi tshinachatatshinephi, hi Hoyakalu hiwaka hkochtshekachatanu. Hi tenhohne hkochtshekanu, hi tshijiko hkochtshekanu, hi kluneru hiwakaymaktako htshinachatanu. Seyni hehe htshininipa, hi pnute pujhanru ptokanu mixkotatshripa. Hike htshininpatka, hike pnute pujhanu hiyrunuko. Wan-hixanu hma mukolujnawakanupwa.
Satu hixa salewnini, ranjihohnetanu. Satu hixa poyikowaxini, himalwuru hchikaletanu.
Satu hixa hyeyixini, Cristo halixatshine kosekatshine repukanu ranjihohnetanna wale tshinanu. Nhihtshiha hijiw-hoho ruyokanna Tsru Hixikatshriwa Cristo hiwaka tshinanu.
Hanjihohneru Hoyakalu munanhaleru, hitskalakanru yeyixatshri. Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hitskalakanru. Hiyrun-koxa majnakowatatshri rixini ruknokahchinikanyehitko rektunuya.
Hiphujetkajinwa hmayxaklekaka. Wan-hixatshinhi hanjihohneyehikakanu hitskalhinripa. Yineru potuka hchinikanuru hanjihohnere himukatatshri potukni.
Hetanru Elias tshinkaluru. Yinerukananni hixa yinwu pixka. Seyni hi rutuk-hanjihohnereta. Hoyakalu ranjijeta hina hmixyawakanupa hiyáhoni mapa mhale hanikaji mhale pejnu hi rinnewata tshij-hoho ranjire tshinanu.
Waneya ranjihohnetatnaka rinnewatatka. Hiyáhoni tshiji ruptshejyatnaka hitaklukaka.
Cristo tshinanu nmoletanune, satu yineru halikakalutu tokantshi hpupjexini, waneya satu satkajinri,
himatanru xye, katukta satkajinri majnakowatatshri halikak-potuko hatnu hapo nwaka hsatokanutnaka, hatnu hapo pupjeyehitatshri riwekle riwekkakanu hiyrunu rektunu hix-potuko hamtakahchinikanyehixyalu.
Hoyakalu nurrenhi waleko ralujyawaka tshinanu, Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru yineru powratatshri tshinanu, hyijnakoxyawakaplu Jesus Cristo halujyawaka, hpolhohoxikolupa wale hrahaya. Hoyakalu hepixle yoptotatshinephi hiyrun-koxa kihle hwachalu hwapotutatshinephi.
Wpoyahnutlu Hoyakalu Riwekkaklewle TshinanuWpoyahnutanru Wutsrukate Jesus Cristo Hiru, Royakalute. Herotu matuxikolu renekwu hiweklu wkahwajyawakapa Jesus Cristo hiwejinixnaka hipuktshiya tshinanu. Hoyakalu hetwamonre tsru potuko tshinanu.
Hoyakalu heneklewle yoptotatshinephi. Mnikawnakatupni wyoptotanru, meyikotni, mimat-himtuwnakatupni, rimretka tenhohneya hixa tshinanupa.
Hislahkalunhi Hoyakalu himukatleyma halixlu tshinanu, hiweklu hkayaxyawaka. Rekhipotuxikolupa hiweklu, hnikawnahohnexinpatka h-marca-xikolu.
Xyemka poyikothi seyni xawakni halikaka hwamonuwata xye hohne pchinjiji, ptowru hixatshri yahtaletlu hkojwakjeru tshinanu.
Seyni hsalewna, halixle hyahoxika, rimathexikowakapa ho halikaklahe halixlu ho hike. Ouro koxa moyakatu, rixirikka tshitshipawayma, waneko pixka rixko halixlu halukkaluru potuko, tshitshipawa pixkalutuyma hyahoxika. Wan-rixko yineru halixle rumukata himalwuretko, ruphujetko walixle, htserpiranatko walixle Jesus Cristo hapojinri klu papko.
Hma metanutni wale seyni hichinikanru. Hi hetanru xawakni seyni halixlu. Wan-hixatshinhi seyni himuwatatshinhi tokantshi mpoyaho hinkakletletkotuyma himuwjeta, tsru ruphujexikolu tshinanu.
Halixle waleni hiweklu heneklewatatshri klu tshinanu hsamenru hiwekkakka.
Wale hiwekkaklewatatshri piranakni. Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine mitshikawlune honra ruchtotapotutluna hiyrunu rujha himatjemletluna mapokatuwa pirana runkakletlerna pirana, klu pixkalutnihe xye halukkaluru hixa nwaka hapokatshripa.
Rujha himatjemletluna kluneru piranni xye hiyrunu rujha himatletluna hiklu rakanhanu xye pirana. Klu tshinanu Cristo Hiwejikaluru mitshi wanna hitokote hwatshri runkakna mitshi Cristo mapokatuwa pirana, Cristo saletle hinatshripa pirana hiyrunu hsaletle wane pnutepa ruphujexikolupa pirana.
Hoyakalu mitshi himatjemkakatkana, hi wannako tshinanupni xye pirana seyni hixa tshinanupni. Xyekaka pirana runkaklena hixa tshinanu, xawakni hinkakka kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana jinkakletakleruneya Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru, tenhohne hichpajikatshri hepixleyma. Haté hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrerune tenhohne hajene hijha himatletlu klunerni xyekaka pirana.
Hoyakalu Haluklu Potukalune Wixyawakapa PiranapniHiyáhoni xawakni hihchinikanu halpokotanu. Hiyokahchinikanutatshinephi. Hoyakalu hihlenu kahwakatshinephi haté nikawnahohnexinipa. Xye henekko Jesus hiphujewnini hohnepa.
Mturune kajnakolune pixkalunephi. Hi hyimanru mitshikawluru het-sotanruru hmahchinikanuklunuwa papko pixka.
Halikaka ptowru potuko hixjexyawaka potukalunephi, htshanixjeru Hoyakalu potukalu rixyawaka pixka.
Klu tshinanu wla htshina Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru: Potukalunephi klu tshinanu Potukalno hita.
Wuru Hoyakalu hiwaka hmunanhini, yinecha mkahwakpiratkatu, ptowru yineru kamhanru hetatshrini tshinanu, xye tshij-hoho hwaka pchinika hkahwakpiratanru Hoyakalu ptowru tshinanuya.
Klu tshinanu himatlu hitsrukatenni hasrujikolu hike mkochpakkatni womkahjekanatanru pirana, hi prata hi ouro himat-nikawnatshri wenru tshinanu wiwekkaka.
Seyni hanjitka Cristo hrahaya, kwenur-potuko. Carneiro whene psojikna hektuntshi machretu pixkalutni Cristo.
Hoyakalu nurehchinikanutlu wan-rixyawaka Cristo xye tshijne hma mkamhaknuklunuwa. Seyni xawakni rakanhakakatkalu Cristo, nikawnahohnepiraxinistsi potuko ramotle tshinanhi.
Wale tshinanu Hoyakalu halixa, Cristo hiwekkakjeru hipuktshiya hiyrunu Cristo hiphujetjeru. Wan-rixa kahwakachalu hiyrunu halixlu Hoyakalu yehi yoptoxikalurupa.
Hamotlu Halikakalutu PiranapniHiyáhoni xawakni halikaka tokanu homkahlu tshinanu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hepixle tshinanu hpowratahchinikanuxnawa hpoyaho hichinikanretletna hmoletanune Cristo tshinanu ptowru hamotluya. Hiyáhoni hichinikkakanu. Hi hixachatatshinephi seyni hihchinikanu psolukayma hichinikkakanu.
Himepe matletatshinhi, hi himat-nikawnatshri matuxikatshinhi halikaka mimat-nikawnakatu matkakatkahi. Hoyakalu tokanni wale, hiwekatshri hike rixiniko mnikawnakatu.
“Klu tshinanu ptowru yineru peklo pixka hixatshrini. Hiyrun-koxa ptowru hixatshri yineru hihlenu kchana hwu pixkalutni. Peklo hiprihachata hiyrun-koxa kchana hwu hijrukachata.
Seyni Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu tokanu rawahohnekanatanu.” Xye tokantshi hinkakletkaluru tokanu hix-yehi, kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana.
Sotlu Hiwekatshine Pixkalune PiranapniHiyáhoni xawakni ptowru hixatshri hahnantshi, ptowru yokwijrewlu, ptowru hixachatatshri, ptowru sotanuhonutshi, tokantshi ptowru hixatshriko hiknokanu.
Hematlune pixka tnutsh-ha hepixlewatatshri hijhapotutatshine, Hoyakalu tokanu wiwejinri hepixatshri hijhapotutanu htseruwniywakapa.
Hiyáhoni xawakni Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hepixle tshinanwu himathetatshinetkahi.
Hiyáhoni wyanwakatanru hatatjewa sotlu hiwejikaluru wapokanwakatanu. Halikaka malukkotumkani yineya seyni Hoyakalu nurrerni wale hiyrunu hijhakalur-potni wale.
Hix-koxa sotlu hiwekatshine pixkalunhi. Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru panathi. Sacerdote-nhi Hoyakalu kotspalenhi, henekachalurkaka henekjetatshinephi Hoyakalu tshinanupa, Hoyakalu halukanru Jesus Cristo tshinanuya.
Hiyáhoni hijhakalur-potni wale sotlu hixa halixatshinhi tshinanu. Seyni malixkane tshinanu: “Kpanawaklerune malukkotu rikahwakluna sotlu seyni hepixlewatatshri potukni, psolupjiko poyehitatshrini wale.”
“Sotlu hitspetkalurukni wale, kojwakahchinikanrewatatshri Hoyakalu tokanu hitspexikatshineya klu tshinanu hmajnakowjetna. Hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu haluklu wan-rixikowakapna wan-hixatshine malixkane.
Seyni hixa halixatshinhi Hoyakalu nurrenhi, hineruneko hixyawakapa, Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu sacerdote-tenhi, yine potukalunetkahi, Hoyakalunuko hixyawakapa. Hoyakalu nuretatkahi hiphujexyawakaplu rixa hihlehchinikanrexyawakhi, mapchahawaka hichpajyawakapa, wale nwaka katawak-potuko nwaka wwiywakapa htshanixikowaka.
Mitshikananu hi Hoyakalu hayinetenhi seyni xawakni Hoyakalunerunetkahi. Mitshikananu hixa hi himathetatkalu Hoyakalu hetwamonre hanu rixa seyni xawakni Hoyakalu hetwamonre yoptotatshinhi.
Cristo Halixatshine Hixa Hiweklexyawakapa PiranapniNuchinikanune potu, hixa hi hewi tshijne hajenekhi hiyrunu hi xye tshijne hitukatshinhi hiyáhoni nanjipotuthi hasujinri hektuntshi mantshi halukanru, yineru hiwekle kamnitatshri.
Yine malixkane hetanu, potuka hiweklerunephi. Yáholu hektutu kamhatshine htshinjetanhi seyni kihleru hkamhaleru tshinanu wanna yehi hkamhajexinri tshinanu, Hoyakalu hapojinri hohnepa rimalwutanruna.
Hyijnakotanru ptowru tokantshi htowuxikolu pirana, yine towuxikolu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Cristo homkahlu tshinanu, towutatshri ho tsru phuru, ptowru yokanatatshriko,
ho tsrukakalunecha rixinna, hyijnakotanna. Klu tshinanu pohirtshine rutakkana wanna, hektutu kamhatshine rapnokaxyawakapna hiyrunu kihleru kamhatshine rimalwuxyawakapna.
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu haluklu wan-hixikowaka. Waneya wan-hixatshinhi, kihleru hkamhaleru tshinanu wanna mchinikanune hike mimatkane tokanu hitshrokkakanu.
Mimaletkonhi seyni hi hektutu hetachatkalunephi mimaletkone hixyawaka tshinanu seyni halikaka Hoyakalu towutlene pixka hixinwa.
Ptowru yineru hkahwakpiratanu. Moletkakatshine Cristo tshinanu hichinikanu. Hoyakalu hpikanu. Towutatshri hkahwakpiratanu.
Halixatshri Cristo Yapkakle Rixyawaka PiranapniTowretshine hyijnakotanna htowutjene ptowru kahwakpirluyma. Hi htowutjene kchinikanurune tsonu hyijnakotanu seyni wanna htowutjene mpotukane koxa hyijnakotanu.
Klu tshinanu kihle hchinikanru Hoyakalu satu yineru Hoyakalu ruchinikanretle tshinanu hsalewniywaka, hike mkamhakatuko saletkoklunu.
Yineru hsalewnini hmajnákonu tshinanu, rakotachaxiniphutlu hanhe rixa hepixletanru? Halikaka Hoyakalu hikchikhihlenutlu kihle hchinikanurune hixyawaka hsalewnini, yáholu kihleru hkamhaleru tshinanu hsalewnini.
Klu tshinanu xyekni htshanixikolu. Cristo hixyawaka pixka, hsalewna hixa tshinanu. Hiyáhoni xye chinikantshi rekhitwu, womkahixyawakaplu.
Cristo hikeklu hektuwatatka. Hiyrun-koxa hi satukna tokantshi yokwirewatatshri hichpaknamaxyalu.
Hektutu htshinatkaluna seyni hi ruhitatka. Hsalewninimkatka seyni hi rujha hapnuretna. Seyni halikaka Hoyakalu, hetamayxaklerewatatshri potukalu hmunanhatka.
Cristo, waleko himaneya hahmuna skita hoho ranikhektunutwu. Hipnatshine pixka wixyawakapa hektuntshi tshinanu seyni halikaka wiwekanu kihleru wkamhiywakapa. Wuhletkatka Cristo kotshipjexikolu tshinanuya.
Klu tshinanu carneiro-ne pupjetatshine pixka wixakanata. Seyni xawakni carneiro hislahatshri pixkalutu, yineru hiwejinri towutatshriko nwaka wsatkakkatka.
Raluk-hixlexikowaka Jeji, Hhanunroyma PiranapniHiyáhoni hixa suxonhi waneko pixka haluk-hixletna hhanurune, hyijnakotanru satkaka hixako hhanuru. Waneyakni satu hnurtshi, hmalixkanuklunru Hoyakalu tokanu, ralixkakka hhanunro hixjexyawaka tshinanu. Hi tunkakle tshinanni.
Ralixkakna jejine rexinipna hhanunrona Hoyakalu kahwakpiraxikolu potuka kamhale rixinipna suxone.
Suxone makawhihlenuxyawaka hi himanna hihlexikolni, hi kamapjiwutsluyma, hi ouro kamhikaluruymako, hi mkatshriymako.
Seyni tohchinikanu, wala hitokote hwatshri metkotu hihlexikolu, mimat-hitsruhkatni. Xye chinikantshi tuhlexinwa, jimatleropni, hwachatatshropni. Wla hixatshri hchinikanu halukkaluru potuko Hoyakalu hetanuya.
Klu tshinanu waneko pixka rixa hihlerexnanwana potukalonni suxonni Hoyakalunni mitshikawlonni, Hoyakalu munanhatshinni. Hyijnakotatkana wannako hhanurna.
Sara-ni pixka, tyijnakotlu Abraão-ni. Tutsrukate ttshinru Abraão-ni. Hixa suxonhi wanna pixkalunetkahi, kihleru hkamhini, hma pijyawakanupa, hma mimyejyawakanupa.
Waneko pixka hixanu hixa hnurtshine, himwahihlenutana hhanunrone himatjemluyma. Halukkalone pixka hixanna suxone. Himatna kayaho mixkonutna wanna himaneyna. Hiweklu Hoyakalu henekachaxyana yoptotatshinepa jeji, hhanunroyma tshinanu, wan-hixanu hanjihohnere hma mimalexikowakanupa Hoyakaluya.
Kihle Hiwekle Menu Halukatshine PiranapniHiyáhoni xawakni ptowrunekhi pa hchinikanurunephi. Hetwamonkakanu. Hichinikkakanu moletkakatshine pixka. Kchinikanurunephi. Himatletkakatshinephi, mayohonephi.
Hi hektutuyma papnutanru hektutu pkamhikjeru. Hiyrun-koxa hi yanhakluyma papnutanru yanhaklu. Seyni halikaka kihlewaka hanjiyehitanna. Klu tshinanu himatanru htshanixkoklunu, htshanixka kihlewaka hyoptoxyawakapa.
Hiyáhoni katuktako hamotlu kihle hiwekle menu hiyrunu rujhinri hix-hohne kihleru rexyawaka, rujhalu ruslahanruxyawaka, hektutu hma tshinyawakanu hiyrunu hinama ruslahanu yokwijru hma tshinyawakanupa.
Klu tshinanu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hetjetna potuka kamrurerune hiyrunu hyijnakjetlu ranjihohnerna. Seyni Hoyakalu kamnitna hektutu kamhatshine.
Salewaktshi Kihleru Kamhikolu Tshinanu PiranapniHiyáhoni hanurnihe kihleru kamhatshri himtukatshri?
Seyni hsalewnini kihleru hkamhaleru tshinanu, hpoyikowatanu. Wanna hamlenu hi hpikanu. Hiyrunu hi hkojwakahchinikanutanu wanna tshinanu.
Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu pixkalunephi ptowru chinikantshiya. Ptowru mayohnutshi hiyrunu ptowru kahwakpirlu chinikantshiyma halpokotanu hinkaklexyawakaplu hixa himwaleru hmunanhaleru pirana ptowru yine hepomhakjene tshinanu.
Homkahitanru powra hchinikan-menu waneyakni pimrine hektuwaka htshinanwakaxiniphi hiyrunu hektu kamhatshine hkahwakkoklunu, seyni kihleru hkamhaleru Cristo tshinanni, hpatewatanhonukna hjihyehichatjene.
Seyni Hoyakalu halujiniplu hsalewniywaka hixa, kihle potlu hsalewnanu kihleru hkamhaleru tshinanu. Seyni hi kihleru hektutu hkamhale tshinanu hsalexikowaka.
Klu tshinanu pa katapka Cristo koxa salewnatka hektuntshi tshinanu. Hiyáhoni kihleru kamhatshri salewnatka hektutu kamhatshri tshinanupa. Wan-rixa Cristo ranijyawakapwu Hoyakalu nwaka. Waneyakni Cristo ruylaxikolu himane tsonu seyni riwejinri hiwekkakhonuklu.
Xye riwekkakjer-honuka himukatle tshinan-koxa samentshi kachitkalurkaka nwaka hyatka Cristo. Wane runkaklewyehixyana samentshine kachitkalune.
Wannani mitshikawlunni, hektuwaka kamhatshinni, Noé-ni klu papko hiwekatshinekananni. Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu mchiretannutni hkahwakachatmaka tsro kanawa kamhako pchinika. Waneklu papko hi hixo yine hiwekkaka. Oito yine tsonu hiwekkaka hahyekachalu tshinanuya.
Xye pirana batiz-lu yaholuni. Xawakni wale koxa hiwekkakwu. Hi mantshi himtuklewatatshri hiknojikolu hiwekkakwu seyni Jesus Cristo hipuktshi hichpajikatshri hiwekkakwu. Ruphujetlu potuka chinikanurunwu Hoyakalu hetanuya.
Jesus Cristo tenhohne yatshritka. Hoyakalu potukle sreta htuplata. Wane rutakka hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrene tenhohne hajene htowuxyawaka, tsru towutatshine tenhohne hajene hiyrunu tenhohne himukatle koxa htowutatka.
Cristo Halixatshine Salewnajexyawaka PiranapniCristo salewniywaka himaneya hixa tshinanu. Wale tshinanu halpokoxinwa xye pixkalutu chinikantshiyma. Klu tshinanu hix-mane saletkoklunu hektuntshi ruchokaka.
Hiyáhoni xawakni wan-hixatshri yineru hi hijhalu himane het-sotanrewle romkahixyawaka, yineru hikchikhihlenrerumka hi romkahitanu. Seyni Hoyakalu hikchikhihlenreru rujha homkahreta riwekka pchinika.
Klu tshinanu wiwekle hiknohatshritka tshinanu wpoyahokakatkalu ptowru potuka malixkane halukanru. Waneklu papko womkahikanatlu hapoklewlu, mantshi het-sotanrewle, himru, hahsalu, tsru niklu hiyrunu hoyakalu minjene himtuklewatatshine kahwakpirlu womkahjekanatatka.
Hiyahokni wanna malixkane himyekatka tsru poyikowlu phuta hkamhaluna hixa hi hapaka wane hwajeta. Hiyáhoni hektutu htshinanwakjethina.
Wanna nanwaka hinkaklexinwa Hoyakalu hepomhinipna, ptowru yineru ho hiwekatshri ho hipnatshri mayxakle halpokohnaputatshri.
Wale tshinanu kihle piranalu potuko, hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana hipnatshine koxa runkakka. Wan-rixkana rukolujikowakapna yinni himaneymana seyni riwejinri riwejinna Hoyakalu tshinanu.
Hichinikkaklu Hixo Hektutu Himaletatshri PiranapniSeyni hi howukatkalu ptowru potuko nikawniywakapa. Hiyáhoni wale tshinanu kahchinikanurunephi, hislahatshinephi hanjihohneru tshinanuya.
Seyni halikaka xye ptowruka yohnik-hijhakalurni hichinikajyawaka. Klu tshinanu hichiniklewlu hixo hektuntshi hitukkakatshrini wale.
Yanamtatshine hapojini kihle yoptole hixanna. Muhjekakkanephi hapokatshine tshinanu.
Ptowru yineru Hoyakalu henekachale yoptotatshritka. Hiyáhoni wale tshinanu hepixkakanu hixa satkakhi henejikolu hyoptotanrutkaymako. Wan-hixjetatka klu tshinanu Hoyakalu henekachale hijhakalur-potuko hislahatshinetkahi.
Satu yineru hinkaklewaxinipa, Hoyakalu tshinyawaka pixka htshinanu. Pimrine repixjexini satu, himatkaltshi Hoyakalu henejyaluyma repixanna. Hoyakalu himalwuxikolupa ptowru potuko tshinanu, Jesus Cristo tshinanuya. Hoyakalu hiphujexikolni, towutatshrini hike rixiniko mnikawnakatupa. Amém.
Kihle Hchinikanuplu Cristo Tshinanu Salewnatshri PiranapniNuchinikanune, hi himyekanu yahtaletlewlu chikolu hapokyehixiniphi, hyahtalexyawakaphi. Hi himyekanu wale pixkalutu yahtaletlewlu hapyehixiniphi.
Seyni hpoyikowatanu, klu tshinanu Cristo salewnale pixka hixa saletletkalunhi. Hiyáhoni Cristo hoyaknu hiphujexikolupa hix-koxa himwapotutanu, tsru himuwluyma potuko.
Cristo hiwaka tshinanu heyikkoklunu, himuwatatshinephi. Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hiyrunu royaknu hix-yehi rawatka.
Hiyahokni hapnokatkoklunu hi hiylalewlu, hi tshowhuwlu, hi hektutu hkamhale tshinanni hi pimrine hyotnexyawaka tshinanu rapnokatka.
