Jesus Hapojinripa PiranapniNuchinikanune, xyekni hepi rixinri yonawahlo hixa nwaka nyokanrero. Nyi hepi yonawahlo tshinanu naluka komyekahchinikanrethi hihchinikanu kihleru, potukalu, xyekaka pirana hichinkapyawakapa.
Tokantshi mitshikawluru, Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine, Hoyakalu nurrene tokanu hichinikanu hiyrun-koxa hixa Wutsrukate Jesus Wiwekkakjeru nurrenwu, tokanu hijretle hichinikanu.
Wla htshinanna heyikatshine: Ha Cristo hapojinri hohnepa runkakletleru, hi hetko rapokanu. Klu tshinanu wutsrukatenni hipninri hohneni haté xawakni hi psojikna yokmanatka. Ptowru potuko rixannukni xye tshiji hiyakoxikolu klu haté xawakni.
Seyni hi rujha himatletluna mitshikawa Hoyakalu hiyakoleru tenhohne hiyrunu tshiji htokanu tsonu tshinanu. Psoji tshiji hitokha rutaka hiyrun-koxa psoji tshiji honha malekate rutaka, htokanu tshinanu tsonu.
Xye tshiji mitshikawako hiyakotkaluru nikawnatka honha hichyatapyawaklu tshinanu.
Seyni xawakni tshiji, tenhohne, xye papko hwatshriwa, himretkalurni wale himako tokantshi himukatle tshinanutnaka hnikatko tshiji tshitshmeroyma. Ruslahka tshiji haté rapokhohnexinipa, Hoyakalu malukkane, hapnokaxikolu hohnepa hnikatkonna yinepni.
Nuchinikanune, hi mimatkane pixka hixanu. Seyni himatanu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakaluya satu hohne hatatjewa mil mhale pejnu rixahotlu hiyrun-koxa mil mhale pejnu pa hohnepka rikahwaklu Hoyakalu.
Satkaka yineru kahwaklu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu hi haluka kamhaletatkalu htshinyawaka pixka. Seyni hike. Kchinikanurni wale. Klu tshinanu hi raluklu ramhiywakamkapa yineru hi satuknako, seyni walemka haluklu ptowru yineru rehchinikanuxyawakapa.
Klu tshinanu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Cristo hininri hohnepa hapokanu, katshowhuru hapokle pixka rixa hapokletanu. Waneklu papkopa tenhohne herutkotka tsru sejirtshiymapa. Xye hohne hikamrurewleru hiprahkanu tsru hameru tshinanu. Xye tshiji hiyrun-koxa ptowru kamhakaluru, xye tshiji hwatshri, nikawnanu.
Xye ptowruka, tshiji hwatshri, tenhohne hwatshri koxa nikawnanu hiyáhoni hi he rekhithi hanu hixahchinikanutatshine haluk-hixletanu chinikantshi potukawaka pirana tshinanu hiyrunu Hoyakalu homkahlu pirana tshinanu?
Hoyakalu hohnepa kahwakkalunephi hiyrunu wale hohne hapokatshripa halukpotutatshinephi. Wale hohnepa tenhohne halhanu, ramhanu. Xye hohne hikamrurewleru hiprahkanu tsru hameru tshinanu.
Seyni hix-yinwu, Hoyakalu tshinyawakatka tshinanu, tenhohne herotexikolu hiyrunu tshiji herotexikolu wkahwakanu. Wane rawanu potuknutshi tsonu.
Cristo Hapojinri Kahwakatshinepwu PiranapniHiyáhoni nuchinikanune, xyekaka hapokatshripa kahwakatshine tshinanu jmererunephi. Kihlehchinikanurunephi Cristo-ya, hi psojikna hektuntshiyma hikchikko, hike mixkanephi.
