Kamtshi Hallirixikolu PiranapniMturune pixkalune, nyonanwakathi klu tshinanu hektunu hiknojikatka Jesus Cristo hiwaka tshinanu.
Nyonanwakathi, tsrune pixkalune klu tshinanu hixa himathetlu hyinuwajikolu hwahohnekanatatshri. Maklujine pixkalune, nyonanwakathi klu tshinanu hixa hallitatkalu kamtshi.
Nyonanwakathi hixa mturune pixkalune klu tshinanu hixa himathetlu Wuru Hoyakalu. Nyonanwakathi tsrune pixkalune klu tshinanu hixa himathetlu hyinuwajikolu hwahohnekanatatshri. Maklujine pixkalune, nyonanwakathi hixa klu tshinanu hixkohchinikanurunhi hiyrunu himretlu Hoyakalu tokanu hiyrunu hixa hallitatkalu kamtshi.
Hi Xye Tshijne Hamoxyawaka PiranapniHi het-sotanutanru xye tshijne hi koxa xye tshijne hajeru hejnu. Xye tshijne ret-sotanuxini satu yineru hi ramotlu Wuru Hoyakalu.
Klu tshinanu ptowruka xye tshijne hwatshri, yiner-mane het-sotanreru, yhaltshi het-sotanrewle, hiyrunu ptowru halixkolewlu, hi Wuru Hoyakalu yehi hichpajikatshrini seyni xye tshijne hichpajikatshrini wale ptowruka.
Xye psol-tshijneka hmahakananumxya ptowru het-sotanrewluymakananuko seyni Hoyakalu halujyawaka kamhatshri hikeklu hohne hnikawnanu.
Cristo Kamnitatshine PiranapniMturune pixkalune, hi howukatkalu xye tshijne nikawniywakapa hiyrunu hixa jempiranyehitlu Cristo kamnitatshri hinatshripa. Xawakni koxa hi heppikatkana Cristo kamnitatshine. Xye tshinanu wimathetlu hi howukatkalu xye tshijne nikawniywakapa.
Hix-yehi ruchpakamxyana seyni hi wepirene rixjekanatna klu tshinanu wepirene rixkamkana hi ruchotatkawuna. Seyni ruchotatkawuna rimathetkanna halikaka wepirene hmixyawakanna.
Seyni pixkontshi henekkalunhi Hoyakalu Potukaluya hiyáhoni ptowru potuka himata.
Hi nyonanwakathi halikakalutu tokantshi hma mimatjemyawakanu tshinanu seyni nyonanwakathi klu tshinanu himatlu halikakalutu tokantshi. Hiyrun-koxa halikakalutu tokantshi hi rawyalu weyawlu.
Katnihe kaylokleru? Kayloklerni Jesus tshinkaluru Cristo hmixyawakanu tshinatshri halikaka. Cristo kamnitatshrini Wuru Hoyakalu hiyrunu Hiwhene malixkatu.
Katukta hi halixlu Whentshi tshinkaluru hi rawya Wuru Hoyakalu, seyni katukta halixlu Whentshi tshinkaluru, Wuru Hoyakalu koxa rawya.
Halixanru tokantshi hyinuwaklekananuko hyijnakotanru pirana. Pnute hya halixlexinri tokantshi hyinuwaklekananuko hyijnakotanru pirana hix-koxa Whentshi tshinkaluru himwanu hiyrun-koxa Wuru Hoyakalu himwanu.
Reneklewatanu runkaklexyatkawu xyeni, hiweklu hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa.
Xyekaka nyonanwakathi hyokwijpiratjene tshinanu.
Pixkontshi Wenejikolu PiranapniSeyni pixkontshi henejikolu himwakowa hiyáhoni hixa hi haluklu satuko hasrujyawakhi klu tshinanu pixkontshi henejikolu hasrukjethi. Hiyrunu rasruklewle halikakalutni hi weyawluni. Hiyáhoni htshina hasruklexyawakhi pixka hixa himwaletanru Cristo.
Mturune pixkalune, waleymalunephi hiyáhoni ruphujewniniklunupa hike wpikanu hiyrunu hi wpatewatanu wale hetanu rapojiniklunupa.
Hiyáhoni xawakni himaxini potukalu rixyawaka Cristo, himatan-koxlu ptowru yineruko Hoyakalu halujyawaka kamhatshri Hoyakalu matkakleru rixyawaka.
Hoyakalu Whenene PiranapniHetanu, hi pso hamotlukananu rixwu Wuru Hoyakalu, Hoyakalu whenene wtshinikowaka. Halikaka Hoyakalu whenetkawu. Hiyahokni xye tshijne hajene hi himathetwu klu tshinanu hi rimathetatkaluna Wuru Hoyakalu.
Nuchinikanune, xawakni halikakni Hoyakalu whenenetkawu. Wanepnawaka hi wimatjemkakatka hanu potu hixatshinektapwu. Seyni wimata, ruphujewniniklunupa Cristo wale pixka potuko wixanu, klu tshinanu wetpotutanru rixyawak-potuko.
Ptowru yineru Cristo munanhatshri, powralu rixinwa. Cristo powranu pixka rixanu.
Katukta hektuwaka hkamhini, yonruru tshinyawaka hpupjexya. Klu tshinanu hektuntshi kamnitlu yonruru pirana.
Hiyrun-koxa hixa himata Cristo hinatka wektunu hkonyawakapwu. Hiyrunu hektuntshi hi rawya Cristo.
Hoyakalu Whenene Hiyrunu Kamtshi Whenene PiranapniMturune pixkalune, hi hitshitanru satu yokwijexyawakhi: Klu tshinanu potukalu kamhatshri waleni potukalu. Cristo potuknu pixka rixa wale yineru.
Ptowru yineru hektuwaka kamhatshri, kamtshinerutkani. Klu tshinanu hyinuwaklekananuko hmajnakowata kamtshi. Hiyáhoni xye tshinanukni ruphujewnapa Hoyakalu Whene, hnikaxyawakaplu kamtshi kamrure.
Ptowru Hoyakalu matkakleru hi hektuwaka hkamhajeta klu tshinanu Hiwejikaluru Potukalu rawya. Hiyáhoni hi rumukata majnakowleta klu tshinanu Hoyakalu whenetkani.
Wane wixa himathetletanna Hoyakalu whenene, kamtshi whenen-koxa: Ptowru yineru potuknutshi mkamhakatu, ho Cristo tshinanu hmoletanru hma muchinikkanuklunru katuktako, wale hi Hoyakalu matkaklerni wale.
Wamotkajyawaka PiranapniKlu tshinanu xyekni mitshikawluru tokantshi hyijnakotanru, wamotkajyawaka.
Hi Caim pixka wixanu, wale kamtshineru hiyáhoni repuru Abel-ni ruylatatka. Haklu tshinanhe ruylatlu? Klu tshinanu waleko hkamrure hektun-tshinanni hiyrunu himolni kihle kamrure rixle tshinanu.
Hiyáhoni nomolene, hi himyekanu xye tshijne hajene hahnanuxiniklunhi.
Wimolene wuchinikanrexyawaka tshinanu wimathexnawa hipuktshi wuchpajyatka hiweklu wjihlokatka. Klu tshinanu katukta hi hichiniklu himole, wale hipuktshikowalu.
Katukta hahnanutjetlu himole, wale jiylalewaklerni. Hiyrunu hixa himata, jiylalewakleru hi rawya hiweklu mnikawnakatupa.
Xye tshinanukni wimathetlu hichiniklewlu. Klu tshinanu Cristo, riwekle ruknoka hixa tshinanu. Hiyáhoni hix-koxa wumukata wiwekle hamtakleta wimolene tshinanu.
Katukta himwalu rejnunkate xye wiwejinri pchinika hepixatshri hiyrunu Cristo tshinanu hmoletanru mahaxikatshri retmaka seyni hi ruchiniklu, wan-hixatshri yineru hi himwalu Hoyakalu hichiniklewle.
Nowhenene pixkalune, hi wtokanu tsonu ho winru tsonu hichinikkajini seyni wuchinikkakanu wkamrureya hiyrunu halikakalutuyma.
Wane wixini wimatanu halikakalunwu hiyrunu wapnanuhchinikanutanu Hoyakalu hetanuya.
Wihchinikanu jihyehixinipwu, halikaka Hoyakalu wihchinikanu yohnikalutni. Ptowru potuka rimata Hoyakalu.
Seyni nuchinikanune, wihchinikanu mjihyehitkanuklunwu waneklu kihle hchinikanwu Hoyakalu hetanuya.
Hiyahokni kluneruktako wanjixinri, walemyo wyoptoxinri klu tshinanu htokanu womkahjeta hiyrunu rukchikhihlenutanru wkamhajeta.
Hiyrunu xyekatkani tokantshi hyokanrer-pirana; hiwhene, Jesus Cristo hiwaka walixyawaka hiyrunu wmoletanune Cristo tshinanu wamotkajyawaka, htshin-towutlexyawakwu pixka wixanu.
Katukta Hoyakalu tokanu homkahita Hoyakaluymalu hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu himwalu wale. Wimata Hoyakalu hix-yehi rawa, klu tshinanu renekwu waleko Hiwejikaluru.
Hoyakalu Pirana Hinkaklewatatshinemka Hiyrunu Hoyakalu Halixatshine PiranapniNuchinikanune, hi ptowru hiwejikaluru tshinikatshriwa halixanu seyni hyahothapkatanru himathexyawakaplu ho Hoyakaluymalutlahe ho hike. Klu tshinanu hixo Hoyakalu pirana hinkakletatshinemka xye tshijne hakanhiyatka.
Wla hixa himathetletanru Hiwejikaluru Hoyakaluymalutu. Katukta wan-tshinanru Jesus Cristo hapokatka himaneyma potuko, rawya Hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu yehi hichpajikatshri.
Seyni hanuruktako hiwejikaluru Jesus Cristo hi halikaka rapokatka himaneya potuko tshinatshri, wale hi Hoyakalu yehi hajerni, seyni halikaka Cristo kamnitatshrikni wale. Hixa jempiranyehitatkalu xye pixkalutu hiwejikaluru hapojyawakapa hiyrunu xawakniko xye tshijne rawatka.
Mturune, Hoyakalunune wanna hallitatka. Klu tshinanu hixa himwaler-potu himukatatshri xye tshijne hwatshri yohnikayalutni wale.
Wanna xye tshijne hajenni. Wale tshinanu xye tshijne hchinikanu pirana hkochtshekna. Hiyrunu xye tshijne hajene hislahtokanutna.
Seyni hixa Hoyakalununwu hiyáhoni Hoyakalu himathetatshine hislahtokanutwu. Seyni Hoyakalunune minje hi yijnakotwu. Wane wixa himathetletlu Hiwejikaluru halikakalutu hiyrunu hiwejikaluru pupjetatshri wimatheta.
Hoyakalukni Hamotlewlu PiranapniNuchinikanune, wuchinikkakanu klu tshinanu hichinijikolu Hoyakalu yehi ruchpajya. Katukta hamotkaka Hoyakalu matkaklerutkani hiyrunu Hoyakalu rimatheta.
Seyni katukta hi hamotlewata hi rimathetlu Hoyakalu klu tshinanu Hoyakalukni hamotlewlu.
Wan-rixa hekhireta Hoyakalu ruchinijyawakwu klu tshinanu xye tshiji hyokanatlu Hiwhene satupkalutu wiwejyawakapa wale tshinanu.
Xyekni hamotlewlu. Himka wamotatkalu Hoyakalu seyni wale hamotatkawu hixa. Hiyahokni hyokanatlu Hiwhene Cristo rumukata wukolukanuwnalkaka ramtakahchinikankajyawakapa.
Nuchinikanune, Hoyakalu hamoxyawakwu pixka wixa hichinikkakletanu.
Xye tshinanu wimata waleymatkawu hiyrunu hixaymatkalu Hoyakalu klu tshinanu renejyatkawu waleko Hiwejikaluru.
Wetlu hiyrunu wuphujtatlu Wuru Hoyakalu yokanatlu Hiwhene xye tshijne hajene hiwekkaklewatatshri rixyawakapa.
Katuktako pohitlu Jesus, Hoyakalu whene rixyawaka, Hoyakalu waleymalu hiyrunu Hoyakalu hwalu.
Wimatlu hiyrunu walixlu Hoyakalu hamotwu hixa. Hoyakalukni hamotlewlu. Hamotlewlu hwatshri Hoyakalu hwatshrini hiyrunu Hoyakalu waleymalu.
Xye tshinanu Hoyakalu hamotle tserutkatka hixaya. Wan-hixatshinwu kihle hchinikanurunepwu jemahchinikanyehixikolu hohne hapojiniklunupa. Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu hixyawak-potuko pixka wix-hixa xye tshijiya.
Hamotkaklu hwiywaka hi rawa hamlehonutshi. Hamlehonutshi salewaktshi hikahwaklu seyni halikak-potu hamotlewlu hakaklu hamlehonutshi. Jhamleholu hi kihleylu hamotlewlu.
Wamotlu Hoyakalu klu tshinanu wale hapka hamotatkawu hixa.
Satu wane tshininiklunwa: “Namotlu Hoyakalu”, seyni rahnanuxinri Cristo tshinanu hmoletanru, kayloklerni wale. Klu tshinanu katukta hi hamotlu Cristo tshinanu hmoletanru, retler-potuko, hi rumukata hamotletlu Hoyakalu, metkot-potuko.
Hixa rawyawu xye Hoyakalu towuxyawu: Hoyakalu hamotatshri tshinikatshriwa, Cristo tshinanu hmoletanru ramotanu.
Halixlewlu Xye Tshijne Hallixikowaka PiranapniPtowru yineru Jesus tshinkaluru Cristo rixyawaka halixatshri, Hoyakalu matkaklerni hiyrunu katukta hamotanru Wuru Hoyakalu ramot-koxlu Hiwhene.
Hoyakalu wamoxiniklunu hiyrunu wkamhiniklunru htowuxyawakwu, wimata Hoyakalu whenene hamoxini.
Klu tshinanu wkamhiniklunru Hoyakalu towuxyawu wekhitlu Hoyakalu wamota. Hiyrunu tokantshi htowuxyawu hi kyapreru womkahixyawaklu.
Hoyakalu matkaklene hallitanru xye tshijne. Xye tshijne hallitatshri, waleni walixle. Xyekni wkaykakjeru.
Katnihe xye tshijne hallitatshri? Xye tshijne hallitatshri waleni Jesus, Hoyakalu whene rixyawaka pirana halixatshri.
Maplu Cristo Hiphujtatatshri PiranapniHonha, hrahtshiyma hinatshri, waleni Jesus Cristo. Hi honha tshinanu tsonu runatka seyni honha hiyrun-koxa hihraha rimapokatka. Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru xye pirana hiphujtatatshri, Hiwejikaluru halikakalutni.
Klu tshinanu mapna hiphujtatatshine tenhohneya, Wuru Hoyakalu, Hoyakalu tokanu hiyrunu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru. Nyi mapamkana seyni satupkalu.
Hiyrun-koxa maplu hiphujtatatshri xye tshijneya: Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru, honha hiyrunu hrahtshi. Seyni nyi mapa pa hchinikanurunni.
Yine hiphujtaler-pirana wyoptojeta, seyni Hoyakalu hiphujtaler-pirana potu halixkalurni. Hoyakalu hiphujtaleru waleni, Hiwhene pirana.
Hoyakalu whene halixatshri xye hiphujtaluru ruphujeta. Seyni katukta hi halixlu Hoyakalu, kaylokleru htshinru Hoyakalu klu tshinanu hi ralixatkalu Hoyakalu tokanu, Hiwhene pirana.
Xyekni Hoyakalu hiphujtaler-pirana. Hoyakalu henekwu hiweklu mnikawnakatupa. Hiyrun-koxa xye hiweklu Hiwhene yehi rukchijika.
Katukta himwalu Hiwhene rimwakoxlu hiweklu. Seyni katukta hi himwalu Hoyakalu whene, hi koxa rimwalu hiweklu.
Hoyakalu Wapohchinikanreru PiranapniXyekaka pirana nyonanwakathi hixa Hoyakalu Whene hiwaka halixatshinhi, himaxyawakaplu hiweklu hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa hwiya, hiyrunu Hoyakalu Whene hiwaka halixyawaka.
Hiyrunu xyeni wmunanhaleru wukchikleru Hoyakaluya. Kluneruktako wanjitanu Hoyakalu hikchikhihlenreru, wale yijnakotwu.
Hiyáhoni wimaxinri hyijnakoxyawakwu Hoyakalu, kluneruktako wanjixinru, wimatkoxlu wyoptotanru wanjireru kluneruktako.
Satu yineru hexiniplu Cristo tshinanu hmoletanru hektuwaka hkamhiywaka, seyni hektuwaka mamha menu hkamhini, Hoyakalu ranjitanu riwekkajyawakaplu. Xye ntshinreru hektuntshi hipuktshi meneklewatkatu. Seyni rawa satu hektuntshi hipuktshi heneklewatatshri. Hi xye pixkalutu tshinanu, nanjihohnekjixa.
Ptowru hixatshri hektutu kamrure hektuntshini. Seyni rawa hektuntshi hipuktshi meneklewatkatu.
Wimatlu, ptowru yineru Hoyakalu matkakleru hi hektuwaka hkamhajeta. Hiyrunu Hoyakalu matkakleru himat-hislahnawa hiyáhoni kamtshi hi yotnekanru.
Wimatlu Hoyakalununetkawu. Wimatkoxlu xye tshijnemka ptowruka htowuta kamtshi.
Cristo Halikaka Hoyakalni Hiyrunu Rimalwuxikowaka PiranapniHiyrun-koxa wimatlu Hoyakalu Whene hapokatka hiyrunu renekwu himatkaltshi wimathexyawaklu halikakalutni wale. Halikakalutuymalunetkawu. Waleni Hiwhene Jesus Cristo. Xyekni Hoyakalu halikakalutu hiyrunu hiwekluni hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa.
<font color=teal>2 João</font>Haliklewlu PiranapniHita, Cristo halixatshine kosekatshrino, yonanwakatlo Tsro pixkaluto, nuretkaluro. Towhenene pixkalun-koxa, nuchinikanune halikakalutu pirana tshinanu nyonanwakata. Hi hita tsonu hichinikhi seyni ptowru yineru halikakalutu pirana himatatshine koxa hichinikhi.
Halikakalutu pirana wimwaleru tshinanu, hixa hwatshri hike rixiniko mnikawnakatupa.
Hoyakalu hepixle hixaymalutu, retwamonrewle hiyrunu hapnanuhchinikanru Wuru Hoyakalu hichpajikatshri hiyrunu Jesus Cristo Wuru Whene yehi hichpajikatshri, halikakalutu piranaya, hamotlewluya.
Hamotkaklu PiranapniNpoyikowpotutatka njempiranyehixinixkana satkaka pwhenene homkahixyawaklu halikakalutu tokantshi htowutakanaxyawakwu Wuru Hoyakalu pixka.
Hiyáhoni xawakni Tsro pixkaluto, nanjityi. Himka herotu yokanruru nyonanwakatyi seyni mitshikawluru hyinuwaklekananuko yokanruru, wjemleru tokanuko nyonanwakatyi. Waleni wuchinikkajyawaka.
Xyeni hichiniklewlu. Womkahixyawakaplu htokanu htowuxyawu. Xyeni wale htokanu hyokanrer-pirana. Homkahixyawakaplu htokanu hyinuwaklekananuko wjemleru pirana pixka.
Yokwijrewpiratatshine PiranapniKlu tshinanu hixo yokwijrewpiratatshine xye tshijne hiphujewniyatka. Hi ruphujetluna Jesus Cristo kahituru potuko rixa hapoklexyawakatkalu xye tshijne. Wan-hixatshri yokwijrewpiratatshrini hiyrunu Cristo kamnitjerni.
Hislahinwa, hma mamtajyawakanuplu hkamrure seyni hyoptoxyawakaplu himlujikolupa psoluka.
Ptowru yineru majnakowatatshri, Cristo hasrukle momkahitkatu hi Hoyakaluymalutni wale. Seyni Cristo hasrukle homkahitatshri Wuru Hoyakaluymalutni hiyrun-koxa Hiwheneymalutni wale.
Satu hapokanwakaxiniphi xye hasruklewlu munkakletkatu, hi hyoptotanru hipjiya hiyrun-koxa hi halikanru.
Klu tshinanu katukta yoptohihlenutlu wan-hixatshri yineru hatatjewa repiretlu hkamrure hektunuya.
Hmahapiraxyawakatka PiranapniHi heppik-pirana naluka yonrenwakathi seyni hi naluka yonretlu papel-mta caneta-ya klu tshinanu naluk-hapyehrethi. Waneklu potu winam-potuko wuhle hiynumsakaklexini hiyrunu wpoyikowpotutanu.
Pimole suxo pixkaluto, nuretkaluro whenene halikanyi.
<font color=teal>3 João</font>Haliklewlu PiranapniHita, Cristo halixatshine kosekatshrino, yonanwakatlu Gaio tshinkaluru, nuchinikanretleru, namotleru halikakalutuya.
Nuchinikanru, naluklu ptowru kihle hiknohle pixyawakapa hiyrunu pomta pixyawakapa, kihle samenuryi pixyawakapa.
Klu tshinanu rapojinixkana Cristo tshinanu wmoletanune pixa pirana runkaklexinixkana halikakalutu pirana himwatshri pixyawaka pirana npoyikowpotutatka. Halikaka, tokantshi halikakalutu yanikatshriyi.
Ptowru kata njempiranyehixinna nowhenene pixkalune tokantshi halikakalutu riyanyawakna, npoyikowpotuta.
Gaio Hihlepiranyehixikolu PiranapniNuchinikanru, kihle hislahleryi Cristo tshinanu wmoletanune tshinanu hiyrunu pmetjejetanune tshinanu.
Klanu hichpajikatshine hinkakletlu puchiniklewjexyawakna pirana. Runkakletluna Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine jemanuya. Pepixanna rumukata yalexyawakna, Hoyakalu hepixle pixka pixanna.
Klu tshinanu Cristo hiwaka tshinanu htshijnena ruchpajyana hiyrunu hike hepixlu hyoptotna judeu mixkane yehiya.
Hiyáhoni waluk-hepixletna wan-hixatshine halikakalutu pirana hepixatshinepa wixyawakapa.
Diótrefes Hiyrunu Demétrio PiranapniHitamka yonanwakatna Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine seyni Diótrefes tshinkaluru hi hikchikhihlenutwu. Ralukpotutlu tsru kahwakpiratkaluru rixyawaka rimwanune yehiya.
Hiyáhoni wane nyinipa hi namtakanru rixjexyawaka. Pnu pejnu hektuwaka htshinanwakatwu. Hi wale tsonu hkamha seyni hi hyoptohihlenutna Cristo tshinanu hmoletanune hiyrunu rimaletna hihle yoptolewlepiratatshine. Hiyrunu rakakna wan-hixatshine Cristo halixatshine hapatjexikowak-yehiya.
Nuchinikanune, hi hyimanru hektutu seyni kihleru hyimanu. Kihleru kamhatshri Hoyakalu hayinerutni seyni hektutu kamhatshri hi rimathetlu Hoyakalu.
Ptowru yineru kihlewaka tshinanwakatlu Demétrio tshinkaluru. Hkamhaleru halikakalutu koxa hiphujtatlu. Hix-koxa hiphujtatlu hiyrunu hixa himatlu wuphujtaleru halikakni.
Hmahapiraxyawakatka PiranapniHixo piranamka nyonanwakpirathi seyni hi naluka yonanwaklethi caneta tinta-teyma.
<sup>(14-15)</sup> Klu tshinanu hi howukchini naluk-hapyehrethi. Waneklu potu winam-potuko wuhle hiynumsakaklexini.  Waneyhi hihlehchinikanrewlu. Wimathetjene halikanyi. Palikanna hhiwakaymana wimathetanune ptowruneka.
<font color=teal>Judas</font>Haliklu PiranapniJudas tshinkalurno Jesus Cristo towrerno, Tiago tshinkaluru molno hita. Nyonanwakathi hixa Wuru Hoyakalu hamotlene, Jesus Cristo hislahlene, htshanixlene.
Nanjitlu hetwamonrewlu, kihle hwachalu hiyrunu hichiniklewlu hwapotutanu hix-yehi.
Klu tshinanu rawna jejine satkaka, hixa hanikajite hapokachatatshine mtshanixkoneko. Mitshikawako hnurexikna rapnokaxikowakapna. Hoyakalu malukanutu homkahitatshinni wanna. Hoyakalu hihlenu hepixlewatatshri, mimaletlewatkatu pirana hkahwakluna. Ruknokluna Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu satupkalutu hiyrunu Wutsrukate Jesus Cristo ruknokna.
Hoyakalu Hapnokaxyawakna Malixkane PiranapniHiyáhoni xawakni satu pirana nuchinikapkakanhi yahmaklu mitshikawako himatatkalu. Hoyakalu mitshi Egito tshijne riwekkajyatkana yine seyni wane pnutetka ruylatatkana wannani malixkanni.
Hiyrun-koxa hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrerune tenhohne hajenekananu, yomuwatsa hostutkalunni hike rixiniko mnikawnakatu klu tshinanu ruknokatkaluna rawakanaxyawakna. Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu hihnanutna mapchahawak-yehiya, tsru hijhakaluru hohne hinatshripa rapnokatkona.
Waneko pixka rixkanna Sodoma, Gomorra poktshi hajenni hiyrun-koxa wanestsi hwa poktshitatshinni, kapoklewaklerunni hiyrunu jejinekakluko het-sotankakatshinni, hsaletkanna tshitshmeroyma, xirnatshri hike rixiniko muwnakatuya. Rimathexikowakapa waneko pixka rixkona, wane pixkalutu kamhatshine.
Waneko pixka rixna, nyi yine jipnawaklerune, mantshi himtukjetatshinni. Hi hkahwakpiratluna Hoyakalu towre hiyáhoni phurune rapatna.
Hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towrerune tenhohne hajene kosekatshri, Miguel tshinkaluru, hi htserutahchinikanuxnawa hektuwaka htshinanwakaxyawaklu tsru kamtshi, Moisés-ni mane hikolukle ruhjekajinna mitshi. Wla tsonu htshina Miguel tshinkaluru, Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu tshihetjetanyi, kamtshi.
Seyni nyi jejine, heyikachatlu hmimatjemanutukna. Rimatajijrerna hmasrujikotnina, hocha hajene mimat-hichinikanuwatkane pixka rixna. Wan-rixa himtuklexinwana.
Hi pa himtukalutu retanna klu tshinanu romkahitluna Caim tshinkalurni pupjere pixkalutu. Hiyrunu ralukpotutluna hpohirewaxyawakapna Balaão tshinkalurni pupjere pixkalutu romkahpotutna. Nikatkalunepni wanna Corá tshinkalurni hkamnirewle hikolukanruni pixka.
Hapatje niklexini hichiniklewlu tshinanu seyni nyi jejine himtuka hapatjejrethi. Hpoyikowatna hma patnuymana, wanna nanwaka tsonu hijha nijituxnawa tsru niklu yehiya. Hohimkohi minnewapiratkatuko, ptowru sretako kanniphalu hanikachaleru pixkalunni wanna. Hahmuna hitshipnatshritka, hisahi klu papko msahiwatkatutka pixkalunni. Hepi kata hipnatshine, hahmunni hitskihi potuko hoplijikaluru pixkalunni.
Nyi yine, teno plojhalu mar powha hwatshri mpokokhatu pixkalunni. Ruphujetluna hkamrurna patewkaklewatatshri tsonu, wenu honneha soli pixka. Katahirine mpohijetanu hwawaklerune pixkalunni wanna. Mapchahawaka, katalu mwiywakanu yehi rumlukkanna hike rixiniko mnikawnakatu mmahletu.
Enoque tshinkalurni sete rixinri Adão-ni klopichni hinkakletlu hinamtatshri pirana nyi jejine pirana. Wla htshinnixka Enoque-ni: Hetanu! Tsru Hixikatshriwa Cristo hinanu. Waleymalunepa htowrerune potukalune tenhohne hajene hixo mil mnupna.
Runanu rukolujyawakapna ptowru yine. Rapnokaxyawakapna wane hanikajite hwatshine Hoyakalu malixkane, hkamrurna ptowruka Hoyakalu mukchikhihlenutanutu tshinanu. Hiyrunu rapnokaxyawakapna hektuwaka kamhatshine, Hoyakalu malukkane htokanna ptowruka, hektuwaka htshinanwakaxyawakluna Hoyakalu tshinanu.
Nyi jejine hihjekakjetatshinni, kahemhajetatshinni. Wannako himanna halukanru homkahitatshinni wanna. Hinamaymana htserpiranaxnawana. Kihler-pirana htshinanwakjetna pimrine rukchikhihlenuxikowakapna wannako.
Hinkaklu Hiyrunu Kojiretlu PiranapniSeyni hixa nuchinikanune, hichiniktokanutanru Wutsrukate Jesus Cristo nurrene tokanu, tokantshi mitshikananu runkakletlerna.
Runkakatkahina mitshi hnikawnahohnepiraxini papko, runanna Hoyakalu tokanu heyikatshinepa wannako hihchinikanna halukleru hektutu homkahitatshinepa.
Raluk-hitspaletanna, wannako hihchinikanna hektutu homkahitatshinni. Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru mwikanni wanna.
Seyni hixa nuchinikanune, halixlu potukal-potuko hoho, hpoyehixinwa. Hanjihohnetanu Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hepixleyma.
Hoyakalu hamotlewleko hwahohnekanatanu. Wutsrukate Jesus Cristo hetwamonuxyawakwu kahwakatshinephi, hiweklu hike rixiniko mnikawnakatu hyoptotanu.
Satkaka yineru hihroka halixletatshri hepixanu.
Pimrine tshitshmero yehi hkochpajinna, riwejyawakapna. Hetwamonutanna seyni hislahinwa. Hahnanutanru himkalna kaptsholu pixkalutu, wanna mane kamrure pitshotatshri.
Hanjihohneru, HimalwuruHimalwutkalurni Hoyakalu wumukata poyehitletjeru wma mujrujyawakanupa hiyrunu Hoyakalu hoyaknu sreta wumukata hitakletjeru, hike mixkanepwu, poyikolunepwu.
Hoyakalu satupkalutu, wiwekkakjeru wkochtshekhiwakata. Wutsrukate Jesus tshinanu hoyaknutshi, tsru hiphujewnatshri, towuwlu hiyrun-koxa himukatlu walenni xye tshiji hmuyakotkanuklunuwa klu papko haté xawakni. Hiyrunu hike rixiniko mnikawnakatupa hohne wan-rixanu. Amém.
<font color=teal>Apocalipse</font>Twu steno raw-yonhata Jesus Cristo hixyawakapa pirana. Hoyakalu yokanatlu xye pirana ruphujexyawakapa rekhixyawakapna htowrene howukchini mapokatpatka pirana. Cristo yokanatlu htowreru hiwejikaluru tenhohne hajeru xyekaka pirana rimatkajyawakaplu htowreru, João tshinkaluru.
João tshinkaluru hinkakletlu ptowruka retanru pirana hiyrunu hewi hyonaxikatka ptowruka runkakle pirana Hoyakalu hinkakle pirana, halikakalutu pirana Jesus Cristo hiphujetleru pirana.
Kihle hchinikanurunephi xye yonha hethatatshinepa. Kihle hchinikanurunephi xye hinkaklu pirana hinatshripa pirana hiphujetatshri jematshinepa, xye yonatkaluru pirana homkahitatshinepa, kihle hchinikanurunephi. Klu tshinanu hi howukchini xye ptowruka hix-yehi hakanhini.
Halikkaluru Sete Hapatjewaka Tshinanu PiranapniHita, João-no, nyonanwakatna Sete, Cristo halixatshine hapatjewaka, Ásia tshijne hajene. Kihle hchinikanurunephi hiyrunu kihle hwachalu henejikowakapa Hoyakaluya hwahohnekanatatshri, xawakni hohne hwatshrini, mitshikawni hiyrunu wale pnut-hohne hwatshrip-koxni. Hiyrunu Hoyakalu tuplaprestsi hwatshine sete hiwejikalune tshinanuya koxa.
Hiyrun-koxa Jesus Cristo tshinanuya xye pirana hiphujetatshripa potukalu. Mitshikananu hiwekatshrini wale ptowruneka hipnatshine tskalaya hiyrunu ptowru pohirtshine Tsru Hixikatshriwatni wale. Wuchinikjerni wale, hixa tshinanu cruz rupniyatka ruknokhektunuxyawakapwu hihraha hiyokle tshinanu.
Hiyrunu ruyakotwu sacerdote-ne neru wixyawaka Ruru, Royakalute kamrure wkamhiywakapa. Hiyáhoni Jesus Cristo renejikowaka ptowru hoyaknutshi hiyrunu ptowru towuwlu ptowru hohne mnikawnakatupa. Amém.
Hetanu. Hohimkohi hoho rapojinipa. Ptowrunek-yine potuko hetanru, haté ruylatjene yohlolewapiya hetanru. Ptowru tshijne hajene tshiyahatanu wale tshinanu. Halikakni. Amém.
João Tshinkaluru Hetleru Hetkaluru PiranapniHita João-no, hix-molekoxno Cristo tshinanu hiyrunu Hoyakalu pohirewaxyawaka hajer-koxno. Hapakapno ptowru salewaktshi tshinanuya hiyrunu kahwakachaklerno Jesus Cristo tshinanuya. Waneya mar powha hanikajite hwatshijitatshri Patmos tshinikowaka nwakanatatka. Kachitkalurukananno klu tshinanu Hoyakalu tokanu nunkakletjekanata hiyrunu Jesus Cristo pirana hiphujetkaluru nunkakletjekanata.
Tsru Hixikatshriwa Cristo hohnerni, Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hepixamtno. Tsru plama njema. Notji sreta ruchpaktokanuxya. Kowi hima pixka htshina.
Wla htshinamta, “Petanrukaka pyonpiranatanu papel-mtaya. Waneya pyokanatanro yonawahlo Cristo halixatshine hapatjexyawakkaka hajene nwaka, sete-ne. Éfeso poktshi nwaka, Esmirna poktshi nwaka, Pérgamo poktshi nwaka, Tiatira poktshi nwaka, Sardes poktshi nwaka, Filadélfia poktshi nwaka, Laodicéia poktshi nwaka.
Waneya nuprotakatka nexyawakaplu niynumsatjeru katni, waneya netlu sete katalu hanikapine, ouro kamhikolu.
Waneya katalu hanikapine hanikajite nexyalu yineru pixkalutu mkatshri hopowalu makatatshri, hijix-potuko rapokamkata. Hista hostutka himkalu poyehitatshri ouro kamhikolu.
Hijiwutsa klatlu ovelha pixi pixka ho neve hlatnu pixka. Tshitshime mero pixka rixayhaleta.
Hijixi hatawna, yomuwa bronze hixirikalurutka hatajnu pixka, hatatjewa forno hwakanatatshri hatajixikolu. Htokanu tsru hokanu sejire pixka htshina.
Hpotukle sreta myo ranijyalu sete katahirine. Hinama ronoxya yohlolewapi hepi sretako hakoxikatshri. Hihoji tkatshi nikotle pixka rixa, hnikotpotuxini tkatshi.
Waneya nexinixkalu, hijixistsi nyawnamxya, hipnatshri pixka. Waneya hyosurukkanotatka hpotukle myo, waneya hit-hoho rutakamyota. Wla htshinno: “Hi ppikanu, Hitakni yinuwakatshrino, rapkatle hwatshri koxno.
Hiwekatshrino. Hipnatshrikananno. Seyni petanu, hiwekhohnekanatatshrino hike rixiniko mnikawnakatupni. Ntowutlu hamhikowak-yehi hiyrunu hipuktshi ntowuta.
Hiyáhoni pyonatanru ptowru potuko petanrukaka pirana. Pyonatanru xawakni hakanhatshri pirana petanru hiyrun-koxa hinatshripa pirana petanru.
Sete katahirine petlene npotukle myo nanikamxinri hiyrunu sete katalu hanikapine, ouro kamhikolu pirana mpohijetanutukananu nuphujetanu. Sete katahirine, hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrerune tenhohne hajene wannani Cristo halixatshine hapatjexikowakkaka hwatshinni. Sete katalune hanikapi, yapkakletlu sete hapatjewakkaka.
Tokantshi Cristo Halixatshine Hapatjetatshine Éfeso Poktshi Hajene Tshinanu PiranapniXye pirana pyonanwakatanru hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine Éfeso poktshi hajene kosekatshri: — Xye tokantshi runkakleta katahirine sete hpotukle myo hanikamxikatshri sete katalu hanikapine, ouro kamhikolu hanikajite yapatshri, wla htshina:
Hkamrure nimata. Nimatlu hkamrurewpotutatka ptowru mchiretannutshiyma. Hiyrunu nimatlu hektutu kkamhaklerune kamrure hi hyima. Himlukanutna jejine nuretkalune tshinikatshinwa seyni hi wan-rixna. Hetna kayloklerune rixyawakna.
Kahwakaklerunhi, ptowru salewaktshi hakotatshinhi. Nhiwaka himalwuxikolu tshinanu hkamrurewata hiyrunu hi hihrokatka.
Wanepnawaka nkahekhi psotsonu klu tshinanu hiknokatkalu mitshikananu hichiniklewle.
Hiyáhoni hichinikapanru xako mitshikananu hchinikanu hma pupjekanatkanuklunuwa waneya hehchinikanutanu. Mitshikananu hkamhajekanatanru kamrurtshi pixka hixanu. Klu tshinanu hma mehchinikanutkanuklununapa nunhapkatanu hix-yehi. Katalu hanikapi pixkalutu nkonanhi.
Seyni xye halikaka waneyhi. Nicolaítas kamrure hahnanuta hit-koxa hahnanuxyawaklu pixka.
Kajnakopnahi hyijnakoxyawakapa, hyijnakotanru Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru tshinyawakna Cristo halixatshine hapatjexikowakkaka hajene: Hallitatshripa nenekanu hnijyawakaplu hahmuna sahi, hahmuna hiweklu heneklewatatshri sahi, Hoyakalu hitaklucha kihler-potuko yehi hanikajite hwatshriya.
Tokantshi Cristo Halixatshine Hapatjetatshine Esmirna Poktshi Hajene Tshinanu PiranapniXye pirana pyonanwakatanru hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine Esmirna poktshi hajene kosekatshri: — “Xye pirana runkakhi mitshikananu hwatshri, hiyrunu rapkatle hwatshri, hipnatshri kananu seyni hiwekatshritka.
Nimathetlu hsalewaklu. Nimatlu hike mwikanemkahi seyni halikaka phurunhi. Nimathetna heyikjene judeu-ne tshinikatshinwa seyni hi halikakni. Seyni tsru kamtshi Satanás maklutenni wanna.
Hi hpikanru salewaktshi hix-yehi hapokatshripa. Hjemanu! Halikaka tsru kamtshi Satanás satkaka hixa preso rutakjixanu hyahoxikowakapa. Dez hohne pejnu hsaletko. Seyni hi hihrokahchinikanutanu yahmaklu hipnanu. Waneyapa phuru hitakjetanru pixkalutu sahyi nenekanhi hiweklu heneklewatatshri.
Kajnakopnahi hyijnakoxyawakapa, hyijnakotanru Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru tshinyawakna Cristo halixatshine hapatjexikowakkaka hajene: Hallirewatatshri hi hetanru hepi rixinri hipuktshi.
Tokantshi Cristo Halixatshine Hapatjetatshine Pérgamo Poktshi Hajene Tshinanu PiranapniXye pirana pyonanwakatanru hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine Pérgamo poktshi hajene kosekatshri: — “Xye pirana runkakhi yohlolewapi ptowru sretako hakoxikatshri hinama honoxikatshri himwatshri.
Nimatlu hwiywaka, tsru kamtshi Satanás pohirewaxyawaka yehi. Seyni nhiwaka homkahle hi hiknokatka hiyrun-koxa hi hiknokatkalu halixlu pirana homkahpotuxyawaka. Antipas tshinkaluru nuphujtatjeru ptowutkolu potuko rupniniklunupapkonatka hix-yehi hiylaxikaluru, tsru kamtshi Satanás hwiywaka yehi, seyni hi hiknok-halixletatka.
Wanepnawaka psotsonu nkahekhi klu tshinanu hixaymalune rawna Balaão hasrukle homkahitatshine. Wale honra mitshi hasrukatkalu Balaque tshinkaluru hmajnakowkakjixyawakna israel-nerune, klu tshinanu mayawletshichakaka nikluru henejikolu hnikjixatkana yine hiyrunu rasrukatkana rapoklewaxyawakapna.
Hix-yehi koxa rawna nicolaítas hasrukle homkahitatshine.
Hiyáhoni hehchinikanutanu! Hma mehchinikanutkanuklunupa nunhapkatanu hixa nwaka waneya nkamnitapanna wan-hixjetatshine nonama hwatshri yohlolewapiyma.
Kajnakopnahi hyijnakoxyawakapa, hyijnakotanru Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru tshinyawakna Cristo halixatshine hapatjexikowakkaka hajene: Hallirewatatshri, maná mimatyehitkotu nenekanru. Hiyrun-koxa nenekanru sotlu tshraji klatalu yonatkaluru hiwaktshi herotu mimatkotu. Hike yineru himatanru hiwaktshi seyni yoptotatshri tsonu himatanru.”
Nimatlu hkamrure Cristo tshinanu, hichiniklewle nimata. Nimatlu hepixlewle pimrine tshinanu hiyrunu halixle pirana nimata. Nimatlu hmachiretannu hakotachale hiyrun-koxa nimatlu xawakni hohne hkamrure hita tshinanu, hekamhale yohnikatka.
Wanepnawaka nkahekhi psotsonu klu tshinanu hixa hetachajetlo suxo Jezabel tshinkaluro Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshro phuta tshinikatshrowa seyni tasrukjetna yine hiyrunu tyokwijetna yine ntowrene rapoklewaxyawakapna hiyrunu hnijyawakapluna nikluru mayawletshicha henekachalurkaka.
Pchini hohnejijimka neneklo tehchinikanuxyawakamkapa tapoklewaxinri seyni hi taluklu.
Hiyáhoni xawakni hapoklewjetatshine jeko nuknokanro wala hiyrunu walayma himopatlewatatshine, tsru salewaktshi potuko yehi, hma mehchinikanutkanuklunupna hkamrureyna.
Wala whenene nuylatanu. Hiyáhoni ptowruka Cristo halixatshine hapatjexikowakkaka hajene himatanu hitakni yineru hchinikanu hiyrunu yineru haji hetjetatshrino. Hiyrunu hixa satkaka wenutko hkamrure wenru pso.
Seyni wla ntshinhi pimrine Tiatira poktshi hajenhi, hixa ptowruneka xye hasruklu momkahitkane hiyrunu hipiranacha pimrine kochtshekleru pirana, tsru kamtshi Satanás tsonu himukata hiphujetleru pirana, mimatkanhi, wla ntshinhi. Hi satuko hinolu nenekanhi wane pnutetka.
Xye tsonu, himwaleru halikaka hi hiknokanu nmapokkanuko pchinika.
Hallirewatatshripa, kamrurtshi nalukanru kamhapotutatshri haté hmahaxyawaka papko potuko, towuwlu nenekanru pa nerkaka htowuwaxyawakapa. Towuwlu Nuru henejyano pixkalutu nenekanru wan-hixatshri yineru.
Kanojeru yomuwajeyma htowuxinna. Kastonolu kajpa kamhikolu pixka rixa himlokkotanunna pa nerkakapni.
Hohisahi nenekanru wan-hixatshri yineru.
Kajnakopnahi hyijnakoxyawakapa, hyijnakotanru Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru tshinyawakna Cristo halixatshine hapatjexikowakkaka hajene.
Tokantshi Cristo Halixatshine Hapatjetatshine Sardes Poktshi Hajene Tshinanu PiranapniXye pirana pyonanwakatanru hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine Sardes poktshi hajene kosekatshri: “Xyekni hinkaklu hixa tshinanu, wla htshina, sete hiwejikalune Hoyakalununni hiyrunu sete katahirine hanikatshri. Nimatlu hkamrure. Hiwekatshine hikahwakkalune seyni halikaka hipnatshinhi.
Hislahinwa, hmixkotanru himwaleru hixetatshri psotsonu, hma mupniywaknupa wale psotsonu koxa. Klu tshinanu hi nukchiklu hkamrure Hoyakalu halukanru hike mmahaxikatu, Hoyakalu hetanu tshinanuya.
Hiyáhoni hichinikanretanru htshinikolu hyoptoleru, hjemleru. Wale pirana xako homkahpotutanu hehchinikanutanu. Klu tshinanu hma muslahiknuklunwa chinpotu napyehitanhi, katshowhuru hapokle pixka. Hi himatanu klu hora-ko napyehitanhi.
Seyni satkakhi hixajiji, Sardes poktshi hajenhi hi pitshotamkaluxnawa. Hitayma hyanna mkatshri klatalu makatatshine. Rumukatna klu tshinanu hike hma tshinanwakaxikowakanna tshinanni.
Hallirewatatshri mkatshri klatalu makatatshripni. Hiyrun-koxa hiwejikaluro steno hi ruchyahiwakaxiko. Seyni wale hiwaka nuphujetanu Nuru Hoyakalu hetanu hiyrunu hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrene tenhohne hajene hetan-koxa.
Kajnakopnahi hyijnakoxyawakapa, hyijnakotanru Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru tshinyawakna Cristo halixatshine hapatjexikowakkaka hajene.
Tokantshi Cristo Halixatshine Hapatjetatshine Filadélfia Poktshi Hajene Tshinanu PiranapniXye pirana pyonanwakatanru hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine Filadélfia poktshi hajene kosekatshri: “Xye pirana runkakhi Hoyakalu, potukal-potuko, halikak-potu, phuru Davi tshinkalurni chave-te himwatshri. Hkotpukka, hike hichyatlu. Ruchyaxini, hike kotpuklu.
Nimatlu hkamrure. Hetanu! Hiphapto nkotpukyehixyahi. Hike himukata hichyaletlu. Kmixkonhi psotsonu. Hiyrun-koxa ntokanu homkahjeta hiyrunu hi hiknokatkalu nhiwaka halixikolu.
Hetanu! Tsru kamtshi Satanás hapatjeyehitatshine, judeu-ne tshinikatshinwa phuta seyni hweyawatna. Wanna halikaka hixa jixistsi nyoptsojitjixapinna, rimathexyawakapna nuchinikjethi.
Hislahatkalu ntokanu ntowuxyahi, hkahwakachaxyawakap-pirana hiyáhoni hit-koxa hepixanhi hma mexyawakanuplu salexikol-hohne hinatshripa, ptowru tshijne hajene yahoxikolu klu papkopa.
Hjemanu! Nunhapkatanu. Hiyáhoni walekaka himwaleru hi hichotanu. Hike yineru mkonyawakanuplu himlujikolu hyoptotanrupa.
Hallirewatatshripa, Noyakalutepji stsihi nixkakanru. Hikeklu maleka ruchpakanutka. Wale hoho Noyakalute hiwaka nyonatanu hiyrunu Noyakalute poktshite hiwaka wale hoho nyonatanu. Wale poktshi Jerusalém poktshi herotetkalurupa tenhohne Noyakalut-yehi hichpajikatshripa. Hiyrun-koxa hitako nhiwaka herotu wale hoho nyonatanu.
Kajnakopnahi hyijnakoxyawakapa, hyijnakotanru Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru tshinyawakna Cristo halixatshine hapatjexikowakkaka hajene.”
Tokantshi Cristo Halixatshine Hapatjetatshine Laodicéia Poktshi Hajene Tshinanu PiranapniXye pirana pyonanwakatanru hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru Cristo halixatshine hapatjetatshine Laodicéia poktshi hajene kosekatshri: “Xye pirana runkakhi Amém tshinkaluru, Hoyakalu pirana hiphujetatshri halikak-potu, mweyawakletu, Hoyakalu hiyakotanrukaka yinuwakatshri.
