Statshi hinotatshri rutaklerna yomuwa kamhikolu chpata pixkalutni. Himejna sejire hixolune cavalo-ne carro-ne kosetatshine yahotkaklu nwaka hyinna pixka htshinhimata, himejna.
Hihchina, heklo hchi pixka rixa. Hinokalewapni hihchina hwatshri. Hihchina kmixkonru yine hsalexyawakapna cinco ksuru pejnu.
Kpohirna. Htowutjerna hiwejikaluru teno pnawaka hinotatshrikni wale. Hiwakni judeu-neru tokanuya, Abadom tshinkaluru seyni grego-neru tokanuya Apolião tshinkalurni. (Raluka tshinreta, knikatakleru.)
Mitshikananu salewaktshi hiknohatka. Seyni hjemanu! Hepi salewaktshi hapokatshripa mahatawa.
Seis Rixinri Kowi Hima PiranapniWaneya seis rixinri hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru kowitatka. Waneya tokantshi nyijnakota. Kapajiru henekachalu yoxikaluru hitajikowaka, ouro kamhikolu hwatshri, quarto hwa mayawle Hoyakalu hoji sreta hwatshri ruchpaktokanuxya.
Wla htshinatkalu tokantshi, seis rixinri hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru, kowi himwatshri: “Puchotanna hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrerune tenhohne hajene, quatro tsru wenu Eufrates wenne tshinikowakastsi hostutkalune.”
Soldado-ne pejnu njempiranata, cavalo-ne yapatshine pejnu. Duzentos milhões pejnu himna.
Netna cavalo-ne hiyrunu wanna yapatshine neta, nupnale pixkalutu nexyana. Statshi hinotatshri chpata serolu tshitshmero pixkalutu, katshino polnuru sotlu safira pixkalutu hiyrunu pwalolu enxofre pixkalutu hwastatna. Cavalo-ne leão jiwu pixka rixjiwutna hiyrun-koxa tshitshmero, tshitshipha hiyrunu enxofre hichpaka namaxyana cavalo-ne.
Satupka mapate (1/3) yinni hiylatkana xye mapa saletlu tshinanu, tshitshmero tshinanu, tshitshipha tshinanu hiyrunu enxofre tshinanu. Cavalo-ne nama hichpajikatshri.
Klu tshinanu cavalo-ne himukatle hinama rawa hiyrunu hihchina rawa. Hihchina himnune pixka rixna, kajiwru. Waleyma hsaletanna yinni.
Seyni pimrine yine hixetatshine xyekaka saletlu muylatkanune, hi rehchinikanyehitluna wannako hkamrurna: hi ruchotluna kamtshine romkahixyawakna, hi mayawletshicha ouro ho prata ho bronze, ho sotlu, ho hahmuna kamhikolu metkatu, majnakotu, myankatu hi rutuk-homkahretna.
Hiyrun-koxa hi rehchinikanyehitluna ruylalewlena, hi hkahontshiwlekna, hi rapoklewlekna, hi htshowhuwlekna rehchinikanuxyana.
Hoyakalu Towreru Tenhohne Hajeru Hiyrunu Yonawahlo Steno PiranapniWaneya satu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru hixkolu neta. Tenhohne hserpijya. Hohimkohi hmakata. Kchitpo hijiw-hoho hwa. Hihoji tkatshi nikotle pixka rixa hiyrunu hiksuje tshitshmero hi pixka rixa.
Yonawahlo steno mtserutu kopralatkaluru himyo ranijya. Hijixi hpotukle sreta mar powha hkatsrexya, pa sta sretate jixi tshiji hkatsrexya.
Waneya tsru plama hsaplewaxya leão hahlal-le pixka. Waneya rali saplewlexinixka sete rutlohle himkaka yanumatatka.
Waneya rali yanumletatka rutlohle tshinyawaka nyinuwaka yonretmaka seyni waneklu potuko tokantshi njema tenhohne hichpajikatshri, wla tshinatshri: “Pihnanutpotutanru tokantshi htshinyawakna sete rutlohle. Hi pyonatanru.”
Waneya hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru netanru, mar powha hiyrunu tshij-hoho katsretatshri, tenhohne hyotukamyota himyo hpotukle sreta.
Waneya hkojiretna yine Hoyakalu hiwaka tshinanu. Hoyakalu honra hiwekatshri hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa, tenhohne, tshiji, mar powha hiyrunu ptowru potuko wane hajeru hiyakotatshrikni. Wla htshinatka Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru: “Hi hohamokaplu hnikawniywakapa hohi.”
Hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru sete rixinri kowixinipa waneya Hoyakalu nikatanru rixahchinikanuxyawaka hkamhiywakapa, yohimakanatkaluru pirana, runkajyatkana htowrene, Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine mitshikawlune.
Waneya plamtshi niynumsakanatjeru, tenhohne hichpajikatshri hima, njematnaka. Wla htshinno: “Hajewa. Pyoptotapanru yonawahlo steno mtserutu kopralatkaluru hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru, mar powha hiyrunu tshij-hoho katsretatshri, myo hwatshri.”
Waneya hiwejikaluru nwaka Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru nwaka nyatka. Waneya wla ntshinru: “Yonawahlo steno mtserutu penekanno.” Waneya wla htshinno: “Pyoptotanru, pnikanru. Pinanwaka kapsaplu seyni pinama potshwaplu wrolha pixka.”
Hiyáhoni nyoptotlu yonawahlo steno mtserutu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru myoya waneya nniklu. Nonama potshwa rixa, wrolha pixka. Seyni nali nikloklexinixkalu yonawahlo steno mtserutu, kapsa nanwaka nixa.
Waneya wla htshinatkanona: “Pujhalu punkaklexyawakatnaklu Hoyakalu tokanu hixolune tshijne hajene yehi, kakojenerurune yehi, kakojeru nrutshi yehi hiyrunu pohirtshine yehi.
Hoyakalupji Yahotaxikolu PiranapniWaneya yahotapije nenekka kanojertshi pixkalutu. Waneya wla htshinnona: “Ppalnanu. Pyahotanru hi psolu Hoyakalupji, kapajiru henekachalu yoxikaluru hitajikowaka hi pso hiyrunu putakyahokanna yine himalwutatshine Hoyakalupji hwatshine hi pejnu.
Seyni Hoyakalupji maleka sreta hwatshri kwa petachatanu, hi pyahotanru wale klu tshinanu wale honra judeu mixkane renekka. Hoyakalu poktshite hkapnikapahitanna quarenta e dois ksuru pejnu.
Hepi Hiphujtatatshine Hinatshripa PiranapniHepi nuphujtatjene mkatshri saco mapa kamhikolu makatatshine nyokanatanu. Waneya Hoyakalu tokanu runkakletanna mil duzentos e sessenta hohne pejnu.
Hepi hiphujtatatshine yapkakletlu hepi oliveira muna hiyrunu hepi nikotapi hwawakle, Hoyakalu ptowru tshijneka Tsru Hixikatshriwate hoji sreta, yopkakhohnekanatatshinni.
Satu yineru haluka saletlexinipna nyi hepi jiphujetaklerune, tshitshmero hichpaknamaxinna hkamnitjene hnikaxyawakapna. Hiyáhoni katukta haluka saletletmakna wla rixa hiylaletkonna.
Kpixkonna tenhohne ruchyaxyawakapna, hina hmixyawakanupa Hoyakalu tokanu runkakletjexyawakna pchinika. Hiyrun-koxa kpixkonna honha htowuxyawakna, hrahtshi rixnatkawa. Kpixkonna ptowru hixatshri salewakluyma tshiji rumtujyawakapna, hi pejnu katakta raluka wan-hixletna wan-rixna.
Waneya rali hinkaklewlexinipna hiphujetatshine hepi waneya kmatsyiru teno pnawaka hichpajikatshri kamnitanna, ralliretanunna, ruylatanunna.
Himanepnina poktshi hijhakaluru hapo yine yapjehijhakalur-potu hiknokachatkona, Wutsrukate Cristo cruz hitajikowaka poktshi. Xye poktshi Sodoma poktshi hiyrunu Egito tshijne pixkalutni.
Ptowru tshijne hajene, pa nerkaka, pa nrukaka yanumaxikatshine, ptowru hixatshri neru hetamanetanna map-hohne hanikaji. Hi ritshi kapnatko manetkana.
Hpoyikowpotutanna yine tshiji hajene nyini hipnatshinni tshinanni. Hmeyiwatanna henekachalkaka renekkakanna klu tshinanu nyi hepi Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine saletpotukanatna xye tshiji hajene.
Waneya map-hohne hanikaji hiknohinixka hinnipha hiweklu heneklewatatshri Hoyakalu yokanreru jihlokmanetna. Hpalnana, hyopkakna. Hiyáhoni hpikpotutatkana wanna hetatshine.
Waneya tsru tokantshi hjemna tenhohne hichpakhimaxikatshri, wla tshinatshri: “Hewi teno hapokanu.” Hiyáhoni wanna hepi tenhohne hyatkana. Hohimkohi hoho hyapna hkamnitjene hetanuko.
Hepi rixinri salewaktshi hiknohatka seyni hjemanu, salewaktshi mapa rixinri hi hohamokapa.
Sete Tixinri Kowi Hima PiranapniWaneya hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru sete rixinri kowitatka. Waneya tsru himkaka hjemka tenhohneya wla tshinatshri: “Xye tshiji hajeru pohirtshikaka Wutsrukate Hoyakalunpatka hiyrunu hnurreru Cristo-npatkani. Hiyrunu wale pohirewahohnekanatanu hike rixiniko mnikawnakatupa.”
Waneya tsrukakalune vinte e quatro, htuplawaklena pohirtshi tuplawakle tuplatatshine, Hoyakalu hoji sreta hwatshine, hyoptsojityehitluna Hoyakalu hiyrunu hihojna tshiji rutspakna. Hoyakalu rimalwutna.
Wla htshina himalwuretluna Hoyakalu: “Wimalwutyi Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu ptowru potuko himukatatshriyi, mitshikananu hwatshriyi, xawakni hohne hwatshriyi, hike rixiniko mnikawnakatupyi. Wimalwutyi klu tshinanu pumukatle tsru potukoyma pyinuwaka pohirewleta.
Xye tshijne hajene malixkane hahnanuwpotuta. Klu tshinanu rapnokaxikolna hohne hapokatka. Hiyrunu hipnatshinni hetmayxaklexikolu papko hapokatka. Rapokpapkoluta ptowrene, ptokanu hinkakletatshine, pnurrene palixjene, phiwaka kahwakpiratatshine, yahmaklu mujhakonni yahmaklu hijhakalun-potu seyni rumlujikolna henekkalunepni. Rapokpapkoluta hnikaxyawakapna yine xye tshijne himtukjetatshine.”
Waneya Hoyakalupji tenhohne hwatshri hitpukatka. Wane rexika Hoyakalupji hitokote hwatshri kapajiru Hoyakalu kojiretle pirana hwiywaka paji. Wanekananru rawrakle, tokantshi himkaka, rutlohle, tsru hiyoliklu tshiji, hiyrunu tsru potu sotluji teno hichpajikatshri.
Suxo Hiyrunu Kamtshi Dragão Tshinkaluru PiranapniWaneya tsru himyekaklewatatshri tenhohne rakanhiya. Sato suxo tkatshi makatatshro hiphujewna. Ksuru tojixi hpuko hwa hiyrunu pohirtshi sahye t-sahyeta doze katahiri hwa sahyetlo.
Kamchiro suxo. Mturu tshino tshinanu t-saplewjeta. Klu tshinanu tmatuwhenpirata.
Waneya satu himyekaklewatatshri tenhohne rakanhiyatnaka. Satu dragão tsruru, serolu hiphujewna. Sete jiwuru, dez hwalutu. Sete jiwlu sahyi pohirtshi sahye, hsahyetna.
Hihchimtayma hkosetlu satupka mapate katahirine (1/3) tenhohne hajerkaka waneya tshij-hoho ruknoklu. Waneya suxo matuwhenpiratatshro hoji sreta hyopkaka Tsru Kamtshi dragão hnijyawakapmaklu towhene hmatuxiniklunupa mturu.
Waneya tmatuwhenetatka. Jejni. Xyepni ptowru tshijne towutatshripni, hike majnaknutshi hetachatatshripni. Hkochtshekkatka toturu. Hoyakalu yehi ranikkatka. Hoyakalu tuplawakle yehi rutakka.
Waneya suxo potshkewaka tya hasukleta. Hoyakalu hihlehnapuxyalo nwaka tya. Wane tohluxiko satu mil duzentos e sessenta hohne pejnu.
Yahotkaklu Tenhohne Hwatshri PiranapniWaneya tsru hiylakkaklu hwa tenhohne. Miguel tshinkaluru hiyrunu repirene hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrerune tenhohne hajene yahotlu Tsru Kamtshi dragão hiyrunu hmaklutene kamtshine. Hiyrun-koxa Tsru Kamtshi dragão hiyrunu hmaklutene kamtshine yahotkakamka.
Ramtakna Tsru Kamtshi dragão hiyrunu repirene kamtshine. Waneya wane wkatanu hi rukchika hwawakletkana tenhohneya.
Hiyáhoni Tsru Kamtshi dragão tsru kananu, wale honukla himnu hitsruka, Tsru Kaylokleru tshinkaluru, Satanás hiwakatletatshri, ptowru tshijne hajene yokwijetatshri, tenhohne malekate ruknojika. Tshij-hoho ruknokkatka wale hiyrun-koxa hmaklutene kamtshine waleyma ruknokatkana.
Waneya satu tokantshi njema tsru himalu tenhohne hichpajikatshri wla tshinatshri: “Xawakni kananu rapokatka hiweklu hohne, himukatlu, Woyakalute pohirewaxyawaka hiyrunu hnurreru Cristo himukatle towuwle hapokatka. Klu tshinanu wmoletanune Cristo tshinanu jihyehitatshri Hoyakalu yehi hohohne hiyrun-koxa hoyetshno hjihyehitjerna, hiknokkatka.
Wmoletanune Cristo tshinanu hallitlu Tsru Kamtshi Carneiro Whene tshinkaluru hraha himukatle tshinanu hiyrun-koxa halikakalutu tokantshi runkakletjetanruna tshinanu. Hiyrun-koxa ralpokoxinwana rupniywakapna. Riweklena hi ramotpotutna.
Hiyáhoni hpoyikowpotutanu tenhohne hiyrunu tenhohne hwatshinhi. Seyni wamonuwatatshinepni tshiji hwatshine hiyrunu mar powha hwatshine, klu tshinanu kamtshi Satanás hix-yehi rujrukatka. Rahnanuwata tsru kamtshi klu tshinanu rimatlu hi hix-hohne waneylu.
Kamtshi Dragão Kojwajyawaklo Suxo PiranapniWaneya rimathexinixka Tsru Kamtshi dragão tshij-hoho ruknojikowakatka hyinuwaka saletletlo suxo, jeji matkakatshro.
Seyni suxo hepi mejro, tsru paktsha meji pixkalutu tenekka tumukata palnalexyawakapa, talpokohnapuxikolu potshkewaka nwaka tyiywakapa. Wane tohluxiko mapa mhale hanikaji pejnu hohne, tma kojwajikowakanupa himnu tshinkaluru tshinanu.
Hiyáhoni himnu tshinkaluru suxo hatjini raplikhatlu honha, tsruhalu wenu pixka, tsruha hanijyawakamkaplo.
Seyni tshiji hepixatkalo suxo. Hiyáhoni tshiji haplaknamata hnikloklu tsruhalu himnu tshinkaluru haplikhatanru.
<sup>(17-18)</sup> Waneya himnu tshinkaluru hahnanuwatatka suxo tshinanu. Hiyáhoni hya hkamnixyawakapna pimrine toklopichane, Hoyakalu tokanu towre hiyrunu halikakalutu pirana Jesus hiphujetleru pirana homkahitatshine.  Tsru Kamtshi dragão ksatu mar powha hwatshri hyopkaka.
Kmatsyiru Mar powha Hichpajikatshri PiranapniWaneya netlu kmatsyiru mar powha kanjikatshri. Dez hwalu hiyrunu sete jiwlu. Hihwakaka rawa dez pohirtshi sahye pixkalutu. Hijiwkaka rawa yonatkaluru Hoyakalu nwaka hektuwaka tshinatshri.
Kmatsyiru netanru mhenoklu pixka rixmanetatka. Seyni hijixi urso jixi pixka rixa, hinama leão nama pixka rixa. Waneya Tsru Kamtshi dragão waleko hpixkonu reneklu, hpohirewnale reneklu hiyrunu tsru towuwlu reneklu.
Satu kmatsyiru jiwu hipnaphutata seyni ruhlewatatnaka. Hiyáhoni ptowru tshijne hajene himyeka kmatsyiru tshinanu. Romkahitatkaluna kmatsyiru.
Hiyáhoni rimalwutluna Tsru Kamtshi dragão klu tshinanu tsru pixkontshi reneklu kmatsyiru. Hiyrun-koxa kmatsyiru rimalwutna. Wla htshina himalwuretluna kmatsyiru: “Hanurhe kmatsyiru pixkalutni? Kathe hakot-kamniretlu?”
Waneya ritshitka kmatsyiru tokantshi hektutu hyanumaxyawaka, htserpiranaxnawa. Renekka wan-rixyawaka quarenta e dois ksuru pejnu.
Hinama hyanumaxyalu hektutu tokantshi Hoyakalu nwaka. Hektutu htshinanwakatlu Hoyakalu hiwaka hiyrunu Hoyakalu hwiywaka hektutu htshinanwakata hiyrun-koxa wanna ptowruneka tenhohne hwatshine hektutu htshinanwakata.
Ptowru tshiji hwatshine, katuktako hi khiwaka Carneiro Whene tshinkaluru, hiylatkaluru papel-te stenoya xye tshijne hiyakotkoklunukananuko, hiweklu heneklewatatshri steno mwa hiwakatkatu, himalwutanru kmatsyiru.
Kajnakopnalu yijnakotanu.
Kachitkalunepa, kachitkalurunepni. Yine nuretkalune hiylatkalunepa pejnu halikaka ruylatkona. Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu nurrene ralixjene haluklu rakotachaxyawakna hiyrunu ralixachaxyawakna.
Kmatsyiru Tshiji Hitokote Hichpajikatshri PiranapniWaneya netlu satu kmatsyiru tshiji hichpajikatshri. Hepi hwalutni carneiro whene pixka. Seyni htokanu dragão tokanu pixka htshinya.
Mitshikananu kmatsyiru himukatleyma pixka rixa kamrurewleta hepi rixinri kmatsyiru, mitshikananu kmatsyiru hetanuya. Hiyrun-koxa htowutjetlu tshiji hiyrunu tshiji hwatshine ptowruneka rimalwuxyawakapluna mitshikananu kmatsyiru, hiylajiwuphutatkalurutka seyni ruhlewatatnaka.
Tsru himyekaklewatatshrikaka hkamhajeta. Haté tenhohne rujrukkajyalu tshitshmero tshij-hoho, ptowru yine hetanu.
Hyokwijetna tshiji hwatshine ptowruneka himyekaklewatatshrikaka hkamhaleruyma, rumukatle renejikolu tshinanu, mitshikananu kmatsyiru hetanu. Runkakjixna xye tshijne hajene mayawletshicha hkamhiywakapna kmatsyiru mayawleya, yohlolewapi kastakjiwuxikalurutka seyni hi rupna.
Kmatsyiru hepi rixinri, yoptopixkonuta kmatsyiru mayawle rinniphakajyawakapa, hyanumaxyawakapa hiyrunu pixkontshi rimwiywakapa ruylaxyawakapna ptowru yine mayawletshicha mimalwutkane pejnu.
Waneya hkamhakjixna yine ptowrunek-yine hijhakalune ho mujhakone ho phurune ho towutachatkalune ho hichotkalune wanna ptowruneka, hpotukle myona ho hijrotna rutak-himaxikolexikolupna.
Hiyáhoni hike himukata maronewletanu, hi rumukata hichanrewletanna mitshikananu kmatsyiru himaxikole mimwakane. Rimaxikole waleni kmatsyiru hiwaka ho h-número-te pejnu.
Xyekni himatkalewlu. Jimatkaleru hitakyahokanru kmatsyiru número-te hi pejnuru. Klu tshinanu wale número-te yapkakletlu jeji hixannu. Waleni seiscentos e sessenta e seis.
Hiwekkakalune Chikale PiranapniWaneya netatkalu. Carneiro Whene tshinkaluru neta Sião mriji tshinikowak-hoho yopkakatshri. Wale ymalune cento e quarenta e quatro mil yine wale hiwaka hiyrunu Ruru hiwaka himwatshine pejnu. Hijrotna hyonaxikatka.
Waneya satu hima njema tenhohne hichpajikatshri. Tsru hokanu sejire pixka htshinhimata hiyrunu rutlohle hima pixka htshina. Tokantshi hima njemanru hixo harpa tokle pixka htshinhimata.
Cento e quarenta e quatro mil yine, pohirtshi tuplawakle sreta, hiwejikalune quatro hiyrunu vinte e quatro tsrukakalune yoptowaka sreta rawna. Herotu chikalu hchikaletna. Halikaka wanna cento e quarenta e quatro yine, tshiji hwakanatatshine hiwejikane tsonuko himukata himatletlu chikaltshi hchikaletanruna.
Nyi jejine, cento e quarenta e quatro mil yine pejnu, suxone mapokmanetkanewa, wannani powrahchinikanurune. Nyi jejine Carneiro Whene tshinkaluru homkahitatshinni hanuktako hyini wale. Nyi yin-yehi hanjixikalunni. Wanna honra mitshikananu henekachalu pixkalune Hoyakalu tshinanunepa hiyrunu Carneiro Whene tshinkaluru tshinanunepa.
Hikeklu rayoklewatna. Hike mixkanni, potukalunni.
Mitshikananu Hiphujetkaluru Tokanu PiranapniWaneya satu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru neta tenhohne palnikatshri. Kihle piranalu potuko hiwekkaklewatatshri pirana hike rixiniko mnikawnakatupa pirana hiphujetatshrini wale. Ptowru tshijne hajeru tshinanupa, ptowru nerkaka tshinanupa, ptowru yineru ptohkaka tshinanupa, ptowru nrukaka tshinanupa hiyrunu ptowru yin-yehi tshinanupa.
Waneya hipokananu hyanumata, wla htshina: “Hkahwakpiratanru Hoyakalu, hiphujetanru royaknu himalwuruyma. Klu tshinanu rapnokatjixle papko hapokatka. Himalwutanru tenhohne, tshiji, mar powha hiyrunu honha hichpakhaxyawaka hiyakotatshri.
Tokantshi Hiphujetlewatatshri Hepi Rixinri PiranapniWaneya satu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru hepi rixinri, mitshikananu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru hatjini hya, wla htshina: “Rallitka, rallitka tsru poktshi Babilônia tshinikowaka! Tkamhaleru hapoklewlu katsh-halu himtuklewatatshri potuko, ptowru tshijne hajene tutahata.”
Tokantshi Hiphujetlewatatshri Mapa Rixinri PiranapniWaneya hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru mapa rixinri homkahitna hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrerune tenhohne hajene hepi kosekatshine. Waneya hipokananu hyanumata, wla htshina: “Katukta kmatsyiru ho kmatsyiru yáholu himalwuta hiyrunu hanurukta himyo ho hijrota, kmatsyiru himaxikole yoptoxikatshri,
wale yineru rutka hirkaluru Hoyakalu jhekan-ha pixkalutu. Katsh-halu myapjetkotu hirapi stono hiyokkalurupa, Hoyakalu jhekanu hiratshinepni wanna. Hiyrunu walepni salewnapotutanuna tshitshmeroya, enxofre-yma hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrerune tenhohne hajene potukalune hetanuya hiyrun-koxa Carneiro Whene tshinkaluru hetanu.
Tshitshipha hsalewniywakna yehi hichpajikatshri, ratskophatanu hikeklu hohne mnikawnakatupa. Hi hohohne hi hoyetshnoko rapnanutanuna wanna ptowrunepnika kmatsyiru ho wale yáholu himalwutatshine pejnu hiyrunu wanna ptowruneka wale hiwaka himaxikole yoptotatshinepni wan-rixkonna.
Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu nurrene ralixjene haluklu rakotachaxyawakna, Hoyakalu tokanu yonatkaluru romkahpotuxyawakna hiyrunu Jesus ralixachaxyawakna.
Tokantshi Hiphujetlewatatshri Quatro Rixinri PiranapniWaneya nyijnakotlu tokantshi tenhohneyalutu wan-tshinatshri: “Xye pirana pyonatanu. Kihlehchinikanurunepni hipnatshine xye hohne pnutpatka Tsru Hixikatshriwa Cristo hiwaka tshinanu hipnatshine.” “Hehe, halikakni,” htshina Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru. “Rapnanutanna hkamrureyna hiyrun-koxa hkamrurna hkamhajekanatanruna hpohitanna.”
Ramikolu PiranapniWaneya netatkalu. Netlu satu hohimkohi klatalu hiyrunu hohimkohi hoho tuplatatshri neta, jeji nikahwaklu. Pohirtshi sahye, ouro kamhikolu, hijiwu hwa hiyrunu hitaklu hamapi hakotasputatshri himyo hkachixya.
Waneya satu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru Hoyakalupji hichpajya. Hsaplewata hohimkohi hoho tuplatatshri nwaka. Tsru saple rixa, wla htshin-sapleta: “Pamanu pamapreyma. Klu tshinanu ramikolu klu papko hapokatka pamyawakaplu tshiji hwatshine klu tshinanu ralixatka tshiji hajeru ramikowakapa.
Waneya hohimkohi hoho tuplatatshri hamlu tshiji, hitaklu hamapiyma.
Waneya satu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru Hoyakalupji, tenhohne hwatshripji hichpajya. Wale koxa himwalu hitaklu hamapi hakotasputatshri.
Waneya hiyrunu satu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru, tshitshi hislahatshrini wale. Kapajiru henekachalu yoxikjexikowaka hinaple ruchpajya. Hsaplewata tsru saple rixa hitaklu hamapi hakotasputatshri himwatshri nwaka. Wla htshin-sapleta: “Putakle hamapi hakotasputatshriyma pamanru uva hawkaka tshiji hajeru. Klu tshinanu ralixatka uva-ji tshiji hajeru.
Tsru poktshi maleka sretate uva katsrekjexikowak-yehi hkatsrexika waneya hrahtshi wane hichpajya. Hrahtshiha trezentos quilômetros howuknu hiyrunu haté cavalo-ne jri tslu pa tennu rapoka hrahtshi.
Tsru Salewnalkaka Hapkatatatshri PiranapniWaneya wane wkatanu netlu satu hetkaluru, tsru potuko himyekaklewatatshri. Waleni sete hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrerune tenhohne hajene, sete tsru salewaktshi hapkatatatshri hanikatshine. Klu tshinanu ralipretkani Hoyakalu jhekanu.
Cristo Hiwekkaklene Chikale PiranapniWaneya netlu tsru mar powha pixkalutu, garrafa phuta kamhikolu, tshitshmeroyma yapjetkaluru. Hiyrun-koxa netna yine, kmatsyiru hiyrunu kmatsyiru yaholu hallitatshine. Kmatsyiru hiwaka número-te hallitatshinekni wanna. Mar powha, garrafa kamhikolu phuta stsi hyopkakakanatna. Harpa-kaka Hoyakalu henejyana htokakanatna.
Hchikaletluna Moisés-ni, Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu towreru chikale hiyrunu Carneiro Whene tshinkaluru chikale. Wla htshina chikaletna: “Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu ptowru potuko himukatatshriyi Pkamrure pkamhaleru tsru potkakni hiyrunu himyekaklewatatshrini! Ptowru tshijne hajeneko pohirtshine ppohityi pixa. Pkamrure pnurexnawa, halikakalutni, potukal-potuko!
Kathe hi pikanyi pixa, Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu? Hiyrun-koxa kathe hi himalwutanyi poyaknu tshinanu? Klu tshinanu pixa tsonupka potukalyi. Ptowru tshijne hajene hinanwakatanyi rimalwuxyawakapyina. Klu tshinanu hiphujetkalurutkani pkamrure, potukal-potuko.”
Hoyakalu Tshiji Saletatshri Yokanaxyawaka PiranapniWaneya rali chikaletletna, netlu Hoyakalu hwiywaka tsonu hruko, nikalumtapji hwatshri kotpukka tenhohneya.
Waneya hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrerune tenhohne hajene sete-ne, sete salewaktshi hanikatshine, Hoyakalupji ruchpajyana. Mkatshri katajiru, klatal-potuko, linho kamhikolu hmakatna hiyrunu histatna ruwtoka ouro kamhikolu.
Waneya satu quatro rixinri hiwejikaluru henekna hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrerune tenhohne hajene sete-ne, sete stono Hoyakalu jhekanu yehi, ouro kamhikolu, Hoyakalu honra hike rixiniko mnikawnakatu hiwekatshri.
Waneya Hoyakalupji katseplu kaphalu Hoyakalu hoyaknu tshinanu hiyrunu ruyakle tshinanu. Hiyáhoni hike yineru himukata jihlokletlu Hoyakalupji, hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrerune tenhohne hajene sete-ne, sete salewaktshi tshiji hma msaletkanu pchinikna.
Mitshikananu Tshiji Saletatshri PiranapniWaneya tsru tokantshi hima njema hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrerune tenhohne hajene hiynumsatatshri. Hoyakalupji hichpakhimaxya. Wla htshina: “Xawakni hyanu, tshij-hoho hipkajinri sete stono hwatshri, Hoyakalu jhekanu yehi.”
Waneya wane hya mitshikananu Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru. Rupkaklu histono hwatshri tshij-hoho. Hiyáhoni hanolu kakchiru, katshinolu potuko hapokyehitna wanna yine ptowrunnika kmatsyiru himaxikole himwatshinni hiyrunu kmatsyiru yáholu himalwutatshinni hoho rapoka hanolu.
Tshiji Saletatshri Hepi Rixinri PiranapniWaneya hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru hepi rixinri, hipkaklu histono hwatshri mar powha hoho. Hiyáhoni honha mar powha hwatshri hrahtshi rixnatkawa, hipnatshrini hrahni pixka. Waneya ptowru mar powha hwatshri hiwekatshri hipnanatka.
Tshiji Saletatshri Mapa Rixinri PiranapniWaneya hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru mapa rixinri, hipkaklu kastonolu hwatshri wenkaka hiyrunu ptowru ruchpakhaxyawakaka hoho hiyáhoni hrahtshi rixnatkawa.
Waneya njemtokanutlu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru, honha towutatshri wla htshina: “Potukalyi pixa Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu, xawakni hohne hwatshriyi, mitshikawluru hwatshri hiyrunu hike rixiniko mnikawnakatu hajeryi. Potukalyi xyekaka papnokaxyalu tshiji hwatshinni tshinanu.
Klu tshinanu pnurrene palixjene hiyrunu ptokanu hinkakletatshine hkochpakahrahatatkana. Hiyáhoni hrahtshi putna. Rapnutkana halikaka.”
Waneya satu tokantshi njema. Kapajiru henekachalu yoxikaluru hitajikowaka hichpaktokanuxya wla tshinatshri: “Ha, Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu, halikak-potuklu hiyrunu potukal-potuko papnokatlekaka papnokaxyana yinni.”
Tshiji Saletatshri Quatro Rixinri PiranapniWaneya hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru quatro rixinri, hipkaklu histono hwatshri tkatshi hoho. Hiyáhoni tkatshi himukatlu renekka hjimyawakapna yine tshitshmeroyma.
Ralhakakanna yine tsru hameruyma. Waneya yine hektutu htshinanwakatluna Hoyakalu xye salewaktshikaka towutatshri. Seyni hi rehchinikanutna yinepni, hi rimalwutluna Hoyakalu royaknu tshinanu.
Tshiji Saletatshri Cinco Rixinri PiranapniWaneya hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru cinco rixinri, hipkaklu histono hwatshri kmatsyiru pohirtshi tuplawakle hoho. Hiyáhoni hpohirewnale mapchahapa, psol-tshijne potuko. Waneya yinni hachkanrutanu tsru tshino retanruna tshinanu.
Hiyrun-koxa tsru tshino hjemanruna tshinanu hiyrunu rutsrerna tshinanu hektuwaka htshinanwakatluna Hoyakalu, tenhohne hajeru. Wanepnawaka hi rehchinikanutna hkamrurna hektutu tshinanna.
Tshiji Saletatshri Seis Rixinri PiranapniWaneya hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru seis rixinri, hipkaklu histono hwatshri tsru wenu Eufrates tshinikowak-hoho. Hiyáhoni wenha hipriha ruhlepokhapoxyawakaplu pohirune tkatshi hichpajyawaka sreta hatnu hapotepa.
Hiyrun-koxa mapa hiwejikalune kananurune neta, tlolo pixka rixmanetna. Satu dragão nama hichpajya, satu kmatsyiru nama hichpajya hiyrunu hoyakalu minje tokanu hinkakletatshri nama ruchpajya satu.
Nyi hiwejikalune, kamtshinni wanna. Himyekaklewatatshrikaka kamhatshine wanna. Xye tshijne pohirene nwaka hiyrunu xye tshijne hajene ptowruneka nwaka yatshinni, rapatjekajyawakapna yinepni hiylakkaklu nwaka, Hoyakalu Ptowru Himukatatshri, tsru kahwakpirlu hohne tshinanu.
Hjemanu! Halikaka katshowhuru hinre, munkakletu pixka nixa hinretanu hita. Hiyáhoni kihlehchinikanurupni yineru, wale hohne kahwakatshri, himkalu hihlepokotatshri. Mamkatu phujewaka myapyawakanupa, hma patewaxyawakanupa.
Hiyáhoni rapatjekakanunna wanna yinepni Armagedom tshinikowaka hebreu tokanuya.
Tshiji Saletatshri Sete Rixinri PiranapniWaneya hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru sete rixinri, hipkaklu histono hwatshri malehohnewaka yehi. Waneya tokantshi tsru himalu potuko Hoyakalupji, tenhohne hwatshripji, pohirtshi tuplawakle yehi, hichpaktokanuxyatka, wla tshinatshri: “Ralixatka.”
Waneya rawatka rawrakle, tokantshi himkaka, rutlohle hiyrunu tshiji hiyoliklu tsrur-potuko. Xye tshij-hoho rawka pchinikna yine xye hi rawapa hiyolik-tshijru wane psolutu.
Tshiji hiyolikle tshinanu wale tsru poktshi mapa hkaniprexnanwa. Hiyrun-koxa ptowru tshijne poktshikaka nikatkatka. Tsru poktshi Babilônia tshinikowaka hi hamtakkatka Hoyakalu hetanuya hiyáhoni katsh-halu copa stono hwatshri pixkalutu, Hoyakalu jhekanu tsru potuko, rutahatanna Babilônia poktshi hajenepni.
Hiyrun-koxa ptowru mar powha hwatshijitatshri nikawnatka hiyrunu ptowru teno mrijiwaka ramhachatatka.
Kapoklewaklero Tshinkaluro PiranapniSatu wanna sete hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrerune tenhohne hajene, sete stono salewaktshi yehi hanikatshine, hiynumsatno waneya wla htshinno: “Punanu. Nekhitanyi hanu tixa hapnokatletka tsru pohitkaluro kapoklewaklero, wala honira tsru poktshi hixo honhastsi hwatshroni.
Walayma rapoklewatna xye tshijne pohirene. Ptowru tshijne hajeru himetatka tapoklewle pohwaka tshinanu.”
Waneya niwejinri ranijyatkano kahnete poktshiri yehi. Waneya wane nexyalo sato suxo kmatsyiru serolu hoho tuplatatshro. Hixo hiwaktshi, Hoyakalu heyikleru wale hoho yonatka. Sete jiwurutu hiyrunu dez hwalutu.
Suxo kapoklewaklero netanro, mkatshri ksaji seronuru hiyrunu serolu potuko tmakata. Ouro hiyrun-koxa sotlujikaka kwenur-potu hiyrunu tuwutu, pérola tshinkaluru-ji tumuhlewata. Tomyo tkachikanaxyalu satu copa stono katseplu chinikantshi kananuru pirana, tmayxajinri tapoklewle pirana.
Tojrota raw-yonhata wla tshinatshri: Yohimakanatkaluru Pirana, Tsru Poktshi Babilônia Tshinikowaka Pirana, Kapoklewaklerone Hinro Hiyrunu Xye Tshijne Mayxaklukaka Hasrukatshro.
Waneya netlo suxo kapoklewaklero himetatshro, Hoyakalu nurrene ralixjene hraha pohwaka tshinanu hiyrunu Jesus homkahlu tshinanu hiylatkalunni hraha pohwaka tshinanu. Hiyáhoni nexinixkalo nimyekpotutatka, hi nimat-hichinikanuwatatka.
Waneya hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru wan-tshinno: “Klu tshinanhe pimyekatka? Xawakni nunkakanyi suxo pirana mimatakanatkotu pirana. Hiyrun-koxa nunkakanyi kmatsyiru, sete jiwurutu hiyrunu dez hwalutu, tutjitjeru pirana.
Kmatsyiru petanru hiwekakanata seyni xawakni hi riweka. Teno pnawaka hamhikowak-yehi hkanijinipa waneya ruylatko. Hiyáhoni yonawahlo steno hiwekkakalune hiwakkaka yonaxikowaka myonhiwakatkone, xye tshijne hwatshine pejnu himyekanu rexinipluna kmatsyiru. Klu tshinanu riwekakanata, xawakni hi riweka seyni ruphujewnapa.
Himatkalnutshi raluka xyekaka rimatjemyawakapa yineru: Sete jiwtshikaka, sete mriji suxo kapoklewaklero tuplaxyawaka piranni. Hiyrunu sete pohirtshine hyapkakleta.
Cinco wanna pohirtshine nikawnatka. Seyni satupka phurutka satu hi hakanhawa. Hiyrun-koxa rakanhinipa pchini tsonu rawanu.
Hiyrun-koxa kmatsyiru hiwekakanatatshri seyni xawakni hi riwekanatka pirana, pohiru oito rixinripa. Pohirune sete hkosekjeneymalutni wale. Seyni hamhikowaka hyanuna.
Dez hwakaka petanru, dez pohirtshinni wanna. Hi hpohirewnana wanna nyi dez pohirtshine seyni towuwlu hyoptotapanna hpohirewaxyawakapna satu hora-pka tsonu kmatsyiruymapa.
Nyi pohirtshine pa hchinikanurunni. Hiyáhoni renekanruna kmatsyiru hpixkonna hiyrunu htowuwlena.
Carneiro Whene tshinkalurumka hkamnitanna seyni rallitanna klu tshinanu wale honukla ptowru tsru hixikatshriwa hitsrukatni wale, Carneiro Whene tshinkaluru. Pohirtshine pohirni wale. Romkahitjene, waleymalunni wanna htomhalenni wanna. Wanna nuretkalune koxa hallitanna. Poyehi halixlerunni wanna.”
Hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru wla htshinno: “Honha petanru kapoklewaklero tuplaxyawaka, yine hixolunkaka, kakoje neruru hiyrunu pa nrukaka yanumaxikatshine hyapkaka.
Dez hwakaka petanru hiyrunu kmatsyiru hahnanutanro kapoklewaklero. Ptowru potuko hkonanrona, mamkato rixkaklona. Tohitu hnikanna hiyrunu tomanni hyoxikanna tshitshmeroyma.
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu henekahchinikanutna, pa hchinikanu rixyawakna Hoyakalu halukanru hkamhiywakna. Hiyáhoni wale tshinanu hpohirewaxyawakna renekanruna kmatsyiru, rali hakanhalexinipa tokantshi Hoyakalu tshinyawaka pejnu.
Suxo kapoklewaklero petanro, tsru poktshi pohitkaluru potuko, ptowru pohirtshine towutatshri tyapkakleta.”
Tsru Poktshi Pohitkaluru Babilônia Tshinikowaka Himtuwnalepa PiranapniWaneya wane wkatanu netlu satu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru, tenhohne hichpajikatshri. Tsru himukatlu himwatshrini hiyrunu royaknu hatatlu tshiji.
Hixko saplewle rixa, wla htshin-sapleta: “Tsru poktshi pohitkaluru Babilônia tshinikowaka yotkakatka! Poyahnu hyotkakatka! Kamtshine hwiywaka rixa, ptowru hiwejikaluru hektutu hwiywaka yohimaxikowaka rixa hiyrunu ptowru kamejiru kananuru, heyikkalurupji rixatka.
Klu tshinanu ptowru tshijne hajeru hirlu katsh-halu, himtuklewatatshri tapoklewle tapiklewaxya tshinanu. Pohirtshine xye tshijne hajene hapoklewata walayma. Hiyrun-koxa maronewatatshine, xye tshijne hajene pohirenni ptowru hixatshri halukkaluru wala yehi hwatshri.”
Waneya satu tokantshi njema tenhohne hichpakhimaxikatshri, wla tshinatshri: “Nonerune wala yehi hasujini. Tektunu hmepirexyawakanupa hiyrunu hma salexikowakanupa walayma.
Klu tshinanu tektunu t-tsepoxnawa haté tenhohne rapkata. Hoyakalu hi hamtaklu hektutu tkamhalerukaka.
Papnutanro tixa hapnokatlewlexyawaka pixka. Tkamhaleru pixa nwaka tkamhinri pso, psatkakyehitanro hepi kata wane pso. Hirapi stono tutakhatanru, hepi kata putakhaxinro.
Kihleru hiweklu texini talixkoxiniklunwa, wane pso salewaktshiko pixkakanro. Klu tshinanu wla ttshinahchinikanuta: Hita pohirewatatshrono, pohirtshi tuplawakle tuplatatshrono. Hi hipnahnurutatshrono hita hiyrunu hikeklu hohne wamontshi netanu.
Hiyáhoni wale tshinanu t-salewnale, hipuktshi, wamontshi hiyrunu natshi hakanhanu pa hohne pchini hohnejiji wale ptowruka tetanu. Hiyrunu tshitshmeroyma tnikaxikolupa psoluyaka. Klu tshinanu himukatatshri potuklu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu tapnokatjeru.
Tsru Poktshi Pohitkaluru Babilônia Tshinikowaka Hamotatshine Wamonnu PiranapniPohirtshine, xye tshijne hajene, hapoklewatatshine, kihle hiweklu hetatshine wala kapoklewakleroymalune, hitshiyahatanro, rikaheknanuwatanrona tyoxijikolupha rexinipna.
Tsalexikolu pikatshine tshinanni howuka hyopkakachatanna. Wla tshinachatatshinepni: “Kwamonuru potuko! Ah, kwamonuru potuko tsru poktshi pohitkaluru Babilônia tshinikowaka, poktshi honukla tsrukakalu potuko! Klu tshinanu satu hora-jiji yaka tsonu papnokatle kachitanatkayi.
Waneya kmaronewaklerune hitshiyahatanro hiyrunu riwamonuwnanrona klu tshinanu hike wane wkatanu hanjitanru rejnunkatna.
Hi nijittshi yapjeruko canela tshinkaluru, hi phamluphaluko, hi phamluhaloko, hi phamlu pahiriko ranjitkana. Hike hanjitanru vinho-ha, hi azeite-ha, hi trigo pahi hixirikkaluruko, hi trigo-jiko, hi pratshineko, hi carneiro-neko, hi cavalo-neko, hi tshiji yapatshrokaka cavalo kosetanroko, hi towrertshichakakako, hi yine hiwejinriko ranjitna yine.
Jichanrewaklerune wla htshinanwakatluna tsru poktshi: “Pet-sotanrekaka, palukanrukak-potuko nikawnatka. Ptowru hixatshri kihleru pohirewnalu hiyrunu ptowru hixatshri kihlekakalu pimwakanatanru pamhinina. Hikeklu hohne rukchikko.”
Waneya hichanrewlu kyinuwakleyalune, tsru poktshini tshinanu pohirewnatshine, howuka hyopkakna, tsru poktshi hapnokaxikolu hamlenu tshinanu. Ritshiyahatanruna, riwamonuwatanruna. Wla htshinna:
“Ah, kwamonuru! Kwamonur-potuko tsru poktshi klu tshinanu mitshikananu mkatshri kihleru psalo saxpaleru, mkatshrimta serolu, mkatshrimta carneiro pixi kamhikolu-mta serolu, ouro, sotlukaka kwenuru hiyrunu pérola-ji mkatshri hihlexikaluru hmakatjekanatna mitshi! Seyni satu hora-pka tshinanu tsonu, ptowru ppohirewnale tsru potuko pamhinina!”
Hiyrun-koxa ptowru tsro kanawa kosekatshri, tsro kanawa yapatshine koxa, hiyrunu tsro kanawkaka kamrurewaxikatshine hiyrunu pimrine mar powha kamrurewaxikatshine ptowruneka howuka hyopkakna.
Waneya tsru poktshi yoxijikolupha rexinixkana, hsaplewpotutna. Wla htshin-sapletna: “Hi rawa xye pixkalutu tsru poktshi!”
Waneya tshiji pahi hpolojiwuxnawana. Hsaplewatna. Htshiyahatna. Wla htshinna: “Hi pa wamonnukananru! Hi pa wamonnukananru tsru poktshi pirana! Klu tshinanu wale poktshi pohirewnale tshinanu ptowru kkanawateru, mar powha hwatshri mitshikananu hpohirewnatka. Seyni satu hora-pka tshinanu tsonu tnikawnapotutanatka.
Hiyáhoni xawakni himuwatanu tenhohne hwatshinhi, Hoyakalunerune, nuretkalunhi hiyrunu Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshinhi. Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu hapnokatlu wale tsru poktshi, rixjekanaxyawakhi tsru poktshi pixka rixlu.
Hikeklu Hpanawaxiko Babilônia Poktshi PiranapniWaneya satu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru hixkolu homuklu satu tsru sotlu, hinolu potuko. Waneya mar powha ruknokatkalu sotlu. Wla htshina: “Wla pso mixkonuyma ruknokkona tsru poktshi Babilônia tshinikowaka. Hikeklu hohne rukchikkonatka.
Hikeklu harpa hima wane jemikotka, hi pimri tokluru himako jemko, hi tumleji hima jemko, hi kowi hima jemko, pixa Babilôniayi hitokoteya. Ptowru hixatshri kamhakaluru hikeklu rukchikkotka pix-yehiya. Pix-yehi hikeklu hohne hjemikotka kamrurewatatshine sejire.
Hiyrun-koxa hikeklu lamparina wane nikoxinixka. Hnunrowatatshri ho hnuruwatatshro tokanu, hikeklu pix-yehi hjemikotka. Hichanrewatatshine pix-yehi yapjetatshine ptowru tshijne hajene hichanrewatatshine yohnik-himukatatshine rixapna mitshi. Klu tshinanu pkahontshiwle ptowru tshijne hajene hyokwijekanata.
Tsru poktshi Babilônia hapnokatka klu tshinanu wane rawa Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine hraha hiyokkaluru hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu nurrene ralixjene hraha hiyokkaluru. Halikaka ptowru yinerni hraha xye tshijne hajeru hiylatkaluru Babilônia poktshi hwahrahata.
Himuwlu Tsru Potuko Tenhohne PiranapniWaneya wane wkatanu tsru himalu, hixolune tokanuhetko njema. Wla tshinatshine: “Himalwutkalurni Hoyakalu! Hiwekkakalurni Hoyakalu! Wuphujetanru Hoyakalu royaknu tshinanu hiyrunu rumukatle tshinanu!
Klu tshinanu Hoyakalu halikakni, potuka hchinikanru rapnokatlo hektutu kkamhaklero potuko suxo kapoklewaklero, ptowru tshijne himtukatshro tektunu tshinanu. Hoyakalu hiylatlo klu tshinanu tuylajekanatna Hoyakalu towrerune.”
Waneya hsaplewatatnakna. Wla htshinna: “Himalwutkalurni Hoyakalu! Tsru poktshi yoxikaluru palnaphata hike rixiniko mnikawnakatupa!”
Waneya tsrukakalune vinte e quatro pejnu hiyrun-koxa hiwejikalune quatro, yoptsojityehitlu Hoyakalustsi waneya rimalwutluna Hoyakalu pohirtshi tuplawakle tuplatatshri. Wla htshinna: “Amém! Himalwutkalurni Hoyakalu!”
Waneya pohirtshi tuplawakle ruchpakhimaxya satu tokantshi wla tshinatshri: “Himalwutanru Woyakalute hixa Hoyakalu towrerunhi, ptowru yineru, yine hijhakalune hiyrunu mujhakone, hiyrunu ptowru yineru Hoyakalu kahwakpiratatshine pejnu.”
Waneya satu tsru himalu njema, hixolune tokanu nikahwaklu, hatatjewa tsru hokanu njema ho tsru rutlohle hima pixkalutu njema wla tshinatshri: “Himalwutkalurni Hoyakalu! Klu tshinanu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu ptowru himukatatshri towuwata!
Wumuwatanu! Wpoyikowatanu! Wpohiwkakanru Hoyakalu! Klu tshinanu rapokpapkoluta Carneiro Whene tshinkaluru hnunrowaxyawakapa. Suxo hanunrotleropa hihlepokotkatka hnunrowlu tshinanupa.
Mkatshri tenekka tmakaxyawakaplu, linho-mta, kihler-potuko, psalo saxpalemtalu, katajir-potuko.” Xye linho-mta hyapkaklu Hoyakalu nurrene ralixjene kamrure, kihleru, potukalu.
Waneya Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru wla htshinno: “Xye pyonatanu: ‘Tshanixkalune Carneiro Whene tshinkaluru hnunrowle nikle hapokatshinepa, halikaka poyikowatatshinepa.” Hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru wla htshinno: “Xyekni Hoyakalu tokanu halikak-potuko.”
Waneya Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajerumka nyoptsojityehita nimalwuxyawakaplu seyni wale wan-tshinno: “Hike, hi wane pixanu! Hit-honra pixje kamrurewatatshrino, Hoyakalu towreru, pmoletanune Cristo tshinanu, Jesus hiphujetatshineymalutno. Hiyáhoni Hoyakalu himalwutanu halikaka!” Klu tshinanu halikaka pirana Jesus hiphujetleru pirana, Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshine mixkotjeru.
Cristo Hallitanna Hkamnitjene PiranapniWaneya netlu tenhohne kotpukkaluru. Hetanu! Satu cavalo klatalu hakanhatka. Cavalo tji yapatshri hiwakni Ptowutkolu Halikakalutu. Potuka hchinikanurni, retamayxaklerewatawa yahotkaklu hkamhiywakapa.
Hiyhale tshitshime pixka rixa hatawnaleta. Hiyrun-koxa híxolu pohirtshi sahyekaka hsahyeta. Khiwaklu yonatkaluruya. Hike himatlu wale hiwaka seyni wale tsonupka himatlu.
Mkatshri hmakatleru, hrahtshi hyonrikka. Hhiwaka, Hoyakalu Tokanu tshinkaluru.
Hiyrunu soldado-ne tenhohne hajene homkahjetlu. Cavalo-ne klatalune hyapna. Mkatshri linho-mta tseyo saxpaleru, klat-powranuru hmakatna.
Wale nama yohlolewapi hakotatshri potuko honoxya. Yohlolewapiyma ruylakna yine, ptowru tshijne hajeneka. Htowutanna hipokananu, yomuwaje pa chikonurutu pixkalutuyma htowutna. Hkatsretanunna yinepni, uva katsrekjexikowaka-paji hwatshine pixka rixanna yinepni rimathexyawakapluna yine Hoyakalu ptowru potuko himukatatshri, hahnanuwle.
Hiyrun-koxa himkalu hiyrunu hitpali raw-yonhata. Wla htshin-yonhata: Pohirtshine Pohire hiyrunu tsru hixikatshinwa Hitsrukatni.
Waneya netlu satu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru tkatshi hoho yopkakatshri. Waneya tsru tokanuyma wla htshinatkana ptowru kamejirune teno yapatshine: “Hinanu. Hapatjetanu tsru niklu yehi Hoyakalu hitakanru.
Waneya wane wkatanu netlu kmatsyiru, pohirtshine xye tshijne hajene hiyrunu wanna soldado-tene hixolune yahoxyawakaplu cavalo yapatshri hiyrunu wale soldado-tene.
Seyni kmatsyiru kachitkatka hiyrunu Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri minjeni, wale honukla himyekaklewatatshrikaka kmatsyiru hetanu kamhajekanatatshri. Wale kachitkatka kmatsyiruyma. Himyekaklewatatshrikaka hkamhaleru tshinanu hyokwijekanatna yine kmatsyiru himaxikle himwatshine, wanna kmatsyiru yáholu kahwakpiratatshine. Hiyáhoni tshitshmero powha yehi, enxofre katshowuphalu yehi ruknokkatkana nyi hepi, hiwekatshineko.
Waneya pimrinepni ruylatkonna yohlolewapi, cavalo yapatshri nama honoxikatshriyma. Waneyakni ptowru kamejiru hinanuwata wannani hitu tshinanu.
Tsru Kamtshi Satanás Hostuxikolu Mil Mhale Pejnu PiranapniWaneya netlu satu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru tenhohne hichpajyawaka. Chave teno pnawaka hichyapi himyo ranijya. Hiyrunu tsru yomuwatsa, tsrukakalu himyo ranijya.
Waneya hkachpotutlu dragão, wale honra himnu hitsruka, Tsru Kamtshini wale, Satanás tshinkalurni. Rostutlu. Mil mhale pejnu hostutkalurni wale.
Waneya hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru teno pnawaka ruknokatkalu Tsru Kamtshi. Waneya wane ruchyayehitlu, roho ripixyalu hma yokwijexyawakanupna yine ptowru tshijne hajene, mil mhale pejnu tsonu. Waneya wane pnutepa rumukata hicholetka pchini tsonu.
Hiyrun-koxa pohirtshi tuplawaklekaka neta. Wane tuplatatshine koxa neta. Towuwlu henekkalune retmayxaklerewaxyawakapna. Hiyrun-koxa yinni hiwejinri neta, kastaknojitkalunni Jesus hiphujexikolu pirana tshinanu hiyrunu Hoyakalu tokanu hinkaklexikolu tshinanu. Nyikaka kmatsyiru hiyrunu kmatsyiru yáhole mkahwakpiratkanni hiyrun-koxa kmatsyiru himaxikole jrottshi hitakkaluru ho myotshi hitakkaluru malukanni wanna. Hiyáhoni nyi yinni Cristo-yma riwekanna hiyrunu hpohirewatanna mil mhale pejnu.
Xyekni mitshikananu hipuktshi hichpajikatshri tshinkaluru. Seyni pimrinni hipnatshinni hi riwekanna haté mil mhale pejnu nikawninipa.
Kihle hchinikanurunepni hiyrunu Hoyakalununepni wanna mitshikananu hiweklutnaka kayatatshinepa. Klu tshinanu hipuktshi, hepi rixinri hi hkachitanna wanna. Sacerdote-nepni Hoyakalu tshinanu hiyrunu Cristo tshinanu. Hiyrun-koxa Cristo-yma hpohirewatanna mil mhale pejnu.
Tsru Kamtshi Satanás Hapnokaxikolu PiranapniMil mhale hiknohinipa waneya Satanás tshinkaluru hkachixikowaka yehi ruchoxikotka.
Waneya ruchpakanu ptowru nerkaka, xye tshiji ptowru sreta hwatshine hyokwijexyawakapa, waleni Gogue hiyrunu Magogue tshinikowaka. Yine ksatuji, mar powha wnaha hwatshri pejnu rapatjexinna hiylakaklu tshinanupa.
Tshij-hoho psoluka hyapanna waneya poktshi, Hoyakalu nurrene ralixjene yehi, halukkaluru poktshi hsajrukanna. Waneya tshitshmero tenhohne, Hoyakalu hwiywaka hichpajini, hyoxikanunna wanna yinepni.
Waneya Tsru Kamtshi hyokwijetjerna tshitshmero powha, enxofre yehi hitokote, ruknokkatka, kmatsyiru hiyrunu hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshri minje hwiywaka potuko. Wane hsaletpotuxikona hohohne, hoyetshno hike rixiniko mnikawnakatupa.
Hapnokatlu Hinatshripa Hapkatatatshri Potuko PiranapniWaneya netlu satu pohirtshi tuplawakle tsru potuko. Klatlu. Hoyakalu wane tuplatatshri koxa neta. Tshiji hiyrunu tenhohne wale hetanu rasujyatka. Hiyáhoni tshiji hiyrunu malehohnewaka hi rukchijika hanukta hya. Hike hetatnaklu.
Waneya hipnatshine neta. Wanna hipnatshine hijhakalune hiyrunu mujhakonpotu Hoyakalu hoji sreta hyopkakna. Waneya yonawahlo stenkaka kopralakka. Satutnaka yonawahlo steno kopralakka, hiwejikaluro steno tshinkaluru. Waneya hipnatshine hikolukkatka hkamhalerna pirana tshinanu, papel-mta hwapiranatatshri yonatkaluru tshinanu.
Hipnatshine mar powha hahyekatshine pejnu wane hkochpajikna. Hipuktshi hiyrunu hamhikowaka hwakanatatshine wane hkochpajikna. Satkaka wanna ptowruneka hikolukkatka hkamhalerna pirana tshinanu, papel-mta hwapiranatatshri yonatkaluru tshinanu.
Waneya hipuktshi hiyrunu hamhikowaka hwakanatatshine tshitshmero powha yehi hiknokkana. Xyekni hipuktshi hepi rixinri pirana.
Ptowru yineru hiwaka pejnu yonawahlo steno hiweklu hinkakletatshri myonhiwakatkotu, tshitshmero powha hiknokkotka.
Malehohnewaka Hiyrunu Tshiji Herotexikolu PiranapniWaneya netlu tshiji herotu hiyrun-koxa malehohnewaka herotu. Klu tshinanu mitshikawluru malehohnewaka hiyrunu mitshikawluru tshiji nikawnatka. Hiyrun-koxa mar powha hi hwatka.
Waneya hita, João-no, hetlu poktshi, Hoyakalu nurreru poktshi, Jerusalém tshinikowaka poktshi herotetkaluru. Hoyakalu yehi, tenhohne hichpajikatshri tshij-hoho hapokatshri. Hihlepokotkaluru hnuruwatatshro pixka hihlepokotkaluro thanurutanrupa tshinanu pixka rixapoktshita.
Waneya tsru tokantshi njema pohirtshi tuplawakle hichpajikatshri hima, wla tshinatshri: “Hjemanu! Hoyakalu hwiywaka yin-yehi rawatka. Wannayma rawanu. Rayinetenepni. Hoyakalu potuko wannaymapa. Wanna Hoyakalutepni.
Hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu cheyiktehatanna ptowruneko. Hikepni hipuktshi, hi wamontshiko, hi tshiyahluko, hi katshinoluko. Wale ptowruka hi hwanu klu tshinanu mitshikawluru hwakanatatshri nikawnanu.”
Waneya Hoyakalu, pohirtshi tuplawakle tuplatatshri wla tshina: “Hjemanu! Ptowru potuko nerotetanu.” Waneya wale wla htshinno: “Pyonatanru xye klu tshinanu xye tokantshi halikakalutu, hakanhatshri pirana potukni.”
Waneya wla htshinatkano: “Xye ptowruka halixatka. Hit-honra mitshikananu hajerno hiyrunu hapkatatatshri potuko hajerno, hyinuwajikol-potukno hiyrunu hmahaxyawak-potuko hajerno. Honunnahatewatatshripa nutahatanu. Honha hiweklu heneklewatatshri hichpakhaxikatshri hajer-ha nenekanru, henekachalur-potuko.
Hallirewatatshri yoptotanru xye hita tshinanuya. Hitapni Royakalutepno. Hiyrun-koxa wale nowhenepni.
Seyni jhamleholune, malixkane, hektutu kamhalu hamotatshine, jiylalewaklerune, kapoklewaklerune, kahontshine, mayawletshicha kahwakpiratatshine, ptowru pejnu kayloklerune wanna ptowruneka kwawaklena tshitshmero yehi, tshitshmero powha nwaka, enxofre yehi. Wane hapokatshinepa hepi rixinri hipuktshipni.
Jerusalém Poktshi Herotu PiranapniWaneya satu wanna, hiwejikalune Hoyakalu towrerune tenhohne hajene sete, salewaktshikaka stono yehi himwatshine, wla tshinno: Puna, nekhitapanyi hnuruwpiratatshro, Carneiro Whene tshinkaluru hnunropa.
Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hanikno. Waneya Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru satu himriji tenolu hitakno. Waneya rekhitno hijhakaluru poktshi tenhohne, Hoyakalu yehi hichpajikatshri wale honukla Hoyakalu poktshite Jerusalém tshinikowaka.
Hoyakalu hoyaknu hatajnuyma ratawna. Sotlu kwenuru jaspe tshinkaluru pixka, katajir-potuko pixka rixa hatawnaleta wale poktshi.
Ptowru sreta cerca-teko rawa mapa jihlojikowaka. Hiyáhoni tkatshi hichpajyawaka sreta cerca-te mapa jihlojikowaka hwa. Tkatshi hichpajyawaka potukle sreta cerca-te mapa jihlojikowaka hwa. Kahnete sreta cerca-te rawa mapa jihlojikowaka. Hiyrun-koxa tkatshi himxijyawaka sreta cerca-te rawa mapa jihlojikowaka.
Poktshi cerca-te, doze sotlu tsrukakalu hoho hwa. Doze Carneiro Whene tshinkaluru nuretanune hiwakkaka, doze sotlu hyonatkatka.
Hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru, niynumsatjeru waneylu satu yahotapije ouro kamhikolu poktshi hyahoxinripa, poktshi hiphaptote hiyrunu poktshi cerca-te hyahoxinripa.
Poktshi quatro tsojrirutu. Rowuknu hiyrunu htsernu pixkakakluni. Hyahotpoktshitlu hyahotaprejeyma, hepi mil duzentos quilômetros psolu. Rowuknu, htsernu hiyrunu htennu pixkakakluni.
Hiyrun-koxa hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru yahotlu poktshi cerca-te. Sessenta e cinco metros pa pixnunru, cerca tsernu yine yahotajexawaklu pixka rixa, Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru.
Poktshi cerca-te sotlute, sotlu kwenuru jaspe tshinkaluru kamhikolu. Tsru poktshi honra ouro hixirikaluru kamhikolu, katajru garrafa pixka.
Poktshi cerca-te hwahoholeru sotlukaka, kwenuru, kihleru ruhlexika. Mitshikananu sotlu cerca hwahoholeru jaspe kamhikolni. Sotlu hepi rixinri cerca hwahoholeru safira kamhikolni. Sotlu mapa rixinri cerca hwahoholeru ágata kamhikolni. Sotlu quatro rixinri cerca hwahoholeru esmeralda kamhikolni.
Sotlu cinco rixinri sardônio kamhikolni. Sotlu seis rixinri sárdio kamhikolni. Sotlu sete rixinri crisólito kamhikolni. Sotlu oito rixinri berilo kamhikolni. Sotlu nove rixinri topázio kamhikolni. Sotlu dez rixinri crisópraso kamhikolni. Sotlu onze rixinri jacinto kamhikolni. Sotlu doze rixinri ametista kamhikolni.
Poktshi cerca-te jihlojikowakkaka hichyaprekaka pérola kamhikolni, doze-na pérola-ne. Satkaka hichyapi satu pérola. Tsru poktshi hapokaka ouro kamhikolu, hixirikaluru potuko, katajru garrafa pixka, wan-rixa.
Hi satukna Hoyakalupji wane nexya. Klu tshinanu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu, ptowru potuko himukatatshri hiyrunu Carneiro Whene tshinkaluru wannakni Hoyakalupjine.
Wale poktshi hi hijhalu tkatshi hiyrun-koxa hi ksuruko rujha klu tshinanu Hoyakalu hoyaknu hatnu nikotlu wane. Carneiro Whene tshinkaluru poktshi katalutekni wale.
Ptowru tshijne hajene wale hatnu yanya. Hiyrun-koxa pohirtshine xye tshijne hajene ranikanruna hpohirewlena.
Poktshi jihlokawaklekaka psol-hohneruka rutpuka. Hiyrun-koxa wane hi rawa hoyetshno.
Ptowru tshijne hajene poktshi nwaka ranikanruna hpohiwlena hiyrun-koxa hpohirewlena.
Hikepni hektuntshi, hi kapatmenuru kamhatshri, hi hayoklewatatshriko wane jihlokanu. Halikaka wale poktshi jihlokatshinepa, Carneiro Whene tshinkaluru yonawahlote steno hiweklu heneklewatatshri tshinkaluru hiwakatkaluru tsonu jihlokanu.
Hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru hekhitno wenu Honha Hiweklu Heneklewatatshri hiwakatletatshri. Xye wenha katajha potuko, garrafa pixka. Hoyakalu hiyrunu Carneiro Whene Tshinkaluru tuplaxyawaka ruchpajyatka wale wenu.
Tsru poktshi hapo hanikajite hiyrunu ptowru sreta wnahaluko rawa hahmuna Hiweklu Heneklewatatshri tshinkaluru. Doze-ru hisahi kakojeru. Ptowru ksurkaka hsahiwjeta. Hisure panerkaka hitskalakatshripni.
Wale poktshi hi rawanu Hoyakalu himtukleru. Wale poktshi rawanu Hoyakalu hiyrunu Carneiro Whene pohirewle tuplawakle. Hiyrun-koxa Hoyakalu towrene himalwutanru.
Hoyakalu hoji potuko retanna hiyrunu hijrotna Hoyakalu hiwaka yonatko.
Wane hi rawanu hoyetshno. Hiyrun-koxa wane hi ralujiko nikotapi, hi tkatshi nikotle ralukanna klu tshinanu Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu nikotyehitanna. Wanna yine pohirewhohnekanatanutka hike rixiniko mnikawnakatupa.
Jesus Hi Hohamokpatka Runinri PiranapniWaneya hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru wla htshinno: “Xyekaka tokantshi halikakalutu piranni hiyrunu rakanhanu halikaka. Tsru Hixikatshriwa Hoyakalu, htokanu hinkakletatshine hihchinikanu hepixatshri, yokanatlu htowreru hiwejikaluru tenhohne hajeru rekhixyawakapna htowrene xyekaka pirana chinpotukawa hakanhatshripa pirana.”
Wla htshina Jesus: “Hyijnakotanu! Pchini tsonu nunanu! Kihle hchinikanurni hinatshripa pirana, xye steno yonatkaluru hwatshri homkahitatshri.”
Hijretlu Hiyrunu Hinkaklukaka Hapkatatatshri PotukotkaHita, João-no xye ptowruka njema hiyrunu netlu. Waneya nali jemletlu, nali hetletlu xye ptowruka waneya nihmamta tshiji nyoptsojityehitmaklu hiwejikaluru Hoyakalu towreru tenhohne hajeru, xye ptowruka nekhitjeru jixistsi, nimalwuxyawakaplu.
Seyni wale wla htshinno: “Hi wane pixanu, klu tshinanu hita pixje towrertshino hita. Pmoletanru Cristo tshinanu Hoyakalu tokanu hinkakletatshineymalutno hita hiyrunu xye tokantshi xye steno yonaxikaluru homkahitatshine pixkalutno hita. Halikaka Hoyakalu himalwutanu!”
Wla htshinno wane pnutetka: “Hi pyohimatanru tokantshi hinatshripa pirana xye steno hwatshri klu tshinanu hi howukchiniplu rakanhiywakapa xyekaka pirana.
Hektutu kamhatshri, rixannu hektuntshi hkamhalepni. Hektu hchinikanuru, rixannu hektunu hchinikanupni. Kihleru kamhatshri rixannu kihleru kamhalepni. Hoyakalunu rixannu Hoyakalunu hixleta.”
Jesus wla tshina: “Hetanu. Pchini tsonu nunanu. Numluklewle hitaymaplu. Satkaka rumlujikolu hyoptotanu hkamrure pixka rixko satkaka.
Hitni mitshikananu hwatshrino hiyrunu hmahle potuko hwatshrino. Yinuwakatshrino hiyrunu hmahaxyawak-potuko hwatshrino, mitshikananu hwatshrino hiyrunu hmahle hwatshrino.
Kihle hchinikanurunni himkalna hopowalu herojikalune rumukata nikletluna hahmuna hiweklu heneklewatatshri sahi hiyrunu poktshi jihlojikowaka rumukata yapletanna.
Hita, Jesus-no yokanatlu ntowreru hiwejikaluru tenhohne hajeru ruphujexyawakaplu xyekaka pirana hixa Cristo tshinanu hapatjetatshinkakhi tshinanu. Hitni pohiru Davi-ni klopichno. Hitni hohisahi hatawnatshrino.
Hoyakalu Hiwejikaluru hiyrunu hnuruwatatshropa wla htshinna: “Puna!” Hiyrun-koxa xye pirana jematshri wla tshina: “Puna!” Honunnahatewatatshri hinanu. Hiyrunu katuktako haluka yoptoletanru honha hiweklu heneklewatatshri henekachal-ha.
Ralipre HinkaklewluHita João-no hinkaklewata, xako hanuktako yineru xyekaka tokantshi xye steno hwatshri hinatshripa pirana yijnakotatshri, Katukta pa pirana hajrijinri xyekaka tokantshi waneya Hoyakalu salewaktshi rajrijinri wale yineru xye steno hwatshri pirana tshinanu.
Hiyrun-koxa satu yineru ho katuktako pa pirana ruchyaxinipa, hinatshripa pirana xye steno hwatshri, Hoyakalu konanru walenumkapa hahmuna hiweklu heneklewatatshri, hiyrun-koxa walenumkapa hwikowaka Hoyakalu poktshite hwatshri, xye steno hwapiranatatshri yehi.
Xyekaka pirana ptowruka hiphujetatshri wla tshina: “Halikaka chinpotukawa nunanu!” Amém. Punanu, Tsru Hixikatshriwa Jesus!
Nanjitlu Wutsrukate Jesus henekachale hihlenu hixa ptowrunekhi tshinanupa.
